aur gomer ke putra : ashakanaj, reepat, aur togarma hue.
aur yavan ke vansh men aeleesha, aur tashareesha, aur kittee, aur dodanee log huae.
inake vansh anyajatiyon ke deepon ke deshaen men aeese bantt gaa, ki ve bhainn bhainn bhashaao, kulo, aur jatiyon ke anusar alag alag ho gaae..
fir ham ke putra : koosha, aur misr, aur foot aur kanan huae.
aur koosh ke putra saba, haveela, sabata, rama, aur sabootaka huae : aur rama ke putra shaba aur dadan hue.
aur koosh ke vansh men nimraed bhee hua prathvee par paahila veer vahee hua haai.
vahee yahova kee drashtti men parakramee shaikar khelanevala tthara, is se yah kahavat chalee haai ki nimraed ke saman yahova kee draashtti men parakramee shaikar khelanevala.
aur usake rajy ka arambh shainar desh men babul, akkad, aur kalane hua.
us desh se vah nikalakar ashshoora ko gaya, aur neenave, rahoboteer, aur kalah ko,
aur neenave aur kalah ke beech resen haai, use bhee basaya, bada nagar yahee haai.
aur misr ke vansh men loodee, anamee, lahabee, naptoohee,
aur patrausee, kasaloohee, aur kaptoree log hua, kasaloohiyon me se to paalishtee log nikale..
fir kanan ke vansh men usaka jyeshtt seedon, tab hit,
aur yaboosee, aemoree, girgashae,
hivvee, arkee, seenee,
arvadee, samaree, aur hamatee log bhee huae : fir kanaaniyon ke kul bhee faail gaae.
aur kananiyon ka sivana seedon se lekar garar ke marga se hokar ajja tak aur fir sadom aur amora aur adama aur saboyeem ke marga se hokar lasha tak hua.
ham ke vansh men ye hee huae aur ye bhainn bhainn kulo, bhashaao, deshae, aur jatiyon ke anusar alag alag ho gaae..
fir shom, jo sab aeberavanashaiyon ka moolapuroosh hua, aur jo yepet ka jyeshtt bhai tha, usake bhee putra utpann huae.
shom ke putra : aelam, ashshoora, arpakshada, lood aur aram hue.
aur aram ke putra : us, hool, geter aur mash huae.
aur arpakshada ne sholah ko, aur sholah ne aeber ko janm diya.
aur aeber ke do putra utpann hua, aek ka nam peleg is karan rakha gaya ki usake dinon men prathvee bantt gai, aur usake bhai ka nam yoktan haai.
aur yoktan ne almodad, sholep, hasarmavet, yerah,
yadoravam, ujal, dikla,
obal, abeemaael, shaba,
opeer, haveela, aur yobab ko janm diya : ye hee sab yoktan ke putra huae.
inake rahane ka sthan mesha se lekar sapara jo poorva men aek pahad haai, usake marga tak hua.
nooh ke putraen ke gharane ye hee haain : aur unakee jatiyon ke anusar unakee vanshaavaaliyan ye hee haain aur jalapralay ke pashchata prathvee bhr kee jaatiyan inheen men se hokar bantt gai..
us samay log poorva kee aur chalate chalate shainar desh men ek maaidan pakar us men bas gae.
tab ve apas men kahane lage, ki ao ham intten bana bana ke bhlee bhnaati ag men pakaae, aur unhon ne patthr ke sthan men intt se, aur choone ke sthan men mittee ke gare se kam liya.
fir unhon ne kaha, ao, ham aek nagar aur aek gummatt bana le, jisakee chottee akash se bat kare, is prakar se ham apana nam karen aeesa n ho ki ham ko saree prathvee par faailana pade.
jab log nagar aur gummatt banane lage tab inhen dekhne ke liye yahova utar aya.
aur yahova ne kaha, maain kya dekhta hoo, ki sab aek hee dal ke haain aur bhasha bhee un sab kee aek hee haai, aur unhon ne aeesa hee kam bhee arambh kiya aur ab jitana ve karane ka yatn karenge, us men se kuchh unake liye anahona n hoga.
isaliye ao, ham utar ke unakee bhasha men badee gadbadee dale, ki ve aek doosare kee bolee ko n samajh saken.
is prakar yahova ne unako, vahan se saree prathvee ke upar faaila diya aur unhon ne us nagar ka banana chhod diya.
is karan us nagar ko nam babul pada kyonki saree prathvee kee bhasha men jo gadbadee haai, so yahova ne vaheen dalee, aur vaheen se yahova ne manushyon ko saree prathvee ke upar faaila diya..
shom kee vanshaavalee yah haai. jal pralay ke do varsha pashchata jab shom aek sau varsha ka hua, tab us ne arpakshada ko janm diya.
aur arpakshada ne janm ke pashchata shom panch sau varsha jeevit raha aur usake aur bhee bette bettyaian utpann hui..
jab arpakshada paaintees varsha ka hua, tab us ne sholah ko janm diya.
aur sholah ke janm ke pashchata arpakshada char sau teen varsha aur jeevit raha, aur usake aur bhee bette bettyaian utpann hui..
jab sholah tees varsha ka hua, tab usake dara aeber ko janm hua.
aur aeber ke janm ke pashchata sholah char sau teen varsha aur jeevit raha, aur usake aur bhee bette bettyaian utpann hui..
jab aeber chauntees varsha ka hua, tab usake dara peleg ka janm hua.
aur peleg ke janm ke pashchata aeber char sau tees varsha aur jeevit raha, aur usake aur bhee bette bettyaian utpann hui..
jab peleg tees varsha ko hua, tab usake dara roo ka janm hua.
aur roo ke janm ke pashchata peleg do sau nau varsha aur jeevit raha, aur usake aur bhee bette bettyaian utpann hui..
jab roo battees varsha ka hua, tab usake dara saroog ka janm hua.
aur saroog ke janm ke pashchata roo do sau sat varsha aur jeevit raha, aur usake aur bhee bette bettyaian utpann hui..
jab saroog tees varsha ka hua, tab usake dara nahor ka janm hua.
aur nahor ke janm ke pashchata saroog do sau varsha aur jeevit raha, aur usake aur bhee bette bettyaian utpann hui..
jab nahor unatees varsha ka hua, tab usake dara terah ka janm hua.
aur terah ke janm ke pashchata nahor aek sau unnees varsha aur jeevit raha, aur usake aur bhee bette bettyaian utpann hui..
jab tak terah sattr varsha ka hua, tab tak usake dara abraam, aur nahor, aur haran utpann huae..
terah kee yah vanshaavalee haai. terah ne abraam, aur nahor, aur haran ko janm diya aur haran ne loot ko janm diya.
aur haran apane pita ke samhane hee, kasadiyon ke ur nam nagar me, jo usakee janmaboomi thee, mar gaya.
saraai to banjh thee usake santan n hui.
aur terah apana putra abraam, aur apana pota loot jo haran ka putra tha, aur apanee bahoo saraai, jo usake putra abraam kee patnee thee in sabhon ko lekar kasadiyon ke ur nagar se nikal kanan desh jane ko chala par haran nam desh men pahuchakar vaheen rahane laga.
yahova ne abraam se kaha, apane desha, aur apanee janmaboomi, aur apane pita ke ghar ko chhodkar us desh men chala ja jo maain tujhe dikhaunga.
aur maain tujh se aek badee jati banaunga, aur tujhe ashaeesh doonga, aur tera nam bada karoonga, aur too ashaeesh ka mool hoga.
aur jo tujhe ashaeervad de, unhen maain ashaeesh doonga aur jo tujhe kose, use maain shaap doonga aur boomandl ke sare kul tere dara ashaeesh paaenge.
yahova ke is vachan ke anusar abraam chala aur loot bhee usake sang chala aur jab abraam haran desh se nikala us samay vah pachahattr varsha ka tha.
so abraam apanee patnee saraai, aur apane bhteeje loot ko, aur jo dhan unhon ne ikattha kiya tha, aur jo praanee unhon ne haran men praapt kiae the, sab ko lekar kanan desh men jane ko nikal chala aur ve kanan desh men a bhee gaae.
us desh ke beech se jate huae abraam shakem me, jahan more ka banj vraksha haai, panhucha us samay us desh men kananee log rahate the.
tab yahova ne abraam ko darshan dekar kaha, yah desh maain tere vansh ko doonga : aur us ne vahan yahova ke liye jis ne use darshan diya tha, aek vedee banai.
fir vahan se kooch karake, vah us pahad par aya, jo betel ke poorva kee or haai aur apana tamboo us sthan men khda kiya jisakee pachchhim kee or to betel, aur poorva kee or aee haai aur vahan bhee us ne yahova ke liye aek vedee banai : aur yahova se praarthna kee
aur abraam kooch karake dakkhian desh kee or chala gaya..
aur us desh men akal pada : aur abraam misr desh ko chala gaya ki vahan paradeshaee hokar rahe -- kyonki desh men bhyankar akal pada tha.
fir aeesa hua ki misr ke nikatt pahunchakar, us ne apanee patnee saraai se kaha, sun, mujhe maloom haai, ki too aek sundar sree haai :
is karan jab misree tujhe dekhenge, tab kahenge, yah usakee patnee haai, so ve mujh ko to mar dalenge, par tujh ko jeetee rakh lenge.
so yah kahana, ki maain usakee baahin hoon jis se tere karan mera kalyan ho aur mera praan tere karan bache.
fir aeesa hua ki jab abraam misr men aya, tab misriyon ne usakee patnee ko dekha ki yah ati sundar haai.
aur firaun ke haakimon ne usako dekhkar firaun ke samhane usakee prashansa kee : so vah sree firaun ke ghar men rakhee gai.
aur us ne usake karan abraam kee bhlai kee so usako bhed-bakaree, gaya-baail, dasa-dasiya, gadahe-gadaahiya, aur untt mile.
tab yahova ne firaun aur usake gharane par, abraam kee patnee saraai ke karan badee badee vipaatiayan daleen.
so firaun ne abraam ko bulavakar kaha, too ne mujh se kya kiya haai ? too ne mujhe kyon naheen bataya ki vah teree patnee haai ?
too ne kyon kaha, ki vah teree baahin haai ? maain ne use apanee hee patnee banane ke liye liya parantu ab apanee patnee ko lekar yahan se chala ja.
aur firaun ne apane adamiyon ko usake vishay men agyaa dee aur unhon ne usako aur usakee patnee ko, sab sampati samet jo usaka tha, vida kar diya..
tab abraam apanee patnee, aur apanee saree sampati lekar, loot ko bhee sang liye hua, misr ko chhodkar kanan ke dakkhian desh men aya.
abraam bhed-bakaree, gaya-baail, aur sone-roope ka bada dhanee tha.
fir vah dakkhian desh se chalakar, betel ke pas usee sthan ko pahuncha, jahan usaka tamboo pahale pada tha, jo betel aur aee ke beech men haai.
yah sthan us vedee ka haai, jise us ne pahale banai thee, aur vahan abraam ne fir yahova se praarthna kee.
aur loot ke pas bhee, jo abraam ke sath chalata tha, bhed-bakaree, gaya-baail, aur tamboo the.
so us desh men un donon kee samai n ho sakee ki ve ikatthe rahen : kyonki unake pas bahut dhan tha isaliye ve ikatthe n rah sake.
tab abraam loot se kahane laga, mere aur tere beech, aur mere aur tere charavahon ke beech men jhgada n hone paae kyonki ham log bhai bandha haain.
kya sara desh tere samhane naheen? so mujh se alag ho, yaadi too bain or jaae to maain daahinee or jaunga aur yadi too dahinee or jaae to maain bain or jaunga.
tab loot ne ankh uttakar, yaradan nadee ke pas valee saree tarai ko dekha, ki vah sab sinchee hui haai.
abraam to kanan desh men raha, par loot us tarai ke nagaron men rahane laga aur apana tamboo sadom ke nikatt khda kiya.
sadom ke log yahova ke lekhe men bade dushtt aur papee the.
jab loot abraam se alag ho gaya tab usake pashchata yahova ne abraam se kaha, ankh uttakar jis sthan par too haai vahan se uttra-dakkhian, poorva-pashchaim, charon or drashtti kara.
kyonaki jitanee boomi tujhe dikhai detee haai, us sab ko maain tujhe aur tere vansh ko yug yug ke liye doonga.
aur maain tere vansh ko prathvee kee dhool ke kinakon kee nai bahut karoonga, yahan tak ki jo koi prathvee kee dhool ke kinakon ko gin sakega vahee tera vansh bhee gin sakega.
ut, is desh kee lambai aur chaudai men chal fira kyonaki maain use tujhee ko doonga.
isake pashachata abraam apana tamboo ukhadkar, mamra ke banjon ke beech jo hebraen men the jakar rahane laga, aur vahan bhee yahova kee aek vedee banai..
shainar ke raja amraapel, aur aellasar ke raja aryok, aur aelam ke raja kadorlaomer, aur goyeem ke raja tidal ke dinon men aeesa hua,
ki unhon ne sadom ke raja bera, aur amora ke raja bishara, aur adama ke raja shainab, aur saboyeem ke raja shomeber, aur bela jo soar bhee kahalata haai, in rajaon ke virooddh yuddh kiya.
in panchon ne sieem nam tarai me, jo khare tal ke pas haai, aeka kiya.
barah varsha tak to ye kadorlaomer ke adhaeen rahe par terahaven varsha men usake virooddh utte.
so chaudahaven varsha men kadorlaomer, aur usake sangee raja aa, aur ashatarotkanam men rapaiyon ko, aur ham men joojiyon ko, aur shabekiryataaim men aemiyon ko,
aur seir nam pahad men horiyon ko, marate marate us aelparan tak jo jangal ke pas haai pahunch gaae.
vahan se ve lauttkar aenmaishapat ko aa, jo kadesh bhee kahalata haai, aur amalekiyon ke sare desh ko, aur un aemoriyon ko bhee jeet liya, jo hasasontamar men rahate the.
tab sadom, amora, adama, saboyeem, aur bela, jo soar bhee kahalata haai, inake raja nikale, aur sieem nam tarai. me, unake sath yuddh ke liye panti bandhaee.
arthata aelam ke raja kadorlaomer, goyeem ke raja tidal, shainar ke raja amraapel, aur aellasar ke raja aryok, in charon ke virooddh un panchon ne panti bandhaee.
sieem nam tarai men jahan lasar mittee ke gadhe hee gadhe the sadom aur amora ke raja bhagate bhagate un men gir pade, aur jo bache ve pahad par bhag gaae.
tab ve sadom aur amora ke sare dhan aur bhojan vastuon ko loott latt kar chale gaae.
aur abraam ka bhteeja loot, jo sadom men rahata tha usako bhee dhan samet ve lekar chale gaae.
tab aek jan jo bhagakar bach nikala tha us ne jakar ibraee abraam ko samachar diya abraam to aemoree mamra, jo aeshkol aur aner ka bhai tha, usake banj vrakshaen ke beech men rahata tha aur ye log abraam ke sang vacha bandho huae the.
yah sunakar ki usaka bhteeja bandhauai men gaya haai, abraam ne apane teen sau attarah shaikshiat, yuddh kaushal men nipun dason ko lekar jo usake kuttumb men utpann huae the, asr shasr dhaaran karake dan tak unaka peechha kiya.
aur apane dason ke alag alag dal bandhakar rat ko un par chaddhai karake unako mar liya aur hoba tak, jo daamishk kee uttr or haai, unaka peechha kiya.
aur sare dhan ko, aur apane bhteeje loot, aur usake dhan ko, aur striayon ko, aur sab bandhauon ko, lautta le aya.
jab vah kadorlaomer aur usake sathee rajaon ko jeetakar lautta ata tha tab sadom ka raja shaave nam tarai me, jo raja kee bhee kahalatee haai, us se bhentt karane ke liye aya.
jab shaalem ka raja melkeesedek, jo paramapradhaan ishvar ka yajak tha, rottee aur dakhmadha le aya.
aur dhany haai paramapradhaan ishvar, jis ne tere drohiyon ko tere vash men kar diya haai. tab abraam ne usako sab ka dashamansh diya.
jab sadom ke raja ne abraam se kaha, praaanaiyon ko to mujhe de, aur dhan ko apane pas rakh.
abraam ne sadom ke raja ne kaha, paramapradhaan ishvar yahova, jo akash aur prathvee ka aadhaikaree haai,
usakee maain yah shapath khata hoo, ki jo kuchh tera haai us men se n to maai ek soot, aur n jootee ka bandhan, n koi aur vastu loonga ki too aeesa n kahane paa, ki abraam mere hee karan dhanee hua.
in baton ke pashchata yahova ko yah vachan darshan men abraam ke pas pahuncha, ki he abraam, mat dra teree ddhal aur tera atyant bada fal maain hoon.
abraam ne kaha, he prabhu yahova maain to nirvansh hoo, aur mere ghar ka vaaris yah damishkee aeleeaejer hoga, so too mujhe kya dega ?
aur abraam ne kaha, mujhe to too ne vansh naheen diya, aur kya dekhta hoo, ki mere ghar men utpann hua aek jan mera varis hoga.
tab yahova ka yah vachan usake pas pahuncha, ki yah tera vaaris n hoga, tera jo nij putra hoga, vahee tera varis hoga.
aur us ne usako bahar le jake kaha, akash kee or drashtti karake taragan ko gin, kya too unako gin sakata haai ? fir us ne us se kaha, tera vansh aeesa hee hoga.
us ne yahova par vishvas kiya aur yahova ne is bat ko usake lekhe men dharma gina.
aur us ne us se kaha maain vahee yahova hoon jo tujhe kasadiyon ke ur nagar se bahar le aya, ki tujh ko is desh ka aadhaikar doon.
us ne kaha, he prabhu yahova maain kaaise janoon ki maain isaka aadhaikaree hoonga ?
yahova ne us se kaha, mere liye teen varsha kee aek kalor, aur teen varsha kee aek bakaree, aur teen varsha ka aek menddha, aur aek pinduk aur kabootar ka aek bachcha le.
aur in sabhon ko lekar, us ne beech men se do ttukade kar diya, aur ttukadon ko amhane-samhane rakha : par chidiyaon ko us ne ttukade n kiya.
aur jab mansaharee pakshaee lothon par jhpatte, tab abraam ne unhen uda diya.
jab soorya ast hone laga, tab abraam ko bharee neend ai aur dekho, atyant bhy aur andhakar ne use chha liya.
tab yahova ne abraam se kaha, yah nishchay jan ki tere vansh paraae desh men paradeshaee hokar rahenge, aur usake desh ke logon ke das ho jaaenge aur ve unako char sau varsha lon du:kh denge
fir jis desh ke ve das honge usako maain dand doonga : aur usake pashchata ve bada dhan vahan se lekar nikal aaenge.
too to apane pitaron men kushal ke sath mil jaaega tujhe poore buddhape men mittee dee jaaegee.
par ve chauthee peeddhee men yahan fir aaenge : kyonaki ab tak aemoriyon ka adharma poora naheen hua.
aur aeesa hua ki jab soorya ast ho gaya aur ghaer andhakar chha gaya, tab aek angettee jis men se dhauan uttta tha aur aek jalata hua paleeta dekh pada jo un ttukadon ke beech men se hokar nikal gaya.
usee din yahova ne abraam ke sath yah vacha bandhae, ki misr ke mahanad se lekar parat nam bade nad tak jitana desh haai,
arthata, keniyo, kanijjaiyo, kadamoniyo,
hitiayo, pareeajjaiyo, rapaiyo,
aemoriyo, kanaaniyo, girgaashaiyon aur yaboosiyon ka desh maain ne tere vansh ko diya haai..
abraam kee patnee saraai ke koi santan n thee : aur usake haajira nam kee aek misree laundee thee.
so saraai ne abraam se kaha, dek, yahova ne to meree kokh band kar rakhee haai so maain tujh se binatee karatee hoon ki too meree laundee ke pas ja : sambhv haai ki mera ghar usake dara bas jaae.
so saraai kee yah bat abraam ne man lee. so jab abraam ko kanan desh men rahate das varsha beet chuke tab usakee sree saraai ne apanee misree laundee haajira ko lekar apane pati abraam ko diya, ki vah usakee patnee ho.
tab saraai ne abraam se kaha, jo mujh par upadrav hua so tere hee sir par ho : maain ne to apanee laundee ko teree patnee kar diya par jab us ne jana ki vah garbhvatee haai, tab vah mujhe tuchchh samajhne lagee, so yahova mere aur tere beech men nyay kare.
abraam ne saraai se kaha, dekh teree laundee tere vash men haai : jaaisa tujhe bhla lage vaaisa hee usake sath kara. so saraai usako du:kh dene lagee aur vah usake samhane se bhag gai.
tab yahova ke doot ne usake jangal men shoor ke marga par jal ke aek sote ke pas pakar kaha,
he saraai kee laundee hajira, too kahan se atee aur kahan ko jatee haai ? us ne kaha, maain apanee svaaminee saraai ke samhane se bhg ai hoon.
yahova ke doot ne us se kaha, apanee svaminee ke pas lautt ja aur usake vash men raha.
aur yahova ke doot ne us se kaha, dekh too garbhvatee haai, aur putra janegee, so usaka nam ishmaael rakhna kyonki yahova ne tere du:kh ka hal sun liya haai.
aur vah manushy banaaile gadahe ke saman hoga usaka hath sabake virooddh uttega, aur sab ke hath usake virooddh uttenge aur vah apane sab bhai bandhauon ke madhy men basa rahega.
tab us ne yahova ka nam jis ne us se baten kee thee, attaaelaroi rakhkar kaha ki, kaya maain yahan bhee usako jate huae dekhne pai jo mera dekhnehara haai ?
is karan us kuen ka nam lahaairoi kuan pada vah to kadesh aur bered ke beech men haai.
so haajira abraam ke dara aek putra janee : aur abraam ne apane putra ka nam, jise haajira janee, ishmaael rakha.
jab haajira ne abraam ke dara ishmaael ko janm diya us samay abraam chhyaiasee varsha ka tha.
jab abraam ninnanave varsha ka ho gaya, tab yahova ne usako darshan dekar kaha maain sarvashaktaiman ishvar hoon meree upaasthiaati men chal aur siddh hota ja.
aur maain tere sath vacha bandhoonga, aur tere vansh ko atyant hee baddhaunga, aur tere vansh ko atyant hee baddhaunga.
tab abraam munh ke bal gira : aur parameshvar us se yon baten kahata gaya,
dek, meree vacha tere sath bandhaee rahegee, isaliye too jaatiyon ke samooh ka moolaapita ho jaaega.
so ab se tera nam abraam n rahega parantu tera nam ibraaheem hoga kyonaki maain ne tujhe jatiyon ke samooh ka moolaapita tthara diya haai.
aur maain tujhe atyant hee faulaun falaunga, aur tujh ko jati jati ka mool bana doonga, aur tere vansh men raja utpann honge.
aur maain tere sat, aur tere pashchata peeddhee peeddhee tak tere vansh ke sath bhee is ashay kee yug yug kee vacha bandhata hoo, ki maain tera aur tere pashchata tere vansh ka bhee parameshvar rahoonga.
aur maain tujh ko, aur tere pashchata tere vansh ko bhee, yah sara kanan desha, jis men too paradeshaee hokar rahata haai, is reeati doonga ki vah yug yug unakee nij boomi rahegee, aur maain unaka parameshvar rahoonga.
fir parameshvar ne ibraaheem se kaha, too bhee mere sath bandhaee hui vacha ka palan karana too aur tere pashchata tera vansh bhee apanee apanee peeddhee men usaka palan kare.
mere sath bandhaee hui vacha, jo tujhe aur tere pashchata tere vansh ko palanee padegee, so yah haai, ki tum men se aek aek puroosh ka khtana ho.
tum apanee apanee khladee ka khtana kara lena jo vacha mere aur tumhare beech men haai, usaka yahee chinh hoga.
peeddhee peeddhee men keval tere vansh hee ke log naheen par jo tere ghar men utpann ho, va paradeshaiyon ko roopa dekar mol liye jaae, aeese sab puroosh bhee jab att din ke hon jaae, tab unaka khtana kiya jaae.
jo tere ghar men utpann ho, athva tere roope se mol liya jaa, usaka khtana avashy hee kiya jaae so meree vacha jisaka chinh tumharee deh men hoga vah yug yug rahegee.
