aur vah ladka baddha aur usaka doodha chhudaya gaya : aur isahak ke doodha chhudane ke din ibraaheem ne badee jevanar kee.
tab sara ko misree haajira ka putra, jo ibraaheem se utpann hua tha, hansee karata hua dekh pada.
so is karan us ne ibraaheem se kaha, is dasee ko putra sahit barabas nikal de : kyonki is dasee ka putra mere putra isahak ke sath bhagee n hoga.
yah bat ibraaheem ko apane putra ke karan buree lagee.
tab parameshvar ne ibraaheem se kaha, us ladke aur apanee dasee ke karan tujhe bura n lage jo bat sara tujh se kahe, use man, kyonaki jo tera vansh kahalaaega so isahak hee se chalega.
dasee ke putra se bhee maain aek jati utpann karoonga isaaliye ki vah tera vansh haai.
so ibraaheem ne bihan ko tadke uttkar rottee aur panee se bhree chamade kee thailee bhee haajira ko dee, aur usake kandho par rakhee, aur usake ladke ko bhee use dekar usako vida kiya : so vah chalee gai, aur bershoba ke jangal men bhraman karane lagee.
jab thailee ka jal chuk gaya, tab us ne ladke ko aek jhadee ke neeche chhod diya.
aur ap us se teer bhr ke ttppe par door jakar usake samhane yah sochakar baaitt gai, ki mujh ko ladke kee mratyu dekhnee n pade. tab vah usake samhane baaittee hui chilla chilla ke rone lagee.
aur parameshvar ne us ladke kee sunee aur usake doot ne svarga se haajira ko pukar ke kaha, he haajira tujhe kya hua ? mat dra kyonki jahan tera ladka haai vahan se usakee avaj parameshvar ko sun padee haai.
ut, apane ladke ko utta aur apane hath se sambhal kyonki maain usake dara ek badee jati banaunga.
parameshvar ne usakee ankhe khol dee, aur usako aek kuna dikhai pada so us ne jakar thailee ko jal se bhrakar ladke ko pilaya.
aur parameshvar us ladke ke sath raha aur jab vah bada hua, tab jangal men rahate rahate dhanudhararee ban gaya.
un dinon men aeesa hua ki abeemelek apane senapaati peekol ko sang lekar ibraaheem se kahane laga, jo kuchh too karata haai us men parameshvar tere sang rahata haai :
so ab mujh se yahan is vishay men parameshvar kee kiriya kha, ki too n to mujh se chhl karega, aur n kabhee mere vansh se karega, parantu jaaisee karoona maain ne tujh par kee haai, vaaisee hee too mujh par aur is desh par bhee jis men too rahata haai karega
ibraaheem ne kaha, maain kiriya khaunga.
aur ibraaheem ne abeemelek ko aek kuaen ke vishay me, jo abeemelek ke dason ne bareeyai se le liya tha, ulahana diya.
tab abeemelek ne kaha, maai naheen janata ki kis ne yah kam kiya : aur too ne bhee mujhe naheen bataya, aur n maai ne aj se paahile isake vishay men kuchh suna.
tak ibraaheem ne bhed-bakaree, aur gaya-baail lekar abeemelek ko diae aur un donon ne apas men vacha bandhaee.
aur ibraaheem ne bhed kee sat bachchee alag kar rakheen.
tab abeemelek ne ibraaheem se poochha, in sat baachchaiyon ka, jo too ne alag kar rakhee haai, kya prayojan haai ?
us ne kaha, too in sat bachchaiyon ko is bat kee sakshaee janakar mere hath se le, ki maai ne kuna khoda haai.
un donon ne jo us sthan men apas men kiriya khai, isee karan usaka nam bershoba pada.
jab unhon ne beshorba men paraspar vacha bandhae, tab abeemelek, aur usaka senapati peekol uttkar paalishtaiyon ke desh men lautt gaae.
aur ibraaheem palishtaiyon ke desh men bahut dinon tak paradeshaee hokar raha..
in baton ke pashchata aeesa hua ki parameshvar ne, ibraaheem se yah kahakar usakee pareeksha kee, ki he ibraaheem : us ne kaha, dek, maain yahan hoon.
us ne kaha, apane putra ko arthata apane ekalaute putra isahak ko, jis se too praem rakhta haai, sang lekar moriyyah desh men chala ja, aur vahan usako ek pahad ke upar jo maain tujhe bataunga homabali karake chaddha.
so ibraaheem bihan ko tadke utta aur apane gadahe par kattee kasakar apane do sevak, aur apane putra isahak ko sang liya, aur homabaali ke liye lakadee cheer lee tab kooch karake us sthan kee or chala, jisakee charcha parameshvar ne us se kee thee.
teesare din ibraaheem ne ankhen uttakar us sthan ko door se dekha.
aur us ne apane sevakon se kaha gadahe ke pas yaheen tthare raho yah ladka aur maain vahan tak jakar, aur dandvata karake, fir tumhare pas lautt aunga.
so ibraaheem ne homabali kee lakadee le apane putra isahak par ladee, aur ag aur chhuree ko apane hath men liya aur ve donon aek sath chal pade.
isahak ne apane pita ibraaheem se kaha, he mere pita us ne kaha, he mere putra, kya bat haai us ne kaha, dek, ag aur lakadee to haain par homabali ke liye bhed kahan haai ?
ibraaheem ne kaha, he mere putra, parameshvar homabaali kee bhed ka upay ap hee karega.
so ve donon sang sang age chalate gaae. aur ve us sthan ko jise parameshvar ne usako bataya tha pahunche tab ibraaheem ne vahan vedee banakar lakadee ko chun chunakar rakha, aur apane putra isahak ko bandha ke vedee par kee lakadee ke upar rakh diya.
aur ibraaheem ne hath baddhakar chhuree ko le liya ki apane putra ko baali kare.
tab yahova ke doot ne svarga se usako pukar ke kaha, he ibraaheem, he ibraaheema us ne kaha, dek, maain yahan hoon.
us ne kaha, us ladke par hath mat baddha, aur n us se kuchh kar : kyonaki too ne jo mujh se apane putra, varan apane ekalaute putra ko bhee, naheen rakh chhoda is se maai ab jan gaya ki too parameshvar ka bhy manata haai.
tab ibraaheem ne ankhe uttai, aur kya dekha, ki usake peechhe aek meddha apane seengo se aek jhadee men bajha hua haai : so ibraaheem ne jake us menddhe ko liya, aur apane putra kee santee homabali karake chaddhaya.
aur ibraaheem ne us sthan ka nam yahova yire rakha : isake anusar aj tak bhee kaha jata haai, ki yahova ke pahad par upay kiya jaaega.
fir yahova ke doot ne doosaree bar svarga se ibraaheem ko pukar ke kaha,
yahova kee yah vanee haai, ki maain apanee hee yah shapath khata hoo, ki too ne jo yah kam kiya haai ki apane putra, varan apane aekalaute putra ko bhee, naheen rakh chhoda
aur prathvee kee saree jatiyan apane ko tere vansh ke karan dhany manengee : kyonki too ne meree bat manee haai.
tab ibraaheem apane sevakon ke pas lautt aya, aur ve sab beshorba ko sang sang gaae aur ibraaheem beshorba men rahata raha..
in baton ke pashchata aeesa hua ki ibraaheem ko yah sandesh mila, ki milka ke tere bhai nahor se santan utpann huae haain.
milka ke putra to ye hua, arthata usaka jetta us, aur us ka bhai booj, aur kamooael, jo aram ka pita hua.
fir kesed, hajao, pildasha, yidalap, aur batooaela.
in atton ko milka ibraaheem ke bhai nahor ke janmaae janee. aur batooael ne ribaka ko utpann kiya.
fir nahor ke rooma nam aek rakhelee bhee thee jis se tebah, gaham, tahasha, aur maka, utpann hue..
sara to aek sau sattais baras kee avastha ko pahunchee aur jab sara kee itanee avastha hui
tab vah kiryatarba men mar gai. yah to kanan desh men haai, aur hebraen bhee kahalata haai : so ibraaheem sara ke liye rone peettne ko vanha gaya.
tab ibraaheem apane murde ke pas se uttkar hitiayon se kahane laga,
maain tumhare beech pahun aur paradeshaee hoon : mujhe apane madhy men kaabirstan ke liye aeesee boomi do jo meree nij kee ho jaa, ki maain apane murde ko gadke apane ankh kee ott karoon.
hitiayon ne ibraaheem se kaha,
tab ibraaheem uttkar khda hua, aur hitiayon ke sammuk, jo us desh ke nivasee the, dandvat karake kahane laga,
yaadi tumharee yah ichchha ho ki maain apane murde ko gadke apanee ankh kee ott karoo, to meree praarthna haai, ki sohar ke putra aepraen se mere liye binatee karo,
ki vah apanee makapelavalee gufaa, jo usakee boomi kee seema par haai usaka poora dam lekar mujhe de de, ki vah tumhare beech kaabirstan ke liye meree nij boomi ho jaae.
aur aepraen to hitiayon ke beech vahan baaitta hua tha. so jitane hittee usake nagar ke faattk se hokar bheetar jate the, un sabhon ke samhane us ne ibraaheem ko uttr diya,
ki he mere prabhu, aeesa nahee, meree suna vah boomi maain tujhe deta hoo, aur us men jo gufaa haai, vah bhee maain tujhe deta hoon apane jaatibhaiyon ke sammukh maain use tujh ko diae deta hoon: so apane murde ko kabra men rakh.
tab ibraaheem ne us desh ke nivaasiyon ke samhane dandvat kee.
aur unake sunate huae aepraen se kaha, yaadi too aeesa chahe, to meree sun : us boomi ka jo dam ho, vah maain dena chahata hoon use mujh se le le, tab maain apane murde ko vahan gaoonga.
aepraen ne ibraaheem ko yah uttr diya,
ki, he mere prabhu, meree bat suna aek boomi ka dam to char sau shokel roopa haai par mere aur tere beech men yah kya haai ? apane murde ko kabra me rakh.
ibraaheem n aepraen kee manakar usako utana roopa taul diya, jitana us ne hitiayon ke sunate huae kaha tha, arthata char sau aeese shokel jo vyapariyon men chalate the.
so aepraen kee boomi, jo mamra ke sammukh kee makapela men thee, vah gufaa samet, aur un sab vrakshaen samet bhee jo us men aur usake charon aur seema par the,
jitane hittee usake nagar ke faattk se hokar bheetar jate the, un sabhon ke samhane ibraaheem ke aadhaikar men pakkee reeati se a gai.
isake pashchata ibraaheem ne apanee patnee sara ko, us makapela valee boomi kee gufaa men jo mamra ke arthata hebraen ke samhane kanan desh men haai, mittee dee.
aur vah boomi gufaa samet, jo us men thee, hitiayon kee or se kabirstan ke liye ibraaheem ke adhaikar men pakkee reeati se a gai.
ibraaheem vraddh tha aur usakee ayu bahut bhee aur yahova ne sab baton men usako ashaeesh dee thee.
so ibraaheem ne apane us das se, jo usake ghar men puraaniya aur usakee saree sampati par adhaikaree tha, kaha, apana hath meree jangha ke neeche rakh :
parantu too mere desh men mere hee kuttumbaiyon ke pas jakar mere putra isahak ke liye aek patnee le aaega.
das ne us se kaha, kadaachita vah sree is desh men mere sath ana n chahe to kya mujhe tere putra ko us desh men jahan se too aya haai le jana padega ?
ibraaheem ne us se kaha, chaukas rah, mere putra ko vahan kabhee n le jana.
svarga ka parameshvar yahova, jis ne mujhe mere pita ke ghar se aur meree janmaboomi se le akar mujh se shapath khakar kaha, ki maain yah desh tere vansh ko doonga vahee apana doot tere age age bhejega, ki too mere putra ke liye vahan se aek sree le aae.
aur yaadi vah sree tere sath ana n chahe tab to too meree is shapath se choott jaaega : par mere putra ko vahan n le jana.
tab us das ne apane svamee ibraaheem kee jangha ke neeche apana hath rakhkar us se isee vishay kee shapath khai.
tab vah das apane svamee ke untto men se das untt chhnattkar usake sab uttm uttm padarthon men se kuchh kuchh lekar chala : aur masopottamiya men nahor ke nagar ke pas pahuncha.
aur us ne untton ko nagar ke bahar aek kuaen ke pas baaittaya, vah sandhya ka samay tha, jis samay striayan jal bhrane ke liye nikalatee haai.
so vah kahane laga, he mere svamee ibraaheem ke parameshvar, yahova, aj mere karya ko siddh kar, aur mere svamee ibraaheem par karoona kara.
dekh maain jal ke is sote ke pas khda hoon aur nagaravasiyon kee beattyaien jal bhrane ke liye nikalee atee haain :
so aeesa hone de, ki jis kanya se maain kahoo, ki apana ghada meree or jhuka, ki maain peeun aur vah kahe, ki le, pee le, peechhe maain tere untto ko bhee peelaungee : so vahee ho jise too ne apane das isahak ke liye ttharaya ho isee reeati maain jan loonga ki too ne mere svamee par karoona kee haai.
aur aeesa hua ki jab vah kah hee raha tha ki ribaka, jo ibraaheem ke bhai nahor ke janmaye milka ke putra, batooael kee bettee thee, vah kandho par ghada liye huae ai.
vah aati sundar, aur kumaree thee, aur kisee puroosh ka munh n dekha tha : vah kuaen men sote ke pas utar gai, aur apana ghada bhr ke fir upar ai.
us ne kaha, he mere prabhu, le, pee le: aur us ne faurtee se ghada utarakar hath men liye liye usako pila diya.
jab vah usako pila chukee, tak kaha, maain tere untton ke liye bhee tab tak panee bhr bhr laungee, jab tak ve pee n chuken.
tab vah faurtee se apane ghade ka jal haude men undelakar fir kuen par bhrane ko daud gai aur usake sab untton ke liye panee bhr diya.
aur vah puroosh usakee or chupachap achambhe ke sath takata hua yah sochata tha, ki yahova ne meree yatra ko sufal kiya haai ki naheen.
jab untt pee chuke, tab us puroosh ne adha tole sone ka aek natth nikalakar usako diya, aur das tole sone ke kangan usake hathon men pahina diae
aur poochha, too kis kee bettee haai? yah mujh ko bata de. kya tere pita ke ghar men hamare ttkaine ke liye sthan haai ?
us ne uttr diya, maain to nahor ke janmaae milka ke putra batooel kee bettee hoon.
fir us ne us se kaha, hamare vahan pual aur chara bahut haai, aur ttkaine ke liye sthan bhee haai.
tab us puroosh ne sir jhukakar yahova ko dandvata karake kaha,
dhany haai mere svamee ibraaheem ka parameshvar yahova, ki us ne apanee karoona aur sachchai ko mere svamee par se hatta naheen liya : yahova ne mujh ko tteek marga par chalakar mere svamee ke bhai bandhauon ke ghar par pahucha diya haai.
aur us knya ne daudkar apanee mata ke ghar men yah sara vrattant kah sunaya.
tab laban jo ribaka ka bhai tha, so bahar kuen ke nikatt us puroosh ke pas dauda gaya.
aur aeesa hua ki jab us ne vah natth aur apanee baahin ribaka ke hathon men ve kangan bhee dekhe, aur usakee yah bat bhee sunee, ki us puroosh ne mujh se aeesee baten kaheen tab vah us puroosh ke pas gaya aur kya dekha, ki vah sote ke nikatt untton ke pas khda haai.
us ne kaha, he yahova kee or se dhany puroosh bheetar a : too kyon bahar khda haai ? maain ne ghar ko, aur untto ke liye bhee sthan taaiyar kiya haai.
aur vah puroosh ghar men gaya aur laban ne untton kee kaattyaian kholakar pual aur chara diya aur usake, aur usake sangee jano ke panv dhaene ko jal diya.
tak us ne kaha, maain to ibraaheem ka das hoon.
aur yahova ne mere svamee ko badee ashaeesh dee haai so vah mahan puroosh ho gaya haai aur us ne usako bhed-bakaree, gaya-baail, sona-roopa, dasa-dasiya, untt aur gadahe diae haai.
aur mere svamee kee patnee sara ke buddhape men us se aek putra utpann hua haai. aur us putra ko ibraaheem ne apana sab kuchh de diya haai.
aur mere svamee ne mujhe yah shapath khailai, ki maain usake putra ke liye kananiyon kee ladkiyon men se jin ke desh men vah rahata haai, koi sree n le aunga.
maain usake pita ke ghar, aur kul ke logon ke pas jakar usake putra ke liye aek sree le aunga.
tab maain ne apane svamee se kaha, kadachita vah sree mere peechhe n aae.
tab us ne mujh se kaha, yahova, jisake samhane maain chalata aya hoo, vah tere sang apane doot ko bhejakar teree yatra ko sufal karega so too mere kul, aur mere pita ke gharane men se mere putra ke liye aek sree le a sakega.
too tab hee meree is shapath se choottega, jab too mere kul ke logon ke pas pahunchega arthata yadi ve mujhe koi sree n de, to too meree shpath se choottega.
so maain aj us kuen ke nikatt akar kahane laga, he mere svamee ibraaheem ke parameshvar yahova, yaadi too meree is yatra ko sufal karata ho :
to dekh maain jal ke is kuen ke nikatt khda hoon so aeesa ho, ki jo kumaree jal bhrane ke liye nikal aa, aur maain us se kahoo, apane ghade men se mujhe thoda panee pila
aur vah mujh se kahe, pee le aur maai tere untto ke peene ke liye bhee panee bhr doongee : vah vahee sree ho jisako too ne mere svamee ke putra ke liye ttharaya ho.
maain man hee man yah kah hee raha tha, ki dekh ribaka kandho par ghada liye huae nikal ai fir vah sote ke pas utarake bhrane lagee : aur maai ne us se kaha, mujhe pila de.
aur us ne faurtee se apane ghade ko kandho par se utarake kaha, le, pee le, peechhe maain tere untton ko bhee pilaungee : so maain ne pee liya, aur us ne untton ko bhee pila diya.
tab maain ne us se poochha, ki too kis kee bettee haai ? aur us ne kaha, maain to nahor ke janmaae milka ke putra batooael kee bettee hoon : tab maain ne usakee nak men vah natt, aur usake hathon men ve kangan paahina diae.
so ab, yadi too mere svamee ke sath krapa aur sachchai ka vyavahar karana chahate ho, to mujh se kaho : aur yadi naheen chahate ho, taubhee mujh se kah do taki maain daahinee or, va bain or fir jaun.
tab laban aur batooael ne uttr diya, yah bat yahova kee or se hui haai : so ham log tujh se n to bhla kah sakate haain n bura.
dek, ribaka tere samhane haai, usako le ja, aur vah yahova ke vachan ke anusar, tere svamee ke putra kee patnee ho jaae.
unaka yah vachan sunakar, ibraaheem ke das ne boomi par girake yahova ko dandvata kiya.
fir us das ne sone aur roope ke gahane, aur vasr nikalakar ribaka ko diae : aur usake bhai aur mata ko bhee us ne anamol anamol vastuaen dee.
tab us ne apane sangee janon samet bhojan kiya, aur rat vaheen bitai : aur tadke uttkar kaha, mujh ko apane svamee ke pas jane ke liye vida karo.
ribaka ke bhai aur mata ne kaha, kanya ko hamare pas kuchh din, arthata kam se kam das din rahane de fir usake pashchata vah chalee jaaegee.
us ne un se kaha, yahova ne jo meree yatra ko sufal kiya haai so tum mujhe mat roko ab mujhe vida kar do, ki maain apane svamee ke pas jaun.
unhon ne kaha, ham kanya ko bulakar poochhte haai, aur dekhenge, ki vah kya kahatee haai.
so unhon ne ribaka ko bulakar us se poochha, kya too is manushy ke sang jaaegee? us ne kaha, han maain jaungee.
tab unhon ne apanee baahin ribaka, aur usakee dhaay aur ibraaheem ke das, aur usake sathee sabhon ko vida kiya.
aur unhon ne ribaka ko ashaeervad deke kaha, he hamaree baahin, too hajaron lakhon kee adimata ho, aur tera vansh apane baairiyon ke nagaron ka aadhaikaree ho.
is par ribaka apanee sahealiyon samet chalee aur untt par chaddhke us puroosh ke peechhe ho lee : so vah das ribaka ko sath lekar chal diya.
isahak jo daakkhian desh men rahata tha, so lahaairoi nam kuen se hokar chala ata tha.
aur ribaka ne bhee ankh uttakar isahak ko dekha, aur dekhte hee untt par se utar padee
tab us ne das se poochha, jo puroosh maaidan par ham se milane ko chala ata haai, so kaun haai? das ne kaha, vah to mera svamee haai. tab ribaka ne ghoonghatt lekar apane munh ko ddhap liya.
aur das ne isahak se apana sara vrattant varnn kiya.
tab isahak ribaka ko apanee mata sara ke tamboo men le aya, aur usako byahakar us se praem kiya : aur isahak ko mata kee mratyu ke pashchata shaaantai hui..
tab ibraaheem ne aek aur patnee byah lee jisaka nam katoora tha.
aur us se jimraan, yokshaan, madana, midhan, yishabak, aur shooh utpann hue.
aur yokshaan se shaba aur dadan utpann hue. aur dadan ke vansh men ashshooree, latooshae, aur lummee log hue.
aur midhan ke putra aepa, aeper, hanok, abeeda, aur aelda hua, se sab katoora ke santan hue.
isahak ko to ibraaheem ne apana sab kuchh diya.
par apanee rakheliyon ke putraen ko, kuchh kuchh dekar apane jeete jee apane putra isahak ke pas se poorab desh men bhej diya.
ibraaheem kee saree avastha aek sau pachahattr varsha kee hui.
aur ibraaheem ka deegharayu hone ke karan arthata poore buddhape kee avastha men praan choott gaya.
aur usake putra isahak aur ishmaael ne, hittee sohar ke putra aepraen kee mamra ke sammukhvalee boomi me, jo makapela kee gufaa thee, us men usako mittee dee gai.
arthata jo boomi ibraaheem ne hitiayon se mol lee thee : usee men ibraaheem, aur us kee patnee sara, donon ko mittee dee gai.
ibraaheem ke marane ke pashchata parameshvar ne usake putra isahak ko jo lahaairoi nam kuen ke pas rahata tha ashaeesh dee..
ishmaael ke putraen ke nam aur vanshaavalee yah haai : arthata ishmaael ka jetta putra nabayot, fir kedar, adabel, mibasam,
mishma, dooma, massa,
hadar, tema, yatoor, napeesha, aur kedama.
ishmaael ke putra ye hee hua, aur inheen ke namon ke anusar inake ganvo, aur chhavaaniyon ke nam bhee pade aur ye hee barah apane apane kul ke pradhaan hue.
ishmaael kee saree avastha aek sau saaintees varsha kee hui : tab usake praan choott gaa, aur vah apane logon men ja mila.
aur usake vansh haveela se shoor tak, jo misr ke sammukh ashshoora ke marga men haai, bas gaae. aur unaka bhag unake sab bhaibandhauon ke sammukh pada..
ibraaheem ke putra isahak kee vanshaavalee yah haai : ibraaheem se isahak utpann hua.
aur isahak ne chalees varsha ka hokar ribaka ko, jo panaram ke vasee, aramee batooael kee bettee, aur aramee laban kee bahin bhee, byah liya.
isahak kee patnee to banjh thee, so us ne usake nimitt yahova se binatee kee: aur yahova ne usakee binatee sunee, so usakee patnee ribaka garbhvatee hui.
aur ladke usake garbh men apas men lipattke aek doosare ko marane lage : tab us ne kaha, meree jo aeesee hee dasha rahegee to maain kyonkar jeevit rahoongee? aur vah yahova kee ichchha poochhne ko gai.
tab yahova ne us se kaha tere garbh men do jatiyan haai, aur teree kokh se nikalate hee do rajy ke log alag alag honge, aur aek rajy ke log doosare se aadhaik samarthee honge aur bada betta chhotte ke adhaeen hoga.
