aur yahova parameshvar ne adam ko boomi kee mittee se racha aur usake nathno men jeevan ka shvas foonk diya aur adam jeevata praanee ban gaya.
aur yahova parameshvar ne poorva kee or adan desh men aek baattkai lagai aur vahan adam ko jise us ne racha tha, rakh diya.
aur yahova parameshvar ne boomi se sab bhanati ke vraksha, jo dekhne men manohar aur jinake fal khane men achchhe haain ugaa, aur baattkai ke beech men jeevan ke vraksha ko aur bhle ya bure ke gyaan ke vraksha ko bhee lagaya.
aur us baattkai ko seenchane ke liye aek mahanadee adan se nikalee aur vahan se age bahakar char dhaara men ho gai.
paahilee dhaara ka nam peeshaena haai, yah vahee haai jo haveela nam ke sare desh ko jahan sona milata haai ghore huae haai.
us desh ka sona chokha hota haai, vahan motee aur sulaaimanee patthr bhee milate haain.
aur doosaree nadee ka nam geehona haai, yah vahee haai jo koosh ke sare desh ko ghore huae haai.
aur teesaree nadee ka nam hiekela haai, yah vahee haai jo ashshoora ke poorva kee or bahatee haai. aur chauthee nadee ka nam farat haai.
jab yahova parameshvar ne adam ko lekar adan kee battkai men rakh diya, ki vah us men kam kare aur usakee raksha kare,
tab yahova parameshvar ne adam ko yah agyaa dee, ki too battkai ke sab vrakshaen ka fal bina khttke kha sakata haai:
par bhle ya bure ke gyaan ka jo vraksha haai, usaka fal too kabhee n khana : kyonaki jis din too usaka fal khaae usee din avashy mar jaaega..
fir yahova parameshvar ne kaha, adam ka akela rahana achchha naheen maai usake liye aek aeesa sahayak banaunga jo us se mel khaae.
aur yahova parameshvar boomi men se sab jati ke banaaile pashuuo, aur akash ke sab bhaati ke pakshiayon ko rachakar adam ke pas le aya ki dekhe, ki vah unaka kya kya nam rakhta haai aur jis jis jeevit praanee ka jo jo nam adam ne rakha vahee usaka nam ho gaya.
so adam ne sab jati ke ghareloo pashuuo, aur akash ke pakshiayo, aur sab jati ke banaaile pashuuon ke nam rakhe parantu adam ke liye koi aeesa sahayak n mila jo us se mel kha sake.
tab yahova parameshvar ne adam ko bharee neend men dal diya, aur jab vah so gaya tab us ne usakee aek pasulee nikalakar usakee santee mans bhr diya.
aur yahova parameshvar ne us pasulee ko jo us ne adam men se nikalee thee, sree bana diya aur usako adam ke pas le aya.
aur adam ne kaha ab yah meree haddiyon men kee haddee aur mere mans men ka mans haai : so isaka nam naree hoga, kyonki yah nar men se nikalee gai haai.
is karan puroosh apane mata pita ko chhodkar apanee patnee se mila rahega aur ve aek tan banen rahenge.
aur adam aur usakee patnee donon nange the, par lajate n the..
tab yakoob ne rahel se krodhait hokar kaha, kya maain parameshvar hoon? teree kokh to usee ne band kar rakhee haai.
rahel ne kaha, achchha, meree laundee bilha hajir haai: usee ke pas ja, vah mere ghauttnon par janegee, aur usake dara mera bhee ghar basega.
to us ne use apanee laundee bilha ko diya, ki vah usakee patnee ho aur yakoob usake pas gaya.
aur bilha garbhvatee hui aur yakoob se usake aek putra utpann hua.
aur rahel ne kaha, parameshvar ne mera nyay chukaya aur meree sunakar mujhe aek putra diya : isaaliye us ne usaka nam dan rakha.
aur rahel kee laundee bilha fir garbhvatee hui aur yakoob se aek putra aur utpann hua.
tab rahel ne kaha, maain ne apanee bahin ke sath bade bal se lipattkar mallayuddh kiya aur ab jeet gai : so us ne usaka nam naptalee rakha.
aur lia: kee laundee jilpa ke bhee yakoob se aek putra utpann hua.
tab lia: ne kaha, aho bhagya! so us ne usaka nam gad rakha.
fir lia: kee laundee jilpa ke yakoob se aek aur putra utpann hua.
tab lia: ne kaha, maai dhany hoon nishchay striayan mujhe dhany kahengee : so us ne usaka nam ashor rakha.
gehoon kee kattnee ke dinon men rooben ko maaidan men doodafal mile, aur vah unako apanee mata lia: ke pas le gaya, tab rahel ne lia: se kaha, apane putra ke doodafalon men se kuchh mujhe de.
us ne us se kaha, too ne jo mere paati ko le liya haai so kya chhottee bat haai ? ab kya too mere putra ke doodafal bhee lene chahatee haai? rahel ne kaha, achchha, tere putra ke doodafalon ke badale vah aj rat ko tere sang soega.
so sanjh ko jab yakoob maaidan se a raha tha, tab lia: us se bhentt karane ko nikalee, aur kaha, tujhe mere hee pas ana hoga, kyonaki maai ne apane putra ke doodafal dekar tujhe sachamuch mol liya. tab vah us rat ko usee ke sang soya.
tab parameshvar ne lia: kee sunee, so vah garbhvatee hui aur yakoob se usake panchavan putra utpann hua.
tab lia: ne kaha, men ne jo apane pati ko apanee laundee dee, isaaliye parameshvar ne mujhe meree manjooree dee haai : so us ne usaka nam issakar rakha.
aur lia: fir garbhvatee hui aur yakoob se usake chhttvan putra utpann hua.
tab lia: ne kaha, parameshvar ne mujhe achchha dan diya haai ab kee bar mera paati mere sang bana rahega, kyonaki mere us se chh: putra utpann chuke haain : se us ne usaka nam jabooloon rakha.
tatpashchata usake aek bettee bhee hui, aur us ne usaka nam deena rakha.
aur parameshvar ne rahel kee bhee sudhai lee, aur usakee sunakar usakee kokh kholee.
so vah garbhvatee hui aur usake aek putra utpann hua so us ne kaha, parameshvar ne meree namadharai ko door kar diya haai.
so us ne yah kahakar usaka nam yoosufa rakha, ki parameshvar mujhe aek putra aur bhee dega.
jab rahel se yoosufa utpann hua, tab yakoob ne laban se kaha, mujhe vida kar, ki maain apane desh aur sthan ko jaun.
meree striayan aur mere ladke-bale, jinake liye maain ne teree seva kee haai, unhen mujhe de, ki maain chala jaun too to janata haai ki maain ne teree kaaisee seva kee haai.
laban ne us se kaha, yaadi teree draashtti men maain ne anugrah paya haai, to rah ja : kyonki maain ne anubhv se jan liya haai, ki yahova ne tere karan se mujhe ashaeesh dee haai.
fir us ne kaha, too tteek bata ki maain tujh ko kya doo, aur maain use doonga.
us ne us se kaha too janata haai ki maain ne teree kaaisee seva kee, aur tere pashu mere pas kis prakar se rahe.
mere apane se pahile ve kitane the, aur ab kitane ho gaae haain aur yahova ne mere ane par tujhe to ashaeesh dee haai : par maain apane ghar ka kam kab karane paunga?
us ne fir kaha, maain tujhe kya doon? yakoob ne kaha, too mujhe kuchh n de yaadi too mere liye ek kam kare, to maai fir teree bhed-bakaariyon ko charaunga, aur unakee raksha karoonga.
aur jab age ko meree majadooree kee charcha tere samhane chale, tab dharma kee yahee sakshaee hogee arthata bakariyon men se jo koi n chitteevalee n chitkabaree ho, aur bhedon men se jo koi kalee n ho, so yaadi mere pas nikale, to choree kee ttharengee.
tab laban ne kaha, tere kahane ke anusar ho.
so us ne usee din sab dhaareevale aur chitkabare bakaro, aur sab chitteevalee aur chitkabaree bakaariyon ko, arthata jin men kuchh ujalapan tha, unako aur sab kalee bhedon ko bhee alag karake apane putraen ke hath saup diya.
aur us ne apane aur yakoob ke beech men teen din ke marga ka antar ttharaya : so yakoob laban kee bhed-bakaariyon ko charane laga.
aur yakoob ne chanar, aur badam, aur amorn vrakshaen kee haree haree chhdiyan lekar, unake chhlaike kaheen kaheen chheelake, unhen dhaareedar bana diya, aeesee ki un chhdiyon kee safaedee dikhai dene lagee.
aur tab chheelee hui chhadiyon ko bhed-bakaariyon ke samhane unake panee peene ke kattauton men khda kiya aur jab ve panee peene ke liye ai tab gabhain ho gai.
tab yakoob ne bhedon ke bachchon ko alag alag kiya, aur laban kee bhed-bakaariyon ke munh ko chitteevale aur sab kale bachchon kee or kar diya aur apane jhundon ko un se alag rakha, aur laban kee bhed-bakaariyon se milane n diya.
aur jab jab balavant bhed-bakaariyan gaabhain hotee thee, tab tab yakoob un chhadiyon ko kattauton me unake samhane rakh deta tha jis se ve chhdiyon ko dekhtee hui gabhain ho jaaen.
par jab nirbal bhed-bakaariyan gaabhain hotee thee, tab vah unhen unake age naheen rakhta tha. is se nirbal nirbal laban kee rahee, aur balavant balavant yakoob kee ho gai.
so vah puroosh atyant dhanaddhy ho gaya, aur usake bahut see bhed-bakaariya, aur launadyaian aur das aur untt aur gadahe ho gaae..
fir laban ke putraen kee ye baten yakoob ke sunane men ai, ki yakoob ne hamare pita ka sab kuchh chheen liya haai, aur hamare pita ke dhan ke karan usakee yah pratishtta haai.
aur yakoob ne laban ke mukhde par draashtti kee aur tad liya, ki vah usake prati pahale ke saman naheen haai.
tab yahova ne yakoob se kaha, apane pitaron ke desh aur apanee janmaboomi ko lautt ja, aur maain tere sang rahoonga.
tab yakoob ne rahel aur lia: ko, maaidan men apanee bhed-bakaariyon ke pas, bulavakar kaha,
tumhare pita ke mukhde se mujhe samajh padta haai, ki vah to mujhe paahile kee nai ab naheen dekhta par mere pita ka parameshvar mere sang haai.
aur tum bhee janatee ho, ki maain ne tumhare pita kee seva shaktai bhr kee haai.
aur tumhare pita ne mujh se chhl karake meree majadooree ko das bar badal diya parantu parameshvar ne usako meree haani karane naheen diya.
jab us ne kaha, ki chitteevale bachche teree majadooree ttharenge, tab sab bhed-bakaariyan chitteevale hee janane lagee, aur jab us ne kaha, ki dhaareevale bachche teree majadooree ttharenge, tab sab bhed-bakaariyan dhaareevale janane lageen.
is reeati se parameshvar ne tumhare pita ke pashu lekar mujh ko de diae.
bhed-bakaariyon ke gaabhain hone ke samay maain ne svapn men kya dekha, ki jo bakare bakaariyon par chaddh rahe haai, so dhaareevale, chitteevale, aur dhabbevale haai.
aur parameshvar ke doot ne svapn men mujh se kaha, he yakoob : maain ne kaha, kya agyaa.
us ne kaha, ankhe uttakar un sab bakaron ko, jo bakaariyon par chaddh rahe haai, dek, ki ve dhaareevale, chitteevale, aur dhabbevale haain kyonaki jo kuchh laban tujh se karata haai, so maain ne dekha haai.
maain us betel ka ishvar hoo, jahan too ne aek khmbhe par tel dal diya, aur meree mannat manee thee : ab chal, is desh se nikalakar apanee janmaboomi ko lautt ja.
tab rahel aur lia : ne us se kaha, kya hamare pita ke ghar men ab bhee hamara kuchh bhag va ansh bacha haai?
kya ham usakee drashtti men paraye n tthareen? dek, us ne ham ko to bech dala, aur hamare roope ko kha baaitta haai.
so parameshvar ne hamare pita ka jitana dhan le liya haai, so hamara, aur hamare ladkebalon ko haai : ab jo kuchh parameshvar ne tujh se kaha so kara.
tab yakoob ne apane ladkebalon aur striayon ko untton par chaddhaya
aur jitane pashuuon ko vah panaram men ikattha karake dhanaddhy ho gaya tha, sab ko kanan men apane pita isahak ke pas jane kee manasa se, sath le gaya.
laban to apanee bhedon ka un katarane ke liye chala gaya tha. aur rahel apane pita ke grahadevataon ko chura le gai.
vah apana sab kuchh lekar bhaga : aur mahanad ke par utarakar apana munh gilad ke pahadee desh kee or kiya..
teesare din laban ko samachar mila, ki yakoob bhag gaya haai.
so us ne apane bhaiyon ko sath lekar usaka sat din tak peechha kiya, aur gilad ke pahadee desh men usako ja pakada.
tab parameshvar ne rat ke svapn men aramee laban ke pas akar kaha, savadhaan rah, too yakoob se n to bhla kahana aur n bura.
aur laban yakoob ke pas pahunch gaya, yakoob to apana tamboo gilad nam pahadee desh men khda kiae pada tha : aur laban ne bhee apane bhaiyon ke sath apana tamboo usee pahadee desh men khda kiya.
too kyon chupake se bhag aya, aur mujh se bina kuchh kahe mere pas se choree se chala aya naheen to maain tujhe anand ke sath mradang aur veena bajavate, aur geet gavate vida karata ?
too ne to mujhe apane bette beattyaien ko choomane tak n diya? too ne moorkhta kee haai.
tum logon kee hani karane kee shaktai mere hath men to haai par tumhare pita ke parameshvar ne mujh se beetee hui rat men kaha, savadhaan rah, yakoob se n to bhla kahana aur n bura.
bhla ab too apane pita ke ghar ka bada aabhailashaee hokar chala aya to chala aya, par mere devataon ko too kyon chura le aya haai?
yakoob ne laban ko uttr diya, maain yah sochakar dr gaya tha : ki kaheen too apanee beattyaien ko mujh se chheen n le.
jis kisee ke pas too apane devataon ko paa, so jeeta n bachega. mere pas tera jo kuchh nikale, so bhai-bandhauon ke samhane pahichanakar le le. kyonaki yakoob n janata tha ki rahel grahadevataon ko chura le ai haai.
yah sunakar laban, yakoob aur lia : aur donon daasiyon ke tambuon me gaya aur kuchh n mila. tab lia: ke tamboo men se nikalakar rahel ke tamboo men gaya.
rahel to grahadevataon ko untt kee kattee men rakhke un par baaittee thee. so laban ne usake sare tamboo men ttttolane par bhee unhen n paya.
rahel ne apane pita se kaha, he mere prabhu is se aprasann n ho, ki maain tere samhane naheen uttee kyonaki maain sreedharma se hoon. so usake ddoonddh ddhanddh karane par bhee grahadevata usako n mile.
tab yakoob krodhait hokar laban se jhgadne laga, aur kaha, mera kya aparadha haai? mera kya pap haai, ki too ne itana krodhait hokar mera peechha kiya haai ?
too ne jo meree saree samagraee ko ttttolakar dekha, so tujh ko saree samagraee men se kya mila? kuchh mila ho to usako yahan apane aur mere bhaiyon ke samahane rakh de, aur ve ham donon ke beech nyay karen.
in bees vasharen se maai tere pas raha un men n to teree bhed-bakaariyon ke garbh gire, aur n tere meddhon ka mans maai ne kabhee khaya.
jise banaaile jantuon ne faad dala usako maain tere pas n lata tha, usakee haani maain hee uttata tha chahe din ko choree jata chahe rat ko, too mujh hee se usako le leta tha.
meree to yah dasha thee, ki din ko to ghaam aur rat ko pala mujhe kha gaya aur neend meree ankhon se bhag jatee thee.
bees varsha tak maain tere ghar men raho chaudah varsha to maai ne teree dono beattyaien ke liye, aur chh: varsha teree bhed-bakaariyon ke liye seva kee : aur too ne meree majadooree ko das bar badal dala.
mere pita ka parameshvar arthata ibraaheem ka parameshvar, jisaka bhy isahak bhee manata haai, yaadi meree or n hota, to nishchay too ab mujhe choochhe hath jane deta. mere du:kh aur mere hathon ke paarishram ko dekhkar parameshvar ne beetee hui rat men tujhe dapatta.
laban le yakoob se kaha, ye beattyaien to meree hee haai, aur ye putra bhee mere hee haai, aur ye bhed-bakaariyon bhee meree hee haai, aur jo kuchh tujhe dekh padta haai so sab mera hee haai : aur ab maain apanee in bettyaien va inake santan se kya kar sakata hoon ?
ab a maain aur too donon apas men vacha bandho, aur vah mere aur tere beech sakshaee ttharee rahe.
tab yakoob ne aek patthr lekar usaka khmbha khda kiya.
tab yakoob ne apane bhai-bandhauon se kaha, patthr ikattha karo yah sunakar unhon ne patthr ikattha karake aek ddher lagaya aur vaheen ddher ke pas unhon ne bhojan kiya.
us ddher ka nam laban ne to yajra sahadutha, par yakoob ne jiliyad rakha.
laban ne kaha, ki yah ddher aj se mere aur tere beech sakshaee rahega. is karan usaka nam jiliyad rakha gaya,
aur mijapa bhee kyonki us ne kaha, ki jab ham us doosare se door rahen tab yahova meree aur teree dekhbhal karata rahe.
yaadi too meree beattyaien ko du:kh de, va unake sivay aur striayan byah le, to hamare sath koi manushy to n rahega par dekh mere tere beech men parameshvar sakshaee rahega.
yah ddher aur yah khmbha donon is bat ke sakshaee rahe, ki hani karane kee manasa se n to maain is ddher ko langhakar tere pas jaunga, n too is ddher aur is khmbhe ko langhakar mere pas aaega.
ibraaheem aur nahor aur unake pita teenon ka jo parameshvar haai, so ham dono ke beech nyay kare. tab yakoob ne usakee shapath khai jisaka bhy usaka pita isahak manata tha.
aur yakoob ne us pahad par melabaali chaddhaya, aur apane bhai-bandhauon ko bhojan karane ke liye bulaya, so unhon ne bhojan karake pahad par rat bitai.
bihan ko laban tadke utta, aur apane bette beattyaien ko choomakar aur ashaeervad dekar chal diya, aur apane sthan ko lautt gaya.
unako dekhte hee yakoob ne kaha, yah to parameshvar ka dal haai so us ne us sthan ka nam mahanaaim rakha..
tab yakoob ne seir desh me, arthata aedom desh me, apane bhai aesav ke pas apane age doot bhej diae.
aur us ne unhen yah agyaa dee, ki mere prabhu aesav se yon kahana ki tera das yakoob tujh se yon kahata haai, ki maain laban ke yahan paradeshaee hokar ab tak raha
aur mere pas gaya-baail, gadahe, bhed-bakaariya, aur dasa-daasiyan haai: so maain ne apane prabhu ke pas isaaliye sandesha bheja haai, ki teree anugrah kee draashtti mujh par ho.
ve doot yakoob ke pas lauttke kahane lage, ham tere bhai aesav ke pas gaae the, aur vah bhee tujh se bhentt karane ko char sau puroosh sang liye huae chala ata haai.
tab yakoob nipatt dr gaya, aur sankatt men pada : aur yah sochakar, apane sangavalon ke, aur bhed-bakaariyo, aur gaya-baailo, aur untto ke bhee alag alag do dal kar liye,
ki yadi aesav akar pahile dal ko marane lage, to doosara dal bhagakar bach jaaega.
fir yakoob ne kaha, he yahova, he mere dada ibraaheem ke parameshvar, too ne to mujh se kaha, ki apane desh aur janmaboomi men lautt ja, aur maain teree bhlai karoonga :
too ne jo jo kam apanee karoona aur sachchai se apane das ke sath kiae haai, ki maain jo apanee chhdee hee lekar is yaradan nadee ke par utar aya, so ab mere do dal ho gaae haai, tere aeese aeese kamon men se maain aek ke bhee yogy to naheen hoon.
meree binatee sunakar mujhe mere bhai aesav ke hath se bacha : maain to us se drata hoo, kaheen aeesa ne ho ki vah akar mujhe aur man samet ladkon ko bhee mar dale.
too ne to kaha haai, ki maain nishchay teree bhlai karoonga, aur tere vansh ko samudr kee baloo ke kinakon ke saman bahut karoonga, jo bahutayat ke mare gine naheen jo sakate.
aur us ne us din kee rat vaheen bitai aur jo kuchh usake pas tha us men se apane bhai aesav kee bhentt ke liye chhantt chhanttkar nikala
arthata do sau bakariya, aur bees bakare, aur do sau bhede, aur bees meddhe,
aur bachchon samet doodha denevalee tees unttaniya, aur chalees gaye, aur das baail, aur bees gadaahiyan aur unake das bachche.
inako us ne jhund jhund karake, apane dason ko saunpakar un se kaha, mere age baddh jao aur jhundon ke beech beech men antar rakho.
fir us ne agale jhund ke rakhvale ko yah agyaa dee, ki jab mera bhai aesav tujhe mile, aur poochhne lage, ki too kis ka das haai, aur kahan jata haai , aur ye jo tere age age haai, so kis ke haain?
tab kahana, ki yah tere das yakoob ke haain. he mere prabhu aesav, ye bhentt ke liye tere pas bheje gaae haai, aur vah ap bhee hamare peechhe peechhe a raha haai.
aur us ne doosare aur teesare rakhvalon ko bhee, varan us sabhon ko jo jhundon ke peechhe peechhe the aeesee hee agyaa dee, ki jab aesav tum ko mile tab isee prakar us se kahana.
aur yah bhee kahana, ki tera das yakoob hamare peechhe peechhe a raha haai. kyonaki us ne yah socha, ki yah bhentt jo mere age age jatee haai, isake dara maain usake krodha ko shaant karake tab usaka darshan karoonga ho sakata haai vah mujh se prasann ho jaae.
so vah bhentt yakoob se pahile par utar gai, aur vah ap us rat ko chhavanee men raha..
usee rat ko vah utta aur apanee donon striayo, aur donon laundyaie, aur gyarahon ladkon ko sang lekar ghaatt se yabbok nadee ke par utar gaya.
aur us ne unhen us nadee ke par utar diya varan apana sab kuchh par utar diya.
aur yakoob ap akela rah gaya tab koi puroosh akar pah fattne tak us se mallayuddh karata raha.
jab us ne dekha, ki maain yakoob par prabal naheen hota, tab usakee jangha kee nas ko chooa so yakoob kee jangha kee nas us se mallayuddh karate hee karate chaddh gai.
tab us ne kaha, mujhe jane de, kyonki bhor hua chahata haai yakoob ne kaha jab tak too mujhe ashaeervad n de, tab tak maain tujhe jane n doonga.
us ne kaha tera nam ab yakoob nahee, parantu israel hoga, kyonaki too parameshvar se aur manushyon se bhee yuddh karake prabal hua haai.
yakoob ne kaha, maain binatee karata hoo, mujhe apana nam bata. us ne kaha, too mera nam kyon poochhta haai? tab us ne usako vaheen ashaeervad diya.
tab yakoob ne yah kahakar us sthan ka nam paneeael rakha: ki parameshvar ko amhane samhane dekhne par bhee mera praan bach gaya haai.
israaelee jo pashuuon kee jangha kee jodvale janghaanas ko aj ke din tak naheen khate, isaka karan yahee haai, ki us puroosh ne yakoob kee jangha kee jod men janghaanas ko chooa tha..
aur yakoob ne ankhen uttakar yah dekha, ki aesav char sau puroosh sang liye huae chala jata haai. tab us ne ladkebalon ko alag alag banttkar lia, aur rahel, aur donon launadyaien ko saup diya.
aur us ne sab ke age ladkon samet launadyaien ko usake peechhe ladkon samet lia: ko, aur sab ke peechhe rahel aur yoosufa ko rakha,
aur ap un sab ke age baddha, aur sat bar boomi par girake dandvata kee, aur apane bhai ke pas pahuncha.
tab aesav us se bhentt karane ko dauda, aur usako day se lagakar, gale se lipattkar chooma : fir ve donon ro pade.
tab us ne ankhe uttakar striayon aur ladke balon ko dekha aur poochha, ye jo tere sath haain so kaun haain? us ne kaha, ye tere das ke ladke haai, jinhen parameshvar ne anugrah karake mujh ko diya haai.
tab ladkon samet launadyaien ne nikatt akar dandvata kee.
fir ladkon samet lia: nikatt ai, aur unhon ne bhee dandvata kee: peechhe yoosufa aur rahel ne bhee nikatt akar dandvata kee.
tab us ne poochha, tera yah bada dal jo mujh ko mila, usaka kya prayojan haai? us ne kaha, yah ki mere prabhu kee anugrah kee drashtti mujh par ho.
aesav ne kaha, he mere bhai, mere pas to bahut haai jo kuchh tera haai so tera hee rahe.
yakoob ne kaha, naheen nahee, yadi tera anugrah mujh par ho, to meree bhentt grahan kar : kyonaki maain ne tera darshan pakar, mano parameshvar ka darshan paya haai, aur too mujh se prasann hua haai.
so yah bhent, jo tujhe bhejee gai haai, grahan kar : kyonaki parameshvar ne mujh par anugrah kiya haai, aur mere pas bahut haai.
fir aesav ne kaha, a, ham baddh chalen: aur maai tere age age chaloonga.
yakoob ne kaha, he mere prabhu, too janata hee haai ki mere sath sukumar ladke, aur doodha deneharee bhed-bakaariyan aur gayen haai yaadi aeese pashu aek din bhee adhaik hanke jaae, to sab ke sab mar jaaenge.
so mera prabhu apane das ke age baddh jaa, aur maain in pashuuon kee gaati ke anusar, jo mere age haai, aur ladkebalon kee gaati ke anusar dhaeere dhaeere chalakar seir men apane prabhu ke pas pahunchoonga.
aesav ne kaha, to apane sangavalon men se maain kai aek tere sath chhod jaun. us ne kaha, yah kyon? itana hee bahut haai, ki mere prabhu kee anugrah kee drashtti mujh par banee rahe.
tab aesav ne usee din seir jane ko apana marga liya.
aur yakoob vahan se kooch karake sukkot ko gaya, aur vahan apane liye aek ghar, aur pashuuon ke liye jhonpade banaae: isee karan us sthan ka nam sukkot pada..
aur yakoob jo panaram se aya tha, so kanan desh ke shakem nagar ke pas kushal kshom se pahunchakar nagar ke samhane dere khde kiae.
aur boomi ke jis khnd par us ne apana tamboo khda kiya, usako us ne shakem ke pita hamor ke putraen ke hath se aek sau kaseeton men mol liya.
aur vahan us ne aek vedee banakar usaka nam aelelohe israael rakha..
aur lia: kee bettee deena, jo yakoob se utpann hui thee, us desh kee ladkiyon se bhentt karane ko nikalee.
tab us desh ke pradhaan hittee hamor ke putra shakem ne use dekha, aur use le jakar usake sath kukarma karake usako bhrashtt kar dala.
tab usaka man yakoob kee bettee deena se lag gaya, aur us ne us kanya se praem kee baten kee, aur us se praem karane laga.
aur shakem ne apane pita hamor se kaha, mujhe is ladkee ko meree patnee hone ke liye dila de.
aur yakoob ne suna, ki shakem ne meree bettee deena ko ashuuddh kar dala haai , par usake putra us samay pashuuon ke sang maaidan men the, so vah unake ane tak chup raha.
aur yakoob ke putra sunate hee maaidan se bahut udas aur krodhait hokar aae: kyonki shakem ne yakoob kee bettee ke sath kukarma karake israael ke gharane se moorkhta ka aeesa kam kiya tha, jisaka karana anuachit tha.
hamor ne un sab se kaha, mere putra shakem ka man tumharee bettee par bahut laga haai, so use usakee patnee hone ke liye usako de do.
aur hamare sang base raho: aur yah desh tumhare samane pada haai is men rahakar lenaden karo, aur isakee boomi ko apane liye le lo.
aur shakem ne bhee deena ke pita aur bhaiyon se kaha, yadi mujh par tum logon kee anugrah kee draashtti ho, to jo kuchh tum mujh se kaha, so maain doonga.
tum mujh se kitana hee mooly va badala kyon n mango, taubhee maain tumhare kahe ke anusar doonga : parantu us kanya ko patnee hone ke liye mujhe do.
tab yah sochakar, ki shakem ne hamaree baahin deena ko ashuuddh kiya haai, yakoob ke putraen ne shakem aur usake pita hamor ko chhl ke sath yah uttr diya,
ki ham aeesa kam naheen kar sakate, ki kisee khtanarahit puroosh ko apanee bahin den kyonaki is se hamaree namadharai hogee :
is bat par to ham tumharee man lenge, ki hamaree nai tum men se har aek puroosh ka khtana kiya jaae.
tab ham apanee beattyaian tumhen byah denge, aur tumharee beattyaian byah lenge, aur tumhare sang base bhee rahenge, aur ham donon aek hee samuday ke manushy ho jaaenge.
par yaadi tum hamaree bat n manakar apana khtana n karaoge, to ham apanee ladkee ko leke yahan se chale jaaenge.
usakee is bat par hamor aur usaka putra shakem prasann hue.
aur vah javan, jo yakoob kee bettee ko bahut chahata tha, is kam ko karane men us ne vilamb n kiya. vah to apane pita ke sare gharane men adhaik pratishttit tha.
so hamor aur usaka putra shakem apane nagar ke faattk ke nikatt jakar nagaravaasiyon ko yon samajhane lage
ki ve manushy to hamare sang mel se rahana chahate haain so unhen is desh men rahake lenaden karane do dekho, yah desh unake liye bhee bahut haai fir ham log unakee bettyaien ko byah le, aur apanee bettyaien ko unhen diya karen.
ve log keval is bat par hamare sang rahane aur aek hee samuday ke manushy ho jane ko prasann haai, ki unakee nai hamare sab purooshaen ka bhee khtana kiya jaae.
kya unakee bhed-bakaariya, aur gaya-baail varan unake sare pashu aur dhan sampaati hamaree n ho jaaegee? itana kee karen ki ham log unakee bat man le, to ve hamare sang rahenge.
so jitane us nagar ke faattk se nikalate the, un sabhon ne hamor kee aur usake putra shakem kee bat manee aur har aek puroosh ka khtana kiya gaya, jitane us nagar ke faattk se nikalate the.
teesare din, jab ve log peeadit pade the, tab aeesa hua ki shaimon aur levee nam yakoob ke do putraen ne, jo deena ke bhai the, apanee apanee talavar le us nagar men nidhadk ghausakar sab purooshaen ko ghaat kiya.
aur hamor aur usake putra shakem ko unhon ne talavar se mar dala, aur deena ko shakem ke ghar se nikal le gaae.
aur yakoob ke putraen ne ghaat kar dalane par bhee chaddhkar nagar ko isaaliye loott liya, ki us men unakee bahin ashuuddh kee gai thee.
unhon ne bhed-bakaree, aur gaya-baail, aur gadahe, aur nagar aur maaidan men jitana dhan tha le liya.
us sab ko, aur unake bala-bachcho, aur striayon ko bhee har le gaa, varan ghar ghar men jo kuchh tha, usako bhee unhon ne loott liya.
tab yakoob ne shaimon aur levee se kaha, tum ne jo us desh ke nivasee kanaaniyon aur paarijjaiyon ke man men meree or gharana utpann karai haai, is se tum ne mujhe sankatt men dala haai, kyonaki mere sath to thode kee log haai, so ab ve ikatthe hokar mujh par chaddhenge, aur mujhe mar dalenge, so maain apane gharane samet satyanash ho jaunga.
unhon ne kaha, kya vah hamaree baahin ke sath veshya kee nai bartav kare?
tab parameshvar ne yakoob se kaha, yahan se kooch karake betel ko ja, aur vaheen raha: aur vahan ishvar ke liye vedee bana, jis ne tujhe us samay darshan diya, jab too apane bhai aesav ke dr se bhaga jata tha.
tab yakoob ne apane gharane se, aur un sab se bhee jo usake sang the, kaha, tumhare beech men jo paraae devata haai, unhen nikal faenko aur apane apane ko shuuddh karo, aur apane vasr badal dalo
aur ao, ham yahan se kooch karake betel ko jaaen vahan maain ishvar ke liye aek vedee banaunga, jis ne sankatt ke din meree sun lee, aur jis marga se maain chalata tha, us men mere sang raha.
so jitane paraae devata unake pas the, aur jitane kundl unake kanon men the, un sabhon ko unhon ne yakoob ko diya aur us ne unako us sindoor vraksha ke neeche, jo shakem ke pas haai, gad diya.
tab unhon ne kooch kiya: aur unake charon or ke nagar nivaasiyon ke man men parameshvar kee or se aeesa bhy sama gaya, ki unhon ne yakoob ke putraen ka peechha n kiya.
vahan us ne aek vedee banai, aur us sthan ka nam aelabetel rakha kyonki jab vah apane bhai ke dr se bhaga jata tha tab parameshvar us par vaheen pragatt hua tha.
fir yakoob ke panaram se ane ke pashchata parameshvar ne doosaree bar usako darshan dekar ashaeesh dee.
aur parameshvar ne us se kaha, ab tak to tera nam yakoob raha haai par age ko tera nam yakoob n rahega, too israael kahalaaega :
fir parameshvar ne us se kaha, maain sarvashaktaiman ishvar hoon: too foole-fale aur baddhe aur tujh se aek jati varan jaatiyon kee aek mandlee bhee utpann hogee, aur tere vansh men raja utpann honge.
aur jo desh maain ne ibraaheem aur isahak ko diya haai, vahee desh tujhe deta hoo, aur tere peechhe tere vansh ko bhee doonga.
tab parameshvar us sthan me, jahan us ne yakoob se baten kee, unake pas se upar chaddh gaya.
aur jis sthan men parameshvar ne yakoob se baten kee, vahan yakoob ne patthr ka aek khmba khda kiya, aur us par argha dekar tel dal diya.
aur jahan parameshvar ne yakoob se baten kee, us sthan ka nam us ne betel rakha.
fir unhon ne betel se kooch kiya aur aepraata thodee hee door rah gaya tha, ki rahel ko bachcha janane kee badee peeda ane lagee.
jab usako badee badee peeda utttee thee tab dhaay ne us se kaha, mat dra ab kee bhee tere betta hee hoga.
tab aeesa hua, ki vah mar gai, aur praan nikalate nikalate us ne us bette ko nam benonee rakha: par usake pita ne usaka nam binyameen rakha.
yon rahel mar gai, aur aepraata, arthata betalehem ke marga me, usako mittee dee gai.
aur yakoob ne usakee kabra par aek khmbha khda kiya: rahel kee kabra ka vahee khmbha aj tak bana haai.
fir israael ne kooch kiya, aur aeder nam gummatt ke age baddhkar apana tamboo khda kiya.
jab israael us desh men basa tha, tab aek din aeesa hua, ki rooben ne jakar apane pita kee rakhelee bilha ke sath kukarma kiya : aur yah bat israael ko maloom ho gai..
yakoob ke barah putra huae. un men se lia: ke putra ye the arthata yakoob ka jetta, rooben, fir shaimon, levee, yahooda, issakar, aur jabooloona.
aur rahel ke putra ye the arthata yoosuf, aur binyameena.
aur rahel kee laundee bilha ke putra ye the arthata dan, aur naptalee.
aur lia: kee laundee jilpa ke putra ye the : arthata gad, aur ashora yakoob ke ye hee putra hua, jo us se panaram men utpann huae..
aur yakoob mamra me, jo kariyataarba, arthata habraen haai, jahan ibraaheem aur isahak paradeshaee hokar rahe the, apane pita isahak ke pas aya.
isahak kee avastha aek sau assee baras kee hui.
aur isahak ka praan choott gaya, aur vah mar gaya, aur vah booddha aur pooree ayu ka hokar apane logon men ja mila: aur usake putra aesav aur yakoob ne usako mittee dee..
aesav jo aedom bhee kahalata haai, usakee yah vanshaavalee haai.
aesav ne to kananee ladkiyan byah leen arthata hittee aelon kee bettee ada ko, aur aholeebama ko jo ana kee bettee, aur hivvee sibon kee naatinee thee.
fir us ne ishmaael kee bettee basamat ko bhee, jo nabayot kee baahin thee, byah liya.
ada ne to aesav ke janmaae aeleepaj ko, aur basamat ne rooael ko utpann kiya.
aur oholeebama ne yoosha, aur yalam, aur korah ko utpann kiya, aesav ke ye hee putra kanan desh men utpann hue.
aur aesav apanee patnaiyo, aur bette-beattyaie, aur ghar ke sab praaanaiyo, aur apanee bhed-bakaree, aur gaya-baail adi sab pashuuo, nidan apanee saree sampati ko, jo us ne kanan desh men sanchay kee thee, lekar apane bhai yakoob ke pas se doosare desh ko chala gaya.
kyonaki unakee sampati itanee ho gai thee, ki ve ikatthe n rah sake aur pashuuon kee bahutayat ke mare us desh me, jahan ve paradeshaee hokar rahate the, unakee samai n rahee.
aesav ke putraen ke nam ye haain arthata aesav kee patnee ada ka putra aeleepaj, aur usee aesav kee patnee basamat ka putra rooaela.
aur aeleepaj ke ye putra hue arthata teman, omar, sapo, gatam, aur kanaja.
aur aesav ke putra aeleepaj ke timna nam aek suraaitin thee, jis ne aeleepaj ke janmaae amalek ko janm diya : aesav kee patnee ada ke vansh men ye hee hue.
aur rooael ke ye putra huae arthata nahat, jerah, shamma, aur mijja : aesav kee patnee basamat ke vansh men ye hee hue.
aur oholeebama jo aesav kee patnee, aur sibon kee naatinee aur ana kee bettee thee, usake ye putra huae : arthata us ne aesav ke janmaae yoosha, yalam aur korah ko janm diya.
aesavavanashaiyon ke aadhaipaati ye huae : arthata aesav ke jette aeleepaj ke vansh men se to teman aadhaipaati, omar aadhaipaati, sapo aadhaipaati, kanaj aadhaipaati,
korah adhaipaati, gatam aadhaipaati, amalekh adhaipaati : aeleepaj vanshaiyon me se, aedom desh men ye hee aadhaipaati huae : aur ye hee ada ke vansh men huae.
aur aesav ke putra rooael ke vansh men ye hue arthata nahat aadhaipaati, jerah aadhaipaati, shamma adhaipaati, mijja adhaipaati: rooaelavanshaiyon men se, aedom desh men ye hee aadhaipaati hue aur ye hee aesav kee patnee basamat ke vansh men huae.
aur aesav kee patnee oholeebama ke vansh men ye hue arthata yoosh adhaipaati, yalam aadhaipaati, korah aadhaipaati, ana kee bettee oholeebama jo aesav kee patnee thee usake vansh men ye hee huae.
aesav jo aedom bhee kahalata haai, usake vansh ye hee haai, aur unake adhaipaati bhee ye hee hue..
seir jo horee nam jaati ka tha usake ye putra us desh men pahile se rahate the arthata lotan, shaebal, shaibon, ana,
deeshaen, aeser, aur deeshaana aedom desh men seir ke ye hee horee jaativale adhaipaati hue.
aur lotan ke putra, horee, aur hemam huae aur lotan kee bahin timna thee.
aur shaebal ke ye putra hue arthata alvan, manahat, aebal, shapo, aur onama.
aur sidon ke ye putra hue arthata ayya, aur ana yah vahee ana haai jis ko jangal men apane pita sibon ke gadahon ko charate charate garam panee ke jhrane mile.
aur ana ke deeshaen nam putra hua, aur usee ana ke oholeebama nam bettee hui.
aur deeshaen ke ye putra hue arthata hemadan, aeshban, yitraan, aur karana.
aeser ke ye putra huae arthata bilhan, javan, aur akana.
deeshaan ke ye putra hue arthata us, aur akana.
horiyon ke aadhaipaati ye hue arthata lotan aadhaipaati, shaebal adhaipaati, shaibon aadhaipaati, ana aadhaipaati,
deeshaen aadhaipaati, aeser aadhaipaati, deeshaan adhaipaati, seir desh men horee jaativale ye hee adhaipaati hue.
fir jab israaeliyon par kisee raja ne rajy n kiya tha, tab bhee aedom ke desh men ye raja hue
arthata bor ke putra bela ne aedom men rajy kiya, aur usakee rajadhaanee ka nam dinhaba haai.
bela ke marane par, bosranivasee jerah ka putra yobab usake sthan par raja hua.
aur yobab ke marane par, temaniyon ke desh ka nivasee hooshaam usake sthan par raja hua.
aur hooshaam ke marane par, badad ka putra hadad usake sthan par raja hua : yah vahee haai jis ne midhaaniyon ko moab ke desh men mar liya, aur usakee rajadhaanee ka nam abeet haai.
aur hadad ke marane par, masrekavasee samla usake sthan par raja hua.
fir samla ke marane par, shaaul jo mahanad ke tattvale rahobot nagar ka tha, so usake sthan par raja hua.
aur shaaul ke marane par, akabor ka putra balhanan usake sthan par raja hua.
oholeebama aadhaipaati, aela aadhaipaati, peenon aadhaipaati,
kanaj adhaipaati, teman aadhaipaati, misabar adhaipaati,
magdeeael aadhaipaati, iram aadhaipaati: aedomavanshaiyon ne jo desh apana kar liya tha, usake nivasasthanon men unake ye hee aadhaipaati hue. aur aedomee jati ka moolapuroosh aesav haai..
yakoob to kanan desh men rahata tha, jahan usaka pita paradeshaee hokar raha tha.
aur yakoob ke vansh ka vrattant yah haai : ki yoosufa satarah varsha ka hokar bhaiyon ke sang bhed-bakaariyon ko charata tha aur vah ladka apane pita kee patnee bilha, aur jilpa ke putraen ke sang raha karata tha : aur unakee buraiyon ka samachar apane pita ke pas pahunchaya karata tha :
aur israael apane sab putraen se baddhke yoosufa se praeeti rakhta tha, kyonki vah usake buddhape ka putra tha : aur us ne usake liye rang biranga angarakha banavaya.
so jab usake bhaiyon ne dekha, ki hamara pita ham sab bhaiyon se aadhaik usee se praeeti rakhta haai, tab ve us se baair karane lage aur usake sath tteek taur se bat bhee naheen karate the.
aur yoosufa ne aek svapn dekha, aur apane bhaiyon se usaka varnn kiya : tab ve us se aur bhee desh karane lage.
aur us ne un se kaha, jo svapn maain ne dekha haai, so suno :
ham log khet men poole bandha rahe haai, aur kya dekhta hoon ki mera poola uttkar seedha khda ho gaya tab tumhare poolon ne mere poole ko charon tarafa se ghor liya aur use dandvata kiya.
tab usake bhaiyon ne us se kaha, kya sachamuch too hamare upar rajy karega ? va sachamuch too ham par prabhuta karega ? so ve usake svapnon aur usakee baton ke karan us se aur bhee adhaik baair karane lage.
fir us ne aek aur svapn dekha, aur apane bhaiyon se usaka bhee yon varnn kiya, ki suno, maain ne aek aur svapn dekha haai, ki soorya aur chandrama, aur gyarah tare mujhe dandvata kar rahe haain.
yah svapn us ne apane pita, aur bhaiyon se varnn kiya : tab usake pita ne usako dapattke kaha, yah kaaisa svapn haai jo too ne dekha haai? kya sachamuch maain aur teree mata aur tere bhai sab jakar tere age boomi par girake dandvata karenge?
usake bhai to usase dah karate the par usake pita ne usake us vachan ko smaran rakha.
aur usake bhai apane pita kee bhed-bakaariyon ko charane ke liye shakem ko gaae.
tab israael ne yoosufa se kaha, tere bhai to shakem hee men bhed-bakaree chara rahen honge, so ja, maain tujhe unake pas bhejata hoon. us ne us se kaha jo agyaa maain haajir hoon.
us ne us se kaha, ja, apane bhaiyon aur bhed-bakaariyon ka hal dekh a ki ve kushal se to haai, fir mere pas samachar le a. so us ne usako hebraen kee tarai men vida kar diya, aur vah shakem men aya.
aur kisee manushy ne usako maaidan meen idhar udhar bhttkate huae pakar us se poochha, too kya ddoonddhta haai?
us ne kaha, maain to apane bhaiyon ko ddoonddhta hoon : krapa kar mujhe bata, ki ve bhed-bakaariyon ko kahan chara rahe haain?
us manushy ne kaha, ve to yahan se chale gaae haain : aur maain ne unako yah kahate suna, ki ao, ham dotan ko chalen. so yoosufa apane bhaiyon ke pas chala, aur unhen dotan men paya.
aur jyonhee unhon ne use door se ate dekha, to usake nikatt ane ke pahile hee use mar dalane kee yuktai kee.
aur ve apas men kahane lage, dekho, vah svapn dekhnehara a raha haai.
so ao, ham usako ghaat karake kisee gadhe men dal de, aur yah kah denge, ki koi dushtt pashu usako kha gaya. fir ham dekhenge ki usake svapnon ka kya fal hoga.
yah sunake rooben ne usako unake hath se bachane kee manasa se kaha, ham usako praan se to n maren.
fir rooben ne un se kaha, lohoo mat bahao, usako jangal ke is gadhe men dal do, aur us par hath mat uttao. vah usako unake hath se chhudakar pita ke pas fir pahunchana chahata tha.
so aeesa hua, ki jab yoosufa apane bhaiyon ke pas pahuncha tab unhon ne usaka rangaabiranga angarakha, jise vah paahine huae tha, utar liya.
aur yoosufa ko uttakar gadhe men dal diya : vah gadha to sookha tha aur us men kuchh jal n tha.
tab ve rottee khane ko baaitt gaae : aur ankhe uttakar kya dekha, ki ishmaaeliyon ka aek dal untto par sugandhadravy, balasan, aur gandharas lade hua, gilad se misr ko chala ja raha haai.
ao, ham use ishmaaeliyon ke hath bech dale, aur apana hath us par n uttaae, kyonki vah hamara bhai aur hamaree haddee aur mans haai, so usake bhaiyon ne usakee bat man lee. tab midhanee vyaparee udhar se hokar unake pas pahunche :
aur rooben ne gadhe par lauttkar kya dekha, ki yoosufa gadhe men naheen haain so us ne apane vasr faade.
aur apane bhaiyon ke pas lauttkar kahane laga, ki ladka to naheen haain ab maain kidhar jaun ?
aur tab unhon ne yoosufa ka angarakha liya, aur aek bakare ko marake usake lohoo men use duba diya.
aur unhon ne us rang birange angarakhe ko apane pita ke pas bhejakar kahala diya ki yah ham ko mila haai, so dekhkar pahichan le, ki yah tere putra ka angarakha haai ki naheen.
us ne usako paahichan liya, aur kaha, han yah mere hee putra ka angarakha haai kisee dushtt pashu ne usako kha liya haai ni:sandeh yoosufa faad dala gaya haai.
tab yakoob ne apane vasr faade aur kamar men ttatt lapetta, aur apane putra ke liye bahut dinon tak vilap karata raha.
aur usake sab bette-bettyaien ne usako shaantai dene ka yatn kiya par usako shaantai n milee aur vah yahee kahata raha, maain to vilap karata hua apane putra ke pas adhaelok men utar jaunga. is prakar usaka pita usake liye rota hee raha.
aur midhaaniyon ne yoosufa ko misr men le jakar poteepar nam, firaun ke aek haakim, aur jalladon ke pradhaan, ke hath bech dala..
unheen dinon men aeesa hua, ki yahooda apane bhaiyon ke pas se chala gaya, aur heera nam ek adullamavasee puroosh ke pas dera kiya.
vahan yahooda ne shooa nam aek kananee puroosh kee bettee ko dekha aur usako byahakar usake pas gaya.
vah garbhvatee hui, aur usake aek putra utpann hua aur yahooda ne usaka nam aer rakha.
aur vah fir garbhvatee hui, aur usake aek putra utpann hua aur usaka nam onan rakha gaya.
fir usake aek putra aur utpann hua, aur usaka nam shola rakha gaya : aur jis samay isaka janm hua us samay yahooda kajeeb men rahata tha.
aur yahooda ne tamar nam aek sree se apane jette aer ka vivah kar diya.
parantu yahooda ka vah jetta aer yahova ke lekhe men dushtt tha, isaaliye yahova ne usako mar dala.
tab yahooda ne onan se kaha, apanee bhaujai ke pas ja, aur usake sath devar ka dharma poora karake apane bhai ke liye santan utpann kara.
onan to janata tha ki santan to meree n ttharegee: so aeesa hua, ki jab vah apanee bhaujai ke pas gaya, tab us ne boomi par veerya girakar nash kiya, jis se aeesa n ho ki usake bhai ke nam se vansh chale.
yah kam jo us ne kiya use yahova aprasann hua: aur us ne usako bhee mar dala.
tab yahooda ne is dr ke mare, ki kaheen aeesa n ho ki apane bhaiyon kee nai shola bhee mare, apanee bahoo tamar se kaha, jab tak mera putra shola siyana n ho tab tak apane pita ke ghar men vidhava kee baaittee rah, so tamar apane pita ke ghar men jakar rahane lagee.
bahut samay ke beetane par yahooda kee patnee jo shooa kee bettee thee so mar gai fir yahooda shaek se choottkar apane mitra heera adullamavasee samet apanee bhed-bakaariyon ka un katarane ke liye timnath ko gaya.
aur tamar ko yah samachar mila, ki tera sasur apanee bhed-bakaariyon ka un katarane ke liye timnath ko ja raha haai.
tab us ne yah sochakar, ki shola siyana to ho gaya par maain usakee sree naheen hone pai apana vidhavapan ka paahirava utara, aur ghoonghatt dalakar apane ko ddhanp liya, aur aenaaim nagar ke faattk ke pas, jo timnath ke marga men haai, ja baaittee:
jab yahooda ne usako dekha, us ne us ko veshya samajha kyonaki vah apana munh ddhape huae thee.
aur vah marga se usakee or fira aur us se kahane laga, mujhe apane pas ane de, kyonaki use yah maloom n tha ki vah usakee bahoo haai. aur vah kahane lagee, ki yadi maain tujhe apane pas ane doo, to too mujhe kya dega?
us ne kaha, maain apanee bakariyon men se bakaree ka ek bachcha tere pas bhej doonga.
us ne poochha, maain tere pas kya rehan rakh jaun? us ne kaha, apanee muhar, aur bajooband, aur apane hath kee chhdee. tab us ne usako ve vasatuen de dee, aur usake pas gaya, aur vah us se garbhvatee hui.
tab vah uttkar chalee gai, aur apana ghoonghatt utarake apana vidhavapan ka paahirava fir pahin liya.
tab us ne vahan ke logon se poochha, ki vah devadasee jo aenaaim men marga kee aek aur baaittee thee, kahan haai? unhon ne kaha, yahan to koi devadasee n thee.
so us ne yahooda ke pas lauttke kaha, mujhe vah naheen milee aur us sthan ke logon ne kaha, ki yahan to koi devadasee n thee.
aur teen maheene ke peechhe yahooda ko yah samachar mila, ki teree bahoo tamar ne vyabhaichar kiya haai varan vah vyabhaichar se garbhvatee bhee ho gai haai. tab yahooda ne kaha, usako bahar le ao, ki vah jalai jaae.
jab use bahar nikal rahe the, tab us ne, apane sasur ke pas yah kahala bheja, ki jis puroosh kee ye vastuen haai, usee se maain garbhvatee hoon fir us ne yah bhee kahalaya, ki pahichan to sahee, ki yah muhar, aur vajooband, aur chhdee kis kee haai.
yahooda ne unhen pahichanakar kaha, vah to mujh se kam doshaee haai kyonki maain ne use apane putra shola ko n byah diya. aur us ne us se fir kabhee prasang n kiya.
jab usake janane ka samay aya, tab yah jan pada ki usake garbh men judve bachche haain.
aur jab vah janane lagee tab aek balak ne apana hath baddhaya: aur dhaay ne lal soot lekar usake hath men yah kahate huye bandha diya, ki pahile yahee utpann hua.
jab us ne hath samett liya, tab usaka bhai utpann ho gaya: tab us dhaay ne kaha, too kyon barabas nikal aya haai ? isaliye usaka nam peres rakha gaya.
peechhe usaka bhai jisake hath men lal soot bandha tha utpann hua, aur usaka nam jerah rakha gaya..
jab yoosufa misr men pahunchaya gaya, tab poteepar nam aek misree, jo firaun ka haakim, aur jalladon ka pradhaan tha, us ne usako ishmaaeliyon ke hat, se jo use vahan le gaae the, mol liya.
aur yoosufa apane misree svamee ke ghar men rahata tha, aur yahova usake sang tha so vah bhagyavana puroosh ho gaya.
aur yoosufa ke svamee ne dekha, ki yahova usake sang rahata haai, aur jo kam vah karata haai usako yahova usake hath se sufal kar deta haai.
tab usakee anugrah kee draashtti us par hui, aur vah usakee seva tthal karane ke liye niyukt kiya gaya : fir us ne usako apane ghar ka adhaikaree banake apana sab kuchh usake hath men saup diya.
aur jab se us ne usako apane ghar ka aur apanee saree sampati ka adhaikaree banaya, tab se yahova yoosufa ke karan us misree ke ghar par ashaeesh dene laga aur kya ghar me, kya maaidan me, usaka jo kuchh tha, sab par yahova kee ashaeesh hone lagee.
so us ne apana sab kuchh yoosufa ke hath men yahan tak chhod diya: ki apane khane kee rottee ko chhod, vah apanee sampati ka hal kuchh n janata tha. aur yoosufa sundar aur roopavana tha.
in baton ke pashchata aeesa hua, ki usake svamee kee patnee ne yoosufa kee or ankh lagai aur kaha, mere sath so.
par us ne asveekar karate huae apane svamee kee patnee se kaha, sun, jo kuchh is ghar men haai mere hath men haai use mera svamee kuchh naheen janata, aur us ne apana sab kuchh mere hath men saup diya haai.
is ghar men mujh se bada koi naheen aur us ne tujhe chhod, jo usakee patnee haai mujh se kuchh naheen rakh chhoda so bhla, maain aeesee badee dushttta karake parameshvar ka aparadhaee kyonkar banoon ?
aur aeesa hua, ki vah prati din yoosufa se baten karatee rahee, par us ne usakee n manee, ki usake pas lette va usake sang rahe.
aek din kya hua, ki yoosufa apana kam kaj karane ke liye ghar men gaya, aur ghar ke sevakon men se koi bhee ghar ke andar n tha.
tab us sree ne usaka vasr pakadkar kaha, mere sath so, par vah apana vasr usake hath men chhodkar bhaga, aur bahar nikal gaya.
yah dekhkar, ki vah apana vasr mere hath men chhodkar bahar bhag gaya,
us sree ne apane ghar ke sevakon ko bulakar kaha, dekho, vah ek ibraee manushy ko hamara tiraskar karane ke liye hamare pas le aya haai. vah to mere sath sone ke matalab se mere pas andar aya tha aur maain unche svar se chilla uttee.
aur meree badee chillahatt sunakar vah apana vasr mere pas chhodkar bhaga, aur bahar nikal gaya.
aur vah usaka vasr usake svamee ke ghar ane tak apane pas rakhe rahee.
tab us ne us se is prakar kee baten kahee, ki vah ibraee das jisako too hamare pas le aya haai, so mujh se hansee karane ke liye mere pas aya tha.
aur jab maain unche svar se chilla uttee, tab vah apana vasr mere pas chhodkar bahar bhag gaya.
apanee patnee kee ye baten sunakar, ki tere das ne mujh se aeesa aeesa kam kiya, yoosufa ke svamee ka kop bhdka.
par yahova yoosufa ke sang sang raha, aur us par karoona kee, aur bandeegrah ke daroga ke anugrah kee draashtti us par hui.
so bandeegrah ke daroga ne un sab bandhauon ko, jo karagar men the, yoosufa ke hath men saup diya aur jo jo kam ve vahan karate the, vah usee kee agyaa se hota tha.
bandeegrah ke daroga ke vash men jo kuchh tha kyonaki us men se usako koi bhee vastu dekhnee n padtee thee isaliye ki yahova yoosufa ke sath tha aur jo kuchh vah karata tha, yahova usako us men safalata deta tha.
sree ne sarpa se kaha, is baattkai ke vrakshaen ke fal ham kha sakate haain.
par jo vraksha battkai ke beech men haai, usake fal ke vishay men parameshvar ne kaha haai ki n to tum usako khana aur n usako choona, naheen to mar jaoge.
tab sarpa ne sree se kaha, tum nishchay n maroge,
varan parameshvar ap janata haai, ki jis din tum usaka fal khaoge usee din tumharee ankhe khul jaaengee, aur tum bhle bure ka gyaan pakar parameshvar ke tuly ho jaoge.
so jab sree ne dekha ki us vraksha ka fal khane men achchha, aur dekhne men manabha, aur buddh idene ke liye chahane yogy bhee haai, tab us ne us men se todkar khaya aur apane pati ko bhee diya, aur us ne bhee khaya.
tab un donon kee ankhe khul gai, aur unako maloom hua ki ve nange haai so unhon ne anjeer ke patte jod jod kar langott bana liye.
tab yahova parameshvar jo din ke ttnde samay baattkai men firata tha usaka shabd unako sunai diya. tab adam aur usakee patnee battkai ke vrakshaen ke beech yahova parameshvar se chhpai gaae.
tab yahova parameshvar ne pukarakar adam se poochha, too kahan haai?
us ne kaha, maain tera shabd baree men sunakar dr gaya kyonaki maain nanga tha isaliye chhpai gaya.
us ne kaha, kis ne tujhe chitaya ki too nanga haai? jis vraksha ka fal khane ko maai ne tujhe barja tha, kya too ne usaka fal khaya haai?
adam ne kaha jis sree ko too ne mere sang rahane ko diya haai usee ne us vraksha ka fal mujhe diya, aur maai ne khaya.
tab yahova parameshvar ne sree se kaha, too ne yah kya kiya haai? sree ne kaha, sarpa ne mujhe bahaka diya tab maai ne khaya.
tab yahova parameshvar ne sarpa se kaha, too ne jo yah kiya haai isaliye too sab ghareloo pashuuo, aur sab banaaile pashuuon se adhaik shaaapit haai too pett ke bal chala karega, aur jeevan bhr mittee chattta rahega :
aur maai tere aur is sree ke beech me, aur tere vansh aur isake vansh ke beech men baair utpann karunga, vah tere sir ko kuchal dalega, aur too usakee aedee ko dsega.
fir sree se us ne kaha, maai teree peeda aur tere garbhvatee hone ke du:kh ko bahut baddhaunga too peedit hokar balak utpann karegee aur teree lalasa tere paati kee or hogee, aur vah tujh par prabhuta karega.
aur adam se us ne kaha, too ne jo apanee patnee kee bat sunee, aur jis vraksha ke fal ke vishay maai ne tujhe agyaa dee thee ki too use n khana usako too ne khaya haai, isaliye boomi tere karan shaaapit haai: too usakee upaj jeevan bhr du:kh ke sath khaya karega :
aur vah tere liye kantte aur unttkattare ugaaegee, aur too khet kee upaj khaaega
aur apane mathe ke paseene kee rottee khaya karega, aur ant men mittee men mil jaaega kyonaki too usee men se nikala gaya haai, too mittee to haai aur mittee hee men fir mil jaaega.
aur adam ne apanee patnee ka nam havva rakha kyonaki jitane manushy jeevit haain un sab kee aadimata vahee hui.
aur yahova parameshvar ne adam aur usakee patnee ke liye chamade ke angarakhe banakar unako pahina diae.
fir yahova parameshvar ne kaha, manushy bhle bure ka gyaan pakar ham men se aek ke saman ho gaya haai: isaliye ab aeesa n ho, ki vah hath baddhakar jeevan ke vraksha ka fal bhee tod ke kha le aur sada jeeavit rahe.
tab yahova parameshvar ne usako adan kee battkai men se nikal diya ki vah us boomi par khetee kare jis me se vah banaya gaya tha.
isaliye adam ko us ne nikal diya aur jeevan ke vraksha ke marga ka pahara dene ke liye adan kee battkai ke poorva kee or karubon ko, aur charon or ghoomanevalee jvalamay talavar ko bhee niyukt kar diya..
in baton ke pashchata aeesa hua, ki misr ke raja ke pilanehare aur pakanehare ne apane svamee ka kuchh aparadha kiya.
tab firaun ne apane un donon hakimon par, arthata pilanehare ke pradhaan, aur pakaneharon ke pradhaan par krodhait hokar
tab jalladon ke pradhaan ne unako yoosufa ke hath saupa, aur vah unakee seva tthal karane laga: so ve kuchh din tak bandeegrah men rahe.
aur misr ke raja ka pilanehara aur pakanehara, jo bandeegrah men band the, un donon ne aek hee rat me, apane apane honahar ke anusar, svapn dekha.
bihan ko jab yoosufa unake pas andar gaya, tab un par us ne jo drashtti kee, to kya dekhta haai, ki ve udas haain.
so us ne firaun ke un haakimon se, jo usake sath usake svamee ke ghar ke bandeegrah men the, poochha, ki aj tumhare munh kyon udas haain ?
tab pilaneharon ka pradhaan apana svapn yoosufa ko yon batane laga: ki maain ne svapn men dekha, ki mere samhane aek dakhlata haai
aur us dakhlata men teen daliyan haain: aur us men mano kaliyan lageen haai, aur ve fooleen aur usake guchchhon men dakh lagakar pak gai.
aur firaun ka kattora mere hath men tha: so maai ne un dakhon ko lekar firaun ke kattore men nichoda aur kattore ko firaun ke hath men diya.
yoosufa ne us se kaha, isaka fal yah haai ki teen daliyon ka arth teen din haai:
so ab se teen din ke bheetar firaun tera sir uncha karega, aur fir se tere pad par tujhe niyukt karega, aur too pahale kee nai firaun ka pilanehara hokar usaka kattora usake hath men fir diya karega.
so jab tera bhla ho jaae tab mujhe smaran karana, aur mujh par krapa karake, firaun se meree charcha chalana, aur is ghar se mujhe chhudva dena.
kyonaki sachamuch ibraaniyon ke desh se mujhe chura kar le aae haai, aur yahan bhee maai ne koi aeesa kam naheen kiya, jisake karan maain is karagar men dala jaun.
yah dekhkar, ki usake svapn ka fal achchha nikala, pakaneharon ke pradhaan ne yoosufa se kaha, maain ne bhee svapn dekha haai, vah yah haai: maai ne dekha, ki mere sir par safaed rottee kee teen ttokaariyan haai:
aur upar kee ttokaree men firaun ke liye sab prakar kee pakee pakai vastuaen haain aur pakshaee mere sir par kee ttokaree men se un vastuon ko kha rahe haain.
yoosufa ne kaha, isaka fal yah haai ki teen ttokaariyon ka arth teen din haai.
so ab se teen din ke bheetar firaun tera sir kattvakar tujhe aek vraksha par ttngava dega, aur pakshaee tere mans ko noch noch kar khaaenge.
aur teesare din firaun ka janmaadin tha, us ne apane sab karmachariyon kee jevanar kee, aur un men se pilaneharon ke pradhaan, aur pakaneharon ke pradhaan donon ko bandeegrah se nikalavaya.
aur pilaneharon ke pradhaan ko to pilanehare ke pad par fir se niyukt kiya, aur vah firaun ke hath men kattora dene laga.
par pakaneharon ke pradhaan ko us ne ttngava diya, jaaisa ki yoosufa ne unake svapnon ka fal un se kaha tha.
fir bhee pilaneharon ke pradhaan ne yoosufa ko smaran n rakha parantu use bool gaya..
poore do baras ke beetane par firaun ne yah svapn dekha, ki vah neel nadee ke kinare par khda haai.
aur us nadee men se sat sundar aur mottee mottee gayen nikalakar kachhar kee ghaas charane lageen.
aur, kya dekha, ki unake peechhe aur sat gaye, jo kuroop aur durbal haai, nadee se nikalee aur doosaree gayon ke nikatt nadee ke tatt par ja khdee hui.
tab ye kuroop aur durbal gayen un sat sundar aur mottee mottee gayon ko kha gai. tab firaun jag utta.
aur vah fir so gaya aur doosara svapn dekha, ki aek dnttee men se sat mottee aur achchhee achchhee balen nikaleen.
aur, kya dekha, ki unake peechhe sat balen patalee aur puravai se murajhai hui nikaleen.
aur in patalee balon ne un saton mottee aur ann se bhree hui balon ko nigal liya. tab firaun jaga, aur use maloom hua ki yah svapn hee tha.
bhor ko firaun ka man vyakul hua aur us ne misr ke sab jyotishaiyo, aur panditon ko bulava bheja aur unako apane svapn bataaen par un men se koi bhee unaka fal firaun se n kah saha.
tab pilaneharon ka pradhaan firaun se bol utta, ki mere aparadha aj mujhe smaran aae:
tab ham donon ne, aek hee rat me, apane apane honahar ke anusar svapn dekha
aur vahan hamare sath aek ibraee javan tha, jo jalladon ke pradhaan ka das tha so ham ne usako bataya, aur us ne hamare svapnon ka fal ham se kaha, ham men se aek aek ke svapn ka fal us ne bata diya.
aur jaaisa jaaisa fal us ne ham se kaha tha, vaaisa kee hua bhee, arthata mujh ko to mera pad fir mila, par vah faansee par lattkaya gaya.
tab firaun ne yoosufa ko bulava bheja. aur vah jhttpatt bandeegrah se bahar nikala gaya, aur bal banavakar, aur vasr badalakar firaun ke samhane aya.
