sun, sare misr desh men sat varsha to bahutayat kee upaj ke honge.
unake pashchata sat varsha akal ke ayenge, aur sare misr desh men log is saree upaj ko bool jayenge aur akal se desh ka nash hoga.
aur sukal bahutayat kee upaja desh men fir smaran n rahega kyonaki akal atyant bhyankar hoga.
aur firaun ne jo yah svapn do bar dekha haai isaka bhed yahee haai, ki yah bat parameshvar kee or se niyukt ho chukee haai, aur parameshvar ise shaeegha hee poora karega.
