so firaun ne apane karmachaariyon se kaha, ki kya ham ko aeesa puroosh jaaisa yah haai, jis men parameshvar ka atma rahata haai, mil sakata haai ?
fir firaun ne yoosufa se kaha, parameshvar ne jo tujhe itana gyaan diya haai, ki tere tuly koi samajhdar aur buddhmaiana naheen
