aur misr desh ke sukal ke ve sat varsha samapt ho gaae.
aur yoosufa ke kahane ke anusar sat vasharen ke liye akal arambh ho gaya. aur sab deshaen men akal padne laga parantu sare misr desh men ann tha.
jab misr ka sara desh bookhon marane laga tab praja firon se chilla chillakar rottee mangane lagee : aur vah sab misriyon se kaha karata tha, yoosufa ke pas jao: aur jo kuchh vah tum se kahe, vahee karo.
so jab akal saree prathvee par faail gaya, aur misr desh men kal ka bhyankar roop ho gaya, tab yoosufa sab bhndaron ko khol kholake misriyon ke hath ann bechane laga.
so saree prathvee ke log misr men ann mol lene ke liye yoosufa ke pas ane lage, kyonaki saree prathvee par bhyankar akal tha.
jab yakoob ne suna ki misr men ann haai, tab us ne apane putraen se kaha, tum aek doosare ka munh kyon dekh rahe ho.
fir us ne kaha, maain ne suna haai ki misr men ann haai isaaliye tum log vahan jakar hamare liye ann mol le ao, jis se ham n mare, varan jeeavit rahen.
so yoosufa ke das bhai ann mol lene ke liye misr ko gaae.
par yoosufa ke bhai binyameen ko yakoob ne yah sochakar bhaiyon ke sath n bheja, ki kaheen aeesa n ho ki us par koi vipaati a pade.
so jo log ann mol lene aae unake sath israael ke putra bhee aae kyonki kanan desh men bhee bharee akal tha.
yoosufa to misr desh ka aadhaikaree tha, aur us desh ke sab logon ke hath vahee ann bechata tha isaaliye jab yoosufa ke bhai aae tab boomi par munh ke bal girake dandvata kiya.
unako dekhkar yoosufa ne paahichan to liya, parantu unake samhane bhola banake kattorata ke sath un se poochha, tum kahan se ate ho? unhon ne kaha, ham to kanan desh se ann mol lene ke liye aae haain.
yoosufa ne to apane bhaiyon ko paahichan liya, parantu unhon ne usako n paahichana.
tab yoosufa apane un svapnon ko smaran karake jo us ne unake vishay men dekhe the, un se kahane laga, tum bheadiae ho is desh kee durdasha ko dekhne ke liye aae ho.
unhon ne us se kaha, nahee, nahee, he prabhu, tere das bhojanavastu mol lene ke liye aae haain.
ham sab aek hee pita ke putra haai, ham seedho manushy haai, tere das bheadiae naheen.
us ne un se kaha, naheen nahee, tum is desh kee durdasha dekhne hee ko aae ho.
tab yoosufa ne un se kaha, maain ne to tum se kah diya, ki tum bhediae ho
so isee reeti se tum parakhe jaoge, firaun ke jeevan kee shapat, jab tak tumhara chhotta bhai yahan n aae tab tak tum yahan se n nikalane paoge.
so apane men se aek ko bhej do, ki vah tumhare bhai ko le aa, aur tum log bandhauvai men rahoge is prakar tumharee baten parakhee jaaengee, ki tum men sachchai haai ki naheen. yadi sachche n tthare tab to firaun ke jeevan kee shapath tum nishchay hee bhediae samajhe jaoge.
tab us ne unako teen din tak bandeegrah men rakha.
teesare din yoosufa ne un se kaha, aek kam karo tab jeevit rahoge kyonki maain parameshvar ka bhy manata hoon
yaadi tum seedho manushy ho, to tum sab bhaiyon men se aek jan is bandeegrah men bandhaua rahe aur tum apane gharavalon kee bookh bujhane ke liye ann le jao.
aur apane chhotte bhai ko mere pas le ao is prakar tumharee baten sachchee ttharengee, aur tum mar dale n jaoge. tab unhon ne vaaisa hee kiya.
rooben ne un se kaha, kya maain ne tum se n kaha tha, ki ladke ke aparadhaee mat bano? parantu tum ne n suna : dekho, ab usake lohoo ka palatta diya jata haai.
yoosufa kee aur unakee batacheet jo aek dubhashaiya ke dara hotee thee is se unako maloom n hua ki vah unakee bolee samajhta haai.
tab vah unake pas se hattkar rone laga fir unake pas lauttkar aur un se batacheet karake un men se shaimon ko chhantt nikala aur usake samhane bandhaua rakha.
tab yoosufa ne agyaa dee, ki unake bore ann se bhro aur aek aek jan ke bore men usake roopaye ko bhee rakh do, fir unako marga ke liye seedha do : so unake sath aeesa hee kiya gaya.
tab ve apana ann apane gadahon par ladakar vahan se chal diae.
saray men jab aek ne apane gadahe ko chara dene ke liye apana bora khola, tab usaka roopaya bore ke mohade par rakha hua dikhlai pada.
tab us ne apane bhaiyon se kaha, mera roopaya to faer diya gaya haai, dekho, vah mere bore men haai tab unake jee men jee n raha, aur ve aek doosare kee aur bhy se takane lage, aur bole, parameshvar ne yah ham se kya kiya haai ?
aur ve kanan desh men apane pita yakoob ke pas aa, aur apana sara vrattant us se is prakar varnn kiya :
ki jo puroosh us desh ka svamee haai, us ne ham se kattorata ke sath baten kee, aur ham ko desh ke bheadiae kaha.
tab ham ne us se kaha, ham seedho log haai, bhediae naheen.
ham barah bhai aek hee pita ke putra haai, aek to jata raha, parantu chhotta is samay kanan desh men hamare pita ke pas haai.
tab us puroosh ne, jo us desh ka svamee haai, ham se kaha, is se maloom ho jaaega ki tum seedho manushy ho tum apane men se aek ko mere pas chhodke apane gharavalon kee bookh bujhane ke liye kuchh le jao.
aur apane chhotte bhai ko mere pas le ao. tab mujhe vishvas ho jaaega ki tum bhediae nahee, seedho log ho. fir maain tumhare bhai ko tumhen saunp doonga, aur tum is desh men len den kar sakoge.
yah kahakar ve apane apane bore se ann nikalane lage, tab, kya dekha, ki aek aek jan ke roopaye kee thailee usee ke bore men rakhee haai : tab roopaye kee thaialiyon ko dekhkar ve aur unaka pita bahut dr gaae.
tab unake pita yakoob ne un se kaha, mujh ko tum ne nirvansh kar diya, dekho, yoosufa naheen raha, aur shaimon bhee naheen aya, aur ab tum binyameen ko bhee le jana chahate ho : ye sab vipaatiayan mere upar a padee haain.
rooben ne apane pita se kaha, yadi maain usako tere pas n lau, to mere donon putraen ko mar dalana too usako mere hath men saunp de, maain use tere pas fir pahuncha doonga.
us ne kaha, mera putra tumhare sang n jaega kyonki usaka bhai mar gaya haai, aur vah ab akela rah gaya : isaliye jis marga se tum jaoge, us men yaadi us par koi vipaati a pade, tab to tumhare karan maain is buddhape kee avastha men shaek ke sath adhaelok men utar jaunga..
aur akal desh men aur bhee bhyankar hota gaya.
jab vah ann jo ve misr se le aae the samapt ho gaya tab unake pita ne un se kaha, fir jakar hamare liye thodee see bhojanavastu mol le ao.
tab yahooda ne us se kaha, us puroosh ne ham ko chitavanee dekar kaha, ki yadi tumhara bhai tumhare sang n aa, to tum mere sammukh n ane paoge.
isaliye yaadi too hamare bhai ko hamare sang bheje, tab to ham jakar tere liye bhojanavastu mol le aaenge
tab israael ne kaha, tum ne us puroosh ko yah batakar ki hamara aek aur bhai haai, kyon mujh se bura bartav kiya ?
unhon ne kaha, jab us puroosh ne hamaree aur hamare kuttuambaiyon kee dasha ko is reeti poochha, ki kya tumhara pita ab tak jeeavit haai? kya tumhare koi aur bhai bhee haai ? tab ham ne in prashnon ke anusar us se varnn kiya fir ham kya janate the ki vah kahega, ki apane bhai ko yahan le ao.
fir yahooda ne apane pita israael se kaha, us ladke ko mere sang bhej de, ki ham chale jaaen is se ham, aur to, aur hamare balabachche marane n paaenge, varan jeevit rahenge.
maain usaka jamin hota hoon mere hee hath se too usako faer lena: yaadi maain usako tere pas pahunchakar samhane n khdakar doo, tab to maain sada ke liye tera aparadhaee ttharoonga.
yaadi ham log vilamb n karate, to ab tab doosaree bar lautt ate.
tab unake pita israael ne un se kaha, yaadi sachamuch aeesee hee bat haai, to yah karo is desh kee uttm uttm vastuon men se kuchh kuchh apane boron men us puroosh ke liye bhentt le jao : jaaise thoda sa balasan, aur thoda sa madha, aur kuchh sugandha dravy, aur gandharas, piste, aur badama.
fir apane apane sath doona roopaya le jao aur jo roopaya tumhare boron ke munh par rakhkar faer diya gaya tha, usako bhee lete jao kadaachita yah bool se hua ho.
aur apane bhai ko bhee sang lekar us puroosh ke pas fir jao,
tab un manushyon ne vah bhent, aur doona roopaya, aur binyameen ko bhee sang liya, aur chal diae aur misr men pahunchakar yoosufa ke samhane khde huae.
unake sath binyameen ko dekhkar yoosufa ne apane ghar ke aadhaikaree se kaha, un manushyon ko ghar men pahuncha do, aur pashu marake bhojan taaiyar karo kyonki ve log dopahar ko mere sang bhojan karenge.
tab vah aadhaikaree puroosh yoosufa ke kahane ke anusar un purooshaen ko yoosufa ke ghar men le gaya.
jab ve yoosufa ke ghar ko pahunchaae gaae tab ve apas men drakar kahane lage, ki jo roopaya pahilee bar hamare boron men faer diya gaya tha, usee ke karan ham bheetar pahunchaae gaae haain jis se ki vah puroosh ham par toott pade, aur hamen vansh men karake apane das banaa, aur hamare gadahon ko bhee chheen le.
tab ve yoosufa ke ghar ke aadhaikaree ke nikatt jakar ghar ke dar par is prakar kahane lage,
ki he hamare prabhu, jab ham paahilee bar ann mol lene ko aae the,
tab ham ne saray men pahunchakar apane boron ko khola, to kya dekha, ki aek aek jan ka poora poora roopaya usake bore ke munh men rakha haai isaaliye ham usako apane sath fir lete aae haain.
aur doosara roopaya bhee bhojanavastu mol lene ke liye laae haain ham naheen janate ki hamara roopaya hamare boron men kis ne rakh diya tha.
us ne kaha, tumhara kushal ho, mat dro: tumhara parameshvar, jo tumhare pita ka bhee parameshvar haai, usee ne tum ko tumhare boron men dhan diya hoga, tumhara roopaya to mujh ko mil gaya tha: fir us ne shaimon ko nikalakar unake sang kar diya.
tab us jan ne un manushyon ko yoosufa ke ghar men le jakar jal diya, tab unhon ne apane panvon ko dhaeya fir us ne unake gadahon ke liye chara diya.
tab yah sunakar, ki aj ham ko yaheen bhojan karana hoga, unhon ne yoosufa ke ane ke samay tak, arthata dopahar tak, us bhentt ko ikattha kar rakha.
jab yoosufa ghar aya tab ve us bhentt ko, jo unake hath men thee, usake sammukh ghar men le gaa, aur boomi par girakar usako dandvata kiya.
us ne unaka kushal poochha, aur kaha, kya tumhara booddha pita, jisakee tum ne charcha kee thee, kushal se haai ? kya vah ab tak jeevit haai ?
unhon ne kaha, han tera das hamara pita kushal se haai aur ab tak jeevit haai tab unhon ne sir jhukakar fir dandvata kiya.
tab us ne ankhe uttakar aur apane sage bhai binyameen ko dekhkar poochha, kya tumhara vah chhotta bhai, jisakee charcha tum ne mujh se kee thee, yahee haai ? fir us ne kaha, he mere putra, parameshvar tujh par anugrah kare.
tab apane bhai ke sneh se man bhr ane ke karan aur yah sochakar, ki maain kahan jakar rou, yoosufa faurtee se apanee kottree men gaya, aur vahan ro pada.
fir apana munh dhaekar nikal aya, aur apane ko shaant kar kaha, bhojan paroso.
tab unhon ne usake liye to alag, aur bhaiyon ke liye bhee alag, aur jo misree usake sang khate the, unake liye bhee alag, bhojan parosa isaaliye ki misree iabiryon ke sath bhojan naheen kar sakate, varan misree aeesa karana gharana samajhte the.
so yoosufa ke bhai usake samhane, bade bade paahile, aur chhotte chhotte peechhe, apanee apanee avastha ke anusar, kram se baaittaae gaae: yah dekh ve vismaita hokar aek doosare kee or dekhne lage.
tab yoosufa apane samhane se bhojana-vastuen utta uttake unake pas bhejane laga, aur binyameen ko apane bhaiyon se pachagunee adhaik bhojanavastu milee. aur unhon ne usake sang manamana khaya piya.
aur mera chandee ka kattora chhotte ke bore ke munh par usake ann ke roopaye ke sath rakh de. yoosufa kee is agyaa ke anusar us ne kiya.
bihan ko bhor hote hee ve manushy apane gadahon samet vida kiae gaae.
ve nagar se nikale hee the, aur door n jane paae the, ki yoosufa ne apane ghar ke adhaikaree se kaha, un manushyon ka peechha kar, aur unako pakar un se kah, ki tum ne bhlai kee santee burai kyon kee haai?
kya yah vah vastu naheen jis men mera svamee peeta haai, aur jis se vah shakun bhee vichara karata haai ? tum ne yah jo kiya haai so bura kiya.
tab us ne unhen ja liya, aur aeesee hee baten un se kaheen.
unhon ne us se kaha, he hamare prabhu, too aeesee baten kyon kahata haai? aeesa kam karana tere dason se door rahe.
dekh jo roopaya hamare boron ke munh par nikala tha, jab ham ne usako kanan desh se le akar tujhe faer diya, tab, bhla, tere svamee ke ghar men se ham koi chandee va sone kee vastu kyonkar chura sakate haain ?
tere dason men se jis kisee ke pas vah nikale, vah mar dala jaa, aur ham bhee apane us prabhu ke das jo jaaen.
us ne kaha tumhara hee kahana sahee, jisake pas vah nikale so mera das hoga aur tum log niraparadha ttharoge.
tab vah ddoonddhne laga, aur bade ke bore se lekar chhotte ke bore tak khoj kee : aur kattora binyameen ke bore men mila.
tab unhon ne apane apane vasr faade, aur apana apana gadaha ladakar nagar ko lautt gaae.
jab yahooda aur usake bhai yoosufa ke ghar par pahunche, aur yoosufa vaheen tha, tab ve usake samhane boomi par gire.
yoosufa ne un se kaha, tum logon ne yah kaaisa kam kiya haai ? kya tum n janate the, ki mujh sa manushy shakun vichar sakata haai ?
yahooda ne kaha, ham log apane prabhu se kya kahen ? ham kya kahakar apane ko nirdoshaee ttharaaen ? parameshvar ne tere dason ke adharma ko pakad liya haai : ham, aur jisake pas kattora nikala vah bhee, ham sab ke sab apane prabhu ke das hee haain.
us ne kaha, aeesa karana mujh se door rahe : jis jan ke pas kattora nikala haai, vahee mera das hoga aur tum log apane pita ke pas kushal kshom se chale jao.
tab yahooda usake pas jakar kahane laga, he mere prabhu, tere das ko apane prabhu se aek bat kahane kee agyaa ho, aur tera kop tere das par n bhdke too to firaun ke tuly haai.
mere prabhu ne apane dason se poochha tha, ki kya tumhare pita va bhai haain ?
aur ham ne apane prabhu se kaha, ha, hamara booddha pita to haai, aur usake buddhape ka aek chhotta sa balak bhee haai, parantu usaka bhai mar gaya haai, isaaliye vah ab apanee mata ka akela hee rah gaya haai, aur usaka pita us se sneh rakhta haai.
tab too ne apane dason se kaha tha, ki usako mere pas le ao, jis se maain usako dekoon.
tab ham ne apane prabhu se kaha tha, ki vah ladka apane pita ko naheen chhod sakata naheen to usaka pita mar jaaega.
aur too ne apane dason se kaha, yaadi tumhara chhotta bhai tumhare sang n aa, to tum mere sammukh fir n ane paoge.
so jab ham apane pita tere das ke pas gaa, tab ham ne us se apane prabhu kee baten kaheen.
tab hamare pita ne kaha, fir jakar hamare liye thodee see bhojanavastu mol le ao.
ham ne kaha, ham naheen ja sakate, ha, yadi hamara chhotta bhai hamare sang rahe, tab ham jaaenge : kyonaki yadi hamara chhotta bhai hamare sang n rahe, to us puroosh ke sammukh n jane paaenge.
tab tere das mere pita ne ham se kaha, tum to janate ho ki meree sree se do putra utpann huae.
aur un men se aek to mujhe chhod hee gaya, aur maain ne nishchay kar liya, ki vah faad dala gaya hoga aur tab se maain usaka munh n dekh paya
so yaadi tum isako bhee meree ankh kee ad men le jao, aur koi vipaati is par pade, to tumhare karan maain is pakke bal kee avastha men du:kh ke sath adhaelok men utar jaunga.
so jab maain apane pita tere das ke pas pahunchoo, aur yah ladka sang n rahe, tab, usaka praan jo isee par attka rahata haai,
fir tera das apane pita ke yahan yah kahake is ladke ka jaamin hua haai, ki yadi maain isako tere pas n pahuncha doo, tab to maain sada ke liye tera aparadhaee ttharoonga.
so ab tera das is ladke kee santee apane prabhu ka das hokar rahane kee agyaa paa, aur yah ladka apane bhaiyon ke sang jane diya jaae.
kyonaki ladke ke bina sang rahe maain kayonkar apane pita ke pas ja sakoonga aeesa n ho ki mere pita par jo du:kh padega vah mujhe dekhna pade..
tab yoosufa un sab ke samhane, jo usake as pas khde the, apane ko aur rok n saka aur pukar ke kaha, mere as pas se sab logon ko bahar kar do. bhaiyon ke samhane apane ko pragatt karane ke samay yoosufa ke sang aur koi n raha.
tab vah chilla chillakar rone laga : aur misriyon ne suna, aur firaun ke ghar ke logon ko bhee isaka samachar mila.
tab yoosufa apane bhaiyon se kahane laga, maain yoosufa hoo, kya mera pita ab tab jeeavit haai ? isaka uttr usake bhai n de sake kyonaki ve usake samhane ghabara gaae the.
fir yoosufa ne apane bhaiyon se kaha, mere nikatt ao. yah sunakar ve nikatt gaae. fir us ne kaha, maain tumhara bhai yoosufa hoo, jisako tum ne misr aneharon ke hath bech dala tha.
ab tum log mat pachhtao, aur tum ne jo mujhe yahan bech dala, is se udas mat ho kyonki parameshvar ne tumhare praanon ko bachane ke liye mujhe age se bhej diya haai.
kyonaki ab do varsha se is desh men akal haai aur ab panch varsha aur aeese hee honge, ki un men n to hal chalega aur n ann katta jaaega.
so parameshvar ne mujhe tumhare age isee liye bheja, ki tum prathvee par jeevit raho, aur tumhare praanon ke bachane se tumhara vansh baddhe.
so shaeegha mere pita ke pas jakar kaho, tera putra yoosufa is prakar kahata haai, ki parameshvar ne mujhe sare misr ka svamee ttharaya haai isaaliye too mere pas bina vilamb kiae chala a.
aur tera nivas goshon desh men hoga, aur to, bette, poto, bhed-bakaariyo, gaya-baailo, aur apane sab kuchh samet mere nikatt rahega.
aur akal ke jo panch varsha aur honge, un men maai vaheen tera palan poshan karoonga aeesa n ho ki to, aur tera gharana, varan jitane tere haai, so bookhon maren.
aur tum apanee ankhon se dekhte ho, aur mera bhai binyameen bhee apanee ankhon se dekhta haai, ki jo ham se baten kar raha haai so yoosufa haai.
aur tum mere sab vibhv ka, jo misr men haai aur jo kuchh tum ne dekha haai, us sab ko mere pita se varnn karana aur turant mere pita ko yahan le ana.
aur vah apane bhai binyameen ke gale se lipattkar roya aur binyameen bhee usake gale se lipattkar roya.
tab vah apane sab bhaiyon ko choomakar un se milakar roya : aur isake pashchata usake bhai us se baten karane lage..
is bat kee charcha, ki yoosufa ke bhai aae haai, firaun ke bhvan tab panhuch gai, aur is se firaun aur usake karmacharee prasann hue.
so firaun ne yoosufa se kaha, apane bhaiyon se kah, ki aek kam karo, apane pashuuon ko ladakar kanan desh men chale jao.
aur apane pita aur apane apane ghar ke logon ko lekar mere pas ao aur misr desh men jo kuchh achchhe se achchha haai vah maain tumhen doonga, aur tumhen desh ke uttm se uttm padarth khane ko milenge.
aur tujhe agyaa milee haai, tum aek kam karo, ki misr desh se apane balabachchon aur striayon ke liye gaadiyon le jao, aur apane pita ko le ao.
aur apanee samagraee ka moh n karana kyonki sare misr desh men jo kuchh achchhe se achchha haai so tumhara haai.
aur israael ke putraen ne vaaisa hee kiya. aur yoosufa ne firaun kee manake unhen gaadiyon dee, aur marga ke liye seedha bhee diya.
un men se ek ek jan ko to us ne ek ek joda vasr bhee diya aur binyameen ko teen sau roope ke ttukade aur panch jode vasr die.
aur apane pita ke pas us ne jo bheja vah yah haai, arthata misr kee achchhee vastuon se lade huae das gadahe, aur ann aur rottee aur usake pita ke marga ke liye bhojanavastu se ladee hui das gadaahiyan.
aur us ne apane bhaiyon ko vida kiya, aur ve chal diae aur us ne un se kaha, marga men kaheen jhgada n karana.
misr se chalakar ve kanan desh men apane pita yakoob ke pas pahuche.
aur us se yah varnn kiya, ki yoosufa ab tak jeevit haai, aur sare misr desh par prabhuta vahee karata haai. par us ne unakee prateeti n kee, aur vah apane ape men n raha.
aur israael ne kaha, bas, mera putra yoosufa ab tak jeevit haai : maain apanee mratyu se pahile jakar usako dekhooga..
tab israael apana sab kuchh lekar kooch karake bershoba ko gaya, aur vahan apane pita isahak ke parameshvar ko baalidan chaddhaae.
tab parameshvar ne israael se rat ko darshan men kaha, he yakoob he yakooba. us ne kaha, kya agyaa.
us ne kaha, maain ishvar tere pita ka parameshvar hoo, too misr men jane se mat dra kyonki maain tujh se vahan ek badee jati banaunga.
maain tere sang sang misr ko chalata hoon aur maain tujhe vahan se fir nishchay le aunga aur yoosufa apana hath teree ankhon par lagaaega.
tab yakoob beshorba se chala: aur israael ke putra apane pita yakoob, aur apane bala-bachcho, aur striayon ko un gadiyon par, jo firaun ne unake le ane ko bhejee thee, chaddhakar chal pade.
aur ve apanee bhed-bakaree, gaya-baail, aur kanan desh men apane ikattha kiae huae sare dhan ko lekar misr men aae.
aur yakoob apane bette-bettyaie, pote-potiyo, nidan apane vansh bhr ko apane sang misr men le aya..
yakoob ke sath jo israaelee, arthata usake bette, pote, aadi misr men aa, unake nam ye haain : yakoob ka jetta to rooben tha.
aur rooben ke putra, hanok, palalo, hesron, aur kamrmee the.
aur shaimon ke putra, yamooael, yameen, ohad, yakeen, sohar, aur aek kananee sree se janma hua shaaul bhee tha.
aur yahooda ke aer, onan, shola, peres, aur jerah nam putra huae to the par aer aur onan kanan desh men mar gaae the.
aur issakar ke putra, tola, pubba, yob aur shaimraen the.
aur jabooloon ke putra, sered, aelon, aur yahalel the.
lia: ke putra, jo yakoob se panaram men utpann huae the, unake bette pote ye hee the, aur in se adhaik us ne usake sath aek bettee deena ko bhee janm diya : yahan tak to yakoob ke sab vanshavale taaintees praanee hue.
fir gad ke putra, siyyon, haggee, shoonee, aesabon, aeree, arodee, aur arelee the.
aur ashor ke putra, yimna, yishva, yisre, aur bareea the, aur unakee bahin serah thee. aur bareea ke putra, heber aur malkeeael the.
jilpa, jise laban ne apanee bettee lian ko diya tha, usake bette pote aadi ye hee the so usake dara yakoob ke solah praanee utpann huae..
fir yakoob kee patnee rahel ke putra yoosufa aur binyameen the.
aur misr desh men on ke yajak poteepera kee bettee asanat se yoosufa ke ye putra utpann hua, arthata manashsho aur aepraaima.
aur binyameen ke putra, bela, beker, ashbel, gera, naman, aehee, rosha, muppeem, huppeem, aur arda the.
rahel ke putra jo yakoob se utpann huae unake ye hee putra the usake ye sab bette pote chaudah praanee huae.
fir dan ka putra hushaeem tha.
aur naptalee ke putra, yahasel, goonee, seser, aur shaillem the.
bilha, jise laban ne apanee bettee rahel ko diya, us ke bette pote ye hee haain usake dara yakoob ke vansh men sat praanee hue.
yakoob ke nij vansh ke jo praanee misr men aa, ve usakee bahuon ko chhod sab milakar chhyaiasatt praanee hue.
aur yoosufa ke putra, jo misr men us se utpann hua, ve do praanee the : is prakar yakoob ke gharane ke jo praanee misr men aae so sab milakar sattr huae..
fir us ne yahooda ko apane age yoosufa ke pas bhej diya, ki vah usako goshon ka marga dikhaae aur ve goshon desh men aae.
tab israael ne yoosufa se kaha, maai ab marane se bhee prasann hoo, kyonki tujhe jeeavit paya aur tera munh dekh liya.
tab yoosufa ne apane bhaiyon se aur apane pita ke gharane se kaha, maain jakar firaun ko yah samachar doonga, ki mere bhai aur mere pita ke sare gharane ke log, jo kanan desh men rahate the, ve mere pas a gaae haain.
aur ve log charavahe haai, kyonki ve pashuuon ko palate aae haain isaliye ve apanee bhed-bakaree, gaya-baail, aur jo kuchh unaka haai, sab le aae haain.
jab firaun tum ko bulake poochhe, ki tumhara udhym kya haai?
tab yah kahana ki tere das ladkapan se lekar aj tak pashuuon ko palate aae haai, varan hamare purakha bhee aeesa hee karate the. is se tum goshon desh men rahane paoge kyonki sab charavahon se misree log gharana karate haain..
tab yoosufa ne firaun ke pas jakar yah samachar diya, ki mera pita aur mere bhai, aur unakee bhed-bakaariya, gaya-baail aur jo kuchh unaka haai, sab kanan desh se a gaya haai aur abhee to ve goshon desh men haain.
fir us ne apane bhaiyon men se panch jan lekar firaun ke samhane khde kar diae.
firaun ne usake bhaiyon se poochha, tumhara udhym kya haai ? unhon ne firaun se kaha, tere das charavahe haai, aur hamare purakha bhee aeese hee rahe.
fir unhon ne firaun se kaha, ham is desh men paradeshaee kee bhanati rahane ke liye aae haain kyonaki kanan desh men bharee akal hone ke karan tere dason ko bhed-bakaariyon ke liye chara n raha : so apane dason ko goshon desh men rahane kee agyaa de.
tab firaun ne yoosufa se kaha, tera pita aur tere bhai tere pas a gaae haai,
aur misr desh tere samhane pada haai is desh ka jo sab se achchha bhag ho, us men apane pita aur bhaiyon ko basa de arthata ve goshon hee desh men rahen : aur yadi too janata ho, ki un men se parishramee puroosh haai, to unhen mere pashuuon ke adhaikaree tthara de.
tab yoosufa ne apane pita yakoob ko le akar firaun ke sammukh khda kiya : aur yakoob ne firaun ko ashaeervad diya.
yakoob ne firaun se kaha, maain to aek sau tees varsha paradeshaee hokar apana jeevan beeta chuka hoon mere jeevan ke din thode aur du:kh se bhre huae bhee the, aur mere bapadade paradeshaee hokar jitane din tak jeevit rahe utane din ka maain abhee naheen hua.
aur yakoob firaun ko ashaeervad dekar usake sammukh se chala gaya.
tab yoosufa ne apane pita aur bhaiyon ko basa diya, aur firaun kee agyaa ke anusar misr desh ke achchhe se achchhe bhag me, arthata ramases nam desh me, boomi dekar unako saunp diya.
aur yoosufa apane pita ka, aur apane bhaiyon ka, aur pita ke sare gharane ka, aek aek ke balabachchon ke gharane kee ginatee ke anusar, bhojan dila dilakar unaka palan poshan karane laga..
aur us sare desh men khane ko kuchh n raha kyonki akal bahut bharee tha, aur akal ke karan misr aur kanan donon desh nash ho gaae.
aur jitana roopaya misr aur kanan desh men tha, sab ko yoosufa ne us ann kee santee jo unake nivasee mol lete the ikattha karake firaun ke bhvan men pahuncha diya.
jab misr aur kanan desh ka roopaya chuk gaya, tab sab misree yoosufa ke pas a akar kahane lage, ham ko bhojanavastu de, kya ham roopaye ke n rahane se tere rahate huae mar jaaen ?
yoosufa ne kaha, yadi roopaye n hon to apane pashu de do, aur maain unakee santee tumhen khane ko doonga.
tab ve apane pashu yoosufa ke pas le aae aur yoosufa unako ghaedo, bhed-bakaariyo, gaya-baailon aur gadahon kee santee khane ko dene laga: us varsha men vah sab jaati ke pashuuon kee santee bhojan dekar unaka palan poshan karata raha.
vah varsha to yon katt gaya tab agale varsha men unhon ne usake pas akar kaha, ham apane prabhu se yah bat chhpai n rakhenge ki hamara roopaya chuk gaya haai, aur hamare sab prakar ke pashu hamare prabhu ke pas a chuke haain isaaliye ab hamare prabhu ke samhane hamare shareer aur boomi chhodkar aur kuchh naheen raha.
ham tere dekhte kyon mare, aur hamaree boomi ko bhojan vastu kee santee mol le, ki ham apanee boomi samet firaun ke das hon : aur hamako beej de, ki ham marane n paae, varan jeeavit rahe, aur boomi n ujade.
tab yoosufa ne misr kee saree boomi ko firaun ke liye mol liya kyonaki us kattnai akal ke padne se misriyon ko apana apana khet bech dalana pada : is prakar saree boomi firaun kee ho gai.
aur aek chhor se lekar doosare chhor tak sare misr desh men jo praja rahatee thee, usako us ne nagaron men lakar basa diya.
par yajakon kee boomi to us ne n mol lee : kyonki yajakon ke liye firaun kee or se nity bhojan ka bandobast tha, aur nity jo bhojan firaun unako deta tha vahee ve khate the is karan unako apanee boomi bechanee n padee.
tab yoosufa ne praja ke logon se kaha, suno, maain ne aj ke din tum ko aur tumharee boomi ko bhee firaun ke liye mol liya haai dekho, tumhare liye yahan beej haai, ise boomi men boo.
aur jo kuchh upaje usaka panchamansh firaun ko dena, bakee char ansh tumhare rahenge, ki tum use apane kheton mane boo, aur apane apane balabachchon aur ghar ke aur logon samet khaya karo.
so yoosufa ne misr kee boomi ke vishay men aeesa niyam ttharaya, jo aj ke din tak chala ata haai, ki panchamansh firaun ko mila kare keval yajakon hee kee boomi firaun kee naheen hui.
aur israaelee misr ke goshon desh men rahane lage aur vahan kee boomi ko apane vash men kar liya, aur foole-fale, aur atyant baddh gaae..
misr desh men yakoob satarah varsha jeevit raha : is prakar yakoob kee saree ayu aek sau saaintalees varsha kee hui.
jab israael ke marane ka din nikatt a gaya, tab us ne apane putra yoosufa ko bulavakar kaha, yaadi tera anugrah mujh par ho, to apana hath meree jangha ke tale rakhkar shapath kha, ki maain tere sath krapa aur sachchai ka yah kam karoonga, ki tujhe misr men mittee n doonga.
jab too apane bapadadon ke sang so jaaega, tab maain tujhe misr se utta le jakar unheen ke kabaaristan men rakoonga tab yoosufa ne kaha, maain tere vachan ke anusar karoonga.
fir us ne kaha, mujh se shapath kha : so us ne us se shapath khai. tab israael ne khatt ke sirahane kee or sir jhukaya..
in baton ke pashchata kisee ne yoosufa se kaha, sun, tera pita beemar haai tab vah manashsho aur aepraaim nam apane donon putraen ko sang lekar usake pas chala.
aur kisee ne yakoob ko bata diya, ki tera putra yoosufa tere pas a raha haai tab israael apane ko sambhalakar khatt par baaitt gaya.
aur yakoob ne yoosufa se kaha, sarvashaktaiman ishvar ne kanan desh ke looj nagar ke pas mujhe darshan dekar ashaeesh dee,
aur kaha, sun, maain tujhe faula-falakar baddhaunga, aur tujhe rajy rajy kee mandlee ka mool banaunga, aur tere pashchata tere vansh ko yah desh de doonga, jis se ki vah sada tak unakee nij boomi banee rahe.
aur ab tere donon putra, jo misr men mere ane se pahile utpann huae haai, ve mere hee ttharenge arthata jis reeti se rooben aur shaimon mere haai, usee reeati se aepraaim aur manashsho bhee mere ttharenge.
aur unake pashchata jo santan utpann ho, vah tere to ttharenge parantu banttvare ke samay ve apane bhaiyon hee ke vansh men gine jaaenge.
jab maain paan se ata tha, tab aepraata pahunchane se thodee hee door pahile rahel kanan desh me, marga me, mere samhane mar gai : aur maain ne use vahee, arthata aepraata jo betaleham bhee kahalata haai, usee ke marga men mittee dee.
yoosufa ne apane pita se kaha, ye mere putra haai, jo parameshvar ne mujhe yahan diae haain : us ne kaha, unako mere pas le a ki maain unhen ashaeervad doon.
israael kee ankhe buddhape ke karan dhaundhalee ho gai thee, yahan tak ki use kam soojhta tha. tab yoosufa unhen unake pas le gaya aur us ne unhen choomakar gale laga liya.
tab israael ne yoosufa se kaha, mujhe asha n thee, ki maain tera mukh fir dekhne paunga : parantu dek, parameshvar ne mujhe tera vansh bhee dikhaya haai.
tab yoosufa ne unhen apane ghauttnon ke beech se hattakar aur apane munh ke bal boomi par girake dandvata kee.
tab yoosufa ne un donon ko lekar, arthata aepraaim ko apane dahine hath se, ki vah israael ke baaen hath pade, aur manashsho ko apane baaen hath se, ki israael ke daahine hath pade, unhen usake pas le gaya.
tab israael ne apana dahina hath baddhakar aepraaim ke sir par jo chhotta tha, aur apana bayan hath baddhakar manashsho ke sir par rakh diya us ne to jan boojhkar aeesa kiya naheen to jetta manashsho hee tha.
fir us ne yoosufa ko ashaeervad dekar kaha, parameshvar jisake sammukh mere bapadade ibraaheem aur isahak apane ko janakar chalate the vahee parameshvar mere janm se lekar aj ke din tak mera charavaha bana haai
aur vahee doot mujhe saree burai se chhudata aya haai, vahee ab in ladkon ko ashaeesh de aur ye mere aur mere bapadade ibraaheem aur isahak ke kahalaaen aur prathvee men bahutayat se baddhen.
jab yoosufa ne dekha, ki mere pita ne apana daahina hath aepraaim ke sir par rakha haai, tab yah bat usako buree lagee : so us ne apane pita ka hath is manasa se pakad liya, ki aepraaim ke sir par se uttakar manashsho ke sir par rakh de.
aur yoosufa ne apane pita se kaha, he pita, aeesa naheen: kyonki jetta yahee haai apana daahina hath isake sir par rakh.
usake pita ne kaha, nahee, sun, he mere putra, maain is bat ko bhlee bhanti janata hoon : yadhyapi is se bhee manushyon kee ek mandlee utpann hogee, aur yah bhee mahana ho jaega, taubhee isaka chhotta bhai is se adhaik mahan ho jaega, aur usake vansh se bahut see jaatiyan nikalengee.
fir us ne usee din yah kahakar unako ashaeervad diya, ki israaelee log tera nam le lekar aeesa ashaeervad diya karenge, ki parameshvar tujhe aepraaim aur manashsho ke saman bana de : aur us ne manashsho se pahile aepraaim ka nam liya.
tab israael ne yoosufa se kaha, dek, maain to marane par hoon : parantu parameshvar tum logon ke sang rahega, aur tum ko tumhare pitaron ke desh men fir pahuncha dega.
aur maain tujh ko tere bhaiyon se aadhaik boomi ka aek bhag deta hoo, jisako maain ne aemoriyon ke hath se apanee talavar aur dhanush ke bal se le liya haai.
fir yakoob ne apane putraen ko yah kahakar bulaya, ki ikatthe ho jao, maain tum ko bataunga, ki ant ke dinon men tum par kya kya beetega.
he rooben, too mera jetta, mera bal, aur mere pauroosh ka paahila fal haai praatishtta ka uttm bhag, aur shaktai ka bhee uttm bhag too hee haai.
too jo jal kee nain ubalanevala haai, isaliye auron se shraeshtt n ttharega kyonki too apane pita kee khatt par chaddha, tab too ne usako ashuuddh kiya vaha mere bichhaune par chaddh gaya..
shaimon aur levee to bhai bhai haai, unakee talavaren upadrav ke hathaiyara haain.
he mere jeev, unake marma men n pad, he meree mahima, unakee sabha men mat mila kyonki unhon ne kop se manushyon ko ghaat kiya, aur apanee hee ichchha par chalakara baailon kee poonchhen kattee haain..
dhaikkar unake kop ko, jo prachand tha aur unake rosh ko, jo nirday tha maain unhen yakoob men alag alag aur israael men tittr bittr kar doonga..
he yahooda, tere bhai tera dhanyavada karenge, tera hath tere shatrauon kee gardan par padega tere pita ke putra tujhe dandvata karenge..
yahooda sinh ka danvaroo haai. he mere putra, too aher karake gufaa men gaya haai : vah sinh va sinhanee kee nai dabakara baaitt gaya afir kaun usako chhedega..
jab tak shaeelo n aae tab tak n to yahooda se rajadand choottega, n usake vansh se vyavastha denevala alag hoga aur rajy rajy ke log usake adhaeen ho jaaenge..
vah apane javan gadahe ko dakhlata me, aur apanee gadahee ke bachche ko uttm jaati kee dakhlata men bandha karega us ne apane vasr dakhmadha me, aur apana paahirava dakhon ke ras men dhaeya haai..
usakee ankhe dakhmadha se chamakeelee aur usake dant doodha se shvet honge..
jabooloon samudr ke teer par nivas karega, vah jahajon ke liye bandaragah ka kam dega, aur usaka parala bhag seedon ke anikatt pahunchega
issakar aek bada aur balavanta gadaha haai, jo pashuuon ke badon ke beech men dabaka rahata haai..
us ne ek vishraamasthan dekhkar, aki achchha haai, aur ek desha, ki manohar haai, apane kandho ko bojh uttane ke liye jhukaya, aur begaree men das ka sa kama karane laga..
dan israael ka aek gotra hokara apane jaatibhaiyon ka nyaya karega..
he yahova, maain tujhee se uddhar pane kee batt johata aya hoon..
gad par aek dal chaddhai to karega par vah usee dal ke pichhle bhag par chhapa marega..
ashor se jo ann utpann hoga vaha uttm hoga, aur vah raja ke yogy svadishtt bhojan diya karega..
naptalee aek choottee hui haarinee haai vah sundar baten bolata haai..
yoosufa balavant lata kee aeka shaakha haai, vah sote ke pas lagee hui falavant lata kee aek shaakha haai usakee daliyan bheet par se chaddhkar faail jatee haain..
dhanudharariyon ne usako kheadit kiya, aur us par teer mare, aur usake peechhe pade haain..
par usaka dhanush draddh raha, aur usakee banh aur hath yakoob ke usee shaaktaiman ishvar ke hathon ke dara faurteele hua, ajisake pas se vah charavaha aaega, jo israael ka patthra bhee ttharega..
yah tere pita ke us ishvar ka kam haai, jo teree sahayata karega, us sarvashaaktaiman ko jo tujhe upar se akash men kee ashaeesho, aur neeche se gahire jal men kee ashaeesho, aur stano, aur garbh kee ashaeeshon dega..
tere pita ke ashaeervad mere pitaron ke ashaeervad se aadhaika baddh gaae haain aur sanatan pahaadiyon kee mana- chahee vastuon kee nai bane rahenge : ve yoosufa ke sir par, jo apane bhaiyon men se nyara hua, usee ke sir ke mukutt par foole falenge..
binyameen faadnehara hundar haai, savere to vah aher bhkshan karega, aur sanjh ko loott bantt lega..
israael ke barahon gotra ye hee haain : aur unake pita ne jis jis vachan se unako ashaeervad diya, so ye hee haain aek aek ko usake ashaeervad ke anusar us ne ashaeervad diya.
tab us ne yah kahakar unako agyaa dee, ki maain apane logon ke sath milane par hoon : isaaliye mujhe hittee aepraen kee boomivalee gufaa men mere bapadadon ke sath mittee dena,
arthata usee gufaa men jo kanan desh men mamra ke samhanevalee makapela kee boomi men haai us boomi ko to ibraaheem ne hittee aepraen ke hath se isee nimitt mol liya tha, ki vah kabaaristan ke liye usakee nij boomi ho.
vahan ibraaheem aur usakee patnee sara ko mittee dee gai aur vaheen isahak aur usakee patnee ribaka ko bhee mittee dee gai aur vaheen maain ne lia: ko bhee mittee dee.
yah agyaa jab yakoob apane putraen ko de chuka, tab apane panv khatt par samett praan chhode, aur apane logon men ja mila.
jab adam apanee patnee havva ke pas gaya tab us ne garbhvatee hokar kaain ko janm diya aur kaha, maai ne yahova kee sahayata se aek puroosh paya haai.
fir vah usake bhai haabil ko bhee janmee, aur habil to bhed-bakaariyon ka charavaha ban gaya, parantu kaain boomi kee khetee karane vala kisan bana.
kuchh dinon ke pashchata kaain yahova ke pas boomi kee upaj men se kuchh bhentt le aya.
aur haabil bhee apanee bhed-bakaariyon ke kai aek pahilautte bachche bhentt chaddhane le aya aur unakee charbee bhentt chaddhai tab yahova ne habil aur usakee bhentt ko to grahan kiya,
parantu kaain aur usakee bhentt ko us ne grahan n kiya. tab kaain ati krodhait hua, aur usake munh par udasee chha gai.
tab yahova ne kaain se kaha, too kyon krodhait hua ? aur tere munh par udasee kyon chha gai haai ?
yaadi too bhla kare, to kya teree bhentt grahan n kee jaaegee ? aur yaadi too bhla n kare, to pap dar par chhpai rahata haai, aur usakee lalasa teree aur hogee, aur too us par prabhuta karega.
tab kaain ne apane bhai haabil se kuchh kaha : aur jab ve maaidan men the, tab kaain ne apane bhai habil par chaddhkar use ghaat kiya.
tab yahova ne kaain se poochha, tera bhai habil kahan haai ? us ne kaha maloom naheen : kya maai apane bhai ka rakhvala hoon ?
us ne kaha, too ne kya kiya haai ? tere bhai ka lohoo boomi men se meree or chillakar meree dohai de raha haai !
isaliye ab boomi jis ne tere bhai ka lohoo tere hath se peene ke liye apana munh khola haai, usakee or se too shaaapit haai.
chahe too boomi par khetee kare, taubhee usakee pooree upaj fir tujhe n milegee, aur too prathvee par bahetoo aur bhgoda hoga.
tab kaain ne yahova se kaha, mera dand sahane se bahar haai.
dek, too ne aj ke din mujhe boomi par se nikala haai aur maai teree draashtti kee ad me rahoonga aur prathvee par bahetoo aur bhgoda rahoonga aur jo koi mujhe paaega, mujhe ghaat karega.
tab kaain yahova ke sammukh se nikal gaya, aur noda nam desh me, jo adan ke poorva kee or haai, rahane laga.
jab kaain apanee patnee ke pas gaya jab vah garbhvatee hui aur hanok ko janmee, fir kaain ne aek nagar basaya aur us nagar ka nam apane putra ke nam par hanok rakha.
aur hanok se irad utpann hua, aur irad ne mahooyaael ko janm diya, aur mahooyaael ne matooshaaael ko, aur matooshaaael ne lemek ko janm diya.
aur lemek ne do striayan byah lee : jin men se aek ka nam ada, aur doosaree ko silla haai.
aur ada ne yabal ko janm diya. vah tambuon men rahana aur janavaron ka palan in dono reeatiyon ka utpadak hua.
aur usake bhai ka nam yoobal haai : vah veena aur bansuree aadi bajon ke bajane kee saree reeti ka utpadak hua.
aur silla ne bhee toobalkaain nam aek putra ko janm diya : vah peetal aur lohe ke sab dhaaravale hathaiyaron ka gaddhnevala hua: aur toobalkaain kee baahin nama thee.
aur lemek ne apanee patnaiyon se kaha, he ada aur he silla meree suno he lemek kee patnaiyo, meree bat par kan lagao: maainne aek puroosh ko jo mere chott lagata tha, arthata aek javan ko jo mujhe ghaayal karata tha, ghaat kiya haai.
jab kaain ka palatta sataguna liya jaaega. to lemek ka sataharaguna liya jaaega.
aur adam apanee patnee ke pas fir gaya aur us ne aek putra ko janm diya aur usaka nam yah kah ke shot rakha, ki parameshvar ne mere liye haabil kee santee, jisako kaain ne ghaat kiya, aek aur vansh tthara diya haai.
aur shot ke bhee aek putra utpann hua aur us ne usaka nam aenosh rakha, usee samay se log yahova se praarthna karane lage..
tab yoosufa apane pita ke munh par girakar roya aur use chooma.
aur yoosufa ne un vaaidhon ko, jo usake sevak the, agyaa dee, ki mere pita kee loth men sugandhadravy bhro tab vaaidhon ne israael kee loth men sugandhadravy bhr diae.
jab usake vilap ke din beet gaa, tab yoosufa firaun ke gharane ke logon se kahane laga, yaadi tumharee anugrah kee draashtti mujh par ho to meree yah binatee firaun ko sunao,
ki mere pita ne yah kahakar, ki dekh maain marane par hoo, mujhe yah shapath khailai, ki jo kabar too ne apane liye kanan desh men khudavai haai usee men maain tujhe mittee doonga isaaliye ab mujhe vahan jakar apane pita ko mittee dene kee agyaa de, tatpashchata maain lautt aunga.
tab firaun ne kaha, jakar apane pita kee khailai hui shapath ke anusar unako mittee de.
so yoosufa apane pita ko mittee dene ke liye chala, aur firaun ke sab karmacharee, arthata usake bhvan ke puraniye, aur misr desh ke sab puraniye usake sang chale.
aur yoosufa ke ghar ke sab log, aur usake bhai, aur usake pita ke ghar ke sab log bhee sang gaae par ve apane balabachcho, aur bhed-bakaariyo, aur gaya-baailon ko goshon desh men chhod gaae.
aur usake sang rath aur savar gaa, so bheed bahut bharee ho gai.
jab ve atad ke khlihan tak, jo yaradan nadee ke par haai pahunche, tab vahan atyant bharee vilap kiya, aur yoosufa ne apane pita ke sat din ka vilap karaya.
atad ke khlihan men ke vilap ko dekhkar us desh ke nivasee kanaaniyon ne kaha, yah to misriyon ka koi bharee vilap hoga, isee karan us sthan ka nam abelaamisraaim pada, aur vah yaradan ke par haai.
aur israael ke putraen ne us se vahee kam kiya jisakee us ne unako agyaa dee thee:
