aur meree vedee par seeddhee se kabhee n chaddhna, kaheen aeesa n ho ki tera tan us par nanga dekh pade..
fir jo niyam tujhe unako samajhane haain ve ye haain..
jab tum koi ibraee das mol lo, tab vah chh: varsha tak seva karata rahe, aur sataven varsha svatantra hokar sentament chala jaae.
yaadi vah akela aya ho, to akela hee chala jaae aur yadi patnee sahit aya ho, to usake sath usakee patnee bhee chalee jaae.
yaadi usake svamee ne usako patnee dee ho aur us se usake bette va beattyaian utpann hui ho, to usakee patnee aur balak usake svamee ke hee rahe, aur vah akela chala jaae.
parantu yadi vah das draddhta se kahe, ki maain apane svamee, aur apanee patnee, aur balakon se praem rakhta hoon isaaliye maain svatantra hokar n chala jaunga
yaadi koi apanee bettee ko dasee hone ke liye bech dale, to vah dasee kee nai bahar n jaae.
yaadi usaka svamee usako apanee patnee banaa, aur fir us se prasann n rahe, to vah use dam se chhudai jane de usaka vishvasaghaat karane ke bad use uparee logon ke hath bechane ka usako aadhaikar n hoga.
chahe vah doosaree patnee kar le, taubhee vah usaka bhojan, vasr, aur sangaati n ghattaae.
aur yaadi vah in teen baton men ghattee kare, to vah sree sentament bina dam chukaae hee chalee jaae..
jo kisee manushy ko aeesa mare ki vah mar jaa, to vah bhee nishchay mar dala jaae.
yaadi vah usakee ghaat men n baaitta ho, aur parameshvar kee ichchha hee se vah usake hath men pad gaya ho, to aeese maranevale ke bhagane ke nimitt maain aek sthan ttharaunga jahan vah bhag jaae.
parantu yadi koi ddhttiai se kisee par chaddhai karake use chhl se ghaat kare, to usako mar ddhalane ke liye meree vedee ke pas se bhee alag le jana..
jo apane pita va mata ko mare-peette vah nishchay mar dala jaae..
jo kisee manushy ko churaa, chahe use le jakar bech dale, chahe vah usake pas paya jaa, to vah bhee nishchay mar dala jaae..
jo apane pita va mata ko shraap de vah bhee nishchay mar dala jaae..
yaadi manushy jhgadte ho, aur aek doosare ko patthr va mukke se aeesa mare ki vah mare naheen parantu bichhaune par pada rahe,
to jab vah uttkar lattee ke sahare se bahar chalane firane lage, tab vah maranevala nirdosh tthare us dasha men vah usake pade rahane ke samay kee haani to bhr de, or usako bhla changa bhee kara de..
yaadi koi apane das va dasee ko sontte se aeesa mare ki vah usake marane se mar jaa, tab to usako nishchay dand diya jaae.
parantu yadi vah do aek din jeevit rahe, to usake svamee ko dand n diya jaae kyonaki vah das usaka dhan haai..
yaadi manushy apas men marapeett karake kisee gaabhairnee sree ko aeesee chott pahuchaa, ki usaka garbh gir jaa, parantu aur kuchh haani n ho, to maranevale se utana dand liya jaae jitana us sree ka pati panch kee sammaati se ttharaae.
parantu yadi usako aur kuchh hani pahunche, to praan kee santee praan ka,
aur ankh kee santee ankh ka, aur dant kee santee dant ka, aur hath kee santee hath ka, aur panv kee santee panv ka,
aur dag kee santee dag ka, aur ghaav kee santee ghaav ka, aur mar kee santee mar ka dand ho..
jab koi apane das va dasee kee ankh par aeesa mare ki foott jaa, to vah usakee ankh kee santee use svatantra karake jane de.
aur yaadi vah apane das va dasee ko marake usaka dant tod dale, to vah usake dant kee santee use svatantra karake jane de..
yaadi baail kisee puroosh va sree ko aeesa seeng mare ki vah mar jaa, to vah baail to nishchay patthravah karake mar dala jaa, aur usaka mans khaya n jaae parantu baail ka svamee nirdosh tthare.
parantu yadi us baail kee paahile se seeng marane kee ban padee ho, aur usake svamee ne jataae jane par bhee usako n bandha rakha ho, aur vah kisee puroosh va sree ko mar dale, tab to vah baail patthravah kiya jaa, aur usaka svamee bhee mar dala jaae.
yaadi us par chhudautee ttharai jaa, to praan chhudane ko jo kuchh usake liye ttharaya jaae use utana hee dena padega.
chahe baail ne kisee bette ko, chahe bettee ko mara ho, taubhee isee niyam ke anusar usake svamee ke sath vyavahar kiya jaae.
yaadi baail ne kisee das va dasee ko seeng mara ho, to baail ka svamee us das ke svamee ko tees shokel roopa de, aur vah baail patthravah kiya jaae..
yaadi koi manushy gadha kholakar va khodakar usako n ddhanpe, aur us men kisee ka baail va gadaha gir pade
to jisaka vah gadha ho vah us haani ko bhr de vah pashu ke svamee ko usaka mol de, aur loth gadhevale kee tthare..
yaadi kisee ka baail kisee doosare ke baail ko aeesee chott lagaa, ki vah mar jaa, to ve dono manushy jeete baail ko bechakar usaka mol apas men adha adha bantt le aur loth ko bhee vaaisa hee bantten.
yaadi koi manushy baail, va bhed, va bakaree churakar usaka ghaat kare va bech dale, to vah baail kee santee pach baail, aur bhed-bakaree kee santee char bhed-bakaree bhr de.
yaadi chor sendha lagate huae pakada jaa, aur us par aeesee mar pade ki vah mar jaa, to usake koon ka dosh n lage
yaadi soorya nikal chuke, to usake koon ka dosh lage avashy haai ki vah hani ko bhr de, aur yadi usake pas kuchh n ho, to vah choree ke karan bech diya jaae.
yaadi koi apane pashu se kisee ka khet va dakh kee baree charaa, arthata apane pashu ko aeesa chhod de ki vah paraae khet ko char le, to vah apane khet kee aur apanee dakh kee baree kee uttm se uttm upaj men se us hani ko bhr de..
yaadi koi ag jalaa, aur vah kantton men lag jaae aur foolon ke ddher va anaj va khda khet jal jaa, to jis ne ag jalai ho vah hani ko nishchay bhr de..
yaadi koi doosare ko roopaae va samagraee kee dharohar dhare, aur vah usake ghar se churai jaa, to yadi chor pakada jaa, to doona usee ko bhr dena padega.
aur yaadi chor n pakada jaa, to ghar ka svamee parameshvar ke pas laya jaa, ki nishchay ho jay ki us ne apane bhai bandha kee sampaati par hath lagaya haai va naheen.
chahe baail, chahe gadahe, chahe bhed va bakaree, chahe vasr, chahe kisee prakar kee aeesee khoi hui vastu ke vishay aparadha kyon n lagaya jay, jise do jan apanee apanee kahate ho, to donon ka mukama parameshvar ke pas aae aur jisako parameshvar doshaee ttharaae vah doosare ko doona bhr de..
yaadi koi doosare ko gadaha va baail va bhed-bakaree va koi aur pashu rakhne ke liye saupe, aur kisee ke bina dekhe vah mar jaa, va chott khaa, va hank diya jaa,
to un dono ke beech yahova kee shapath khailai jaae ki maain ne isakee sampaati par hath naheen lagaya tab sampaati ka svamee isako sach mane, aur doosare ko use kuchh bhee bhr dena n hoga.
yaadi vah sachamuch usake yahan se churaya gaya ho, to vah usake svamee ko use bhr de.
aur yaadi vah faad dala gaya ho, to vah faade huae ko praman ke liye le aa, tab use usako bhee bhr dena n padega..
fir yadi koi doosare se pashu mang laa, aur usake svamee ke sang n rahate usako chott lage va vah mar jaa, to vah nishchay usakee hani bhr de.
yaadi usaka svamee sang ho, to doosare ko usakee hani bhrana n pade aur yaadi vah bhade ka ho to usakee hani usake bhade men a gai..
yaadi koi puroosh kisee kanya ko jisake byah kee bat n lagee ho fausalakar usake sang kukarma kare, to vah nishchay usaka mol deke use byah le.
parantu yadi usaka pita use dene ko bilkul inakar kare, to kukarma karanevala kanyaon ke mol kee reeti ke anusar roopaye taul de..
too dain ko jeevit rahane n dena..
jo koi pashuugaman kare vah nishchay mar dala jaae..
jo koi yahova ko chhod kisee aur devata ke liye baali kare vah satyanash kiya jaae.
aur paradeshaee ko n satana aur n us par andhor karana kyonki misr desh men tum bhee paradeshaee the.
kisee vidhava va anath balak ko du:kh n dena.
yaadi tum aeeson ko kisee prakar ka du:kh do, aur ve kuchh bhee meree dohai de, to maain nishchay unakee dohai sunoonga
tab mera krodha bhdkega, aur maain tum ko talavar se maravaunga, aur tumharee paatnaiyan vidhava aur tumhare balak anath ho jaaenge..
yaadi too meree praja men se kisee deen ko jo tere pas rahata ho roopaae ka ren de, to us se mahajan kee nai byaj n lena.
yaadi too kabhee apane bhaibandha ke vasr ko bandhak karake rakh bhee le, to soorya ke ast hone tak usako lautta dena
kyonaki vah usaka aek hee oddhna haai, usakee deh ka vahee akela vasr hoga fir vah kise oddhkar soaega? tobhee jab vah meree dohai dega tab maain usakee sunoonga, kyonaki maain to karoonamay hoon..
parameshvar ko shraap n dena, aur n apane logon ke pradhaan ko shraap dena.
apane kheton kee upaj aur falon ke ras men se kuchh mujhe dene men vilamb n karana. apane betton men se pahilautte ko mujhe dena.
aur tum mere liye paavitra manushy banana is karan jo pashu maaidan men faada hua pada mile usaka mans n khana, usako kuton ke age faenk dena..
joottee bat n faailana. anyayee sakshaee hokar dushtt ka sath n dena.
burai karane ke liye n to bahuton ke peechhe ho lena aur n unake peechhe firake mukamen men nyay bigadne ko sakshaee dena
aur kangal ke mukamen men usaka bhee paksha n karana..
fir yadi too apane baairee ke gadahe ko bojh ke mare daba hua dekhe, to chahe usako usake svamee ke liye chhudane ke liye tera man n chahe, taubhee avashy svamee ka sath dekar use chhuda lena..
tere logon men se jo daaridra hon usake mukame men nyay n bigadna.
jootte mukame se door rahana, aur nirdosh aur dharmee ko ghaat n karana, kyonki maain dushtt ko nirdosh n ttharaunga.
ghoos n lena, kyonaki ghoos dekhne valon ko bhee andha kar deta, aur dharmiyon kee baten palatt deta haai.
paradeshaee par andhor n karana tum to paradeshaee ke man kee baten janate ho, kyonaki tum bhee misr desh men paradeshaee the..
chh: varsha to apanee boomi men bona aur usakee upaj ikatthee karana
parantu sataven varsha men usako padtee rahane dena aur vaaisa hee chhod dena, to tere bhai bandhauon men ke daridra log us se khane paae, aur jo kuchh un se bhee bache vah banaaile pashuuon ke khane ke kam men aae. aur apanee dakh aur jalapai kee baariyon ko bhee aeese hee karana.
chh: din tak to apana kam kaj karana, aur sataven din vishraam karana ki tere baail aur gadahe sustaae, aur teree daasiyon ke bette aur paradeshaee bhee apana jee ttnda kar saken.
aur jo kuchh maain ne tum se kaha haai us men savadhaan rahana aur doosare devataon ke nam kee charcha n karana, varan ve tumhare munh se sunai bhee n den.
praati varsha teen bar mere liye pabrba manana.
akhmeeree rottee ka pabrba manana us men meree agyaa ke anusar abeeb maheene ke niyat samay par sat din tak akhmeeree rottee khaya karana, kyonaki usee maheene men tum misr se nikal aae. aur mujh ko koi choochhe hath apana munh n dikhaae.
aur jab teree boi hui khetee kee paahilee upaj taaiyar ho, tab kattnee ka pabrba manana. aur varsha ke ant men jab too parishram ke fal battor ke ddher lagaa, tab battoran ka pabrba manana.
praati varsha teenon bar tere sab puroosh prabhu yahova ko apana munh dikhaaen..
mere balipashu ka lohoo khmeeree rottee ke sang n chaddhana, aur n mere pabrba ke uttm balidan men se kuchh bihan tak rahane dena.
apanee boomi kee pahilee upaj ka pahila bhag apane parameshvar yahova ke bhvan men le ana. bakaree ka bachcha usakee mata ke doodha men n pakana..
sun, maain aek doot tere age age bhejata hoon jo marga men teree raksha karega, aur jis sthan ko maai ne taaiyar kiya haai us men tujhe pahunchaaega.
usake samhane savadhaan rahana, aur usakee manana, usaka virodha n karana, kyonaki vah tumhara aparadha kshama n karega isaaliye ki us men mera nam rahata haai.
aur yaadi too sachamuch usakee mane aur jo kuchh maain kahoon vah kare, to maai tere shatrauon ka shatra aur tere draehiyon ka draehee banoonga.
is reeati mera doot tere age age chalakar tujhe aemoree, hittee, parajjee, kananee, hibbee, aur yaboosee logon ke yahan pahunchaaega, aur maain unako satyanash kar daloonga.
unake devataon ko dandvata n karana, aur n unakee upasana karana, aur n unake se kam karana, varan un mooraton ko pooree reeti se satyanash kar dalana, aur un logon kee latton ke ttukade ttukade kar dena.
aur tum apane parameshvar yahova kee upasana karana, tab vah tere ann jal par ashaeesh dega, aur tere beech men se rog door karega.
tere desh men n to kisee ka garbh girega aur n koi banjh hogee aur teree ayu maain pooree karoonga.
jitane logon ke beech too jayega un sabhon ke man men maai apana bhy pahile se aeesa samava doonga ki unako vyakul kar doonga, aur maain tujhe sab shatrauon kee peett dikhaunga.
aur maain tujh se pahile barorn ko bhejoonga jo hibbee, kananee, aur hittee logon ko tere samhane se bhga ke door kar dengee.
jab tak too fool falakar desh ko apane aadhaikar men n kar le tab tak maain unhen tere age se thoda thoda karake nikalata rahoonga.
maain lal samudra se lekar paalishtaiyon ke samudra tak aur jangal se lekar mahanad tak ke desh ko tere vash men kar doonga maain us desh ke nivaasiyon ko bhee tere vash men kar doonga, aur too unhen apane samhane se barabas nikalega.
too n to un se vacha bandhana aur n unake devataon se.
ve tere desh men rahane n paae, aeesa n ho ki ve tujh se mere virooddh pap karaaen kyonaki yadi too unake devataon kee upasana kare, to yah tere liye fanda banega..
fir us ne moosa se kaha, to, haroon, nadab, abeeho, aur israaeliyon ke sattr puraaniyon samet yahova ke pas upar akar door se dandvata karana.
tab moosa ne logon ke pas jakar yahova kee sab baten aur sab niyam suna diae tab sab log aek svar se bol utte, ki jitanee baten yahova ne kahee haain un sab baton ko ham manenge.
tab moosa ne yahova ke sab vachan likh diae. aur bihan ko savere uttkar parvat ke neeche aek vedee aur israael ke barahon gotraen ke anusar barah khmbhe bhee banavaae.
tab us ne kai israaelee javanon ko bheja, jinhon ne yahova ke liye homabaali aur baailon ke melabali chaddhaae.
aur moosa ne adha lohoo to lekar kattaron men rakha, aur adha vedee par chhdik diya.
tab vacha kee pustak ko lekar logon ko paddh sunaya use sunakar unhon ne kaha, jo kuchh yahova ne kaha haai us sab ko ham karenge, aur usakee agyaa manenge.
tab moosa ne lohoo ko lekar logon par chhdik diya, aur un se kaha, dekho, yah us vacha ka lohoo haai jise yahova ne in sab vachanon par tumhare sath bandhaee haai.
tab moosa, haroon, nadab, abeehoo aur israaeliyon ke sattr puraaniae upar gaa,
aur israael ke parameshvar ka darshan kiya aur usake charanon ke tale neelamanai ka chabootara sa kuchh tha, jo akash ke tuly hee svachchh tha.
aur us ne israaeliyon ke pradhaanon par hath n baddhaya tab unhon ne parameshvar ka darshan kiya, aur khaya piya..
tab yahova ne moosa se kaha, pahad par mere pas chaddh, aur vahan raha aur maai tujhe patthr kee paattyaiaae, aur apanee likhee hui vyavastha aur agyaa doonga, ki too unako sikhaae.
tab moosa yahoshoo nam apane tthaluae samet parameshvar ke parvat par chaddh gaya.
ki jab tak ham tumhare pas fir n aaen tab tak tum yaheen hamaree batt johate raho aur suno, haroon aur hoor tumhare sang haain to yaadi kisee ka mukama ho to unheen ke pas jaae.
tab moosa parvat par chaddh gaya, aur badal ne parvat ko chha liya.
tab yahova ke tej ne seenaai parvat par nivas kiya, aur vah badal us par chh: din tak chhaya raha aur sataven din us ne moosa ko badal ke beech men se pukara.
aur israaeliyon kee draashtti men yahova ka tej parvat kee chottee par prachand ag sa dekh padta tha.
tab moosa badal ke beech men pravesh karake parvat par chaddh gaya. aur moosa parvat par chalees din aur chalees rat raha..
yahova ne moosa se kaha,
israaeliyon se yah kahana, ki mere liye bhentt laaen jitane apanee ichchha se dena chahen unheen sabhon se meree bhentt lena.
aur jin vastuon kee bhentt un se lenee haain ve ye haain arthata sona, chandee, peetal,
neele, baainjanee aur lal rang ka kapada, sooksham sanee ka kapada, bakaree ka bal,
lal rang se rangee hui meddhon kee khale, suison kee khale, babool kee lakadee,
ujiyale ke liye tel, abhaishok ke tel ke liye aur sugandhiat dhoop ke liye sugandha dravy,
aepod aur chaparas ke liye sulaaimanee patthr, aur jadne ke liye maanai.
jo kuchh maain tujhe dikhata hoo, arthata nivasasthan aur usake sab saman ka namoona, usee ke anusar tum log use banana..
babool kee lakadee ka aek sandook banaya jaae usakee lambai addhai hat, aur chaudai aur unchai deddh deddh hath kee hon.
aur usako chokhe sone se bheetar aur bahar maddhvana, aur sandook ke upar charon or sone kee bad banavana.
aur sone ke char kade ddhlavakar usake charon payon par, aek alang do kade aur doosaree alang bhee do kade lagavana.
fir babool kee lakadee ke dnde banavana, aur unhe bhee sone se maddhvana.
aur dndon ko sandook kee donon alangon ke kadon men dalana jis se unake bal sandook uttaya jaae.
aur jo sakshaeepatra maain tujhe doonga use usee sandook men rakhna.
fir chokhe sone ka aek praayashchaitt ka ddhkana banavana usakee lambai addhai hat, aur chaudai deddh hath kee ho.
aur sona ddhalakar do karoob banavakar praayashchaitt ke ddhkane ke donon siron par lagavana.
aek karoob to aek sire par aur doosara karoob doosare sire par lagavana aur karoobon ko aur praayashchaitt ke ddhkane ko usake hee ttukade se banakar usake dono siron par lagavana.
aur un karoobon ke pankh upar se aeese faaile huae banen ki praayashchaitt ka ddhkana un se ddhnpa rahe, aur unake mukh amhane-samhane aur praayaashchaitt ke ddhkane kee or rahen.
aur praayaashchaitt ke ddhkane ko sandook ke upar lagavana aur jo sakshaeepatra maain tujhe doonga use sandook ke bheetar rakhna.
aur maain usake upar rahakar tujh se mila karoonga aur israaeliyon ke liye jitanee agyaaaen mujh ko tujhe denee hongee, un sabhon ke vishay maain praayashchaitt ke ddhkane ke upar se aur un karoobon ke beech men se, jo sakshaeepatra ke sandook par honge, tujh se vartalap kiya karoonga..
fir babool kee lakadee kee aek mej banavana usakee lambai do hat, chaudai aek hat, aur unchai deddh hath kee ho.
use chokhe sone se maddhvana, aur usake charon or sone kee ek bad banavana.
aur usake charon or char angul chaudee aek pattree banavana, aur is pattree ke charon or sone kee aek bad banavana.
aur sone ke char kade banavakar mej ke un charon konon men lagavana jo usake charon payon men honge.
ve kade pattree ke pas hee ho, aur dndon ke gharon ka kam den ki menja unheen ke bal uttai jaae.
aur dndon ko babool kee lakadee ke banavakar sone se maddhvana, aur meja unheen se uttai jaae.
aur usake parat aur dhoopadan, aur chamache aur undelane ke kattore, sab chokhe sone ke banavana.
aur meja par mere age bhentt kee rottyaian nity rakha karana..
fir chokhe sone kee aek deevatt banavana. sona ddhlavakar vah deevat, paye aur dndee saahit banaya jaae usake pushpakosha, gantt aur fool, sab aek hee ttukade ke banen
aur usakee alangon se chh: daliyan nikale, teen daliyan to deevatt kee aek alang se aur teen daliyan usakee doosaree alang se nikalee hui hon
aek aek dalee men badam ke fool ke saman teen teen pushpakosha, aek aek gant, aur aek aek fool hon deevatt se nikalee hui chhhon daliyon ka yahee akar ya roop ho
aur deevatt kee dndee men badam ke fool ke saman char pushpakosh apanee apanee gantt aur fool samet hon
aur deevatt se nikalee hui chhhon daliyon men se do do daaliyon ke neeche aek aek gantt ho, ve deevatt samet aek hee ttukade ke bane huae hon.
unakee gantte aur daaliya, sab deevatt samet ek hee ttukade kee ho, chokha sona ddhlavakar poora deevatt ek hee ttukade ka banavana.
aur sat deepak banavana aur deepak jalaae jaaen ki ve deevatt ke samhane prakash den.
vah sab in samast saman samet kikkar bhr chokhe sone ka bane.
aur savadhaan rahakar in sab vastuon ko us namoone ke saman banavana, jo tujhe is parvat par dikhaya gaya haai..
fir nivasasthan ke liye das parade banavana inako battee hui saneevale aur neele, baainjanee aur lal rang ke kapade ka kaddhai ke kam kiae huae karoobon ke sath banavana.
aek aek parade kee lambai atthais hath aur chaudai char hath kee ho sab parade aek hee nap ke hon.
panch parade aek doosare se jude huae hon aur fir jo panch parade rahenge ve bhee aek doosare se jude huae hon.
aur jahan ye donon parade jode jaaen vahan kee donon chhoron par neelee neelee faliyan lagavana.
donon chhoron men pachas pachas faaliyan aeese lagavana ki ve amhane samhane hon.
fir nivas ke upar tamboo ka kam dene ke liye bakaree ke bal ke gyarah parade banavana.
aek aek parade kee lambai tees hath aur chaudai char hath kee ho gyarahon parade aek hee nap ke hon.
aur panch parade alag aur fir chh: parade alag judvana, aur chhttven parade ko tamboo ke samhane mod kar duhara kar dena.
aur too pachas ankaue us parade kee chhor men jo bahar se milaya jaaega aur pachas hee ankade doosaree or ke parade kee chhor men jo bahar se milaya jaaega banavana.
aur peetal ke pachas ankade banana, aur ankadon ko faaliyon men lagakar tamboo ko aeesa judvana ki vah milakar aek hee ho jaae.
aur tamboo ke paradon ka lattka hua bhag, arthata jo adha patt rahega, vah nivas kee pichhlee or lattka rahe.
aur tamboo ke paradon kee lambai me se hath bhr idhar, aur hath bhr udhar nivas ke ddhankane ke liye usakee donon alangon par lattka hua rahe.
fir tamboo ke liye lal rang se rangee hui meddhon kee khalon ka aek oddhna aur usake upar sooison kee khalon ka bhee aek oddhna banavana..
fir nivas ko khda karane ke liye babool kee lakadee ke takhte banavana.
aek aek takhte kee lambai das hath aur chaudai deddh hath kee ho.
aek aek takhte men aek doosare se jodee hui do do choolen hon nivas ke sab takhton ko isee bhanati se banavana.
aur nivas ke liye jo takhte too banavaaega un men se bees takhte to dakkhian kee or ke liye hon
aur beeson takhton ke neeche chandee kee chalees kursiyan banavana, arthata aek aek takhte ke neeche usake choolon ke liye do do kuarsiyan.
aur nivas kee doosaree alang, arthata uttr kee or bees takhte banavana.
aur unake liye chandee kee chalees kursiyan banavana, arthata aek aek takhte ke neeche do do kuarsiyan hon.
aur nivas kee pichhlee alang, arthata aek aek takhte ke neeche do do kursiyan hon.
aur pichhle alang men nivas ke konon ke liye do takhte banavana
aur ye neeche se do do bhag ke hon aur donon bhag upar ke sire tak aek aek kade men milaye jaaen donon takhton ka yahee roop ho ye to donon konon ke liye hon.
aur att takhten ho, aur unakee chandee kee solah kuarsiyan hon arthata aek aek takhte ke neeche do do kuarsiyan hon.
fir babool kee lakadee ke bende banavana, arthata nivas kee aek alang ke takhton ke liye panch,
aur nivas kee doosaree alang ke takhton ke liye panch bende, aur nivas kee jo alang paashchaim kee or pichhle bhag men hogee, usake liye panch bende banavana.
fir takhton ko sone se maddhvana, aur unake kade jo bendon ke gharon ka kam denge unhen bhee sone ke banavana aur bedon ko bhee sone se maddhvana.
aur nivas ko is reeati khda karana jaaisa is parvat par tujhe dikhaya gaya haai..
fir neele, baaijanee aur lal rang ke aur battee hui sooksham saneevale kapade ka aek beechavala parda banavana vah kaddhai ke kam kiye huae karoobon ke sath bane.
aur usako sone se maddhe huae babool ke char khmbhon par lattkana, inakee ankadiyan sone kee ho, aur ye chandee kee char kursiyon par khdee rahen.
aur beechavale parde ko ankaadiyon ke neeche lattkakar, usakee ad men sakshaeepatra ka sandook bheetar liva le jana so vah beechavala parda tumhare liye paavitrasthan ko paramapavitrasthan se alag kiye rahe.
fir paramapaavitra sthan men sakshaeepatra ke sandook ke upar praayashchaitt ke ddhkane ko rakhna.
aur us parde ke bahar nivas kee uttr alag meja rakhna aur usakee dakkhian alang meja ke samhane deevatt ko rakhna.
fir tamboo ke dar ke liye neele, baainjanee aur lal rang ke aur battee hui sooksham saneevale kapade ka kaddhai ka kam kiya hua aek parda banavana.
fir vedee ko babool kee lakadee kee, panch hath lambee aur panch hath chaudee banavana vedee chaukor ho, aur usakee unchai teen hath kee ho.
aur usake charon konon par char seeng banavana ve us samet aek hee ttukade ke ho, aur use peetal se maddhvana.
aur usakee rakh uttane ke patra, aur faavaadiya, aur kattore, aur kantte, aur angeettyaian banavana usaka kul saman peetal ka banavana.
aur usake peetal kee jalee aek jhnjhree banavana aur usake charon siron men peetal ke char kade lagavana.
aur us jhnjhree ko vedee ke charon or kee kanganee ke neeche aeese lagavana, ki vah vedee kee unchai ke madhy tak pahunche.
aur vedee ke liye babool kee lakadee ke dnde banavana, aur unhen peetal se maddhvana.
aur dnde kadon men dale jaae, ki jab jab vedee uttai jaae tab ve usakee donon alangon par rahen.
vedee ko takhton se khokhlee banavana jaaisee vah is parvat par tujhe dikhai gai haai vaaisee hee banai jaae..
fir nivas ke angan ko banavana. usakee dakkhian alang ke liye to battee hui sooksham sanee ke kapade ke sab padorn ko milaae ki usakee lambai sau hath kee ho aek alang par to itana hee ho.
aur unake bees khmbhe bane, aur inake liye peetal kee bees kursiyan bane, aur khmbhon ke kunde aur unakee pattiyan chandee kee hon.
aur usee bhanati angan kee uttr alang kee lambai men bhee sau hath lambe parde ho, aur unake bhee bees khmbhe aur inake liye bhee peetal ke bees khane hon aur un khmbhon ke kunde aur pattiyan chandee kee hon.
fir angan kee chaudai men paachchhim kee or pachas hath ke parde ho, unake khmbhe das aur khane bhee das hon.
aur poorab alang par angan kee chaudai pachas hath kee ho.
aur angan ke dar kee aek or pandrah hath ke parde ho, aur unake khmbhe teen aur khane teen hon.
aur doosaree or bhee pandrah hath ke parde ho, unake bhee khmbhe teen aur khane teen hon.
aur angan ke dar ke liye aek parda banavana, jo neele, baainjanee aur lal rang ke kapade aur battee hui sooksham sanee ke kapade ka kamadar bana hua bees hath ka ho, usake khmbhe char aur khane bhee char hon.
angan kee charon or ke sab khmbhe chandee kee pattiyon se jude huae ho, unake kunde chandee ke aur khane peetal ke hon.
angan kee lambai sau hath kee, aur usakee chaudai barabar pachas hath kee aur usakee kanat kee unchai panch hath kee ho, usakee kanat battee hui suksham sanee ke kapade kee bane, aur khmbhon ke khane peetal ke hon.
nivas ke bhanti bhanati ke bartan aur sab saman aur usake sab koontten aur angan ke bhee sab koontte peetal hee ke hon..
fir too israaeliyon ko agyaa dena, ki mere pas deevatt ke liye koott ke nikala hua jalapai ka nirmal tel le ana, jis se deepak nity jalata rahe.
fir too israaeliyon men se apane bhai haroon, aur nadab, abeeho, aeliajaar aur itamar nam usake putraen ko apane sameep le ana ki ve mere liye yajak ka kam karen.
aur too apane bhai haroon ke liye vibhv aur shaebha ke nimitt pavitra vasr banavana.
aur jitanon ke day men buaddh ihaai, jinako maain ne buaddh idenevalee atma se paripoorn kiya haai, unako too haroon ke vasr banane kee agyaa de ki vah mere nimitt yajak ka kam karane ke liye paavitra banen.
aur jo vasr unhen banane honge ve ye haai, arthata seenabanda aur aepod, aur jama, char khane ka angarakha, purohit ka ttop, aur kamarabanda ye hee pavitra vasr tere bhai haroon aur usake putraen ke liye banaae jaaen ki ve mere liye yajak ka kam karen.
aur ve sone aur neele aur baainjanee aur lal rang ka aur sooksham sanee ka kapada len..
aur ve aepod ko sone, aur neele, baainjanee aur lal rang ke kapade ka aur battee hui sooksham sanee ke kapade ka banaae, jo ki nipun kaddhai ke kam karanevale ke hath ka kam ho.
aur vah is tarah se joda jaae ki usake dono kandhaen ke sire apas men mile rahen.
aur aepod par jo kaddha hua pattuka hoga usakee banavatt usee ke saman ho, aur ve donon bina jod ke ho, aur sone aur neele, baainjanee aur lal rangavale aur battee hui sooksham saneevale kapade ke hon.
fir do sulaaimanee manai lekar un par israael ke putraen ke nam khudavana,
maanai khodanevale ke kam se jaaise chhapa khoda jata haai, vaaise hee un do manaiyon par israael ke putraen ke nam khudavana aur unako sone ke khanon men jadva dena.
aur donon manaiyon ko aepod ke kandhaen par lagavana, ve israaeliyon ke nimitt smaran dilavane vale manai ttharenge arthata haroon unake nam yahova ke age apane donon kandhaen par smaran ke liye lagaae rahe..
fir sone ke khane banavana,
aur doriyon kee nain goonthe huae do janjeer chokhe sone ke banavana aur goonthe huae janjeeron ko un khanon men jadvana.
fir nyay kee chaparas ko bhee kaddhai ke kam ka banavana aepod kee nain sone, aur neele, baainjanee aur lal rang ke aur battee hui sooksham sanee ke kapade kee use banavana.
vah chaukor aur doharee ho, aur usakee lambai aur chaudai aek aek bitte kee hon.
aur us men char panti manai jadana. paahilee panti men to manaiky, padamarag aur laladee hon
doosaree panati men marakat, neelamaanai aur heera
teesaree panti men lasham, sooryakant aur neelama
aur chauthee panati men faeeroja, sulaaimanee manai aur yashab hon ye sab sone ke khanon men jade jaaen.
aur israael ke putraen ke jitane nam haain utane maanai ho, arthata unake namon kee ginatee ke anusar barah nam khude, barahon gotraen men se aek aek ka nam aek aek manai par aeese khude jese chhapa khoda jata haai.
fir chaparas par doriyon kee nai. goonthe huae chokhe sone kee janjeer lagavana
aur chaparas men sone kee do kadiyan lagavana, aur donon kaadiyon ko chaparas ke dono siron par lagavana.
aur sone ke donon goonthe janjeeron ko un donon kadiyon men jo chaparas ke siron par hongee lagavana
aur goonthe huae dono janjeeron ke donon bakee siron ko donon khanon men jadva ke aepod ke donon kandhaen ke bandhanon par usake samhane lagavana.
fir sone kee do aur kaadiyan banavakar chaparas ke donon siron par, usakee us kor par jo aepod kee bheetar kee or hogee lagavana.
fir unake sivay sone kee do aur kadiyan banavakar aepod ke donon kandhaen ke bandhanon par, neeche se unake samhane aur usake jod ke pas aepod ke kaddhe huae pattuke ke upar lagavana.
aur chaparas apanee kaadiyon ke dara aepod kee kaadiyon men neele faeete se bandhaee jaa, is reeati vah aepod ke kaddhe huae pattuke par banee rahe, aur chaparas aepod par se alag n hone paae.
aur jab jab haroon pavitrasthan men pravesh kare, tab tab vah nyay kee chaparas par apane day ke upar israaeliyon ke namon ko lagaae rahe, jis se yahova ke samhane unaka smaran nity rahe.
fir aepod ke bage ko sampoorn neele rang ka banavana.
aur usakee banavatt aeesee ho ki usake beech men sir dalane ke liye chhed ho, aur us chhed kee charon or bakhtar ke chhed kee see aek bunee hui kor ho, ki vah fattne n paae.
aur usake neechevale ghore men charon or neeele, baainjanee aur lal rang ke kapade ke anar banavana, aur unake beech beech charon or sone kee ghantteeyan lagavana,
arthata aek sone kee ghanttee aur aek anar, fir aek sone kee ghanttee aur aek anar, isee reeti bage ke neechevale ghore men charon or aeesa hee ho.
aur haroon aek bage ko seva tthal karane ke samay pahina kare, ki jab jab vah pavitrasthan ke bheetar yahova ke samhane jaa, va bahar nikale, tab tab usaka shabd sunai de, naheen to vah mar jaaega.
fir chokhe sone ka aek tteeka banavana, aur jaaise chhape men vaaise hee us men ye akshar khoden jaae, arthata yahova ke liye paavitra.
aur use neele faeete se bandhana aur vah pagadee ke samhane ke hisse par rahe.
aur haroon ke mathe par rahe, isaaliye ki israaelee jo kuchh pavitra ttharaae, arthata jitanee pavitra vastuaen bhentt men chaddhaven un paavitra vastuon ka dosh haroon uttaae rahe, aur vah nity usake mathe par rahe, jis se yahova un se prasann rahe..
aur angarakhe ko sooksham sanee ke kapade ka charakhana bunavana, aur aek pagadee bhee sooksham sanee ke kapade kee banavana, aur karachobee kam kiya hua aek kamaraband bhee banavana..
fir haroon ke putraen ke liye bhee angarakhe aur kamaraband aur ttopiyan banavana ye vasr bhee vibhv aur shaebha ke liye banen.
aur unake liye sanee ke kapade kee janghaiya banavana jin se unaka tan ddhpa rahe ve kamar se jangha tak kee hon
aur jab jab haroon va usake putra milapavale tamboo men pravesh kare, va pavitra sthan men seva tthal karane ko vedee ke pas jaaen tab tab ve un janghaiyon ko paahine rahe, n ho ki ve papee ttharen aur mar jaaen. yah haroon ke liye aur usake bad usake vansh ke liye bhee sada kee vidhai ttharen..
aur unhen paavitra karane ko jo kam tujhe un se karana haai, ki ve mere liye yajak ka kam karen vah yah haai. aek nirdosh bachhda aur do nirdosh menddhe lena,
aur akhmeeree rottee, aur tel se sane huae maaide ke akhmeeree faulake, aur tel se chupadee hui akhmeeree papadiyan bhee lena. ye sab gehoon ke maaide ke banavana.
inako aek ttokaree men rakhkar us ttokaree ko us bachhde aur un donon menddho samet sameep le ana.
fir haroon aur usake putraen ko milapavale tamboo ke dar ke sameep le akar jal se nahalana.
tab un vasren ko lekar haroon ko angarakha or aepod ka baga paahinana, aur aepod aur chaparas bandhana, aur aepod ka kaddha hua pattuka bhee bandhana
aur usake sir par pagadee ko rakhna, aur pagadee par pavitra mukutt ko rakhna.
tab aabhaishok ka tel le usake sir par dalakar usaka abhaishok karana.
fir usake putraen ko sameep le akar unako angarakhe pahinana,
aur usake arthata haroon aur usake putraen ke kamar bandhana aur unake sir par ttopiyan rakhna jis se yajak ke pad par sada unaka hak rahe. isee prakar haroon aur usake putraen ka sanskar karana.
aur bachhde ko milapavale tamboo ke samhane sameep le ana. aur haroon aur usake putra bachhde ke sir par apane apane hath rakhe,
tab us bachhde ko yahova ke sammukh milapavale tamboo ke dar par balidan karana,
aur bachhde ke lohoo men se kuchh lekar apanee ungalee se vedee ke seengon par lagana, aur shosh sab lohoo ko vedee ke paae par undel dena
aur jis charabee se antadiyan ddhpee rahatee haai, aur jo jhlilee kaleje ke upar hotee haai, unako aur dono gudorn ko unake upar kee charabee samet lekar sab ko vedee par jalana.
aur bachhde ka mans, aur khal, aur gobar, chhavanee se bahar ag men jala dena kyonki yah papabali hoga.
fir aek meddha lena, aur haroon aur usake putra usake sir par apane apane hath rakhe,
tab us meddhen ko baali karana, aur usaka lohoo lekar vedee par charon or chhdikana.
tab us poore meddhe ko vedee par jalana vah to yahova ke liye homabaali hoga vah sukhdayak sugandha aur yahova ke liye havan hoga.
fir doosare meddhe ko lena aur haroon aur usake putra usake sir par apane apane hath rakhe,
tab us mende ko bali karana, aur usake lohoo men se kuchh lekar haroon aur usake putraen ke daahine kan ke sire par, aur unake dahine hath aur daahine panv ke angootton par lagana, aur lohoo ko vedee par charon or chhdik dena.
fir vedee par ke loho, aur aabhaishok ke tel, in dono men se kuchh kuchh lekar haroon aur usake vasren par, aur usake putraen aur unake vasren par bhee chhdik dena tab vah apane vasren samet aur usake putra bhee apane apane vasren samet pavitra ho jaaenge.
tab meddhe ko sanskaravala janakar us men se charabee aur mottee poonchh ko, aur jis charabee se antadiyan ddhpee rahatee haain usako, aur kaleje par kee jhlilee ko, aur charabee samet donon gudorn ko, aur dahine putthe ko lena,
aur akhmeeree rottee kee ttokaree jo yahova ke age dharee hogee us men se bhee aek rottee, aur tel se sane huae maaide ka aek faulaka, aur aek papadee lekar,
in sab ko haroon aur usake putraen ke hathon men rakhkar hilaae jane kee bhentt ttharake yahova ke age hilaya jaae.
tab un vastuon ko unake hathon se lekar homabali kee vedee par jala dena, jis se vah yahova ke samhane sukhdayak sugandha tthare vah to yahova ke liye havan hoga.
fir haroon ke sanskar ko jo menddha hoga usakee chhatee ko lekar hilaae jane kee bhentt ke liye yahova ke age hilana aur vah tera bhag ttharega.
aur haroon aur usake putraen ke sanskar ka jo meddha hoga, us men se hilaae jane kee bhenttvalee chhatee jo hilai jaaegee, aur uttaae jane ka bhenttvala puttha jo uttaya jaaega, in donon ko pavitra ttharana.
aur ye sada kee vidhai kee reeti par israaeliyon kee or se usaka aur usake putraen ka bhag tthare, kayonaki ye uttaae jane kee bhentten ttharee haain aur yah israaeliyon kee or se unake melabaaliyon men se yahova ke liye uttaaee jane kee bhentt hogee.
usake putraen ke jo usake sthan par yajak hoga, vah jab pavitrasthan men seva tthal karane ko milap vale tamboo men pahile aa, tab un vasren ko sat din tak pahine rahen.
fir yajak ke sanskar ka jo meddha hoga use lekar usaka mans kisee paavitra sthan men pakana
tab haroon apane putraen samet us meddhe ka mans aur ttokaree kee rottee, donon ko milapavale tamboo ke dar par khaae.
aur jin padathorn se unaka sanskar aur unhen paavitra karane ke liye praayaashchaitt kiya jaaega unako to ve khaae, parantu paraae kul ka koi unhen n khane paa, kyonki ve pavitra honge.
aur yaadi sanskaravale mans va rottee men se kuchh bihan tak bacha rahe, to us bache huae ko ag men jalana, vah khaya n jaae kyonaki vah pavitra hoga.
aur maain ne tujhe jo jo agyaa dee haai, un sabhon ke anusar too haroon aur usake putraen se karana aur sat din tak unaka sanskar karate rahana,
arthata papabaali ka aek bachhda praayaashchaitt ke liye praatidin chaddhana. aur vedee ko bhee praayashchaitt karane ke samay shuuddh karana, aur use paavitra karane ke liye usaka aabhaishok karana.
sat din tak vedee ke liye praayaashchaitt karake use paavitra karana, aur vedee param paavitra ttharegee aur jo kuchh us se choo jaaega vah bhee paavitra ho jaaega..
jo tujhe vedee par nity chaddhana hoga vah yah haai arthata pratidin aek aek varsha ke do bhedee ke bachche.
aek bhed ke bachche ko to bhor ke samay, aur doosare bhed ke bachche ko godhooli ke samay chaddhana.
aur aek bhed ke bachche ke sang heen kee chauthai koottke nikale huae tel se sana hua aepa ka dasavan bhag maaida, aur argha ke liye hee kee chauthai dakhmadha dena.
aur doosare bhed ke bachche ko godhooli ke samay chaddhana, aur usake sath bhor kee reeti anusar annabaali aur argha donon dena, jis se vah sukhdayak sugandha aur yahova ke liye havan tthare.
tumharee peeddhee peeddhee men yahova ke age milapavale tamboo ke dar par nity aeesa hee homabali hua kare yah vah sthan haai jis men maain tum logon se isaaliye mila karoonga, ki tujh se baten karoon.
aur maain israaeliyon se vaheen mila karoonga, aur vah tamboo mere tej se paavitra kiya jaaega.
aur maain milapavale tamboo aur vedee ko paavitra karoonga, aur haroon aur usake putraen ko bhee paavitra karoonga, ki ve mere liye yajak ka kam karen.
aur maain israaeliyon ke madhy nivas karoonga, aur unaka parameshvar ttharoonga.
tab ve jan lenge ki maain yahova unaka parameshvar hoo, jo unako misr desh se isaliye nikal le aya, ki unake madhy nivas karoon maain hee unaka parameshvar yahova hoon..
aur vah sree garbhvatee hui aur usake aek putra utpann hua aur yah dekhkar ki yah balak sundar haai, use teen maheene tak chhpai rakha.
aur jab vah use aur chhpai n sakee tab usake liye sarakandon kee aek ttokaree lekar, us men balak ko rakhkar neel nadee ke teer par kanson ke beech chhod ai.
us balak ki bahin door khdee rahee, ki dekhe isaka kya hal hoga.
tab firaun kee bettee nahane ke liye nadee ke teer ai usakee saakhaiyan nadee ke teer teer tthalane lageen tab us ne kanson ke beech ttokaree ko dekhkar apanee dasee ko use le ane ke liye bheja.
tab us ne use kholakar dekha, ki aek rota hua balak haai tab use taras aya aur us ne kaha, yah to kisee ibraee ka balak hoga.
tab balak kee bahin ne firaun kee bettee se kaha, kya maain jakar ibraee striayon men se kisee dhaai ko tere pas bula le aun jo tere liye balak ko doodha pilaya kare?
firaun kee bettee ne kaha, ja. tab ladkee jakar balak kee mata ko bula le ai.
firaun kee bettee ne us se kaha, too is balak ko le jakar mere liye doodha pilaya kar, aur maain tujhe majadooree doongee. tab vah sree balak ko le jakar doodha pilane lagee.
jab balak kuchh bada hua tab vah use firaun kee bettee ke pas le gai, aur vah usaka betta tthara aur us ne yah kahakar usaka nam moosa rakha, ki maain ne isako jal se nikal liya..
un dinon men aeesa hua ki jab moosa javan hua, aur bahar apane bhai bandhauon ke pas jakar unake du:khon par draashtti karane laga tab us ne dekha, ki koi misree jan mere ek ibraee bhai ko mar raha haai.
jab us ne idhar udhar dekha ki koi naheen haai, tab us misree ko mar dala aur baloo men chhpai diya..
fir doosare din bahar jakar us ne dekha ki do ibraee puroosh apas men marapeett kar rahe haain us ne aparadhaee se kaha, too apane bhai ko kyon marata haai ?
jab firaun ne yah bat sunee tab moosa ko ghaat karane kee yuaktai kee. tab moosa firaun ke samhane se bhaga, aur midhan desh men jakar rahane laga aur vah vahan aek kuaen ke pas baaitt gaya.
midhan ke yajak kee sat bettyaian thee aur ve vahan akar jal bhrane lagee, ki kattauton men bhrake apane pita kee bhedbakariyon ko pilaaen.
tab charavahe akar unako hattane lage is par moosa ne khda hokar unakee sahayata kee, aur bhed-bakaariyon ko panee pilaya.
jab ve apane pita rooael ke pas fir ai, tab us ne un se poochha, kya karan haai ki aj tum aeesee faurtee se ai ho ?
unhon ne kaha, ek misree puroosh ne ham ko charavahon ke hath se chhudaya, aur hamare liye bahut jal bhrake bhed-bakaariyon ko pilaya.
tab us ne apanee beattyaien se kaha, vah puroosh kahan haai ? tum usako kyon chhod ai ho ? usako bula le ao ki vah bhojan kare.
aur moosa us puroosh ke sath rahane ko prasann hua us ne use apanee bettee sippora ko byah diya.
aur usake aek putra utpann hua, tab moosa ne yah kahakar, ki maain any desh men paradeshaee hoo, usaka nam gesharem rakha..
bahut dinon ke beetane par misr ka raja mar gaya. aur israaelee kattnai seva ke karan lambee lambee sans lekar ahen bhrane lage, aur pukar utte, aur unakee dohai jo kattnai seva ke karan hui vah parameshvar tak pahunchee.
aur parameshvar ne unaka karahana sunakar apanee vacha ko, jo us ne ibraaheem, aur isahak, aur yakoob ke sath bandhaee thee, smaran kiya.
aur parameshvar ne israaeliyon par draashtti karake un par chitt lagaya..
fir dhoop jalane ke liye babool kee lakadee kee vedee banana.
