so ve tujh se mil jaae, aur milapavale tamboo kee saree sevakai kee vastuon kee raksha kiya karen parantu jo tere kul ka n ho vah tum logon ke sameep n ane paae.
aur paavitrasthan aur vedee kee rakhvalee tum hee kiya karo, jis se israaeliyon par fir kop n bhdke.
parantu maain ne ap tumhare levee bhaiyon ko israaeliyon ke beech se alag kar liya haai, aur ve milapavale tamboo kee seva karane ke liye tum ko aur yahova ko saunp diye gaae haain.
fir yahova ne haroon se kaha, sun, maai ap tujh ko uttai hui bhentt saunp deta hoo, arthata israaeliyon kee paavitra kee hui vastuen jitanee hon unhen maain tera abhaishok vala bhag ttharakar tujhe aur tere putraen ko sada ka hak karake de deta hoon.
jo paramapavitra vastuaen ag men hom n hee jaaengee ve teree hee tthare, arthata israaeliyon ke sab chaddhavon men se unake sab annabaali, sab papabali, aur sab doshabali, jo ve mujh ko de, vah tere aur tere putraen ke liye paramapavitra ttharen.
unako paramapavitra vastu janakar khaya karana unako har ek puroosh kha sakata haai ve tere liye paavitra haain.
fir ye vastuen bhee teree tthare, arthata jitanee bhentt israaelee hilane ke liye de, unako maain tujhe aur tere bette-bettyaien ko sada ka hak karake de deta hoon tere gharane men jitane shuuddh hon vah unhen kha sakenge.
fir uttm se uttm naya dakhmadha, aur gehoo, arthata inakee pahalee upaj jo ve yahova ko de, vah maain tujh ko deta hoon.
unake desh ke sab prakar kee pahalee upaj, jo ve yahova ke liye le ae, vah teree hee tthare tere gharane men jitane shuuddh hon ve unhen kha sakengen.
israaeliyon men jo kuchh arpan kiya jaae vah bhee tera hee tthare.
sab praanaiyon men se jitane apanee apanee man ke pahilautte ho, jinhen log yahova ke liye chaddhaae, chahe manushy ke chahe pashu ke paahilautte ho, ve sab tere hee ttharen parantu manushyon aur ashuuddh pashuuon ke paahilautton ko dam lekar chhod dena.
aur jinhen chhudana ho, jab ve maheene bhr ke hon tab unake liye apane ttharaae huae mol ke anusar, arthata pavitrasthan ke bees gera ke shokel ke hisab se panch shokel leke unhen chhodna.
par gay, va bhedee, va bakaree ke pahilautte ko n chhodna ve to paavitra haain. unake lohoo ko vedee par chhdik dena, aur unakee charabee ko havy karake jalana, jis se yahova ke liye sukhdayak sugandha ho
parantu unaka mans tera tthare, aur hilai hui chhatee, aur dahinee jangha bhee tera hee tthare.
paavitra vastuon kee jitanee bhentten israaelee yahova ko de, un sabhon ko maain tujhe aur tere bette-beattyaien ko sada ka hak karake de deta hoon: yah to tere aur tere vansh ke liye yahova kee sada ke liye namak kee attl vacha haai.
fir yahova ne haroon se kaha, israaeliyon ke desh men tera koi bhag n hoga, aur n unake beech tera koi ansh hoga unake beech tera bhag aur tera ansh maain hee hoon..
fir milapavale tamboo kee jo seva levee karate haain usake badale maain unako israaeliyon ka sab dashamansh unaka nij bhag kar deta hoon.
aur bhavishy men israaelee milapavale tamboo ke sameep n aae, aeesa n ho ki unake sir par pap lage, aur ve mar jaaen.
parantu levee milapavale tamboo kee seva kiya kare, aur unake adharma ka bhar ve hee uttaya karen yah tumharee peeddheeyon men sada kee vidhai tthare aur israaeliyon ke beech unaka koi nij bhag n hoga.
kyonaki israaelee jo dashamansh yahova ko uttai hui bhentt karake denge, use maain leviyon ko nij bhag karake deta hoo, iseealiye maain ne unake vishay men kaha haai, ki israaeliyon ke beech koi bhag unako n mile.
fir yahova ne moosa se kaha,
too leaviyon se kah, ki jab jab tum israaeliyon ke hath se vah dashamansh lo jise yahova tum ko tumhara nij bhag karake un se dilata haai, tab tab us men se yahova ke liye aek uttai hui bhentt karake dashamansh ka dashamansh dena.
is reeati tum bhee apane sab dashamanshaen men se, jo israaeliyon kee or se paoge, yahova ko aek uttai hui bhentt dena aur yahova kee yah uttai hui bhentt haroon yajak ko diya karana.
jitane dan tum pao un men se har aek ka uttm se uttm bhag, jo pavitra tthara haai, so use yahova ke liye uttai hui bhentt karake pooree pooree dena.
isaliye too leaviyon se kah, ki jab tum us men ka uttm se uttm bhag uttakar do, tab yah tumhare liye khalihan men ke ann, aur rasakund ke ras ke tuly gina jaaega
aur usako tum apane gharanon samet sab sthanon men kha sakate ho, kyonki milapavale tamboo kee jo seva tum karoge usaka badala yahee tthara haai.
aur jab tum usaka uttm se uttm bhag uttakar do tab usake karan tum ko pap n lagega. parantu israaeliyon kee paavitra kee hui vastuon ko apavitra n karana, aeesa n ho ki tum mar jao..
fir yahova ne moosa aur haroon se kaha,
vyavastha kee jis vidhai kee agyaa yahova deta haai vah yah haai ki too israaeliyon se kah, ki mere pas aek lal nirdosh baachhyai le ao, jis men koi bhee dosh n ho, aur jis par jooa kabhee n rakha gaya ho.
tab aeleeajar yajak ko do, aur vah use chhavanee se bahar le jaa, aur koi usako usake samhane baalidan kare
tab aeleeajar yajak apanee ungalee se usaka kuchh lohoo lekar milapavale tamboo ke samhane kee or sat bar chhdik de.
tab koi us bachhyai ko khal, mans, loho, aur gobar samet usake samhane jalaae
tab vah apane vasr dhaeae aur snan kare, isake bad chhavanee men to aa, parantu sanjh tak ashuuddh rahe.
aur jo manushy usako jalaae vah bhee jal se apane vasr dhaeae aur snan kare, aur sanjh tak ashuuddh rahe.
fir koi shuuddh puroosh us bachhyai kee rakh battorakar chhavanee ke bahar kisee shuuddh sthan men rakh chhode aur vah rakh israaeliyon kee mandlee ke liye ashuuddhta se chhudanevale jal ke liye rakhee rahe vah to papabaali haai.
aur jo manushy baachhyai kee rakh battore vah apane vasr dhaea, aur sanjh tak ashuuddh rahe. aur yah israaeliyon ke liye, aur unake beech rahanevale paradeashaiyon ke liye bhee sada kee vidhai tthare.
jo kisee manushy kee loth chooae vah sat din tak ashuuddh rahe
aeesa manushy teesare din us jal se pap chhudakar apane ko pavan kare, aur sataven din shuuddh tthare parantu yadi vah teesare din ap ko pap chhudakar pavan n kare, to sataven din shuuddh ttharega.
jo koi kisee manushy kee loth chookar pap chhudakar apane ko pavan n kare, vah yahova ke nivasasthan ka ashuuddh karanevala ttharega, aur vah praanee israael men se nash kiya jaae ashuuddhta se chhudanevala jal us par n chhdika gaya, is karan vah ashuuddh ttharega, usakee ashuuddhta us men bachee rahegee.
yaadi koi manushy dere men mar jaae to vyavastha yah yah haai, ki jitane us dere men rahe, va us men jaae, ve sab sat din tak ashuuddh rahen.
aur har aek khula hua patra, jis par koi ddhkana laga n ho, vah ashuuddh tthare.
aur jo koi maaidan men talavar se mare huae ko, va apanee mratyu se mare huae ko, va manushy kee haddee ko, va kisee kabra ko chooa, to sat din tak ashuuddh rahe.
ashuuddh manushy ke liye jalaae huae papabali kee rakh men se kuchh lekar patra men dalakar us par sote ka jal dala jaae
tab koi shuuddh manushy joofaa lekar us jal men dubakar jal ko us dere par, aur jitane patra aur manushy us men ho, un par chhdike, aur haddee ke, va mare huae ke, va apanee mratyu se mare huae ke, va kabra ke choonevale par chhdik de
vah shuuddh puroosh teesare din aur sataven din us ashuuddh manushy par chhdike aur sataven din vah usake pap chhudakar usako pavan kare, tab vah apane vasren ko dhaekar aur jal se snan karake sanjh ko shuuddh tthare.
aur jo koi ashuuddh hokar apane pap chhudakar apane ko pavan n karaa, vah praanee yahova ke paavitra sthan ka ashuuddh karanevala ttharega, is karan vah mandlee ke beech men se nash kiya jaae ashuuddhta se chhudanevala jal us par n chhdika gaya, is karan se vah ashuuddh ttharega.
aur yah unake liye sada kee vidhai tthare. jo ashuuddhta se chhudanevala jal chhdike vah apane vasren ko dhaeae aur jis jan se ashuuddhta se chhudanevala jal choo jaae vah bhee sanjh tak ashuuddh rahe.
aur jo kuchh vah ashuuddh manushy chooae vah bhee ashuuddh tthare aur jo praanee us vastu ko chooae vah bhee sanjh tak ashuuddh rahe..
israaeliyon ke misr desh se nikal jane ke doosare varsha ke doosare maheene ke paahile din ko, yahova ne seenaai ke jangal men milapavale tamboo me, moosa se kaha,
israaeliyon kee saree mandlee ke kulon aur pitaron ke gharanon ke anusar, aek aek puroosh kee ginatee nam le lekar karana
aur tumhare sath aek aek gotra ka aek aek puroosh bhee ho jo apane pitaron ke gharane ka mukhy puroosh ho.
tumhare un sathaiyon ke nam ye haai, arthata rooben ke gotra men se shadeur ka putra aeleesoora
shaimon ke gotra men se sooreeshaai ka putra shaloomeeaela
yahooda ke gotra men se ammeenadab ka putra nahashaena
issakar ke gotra men se sooa ka putra natanela
jabooloon ke gotra men se helon ka putra aeleeaba
yoosufavanshaiyon men se ye haai, arthata aerpaaim ke gotra men se ammeehood ka putra aeleeshaama, or manashsho ke gotra men se padasoor ka putra gamleeaela
binyameen ke gotra men se gidonee ka putra abeedana
dan ke gotra men se ammeeshaai ka putra aheeaeejera
ashor ke gotra men se okran ka putra pageeaela
gad ke gotra men se dooael ka putra aelyasapa
mandlee men se jo puroosh apane apane pitaron ke gotraen ke pradhaan hokar bulaae gaae ve ye hee haai, aur ye israaeliyon ke hajaron men mukhy puroosh the.
aur jin purooshaen ke nam upar likhe haain unako sath lekar,
moosa aur haroon ne doosare maheene ke paahile din saree mandlee ikatthee kee, tab israaeliyon ne apane apane kul aur apane apane pitaron ke gharane ke anusar bees varsha va us se aadhaik avasthavalon ke namon kee ginatee karava ke apanee apanee vanshaavalee likhvai
jis prakar yahova ne moosa ko jo agyaa dee thee usee ke anusar us ne seenaai ke jangal men unakee ganna kee..
aur israael ke pahilautte rooben ke vansh ne jitane puroosh apane kul aur apane pitaron ke gharane ke anusar bees varsha va us se aadhaik avastha ke the aur yuddh karane ke yogy the, ve sab apane apane nam se gine gaae:
aur rooben ke gotra ke gine huae puroosh saddhe chhyaialees hajar the..
aur shaimon ke vansh ke log jitane puroosh apane kulon aur apane pitaron ke gharanon ke anusar bees varsha va us se aadhaik avastha ke the, aur jo yuddh karane ke yogy the ve sab apane apane nam se gine gaae:
aur shaimon ke gotra ke gine huae puroosh unasatt hajar teen sau the..
aur gad ke vansh ke jitane puroosh apane kulon aur apane pitaron ke gharanon ke anusar bees varsha va us se aadhaik avastha ke the aur jo yuddh karane ke yogy the, ve sab apane apane nam se gine gaae:
aur gad ke gotra ke gine huae puroosh paaintalees hajar saddhe chh: sau the..
aur yahooda ke vansh ke jitane puroosh apane kulon aur apane pitaron ke gharanon ke anusar bees varsha va us se aadhaik avastha ke the aur jo yuddh karane ke yogy the, ve sab apane apane nam se gine gaae:
aur yahooda ke gotra ke gine huae puroosh chauhattr hajar chh: sau the..
aur issakar ke vansh ke jitane puroosh apane kulon aur apane pitaron ke gharanon ke anusar bees varsha va us se aadhaik avastha ke the aur jo yuddh karane ke yogy the, ve sab apane apane nam se gine gaae:
aur issakar ke gotra ke gine huae puroosh chauvan hajar char sau the..
aur jabooloon ve vansh ke jitane puroosh apane kulon aur apane pitaron ke gharanon ke anusar bees varsha va us se aadhaik avastha ke the aur jo yuddh karane ke yogy the, ve sab apane apane nam se gine gaae:
aur jabooloon ke gotra ke gine huae puroosh sattavan hajar char sau the..
aur yoosufa ke vansh men se aepraaim ke vansh ke jitane puroosh apane kulon aur apane pitaron ke gharanon ke anusar bees varsha va us se aadhaik avastha ke the aur jo yuddh karane ke yogy the, ve sab apane apane nam se gine gaae:
aur manashsho ke vansh ke jitane puroosh apane kulon aur apane pitaron ke gharanon ke anusar bees varsha va us se aadhaik avastha ke the aur jo yuddh karane ke yogy the, ve sab apane apane nam se gine gaae:
aur manashsho ke gotra ke gine huae puroosh battees hajar do sau the..
aur binyameen ke vansh ke jitane puroosh apane kulon aur apane pitaron ke gharanon ke anusar bees varsha va us se aadhaik avastha ke the aur jo yuddh karane ke yogy the, ve sab apane apane nam se gine gaae:
aur binyameen ke gotra ke gine huae puroosh paaintees hajar char sau the..
aur dan ke vansh ke jitane puroosh apane kulon aur apane pitaron ke gharanon ke anusar bees varsha va us se aadhaik avastha ke the aur jo yuddh karane ke yogy the, ve apane apane nam se gine gaae:
aur dan ke gotra ke gine huae puroosh basatt hajar sat sau the..
aur ashor ke vansh ke jitane puroosh apane kulon aur apane pitaron ke gharanon ke anusar bees varsha va usase aadhaik avastha ke the aur jo yuddh karane ke yogy the, ve sab apane apane nam se gine gaae:
aur ashor ke gotra ke gine huae puroosh saddhe aekatalees hajar the..
aur naptalee ke vansh ke jitane puroosh apane kulon aur apane pitaron ke gharanon ke anusar bees varsha va us se aadhaik avastha ke the aur jo yuddh karane ke yogy the, ve sab apane apane nam se gine gaae:
aur naptalee ke gotra ke gine huae puroosh tirapan hajar char sau the..
is prakar moosa aur haroon aur israael ke barah pradhaanon ne, jo apane apane pitaron ke gharane ke pradhaan the, un sabhon ko gin liya aur unakee ginatee yahee thee.
so jitane israaelee bees varsha va us se aadhaik avastha ke hone ke karan yuddh karane ke yogy the ve apane pitaron ke gharanon ke anusar gine gaa,
in men leveey apane pitaron ke gotra ke anusar naheen gine gaae.
kyonaki yahova ne moosa se kaha tha,
ki leveey gotra kee ginatee israaeliyon ke sang n karana
parantu too leviyon ko sakshaee ke tamboo par, aur usake kul saman par, nidan jo kuchh us se sambandha rakhta haai us par aadhaikaree niyukt karana aur kul saman saahit nivas ko ve hee uttaya kare, aur ve hee us men seva tthal bhee kiya kare, aur tamboo ke asapas ve hee apane dere dala karen.
aur jab jab nivas ka kooch ho tab tab leveey usako gira de, aur jab jab nivas ko khda karana ho tab tab leveey usako khda kiya karen aur yaadi koi doosara sameep aae to vah mar dala jaae.
aur israaelee apana apana dera apanee apanee chhavanee men aur apane apane jhnde ke pas khda kiya karen
par leveey apane dere sakshaee ke tamboo hee kee charon or khde kiya kare, kaheen aeesa n ho ki israaeliyon kee mandlee par kop bhdke aur leveey sakshaee ke tamboo kee raksha kiya karen.
jo agyaaaen yahova ne moosa ko dee theen israaeliyon ne unheen ke anusar kiya..
paahile maheene men saree israaelee mandlee ke log seenaai nam jangal men a gaa, aur kadesh men rahane lage aur vahan maariyam mar gai, aur vaheen usako mittee dee gai.
vahan mandlee ke logon ke liye panee n mila so ve moosa aur haroon ke virooddh ikatthe huae.
aur log yah kahakar moosa se jhgadne lage, ki bhla hota ki ham us samay hee mar gaae hote jab hamare bhai yahova ke samhane mar gaae!
aur tum yahova kee mandlee ko is jangal men kyon le aae ho, ki ham apane pashuuon samet yahan mar jaae?
aur tum ne ham ko misr se kyon nikalakar is bure sthan men pahunchaya haai? yahan to beech, va anjeer, va dakhlata, va anar, kuchh naheen haai, yahan tak ki peene ko kuchh panee bhee naheen haai.
tab moosa aur haroon mandlee ke samhane se milapavale tamboo ke dar par jakar apane munh ke bal gire. aur yahova ka tej unako dikhai diya.
tab yahova ne moosa se kaha,
us lattee ko le, aur too apane bhai haroon samet mandlee ko ikattha karake unake dekhte us chattan se baten kar, tab vah apana jal degee is prakar se too chattan men se unake liye jal nikal kar mandlee ke logon aur unake pashuuon ko pila.
aur moosa aur haroon ne mandlee ko us chattan ke samhane ikattha kiya, tab moosa ne us se kah, he danga karanevalo, suno kya ham ko is chattan men se tumhare liye jal nikalana hoga?
tab moosa ne hath uttakar lattee chattan par do bar maree aur us men se bahut panee foott nikala, aur mandlee ke log apane pashuuon samet peene lage.
parantu moosa aur haroon se yahova ne kaha, tum ne jo mujh par vishvas naheen kiya, aur mujhe israaeliyon kee draashtti men pavitra naheen ttharaya, isaliye tum is mandlee ko us desh men pahunchane n paoge jise maain ne unhen diya haai.
us sote ka nam mareeba pada, kyonki israealiyon ne yahova se jhgada kiya tha, aur vah unake beech paavitra ttharaya gaya..
fir moosa ne kadesh se aedom ke raja ke pas doot bheje, ki tera bhai israael yon kahata haai, ki ham par jo jo klesh pade haain vah too janata hoga
arthata yah ki hamare purakha misr men gaae the, aur ham misr men bahut din rahe aur mistriyon ne hamare purakhaon ke sath aur hamare sath bhee bura bartav kiya
parantu jab ham ne yahova kee dohai dee tab us ne hamaree sunee, aur aek doot ko bhejakar hamen misr se nikal le aya haai so ab ham kadesh nagar men haain jo tere sivane hee par haai.
so hamen apane desh men se hokar jane de. ham kisee khet va dakh kee baree se hokar n chalenge, aur kooon ka panee n peeaenge sadka-sadk hokar chale jaaenge, aur jab tak tere desh se bahar n ho jaae, tab tak n daahine n baaen mudenge.
parantu aedomiyon ne usake pas kahala bheja, ki too mere desh men se hokar mat ja, naheen to maain talavar liye huae tera samhana karane ko nikaloonga.
israaeliyon ne usake pas fir kahala bheja, ki ham sadk hee sadk chalenge, aur yaadi ham aur hamare pashu tera panee peeae, to usaka dam denge, ham ko aur kuchh nahee, keval panv panv chalakar nikal jane de.
parantu us ne kaha, too ane n paaega. aur aedom badee sena lekar bhujabal se usaka samhana karane ko nikal aya.
is prakar aedom ne israael ko apane desh ke bheetar se hokar jane dene se inkar kiya isaliye israael usakee or se mud gaae..
tab israaeliyon kee saree mandlee kadesh se kooch karake hor nam pahad ke pas a gai.
haroon apane logon meen ja milega kyonki tum dono ne jo mareeba nam sote par mera kahana chhodkar mujh se balava kiya haai, is karan vah us desh men jane n paaega jise maain ne israaeliyon ko diya haai.
so too haroon aur usake putra aeleeajar ko hor pahad par le chala
aur haroon ke vasr utarake usake putra aeleeajar ko pahina tab haroon vaheen marakar apane logon me ja milega.
yahova kee is agyaa ke anusar moosa ne kiya ve saree mandlee ke dekhte hor pahad par chaddh gaae.
tab moosa ne haroon ke vasr utarake usake putra aeleeajar ko pahinaae aur haroon vaheen pahad kee chottee par mar gaya. tab moosa aur aeleeajar pahad par se utar aae.
aur jab israael kee saree mandlee ne dekha ki haroon ka praan choott gaya haai, tab israael ke sab gharane ke log usake liye tees din tak rote rahe..
tab arad ka kananee raja, jo daakkhian desh men rahata tha, yah sunakar, ki jis marga se ve bheadiye aae the usee marga se ab israaelee a rahe haai, israael se lada, aur un men se kitanon ko bandhaua kar liya.
tab israaeliyon ne yahova se yah kahakar mannat manee, ki yadi too sachamuch un logon ko hamare vash men kar de, to ham unake nagaron ko satyanash kar denge.
israael kee yah bat sunakar yahova ne kanaaniyon ko unake vash men kar diya so unhon ne unake nagaron samet unako bhee satyanash kiya is se us sthan ka nam horma rakha gaya..
fir unhon ne hor pahad se kooch karake lal samudra ka marga liya, ki aedom desh se bahar bahar ghoomakar jaaen aur logon ka man marga ke karan bahut vyakul ho gaya.
so ve parameshvar ke virooddh bat karane lage, aur moosa se kaha, tum log ham ko misr se jangal men marane ke liye kyon le aae ho? yahan n to rottee haai, aur n panee, aur hamare praan is nikammee rottee se dukhait haain.
so yahova ne un logon men tej vishavale sanp bheje, jo unako dsane lage, aur bahut se israaelee mar gaae.
tab log moosa ke pas jakar kahane lage, ham ne pap kiya haai, ki ham ne yahova ke aur tere virooddh baten kee haain yahova se praarthna kar, ki vah sanpon ko ham se door kare. tab moosa ne unake liye praarthna kee.
yahova ne moosa se kaha aek tej vishavale sanp kee pratima banavakar khmbhe par lattka tab jo sanp se dsa hua usako dekh le vah jeeavit bachega.
so moosa ne peetal ko aek sanp banavakar khmbhe par lattkaya tab sanp ke dse huon men se jis jis ne us peetal ke sanp ko dekha vah jeeavit bach gaya.
aur obot se kooch karake abareem nam deehon men dere dale, jo poorab kee or moab ke samhane ke jangal men haai.
vanha se kooch karake unhon ne jered nam nale men dere dale.
vahan se kooch karake unhon ne anorn nadee, jo jangal men bahatee aur aemoriyon ke desh se nikalatee haai, usakee paralee or dere khde kiae kyonaki arnon moaabiyon aur aemoriyon ke beech hokar moab desh ka sivana tthara haai.
is karan yahova ke sangraam nam pustak men is prakar likha haai, ki soopa men baheb, aur anorn ke nale,
