isaka karan yah haai, ki seen jangal me, kadesh ke mareeba nam sote par, tum donon ne mera aparadha kiya, kyonaki tum ne israaeliyon ke madhy men mujhe paavitra n ttharaya.
isaliye vah desh jo maain israaeliyon ko deta hoo, too apane samhane dekh lega, parantu vahan jane n paaega..
us ne kaha, yahova seenaai se aya, aur seir se unake liye uday hua us ne paran parvat par se apana tej dikhaya, aur lakhon paavitraen ke madhy men se aya, usake dahine hath se unake liye jvalamay vidhaiyan nikaleen..
vah nishchay desh desh ke logon se praem karata haai usake sab paavitra log tere hath men haain: ve tere panvon ke pas baaitte rahate haai,
moosa ne hamen vyavastha dee, aur yakoob kee mandlee ka nij bhag ttharee..
jab praja ke mukhy mukhy puroosha, aur israael ke gotraee aek sang hokar aekaatrait hua, tab vah yashooroon men raja tthara..
rooben n mare, varan jeeavit rahe, taubhee usake yahan ke manushy thode hon..
aur yahooda par yah ashaeervad hua jo moosa ne kaha, he yahova too yahooda kee sun, aur use usake logon ke pas pahuncha. vah apane liye ap apane hathon se lada, aur too hee usake drohiyon ke virooddh usaka sahayak ho..
fir levee ke vishay men us ne kaha, tere tummeem aur ureem tere bhkt ke pas haai, jisako too ne massa men parakh liya, aur jisake sath mareeba nam sote par tera vadaavivad hua
us ne to apane mata pita ke vishay men kaha, ki maain unako naheen janata aur n to us ne apane bhaiyon ko apana mana, aur n apane putraen ko paahichana. kyonki unhon ne teree baten manee, aur ve teree vacha ka palan karate haain..
ve yakoob ko tere niyam, aur israael ko teree vyavastha sikhaaenge aur tere age dhoop aur teree vedee par sarvang pashu ko homabaali karenge..
he yahova, usakee sampaati par ashaeesh de, aur usake hathon kee seva ko grahan kara usake virodhaiyon aur baairiyon kee kamar par aeesa mar, ki ve fir n utt saken..
fir us ne binyameen ke vishay men kaha, yahova ka vah piry jan, usake pas nidr vas karega aur vah din bhr us par chhaya karega, aur vah usake kandhaen ke beech raha karata haai..
fir yoosufa ke vishay men us ne kaha isaka desh yahova se ashaeesh paae arthata akash ke anamol padarth aur os, aur vah gahira jal jo neeche haai,
aur soorya ke pakaae huae anamol fal, aur jo anamol padarth chandrama ke ugaae ugate haai,
aur praacheen pahadon ke uttm padarth, aur sanatan pahadiyon ke anamol padarth,
aur prathvee aur jo anamol padarth us men bhre haai, aur jo jhadee men rahata tha usakee prasannata. in sabhon ke vishay men yoosufa ke sir par, arthata usee ke sir ke chand par jo apane bhaiyon se nyara hua tha ashaeesh hee ashaeesh fale..
vah pratapee haai, mano gaya ka pahilautta haai, aur usake seeng banaaile baail ke se haain un se vah desh desh ke logon ko, varan prathvee ke chhor tak ke sab manushyon ko ddhkelega ve aepraaim ke lakhon lak, aur manashsho ke hajaron hajar haain..
fir jabooloon ke vishay men us ne kaha, he jabooloon, too bahar nikalate samay, aur he issakar, too apane deron men anand kare..
ve desh desh ke logon ko pahad par bulaaenge ve vahan dharmayagya karenge kyonaki ve samudr ka dhan, aur baloo ke chhpai huae anamol padarth se labh uttaaenge..
fir gad ke vishay men us ne kaha, dhany vah haai jo gad ko baddhata haai! gad to sinhanee ke saman rahata haai, aur banh ko, varan sir ke chand tak ko faad dalata haai..
aur us ne paahila ansh to apane liye chun liya, kyonaki vahan rais ke yogy bhag rakha hua tha tab us ne praja ke mukhy mukhy purooshaen ke sang akar yahova ka ttharaya hua dharma, aur israael ke sath hokar usake niyam ka praatipalan kiya..
fir dan ke vishay men us ne kaha, dan to bashaan se koodanevala sinh ka bachcha haai..
fir naptalee ke vishay men us ne kaha, he naptalee, too jo yahova kee prasannata se trapt, aur usakee ashaeesh se bhrapoor haai, too paachchhim aur dakkhian ke desh ka adhaikaree ho..
tere joote lohe aur peetal ke honge, aur jaaise tere din vaaisee hee teree shaaktai ho..
he yashooroon, ishvar ke tuly aur koi naheen haai, vah teree sahayata karane ko akash par, aur apana pratap dikhata hua akashamandl par savar hokar chalata haai..
anadi parameshvar tera grahadhaam haai, aur neeche sanatan bhujaaen haain. vah shatrauon ko tere samhane se nikal deta, aur kahata haai, unako satyanash kar de..
aur israael nidr basa rahata haai, ann aur naye dakhmadha ke desh men yakoob ka sota akela hee rahata haai aur usake upar ke akash se os pada karatee haai..
he israael, too kya hee dhany haai! he yahova se uddhar pai hui praja, tere tuly kaun haai? vah to teree sahayata ke liye ddhal, aur tere pratap ke liye talavar haai tere shatra tujhe sarahenge, aur too unake unche sthanon ko raundega..
fir moosa moab ke araba se nabo pahad par, jo pisaga kee aek chottee aur yareeho ke samhane haai, chaddh gaya aur yahova ne usako dan tak ka gilad nam sara desha,
aur naptalee ka sara desha, aur aepraaim aur manashsho ka desha, aur pachchhim ke samudr tak ka yahooda ka sara desha,
tab yahova ne us se kaha, jis desh ke vishay men maain ne ibraaheem, isahak, aur yakoob se shapath khakar kaha tha, ki maain ise tere vansh ko doonga vah yahee haai. maain ne isako tujhe sakshaat dikhla diya haai, parantu too par hokar vahan jane n paaega.
tab yahova ke kahane ke anusar usaka das moosa vaheen moab desh men mar gaya,
aur us ne use moab ke desh men betapor ke samhane aek tarai men mittee dee aur aj ke din tak koi naheen janata ki usakee kabra kahan haai.
moosa apanee mratyu ke samay aek sau bees varsha ka tha parantu n to usakee ankhen dhaundhalee padee, aur n usaka pauroosh ghatta tha.
aur israaelee moab ke araba men moosa ke liye tees din tak rote rahe tak moosa ke liye rone aur vilap karane ke din poore hue.
aur noon ka putra yahoshoo buaddhmaianee kee atma se paripoorn tha, kyonaki moosa ne apane hath us par rakhe the aur israaelee us agyaa ke anusar jo yahova ne moosa ko dee thee usakee manate rahe.
aur moosa ke tuly israael men aeesa koi nabee naheen utta, jis se yahova ne amhane-samhane baten kee,
aur usako yahova ne firaun aur usake sab karmachaariyon ke samhane, aur usake sare desh me, sab chinh aur chamatkar karane ko bheja tha,
aur us ne sare israaeliyon kee draashtti men balavant hath aur bade bhy ke kam kar dikhaae..
tab ham mudkar bashaan ke marga se chaddh chale aur bashaan ka og nam raja apanee saree sena samet hamara samhana karane ko nikal aya, ki aedraei men yuddh kare.
tab yahova ne mujh se kaha, us se mat dra kyonaki maain usako saree sena aur desh samet tere hath men kiae deta hoo aur jaaisa too ne heshabon ke nivasee aemoriyon ke raja seehon se kiya haai vaaisa hee us se bhee karana.
so is prakar hamare parameshvar yahova ne saree sena samet bashaan ke raja og ko bhee hamare hath men kar diya aur ham usako yaha tak marate rahe ki un men se koi bhee n bach paya.
usee samay ham ne unake sare nagaron ko le liya, koi aeesa nagar n rah gaya jise ham ne us se n le liya ho, is reeati argob ka sara desha, jo bashaan men og ke rajy men tha aur us men satt nagar the, vah hamare vash men a gaya.
ye sab nagar gaddhvale the, aur unake unchee unchee shaharapanah, aur faattk, aur bede the, aur inako chhod bina shaharapanah ke bhee bahut se nagar the.
aur jaaisa ham ne heshabon ke raja seehon ke nagaron se kiya tha vaaisa hee ham ne in nagaron se bhee kiya, arthat sab base huae nagaron ko striayon aur balabachchon samet satyanash kar dala.
parantu sab ghareloo pashu aur nagaron kee loott ham ne apanee kar lee.
yon ham ne us samay yaradan ke is par rahanevale aemoriyon ke donon rajaon ke hath se arnon ke nale se lekar hermon parvat tak ka desh le liya.
hemorn ko seedonee log siryon, aur aemoree log saneer kahate haain.
samathr desh ke sab nagar, aur sara gilad, aur salka, aur aerdei tak jo og ke rajy ke nagar the, sara bashaan hamare vash men a gaya.
jo rapai rah gaae the, un men se keval bashaan ka raja og rah gaya tha, usakee charapai jo lohe kee haai vah to ammaeaniyon ke rabba nagar men padee haai, sadhaaran puroosh ke hath ke hisab se usakee lambai nau hath kee aur chaudai char hath kee haai.
jo desh ham ne us samay apane aadhaikar men le liya vah yah haai, arthat anorn ke nale ke kinarevale aroaer nagar se le sab nagaron samet gilad ke pahadee desh ka adha bhag, jise maain ne roobeaniyon aur gaadiyon ko de diya,
aur manashshoi yair ne gashooriyon aur makavaasiyon ke sivanon tak argob ka sara desh le liya, aur bashaan ke nagaron ka nam apane nam par habbotyair rakha, aur vahee nam aj tak bana haai.
aur maain ne gilad desh makeer ko de diya,
aur roobeniyon aur gaadiyon ko maain ne gilad se le anorn ke nale tak ka desh de diya, arthat us nale ka beech unaka sivana ttharaya, aur yabbok nadee tak jo ammoniyon ka sivana haai
aur kinnoret se le pisaga kee salamee ke neeche ke araba ke tal tak, jo khara tal bhee kahalata haai, araba aur yaradan kee poorva kee or ka sara desh bhee maain ne unheen ko de diya..
aur us samay maain ne tumhen yah agyaa dee, ki tumhare parameshvar yahova ne tumhen yah desh diya haai ki use apane aadhaikar men rakho tum sab yoddha haathaiyaraband hokar apane bhai israaaeliyon ke age age par chalo.
parantu tumharee striaya, aur balabachche, aur pashu, jinhen maain janata hoo ki bahut se haai, vah sab tumhare nagaron men jo maain ne tumhen diae haain rah jaae.
aur jab yahova tumhare bhaiyon ko vaaisa vishraam de jaaisa ki us ne tum ko diya haai, aur ve us desh ke aadhaikaree ho jaae jo tumhara parameshvar yahova unhen yaradan par deta haai tab tum bhee apane apane aadhaikar kee boomi par jo maain ne tumhen dee haai lauttoge.
fir maain ne usee samay yahoshoo se chitakar kaha, too ne apanee akho se dekha haai ki tere parameshvar yahova ne in donon rajaon se kya kya kiya haai vaaisa hee yahova un sab rajyon se karega jin men too par hokar jaaega.
usee samay maain ne yahova se gidgidakar binatee kee, ki he prabhu yahova,
too apane das ko apanee maahima aur balavant hath dikhane laga haai svarga men aur prathvee par aeesa kaun devata haai jo tere se kam aur parakram ke karma kar sake?
isaliye mujhe par jane de ki yaradan parake us uttm desh ko, arthat us uttm pahad aur labanon ko bhee dekhne pau.
parantu yahova tumhare karan mujh se rooshtt ho gaya, aur meree n sunee kintu yahova ne mujh se kaha, bas kara is vishay men fir kabhee mujh se baten n karana.
pisaga pahad kee chottee par chaddh ja, aur poorva, pachchhim, uttr, daakkhian, charon or draashtti karake us desh ko dekh le kyonaki too is yaradan ke par jane n paaega.
aur yahoshoo ko agyaa de, aur use ddhaddhs dekar draddh kara kyonaki in logon ke age age vahee par jaaeega, aur jo desh too dekhega usako vahee unaka nij bhag kara dega.
tab ham betapor ke samhane kee tarai men tthare rahe..
ab, he israael, jo jo vidhai aur niyam maain tumhen sikhana chahata hoon unhen sun lo, aur un par chalo jis se tum jeevit raho, aur jo desh tumhare pitaron ka parameshvar yahova tumhen deta haai us men jakar usake adhaikaree ho jao.
jo agyaa maain tum ko sunata hoon us men n to kuchh baddhana, aur n kuchh ghattana tumhare parameshvar yahova kee jo jo agyaa maain tumhen sunata hoon unhen tum manana.
tum ne to apanee ankhon se dekha haai ki balapor ke karan yahova ne kya kya kiya arthata jitane manushy balapor ke peechhe ho liye the un sabhon ko tumhare parameshvar yahova ne tumhare beech men se satyanash kar dala
parantu tum jo apane parameshvar yahova ke sath lipatte rahe ho sab ke sab aj tak jeeavit ho.
suno, maain ne to apane parameshvar yahova kee agyaa ke anusar tumhen vidhai aur niyam sikhaae haai, ki jis desh ke aadhaikaree hone jate ho us men tum unake anusar chalo.
so tum unako dhaaran karana aur manana kyonaki aur deshaen ke logon ke samhane tumharee buaddh iddh aur samajh isee se pragatt hogee, arthata ve in sab vidhaiyon ko sunakar kahenge, ki nishchay yah badee jati buddhmaian aur samajhdar haai.
dekho, kaun aeesee badee jaati haai jisaka devata usake aeese sameep rahata ho jaaisa hamara parameshvar yahova, jab ki ham us ko pukarate haain?
fir kaun aeesee badee jaati haai jisake pas aeesee dharmamay vidhai aur niyam ho, jaaisee ki yah saree vyavastha jise maain aj tumhare samhane rakhta hoon?
yah atyant avashyak haai ki tum apane vishay men sachet raho, aur apane man kee badee chaukasee karo, kaheen aeesa n ho ki jo jo baten tum ne apanee ankhon se dekheen unako bool jao, aur vah jeevan bhr ke liye tumhare man se jatee rahe kintu tum unhen apane betton poton ko sikhana.
vishosh karake us din kee baten jis men tum horeb ke pas apane parameshvar yahova ke samhane khde the, jab yahova ne mujh se kaha tha, ki un logon ko mere pas ikattha kar ki maain unhen apane vachan sunau, jis se ve seekhe, taki jitane din ve prathvee par jeevit rahen utane din mera bhy manate rahe, aur apane ladke balon ko bhee yahee sikhaaen.
tab tum sameep jakar us parvat ke neeche khde hua, aur vah pahad ag se dhadhak raha tha, aur usakee lau akash tak pahunchatee thee, aur usake charon or andhiayara, aur badal, aur ghaer andhakar chhaya hua tha.
tak yahova ne us ag ke beech men se tum se baten kee baton ka shabd to tum ko sunai pada, parantu koi roop n dekha keval shabd hee shabd sun pada.
aur us ne tum ko apanee vacha ke dason vachan batakar unake manane kee agyaa dee aur unhen patthr kee do paattyaiaon par likh diya.
isaliye tum apane vishay men bahut savadhaan rahana. kyonaki jab yahova ne tum se horeb parvat par ag ke beech men se baten kee tab tum ko koi roop n dekh pada,
kaheen aeesa n ho ki tum bigadkar chahe puroosh chahe sree ke,
chahe prathvee par chalanevale kisee pashu, chahe akash men udnevale kisee pakshaee ke,
chahe boomi par renganevale kisee jantu, chahe prathvee ke jal men rahanevalee kisee machhlee ke roop kee koi mootira khodakar bana lo,
va jab tum akash kee or ankhe uttakar, soorya, chandrama, aur taron ko, arthata akash ka sara taragan dekho, tab bahakakar unhen dandvata karake unakee seva karane lago jinako tumhare parameshvar yahova ne dharatee par ke sab deshavalon ke liye rakha haai.
aur tum ko yahova lohe ke bhtthe ke sareekhe misr desh se nikal le aya haai, isaliye ki tum usakee prajaroopee nij bhag ttharo, jaaisa aj pragatt haai.
fir tumhare karan yahova ne mujh se krodha karake yah shapath khai, ki too yaradan par jane n paaega, aur jo uttm desh israaeliyon ka parameshvar yahova unhen unaka nij bhag karake deta haai us men too pravesh karane n paaega.
kintu mujhe isee desh men marana haai, maain to yaradan par naheen ja sakata parantu tum par jakar us uttm desh ke adhaikaree ho jaoge.
isaliye apane vishay men tum savadhaan raho, kaheen aeesa n ho ki tum us vacha ko boolakar, jo tumhare parameshvar yahova ne tum se bandhaee haai, kisee aur vastu kee mootira khodakar banao, jise tumhare parameshvar yahova ne tum ko mana kiya haai.
yaadi us desh men rahate rahate bahut din beet jane par, aur apane bette-pote utpann hone par, tum bigadkar kisee vastu ke roop kee moorti khodakar banao, aur is reeti se apane parameshvar yahova ke prati burai karake use aprasann kar do,
to maain aj akash aur prathvee ko tumhare virooddh sakshaee karake kahata hoo, ki jis desh ke aadhaikaree hone ke liye tum yaradan par jane par ho us men tum jaldee bilkul nash ho jaoge aur bahut din rahane n paoge, kintu pooree reeti se nashtt ho jaoge.
aur yahova tum ko desh desh ke logon men titar bitar karega, aur jin jatiyon ke beech yahova tum ko pahunchaaega un men tum thode hee se rah jaoge.
aur vahan tum manushy ke banaae huae lakadee aur patthr ke devataon kee seva karoge, jo n dekhte, aur n sunate, aur n khate, aur n soonghate haain.
parantu vahan bhee yaadi tum apane parameshvar yahova ko ddoonddhoge, to vah tum ko mil jaaega, sharta yah haai ki tum apane poore man se aur apane sare praan se use ddoonddho.
ant ke dinon men jab tum sankatt men pado, aur ye sab vipaatiayan tum par a padengee, tab tum apane parameshvar yahova kee or firo aur usakee manana
kyonaki tera parameshvar yahova dayalu ishvar haai, vah tum ko n to chhodega aur n nashtt karega, aur jo vacha us ne tere pitaron se shapath khakar bandhaee haai usako naheen boolega.
aur jab se parameshvar ne manushy ho utpann karake prathvee par rakha tab se lekar too apane utpann hone ke din tak kee baten pooch, aur akash ke aek chhor se doosare chhor tak kee baten pooch, kya aeesaee badee bat kabhee hui va sunane men ai haai?
kya koi jaati kabhee parameshvar kee vanee ag ke beech men se atee hui sunakar jeevit rahee, jaaise ki too ne sunee haai?
fir kya parameshvar ne aur kisee jaati ko doosaree jaati ke beech men nikalane ko kamar bandhakar pareeksha, aur chinh, aur chamatkar, aur yudd, aur balee hat, aur baddhai hui bhuja se aeese bade bhyanak kam kia, jaaise tumhare parameshvar yahova ne misr men tumhare dekhte kiae?
yah sab tujh ko dikhaya gaya, isaliye ki too jan rakhe ki yahova hee parameshvar haai usako chhod aur koi haai hee naheen.
akash men se us ne tujhe apanee vanee sunai ki tujhe shaiksha de aur prathvee par us ne tujhe apanee badee ag dikhai, aur usake vachan ag ke beech men se ate huae tujhe sun pade.
aur us ne jo tere pitaron se praem rakha, is karan unake peechhe unake vansh ko chun liya, aur pratyaksha hokar tujhe apane bade samathrya ke dara misr se isaaliye nikal laya,
ki tujh se badee aur samarthee jatiyon ko tere age se nikalakar tujhe unake desh men pahunchaa, aur use tera nij bhag kar de, jaaisa aj ke din dikhai padta haai
so aj jan le, aur apane man men soch bhee rak, ki upar akash men aur neeche prathvee par yahova hee parameshvar haai aur koi doosara naheen.
aur too usakee vidhaiyon aur agyaaon ko jo maain aj tujhe sunata hoon manana, isaaliye ki tera aur tere peechhe tere vansh ka bhee bhla ho, aur jo desh tera parameshvar yahova tujhe deta haai us men tere din bahut varan sada ke liye hon.
tab moosa ne yaradan ke par poorva kee or teen nagar alag kia,
isaliye ki jo koi bina jane aur bina pahale se baair rakhe apane kisee bhai ko mar dale, vah un men se kisee nagar men bhag jaa, aur bhagakar jeevit rahe:
arthata roobeniyon ka beser nagar jo jangal ke samathr desh men haai, aur gaadiyon ke gilad ka ramot, aur manashshoiyon ke bashaan ka golana.
ye hee ve chitauaniyan aur niyam haain jinhen moosa ne israaeliyon ko us samay kah sunaya jab ve misr se nikale the,
arthata yaradan ke par betapor ke samhane kee tarai me, aemoriyon ke raja heshabonavasee seehon ke desh me, jis raja ko unhon ne misr se nikalane ke peechhe mara.
aur unhon ne usake desh ko, aur bashaan ke raja og ke desh ko, apane vash men kar liya yaradan ke par sooryoday kee or rahanevale aemoriyon ke rajaon ke ye desh the.
yah desh arnon ke nale ke chhoravale aroaer se lekar seeon, jo hemorn bhee kahalata haai,
us parvat tak ka sara desha, aur pisaga kee salamee ke neeche ke araba ke tal tak, yaradan par poorva kee or ka sara araba haai.
moosa ne sare israaeliyon ko bulavakar kaha, he israaeliyo, jo jo vidhai aur niyam maain aj tumhen sunata hoon ve suno, isaaliye ki unhen seekhkar manane men chaukasee karo.
hamare parameshvar yahova ne to horeb par ham se vacha bandhaee.
is vacha ko yahova ne hamare pitaron se nahee, ham hee se bandha, jo yahan aj ke din jeevit haain.
yahova ne us parvat par ag ke beech men se tum logon se amhane samhane baten kee
us ag ke dr ke mare tum parvat par n chaddhe, isaaliye maain yahova ke aur tumhare beech usaka vachan tumhen batane ko khda raha. tab us ne kaha,
mujhe chhod doosaron ko parameshvar karake n manana..
tu apane liye koi moorti khodakar n banana, n kisee kee praatima banana jo akash me, va prathvee ke jal men haai
too unako dandvata n karana aur n unakee upasana karana kyonki maain tera parameshvar yahova jalan rakhnevala ishvar hoo, aur jo mujh se baair rakhte haain unake betto, poto, aur parapoton ko pitaron ka dand diya karata hoo,
aur jo mujh se praem rakhte aur meree agyaaon ko manate haain un hajaron par karoona kiya karata hoon.
too apane parameshvar yahova ka nam vyarth n lena kyonaki jo yahova ka nam vyarth le vah unako nirdosh n ttharaaega..
too vishraamadin ko manakar pavitra rakhna, jaaise tere parameshvar yahova ne tujhe agyaa dee.
chh: din to parishram karake apana sara kamakaj karana
