usee din logon ne bade bade melabaali chaddhaa, aur anand liya kyonaki parameshvar ne unako bahut hee anandait kiya tha striayon ne aur balabachchon ne bhee anand kiya. aur yarooshalem ke anand kee dhvaani door door tak faail gai.
usee din khjaanon ke, uttai hui bhentton ke, pahilee paahilee upaj ke, aur dashamanshaen kee kottriyon ke aadhaikaree ttharaae gaa, ki un men nagar nagar ke kheton ke anusar un vastuon ko jama kare, jo vyavastha ke anusar yajakon aur leviyon ke bhag men kee thee kyonaki yahoodee upasthit yajakon aur leviyon ke karan anaandait the.
isaliye ve apane parameshvar ke kam aur shuuddhata ke vishay chaukasee karate rahe aur gavaaiye or darapal bhee daud aur usake putra sulaaiman kee agyaa ke anusar vaaisa hee karate rahe.
praacheenakal, arthata daud aur asap ke dinon men to gavaaiyon ke pradhaan the, aur parameshvar kee stuati aur dhanyavad ke geet gaae jate the.
aur jarubbabel aur nahemayah ke dinon men sare israaaelee, gavaaiyon aur darapalon ke pratidin ka bhag dete rahe aur ve leviyon ke ansh paavitra karake dete the aur leveey haroon kee santan ke ansh pavitra karake dete the.
usee din moosa kee pustak logon ko paddhkar sunai gai aur us men yah likha hua mila, ki koi ammonee va moabee parameshvar kee sabha men kabhee n ane pae
kyonaki unhon ne ann jal lekar israaaeliyon se bhentt naheen kee, varan bilam ko unhen shaap dene ke liye daakshiana dekar bulavaya tha--taubhee hamare parameshvar ne us shaap ko ashaeesh se badal diya.
is se paahile aelyashaeeb yajak jo hamare parameshvar ke bhvan kee kottriyon ka aadhaikaree aur tobiyyah ka sambandhaee tha.
us ne tobiyyah ke liye ek badee kottree taaiyar kee thee jis men pahile annabaali ka saman aur loban aur patra aur anaj, naye dakhmadha aur ttttke tel ke dashamansha, jinhen leviyo, gavaaiyon aur darapalon ko dene kee agyaa thee, rakhee hui thee aur yajakon ke liye uttai hui bhentt bhee rakhee jatee theen.
parantu maain is samay yarooshalem men naheen tha, kyonki babel ke raja artakshatra ke batteesaven varsha men maain raja ke pas chala gaya. fir kitane dinon ke bad raja se chhuttee mangee,
aur maain yarooshalem ko aya, tab maain ne jan liya, ki aelyashaeeb ne tobiyyah ke liye parameshvar ke bhvan ke anganon men aek kottree taaiyar kar, kya hee burai kee haai.
ise maain ne bahut bura mana, aur tobiyyah ka sara ghareloo saman us kottree men se faenk diya.
tab meree agyaa se ve kottriyan shuuddh kee gai, aur maain ne parameshvar ke bhvan ke patra aur annabali ka saman aur loban un men fir se rakhva diya.
fir mujhe maloom hua ki leviyon ka bhag unhen naheen diya gaya haai aur is karan kam karanevale leveey aur gavaaiye apane apane khet ko bhag gaae haain.
tab maain ne hakimon ko danttkar kaha, parameshvar ka bhvan kyon tyaga gaya haai? fir maain ne unako ikattha karake, aek aek ko usake sthan par niyukt kiya.
tab se sab yahoodee anaj, naye dakhmadha aur ttttke tel ke dashamansh bhndaron men lane lage.
aur maain ne bhndaron ke aadhaikaree sholemyah yajak aur sadok munshaee ko, aur leaviyon men se padayah ko, aur unake neeche hanan ko, jo mattanyah ka pota aur jakkoor ka putra tha, niyukt kiya ve to vishvasayogy gine jate the, aur apane bhaiyon ke may banttna unaka kam tha.
he mere parameshvar ! mera yah kam mere hit ke liye smaran rak, aur jo jo sukarma maain ne apane parameshvar ke bhvan aur us men kee aradhana ke vishay kiae haain unhe mitta n dala.
unheen dinon men maain ne yahooda men kitanon ko dekha jo vishraamadin ko haaidon men dakh raundate, aur pooliyon ko le ate, aur gadahon par ladate the vaaise hee ve dakhmadha, dak, anjeer aur bhanti bhanati ke bojh vishraamadin ko yarooshalem men late the tab jis din ve bhojanavastu bechate the, usee din maain ne unako chita diya.
fir us men soree log rahakar machhlee aur bhanti bhanati ka sauda le akar, yahoodiyon ke hath yarooshalem men vishraamadin ko becha karate the.
tab maain ne yahooda ke raison ko danttkar kaha, tum log yah kya burai karate ho, jo vishraamadin ko apaavitra karate ho?
kya tumhare purakha aeesa naheen karate the? aur kya hamare parameshvar ne yah sab vipaattai ham par aur is nagar par n dalee? taubhee tum vishraamadin ko apaavitra karane se israaael par parameshvar ka krodha aur bhee bhdkate jate ho.
isaliye vyoparee aur bhanati bhanati ke saude ke bechanevale yarooshalem ke bahar do aek ber ttkaie.
tab maain ne unako chitakar kaha, tum log shaharapanah ke samhane kyon ttkaite ho? yaadi tum fir aeesa karoge to maain tum par hath baddhaunga. isaliye us samay se ve fir vishraamabar ko naheen aae.
tab maain ne leviyon ko agyaa dee, ki apane apane ko shuuddh karake faattkon kee rakhvalee karane ke liye aya karo, taaki vishraamadin pavitra mana jaae. he mere parameshvar ! mere hit ke liye yah bhee smaran rakh aur apanee badee karuna ke anusar mujh par taras kha.
fir unheen dinon men mujh ko aeese yahoodee dikhai pade, jinhon ne ashadodee, ammonee aur moabee striayan byah lee theen.
aur unake ladkebalon kee adhaee bolee ashadodee thee, aur ve yahoodee bolee n bol sakate the, donon jati kee bolee bolate the.
tab maain ne unako dantta aur kosa, aur un men se kitanon ko pittva diya aur unake bal nuchavaae aur unako parameshvar kee yah shapath khailai, ki ham apanee bettyaian unake betton ke sath byah men n denge aur n apane liye va apane betton ke liye unakee beettyaian byah men lenge.
kya israaael ka raja sulaaiman isee prakar ke pap men n fansa th? bahuteree jaatiyon men usake tuly koi raja naheen hua, aur vah apane parameshvar ka piry bhee tha, aur parameshvar ne use sare israaael ke upar raja niyukt kiya parantu usako bhee anyajaati striayon ne pap men fansaya.
to kya ham tumharee sunakar, aeesee badee burai karen ki anyajaati kee striayan byah kar apane parameshvar ke viruddh pap karen?
aur aelyashaeeb mahayajak ke putra yoyada ka aek putra, horonee samballat ka damad tha, isaliye maain ne usako apane pas se bhga diya.
he mere parameshvar unakee hani ke liye yajakapad aur yajakon or leviyon kee vacha ka toda jana smaran rakh.
is prakar maain ne unako sab anyajatiyon se shuuddh kiya, aur aek aek yajak aur leveey kee baree aur kam tthara diya.
fir maain ne lakadee kee bhentt le ane ke vishosh samay tthara dia, aur paahilee paahilee upaj ke dene ka prabandha bhee kiya. he mere parameshvar ! mere hit ke liye mujhe smaran kara.
hakalyah ke putra nahemayah ke vachana. beesaven varsha ke kisalave nam maheene me, jab maain shooshan nam rajagaddh men rahata tha,
tab hananee nam mera aek bhai aur yahooda se aae huae kai aek purush aae tab maain ne un se un bache huae yahoodiyon ke vishay jo bandhauai se choott gaae the, aur yarooshalem ke vishy men poochha.
ye baten sunate hee maain baaittkar rone laga aur kitane din tak vilap karata aur svarga ke parameshvar ke sammukh upavas karata aur yah kahakar praarthna karata raha.
he svarga ke parameshvar yahova, he mahan aur bhyayogy ishvar ! too jo apane praem rakhnevale aur agyaa mananevale ke vishy apanee vacha palata aur un par karuna karata haai
too kan lagaae aur ankhen khole rah, ki jo praarthna maain tera das is samay tere das israaaeliyon ke liye din rat karata rahata hoo, use too sun le. maain israaaeliyon ke papon ko jo ham logon ne tere viruddh kiae haai, man leta hoo. maain aur mere pita ke gharane donon ne pap kiya haai.
ham ne tere samhane bahut burai kee haai, aur jo agyaaae, vidhaiyan aur niyam too ne apane das moosa ko diae the, unako ham ne naheen mana.
us vachan kee sudhai le, jo too ne apane das moosa se kaha tha, ki yadi tum log vishvasaghaat karo, to maain tum ko desh desh ke logon men titar bitar karoonga.
parantu yadi tum meree or firo, aur meree agyaaaen mano, aur un par chalo, to chahe tum men se nikale huae log akash kee chhor men bhee ho, taubhee maain unako vahan se ikattha karake us sthan men pahunchaunga, jise maain ne apane nam ke nivas ke liye chun liya haai.
ab ve tere das aur teree praja ke log haain jinako too ne apanee badee samarth aur balavant hath ke dara chhuda liya haai.
he prabhu binatee yah haai, ki too apane das kee praarthna par, aur apane un dason kee praarthna par, jo tere nam ka bhy manana chahate haai, kan laga, aur aj apane das ka kam sufal kar, aur us purush ko us par dayalu kara. maain to raja ka piya tha.
artakshatra raja ke beesaven varsha ke neesan nam maheene me, jab usake samhane dakhmadha tha, tab maain ne dakhmadha uttakar raja ko diya. is se paahile maain usake samhane kabhee udas n hua tha.
tab raja ne mujh se poochha, too to regee naheen haai, fir tera munh kyon utara haai? yah to man hee kee udasee hogee.
tab maain atyant dr gaya. aur raja se kaha, raja sada jeevit rahe ! jab vah nagar jis men mere purakhaon kee kabaren haai, ujad pada haai aur usake faattk jale huae haai, to mera munh kyon n utare?
raja ne mujh se poochha, fir too kya mangata haai? tab maain ne svarga ke parameshvar se praarthna karake, raja se kaha
yaadi raja ko bhaa, aur too apane das se prasann ho, to mujhe yahooda aur mere purakhaon kee kabaron ke nagar ko bhej, taaki maain use banaun.
tab raja ne jisake pas ranee bhee baaittee thee, mujh se poochha, too kitane din tak yatra men rahega? aur kab laaittega? so raja mujhe bhejane ko prasann hua aur maain ne usake liye aek samay niyukt kiya.
aur sarakaree jangal ke rakhvale asap ke liye bhee is ashay kee chitthee mujhe dee jaae taaki vah mujhe bhvan se lage huae rajagaddh kee kaadiyon ke liye, aur shaharapanah ke, aur us ghar ke liye, jis men maain jakar rahoonga, lakadee de. mere parameshvar kee krapadrashtti mujh par thee, isaaliye raja ne yah binatee grahan kiya.
tab maain ne mahanad ke par ke adhaipaatiyon ke pas jakar unhen raja kee chitthiyan deen. ija ne mere sang senapaati aur savar bhee bheje the.
yah sunakar ki aek manushy israaaeliyon ke kalyan ka upay karane ko aya haai, horonee samballat aur tobiyah nam karmacharee jo ammonee tha, un donon ko bahut bura laga.
jab maain yarooshalem pahunch gaya, tab vahan teen din raha.
tab maain thode purushaeen ko lekar rat ko utta maain ne kisee ko naheen bataya ki mere parameshvar ne yarooshalem ke hit ke liye mere man men kya upajaya tha. aur apanee savaree ke pashu ko chhod koi pashu mere sang n tha.
maain rat ko tarai ke faattk men hokar nikala aur ajagar ke sote kee or, aur koodafaattk ke pas gaya, aur yarooshalem kee toottee padee hui shaharapanah aur jale faattkon ko dekha.
tab maain age baddhkar sote ke faattk aur raja ke kund ke pas gaya parantu meree savaree ke pashu ke liye age jane ko sthan n tha.
tab maain rat hee rat nale se hokar shaharapanah ko dekhta hua chaddh gaya fir ghoomakar taii ke faattk se bheetar aya, aur is prakar lautt aya.
aur haakim n janate the ki maain kahan gaya aur kya karata tha varan maain ne tab tak n to yahoodiyon ko kuchh bataya tha aur n yajakon aur n raison aur n hakimon aur n doosare kam karanevalon ko.
tab maain ne un se kaha, tum to ap dekhte ho ki ham kaaisee durdasha men haai, ki yarooshalem ujad pada haai aur usake faattk jale huae haain. to ao, ham yarooshalem kee shaharapanah ko banaae, ki bhvishy men hamaree namadharai n rahe.
fir maain ne unako batalaya, ki mere parameshvar kee krapadraashtti mujh par kaaisee hui aur raja ne mujh se kya kya baten kahee theen. tab unhon ne kaha, ao ham kamar bandhakar banane lagen. aur unhon ne is bhle kam ko karane ke liye hiyav bandha liya.
yah sunakar horonee samballat aur tobiyah nam karmacharee jo ammonee tha, aur geshom nam aek arabee, hameen tttthon men udane lage aur hamen tuchchh janakar kahan lage, yah tum kya kam karate ho.
kya tum raja ke viruddh balava karoge? tab maain ne unako uttar dekar un se kaha, svarga ka parameshvar hamara kam sufal karega, isaliye ham usake das kamar bandhakar banaaenge parantu yarooshalem men tumhara n to koi bhag, n hakk, n smarak haai.
tab aelyashaeeb mahayajak ne apane bhai yajakon samet kamar bandhakar bhedfaattk ko banaya. unhon ne usakee pratishtta kee, aur usake pallon ko bhee lagaya aur hammea nam gummatt tak varan hananel ke gummatt ke pas tak unhon ne shaharapanah kee praatishtta kee.
us se age yareeho ke manushyon ne banaya. aur in se age imraee ke putra jakkoor ne banaya .
aur un se age maremot ne jo hakkos ka pota aur uriyah ka putra tha, marammat kee. aur in se age mashuullam ne jo mashojabel ka pota, aur barekyah ka putra tha, marammat kee. aur is se age bana ke putra sadok ne marammat kee.
aur in se age takoiyon ne marammat kee parantu unake raison ne apane prabhu kee seva ka jooa apanee gardan par n liya.
fir purane faattk kee marammat paseh ke putra yoyada aur basodayah ke putra mashuullam ne kee unhon ne usakee kadiyan lagai, aur usake palle, tale aur bende lagaae.
aur un se age gibonee malatyah aur meronotee yadon ne aur gibon aur mispa ke manushyon ne mahanad ke par ke aadhaipaati ke sinhasan kee or se marammat kee.
un se age harhayah ke putra ujeeel ne aur aur sunaron ne marammat kee. aur is se age hananyah ne, jo gaandhiayon ke samaj ka tha, marammat kee aur unhon ne chaudee shaharapanah tak yarooshalem ko draddh kiya.
aur un se age hoor ke putra rapayah ne, jo yarooshalem ke adho jile ka haakim tha, marammat kee.
aur un se age harumap ke putra yadayah ne apane hee ghar ke samhane marammat kee aur is se age hashabnayah ke putra hattoosh ne marammat kee.
hareem ke putra maalkaiyah aur pahattoab ke putra hashshoob ne aek aur bhag kee, aur bhtton ke gummatt kee marammat kee.
is se age yarooshalem ke adho jile ke haakim hallohesh ke putra shalloom ne apanee bettyaien samet marammat kee.
tarai ke faattk kee marammat hanoon aur janoh ke nivaasiyon ne kee unhon ne usako banaya, aur usake tale, bende aur palle lagaa, aur hajar hath kee shaharapanah ko bhee arthata koodafaattk tak banaya.
aur koodafaattk kee marammat rekab ke putra maalkaiyah ne kee, jo bethkkerem ke jile ka haakim tha usee ne usako banaya, aur usake tale, bende aur palle lagaae.
aur sotafaattk kee marammat kolhoje ke putra shalloom ne kee, jo mispa ke jile ka haakim tha usee ne usako banaya aur patta, aur usake tale, bende aur palle lagaae aur usee ne raja kee baree ke pas ke sholah nam kund kee shaharapanah ko bhee daudapur se utaranevalee seeddhee tak banaya.
usake bad aj ajabook ke putra nahemayah ne jo betasoor ke adho jile ka haakim tha, daud ke kaabirstan ke samhane tak aur banaae huae pokhre tak, varan veeron ke ghar tak bhee marammat kee.
usake bad unake bhaiyon samet keela ke adho jile ke haakim henadad ke putra bavvaai ne marammat kee.
us se age ek aur bhag kee marammat jo shaharapanah ke mod ke pas shasren ke ghar kee chaddhai ke samhane haai, yeshu ke putra ejaer ne kee, jo mispa ka hakim tha.
fir aek aur bhag kee arthata usee mod se le aelyashaeeb mahayajak ke ghar ke dar tak kee marammat jabbaai ke putra barook ne tan man se kee.
isake bad aek aur bhag kee arthata aelyashaeeb ke ghar ke dar se le usee ghar ke sire tak kee marammat, maremot ne kee, jo hakkos ka pota aur uriyah ka putra tha.
usake bad un yajakon ne marammat kee jo tarai ke manushy the.
unake bad binyameen aur hashshoob ne apane ghar ke samhane marammat kee aur inake peechhe ajaryah ne jo maseyah ka putra aur ananyah ka pota tha apane ghar ke pas marammat kee.
tab aek aur bhag kee, arthata ajaryah ke ghar se lekar shaharapanah ke mod tak varan usake kone tak kee marammat henadad ke putra binnooi ne kee.
fir usee mod ke samhane jo uncha gummatt rajabhvan se bahar nikala hua bandeegrah ke angan ke pas haai, usake samhane ujaai ke putra palal ne marammat kee. isake bad parosh ke putra padayah ne marammat kee.
nateen log to opel men poorab kee or jalafaattk ke samhane tak aur bahar nikale huae gummatt tak rahate the.
padayah ke bad takoiyon ne aek aur bhag kee marammat kee, jo bahar tikale huae bade gummatt ke samhane aur obel kee shaharapanah tak haai.
fir ghaedafaattk ke upar yajakon ne apane apane ghar ke samhane marammat kee.
inake bad immer ke putra sadok ne apane ghar ke samhane marammat kee aur tab pooravee faattk ke rakhvale shakanyah ke putra samayah ne marammat kee.
isake bad sholemyah ke putra hananyah aur salap ke chhttven putra hanoon ne aek aur bhag kee marammat kee. tab berekyah ke putra mashuullam ne apanee kottree ke samhane marammat kee.
usake bad maalkaiyah ne jo sunar tha natinon aur vyapaariyon ke sthan tak ttharaae huae sthan ke faattk ke samhane aur kone ke kotte tak marammat kee.
aur konevale kotte se lekar bhedfaattk tak sunaron aur vyapariyon ne marammat kee.
jab samballat ne suna ki yahoodee log shaharapanah ko bana rahe haai, tab us ne bura mana, aur bahut risiyakar yahoodiyon ko tttthon men udane laga.
usake pas to ammonee tobiyah tha, aur vah kahane laga, jo kuchh ve bana rahe haai, yadi koi geedad bhee us par chaddhe, to vah unakee banai hui patthr kee shaharapanah ko tod dega.
he hamare parameshvar sun le, ki hamara apaman ho raha haai aur unaka kiya hua apaman unheen ke sir par lautta de, aur unhen bandhauai ke desh men luttva de.
aur unaka adharma too n ddhanp, aur n unaka pap tere sammukh se mittaya jaae kyonki unhon ne tujhe shaharapanah bananevalon ke samhane krodha dilaya haai.
aur ham logon ne shaharapanah ko banaya aur saree shaharapanah adhaee unchai tak jud gai. kyonaki logon ka man us kam men nit laga raha.
jab samballat aur tobiyah aur arabiyo, ammoniyon aur ashadodiyon ne suna, ki yarooshalem kee shaharapanah kee marammat hotee jatee haai, aur us men ke nake band hone lage haai, tab unhon ne bahut hee bura mana
aur sabhon ne aek man se goshttee kee, ki jakar yarooshalem se lade, aur us men gadbadee dalen.
parantu ham logon ne apane parameshvar se praarthna kee, aur unake dr ke mare unake viruddh din rat ke paharuae tthara diae.
aur yahoodee kahane lage, ddhonevalon ka bal ghatt gaya, aur mittee bahut padee haai, isaliye shaharapanah ham se naheen ban sakatee.
aur hamare shatra kahane lage, ki jab tak ham unake beech men n mahunche, aur unhen ghaat karake vah kam band n kare, tab tak unako n kuchh maloom hoga, aur n kuchh dikhai padega.
fir jo yahoodee unake as pas rahate the, unhon ne sab sthanon se das bar a akar, ham logon se kaha, tum ko hamare pas lautt ana chahiye.
is karan maain ne logon ko talavare, barchhrian aur dhanush dekar shaharapanah ke peechhe sab se neeche ke khule sthanon men gharane gharane ke anusar baaitta diya.
tab maain dekhkar utta, aur raison aur haakimon aur aur sab logon se kaha, un se mat dro prabhu jo mahan aur bhyayogy haai, usee ko smaran karake, apane bhaiyo, betto, bettyaie, striayon aur gharon ke liye yuddh karana.
aur us din se mere adho sevak to us kam me lage rahe aur adho barchhrie, talavaro, dhanushaen aur jhlaimon ko dhaaran kiae rahate the aur yahooda ke sare dharane ke peechhe haakim raha karate the.
shaharapanah ke bananevale aur bojh ke ddhonevale donon bhar uttate the, arthta aek hath se kam karate the aur doosare hath se hathaiyar pakade rahate the.
aur raj apanee apanee jangha par talavar lattkaae huae banate the. aur narasinge ka foonkanevala mere pas rahata tha.
isaliye maain ne raiso, hakimon aur sab logon se kaha, kam to bada aur faaila hua haai, aur ham log shaharapanah par alag alag aek doosare se door rahate haain.
isaliye jidhar se narasinga tumhen sunai de, udhar hee hamare pas ikatthe ho jana. hamara parameshvar hamaree or se ladega.
yon ham kam men lage rahe, aur un men adho, pau fattne se taron ke nikalane tak baarchhrian liye rahate the.
fir usee samay maain ne logon se yah bhee kaha, ki aek aek manushy apane das samet yarooshalem ke bheetar rat bitaya kare, ki ve rat ko to hamaree rakhvalee kare, aur din ko kam men lage rahen.
aur n to maain apane kapade utarata tha, aur n mere bhai, n mere sevak, n ve paharuae jo mere anuchar the, apane kapade utarate the sab koi panee ke pas hathaiyar liye huae jagate the.
tab log aur unakee striayon kee or se unake bhai yahoodiyon ke kiruddh badee chillahatt machee.
kitane to kahate the, ham apane bette-beattyaien samet bahut praanee haai, isaaliye hamen ann milana chahiye ki use khakar jeevit rahen.
aur kitane kahate the, ki ham apane apane kheto, dakh kee bariyon aur gharon ko mahangee ke karan bandhak rakhte haai, ki hamen ann mile.
fir kitane yah kahate the, ki ham ne raja ke kar ke liye apane apane kheton aur dakh kee bariyon par rupaya udhaar liya.
parantu hamara aur hamare bhaiyon ka shareer aur hamare aur unake ladkebale aek hee saman haai, taubhee ham apane bette-bettyaien ko das banate haain varan hamaree koi koi bettee dasee bhee ho chukee haain aur hamara kuchh bas naheen jalata, kyonki hamare khet aur dakh kee bariyan auron ke hath padee haain.
yah chillahatt or ye baten sunakar maain bahut krodhait hua.
tab apane man men soch vichar karake maain ne raison aur hakimon ko ghaudkakar kaha, tum apane apane bhai se byaj lete ho. tab maain ne unake viruddh aek badee sabha kee.
aur maain ne un se kaha, ham logon ne to apanee shaktai bhr apane yahoodee bhaiyon ko jo anyajatiyon ke hath bik gaae the, dam dekar chhudaya haai, fir kya tum apane bhaiyon ko bechoge? kya ve hamare hath bikenge? tab ve chup rahe aur kuchh n kah sake.
fir maain kahata gaya, jo kam tum karate ho vah achchha naheen haai kya tum ko is karan hamare parameshvar ka bhy manakar chalana n chaahiye ki hamare shatra jo anyajati haai, ve hamaree namadharai n karen?
aj hee anako unake khet, aur dak, aur jalapai kee bariya, aur ghar faer do aur jo rupaya, ann, naya dakhmadha, aur ttttka tel tum un se le lete ho, usaka sauvan bhag faer do?
anhon ne kaha, ham unhen faer denge, aur un se kuchh n lenge jaaisa too kahata haai, vaaisa hee ham karenge. tab maain ne yajakon ko bulakar un logon ko yah shapath khailai, ki ve isee vachan ke anusar karenge.
fir maain ne apane kapade kee chhor jhadkar kaha, isee reeati se jo koi is vachan ko poora n kare, usako parameshvar jhadkar, usaka ghar aur kamai us se chhudaa, aur isee reeti se vah jhada jaa, aur choochha ho jaae. tab saree sabha ne kaha, amen ! aur yahova kee stuati kee. aur logon ne is vachan ke anusar kam kiya.
fir jab se maain yahooda desh men unaka aadhaipaati ttharaya gaya, arthata raja artakshatra ke beesaven varsha se le usake batteesaven varsha tak, arthata barah varsha tak maain aur mere bhai adhaipaati ke hak ka bhojan khate rahe.
parantu pahile aadhaipaati jo mujh se age the, vah praja par bhar dalate the, aur un se rottee, aur dakhmadha, aur is se adhaik chalees shokel chandee lete the, varan unake sevak bhee praja ke upar aadhaikar jatate the parantu maain aeesa naheen karata tha, kyonaki maain yahova ka bhy manata tha.
fir maain shaharapanah ke kam men lipatta raha, aur ham logon ne kuchh boomi mol n lee aur mere sab sevak kam karane ke liye vahan ikatthe rahate the.
