parantu unhon ne aur hamare purakhaon ne aabhaiman kiya, aur hatteele bane aur teree agyaaaen n manee
aur agyaa manane se inakar kiya, aur jo ashcharyakarma too ne unake beech kiae the, unaka smaran n kiya, varan hatt karake yahan tak balava karanevale bane, ki aek pradhaan ttharaya, ki apane dasatv kee dasha men lautte. parantu too kshama karanevala anugrahakaree aur dayalu, vilamb se kop karanevala, aur atikarunamay ishvar haai, too ne unako n tyaga.
