aester ranee ne uttar diya, he raja ! yaadi too mujh par prasann haai, aur raja ko yah sveekar ho, to mere nivedan se mujhe, aur mere mangane se mere logon ko praandan mile.
kyonaki maain aaair meree jati ke log bech dale gaae haai, aur ham sab vidhvansaghaat aur nash kiae janevale haain. yaadi ham keval dasa-dasee ho jane ke liye bech dale jate, to maain chup rahatee chahe us dasha men bhee vah virodhaee raja kee haani bhr n sakata.
tab raja kshayarsha ne aester ranee se poochha, vah kaun haai? aur kahan haai jis ne aeesa karane kee manasa kee haai?
aester ne uttar diya haai ki vah virodhaee aur shatra yahee dushtt haman haai. tab haman raja-ranee ke samhate bhyabheet ho gaya.
raja to jalajalahatt men a, madha peene se uttkar, rajabhvan kee baree men nikal gaya aur haman yah dekhkar ki raja ne meree hani ttanee hogee, aester ranee se praandan mangane ko khda hua.
jab raja rajabhvan kee baree se dakhmadha peene ke sthan men lautt aya tab kya dekha, ki haman usee chaukee par jis par aester baaittee haai pada haai aur raja ne kaha, kya yah ghar hee men mere samhane hee ranee se barabas karana chahata haai? raja ke munh se yah vachan nikala hee tha, ki sevakon ne haman ka munh ddhanp diya.
tab raja ke samhane upasthit rahanevale khojon men se havana nam aek ne raja se kaha, haman ko yahan pachas hath uncha faansee ka aek khmbha khda haai, jo us ne mordakaai ke liye banavaya haai, jis ne raja ke hit kee bat kahee thee. raja ne kaha, usako usee par lattka do.
tab haman usee khmbhe par jo us ne mordakaai ke liye taaiyar karaya tha, lattka diya gaya. is par raja kee jalajalahatt ttndee ho gai.
usee din raja kshayarsha ne yahoodiyon ke virodhaee haman ka gharabar ester ranee ko de diya. aur mordakaai raja ke samhane aya, kyonki ester ne raja ko bataya tha, ki us se usaka kya nata tha
tab raja ne apanee vah angoottee jo us ne haman se le lee thee, utar kar, mordakaai ko de dee. aur aesater ne mordakaai ko haman ke gharabar par adhaikaree niyukt kar diya.
fir aester doosaree bar raja se bolee aur usake panv par gir, ansoo baha bahakar us se gidgidakar bintee kee, ki agagee haman kee burai aur yahoodiyon kee haani kee usakee yuktai nishfal kee jaae.
tab aester uttkar raja ke samhane khdee hui aur kahane lagee ki yadi raja ko sveekar ho aur vah mujh se prasann haai aur yah bat usako tteek jan pade, aur maain bhee usako achchhee lagatee hoo, to jo chitthiyan hammadata agagee ke putra haman ne raja ke sab praanton ke yahoodiyon ko nash karane kee yuktai karake likhai thee, unako palattne ke liye likha jaae.
kyonaki maain apane jaati ke logon par padnevalee us vipaattai ko kis reeti se dekh sakoongee? aur maain apane bhaiyon ke vinash ko kyonkar dekh sakoongee?
so tum apanee samajh ke anusar raja ke nam se yahoodiyon ke nam par likho, aur raja kee angoottee kee chhap bhee lagao kyonki jo chitthee raja ke nam se likhee jaa, aur us par usakee angoottee kee chhap lagai jaa, usako koi bhee palatt naheen sakata.
so usee samay arthata seevan nam teesare maheene ke teisaven din ko raja ke lekhk bulavaae gaae aur jis jis bat kee agyaa mordakaai ne unhen dee thee use yahoodiyon aur aadhaipaatiyon aur hindustan se lekar koosh tak, jo aek sau sattais praant haai, un sabhon ke aadhaipaatiyon aur haakimon ko aek aek praant ke aksharon men aur aek aek desh ke logon kee bhasha me, aur yahoodiyon ko unake aksharon aur bhasha men likhee gai.
mordakaai ne raja kshayarsha ke nam se chitthiyan likhakar, aur un par raja kee angoottee kee chhap lagakar, veg chalanevale sarakaree ghaedo, khchcharon aur sandniyon kee dak lagakar, harakaron ke hath bhej deen.
in chitthiyon men sab nagaron ke yahoodiyon ko raja kee or se anumati dee gai, ki ve ikatthe hon aur apana apana praan bachane ke liye taaiyar hokar, jis jati va praant se log anyay karake unako va unakee striayon aur balabachchon ko dukh dena chahe, unako vidhvansaghaat aur nash kare, aur unakee dhan sammattai loott len.
aur yah raja kshayarsha ke sab praanton men aek hee din men kiya jaa, arthata adar nam barahaven maheene ke terahaven din ko.
is agyaa ke lekh kee nakale, samast praanton men sab deshon ke logon ke pas khulee hui bhejee gai taaki yahoodee us din apane shatrauon se palatta lene ko taaiyar rahen.
so harakare veg chalanevale sarakaree ghaedon par savar hokar, raja kee agyaa se fauta karake jaldee chale gaa, aur yah agyaa shooshan rajagaddh men dee gai thee.
tab mordakaai neele aur shvet rang ke rajakeey vasr paahine aur sir par sone ka bada mumutt dhare huae aur sookshamasan aur baainjanee rang ka baga paahine hua, raja ke sammukh se nikala, aur shooshan nagar ke log anand ke mare lalakar utte.
aur yahoodiyon ko anand aur harsha hua aur unakee badee praatishtta hui.
aur jis jis praant, aur jis jis nagar me, jahan kaheen raja kee agyaa aur niyam pahunche, vahan vahan yahoodiyon ko anand aur harsha hua, aur unhon ne jevanar karake us din ko khushaee ka din mana. aur us desh ke logon men se bahut log yahoodee ban gaa, kyonki unake man men yahoodiyon ka dr sama gaya tha.
adar nam barahaven maheene ke terahaven din ko, jis din raja kee agyaa aur niyam poore hone ko the, aur yahoodiyon ke shatra un par prabal hone kee asha rakhte the, parantu isake ulatte yahoodee apane vaairiyon par prabal hua, us din,
yahoodee log raja kshayarsha ke sab praanton men apane apane nagar men ikatthe hua, ki jo unakee hani karane ka yatn kare, un par hath chalaae. aur koi unaka samhana n kar saka, kyonaki unaka bhy desh desh ke sab logon ke man men sama gaya tha.
varan praanton ke sab haakimon aur aadhaipaatiyon aur pradhaanon aur raja ke karmachaariyon ne yahoodiyon kee sahayata kee, kyonki unake man men mordakaai ka bhy sama gaya tha.
mordakaai to raja ke yahan bahut pratishttit tha, aur usakee keettair sab praanton men faail gai varan us purush mordakaai kee mahima baddhtee chalee gai.
aur yahoodiyon ne apane sab shatrauon ko talavar se marakar aur ghaat karake nash kar dala, aur apane vaairiyon se apanee ichchha ke anusar bartav kiya.
aur shooshan rajagaddh men yahoodiyon ne panch sau manushyon ko ghaat karake nash kiya.
aur unhon ne parshandata, dalpon, aspata,
porata, adalya, areedata,
parmashata, areesaai, areedaai aur vaaijata,
arthata hammadata ke putra yahoodiyon ke virodhaee haman ke dason putraen ko bhee ghaat kiya parantu unake dhan ko n lootta.
usee din shooshan rajagaddh men ghaat kiae huon kee ginatee raja ko sunai gai.
tab raja ne aester ranee se kaha, yahoodiyon ne shooshan rajagaddh hee men panch sau manushy aur haman ke dason putraen ko bhee ghaat karake nash kiya haai fir rajy ke aur aur praanton men unhon ne n jane kya kya kiya hoga ! ab is se aadhaik tera nivedan kya haai? vah bhee poora kiya jaaega. aur too kya mangatee haai? vah bhee tujhe diya jaaega.
aester ne kaha, yadi raja ko sveekar ho to shooshan ke yahoodiyon ko aj kee nai kal bhee karane kee agyaa dee jaa, aur haman ke dason putra faansee ke khmbhen par lattkaae jaaen.
raja ne kaha, aeesa kiya jaae yah agyaa shooshan men dee gai, aur haman ke dason putra lattkaae gaae.
aur shooshan ke yahoodiyon ne adar maheene ke chaudahaven din ko bhee ikatthe hokar shooshan men teen sau purushaen ko ghaat kiya, parantu dhan ko n lootta.
rajy ke aur aur praanton ke yahoodee ikatthe hokar apana apana praan bachane ke liye khde hua, aur apane vaairiyon men se pachahattar hajar manushyon ko ghaat karake apane shatrauon se vishraam paya parantu dhan ko n lootta.
yah adar maheene ke terahaven din ko kiya gaya, aur chaudahaven din ko unhon ne vishraam karake jevanar kee aur anand ka din ttharaya.
is karan dehatee yahoodee jo bina shaharapanah kee baastaiyon men rahate haai, ve adar maheene ke chaudahaven din ko anand or jevanar aur khushaee aur apas men baaina bhejane ka din niyukt karake manate haain.
aur yah agyaa dee, ki adar maheene ke chaudahaven aur usee maheene ke pandrahaven din ko prati varsha mana karen.
jin men yahoodiyon ne apane shatrauon se vishraam paya, aur yah maheena jis men shaek anand se, aur vilap khushaee se badala gaya mana karen aur unako jevanar aur anand aur aek doosare ke pas baaina bhejane or kangalon ko dan dene ke din manen.
aur yahoodiyon ne jaaisa arambh kiya tha, aur jaaisa mordakaai ne unhen likha, vaaisa hee karane ka nishchay kar liya.
kyonaki hammadata agagee ka putra haman jo sab yahoodiyon ka virodhaee tha, us ne yahoodiyon ke nash karane kee yuktai kee, aur unhen mitta dalane aur nash karane ke liye poor arthata chitthee dalee thee.
parantu jab raja ne yah jan liya, tab us ne agyaa dee aur likhvai ki jo dushtt yuaktai haman ne yahoodiyon ke viruddh kee thee vah usee ke sir par palatt aa, tab vah aur usake putra faansee ke kshambhon par lattkaae gaae.
is karan un dinon ka nam poor shabd se pooreem rakha gaya. is chitthee kee sab baton ke kara, aur jo kuchh unhon ne is vishay men dekha aur jo kuchh un par beeta tha, usake karan bhee
yahoodiyon ne apane apane liye aur apanee santan ke liye, aur un sabhon ke liye bhee jo un men mil gaae the yah attl pran kiya, ki us lekh ke anusar prati varsha usake ttharaae huae samay men ve ye do din manen.
aur peeddhee peeddhee, kul kul, praant praant, nagar nagar men ye din smaran kiae aur mane jaaenge. aur pooreem nam ke din yahoodiyon men kabhee n mittenge aur unaka smaran unake vansh se jata n rahega.
fir abeehaail kee bettee aester ranee, aur mordakaai yahoodee ne, pooreem ke vishay yah doosaree chitthee bade aadhaikar ke sath likhee.
isakee nakalen mordakaai ne kshayarsha ke rajy ke, aek sau sattaison praanton ke sab yahoodiyon ke pas shaantai denevalee aur sachchee baton ke sath is ashay se bhejee,
ki pooreem ke un dinon ke vishosh ttharaae huae samayon men mordakaai yahoodee aur aester ranee kee agyaa ke anusar, aur jo yahoodiyon ne apane aur apanee santan ke liye ttan liya tha, usake anusar bhee upavas aur vilap kiae jaaen.
aur pooreem ke vishy ka yah niyam aester kee agyaa se bhee sthiar kiya gaya, aur unakee charcha pustak men likhee gai.
mera praan jeeavit rahane se ukatata haai maain svatantrata poorvak kudkudaunga aur maain apane man kee kadvahatt ke mare baten karoonga.
maai ishvar se kahoonga, mujhe doshaee n tthara mujhe bata de, ki too kis karan moojh se mukama ladta haai?
kya tujhe andhor karana, aur dushtton kee yuaktai ko sufal karake apane hathon ke banaae huae ko nikamma janana bhla lagata haai?
kya teree deshdhaariyon kee see bankhen haai? aur kya tera dekhna manushy ka sa haai?
kya tere din manushy ke din ke saman haai, va tere varsha purush ke samayon ke tuly haai,
ki too mera adharma ddoonddhta, aur mera pap poochhta haai?
tujhe to maloom hee haai, ki maain dushtt naheen hoo, aur tere hath se koi chhudanevala naheen !
too ne apane hathon se mujhe tteek racha haai aur jodkar banaya haai taubhee mujhe nash kiae dalata haai.
smaran kar, ki too ne mujh ko goondhaee hui mittee kee nai banaya, kya too mujhe fir dhool men milaaega?
kya too ne mujhe doodha kee nai undelakar, aur dahee ke saman jamakar naheen banaya?
fir too ne mujh par chamada aur mans chaddhaya aur haaddiyan aur nasen goonthkar mujhe banaya haai.
too ne mujhe jeevan diya, aur mujh par karuna kee haai aur teree chaukasee se mere praan kee raksha hai haai.
taubhee too ne aeesee baton ko apane man men chhpai rakha maain to jan gaya, ki too ne aeesa hee karane ko ttana tha.
jo maain pap karoo, to too usaka lekha lega aur adharma karane par mujhe nidash n ttharaaega.
jo maain dushttta karoon to mujh par hay ! aur jo maain dhama banoon taubhee maain sir n uttaunga, kyonaki maain apaman se bhra hua hoon aur apane dukh par dhyan rakhta hoo.
aur chahe sir uttaun taubhee too sinh kee nai mera aher karata haai, aur fir mere viruddh ashcharyakarma karata haai.
mera hona n hone ke saman hota, aur pett hee se kabra ko pahunchaya jata.
kya mere din thode naheen? mujhe chhod de, aur meree or se munh faer le, ki mera man thoda shaant ho jaae
is se paahile ki maain vahan jau, jahan se fir n lautoonga, arthata aandhiayare aur dhaer andhakar ke desh me, jahan andhakar hee andhakar haai
aur mratyu ke andhakar ka desh jis men sab kuchh gadbad haai aur jahan prakash bhee aeesa haai jaaisa andhakara.
tab namatee sopar ne kaha
bahut see baten jo kahee gai haai, kya unaka uttar dena n chaahiye? kya bakavadee manushy dhama ttharaya jaae?
kya tere bade bol ke karan log chup rahen? aur jab too ttttha karata haai, to kya koi tujhe laajjait n kare?
too to yah kahata haai ki mera siddhant shuuddh haai aur maain ishvar kee drashtti men pavitra hoo.
parantu bhla ho, ki ishvar svayan baten kare, aur tere viruddh munh khole,
aur tujh par buaddhi kee gupt baten pragatt kare, ki unaka marma teree buddhi se baddhkar haai. isaaliye jan le, ki ishvar tere adharma men se bahut kuchh bool jata haai.
kya too ishvar ka gooddh bhed pa sakata haai? aur kya too sarvashaktaiman ka marma pooree reeti se chanch sakata haai?
vah akash sa uncha haai too kya kar sakata haai? vah adhaelok se gaahira haai, too kahan samajh sakata haai?
usakee map prathvee se bhee lambee haai aur samudra se chaudee haai.
jab ishvar beech se gujarakar band kar de aur adalat men bulaa, to kaun usako rok sakata haai.
kyonaki vah pakhndee manushyon ka bhed janata haai, aur anarth kam ko bina soch vichar kiae bhee jan leta haai.
panantu manushy choochha aur nirbauddhi hota haai kyonki manushy janm hee se jangalee gadahe ke bachche ke saman hota haai.
yaadi too apana man shuuddh kare, aur ishvar kee or apane hath faailaa,
aur jo koi anarth kam tujh se hota ho use door kare, aur apane deron men koi kuttlaita n rahane de,
tab to too nishchay apana munh nishkalank dikha sakega aur too sthir hokar kabhee n drega.
tab too apana dukh bool jaaega, too use us panee ke saman smaran karega jo bah gaya ho.
aur tera jeevan dopahar se bhee aadhaik prakashaman hoga aur chahe andhora bhee ho taubhee vah bhor sa ho jaaega.
aur tujhe asha hogee, is karan too nirbhy rahega aur apane charon or dekh dekhkar too nirbhy vishraam kar sakega.
aur jab too lettega, tab koi tujhe draaega naheen aur bahutere tujhe prasann karate ka yatn karenge.
parantu dushtt logon kee ankhen rah jaaengee, aur unhen koi sharun sthan n milega aur unakee asha yahee hogee ki praan nikal jaae.
