nisandeh manushy to tum hee ho aur jab tum maroge tab buaddhi bhee jatee rahegee.
parantu tumharee nai mujh men bhee samajh haai, maain tum logon se kuchh teecha naheen hoo kaun aeesa haai jo aeesee baten n janata ho?
maain ishvar se praarthna karata tha, aur vah meree sun diya karata tha parantu ab mere padosee mujh par hansate haain jo dhama aur khra manushy haai, vah hansee ka karan ho gaya haai.
dukhee log to suakhaiyon kee samajh men tuchchh jane jate haain aur jinake panv fisala chahate haain unaka apaman avashy hee hota haai.
prathvee par dhyan de, tab us se tujhe shaiksha milegee or samudra kee machhaliyan bhee tujh se varnn karengee.
kaun in baton ko naheen janata, ki yahova hee ne apane hath se is sansar ko banaya haai.
usake hath men ek ek jeevadhaaree ka praa, aur ek ek dehadhaaree manushy kee atma bhee rahatee haai.
jaaise jeebh se bhojan chakha jata haai, kya vaaise hee kan se vachan naheen parakhe jate?
booddhan men buddhi pai jatee haai, aur lambee ayuvalon men samajh hotee to haai.
ishvar men pooree buaddhi aur parakram paae jate haain yuktai aur samajh usee men haain.
dekho, jisako vah ddha de, vah fir banaya naheen jata jis manushy ko vah band kare, vah fir khola naheen jata.
dekho, jab vah vashara ko rok rakhta haai to jal sookh jata haai fir jab vah jal chhod deta haai tab prathvee ulatt jatee haai.
us men samathrya aur khree buaddhi pai jatee haai dhaekh denevala aur dhaekha khanevala donon usee ke haain.
vah mantraiyon ko loottkar bandhauai men le jata, aur nyaayiyon ko moorkh bana deta haai.
vah rajaon ka aadhaikar tod deta haai aur unakee kamar par bandhan bandhavata haai.
vah yajakon ko loottkar bandhauai men le jata aur samaathairyon ko ulatt deta haai.
