ve bin ujiyale ke andhore men ttttolate firate haain aur vah unhen aeesa bana deta haai ki ve matavale kee nai dgamagate huae chalate haain.
suno, maain yah sab kuchh apanee ankh se dekh chuka, aur apane kan se sun chuka, aur samajh bhee chuka hoo.
jo kuchh tum janate ho vah maain bhee janata hoo maain tum logon se kuchh kam naheen hoo.
maain to sarvashaktaiman se baten karoonga, aur meree abhailasha ishvar se vadaavivad karane kee haai.
parantu tum log joottee bat ke gaddhnevale ho tum sabake sab nikamme vaaidh ho.
bhla hota, ki tum bilakul chup rahate, aur is se tum buddhiman ttharate.
mera vivad suno, aur meree bahas kee baton par kan lagao.
kya tum ishvar ke nimitt tteddhee baten kahoge, aur usake paksha men kapatt se bologe?
kya tum usaka pakshapat karoge? aur ishvar ke liye mukama chalaoge.
kya yah bhla hoga, ki vah tum ko janche? kya jaaisa koi manushy ko dhaekha de, vaaisa hee tum kya usako bhee dhokha doge?
jo tum chhpaikar pakshapat karo, to vah nishchay tum ko danttega.
