mujh se kitane adharma ke kam aur pap huae haain? mere aparadha aur pap mujhe jata de.
too kis karan apana munh faer leta haai, aur mujhe apana shatra ginata haai?
kya too udte huae patte ko bhee kanpaaega? aur sookhe dnttl ke peechhe padega?
too mere liye kaattnai dukhon kee agyaa deta haai, aur meree javanee ke adharma ka fal mujhe bhugata deta haai.
aur mere panvon ko katt men ttonkata, aur meree saree chal chalan dekhta rahata haai aur mere panvon kee charon or seema bandha leta haai.
aur maain sadee galee vastu ke tuly hoon jo nash ho jatee haai, aur keeda khaae kapade ke tuly hoo.
manushy jo sree se utmann hota haai, vah thede dinon ka aur dukh se bhra rahata haai.
vah fool kee nai khailata, fir toda jata he vah chhaya kee reeti par ddhl jata, aur kaheen ttharata naheen.
fir kya too aeese par drashtti lagata haai? kya too mujhe apane sath kachaharee men ghaseettta haai?
ashuuddh vastu se shuuddh vastu ko kaun nikal sakata haai? koi naheen.
manushy ke din niyukt kiae gaae haai, aur usake maheenon kee ginatee tere pas likhee haai, aur too ne usake liye aeesa sivana bandha haai jise vah par naheen kar sakata,
is karan us se apana munh faer le, ki vah aram kare, jab tak ki vah majadoor kee nai apana din poora n kar le.
vuksha kee to asha rahatee haai, ki chahe vah katt dala bhee jaa, taubhee fir panapega aur us se narma narma daaliyan nikalatee hee rahengee.
chahe usakee jad boomi men puranee bhee ho jaa, aur usaka toontt mittee men sookh bhee jaa,
taubhee vashara kee gandha pakar vah fir panapega, aur paudho kee nai us se shaakhaaen foottengee.
parantu purush mar jata, aur pada rahata haai jab usaka praan choott gaya, tab vah kahan raha?
