teree drashtti men ham to apane sab purakhaon kee nai paraae aur paradeshaee haain prathvee par hamare din chhaya kee nai beete jate haai, aur hamara kuchh ttkaiana naheen.
he hamare parameshvar yahova ! vah jo bada sanchay ham ne tere paavitra nam ka aek bhvan banane ke liye kiya haai, vah tere hee hath se hame mila tha, aur sab tera hee haai.
aur he mere parameshvar ! maain janata hoo ki too man ko janchata haai aur sidhaai se prasann rahata haai maain ne to yah sab kuchh man kee sidhaai aur apanee ichchha se diya haai aur ab maain ne anand se dekha haai, ki teree praja ke log jo yahan upasthiat haai, vah apanee ichchha se tere liye bhentt dete haain.
he yahova ! he hamare purakha ibraaheem, isahak aur israaael ke parameshvar ! apanee praja ke man ke vicharon men yah bat banaae rakh aur unake man apanee or lagaae rakh.
aur mere putra sulaaiman ka man aeesa khra kar de ki vah teree agyaaon chitauaniyon aur vidhaiyon ko manata rahe aur yah sab kuchh kare, aur us bhvan ko banaa, jisakee taaiyaree maain ne kee haai.
tab daud ne saree sabha se kaha, tum apane parameshvar yahova ka dhanyavad karo. tab sabha ke sab logon ne apane pitaron ke parameshvar yahova ka dhanyavad kiya, aur apana apana sir jhukakar yahova ko aur raja ko dandvat kiya.
fir unhon ne daud ke putra sulaaiman ko doosaree bar raja ttharakar yahova kee or se pradhaan hone ke liye usaka aur yajak hone ke liye sadok ka abhaishok kiya.
tab sulaaiman apane pita daud ke sthan par raja hokar yahova ke sinhasan par virajane laga aur bhagyavan hua, aur israaael usake adhaeen hua.
aur sab haakimon aur shooraveeron aur raja daud ke sab putraen ne sulaaiman raja kee adhaeenata angeekar kee.
aur yahova ne sulaaiman ko sab israaael ke dekhte bahut baddhaya, aur use aeesa rajakeey aeeshvarya diya, jaaisa us se paahile israaael ke kisee raja ka n hua tha.
is prakar yihau ke putra daud ne sare israaael ke upar rajy kiya.
aur usake israaael par rajy karane ka samay chalees varsha ka tha us ne sat varsha to hebraen men aur taaintees varsha yarooshalem men rajy kiya.
aur vah poore booddhape kee avastha men deegharayu hokar aur dhan aur vibhv, manamana bhogakar mar gaya aur usaka putra sulaaiman usake sthan par raja hua.
aadi se ant tak raja daud ke sab kamon ka vrattant,
aur usake sab rajy aur parakram ka, aur us par aur israaael par, varan desh desh ke sab rajyon par jo kuchh beeta, isaka bhee vrattant shamooael dasha aur natan nabee aur gad dasha kee pustakon men likha hua haai.
israaael ke ye putra huae rooben, shaimon, levee, sahooda, issakar, jabooloon, dana.
yoosuf, binyameen, nantalee, gad aur ashora.
yahooda ke ye putra huae aer, onan aur shola, usake ye teenon putra, batashoo nam aek kananee sree se utpann huae. aur yahooda ka jetta aer, yahova kee drashtti men bura tha, is karan us ne usako mar dala.
yahooda kee bahoo tamar se peres aur jerah utpann hue. yahooda ke sab putra panch huae.
meres ke putra hesraen aur hamoola.
fir kama ka putra akar jo arpan kee hui pastu ke vishay men vishvasaghaat karake israaaeliyon ka kashtt denevala hua.
aur aetan ka putra ajaryaha.
hesraen ke jo putra utpann huae yarael, ram aur kaloobaai.
aur ram se ammeenadab aur ammeenadab se nahashaen utpann hua jo yahoodiyon ka pradhaan bana.
aur nahashaen se salma aur salma se boaj,
aur boaj se obed aur obed se yishau utpann hua.
aur yishau se usaka jetta aeleeab aur doosara abeenadab teesara shaima.
chautha natanel aur panchavan raain. chhtta osem aur satavan daud utpann hua.
inakee baahinen sarooyah or abeegaail theen.
aur sarooyah ke putra abeeshau, yoab aur asahel ye teen the.
aur abeegaail se amasa utpann hua, aur amasa ka pita ishmaaelee yeter tha.
hesraen ke putra kaleb ke ajooba nam aek stree se, aur yareeot se, bette utpann hue aur isake putra ye hooae arthata yeshor, shobab aur adana.
jab ajooba mar gai, sab kaleb ne aepraat ko byah liya aur jisase hoor utpann hua.
aur hoor se uree aur uree se basalel utpann hua.
isake bad hesraen gilad ke pita makeer kee bettee ke pas gaya, jise us ne tab byah liya, jab vah satt varsha ka tha aur us se sagoob utpann hua.
aur gashoor aur aram ne yair kee bastaiyon ko aur ganvon samet kanat ko, un se le liya ye sab nagar milakar satt the. ye sab gilad ke pita makeer ke putra huae.
aur jab hesraen kalebepraata men mar gaya, tab usakee aabiyyah nam sree se ashahoor utpann hua jo tako ka pita hua.
aur hesraen ke jette yarael ke ye putra huae arthata ram jo usaka jetta tha aur boona, oren, osem aur yaahiyyaha.
aur yarael kee aek aur patnee thee, jisaka nam atara tha vah onam kee mata thee.
aur yarael ke jette ram ke ye putra hua, arthata mas, yameen aur aekera.
aur onam ke putra shammaai aur yada hue. aur shammaai ke putra nadab aur abeeshoor hue.
aur abeeshoor kee patnee ka nam abeehaail tha, aur us se ahaban aur moleed utpann huae.
aur nadab ke putra seled aur atpaaim huae seled to nisantan mar gaya. aur attaaim ka putra yishaee.
aur yishaee ka putra shoshaan aur shoshaan ka putra ahalaai.
fir shammaai ke bhai yada ke putra yeter aur yonatan huae yeter to nisantan mar gaya.
yanatan ke putra pelet aur jaja yarael ke putra ye huae.
shoshaan ke to betta n hua, keval beattyaian hui. shoshaan ke pas yarha nam aek misraee das tha.
aur shoshaan ne usako apanee bettee byah dee, aur us se attaai utpann hua.
jabad se aepalal, aepalal se obeda.
obed se yeho, yehoo se ajaryaha.
ajaryah se helaais, helaais se aelasa.
aelasa se sismaai, sismaai se shallooma.
shalloom se yakamyah aur yakamyah se aeleeshaama utpann hue.
fir yarael ke bhai kaleb ke ye putra huae arthata usaka jetta mesha jo jeep ka pita hua. aur maresha ka putra hebraen bhee usee ke vansh men hua.
aur hebraen ke putra korah, tappooh, rekem aur shoma.
aur shoma se yorkam ka pita raham aur rekem se shammaai utpann hua tha.
aur shammaai ka putra maon hua aur maon betsoor ka pita hua.
fir aepa jo kaleb kee rakhelee thee, us se haran, mosa aur gajej utpann hue aur haran se gajej utpann hua.
fir yahadaai ke putra regem, yotam, geshaan, pelet, aepa aur shaapa.
aur maka jo kaleb kee rakhelee thee, us se shober aur tirhana utpann hue.
fir us se madamanna ka pita shaap aur makabena aur giba ka pita shaba utpann hue. aur kaleb kee bettee akasa thee. kaleb ke putra yen hue.
aepraata ke jette hoor ka putra kiryatyareem ka pita shaebala.
betalehem ka pita salma aur betagader ka pita harepa.
aur kiryatyareem ke pita shaebal ke vansh men haroae adho manuhotavasee,
fir salma ke vansh men betalehem aur natopai, atraetabetyoab aur adho manahatee, soree.
fir yabes men rahanevale lekhkon ke kul arthata tiratee, shaimatee aur sookatee huae. ye rekab ke gharane ke moolapurush hamman ke vanshavale kenee haain.
daud ke putra jo hebraen men us se utpann huae ve ye haain jetta amnon jo yijraelee aheenoam se, doosara daaniyyel jo karmelee abeegaail se utpann hua.
teesara abashaalom jo gashoor ke raja talmaai kee bettee maka ka mutra tha, chautha odaniyyah jo harageet ka putra tha.
panchavan shapatyah jo abeetal se, aur chhttvan yitraam jo usakee sree aegla se utpann hua.
daud se hebraen men chh putra utpann hua, aur vahan us ne saddhe sat varsha rajy kiya aur yarooshalem men taaintees varsha rajy kiya.
aur yarooshalem men usake ye putra utpann huae arthata shaima, shaebab, tatan aur sulaaiman, ye charo ammeeael kee bettee batashoo se utpann huae.
aur yibhar, aeleeshaama aeleepeleta.
negah, nepeg, yapee.
aeleeshaama, aelyada aur aeleemelet, ye nau putra the, ye sab daud ke putra the.
aur inako chhod rakhealiyon ke bhee putra the, aur inakee bahin tamar thee.
fir sulaaiman ka putra rahabam utpann hua rahabam ka aabiyyah ka asa, asa ka yahoshaapata.
yoash ka amasyah, amasyah ka ajaryah, ajaryah ka yotama.
yotam ka ahaj, ahaj ka hijaakiyyah, hijaakiyyah ka manashsho.
manashsho ka amon, aur amon ka yoshaiyyah putra hua.
aur yoshaiyyah ke putra usaka jeia yohanan, doosara yahoyakeema teesara sidaakiyyah, chauaitha shallooma.
aur yahoyakeem ka putra yakonyah, isaka putra sidaakiyyaha.
or yakonyah ka putra asseer, usaka putra shaalateeaela.
aur malkeeram, padayah, shoenassar, yakamyah, hoshaama aur nadabyaha.
aur padayah ke putra jarubbabel aur shaimee huae aur jarubbabel ke putra mashuullam aur hananyah, jinakee baheen shalomeet thee.
aur hashooba, ohel, berekyah, hasadhah aur yooshamesed, pancha.
aur hananyah ke putra palatyah aur yashaayaha. aur rapayah ke putra arnan ke putra obadhah ke putra aur shakanyah ke putra.
aur takanyah ka putra shamayaha. aur shamayah ke putra hattoosh aur yigal, bareeh, naryah aur shapat, chh .
aur naryah ke putra aelyoaenaai, hijaakiyyah aur ajraeekam, teena.
aur aelyoaenaai ke putra hodabyah, aelyashaeeb, palayah, akakoob, yohanan, dalayah aur ananee, sata.
yahooda ke putra peres, hesraen, kama, hoor aur shaebala.
aur shaebal ke putra rayah se yahat aur yahat se ahoomaai aur lahad utpann hua, ye sorai kul haain.
aur aetam ke pita ke ye putra huae arthata yijrael, yishma aur yidasha, jinakee bahin ka nam hassalelaponee tha.
aur gador ka pita panooael, aur roosha ka pita aejera. ye aepraata ke jette hoor ke santan haai, jo betalehem ka pita hua.
aur nara se ahujjam, heper, temanee aur hahashataree utpann hua, nara ke ye hee putra, hue.
aur hela ke putra, seret, yisahar aur aemnana.
fir kos se anoob aur sobeva utpann huae aur usek vansh men haroon ke putra aharhel ke kul bhee utpann hue.
aur yabes apane bhiyon se adhaik pratishttit hua, aur usakee mata ne yah kahakar usaka nam yabes rakha, ki maain ne ise peedit hokar utpann kiya.
aur yabes ne israaael ke parameshvar ko yah kahakar pukara, ki bhla hota, ki too mujhe sachamuch ashaeesh deta, aur mera desh baddhata, aur tera hath mere sath rahata, aur too mujhe burai se aeesa bacha rakhta ki maain us se peeadit t hota ! aur jo kuchh us ne manga, vah parameshvar ne use diya.
fir shooha ke bhai kaloob se aeshaton ka pita maheer utpann hua.
aur aeshaton ke vansh men rama ka gharana, aur paseh aur irnahash ka pita taahinna utpann hua, reka ke log ye hee haain.
aur kanaj ke putra, otneeael aur sarayah, aur otneeael ka putra hatata.
monotaai se opra aur sarayah se yoab jo geharashaeem ka pita hua ve kareegar the.
aur yapunne ke putra kaleb ke putra aela aur nam, aur aela ke putra kanaja.
aur yahallel ke putra, jeep, jeepa, teeraya aur asarela.
aur usakee yahoodin sree se gador ka pita yered, soko ke pita heber aur janoh ke pita yakooteeael utpann hua, ye firon kee bettee bitya ke putra the jise mered ne byah liya tha.
aur hodiyyah kee sree jo naham kee baahin thee, usake putra keela ka pita aek geremee aur aeshatamo ka pita aek makai.
aur shaeemon ke putra amnon, rinna, benhanan aur tolon aur yishaee ke putra johet aur benajoheta.
yahooda ke putra shola ke putra leka ka pita aer, maresha ka pita lada aur ashabe ke gharane ke kul jis men san ke kapade ka kam hota tha.
aur yokeem aur kojeba ke manushy aur yoash aur sarap jo moab men prabhuta karate the aur yashoob, lehem inaka vrattant praacheen haai.
ye kumhar the, aur nataim aur gadera men rahate the jahan ve raja ka kamakaj karate huae usake pas rahate the.
shaimon ke putra namooael, yameen, yareeb, jerah aur shaaula.
aur shaaul ka putra shalloom, shalloom ka putra mibasam aur mibasam ka mishma hua.
aur mishma ka putra hammooael, usaka putra jakkoor, aur usaka putra shaimee.
shaimee ke solah bette aur chh beattyaian hui parantu usake bhaiyon ke bahut bette n hue aur unaka sara kul yahoodiyon ke barabar n baddha.
ve bershaba, molada, hasarshooala.
bilha, aesem, tolada.
batooael, horma, silkag,
betamarkabot, hasasrooseem, betabiree aur shaaraaim men bas gaae daud ke rajay ke samay tak unake ye hee nagar rahe.
aur unake ganv aetam, aeen, rimmon, token aur ashaan nam panch nagara.
aur bal tak jitane ganv in nagaron ke asapas the, unake basane ke sthan ye hee the, aur yah unakee vanshaavalee haain.
fir mashaebab aur yamlek aur apasyah ka putra yoshaa.
aur yoael aur yoshaibyah ka putra yeho, jo sarayah ka pota, aur aseeael ka paramota tha.
aur shaipee ka putra jeeja jo allon ka putra, yah yadayah ka putra, yah shaimraee ka putra, yah shamayah ka putra tha.
ye jinake nam likhen huae haai, apane apane kul men pradhaan the aur unake pitaron ke gharane bahut baddh gaae.
ye apanee bhed-bakaariyon ke liye charai ddoonddhne ko gador kee ghaattee kee tarai kee poorva or tak gaae.
aur unako uttam se uttam charai milee, aur desh lamba-chauda, chaait aur shaanati ka tha kyonki vahan ke paahile rahanevale ham ke vansh ke the.
aur jinake nam upar likhe haai, unhon ne yahooda ke raja hijaakiyyah ke dinon men vahan akar jo moonee vahan mile, unako deron samet marakar aeesa satyanash kar dala ki ah tak unaka pata naheen haai, aur ve unake sthan men rahane lage, kyonaki vahan unakee bhed-bakaariyon ke liye charai theen.
aur un men se arthata shaimoniyon men se pach sau purush apane upar palatyah, naryah, rapayah aur ujjeeael nam yishaee ke putraen ko apane pradhaan ttharaya
tab ve seid pahad ko gaa, aur jo amelekee bachakar rah gaae the unako mara, aur aj ke din tab vahan rahate haain.
israaael ka jetta to rooben tha, parantu us ne jo apane pita ke bichhaune ko ashuud kiya, is karan jette ka aadhaikar israaael ke putra yoosufa ke putraen ko diya gaya. vanshaavalee jette ke adhaikar ke anusar naheen ttharee.
kyoki yahooda apane bhiyon par prabal ho gaya, aur pradhaan usake vansh se hua parantu jette ka adhaikar yoosufa ka tha.
israaael ke jette putra rooben ke putra ye hua, arthata hanok, pallo, hesraen aur kama.
shaimee ka meeka, meeka ka rayah, rayah ka bala.
aur bal ka putra bera, isako ashshoor ka raja tilagataapilaneser bandhauai men le gaya aur vah roobeniyo ka pradhaan tha.
aur usake bhaiyon kee chanshavalee ke likhte yamay ve apane apane kul ke anusar ye tthare, arthata mukhy to yeeael, fir jakaryaha.
aur ajaj ka putra bela jo shoma ka pota aur yoael ka parapota tha, vah aroaer men aur nabo aur balmon tak rahata tha.
aur poorva or vah us jangal ke sivane tak raha jo parat mahanad tak mahunchata haai, kyonaki unake pashu gilad desh men baddh gaae the.
aur shaul ke dinon men unhon ne haagiryon se yuddh kiya, aur hagraee unake hath se mare gaae tab ve gilad kee saree poorabee alang men apane deron men rahane lage.
gadee unake samhane salka tak bashaan desh men rahate the.
arthata mukhy to yoael aur doosara shaapam fir yanaai aur shaapat, ye bashaan men rahate the.
aur unake bhai apane apane pitaron ke gharanon ke anusar meekaael, mashuullam, shoba, yoraai, yakan, jee aur aeber, sat the.
ye abeehaail ke putra the, jo hooree ka putra tha, yah yorah ka putra, yah gilad ka putra, yah mikaael ka putra, yah yashaeeshau ka putra, yah yahado ka putra, yah booj ka putra tha.
inake pitaron ke gharanon ka mukhy poorush abdeeael ka putra, aur goonee ka pota ahee tha.
ye log bashaan me, gilad aur usake ganvon me, aur shaaron kee sab charaiyon men usakee paralee or tak rahate the.
in sabhon kee vanshaavalee yahooda ke raja yonatan ke dinon aur israaael ke raja yarobam ke dinon men likhee gai.
roobeniyo, gadiyon aur manashshon ke adho gotra ke yoddha jo ddhal bandhane, talavar chalane, aur dhanush ke teer chhodne ke yogy aur yuddh karana seekhe huae the, ve chauvalees hajar sat sau satt the, jo yuddh men jane ke yogy the.
inhon ne haagiryon aur yatoor napeesh aur nodab se yuddh kiya tha.
unake viruddh inako sahayata milee, aur agraee un sab samet jo unake sath the unake hath men kar diae gaa, kyonaki yuddh men inhon ne parameshvar kee dohai dee thee aur us ne unakee binatee is karan sunee, ki inhon ne us par bhrosa rakha tha.
aur inhon ne unake pashu har lia, arthaata untt to pachas hajar, bhed-bakaree addhai lak, gadahe do hajar, aur manushy aek lakh bandhauae karake le gaae.
aur bahut se mare pade the kyonaki vah ladai parameshvar kee or se hui. aur ye unake sthan men banshuuai ke samay tak base rahe.
fir manashsho ke adho gotra kee santan us desh men base, aur ve bashaan se le balheman, aur saneer aur heman parvat tak faail gaae.
aur unhon ne apane pitaron ke parameshvar se vishvasaghaat kiya, aur us desh ke log jinako parameshvar ne unake samhane se vinash kiya tha, unake devataon ke peechhe yyabhaichaarin kee nai ho liae.
isaliye israaael ke parameshvar ne ashshoor ke raja pool aur ashshoor ke raja tilagatpailaneser ka man ubhara, aur inhon ne unhen arthata roobeniyo, gadiyon aur manashsho ke adho gotra ke logon ko bandhaua karake halah, habor aur hara aur gojan nadee ke pas pahuncha diya aur ve aj ke din tak vaheen rahate haain.
levee ke putra geshan, kahat aur mararee.
aur kahat ke putra, amraam, yisahar, hebraen aur ujjeeaela.
aur amraam kee santan haroon, moosa aur maariyanm, aur haroon ke putra, nadab, abeeho, aeleeajar aur itamara.
aeleeajar se peenahas, peenahas se abeeshoo.
abeeshoo se bukkee, bukkee se ujjee.
ujjee se jaraah, jaraah se marayota.
marayot se amaryah, amaryah se aheetooba.
aheemas se ajaryah, ajaryah se yohanana.
aur yohanan se ajaryah, utpann hua jo sulaaiman ke yarooshalem men banaae huae bhvan men yajak ka kam karata tha
fir ajaryah se amaryah, amaryah se yaheetooba.
yaheetoob se sadok, sadok se shallooma.
shalloom se hilaakiyyah, hilaakiyyah se ajaryaha.
ajaryah se sarayah, aur sarayah se yahosadak utpann hua.
aur jab yahova, yahooda aur yarooshalem ko nabookadanessar ke dara bandhaua karake le gaya, tab yahosadak bhee bandhaua hokar gaya.
levee ke putra gesham, kahat aur mararee.
aur gesham ke putraen ke nam ye the, arthata libnee aur shaimee.
aur kahat ke putra amraam, yisahar, hebraen aur ujjeeaela.
aur mararee ke putra mahalee aur mooshaee aur apane apane pitaron ke gharanon ke anusar leviyon ke kul ye huae.
arthata, geshan ka putra libnee hua, libnee ka yahat, yahat ka jimma.
jimma ka yoah, yoah ka io, io ka jerah, aur jerah ka putra yataraai hua.
fir kahat ka putra ammeenadab hua, ammeenadab ka korah, korah ka asseera.
asseer ka aelkana, aelkana ka aebyasap, aebyasap ka asseera.
asseer ka tahat, tahat ka ureeael, ureeael ka ujjaiyyah aur ujjaiyyah ka putra shaaul hua.
fir aelkana ke putra amasaai aur aheemota.
aelkana ka putra sopaai, sopaai ka nahata.
nahat ka aeleeab, aeleeab ka yaroham, aur yaroham ka putra aelkana hua.
aur shamooael ke putra, usaka jetta yoael aur doosara abiyyah hua.
ujja ka shaima shaima ka haaggaiyyah aur haggaiyyah ka putra asayah hua.
fir jinako daud ne sandook ke ttkaiana pane ke bad yahova ke bhvan men gane ke aadhaikaree tthara diyaya ve ye haain.
jab tab sulaaiman yarooshalem men yahova ke bhvan ko banava n chuka, tab tak ve milapavale tamboo ke nivas ke samhane gane ke dara seva karate the aur is seva men niyam ke anusar upasthiat hua karate the.
jo apane apane putraen samet upaasthiat hua karate the ve ye haai, arthata kahaatiyon men se heman gavaaiya jo yoael ka putra tha, aur yoael shamuael ka.
shamooael aelkana ka, aelkana yaroham ka, yaroham aeleeael ka, aeleeael toh ka.
toh soop ka, soop aelkana ka, aelkana mahat ka, mahat amasaai ka.
amasaai aelkana ka, aelkana yoael ka, yoael ajaryah ka, ajaryah sapanyah ka.
samanyah tahat ka, tahat asseer ka, asseer aebyasap ka, aettyasap korah ka.
aur usaka bhai asap jo usake daahine khda hua karata tha vah berekyah ka putra tha, aur berekyah shaima ka.
shaima meekaael ka, meekaael baseyah ka, baseyah maalmaiyyah ka.
maalkaiyyah aetnee ka, aetnee jerah ka, jerah adayah ka.
adayah aetan ka, aetan jimma ka, jimma shaimee ka.
shaimee yahat ka, yahat gesham ka, gesham levee ka putra tha.
aur bai or unake bhai mararee khde hote the, arthata aetav jo keeshaee ka putra tha, aur keeshaee abdee ka, abdee mallook ka.
mallook hashabyah ka, hashabyah amasyaah ka, amasyah hilaakiyyah ka.
hilaakiyyah amasee ka, amasee banee ka, banee shomer ka.
shomer mahalee ka, mahalee mooshaee ka, mooshaee mararee ka, aur mararee levee ka putra tha.
aur inake bhai jo leveey the vah parameshvar ke bhvan ke nivas kee sab prakar kee seva ke liye arpan kiae huae the.
parantu haroon aur usake putra hopabali kee vedee, aur dhoop kee vedee donon par baalidan chaddhate, aur param paavitrasthan ka sab kam karate, aur israaaeliyon ke liye praayaashchait karate the, jaaise ki parameshvar ke das moosa ne agyaaaaen dee theen.
