so tum jo aek jagah men ikatthe hote ho to yah prabhu bhoj khane ke liye naheen.
kyonaki khane ke samay aek doosare se paahile apana bhoj kha leta haai, so koi to bookha rahata haai, aur koi matavala ho jata haai.
kya khane peene ke liye tumhare ghar naheen? ya parameshvar kee kaleeasiya ko tuchchh janate ho, aur jin ke pas naheen haai unhen laajjait karate ho? maain tum se kya kahoon? kya is bat men tumharee prashansa karoon? maain prashansa naheen karata.
kyonaki yah bat mujhe prabhu se pahunchee, aur maain ne tumhen bhee pahuncha dee ki prabhu yeeshu ne jis rat pakadvaya gaya rottee lee.
aur dhanyavad karake use todee, aur kaha ki yah meree deh haai, jo tumhare liye haai: mere smaran ke liye yahee kiya karo.
isee reeti se us ne biyaree ke peechhe kattora bhee liya, aur kaha yah kattora mere lohoo men nai vacha haai: jab kabhee peeo, to mere smaran ke liye yahee kiya karo.
kyonaki jab kabhee tum yah rottee khate, aur is kattore men se peete ho, to prabhu kee mratyu ko jab tak vah n aa, prachar karate ho.
isaliye jo koi anuachit reeti se prabhu kee rottee khaa, ya usake kattore men se peea, vah prabhu kee deh aur lohoo ka aparadhaee ttharega.
isaliye manushy apane ap ko janch le aur isee reeati se is rottee men se khaa, aur is kattore men se peeae.
kyeanki jo khate-peete samay prabhu kee deh ko n paahichane, vah is khane aur peene se apane upar dand lata haai.
isee karan tum men se bahut se nirbal aur rogee haai, aur bahut se so bhee gaae.
yaadi ham apane ap men janchate, to dand n pate.
parantu prabhu hamen dand dekar hamaree tadna karata haai isaliye ki ham sansar ke sath doshaee n ttharen.
isaliye, he mere bhaiyo, jab tum khane ke liye ikatthe hote ho, to aek doosare ke liye tthara karo.
yaadi koi bookha ho, to apane ghar men kha le jis se tumhar ikattha hona dand ka karan n ho: aur shosh baton ko maain akar tteek kar doonga..
he bhaiyo, maain naheen chahata ki tum atmaik baradanon ke vishay men agyaat raho.
tum janate ho, ki jab tum anyajaati the, to goongee mooraton ke peechhe jese chalaae jate the vaaise chalate the.
isaliye maain tumhen chitaunee deta hoon ki jo koi parameshvar kee atma kee aguai se bolata haai, vah naheen kahata ki yeeshu srapit haai aur n koi paavitra atma ke bina kah sakata haai ki yeeshu prabhu haai..
baradan to kai prakar ke haai, parantu atma aek hee haai.
kintu sab ke labh pahunchane ke liye har aek ko atma ka prakash diya jata haai.
kyonaki aek ko atma ke dara buadi kee baten dee jatee haain aur doosare ko usee atma ke anusar gyaan kee baten.
aur kisee ko usee atma se vishvasa aur kisee ko usee aek atma se changa karane ka baradan diya jata haai.
fir kisee ko samarth ke kam karane kee shaaktai aur kisee ko bhavishyadanee kee aur kisee ko anek prakar kee bhashaa aur kisee ko bhashaaon ka arth batana.
parantu ye sab prabhavashaalee kayrya vahee aek atma karavata haai, aur jise jo chahata haai vah bantt deta haai..
kyonaki jis prakar deh to aek haai aur usake ang bahut se haai, aur us aek deh ke sab ang, bahut hone par bhee sab milakar aek hee deh haai, usee prakar maseeh bhee haai.
kyonaki ham sab ne kya yahoodee ho, kya yunanee, kya das, kya svatantra aek hee atma ke dara aek deh hone ke liye bapatisma liya, aur ham aek ko aek hee atma pilaya gaya.
isaliye ki deh men aek hee ang nahee, parantu bahut se haain.
yaadi panv kahe: ki maain hath nahee, isaaliye deh ka nahee, to kya vah is karan deh ka naheen?
aur yaadi kan kahe ki maain ankh ka nahee, isaaliye deh ka nahee, to kya vah is karan deh ka naheen.
yaadi saree deh ankh kee hotee to sunana kahan se hota? yaadi saree deh kan hee hotee to soonghana kahan hota?
parantu sachamuch parameshvar ne ango ko apanee ichchha ke anusar aek aek karake deh men rakha haai.
yaadi ve sab aek hee ang hote, to deh kahan hotee?
parantu ab ang to bahut se haai, parantu deh aek hee haai.
ankh hath se naheen kah sakatee, ki mujhe tera prayojan nahee, aur n sir panvon se kah sakata haai, ki mujhe tumhara prayojan naheen.
parantu deh ke ve ang jo auron se nirbal dekh padte haai, bahut hee avashyak haain.
aur deh ke jin ango ko ham adar ke yogy naheen samajhte haain unhee ko ham aadhaik adar dete haain aur hamare shaebhaheen ang aur bhee bahut shaebhayaman ho jate haain.
fir bhee hamare shaebhayaman ango ke is ka prayojan nahee, parantu parameshvar ne deh ko aeesa bana diya haai, ki jis ang ko ghattee thee usee ko aur bhee bahut adar ho.
taaki deh men foott n pade, parantu ang aek doosare kee barabar chinta karen.
isaliye yaadi aek ang du:kh pata haai, to sab ang usake sath du:kh pate haain aur yaadi aek ang kee badai hotee haai, to usake sath sab ang anand manate haain.
isee prakar tum sab milakar maseeh kee deh ho, aur alag alag usake ang ho.
aur paramashevar ne kaleesiya men alag alag vyaktai niyukt kiae haain prathm praerit, doosare bhvishyadvkta, teesare shaikshak, fir samarth ke kam karanevale, fir changa karanevale, aur upakar karanevale, aur pradhaan, aur nana prakar kee bhasha balanevale.
kya sab praearit haain? kya sab bhavishyadvkta haain? kya sab upadeshak haain? kya sab samarth ke kam karanevale haain?
kya sab ko changa karane ka baradan mila haai? kya sab nana prakar kee bhasha bolate haain?
kya sab anuvad karate haain? tum badee se badee baradanon kee dhaun men raho! parantu maain tumhen aur bhee sab se uttm marga batata hoon..
yaadi maain manushyo, aur savargadooton kee boliyan boloo, aur praem n rakoo, to maain ttnattnata hua peetal, aur jhnjhnatee hui jhanjh hoon.
aur yaadi maain bhavishyadanee kar sakoo, aur sab bhedon aur sab prakar ke gyaan ko samajoo, aur mujhe yahan tak poora vishvas ho, ki maain pahadon ko hatta doo, parantu praem n rakoo, to maain kuchh bhee naheen.
aur yaadi maain apanee sampoorn sanpaati kangalon ko khaila doo, ya apanee deh jalane ke liye de doo, aur praem n rakoo, to mujhe kuchh bhee labh naheen.
praem dhaeerajavant haai, aur krapal haai praem dal naheen karata praem apanee badai naheen karata, aur foolata naheen.
vah sab baten sah leta haai, sab baton kee prateeti karata haai, sab baton kee asha rakhta haai, sab baton men dhaeeraj dharata haai.
praem kabhee ttlata naheen bhavishyadaanaiyan ho, to samapt ho jaaengee, bhashaaaen ho to jatee rahengee gyaan ho, to mitt jaaega.
kyonaki hamara gyaan adhoora haai, aur hamaree bhavishyadanee adhooree.
parantu jab sarvaasiddh aaega, to adhoora mitt jaaega.
jab maain balak tha, to maain balakon kee nain bolata tha, balakon ka sa man tha balakon kee see samajh thee parantu siyana ho gaya, to balakon kee baten chhod dee.
ab hamen darpan men dhaundhala sa dikhai deta haai parantu us samay amane samhane dekhenge, is samay mera gyaan adhoora haai parantu us samay aeesee pooree reeti se pahichanoonga, jaaisa maain pahichana gaya hoon.
par ab vishvas, asha, praem ye teenon sthai haai, par in men sab se bada praem haai.
praem ka anukaran karo, aur atmaik baradanon kee bhee dhaun men raho vishosh karake yah, ki bhvishyadanee karo.
kyonaki jo anyabhasha men baten karata haai vah manushyon se nahee, parantu parameshvar se baten karata haai isaliye ki us kee koi naheen samajhta kyonaki vah bhett kee baten atma men hokar bolata haai.
parantu jo bhvishyadanee karata haai, vah manushyon se unnati, aur upadesha, aur shaantai kee baten kahata haai.
jo any bhasha men baten karata haai, vah apanee hee unnaati karata haai parantu jo bhvishyadanee karata haai, vah kaleesiya kee unnaati karata haai.
maain chahata hoo, ki tum sab any bhashaaon men baten karo, parantu aadhaikatar yah chahata hoon ki bhvishyadanee karo: kyonaki yadi anyany bhasha bolanevala kaleeasiya kee unnaati ke liye anuvad n kare to bhavishyadvvanee karanevala us se baddhkar haai.
isaliye he bhaiyo, yadi maain tumhare pas akar anyany bhasha men baten karoo, aur prakasha, ya gyaan, ya bhavishyadanee, ya upadesh kee baten tum se n kahoo, to mujh se tumhen kya labh hoga?
isee prakar yaadi nirjeev vastuaen bhee, jin se dhvaani nikalatee haai jese bansuree, ya been, yadi un ke svaron men bhed n ho to jo foonka ya bajaya jata haai, vah kyonkar paahichana jaaega?
aur yaadi turahee ka shabd safa n ho to kaun ladai ke liye taaiyaree karega?
aeese hee tum bhee yadi jeebh se safa baten n kaho, to jo kuchh kaha jata haai? vah kyonkar samajha jaaega? tum to hava se baten karanevale ttharoge.
jagat men kitane kee prakar kee bhashaaaen kyon n ho, parantu un men se koi bhee bina arth kee n hogee.
isaliye yaadi maain kisee bhasha ka arth n samajoo, to bolanevale kee drashtti men paradeshaee ttharoonga aur bolanevala mere drashtti men paradeshaee ttharega.
isaliye tum bhee jab aatmaik baradanon kee dhaun men ho, to aeesa prayatn karo, ki tumhare baradanon kee unnati se kaleeasiya kee unnaati ho.
is karan jo any bhasha bole, to vah praarthna kare, ki usaka anuvad bhee kar sake.
isaliye yaadi maain any bhasha men praarthna karoo, to meree atma praarthna karatee haai, parantu meree buaddh ikam naheen detee.
so kya karana chahiae? maain atma se bhee praarthna karoonga, aur buddh ise bhee praarthna karoonga maain atma se gaunga, aur buaddh ise bhee gaunga.
naheen to yadi too atma hee se dhanyavad karega, to fir agyaanee tere dhanyavad par ameen kyonaki kahega? isaaliye ki vah to naheen janata, ki too kya kahata haai?
too to bhlee bhanati se dhanyavad karata haai, parantu doosare kee unnati naheen hotee.
maain apane parameshvar ka dhanyavad karata hoo, ki maain tum sab se aadhaik anyany bhasha men bolata hoon.
parantu kaleeasiya men any bhasha men das hajar baten kahane se yah mujhe aur bhee achchha jan padta haai, ki auron ke sikhane ke liye buaddh ise panch hee baten kahoon..
he bhaiyo, tum samajh men balak n bano: taubhee burai men to balak raho, parantu samajh men siyane bano.
vyavastha men likha haai, ki prabhu kahata haai maain any bhasha bolanevalon ke dara, aur paraae mukh ke dara in logon se bat karoonga taubhee ve meree n sunenge.
so yaadi kaleeasiya aek jagah ikatthee ho, aur sab ke sab anyany bhasha bole, aur anapaddhe ya avishvasee log bheetar a jaaen to kya ve tumhen pagal n kahenge?
aur usake man ke bhe pragatt ho jaaenge, aur tab vah munh ke bal girakar parameshvar ko dandvat karega, aur man lega, ki sachamuch parameshvar tumhare beech men haai.
isaliye he bhaiyo kya karana chahiae? jab tum ikatthe hote ho, to har aek ke day men bhjan, ya upadesha, ya anyabhasha, ya prakasha, ya anyabhasha ka arth batana rahata haai: sab kuchh atmaik unnati ke liye hona chahiae.
yaadi any bhasha men baten karaneen ho, to do do, ya bahut ho to teen teen jan baree baree bole, aur aek vyaaktai anuvad kare.
parantu yadi anuvad karanevala n ho, to anyabhasha balanevala kaleesiya men shaant rahe, aur apane man se, aur parameshvar se baten kare.
bhavishyadvktaon men se do ya teen bole, aur shosh log un ke vachan ko parakhen.
parantu yadi doosare par jo baaitta haai, kuchh ishvareey prakash ho, to paahila chup ho jaae.
kyonaki tum sab aek aek karake bhvishyadanee kar sakate ho taki sab seekhe, aur sab shaaantai paaen.
aur bhavishyadvktaon kee atma bhvishyadvktaon ke vash men haai.
kyenaki parameshvar gadbadee ka nahee, parantu shaantai ka kartta haai jaaisa pavitra logon kee sab kaleeasiyaon men haai..
striayan kaleeasiya kee sabha men chup rahe, kyonki unhen baten karane kee agyaa nahee, parantu adhaeen rahane kee agyaa haai: jaaisa vyavastha men likha bhee haai.
aur yaadi ve kuchh seekhna chahe, to ghar men apane apane pati se poochhe, kyonki sree ka kaleeasiya men baten karana lajja kee bat haai.
kyon paramashevar ka vachan tum men se nikala? ya keval tum hee tak pahuncha haai?
yaadi koi manushy apane ap ko bhavishyadvkta ya aatmaik jan samajhe, to yah jan le, ki jo baten maain tumhen likhta hoo, ve prabhu kee agyaaaen haain.
parantu yadi koi n jane, to n jane..
so he bhaiyo, bhvishyadanee karane kee dhaun men raho aur anyabhasha bolane se mana n karo.
par saree baten sabhyata aur kramanusar kee jaaen.
he bhaiyo, maain tumhen vahee susamachar batata hoon jo pahile suna chuka hoo, jise tum ne angeekar bhee kiya tha aur jis men tum sthiar bhee ho.
usee ke dara tumhara uddhar bhee hota haai, yaadi us susamachar ko jo maain ne tumhen sunaya tha smaran rakhte ho naheen to tumhara vishvas karana vyarth hua.
isee karan maain ne sab se pahile tumhen vahee bat pahuncha dee, jo mujhe pahunchee thee, ki pavitra shaasr ke vachan ke anusar yeeshu maseeh hamare papon ke liye mar gaya.
or gada gaya aur pavitra shaasr ke anusar teesare din jee bhee utta.
aur kaaifaa ko tab barahon ko dilai diya.
fir panch sau se aadhaik bhaiyon ko aek sath dikhai diya, jin men se bahutere ab tak vartaman haain par kitane so gaae.
fir yakoob ko dikhai diya tak sab praeriton ko dikhai diya.
aur sab ke bad mujh ko bhee dikhai diya, jo mano adhoore dinon ka janma hoon.
kyonaki maain praariton men sab se chhotta hoo, baran praarit kahalane ke yogy bhee nahee, kyonki maain ne parameshvar kee kaleesiya ko sataya tha.
parantu maain jo kuchh bhee hoo, parameshvar ke anugrah se hoon: aur usaka anugrah jo mujh par hua, vah vyarth naheen huaddh paranatu maain ne un sab se baddhkar paarishram bhee kiya: taubhee yah meree or se naheen hua parantu parameshvar ke anugrah se jo mujh par tha.
so chahe maain hoo, chahe ve ho, ham yahee prachar karate haai, aur isee par tum ne vishvas bhee kiya..
yaadi mare huon ka punarootthan hee nahee, to maseeh bhee naheen jee utta.
aur yaadi maseeh bhee naheen jee utta, to hamara prachar karana bhee vyarth haai aur tumhara vishvas bhee vyarth haai.
aur yaadi murde naheen jee uttte, to maseeh bhee naheen jee utta.
aur yaadi maseeh naheen jee utta, to tumhara vishvas vyarth haai aur tum ab tak apane papon men fanse ho.
baran jo maseeh me so gaae haai, ve bhee nash huae.
yaadi ham keval isee jeevan men maseeh se asha rakhte haain to ham sab manushyon se aadhaik abhage haain..
parantu sachamuch maseeh mudorn men se jee utta haai, aur jo so gaae haai, un men pahila fal hua.
kyonaki jab manushy ke dara mratyu ai to manushy hee ke dara mare huon ka punarootthan bhee aya.
aur jaaise adam men sab marate haai, vaaisa hee maseeh men sab jilaae jaaenge.
parantu har aek apanee apanee baree se paahila fal maseeha fir maseeh ke ane par usake loga.
is ke bad ant hoga us samay vah saree pradhaanata aur sara adhaikar aur samarth ka ant karake rajy ko parameshvar pita ke hath men saunp dega.
kyonaki jab tak ki vah apane baaiariyon ko apane panvon tale n le aa, tab tak usaka rajy karana avashy haai.
sab se aantaim baairee jo nash kiya jaaega vah mratyu haai.
kyeanki parameshvar ne sab kuchh usake panvon tale kar diya haai, parantu jab vah kahata haai ki sab kuchh usake adhaeen kar diya gaya haai to pratyaksha haai, ki jis ne sab kuchh usake adhaeen kar diya, vah ap alag raha.
aur jab sab kuchh usake adhaeen ho jaaega, to putra ap bhee usake adhaeen ho jaaega jis ne sab kuchh usake adhaeen kar diya taaki sab men parameshvar hee sab kuchh ho..
naheen to jo log mare huon ke liye bapatisma lete haai, ve kya karenge? yadi murde jee uttte hee naheen? to fir kyon un ke liye bapatisma lete haain?
aur ham bhee kyon har ghadee jakhaim men pade rahate haain?
he bhaiyo, mujhe us ghamand kee sonh jo hamare maseeh yeeshu men maain tumhare vishay men karata hoo, ki maain praati din marata hoon.
yaadi maain manushy kee reeati par ifisus men bana-pashuuon se lada, to mujhe kya labh hua? yadi murde jilaae naheen jaaenge, to ao, khaae-peea, kyonaki kal to mar hee jaaenge.
dhaekha n khana, buree sangati achchhe charitra ko bigad detee haai.
dharma ke liye jag utto aur pap n karo kyonki kitane aeese haain jo parameshvar ko naheen janate, maain tumhen lajjait karate ke liye yah kahata hoon..
ab koi yah kahega, ki murde kis reeti se jee uttte haai, aur kisee deh ke sath ate haain?
he nirbuadi, jo kuchh tu bota haai, jab tak vah n mare jilaya naheen jata.
or je too bota haai, yah vah deh naheen jo utpann honevalee haai, parantu nira dana haai, chahe gehoon ka, chahe kisee aur anaj ka.
parantu parameshvar apanee ichchha ke anusar us ko deh deta haai aur har aek beej ko us kee vishosh deha.
sab shareer aek sareekhe nahee, parantu manushyon ka shareer aur haai, pashuuon ka shareer aur haai paakshiayon ka shareer aur haai machhiilayon ka shareer aur haai.
svargeey deh haai, aur pathairv deh bhee haai: parantu svargeeyah dehon ka tej aur haai, aur pathairv ka aura.
soorya ka tej aur haai, chand ka tej aur haai, aur taraganon ka tej aur haai, kyonaki aek tare se doosare tare ke tej me antar haai.
vah anadar ke sath boya jata haai, aur tej ke sath jee uttta haai nirbalata ke sath boya jata haai aur samarth ke sath jee uttta haai.
svabhaavik deh boi jatee haai, aur aatmaik deh jee utttee haai: jab ki svabhavik deh haai, to aatmaik deh bhee haai.
aeesa hee likha bhee haai, ki prathm manushy, arthata adam, jeevit praanee bana aur aantaim adam, jeevanadayak atma bana.
prathm manushy dharatee se arthata mittee ka tha doosara manushy svargeey haai.
jaaisa vah mittee ka tha vaaise hee aur mittee ke haain aur jaaisa vah svargeey haai, vaaise hee aur bhee svargeey haain.
aur jaaise ham ne usaka roop jo mittee ka tha dhaaran kiya vaaise hee us svargeey ka roop bhee dhaaran karenge..
he bhaiyo, maain yah kahata hoon ki mans aur lohoo parameshvar ke rajy ke aadhaikaree naheen ho sakate, aur n vinash avinashaee ka adhaikaree ho sakata haai.
dekhe, maain tum se bhed kee bat kahata hoon: ki ham sab to naheen soaenge, parantu sab badal jaaenge.
aur yah kshan bhr me, palak marate hee pichhlee turahee foonkate hee hoga: kayonaki turahee foonkee jaaegee aur murde aavinashaee dasha men uttaae janaege, aur ham badal jaaenge.
kyonaki avashy haai, ki vah nashaman deh avinash ko pahin le, aur yah maranahar deh amarata ko pahin le.
aur jab yah nashaman aavinash ko pahin lega, aur yah maranahar amarata ko paahin lega, tak vah vachan jo likha haai, poora ho jaaega, ki jay ne mratyu ko nigal liya.
he mratyu teree jay kahan raheen?
he mratyu tera dnk kahan raha? mratyu ka dnk pap haai aur pap ka bal byavastha haai.
parantu parameshvar ka dhanyavad ho, jo hamare prabhu yeeshu maseeh ke dara hamen jayavant karata haai.
so he mere piry bhaiyo, draddh aur attl raho, aur prabhu ke kam men sarvada baddhte jao, kyonki yah janate ho, ki tumhara paarishram prabhu men vyarth naheen haai..
ab us chande ke vishay men jo paavitra logon ke liye kiya jata haai, jaaisee agyaa maain ne galatiya kee kaleesiyaon ko dee, vaaisa hee tum bhee karo.
saptah ke paahile din tum men se har aek apanee amadanee ke anusar kuchh apane pas rakh chhoda kare, ki mere ane par chanda n karana pade.
aur jab maain aunga, to jinhen tum chahoge unhen maain chitthiyan dekar bhej doonga, ki tumhara dan yarooshalem pahuncha den.
aur yaadi mera bhee jana uchit hua, to ve mere sath jaaenge.
aur maain makiduaniya hokar to jana hee haai.
parantu sambhv haai ki tumhare yahan hee tthar jaun aur sharad retu tumhare yanha katoo, tab jis or mera jana ho, us or tum mujhe pahuncha do.
kyonaki maain ab marga men tum se bhentt karana naheen chahata parantu mujhe asha haai, ki yadi prabhu chahe to kuchh samay tak tumhare sath rahoonga.
paranatu maain peantaikust tak ifisus men rahoonga.
kyonaki mere liye aek bada aur upayogee dar khula haai, aur virodhaee bahut se haain..
yaadi teemuathaiyus a jaa, to dekhna, ki vah tumhare yahan nidr rahe kyonki vah meree nai prabhu ka kam karata haai.
isaliye koi use tuchchh n jane, parantu use kushal se is or pahuncha dena, ki mere pas a jaae kyonaki maain us kee batt joh raha hoo, ki vah bhaiyon ke sath aae.
aur bhai apullos se maain ne bahut binatee kee haai ki tumhare pas bhaiyon ke sath jaae parantu us ne us samay jane kee kuchh bhee ichchha n kee, parantu jab avasar paaega, tab a jaaega.
jagate raho, vishvas men sthiar raho, purooshaarth karo, balavant hoo.
he bhaiyo, tum staifanas ke gharane ko janate ho, ki ve akhya ke pahile fal haai, aur pavitra logon kee seva ke liye taaiyar rahate haain.
so maain tum se binatee karata hoon ki aeeson ke adhaeen raho, baran har aek ke jo is kam men paarishramee aur sahakarmee haain.
aur maain staifanas aur fooratoonatus aur akhikus ke ane se anaandait hoo, kyonki unhon ne tumharee dhattee ko pooree kee haai.
aur unhon ne meree aur tumharee atma ko chaain diya haai isaliye aeeson ko mano..
sab bhaiyon ka tum ko namaskara: paavitra chumban se apas men namaskar karo..
mujh paulus ka apane hath ka likha hua namaskara: yadi koi prabhu se praem n rakhe to vah srapit ho.
hamara prabhu anevala haai.
prabhu yeeshu maseeh ka anugrah tum par hota rahe.
mera praem maseeh yeeshu men tum sab se rahe. ameena..
paulus kee or se jo parameshvar kee ichchha se yeeshu maseeh ka praearit hone ke liye bulaya gaya aur bhai sosthianes kee or se.
parameshvar kee us kaleesiya ke niam jo kuarinthus men haai, arthata un ke nam jo maseeh yeeshu men paavitra kiae gaa, aur paavitra hone ke liye bulaae gaae haain aur un sab ke nam bhee jo har jagah hamare aur apane prabhu yeeshu maseeh ke nam kee praarthna karate haain.
hamare pita parameshvar aur prabhu yeeshu maseeh kee or se tumhen anugrah aur shaaantai milatee rahe..
maain tumhare vishay men apane parameshvar ka dhanyavad sada karata hoo, isaaliye ki parameshvar ka yah anugrah tum par maseeh yeeshu men hua.
ki us men hokar tum har bat men arthata sare vachan aur sare gyaan men dhanee kiae gaae.
ki maseeh kee gavahee tum men pakkee nikalee.
yahan tak ki kisee baradan men tumhen ghattee nahee, aur tum hamare prabhu yeeshu maseeh ke pragatt hone kee batt johate rahate ho.
vah tumhen ant tak draddh bhee karega, ki tum hamare prabhu yeeshu maseeh ke din men nirdosh ttharo.
parameshvar sachcha haai jis ne tum ko apane putra hamare prabhu yeeshu maseeh kee sangati men bulaya haai..
he bhaiyo, maain tum se yeeshu maseeh jo hamara prabhu haai usake nam ke dara binatee karata hoo, ki tum sab aek hee bat kaho aur tum men foott n ho, parantu aek hee man aur aek hee mat hokar mile raho.
kyonaki he mere bhaiyo, khloae ke gharane ke logon ne mujhe tumhare vishay men bataya haai, ki tum men jhgade ho rahe haain.
mera kahana yah haai, ki tum men se koi to apane ap ko paulus ka, koi apullos ka, koi kaaifaa ka, koi maseeh ka kahata haai.
kya maseeh batt gaya? kya paulus tumhare liye kroos par chaddhaya gaya? ya tumhen paulus ke nam par bapatisma mila?
maain parameshvar ka dhanyavad karata hoo, ki krispus aur gayus ko chhod, maain ne tum men se kisee ko bhee bapatisma naheen diya.
kaheen aeesa nah ho, ki koi kahe, ki tumhen mere nam par bapatisma mila.
aur maain ne staifanas ke gharane ko bhee bapaatisma diya in ko chhod, maain naheen janata ki maain ne aur kisee ko bapatisma diya.
kyonaki maseeh ne mujhe bapaatisma dene ko nahee, baran susamachar sunane ko bheja haai, aur yah bhee shabdon ke gyaan ke anusar nahee, aeesa n ho ki maseeh ka kroos vyarth tthare.
kyonaki kroos kee katha nash honevalon ke nikatt moorkhta haai, parantu ham uddhar panevalon ke nikatt parameshvar kee samarth haai.
kyoki likha haai, ki maain gyaanavanon ke gyaan ko nash karoonga, aur samajhdaron kee samajh ko tuchchh kar doonga.
kyonaki jab parameshvar ke gyaan ke anusar sansar ne gyaan se parameshvar ko n jana to parameshvar ko yah achchha laga, ki is prakar kee moorkhta ke dara vishvas karanevalon ko uddhar de.
yahoodee to chinh chahate haai, aur yoonanee gyaan kee khoj men haain.
parantu ham to us kroos par chaddhaae huae maseeh ka prachar karate haain jo yahoodiyon ke nikatt ttokar ka kara, aur anyajaatiyon ke nikatt moorkhta haai.
parantu jo bulaae huae haain kya yahoodee, kya yoonanee, un ke nikatt maseeh parameshvar kee samarth, aur parameshvar ka gyaan haai.
kyonaki parameshvar kee moorkhta manushyon ke gyaan se gyaanavan haai aur parameshvar kee nirbalata manushyon ke bal se bahut balavan haai..
parantu parameshvar ne jagat ke moorkhon ko chun liya haai, ki gyaanavalon ko laajjait kare aur parameshvar ne jagat ke nirbalon ko chun liya haai, ki balavanon ko laajjait kare.
aur parameshvar ne jagat ke neechon aur tuchchhon ko, baran jo haain bhee naheen un ko bhee chun liya, ki unhen jo haai, vyarth ttharaae.
taaki koi praanee parameshvar ke samhane ghamand n karane paae.
parantu usee kee or se tum maseeh yeeshu men ho, jo parameshvar kee or se hamare liye gyaan tthara arthata dharma, aur pavitrata, aur chhuttkara.
taaki jaaisa likha haai, vaaisa hee ho, ki jo ghamand kare vah prabhu men ghamand kare..
aur he bhaiyo, jab maain parameshvar ka bhed sunata hua tumhare pas aya, to vachan ya gyaan kee uttmata ke sath naheen aya.
kyonaki maain ne yah ttan liya tha, ki tumhare beech yeeshu maseeh, baran kroos par chaddhaae huae maseeh ko chhod aur kisee bat ko n janoon.
aur maain nirbalata aur bhy ke sat, aur bahut thrathrata hua tumhare sath raha.
or mere vachan, aur mere prachar men gyaan kee lubhanevalee baten naheen parantu atma aur samarth ka praman tha.
isaliye ki tumhara vishvas manushyon ke gyaan par nahee, parantu parameshvar kee samarth par nirbhr ho..
fir bhee siddh logon men ham gyaan sunate haain: parantu is sansar ka aur is sansar ke nash honevale hakimon ka gyaan naheen.
parantu ham parameshvar ka vah gupt gyaan, bhed kee reeti par batate haai, jise parameshvar ne sanatan se hamaree maahima ke liye ttharaya.
jise is sansar ke haakimon men se kisee ne naheen jana, kyonaki yadi janate, to tejomay prabhu ko kroos par n chaddhate.
parantu jaaisa likha haai, ki jo ankh ne naheen dekhee, aur kan ne naheen suna, aur jo baten manushy ke chitt men naheen chaddhee ve hee haai, jo parameshvar ne apane praem rakhnevalon ke liye taaiyar kee haain.
parantu parameshvar ne un ko apane atma ke dara ham par pragatt kiya kyonaki atma ke dara ham par pragatt kiya kyonaki atma sab bate, baran parameshvar kee gooddh baten bhee janchata haai.
manushyon men se kaun kisee manushy kee baten janata, keval manushy kee baten bhee koi naheen janata, keval paramevar ka atma.
parantu ham ne sansar kee atma nahee, parantu vah atma paya haai, jo parameshvar kee or se haai, ki ham un baton ko jane, jo parameshvar ne hamen dee haain.
jin ko ham manushyon ke gyaan kee sikhai hui baton men nahee, parantu atma kee sikhai hui baton me, atmaik baten aatmaik baton se mila milakar sunate haain.
paranatu shaareerik manushy parameshvar ke atma kee baten grahan naheen karata, kyonaki ve us kee drashtti men moorkhta kee baten haai, aur n vah unhen jan sakata haai kyonaki un kee janch aatmaik reeti se hotee haai.
aatmaik jan sab kuchh janchata haai, parantu vah ap kisee se jancha naheen jata.
kyonaki prabhu ka man kis ne jana haai, ki use sikhlaae? parantu ham men maseeh ka man haai..
he bhaiyo, maain tum se is reeati se baten n kar saka, jaaise aatmaik logon se parantu jaaise shaareerik logon se, aur un se jo maseeh men balak haain.
men ne tumhen doodha pilaya, ann n khailaya kyonki tum us ko n kha sakate the baran ab tak bhee naheen kha sakate ho.
isaliye ki jab aek kahata haai, ki maain paulus ka hoo, aur doosara ki maain apullos ka hoo, to kya tum manushy naheen?
apullos kya haai? aur paulus kya? keval sevak, jin ke dara tum ne vishvas kiya, jaaisa har aek ko prabhu ne diya.
maain ne lagaya, apullos ne seencha, parantu parameshvar ne baddhaya.
isaliye n to laganevala kuchh haai, aur n seenchanevala, parantu parameshvar jo baddhanevala haai.
laganevala aur seenchanevala danon aek haain parantu har aek vyaaktai apane hee parishram ke anusar apanee hee majadooree paaega.
kyonaki ham parameshvar ke sahakarmee haain tum parameshvar kee khetee aur parameshvar kee rachana ho.
kyonaki us nev ko chhod jo padee haai, aur vah yeeshu maseeh haai koi doosaree nev naheen dal sakata.
aur yaadi koi is nev par sona ya chandee ya bahumol patthr ya katt ya ghaas ya foos ka raa rakhta haai.
to har aek ka kam pragatt ho jaaega kyonaki vah din use bataaega isaliye ki ag ke sath pragatt hoga: aur vah ag har aek ka kam parakhegee ki kaaisa haai?
jis ka kam us par bana hua sthiar rahega, vah majadooree paaega.
aur yaadi kisee ka kam jal jaaega, to hani uttaaega par vah ap bach jaaega parantu jalate jalate..
kya tum naheen janate, ki tum parameshvar ka mandair ho, aur parameshvar ka atma tum men vas karata haai?
yaadi koi parameshvar ke maandair ko nash karega to parameshvar use nash karega kyonaki parameshvar ka mandair pavitra haai, aur vah tum ho.
koi apan ap ko dhaekha n de: yadi tum men se koi is sansar men apane ap ko gyaanee samajhe, to moorkh bane ki gyaanee ho jaae.
kyonaki is sansar ka gyaan parameshvar ke nikatt moorkhta haai, jaaisa likha haai ki vah gyaaniyon ko un kee chaturai men fansa deta haai.
aur fir prabhu gyaaaniyon kee chintaon ko janata haai, ki vyarth haain.
isaliye manushyon par koi ghamand n kare, kyonaki sab kuchh tumhara haai.
kya paulus, kya apullos, kya kaaifaa, kya jagat, kya jeevan, kya mara, kya vartaman, kya bhavishy, sab kuchh tumhara haai,
aur tum maseeh ke ho, aur maseeh parameshvar ka haai..
manushy hamen maseeh ke sevak aur parameshvar ke bhedon ke bhndaree samajhe.
fir yahan bhndaree men yah bat dekhee jatee haai, ki vishvas yogy nikale.
parantu meree draashtti men yah bahut chhottee bat haai, ki tum ya manushyon ka koi nyayee mujhe parakhe, baran maain ap hee apane ap ko naheen parakhta.
kyonaki mera man mujhe kisee bat men doshaee naheen ttharata, parantu is se maain nirdosh naheen ttharata, kyonaki mera parakhne vala prabhu haai.
so jab tak prabhu n aa, samay se paahile kisee bat ka nyay n karo: vahee to andhakar kee chhpaiee baten jyoti men dikhaaega, aur manon kee matiyon ko pragatt karega, tab parameshvar kee or se har aek kee prashansa hogee..
he bhaiyo, maain ne in baton men tumhare liye apanee aur apullos kee charcha, drashttant kee reeti par kee haai, isaliye ki tum hamare dara yah seekho, ki likhe huae se age n baddhna, aur aek ke paksha men aur doosare ke virodha men garva n karana.
kyonaki tujh men aur doosare men kaun bhed karata haai? aur tere pas kya haai jo too ne doosare se naheen paya: aur jab ki tu ne doosare se paya haai, to aeesa ghamand kyon karata haai, ki manon nahee paya?
tum to trapt ho chuke tum dhanee ho chuke, tum ne hamare bina rajy kiya parantu bhla hota ki tum rajy karate ki ham bhee tumhare sath rajy karate.
meree samajh men parameshvar ne ham praariton ko sab ke bad un logon kee nai ttharaya haai, jin kee mratyu kee agyaa ho chukee ho kyonki ham jagat aur svargadooton aur manushyon ke liye tamasha tthare haain.
ham is ghadee tak bookhe-pyase aur nange haai, aur ghoose khate haain aur mare mare firate haain aur apane hee hathon ke kam karake paarishram karate haain.
log bura kahate haai, ham ashaeesh dete haain ve satate haai, ham sahate haain.
ve badana karate haai, ham binatee karate haain: ham aj tak jagat ke koode aur sab vastuon kee khurachan kee nai tthare haain..
maain tumhen lajjait karate ke liye ye baten naheen likhta, parantu apane piry balak janakar unhen chitat hoon.
kyeanki yadi maseeh men tumhare sikhanevale das hajar bhee hote, taubhee tumhare pita bahut se nahee, isaaliye ki maseeh yeeshu men susamachar ke dara maain tumhara pita hua.
so maain tum se binatee karata hoo, ki meree see chal chalo.
isaliye maain ne teemuathaiyus ko jo prabhu men mera piry aur vishvasayogy putra haai, tumhare pas bheja haai, aur vah tumhen maseeh men mera charitra smaran karaaega, jaaise ki maain har jagah har aek kaleeasiya men upadesh karata hoon.
uparantu prabhu chahe to maain tumhare pas shaeegha hee aunga, aur un foole huon kee baton ko nahee, parantu un kee samarth ko jan loonga.
kyonaki paramashevar ka rajy baton men nahee, parantu samarth men haai.
tum kya chahate ho? kya maain chhdee lekar tumhare pas aun ya praem aur namrata kee atma ke sath?
yahan tak sunane men ata haai, ki tum men vyaabhaichar hota haai, baran aeesa vyabhaichar jo anyajatiyon men bhee naheen hota, ki aek manushy apane pita kee patnee ko rakhta haai.
aur tum shaek to naheen karate, jis se aeesa kam karanevala tumhare beech men se nikala jata, parantu ghamand karate ho.
maain to shareer ke bhav se door tha, parantu atma ke bhav se tumhare sath hokar, mano upasthiaati hee dasha men aeese kam karanevale ke vishay men yah agyaa de chuka hoon.
ki jab tum, aur meree atma, hamare prabhu yeeshu kee samarth ke sath ikatthe ho, to aeesa manushy, hamare prabhu yeeshu ke nam se.
shareer ke vinash ke liye shautan ko saunpa jaa, taki us kee atma prabhu yeeshu ke din men uddhar paae.
tumhara ghamand karana achchha naheen kya tum naheen janate, ki thoda sa khmeer poore goondho huae atte ko khmeer kar deta haai.
purana khmeer nikal kar, apane ap ko shuuddh karo: ki naya goondha hua atta ban jao taaki tum akhmeeree ho, kyonaki hamara bhee fasah jo maseeh haai, baalidan hua haai.
so ao ham utsav men anand manave, n to purane khmeer se aur n burai aur dushttta ke khmeer se, parantu seedhaai aur sachchai kee akhmeeree rottee se..
maain ne apanee patraee men tumhen likha haai, ki vyaabhaichaariyon kee sangaati n karana.
yah nahee, ki tum bilakul is jagat ke vyabhaichaariyo, ya lobhaiyo, ya andhor karanevalo, ya mootiapoojakon kee sangaati n karo kyonki is dasha men to tumhen jagat men se nikal jana hee padta.
mera kahana yah haai ki yadi koi bhai kahalakar, vyaabhaicharee, ya lobhee, ya mootiapoojak, ya galee denevala, ya piyakkad, ya andhor karanevala ho, to us kee sangati mat karana baran aeese manushy ke sath khana bhee n khana.
kyonaki mujhe baharavalon ka nyay karane se kya kama? kya tum bheetaravalon ka nyay naheen karate?
parantu baharavalon ka nyay parameshvar karata haai: isaaliye us kukarmee ko apane beech men se nikal do..
kya tum men se kisee ko yah hiyav haai, ki jab doosare ke sath jhgada ho, to faaisale ke liye aadhairmiyon ke pas jaae aur paavitra lagon ke pas n jaae?
kya tum naheen janate, ki pavitra log jagat ka nyay karenge? so jab tumhen jagat ka nyay karana he, to kya tum chhotte se chhotte jhgadon ka bhee nirny karane ke yogy naheen?
kya tum naheen janate, ki ham svargadooton ka nyay karenge? to kya sansarik baton ka nirny karana ho, to kya unheen ko baaittaoge jo kaleeasiya men kuchh naheen samajhe jate haain?
so yaadi tumhen sansarik baton ka nirny karana ho, to kya unheen ko baaittaoge jo kaleeasiya men kuchh naheen samajhe jate haain?
maain tumhen lajjait karane ke liye yah kahata hoon: kya sachamuch tum men se aek bhee buddhmaian naheen milata, jo apane bhaiyon ka nirny kar sake?
parantu sachamuch tum men bada dosh to yah haai, ki apas men mukama karate ho: baran anyay kyon naheen sahate? apanee hani kyon naheen sahate?
baran anyay karate aur hani pahunchate ho, aur vah bhee bhaiyon ko.
kya tum naheen janate, ki anyayee log parameshvar ke rajy ke varis n honge? dhaekha n khao, n veshyagamee, n mootiapoojak, n parasreegamee, n luchche, n purooshagamee.
n chor, n lobhee, n piyakkad, n galee denevale, n andhor karanevale parameshvar ke rajy ke vaaris honge.
aur tum men se kitane aeese hee the, parantu tum prabhu yeeshu maseeh ke nam se aur hamare parameshvar ke atma se dhaeae gaa, aur pavitra huae aur dharmee tthare..
sab vastuaen mere liye uchit to haai, parantu sab vastuaen labh kee nahee, sab vastuen mere liye uchit haai, parantu maain kisee bat ke adhaeen n hoonga.
bhojan pett ke liye, aur pett bhojan ke liye haai, parantu parameshvar is ko aur us ko donon ko nash karega, parantu deh vyaabhaichar ke liye nahee, baran prabhu ke liye aur prabhu deh ke liye haai.
aur parameshvar ne apanee samarth se prabhu ko jilaya, aur hamen bhee jilaaega.
kya tum naheen janate, ki jo koi veshya se sangaati karata haai, vah usake sath aek tan ho jata haai kyonki vah kahata haai, ki ve donon aek tan honge.
aur jo prabhu kee sangati men rahata haai, vah usake sath aek atma ho jata haai.
vyabhaichar se bache raho: jitane aur pap manushy karata haai, ve deh ke bahar haai, parantu vyabhaichar karanevala apanee hee deh ke virooddh pap karata haai.
kya tum naheen janate, ki tumharee deh paavitraatma ka mandair haai jo tum men basa hua haai aur tumhen parameshvar kee or se mila haai, aur tum apane naheen ho?
kayonaki dam dekar mol liye gaae ho, isaliye apanee deh ke dara parameshvar kee mahima karo..
un baton ke vishay men jo tum ne likhee, yah achchha haai, ki puroosh sree ko n chhue.
parantu vyaabhaichar ke dr se har aek puroosh kee patnee, aur har aek satraee ka pati ho.
paati apanee patnee ka hakk poora kare aur vaaise hee patnee bhee apane pati ka.
patnee ko apanee deh par aadhaikar naheen par usake pati ka adhaikar haai vaaise hee pati ko bhee apanee deh par adhaikar nahee, parantu patnee ko.
tum aek doosare se alag n raho parantu keval kuchh samay tak apas kee sammaati se ki praarthna ke liye avakash mile, aur fir aek sath raho, aeesa n ho, ki tumhare asanyam ke karan shautan tumhen parakhe.
parantu maain jo yah kahata hoon vah anumati haai n ki agyaa.
maain yah chahata hoo, ki jaaisa maain hoo, vaaisa hee sab manushy hon parantu har aek ko parameshvar kee or se vishosh vishosh baradan mile haain kisee ko kisee prakar ka, aur kisee ko kisee aur prakar ka..
parantu maain aavivaahiton aur vidhavaon ke vishay men kahata hoo, ki un ke liye aeesa hee rahana achchha haai, jaaisa maain hoon.
parantu yadi ve sanyam n kar sake, to vivah karen kyonaki vivah karana kamatur rahane se bhla haai.
jin ka byah ho gaya haai, un ko maain nahee, baran prabhu agyaa deta haai, ki patnee apane pati se alag n ho.
aur yaadi alag bhee ho jaa, to bin doosara byah kiae rahe ya apane paati se fir mel kar le aur n paati apanee patnee ko chhode.
doosaren se prabhu nahee, parantu maain hee kahata hoo, yadi kisee bhai kee patnee vishvas n rakhtee ho, aur usake sath rahate se prasann ho, to vah use n chhode.
aur jis sree ka pati vishvas n rakhta ho, aur usake sath rahane se prasann ho vah paati ko n chhode.
kyonaki aeesa paati jo vishvas n rakhta ho, vah patnee ke karan pavitra ttharata haai, aur aeesee patnee jo vishvas naheen rakhtee, paati ke karan paavitra ttharatee haai naheen to tumhare ladkebalen ashuuddh hote, parantu ab to paavitra haain.
parantu jo puroosh vishvas naheen rakhta, yaadi vah alag ho, to alag hone do, aeesee dasha men koi bhai ya baahin bandhan men naheen parantu parameshvar ne to hamen mel milap ke liye bulaya haai.
par jausa prabhu ne har aek ko bantta haai, aur parameshvar ne har aek ko bulaya haai vaaisa hee vah chale: aur maain sab kaleesiyaon men aeesa hee ttharatah hoon.
jo khtana kiya hu bulaya gaya ho, vah khtanaraahit n bane: jo khtanaraahit bulaya gaya ho, vah khtana n karaae.
n khtana kuchh haai, aur n khtanaraahit parantu parameshvar kee agyaaon ko manana hee sab kuchh haai.
har aek jan jis dasha men bulaya gaya ho, usee men rahe.
yaadi too das kee dasha men bulaya gaya ho to chinta n kara parantu yaadi too svatantra ho sake, to aeesa hee kam kara.
kyonaki jo das kee dasha men prabhu men bulaya gaya haai, vah prabhu ka svatantra kiya hua haai: aur vaaise hee jo svatantrata kee dasha men bulaya gaya haai, vah maseeh ka das haai.
tum dam dekar mol liye gaae ho, manushyon ke das n bano.
he bhaiyo, jo koi jis dasha men bulaya gaya ho, vah usee men parameshvar ke sath rahe..
kunvaariyon ke vishay men prabhu kee koi agyaa mujhe naheen milee, parantu vishvasayogy hone ke liye jaaisee daya prabhu ne mujh par kee haai, usee ke anusar sammaati deta hoon.
yaadi tere patnee haai, to us se alag hone ka yatn n kara: aur yaadi tere patnee nahee, to patnee kee khoj n kara:
parantu yadi too byah bhee kare, to pap naheen aur yadi kunvaree byahee jaae to koi pap naheen parantu aeeson ko shaareearik dukh hoga, aur maain bachana chahata hoon.
he bhaiyo, maain yah kahata hoo, ki samay kam kiya gaya haai, isaliye chaahiae ki jin ke patnee ho, ve aeese hon mano un ke patnee naheen.
aur ronevale aeese ho, mano rote naheen aur anand karanevale aeese ho, mano anand naheen karate aur mol lenevale aese ho, ki mano un ke pas kuchh haai naheen.
aur is sansar ke baratanevale aeese ho, ki sansar hee ke n ho len kyonki is sansar kee reeti aur vyavahar badalate jate haain.
so maain yah chahata hoo, ki tumhen chinta n ho: aavivaahit puroosh prabhu kee baton kee chinta men rahata haai, ki prabhu ko kyonkar prasann rakhe.
parantu vivaahit manushy sansar kee baton kee chinta men rahata haai, ki apanee patnee ko kis reeti se prasann rakhe.
vivaahita aur aavivaahita men bhee bhed haai: avivaahita prabhu kee chinta men rahatee haai, ki vah deh aur atma donon men paavitra ho, parantu vivaahita sansar kee chinta men rahatee haai, ki apane pati ko prasann rakhe.
yah bat tumhare hee labh ke liye kahata hoo, n ki tumhen fansane ke liye, baran isaaliye ki jaaisa sohata haai, vaaisa hee kiya jaae ki tum aek chitt hokar prabhu kee seva men lage raho.
aur yaadi koi yah samajhe, ki maain apanee us kunvaree ka hakk man raha hoo, jis kee javanee ddhl chalee haai, aur prayojan bhee hoa, to jaaisa chahe, vaaisa kare, is men pap nahee, vah usaka byah hone de.
parantu jo man men draddh rahata haai, aur us ko prayojan n ho, baran apanee ichchha pooree karane men adhaikar rakhta ho, aur apane man men yah bat ttan lee ho, ki maain apanee kunvaree ladkee ko bin byahee rakoonga, vah achchha karata haai.
so jo apanee kunvaree ka byah kar deta haai, vah achchha karata haai aur jo byah naheen kar deta, vah aur bhee achchha karata haai.
jab tak kisee sree ka paati jeevit rahata haai, tab tak vah us se bandhaee hui haai, parantu jab usaka pati mar jaa, to jis se chahe vivah kar sakatee haai, parantu keval prabhu men.
paranatu jesee haai yaadi vaaisee hee rahe, to mere vichar men aur bhee dhany haai, aur maain samajhta hoo, ki parameshvar ka atma mujh men bhee haai..
ab mooraton ke samhane baali kee hui vastuon ke vishay men ham janate haai, ki ham sab ko gyaan haai: gyaan ghamand utpann karata haai, parantu praem se unnaati hotee haai.
yaadi koi samajhe, ki maain kuchh janata hoo, to jaaisa janana chahiae vaaisa ab tak naheen janata.
parantu yadi koi parameshvar se praem rakhta haai, to use parameshvar pahichanata haai.
so mooraton ke samhane baali kee hui vastuon ke khane ke vishay men ham janate haai, ki moorat jagat men koi vastu nahee, aur aek ko chhod aur koi parameshvar naheen.
yadhypi akash men aur prathvee par bahut se ishvar kahalate haai, jaaisa ki bahut se ishvar or bahut se prabhu haain.
parantu sab ko yah gyaan nahee parantu kitane to ab tak moorat ko kuchh samajhne ke karan mooraton ke samhane bali kee hui ko kuchh vastu samajhkar khate haai, aur un ka vivek nirbal hokar ashuuddh hota haai.
bhejan hamen parameshvar ke nikatt naheen pahunchata, yadi ham n khana, to hamaree kuchh haani nahee, aur yadi khaae, to kuchh labh naheen.
parantu chaukas raho, aeesa n ho, ki tumharee yah svatantrata kaheen nirbalon ke liye ttokar ka karan ho jaae.
kyeanki yadi koi tujh gyaanee ko moorat ke mandair men bhojan karate dekhe, aur vah nirbal jan ho, to kya usake vivek men moorat ke samhane bali kee hui vastu ke khane ka hiyav n ho jaaega.
is reeati se tere gyaan ke karan vah nirbal bhai jis ke liye maseeh mara nash ho jaaega.
so bhaiyon ka aparadha karane se or un ke nirbal vivek ko chott dene se tum maseeh ka aparadha karate ho.
is karan yadi bhojan mere bhai ko ttokar khailaa, to maain kabhee kisee reeati se mans n khaunga, n ho ki maain apane bhai ke ttokar ka karan banoon.
kya maain svatantra naheen? kya maain praarit naheen? kya maain ne yeeshu ko jo hamara prabhu haai, naheen dekha, kya tum prabhu men mere banaae huae naheen?
yaadi maain auron ke liye praerit nahee, taubhee tumhare liye to hoon kyonaki tum prabhu men meree praearitai par chhap ho.
jo mujhe janchate haai, un ke liye yeeh mera uttr haai.
kya hamen yah aadhaikar nahee, ki kisee maseehee baahin ko byah kar ke liae fire, jaaisa aur praearit aur prabhu ke bhai aur kaaifaa karate haain?
ya keval mujhe aur baranabas ko adhaikar naheen ki kamai karana chhoden.
kaun kabhee apanee girah se khakar sipahee ka kam karata haai: kaun dakh kee baree lagakar usaka fal naheen khata? kaun bhedon kee rakhvalee karake un ka doodha naheen peeta?
kya maain ye baten manushy hee kee reeti par bolata hoon?
kya vyavastha bhee yahee naheen kahatee? kyonki moosa kee vyavastha men likha haai ki danae men chalate huae baail ka munh n bandhana: kya parameshvar baailon hee kee chinta karata haai? ya vishosh karake hamare liye kahata haai.
ha, hamare liye hee likha gaya, kyonki uchit haai, ki jatanevala asha se jote, aur davanevala bhagee hone kee asha se davanee kare.
so jab ki ham ne tumhare liye aatmaik vastuen boi, to kya yah koi badee bat haai, ki tumharee shaareearik vastuon kee fasal katten.
jab auron ka tum par yah adhaikar haai, to kya hamara is se aadhaik n hoga? parantu ham yah aadhaikar kam men naheen laae parantu sab kuchh sahate haai, ki hamare dara maseeh ke susamachar kee kuchh rok n ho.
kya tum naheen janate ki jo pavitra vastuon kee seva karate haai, ve mandair men se khate haain aur jo vedee kee seva karate haain ve vedee ke sath bhagee hote haain?
isee reeti se prabhu ne bhee ttharaya, ki jo log susamachar sunate haai, un kee jeevika susamachar se ho.
parantu maain in men se koi bhee bat kam men n laya, aur maain ne to ye baten isaaliye naheen likhee, ki mere liye aeesa kiya jaa, kyonaki is se to mera marana hee bhla haai ki koi mera ghamand vyarth ttharaae.
aur yaadi maain susamachar sunau, to mera kuchh ghamand naheen kyonaki yah to mere liye avashy haai aur yadi maain susamachar n sunau, to mujh par haya.
kyonaki yadi apanee ichchha se yah karata hoo, to majadooree mujhe milatee haai, aur yaadi apanee ichchha se naheen karata, taubhee bhndareepan mujhe saunpa gaya haai.
so meree kaun see majadooree haai? yah ki susamachar sunane men maain maseeh ka susamachar sent ment kar doon yahan tak ki susamachar men jo mera adhaikar haai, us ko maain pooree reeati se kam men laun.
kyonaki sab se svatantra hone par bhee maain ne apane ap ko sab ka das bana diya haai ki adhaik logon ko kheench laun.
maain yahoodiyon ke liye yahoodee bana ki yahoodiyon ko kheench lau, jo log vyavastha ke adhaeen haain un ke liye maain vyavastha ke adhaeen n hone par bhee vyavastha ke adhaeen bana, ki unhen jo vyavastha ke adhaeen haai, kheench laun.
vyavasthaheenon ke liye maain jo parameshvar kee vyavastha se heen nahee, parantu maseeh kee vyavastha ke adhaeen hoon vyavasthaheen sa bana, ki vyavasthaheenon ko kheench laun.
maain nirbalon ke liye nirbal sa bana, ki nirbalon ko kheench lau, maain sab manushyon ke liye sab kuchh bana hoo, ki kisee n kisee reeati se kai aek ka uddhar karaun.
kya tum naheen janate, ki daud men to chhaudte sab hee haai, parantu inam aek hee le jata haai? tum vaaise hee daudo, ki jeeto.
aur har aek pahalavan sab prakar ka sanyam karata haai, ve to aek murajhanevale mukutt ko pane ke liye yah sab karate haai, parantu ham to us mukutt ke liye karate haai, jo murajhane ka naheen.
isaliye maain to isee reeati se daudta hoo, parantu beattkaiane nahee, maain bhee isee reeti se mukkon se ladta hoo, parantu us kee nain naheen jo hava peettta hua ladta haai.
paranatu maain apanee deh ko marata koottta, aur vash men lata hoon aeesa n ho ki auron ko prachar karake, maain ap hee kisee reeati se nikamma ttharoon..
us jeevan ke vachan ke vishay men jo aadi se tha, jise ham ne suna, aur jise apanee ankhon se dekha, varan jise ham ne dhyan se dekha aur hathon se chooa.
yah jeevan pragatt hua, aur ham ne use dekha, aur us kee gavahee dete haai, aur tumhen us anant jeevan ka samachar dete haai, jo pita ke sath tha, aur ham par pragatt hua.
jo kuchh ham ne dekha aur suna haai usaka samachar tumhen bhee dete haai, isaaliye ki tum bhee hamare sath sahabhagee ho aur hamaree yah sahabhaagita pita ke sat, aur usake putra yeeshu maseeh ke sath haai.
aur ye baten ham isaaliye likhte haai, ki hamara anand poora ho jaae..
jo samachar ham ne us se suna, aur tumhen sunate haai, vah yah haai ki parameshvar jyoti haain: aur us men kuchh bhee andhakar naheen.
yaadi ham kahe, ki usake sath hamaree sahabhagita haai, aur fir andhakar men chale, to ham jootte haain: aur saty par naheen chalate.
par yaadi jaaisa vah jyoti men haai, vaaise hee ham bhee jyoti men chale, to aek doosare se sahabhaagita rakhte haain aur usake putra yeeshu maseeh ka lohoo hamen sab papon se shuuddh karata haai.
yaadi ham apane papon ko man le, to vah hamare papon ko kshama karane, aur hamen sab adharma se shuuddh karane men vishvasayogy aur dharmee haai.
yaadi kahen ki ham ne pap naheen kiya, to use jootta ttharate haai, aur usaka vachan ham men naheen haai..
he mere balako, maain ye baten tumhen isaaliye likhta hoo, ki tum pap n karo aur yadi koi pap kare, to pita ke pas hamara aek sahayak haai, arthata dhaaarmik yeeshu maseeha.
aur vahee hamare papon ka praayaashchaitt haai: aur keval hamare hee nahee, baran sare jagat ke papon ka bhee.
yaadi ham us kee agyaaon ko manenge, to us se ham jan lenge ki ham use jan gaae haain.
jo koi yah kahata haai, ki maain use jan gaya hoo, aur us kee agyaaon ko naheen manata, vah jootta haai aur us men saty naheen.
par jo koi usake vachan par chale, us men sachamuch parameshvar ka praem siddh hua haai: hamen isee se maloom hota haai, ki ham us men haain.
so koi yah kahata haai, ki maain us men bana rahata hoo, use chaahiae ki ap bhee vaaisa hee chale jaaisa vah chalata tha.
he piryo, maain tumhen koi nai agyaa naheen likhta, par vahee puranee agyaa jo arambh se tumhen milee haai yah puranee agyaa vah vachan haai, jise tum ne suna haai.
fir maain tumhen nai agyaa likhta hoon aur yah to us men aur tum men sachchee ttharatee haai kayonki andhakar mittta jata haai aur saty kee jyoti abhee chamakane lagee haai.
jo koi yah kahata haai, ki maain jyoti men hoon aur apane bhai se baair rakhta haai, vah ab tak andhakar hee men haai.
jo koi apane bhai se praem rakhta haai, vah jyoti men rahata haai, aur ttokar naheen kha sakata.
par jo koi apane bhai se baair rakhta haai, vah andhakar men haai, aur andhakar men chalata haai aur naheen janata, ki kahan jata haai, kyonaki andhakar ne us kee ankhe andhaee kar dee haain..
he balako, maain tumhen isaaliye likhta hoo, ki usake nam se tumhare pap kshama hue.
he pitaro, maain tumhen isaliye likhta hoo, ki jo adi se haai, tum use janate ho: he javano, maain tumhen isaliye likhta hoo, ki tum ne us dushtt par jay pai haai: he ladkon maain ne tumhen isaaliye likha haai, ki tum pita ko jan gaae ho.
he pitaro, maain ne tumhen isaliye likha haai, ki jo adi se haai tum use jan gaae ho: he javano, maain ne tumhen isaaliye likha haai, ki balavant ho, aur parameshvar ka vachan tum men bana rahata haai, aur tum ne us dushtt par jay pai haai.
tum n to sansar se aur n sansar men kee vastuon se praem rakho: yadi koi sansar se praem rakhta haai, to us men pita ka praem naheen haai.
aur sansar aur us kee aabhailashaaaen donon mittte jate haai, par jo parameshvar kee ichchha par chalata haai, vah sarvada bana rahega..
he ladko, yah antaim samay haai, aur jaaisa tum ne suna haai, ki maseeh ka virodhaee anevala haai, usake anusar ab bhee bahut se maseeh ke virodhaee utte haain is se ham janate haai, ki yah antaim samay haai.
ve nikale to ham hee men se, par ham men ke the naheen kyonki yadi ham men ke hote, to hamare sath rahate, par nikal isaliye gaae ki yah pragatt ho ki ve sab ham men ke naheen haain.
aur tumhara to us pavitra se aabhaishok hua haai, aur tum sab kuchh janate ho.
maain ne tumhen isaaliye naheen likha, ki tum saty ko naheen janate, par isaaliye, ki use janate ho, aur isaliye ki koi joot, saty kee or se naheen.
jootta kaun haai? keval vah, jo yeeshu ke maseeh hone ka inkar karata haai aur maseeh ka virodhaee vahee haai, jo pita ka aur putra ka inkar karata haai.
jo koi putra ka inkar karata haai usake pas pita bhee naheen: jo putra ko man leta haai, usake pas pita bhee haai.
jo kuchh tum ne arambh se suna haai vahee tum men bana rahe: jo tum ne arambh se suna haai, yaadi vah tum men bana rahe, to tum bhee putra me, aur pita men bane rahoge.
aur jis kee us ne ham se pratigyaa kee vah anant jeevan haai.
maain ne ye baten tumhen us ke vishay men likhee haai, jo tumhen bhramate haain.
aur tumhara vah abhaishok, jo us kee or se kiya gaya, tum men bana rahata haai aur tumhen is ka prayojan nahee, ki koi tumhen sikhaa, baran jaaise vah aabhaishok jo us kee or se kiya gaya tumhen sab baten sikhata haai, aur yah sachcha haai, aur jootta naheen: aur jaaisa us ne tumhen sikhaya haai vaaise hee tum us men bane rahate ho.
nidan, he balako, us men bane raho ki jab vah pragatt ho, to hamen hiyav ho, aur ham usake ane par usake samhane laajjait n hon.
dekho pita ne ham se kaaisa praem kiya haai, ki ham parameshvar kee santan kahalaae, aur ham haain bhee: is karan sansar hamen naheen janata, kyonki us ne use bhee naheen jana.
he piryo, abhee ham parameshvar kee santan haai, aur ab tak yah pragatt naheen hua, ki ham kya kuchh honge! itana janate haai, ki jab vah pragatt hoga to ham bhee usake saman honge, kyonaki us ko vaaisa hee dekhenge jaaisa vah haai.
aur jo koi us par yah asha rakhta haai, vah apane ap ko vaaisa hee pavitra karata haai, jaaisa vah pavitra haai.
jo koi pap karata haai, vah vyavastha ka virodha karata haai or pap to vyavastha ka virodha haai.
aur tum janate ho, ki vah isaaliye pragatt hua, ki papon ko har le jaae aur usake svabhav men pap naheen.
jo koi us men bana rahata haai, vah pap naheen karata: jo koi pap karata haai, us ne n to use dekha haai, aur n us ko jana haai.
he balako, kisee ke bhramane men n ana jo dharma ke kam karata haai, vahee us kee nain dharmee haai.
jo koi pap karata haai, vah shautan kee or se haai, kyonaki shautan arambh hee se pap karata aya haai: parameshvar ka putra isaaliye pragatt hua, ki shautan ke kamon ko nash kare.
jo koi parameshvar se janma haai vah pap naheen karata kyonaki usaka beej us men bana rahata haai: aur vah pap kar hee naheen sakata, kyonaki parameshvar se janma haai.
isee se parameshvar kee santan, aur shautan kee santan jane jate haain jo koi dharma ke kam naheen karata, vah parameshvar se nahee, aur n vah, jo apane bhai se praem naheen rakhta.
kyonaki jo samachar tum ne arambh se suna, vah yah haai, ki ham aek doosare se baair rakhe.
aur kaain ke saman n bane, jo us dushtt se tha, aur jis ne apane bhai ko ghaat kiya: aur use kis karan ghaat kiya? is karan ki usake kam bure the, aur usake bhai ke kam dharma ke the..
he bhaiyo, yadi sansar tum se baair karata haai to achambha n karana.
ham janate haai, ki ham mratyu se par hokar jeevan men pahunche haain kyonaki ham bhaiyon se praem rakhte haain: jo praem naheen rakhta, vah mratyu kee dasha men rahata haai.
jo koi apane bhai se baair rakhta haai, vah hatyara haai aur tum janate ho, ki kisee hatyare men anant jeevan naheen rahata.
ham ne praem isee se jana, ki us ne hamare apane praan de diae aur hamen bhee bhaiyon ke liye praan dena chaahiae.
he balako, ham vachan aur jeebh hee se nahee, par kam aur saty ke dara bhee praem karen.
isee se ham janenge, ki ham saty ke haain aur jis bat men hamara man hamen dosh dega, use vishay men ham usake samhane apane apane man ko ddhaddhs de sakenge.
kyonaki parameshvar hamare man se bada haai aur sab kuchh janata haai.
he piryo, yadi hamara man hamen dosh n de, to hamen parameshvar ke samhane hiyav hota haai.
aur jo kuchh ham mangate haai, vah hamen us se milata haai kyonaki ham us kee agyaaon ko manate haain aur jo use bhata haai vahee karate haain.
aur us kee agyaa yah haai ki ham usake putra yeeshu maseeh ke nam par vishvas karen aur jaaisa us ne hamen agyaa dee haai usee ke anusar apas men praem rakhen.
aur jo us kee agyaaon ko manata haai, vah is me, aur yah us men bana rahata haai: aur isee se, arthata us atma se jo us ne hamen diya haai, ham janate haai, ki vah ham men bana rahata haai..
he piryo, har aek atma kee prateeati n karo: baran atmaon ko parakho, ki ve parameshvar kee or se haain ki naheen kyonki bahut se jootte bhavishyadvkta jagat men nikal khde huae haain.
parameshvar ka atma tum isee reeti se pahachan sakate ho, ki jo koi atma man letee haai, ki yeeshu maseeh shareer men hokar aya haai vah parameshvar kee or se haai.
aur jo koi atma yeeshu ko naheen manatee, vah parameshvar kee or se naheen aur vahee to maseeh ke virodhaee kee atma haai jis kee charcha tum sun chuke ho, ki vah anevala haai: aur ab bhee jagat men haai.
he balako, tum parameshvar ke ho: aur tum ne un par jay pai haai kyonaki jo tum men haai, vah us se jo sansar men haai, bada haai.
ve sansar ke haai, is karan ve sansar kee baten bolate haai, aur sansar un kee sunata haai.
ham parameshvar ke haain: jo parameshvar ko janata haai, vah hamaree sunata haai jo parameshvar ko naheen janata vah hamaree nahanee sunata isee prakar ham saty kee atma aur bhram kee atma ko pahachan lete haain.
jo praem naheen rakhta, vah parameshvar ko naheen janata haai, kyonaki parameshvar praem haai.
jo praem parameshvar ham se rakhta haai, vah is se pragatt hua, ki parameshvar ne apane aekalaute putra ko jagat men bheja haai, ki ham use dara jeevan paaen.
praem is men naheen ki ham ne parameshvar ne praem kiya par is men haai, ki us ne ham se praem kiya aur hamare papon ke praayashchaitt ke liye apane putra ko bheja.
he piryo, jab parameshvar ne ham se aeesa praem kiya, to ham ko bhee apas men praem rakhna chaahiae.
parameshvar ko kabhee kisee ne naheen dekha yaadi ham apas men praem rakhe, to parameshvar ham men bana rahata haai aur usaka praem ham men siddh ho gaya haai.
isee se ham janate haai, ki ham us men bane rahate haai, aur vah ham men kyonaki us ne apane atma men se hamen diya haai.
aur ham ne dekh bhee liya aur gavahee dete haai, ki pita ne putra ko jagat ka uddharakarta karake bheja haai.
jo koi yah man leta haai, ki yeeshu parameshvar ka putra haai: parameshvar us men bana rahata haai, aur vah parameshvar men.
aur jo praem parameshvar ham se rakhta haai, us ko ham jan gaa, aur hamen us kee prateeti haai parameshvar praem haai: jo praem men bana rahata haai, vah parameshvar men bana rahata haai aur parameshvar us men bana rahata haai.
isee se praem ham men siddh hua, ki hamen nyay ke din hiyav ho kyonaki jaaisa vah haai, vaaise hee sansar men ham bhee haai.
praem men bhy naheen hota, baran siddh praem bhy ko door kar deta haai, kyonki bhy ke kashtt hota haai, aur jo bhy karata haai, vah praem men siddh naheen hua.
ham isaliye praem karate haai, ki pahile us ne ham se praem kiya.
yaadi koi kahe, ki maain parameshvar se praem rakhta hoon aur apane bhai se baair rakhe to vah jootta haai: kyonki jo apane bhai se, jis us ne dekha haai, praem naheen rakhta, to vah parameshvar se bhee jise us ne naheen dekha, praem naheen rakh sakata.
aur us se hamen yah agyaa milee haai, ki jo koi apane parameshvar se praem rakhta haai, vah apane bhai se bhee praem rakhe..
jisaka yah vishvas haai ki yeeshu hee maseeh haai, vah parameshvar se utpann hua haai aur jo koi utpann karanevale se praem rakhta haai, vah us se bhee praem rakhta haai, jo us se utpann hua haai.
aur parameshvar ka praem yah haai, ki ham us kee agyaaon ko manen aur us kee agyaaaen kattnai naheen.
kyonaki jo kuchh parameshvar se utpann hua haai, vah sansar par jay praapt karata haai, aur vah vijay jis se sansar par jay praapt hotee haai hamara vishvas haai.
sansar par jay panevala kaun haai? keval vah jis ka vishvas haai, ki yeeshu, parameshvar ka putra haai.
yahee haai vah, jo panee aur lohoo ke dara aya tha arthata yeeshu maseeha: vah n keval panee ke dara, baran panee aur lohoo donon ke dara aya tha.
aur jo gavahee deta haai, vah atma haai kyonki atma saty haai.
aur gavahee denevale teen haain atma, aur panee, aur lohoo aur teenon aek hee bat par sammat haain.
jab ham manushyon kee gavahee man lete haai, to parameshvar kee gavahee to us se baddhkar haai aur parameshvar kee gavahee yah haai, ki us ne apane putra ke vishay men gavahee dee haai.
jo parameshvar ke putra par vishvas karata haai, vah apane hee men gavahee rakhta haai jis ne parameshvar ko prateeati naheen kee, us ne use jootta ttharaya kyonaki us ne us gavahee par vishvas naheen kiya, jo parameshvar ne apane putra ke vishay men dee haai.
aur vah gavahee yah haai, ki parameshvar ne hamen anant jeevan diya haai: aur yah jeevan usake putra men haai.
jis ke pas putra haai, usake pas jeevan haai aur jis ke pas parameshvar ka putra nahee, usake pas jeevan bhee naheen haai..
maain ne tumhe, jo parameshvar ke putra ke nam par vishvas karate ho, isaaliye likha haai ki tum jano, ki anant jeevan tumhara haai.
aur hamen usake samhane jo hiyav hota haai, vah yah haai ki yadi ham us kee ichchha ke anusar kuchh mangate haai, to hamaree sunata haai.
aur jab ham janate haai, ki jo kuchh ham mangate haain vah hamaree sunata haai, to yah bhee janate haai, ki jo kuchh ham ne us se manga, vah paya haai.
