tab israaael ke raja ne yahoshaapat se kaha, kya maain ne tujh se n kaha tha, ki vah mere vishay kalyan kee naheen hani hee kee bhvishyadanee karega.
meekayah ne kaha is karan too yahova ka yah vachan sun ! mujhe sinhasan par virajaman yahova aur usake pas daahine banyen khdee iui svarga kee samast sena dikhai dee haai.
tab yahova ne poochha, ahab ko kaun aeesa bahakaaega, ki vah gilad ke ramo par chaddhai karake khet aae tab kisee te kuch, aur kisee ne kuchh kaha.
