tab yajak ne usako pavitra rottee dee kyonki doosaree rottee vahan n thee, keval bhentt kee rottee thee jo yahova ke sammukh se uttai gai thee, ki usake utta lene ke din garam rottee rakhee jaae.
usee din vahan doeg nam shaaul ka ek karmacharee yahova ke age rooka hua tha vah edomee aur shaaul ke charavahon ka muakhaiya tha.
