tab raja ne doaeg se kaha, too mudkar yajakon ko mar dala. tab aedomee doaeg ne mudkar yajakon ko mara, aur us din saneevala aepod pahine huae pachasee purooshaen ko ghaat kiya.
aur yajakon ke nagar nob ko us ne striayon-purooshae, aur balabachcho, aur doodhapiuvo, aur baailo, gadaho, aur bhed-bakaariyon samet talavar se mara.
parantu aheetoob ke putra aheemelek ka aebyatar nam aek putra bach nikala, aur daud ke pas bhag gaya.
tab aebyatar ne daud ko bataya, ki shaaul ne yahova ke yajakon ko badha kiya haai.
aur daud ne aebyatar se kaha, jis din aedomee doaeg vahan tha, usee din maain ne jan liya, ki vah nishchay shaaul ko bataaega. tere pita ke samast gharane ke mare jane ka karan maain hee hua.
isaliye too mere sath nidr raha jo mere praan ka graahak haai vahee tere praan ka bhee graahak haai parantu meere sath rahane se teree raksha hogee..
aur daud ko yah samachar mila ki palishtee log keela nagar se yuddh kar rahe haai, aur khlihanon ko loott rahe haain.
tab daud ne yahova se poochha, ki kya maain jakar paalishtaiyon ko maroon? yahova ne daud se kaha, ja, aur paalishtaiyon ko mar ke keela ko bacha.
parantu daud ke janon ne us se kaha, ham to is yahooda desh men bhee drate rahate haai, yadi ham keela jakar palishtaiyon kee sena ka samhana kare, to kya bahut adhaik dr men n padenge?
tab daud ne yahova se fir poochha, aur yahova ne use uttr dekar kaha, kamar bandhakar keela ko ja kyonaki maain paalishtaiyon ko tere hath men kar doonga.
isaliye daud apane janon ko sang lekar keela ko gaya, aur paalishtaiyon se ladkar unake pashuuon ko hank laya, aur unhen badee mar se mara. yon daud ne keela ke nivaasiyon ko bachaya.
jab aheemelek ka putra aebyatar daud ke pas keela ko bhag gaya tha, tab hath men aepod liae huae gaya tha..
tab shaaul ko yah samachar mila ki daud keela ko gaya haai. aur shaaul ne kaha, parameshvar ne use mere hath men kar diya haai vah to faattk aur bendevale nagar men ghausakar band ho gaya haai.
tab shaaul ne apanee saree sena ko ladai ke liye bulavaya, ki keela ko jakar daud aur usake janon ko ghor le.
tab daud ne jan liya ki shaaul meree haani ki yuktai kar raha haai isaaliye us ne aebyatar yajak se kaha, aepod ko nikatt le a.
tab daud ne kaha, he israael ke parameshvar yahova, tere das ne nishchay suna haai ki shaaul mere karan keela nagar nash karane ko ana chahata haai.
kya keela ke log mujhe usake vash men kar denge? kya jaaise tere das ne suna haai, vaaise hee shaaul aaega? he israael ke parameshvar yahova, apane das ko yah bata. yahova ne kaha, ha, vah aaega.
fir daud ne poochha, kya keela ke log mujhe aur mere janon ko shaaul ke vash men kar denge? yahova ne kaha, ha, ve kar denge.
tab daud aur usake jan jo koi chh: sau the keela se nikal gaa, aur idhar udhar jahan kaheen ja sake vahan gaae. aur jab shaaul ko yah bataya gaya ki daud keela se nikala bhag haai, tab us ne vahan jane kee manasa chhod dee..
jab daud jo jangal ke gaddhon men rahane laga, aur pahadee desh ke jeep nam jangal men raha. aur shaaul use praati din ddoonddhta raha, parantu parameshvar ne use usake hath men n padne diya.
aur daud ne jan liya ki shaaul mere praan kee khoj men nikala haai. aur daud jeep nam jangal ke horesh nam sthan men tha
ki shaaul ka putra yonatan uttkar usake pas horesh men gaya, aur parameshvar kee charcha karake usako ddhaddhs dilaya.
us ne us se kaha, mat dra kyonaki too mere pita shaaul ke hath men n padega aur too hee israel ka raja hoga, aur maain tere neeche hoonga aur is bat ko mera pita shaaul bhee janata haai.
tab un donon ne yahova kee shapath khakar apas men vacha bandhaee tab daud horesh men rah gaya, aur yonatan apane ghar chala gaya.
tab jeepee log giba men shaaul ke pas jakar kahane lage, daud to hamare pas horesh ke gaddhon me, arthata us hakeela nam pahadee par chhpai rahata haai, jo yashaeemon ke dakkhian kee or haai.
tum chalakar aur bhee nishchay kar lo aur dekh bhalakar jan lo, aur usake adde ka pata laga lo, aur boojho ki usako vahan kisane dekha haai kyonki kisee ne mujh se kaha haai, ki vah badee chaturai se kam karata haai.
isaliye jahan kaheen vah chhpai karata haai un sab sthanon ko dekh dekhkar pahichano, tab nishchay karake mere pas lautt ana. aur maain tumhare sath chaloonga, aur yadi vah us desh men kaheen bhee ho, to maain use yahooda ke hajaron men se ddoonddh nikaloonga.
tab ve chalakar shaaul se paahile jeep ko gaae. parantu daud apane janon samet maon nam jangal men chala gaya tha, jo araba men yashaeemon ke dakkhian kee or haai.
tab shaaul apane janon ko sath lekar usakee khoj men gaya. isaka samachar pakar daud parvat par se utarake maon jangal men rahane laga. yah sun shaaul ne maon jangal men daud ka peechha kiya.
shaaul to pahad kee aek or, aur daud apen janon samet pahad kee doosaree or ja raha tha aur daud shaaul ke dr ke mare jaldee ja raha tha, aur shaaul apane janon samet daud aur usake janon ko pakadne ke liye ghora banana chahata tha,
ki aek doot ne shaaul ke pas akar kaha, faurtee se chala a kyonaki palishtaiyon ne desh par chaddhai kee haai.
yah sun shaaul daud ka peechha chhodkar paalishtaiyon ka samhana karane ko chala is karan us sthan ka nam selahammahalakot pada.
vahan se daud chaddhkar aenagadee ke gaddhon men rahane laga..
jab shaaul paalishtaiyon ka peechha karake lautta, tab usako yah samachar mila, ki daud aenagadee ke jangal men haai.
tab shaaul samast israaeliyon men se teen hajar ko chhanttkar daud aur usake janon ko banaaile bakaron kee chattanon par khojane gaya.
jab vah marga par ke bhedshaalon ke pas pahuncha jahan aek gufaa thee, tab shaaul disha firane ko usake bheetar gaya. aur usee gufaa ke konon men daud aur usake jan baaitte huae the.
tab daud ke janon ne us se kaha, sun, aj vahee din haai jisake vishay yahova ne tujh se kaha tha, ki maain tere shatra ko tere hath men saunp doonga, ki too us se manamana bartav kar le. tab daud ne uttkar shaaul ke bage kee chhor ko chhpaikar katt liya.
isake peechhe daud shaaul ke bage kee chhor kattne se pachhtaya.
aur apane janon se kahane laga, yahova n kare ki maain apane prabhu se jo yahova ka abhaishaikt haai aeesa kam karoo, ki us par hath chalau, kyonki vah yahova ka abhaishaikt haai.
aeesee baten kahakar daud ne apane janon ko ghaudkee lagai aur unhen shaaul kee haani karane ko uttne n diya. fir shaaul uttkar gufaa se nikala aur apana marga liya.
usake peechhe daud bhee uttkar gufaa se nikala aur shaaul ko peechhe se pukar ke bola, he meere prabhu, he raja. jab shaaul ne fir ke dekha, tab daud ne boomi kee or sir jhukakar dandvata kee.
aur daud ne shaaul se kaha, jo manushy kahate haai, ki daud teree hani chahata haai unakee too kyon sunata haai?
dek, aj too ne apanee ankhon se dekha haai ki yahova ne aj gufaa men tujhe mere hath saunp diya tha aur kisee kisee ne to mujh se tujhe marane ko kaha tha, parantu mujhe tujh par taras aya aur maain ne kaha, maain apane prabhu par hath n chalaunga kyonki vah yahova ka abhaishaikt haai.
fir, he mere pita, dek, apane bage kee chhor mere hath men dekh maain ne tere bage kee chhor to katt lee, parantu tujhe ghaat n kiya is se nishchay karake jan le, ki meere man men koi burai va aparadha ka soch naheen haai. aur maain ne tera kuchh aparadha naheen kiya, parantu too mere praan lene ko mano usaka aher karata rahata haai.
yahova mera aur tera nyay kare, aur yahova tujh se mera palatta le parantu mera hath tujh par n uttega.
praacheenon ke neeti vachan ke anusar dushttta dushtton se hotee haai parantu mera hath tujh par n uttega.
israael ka raja kis ka peechha karane ko nikala haai? aur kis ke peechhe pada haai? aek mare kutte ke peechhe! aek pissoo ke peechhe!
isaliye yahova nyayee hokar mera tera vichar kare, aur vichar karake mera mukama lade, aur nyay karake mujhe tere hath se bachaae.
daud shaaul se ye baten kahee chuka tha, ki shaaul ne kaha, he mere bette daud, kya yah tera bol haai? tab shaaul chillakar rone laga.
fir us ne daud se kaha, too mujh se adhaik dharmee haai too ne to mere sath bhlai kee haai, parantu maain ne tere sath burai kee.
aur too ne aj yah pragatt kiya haai, ki too ne mere sath bhlai kee haai, ki jab yahova ne mujhe tere hath men kar diya, tab too ne mujhe ghaat n kiya.
bhla! kya koi manushy apane shatra ko pakar kushal se jane deta haai? isaaliye jo too ne aj mere sath kiya haai, isaka achchha badala yahova tujhe de.
aur ab, mujhe maloom hua haai ki too nishchay raja ko jaaega, aur israael ka rajy tere hath men sthiar hoga.
tab daud ne shaaul se aeesee hee shapath khai. tab shaaul apane ghar chala gaya aur daud apane janon samet gaddhon men chala gaya.
maon men aek puroosh rahata tha jisaka mal karmel men tha. aur vah puroosh bahut bada tha, aur usake teen hajar bhede, aur aek hajar bakariyon theen aur vah apanee bhedon ka un katar raha tha.
us puroosh ka nam nabal, aur usakee patnee ka nam abeegaail tha. sree to buddhmaian aur roopavatee thee, parantu puroosh kattor, aur bure bure kam karanevala tha vah to kalebavanshaee tha.
jab daud ne jangal men samachar paya, ki nabal apanee bhedon ka un katar raha haai
tab daud ne das javanon ko vahan bhej diya, or daud ne un javanon se kaha, ki karmel men nabal ke pas jakar meree or se usaka kushalakshom poochho.
aur us se yon kaho, ki too chiranjeev rahe, tera kalyan ho, aur tera gharana kalyan se rahe, aur jo kuchh tera haai vah kalyan se rahe.
maain ne suna haai, ki jo too un katar raha haai tere charavahe ham logon ke pas rahe, aur n to ham ne unakee kuchh hani kee, aur n unaka kuchh khoya gaya.
apane javanon se yah bat poochh le, aur ve tujh ka bataaenge. so in javanon par tere anugrah kee drashtti ho ham to anand ke samay men aae haai, isaaliye jo kuchh tere hath lage vah apane dason aur apane bette daud ko de.
aeesee aeesee baten daud ke javan jakar usake nam se nabal ko sunakar chup rahe.
nabal ne daud ke janon ko uttr dekar un se kaha, daud kaun haai? yishau ka putra kaun haai? aj kal bahut se das apane apane svamee ke pas se bhag jate haain.
kya maain apanee rottee-panee aur jo pashu maain ne apane kataranevalon ke liye mare haain lekar aeese logon ko de doo, jinako maain naheen janata ki kahan ke haain?
tab daud ke javanon ne lauttkar apana marga liya, aur lauttkar usako se sab baten jyon kee tyon suna deen.
tab daud ne apane janon se kaha, apanee apanee talavar bandha lo. tab unhon ne apanee apanee talavar bandha lee aur daud ne bhee apanee talavar bangha lee aur koi char sau puroosh daud ke peechhe peechhe chale, aur do sau saman ke pas rah gaae.
parantu aek sevak ne nabal kee patnee abeegaail ko bataya, ki daud ne jangal se hamare svamee ko ashaeervad dene ke liye doot bheje the aur us ne unhen lalakara diya.
parantu ve manushy ham se bahut achchha bartav rakhte the, aur jab tak ham maaidan men rahate huae unake pas aya jaya karate the, tab tak n to hamaree kuchh hani hui, aur n hamara kuchh khoya gaya
jab tak ham un ke sath bhed-bakaariyan charate rahe, tab tak ve rat din hamaree ad bane rahe.
isaliye ab soch vichar kar ki kya karana chaahiae kyonaki unhon ne hamare svamee kee or usake samast gharane kee hani ttanee hogee, vah to aeesa dushtt haai ki us se koi bol bhee naheen sakata.
ab abeegaail ne faurtee se do sau rottee, aur do kuppee dakhmadha, aur panch bheadiyon ka mans, aur panch saa boona hua anaj, aur aek sau guchchhe kishaamisha, aur anjeeron kee do sau ttiikayan lekar gadahon par ladavai.
aur us ne apane javanon se kaha, tum mere age age chalo, maain tumhare peechhe peechhe atee hoon paranatu us ne apane pati nabal se kuchh n kaha.
vah gadahe par chaddhee hui pahad kee ad men utaree jatee thee, aur daud apane janon samet usake samahane utara ata tha aur vah unako milee.
daud ne to socha tha, ki maain ne jo jangal men usake sab mal kee aeesee raksha kee ki usaka kuchh bhee n khoya, yah ni:sandeh vyarth hua kyonaki us ne bhlai ke badale mujh se burai hee kee haai.
yaadi bihan ko ujiyala hone tak us jan ke samast logon men se aek ladke ko bhee maain jeevit chhodoo, to parameshvar mere sab shatrauon se aeesa hee, varan is se bhee adhaik kare.
daud ko dekh abeegaail faurtee karake gadahe par se utar padee, aur daud ke sammukh munh ke bal boomi par girakar dandvata kee.
fir vah usake panv par girake kahane lagee, he mere prabhu, yah aparan mere hee sir par ho teree dasee tujh se kuchh kahana chahatee haai, aur too apanee dasee kee baton ko sun le.
mera prabhu us dushtt nabal par chitt n lagaae kyonki jaaisa usaka nam haai vaaisa hee vah ap haai usaka nam to nabal haai, aur sachamuch us men mooddhta pai jatee haai parantu mujh teree dasee ne apane prabhu ke javanon ko jinhen too ne bheja tha n dekha tha.
aur ab, he mere prabhu, yahova ke jeevan kee shapath aur tere jeevan kee shapat, ki yahova ne jo tujhe koon se aur apane hath ke dara apana palatta lene se rok rakha haai, isaaliye ab tere shatra aur mere prabhu kee haati ke chahanevale nabal hee ke saman ttharen.
aur ab yah bhentt jo teree dasee apane prabhu ke pas lai haai, un javanon ko dee jaae jo mere prabhu ke sath chalate haain.
apanee dasee ka aparadha kshama kara kyonaki yahova nishchay mere prabhu ka ghar basaaega aur sthiar karega, isaliye ki mera prabhu yahova kee or se ladta haai aur janm bhr tujh men koi burai naheen pai jaaegee.
isaliye jab yahova mere prabhu ke liye yah samast bhlai karega jo us ne tere vishay men kahee haai, aur tujhe israael par pradhaan karake ttharaaega,
tab tujhe is karan pachhtana n hoga, va mere prabhu ka day peeadit n hoga ki too ne akaran koon kiya, aur mere prabhu ne apana palatta ap liya haai. fir jab yahova mere prabhu se bhlai kare tab apanee dasee ko smaran karana.
aur tera vivek dhany haai, aur too ap bhee dhany haai, ki too ne mujhe aj ke din koon karane aur apana palatta ap lene se rok liya haai.
kyonaki sachamuch israael ka parameshvar yahova, jis ne mujhe teree hani karane se roka haai, usake jeevan kee shapat, yaadi too faurtee karake munjh se bhentt karane ko n atee, to ni:sandeh bihan ko ujiyala hone tak nabal ka koi ladka bhee n bachata.
tab daud ne use grahan kiya jo vah usake liye lai thee fir us se us ne kaha, apane ghar kushal se ja sun, maain ne teree bat manee haai aur teree binatee grahan kar lee haai.
tab abeegaail nabal ke pas lautt gai aur kya dekhtee haai, ki vah ghar men raja kee see jevanar kar raha haai. aur nabal ka man magan haai, aur vah nasho men aati choor ho gaya haai isaliyeus ne bhor ke ujiyalehane se pahile us se kuchh bhee n kaha.
bihan ko jab nabal ka nasha utar gaya, tab usakee patnee ne use kul hal suna diya, tab usake man ka hiyav jata raha, aur vah patthr sa sunn ho gaya.
aur das din ke pashchata yahova ne nabal ko aeesa mara, ki vah mar gaya.
nabal ke marane ka hal sunakar daud ne kaha, dhany haai yahova jis ne nabal ke sath meree namadharai ka mukama ladkar apane das ko burai se rok rakha aur yahova ne nabal kee buraiko usee ke sir par lad diya haai. tab daud ne logon ko abeegaail ke pas isaliye bheja ki ve us se usakee patnee hone kee batacheet karen.
to jab daud ke sevak karmel ko abeegaail ke pas pahunche, tab us se kahane lage, ki daud ne hamen tere pas isaliye bheja haai ki too usakee patnee bane.
tab vah uttee, aur munh ke bal boomi par gir dandvata karake kaha, teree dasee apane prabhu ke sevakon ke charan dhaene ke liye laundee bane.
