jo apana dhan byaj adi baddhtee se baddhata haai, vah usake liye battorata haai jo kangalon par anugrah karata haai.
jo apana kan vyavastha sunane se faer leta haai, usakee praarthna gharaanait ttharatee haai.
jo seedho logon ko bhttkakar kumarga men le jata haai vah apane khode huae gadhe men ap hee girata haai parantu khre log kalyan ke bhagee hote haain.
dhanee puroosh apanee drashtti men buddhmaian hota haai, parantu samajhdar kangal usaka marma boojh leta haai.
jab dharmee log jayavant hote haai, tab badee shaebha hotee haai parantu jab dushtt log prabal hote haai, tab manushy apane ap ko chhpaiata haai.
jo apane aparadha chhpai rakhta haai, usaka karya sufal naheen hota, parantu jo unako man leta aur chhod bhee deta haai, us par daya kee jayegee.
jo manushy nirantar prabhu ka bhy manata rahata haai vah dhany haai parantu jo apana man kattor kar leta haai vah vipaati men padta haai.
kangal praja par prabhuta karanevala dushtt garajanevale sinh aur ghoomanevale reechh ke saman haai.
jo pradhaan mandabuddh ika hota haai, vahee bahut andhor karata haai aur jo lalach ka baairee hota haai vah deegharayu hota haai.
jo kisee praanee kee hatya ka aparadhaee ho, vah bhagakar gadhe men girega koi usako n rokega.
jo seedhaai se chalata haai vah bachaya jata haai, parantu jo tteddhee chal chalata haai vah achanak gir padta haai.
jo apanee boomi ko jota-boya karata haai, usaka to pett bhrata haai, parantu jo nikamme logon kee sangati karata haai vah kangalapan se ghaira rahata haai.
sachche manushy par bahut ashaeervad hote rahate haai, parantu jo dhanee hon se utavalee karata haai, vah nirdosh naheen ttharata.
pakshapat karana achchha naheen aur yah bhee achchha naheen ki puroosh aek ttukade rottee ke liye aparadha kare.
lobhee jan dhan praapt karane men utavalee karata haai, aur naheen janata ki vah ghattee men padega.
jo kisee manushy ko danttta haai vah ant men chapaloosee karanevale se aadhaik pyara ho jata haai.
jo apane man-bap ko loottkar kahata haai ki kuchh aparadha nahee, vah nash karanevale ka sangee ttharata haai.
jo apane upar bhrosa rakhta haai, vah moorkh haai aur jo buddh ise chalata haai, vah bachata haai.
jo nirdhan ko dan deta haai use ghattee naheen hotee, parantu jo us se duashtti faer leta haai vah shaap par shaap pata haai.
jab dushtt log prabal hote haain tab to manushy ddoonddhe naheen milate, parantu jab ve nash ho jate haai, tab dharmee unnaati karate haain..
jo bar bar dantte jane par bhee hatt karata haai, vah achanak nash ho jaaega aur usaka koi bhee upay kam n aaega.
jab dharmee log shairomanai hote haai, tab praja anandait hotee haai parantu jab dushtt prabhuta karata haai tab praja hay maratee haai.
jo puroosh buaddh ise praeeti rakhta haai, apane pita ko anandait karata haai, parantu veshyaon kee sangaati karanevala dhan ko uda deta haai.
raja nyay se desh ko sthiar karata haai, parantu jo bahut ghoos leta haai usako ulatt deta haai.
jo puroosh kisee se chikanee chupadee baten karata haai, vah usake paairon ke liye jal lagata haai.
bure manushy ka aparadha fanda hota haai, parantu dharmee anandait hokar jayajayakar karata haai.
ttttha karanevale log nagar ko foonk dete haai, parantu buaddhmaian log krodha ko ttnda karate haain.
jab buaddhmaian mooddh ke sath vadavivad karata haai, tab vah mooddh krodhait hota aur ttttha karata haai, aur vahan shaaantai naheen rahatee.
hatyare log khre puroosh se baair rakhte haai, aur seedho logon ke praan kee khoj karate haain.
moorkh apane sare man kee bat khol deta haai, parantu buaddhmaian apane man ko rokata, aur shaant kar deta haai.
jab haakim joottee bat kee or kan lagata haai, tab usake sab sevak dushtt ho jate haain.
nirdhan aur andhor karanevala puroosh aek saman haai aur yahova donon kee ankhon men jyoti deta haai.
jo raja kangalon ka nyay sachchai se chukata haai, usakee gaee sadaaiv sthiar rahatee haai.
chhdee aur dantt se buddh ipraapt hotee haai, parantu jo ladka yoniee chhoda jata haai vah apanee mata kee lajja ka karan hota haai.
dushtton ke badne se aparadha bhee baddhta haai parantu ant men dharmee log unaka girana dekh lete haain.
apane bette kee tadna kar, tab us se tujhe chaain milega aur tera man sukhee ho jaaega.
jahan darshan kee bat naheen hotee, vahan log nirankush ho jate haai, aur jo vyavastha ko manata haai vah dhany hota haai.
das baton hee ke dara sudhaara naheen jata, kyonki vah samajhdar bhee naheen manata.
kya too baten karane men utavalee karanevale manushy ko dekhta haai? us se aadhaik to moorkh hee se asha haai.
jo apane das ko usake ladkapan se sukumarapan men palata haai, vah das ant men usaka betta ban baaittta haai.
krodha karanevala manushy jhgada machata haai aur atyant krodha karanevala aparadhaee hota haai.
manushy garva ke karan neecha khata haai, parantu namra atmavala mahima ka aadhaikaree hota haai.
jo chor kee sangaati karata haai vah apane praan ka baairee hota haai shapath khane par bhee vah bat ko pragatt naheen karata.
manushy ka bhy khana fanda ho jata haai, parantu jo yahova par bhrosa rakhta haai vah unche sthan par chaddhaya jata haai.
haakim se bhentt karana bahut log chahate haai, parantu manushy ka nyay yahova kee karata haai.
he mere putra, yaadi too mere vachan grahan kare, aur meree agyaaon ko apane day men rakh chhode,
aur buaddh ikee bat dhyan se sune, aur samajh kee bat man lagakar soche
aur praveenta aur samajh ke liye aati yatn se pukare,
or usako chandee kee nain ddoonddhe, aur gupt dhan ke saman usee khoj men laga rahe
to too yahova ke bhy ko samajhega, aur parameshvar ka gyaan tujhe praapt hoga.
kyonaki buddh iyahova hee deta haai gyaan aur samajh kee baten usee ke munh se nikalatee haain.
vah seedho logon ke liye khree buddh irakh chhodta haai jo khrai se chalate haai, unake liye vah ddhal ttharata haai.
vah nyay ke pathon kee dekh bhal karata, aur apane bhkton ke marga kee raksha karata haai.
tab too dharma aur nyay, aur seedhaai ko, nidan sab bhlee-bhlee chal samajh sakega
kyonaki buddh ito tere day men pravesh karegee, aur gyaan tujhe manabha lagega
taaki tujhe burai ke marga se, aur ulatt faer kee baton ke kahane valon se bachaa,
jo seedhaai ke marga ko chhod dete haai, taki andhore marga men chalen
jo burai karane se anandait hote haai, aur dushtt jan kee ulatt faer kee baton men magan rahate haain
jinakee chalachalan tteddhee meddhee aur jinake marga bigade huae haain..
tab too parai sree se bhee bachega, jo chikanee chupadee baten bolatee haai,
aur apanee javanee ke sathee ko chhod detee, aur jo apane parameshvar kee vacha ko bool jatee haai.
usaka ghar mratyu kee ddhlan par haai, aur usee dgaren mare huon ke beech pahunchatee haain
jo usake pas jate haai, un men se koi bhee lauttkar naheen ata aur n ve jeevan ka marga pate haain..
too bhle manushyon ke marga men chal, aur dhaarmiyon kee batt ko pakade raha.
kyonaki dharmee log desh men base raheenge, aur khre log hee us men bane rahenge.
dushtt log desh men se nash honge, aur vishvasaghaatee us men se ukhade jaaenge..
yake ke putra agoor ke prabhavashaalee vachana.. us puroosh ne iteeael aur ukkal se yah kaha,
nishchay maain pashu sareekha hoo, varan manushy kahalane ke yogy bhee naheen aur manushy kee samajh mujh men naheen haai.
n maain ne buaddh ipraapt kee haai, aur n paramapavitra ka gyaan mujhe mila haai.
kaun svarga men chaddhkar fir utar aya? kis ne vayu ko apanee mutthee men battor rakha haai? kis ne mahasagar ko apane vasr men bandha liya haai? kis ne prathvee ke sivanon ko ttharaya haai? usaka nam kya haai? aur usake putra ka nam kya haai? yaadi too janata ho to bata!
ishvar ka aek aek vachan taya hua haai vah apane sharanagaton kee ddhal tthara haai.
usake vachanon men kuchh mat baddha, aeesa n ho ki vah tujhe dantte aur too jootta tthare..
maain ne tujh se do var mange haai, isaaliye mere marane se pahile unhen mujhe dene se munh n mod:
aeesa n ho, ki jab mera pett bhr jaa, tab maain inkar karake kahoon ki yahova kaun haai? va apana bhag khokar choree karoo, aur apane parameshvar ka nam anuachit reeti se loon.
kisee das kee, usake svamee se chugalee n karana, aeesa n ho ki vah tujhe shaap de, aur too doshaee ttharaya jaae..
aeese log haai, jo apane pita ko shaap dete aur apanee mata ko dhany naheen kahate.
aeese log haain jo apanee draashtti men shuuddh haai, taubhee unaka maail dhaeya naheen gaya.
aek peeddhee ke log aeese haain unakee draashtti kya hee ghamand se bhree rahatee haai, aur unakee ankhen kaaisee chaddhee hui rahatee haain.
aek peeddhee ke log aeese haai, jinake dant talavar aur unakee daddhen chhuariyan haai, jin se ve deen logon ko prathvee par se, aur daaridraen ko manushyon men se mitta dalen..
jaaise jonk kee do bechhyaian hotee haai, jo kahatee haain de, de, vaaise hee teen vastuaen haai, jo trapt naheen hoteen varan char haai, jo kabhee naheen kahatee, basa.
adhaelok aur banjh kee kok, boomi jo jal pee peekar trapt naheen hotee, aur ag jo kabhee naheen kahatee, basa..
jis ankh se koi apane pita par anadar kee draashtti kare, aur apaman ke sath apanee mata kee agyaa n mane, us ankh ko tarai ke kauve khod khodakar nikalenge, aur ukab ke bachche kha dalenge..
teen baten mere liye aadhaik kattnai haai, varan char haai, jo meree samajh se pare haain:
akash men ukab pakshaee ka marga, chattan par sarpa kee chal, samudra men jahaj kee chal, aur kanya ke sang puroosh kee chala..
teen baton ke karan prathvee kanpatee haai varan char haai, jo us se sahee naheen jateen:
das ka raja ho jana, mooddh ka pett bhrana
ghainaunee sree ka byaha jana, aur dasee ka apanee svaamin kee varis hona..
prathvee par char chhotte jantu haai, jo atyant buaddhmaian haain:
chyoottyaian nirbal jaati to haai, parantu dhoopakal men apanee bhojanavastu battoratee haain
shaapan balee jati nahee, taubhee unakee manden pahadon par hotee haain
ttiiddayon ke raja to naheen hota, taubhee ve sab kee sab dal bandha bandhakar payan karatee haain
aur chhpaikalee hath se pakadee to jatee haai, taubhee rajabhvanon men rahatee haai..
teen sundar chalanevale praanee haain varan char haai, jin kee chal sundar haai:
sinh jo sab pashuuon men parakramee haai, aur kisee ke dr se naheen hattta
shaikaree kutta aur bakara, aur apanee sena samet raja.
yaadi too ne apanee baddhai karane kee mooddhta kee, va koi buree yuaktai bandhaee ho, to apane munh par hath dhara.
kyonaki jaaise doodha ke mathne se makkhn aur nak ke marodne se lohoo nikalata haai, vaaise hee krodha ke bhdkane se jhgada utpann hota haai..
lamooael raja ke prabhavashaalee vachan, jo usakee mata ne use sikhaae..
he mere putra, he mere nij putra! he meree mannaton ke putra!
apana bal striayon ko n dena, n apana jeevan unake vash kar deta jo rajaon ka pauroosh kho detee haain.
he lamooael, rajaon ka dakhmagha peena unako shaebha naheen deta, aur maadira chahana, raiyon ko naheen fabata
maadira usako pilao jo marane par haai, aur dakhmadha udas manavalon ko hee dena
jis se ve peekar apanee daaridrata ko bool jaaen aur apane kaattnai shram fir smaran n karen.
goonge ke liye apana munh khol, aur sab anathon ka nyay uchit reeti se kiya kara.
apana munh khol aur dharma se nyay kar, aur deen daaridraen ka nyay kara.
bhlee patnee kaun pa sakata haai? kyonaki usaka mooly moongon se bhee bahut adhaik haai. usake paati ke man men usake prati vishvas haai.
aur use labh kee ghattee naheen hotee.
vah apane jeevan ke sare dinon men us se bura nahee, varan bhla hee vyavahar karatee haai.
vah un aur san ddoonddh ddoonddhkar, apane hathon se prasannata ke sath kam karatee haai.
vah vyopar ke jahajon kee nai apanee bhojanavastuaen door se mangavatee haain.
vah rat hee ko utt baaitttee haai, aur apane gharane ko bhojan khailatee haai aur apanee laundiyon ko alag alag kam detee haai.
vah kisee khet ke vishay men soch vichar karatee haai aur use mol le letee haai aur apane parishram ke fal se dakh kee baree lagatee haai.
vah apanee kaatt iko bal ke faentte se kasatee haai, aur apanee bahon ko draddh banatee haai.
vah atteran men hath lagatee haai, aur charakha pakadtee haai.
vah deen ke liye mutthee kholatee haai, aur daaridra ke sanbhalane ko hath baddhatee haai.
vah apane gharane ke liye him se naheen dratee, kyonaki usake ghar ke sab log lal kapade paahinate haain.
vah taakiye bana letee haai usake vasr sooksham san aur baainjanee rang ke hote haain.
jab usaka paati sabha men desh ke puraaniyon ke sang baaittta haai, tab usaka sanman hota haai.
vah san ke vasr banakar bechatee haai aur vyoparee ko kamaraband detee haai.
vah bal aur pratap ka pahirava pahine rahatee haai, aur anevale kal ke vishay par hansatee haai.
vah buaddh ikee bat bolatee haai, aur usake vachan krapa kee shaiksha ke anusar hote haain.
vah apane gharane ke chalachalan ko dhyan se dekhtee haai, aur apanee rottee bina paarishram naheen khatee.
usake putra utt uttkar usako dhany kahate haai, unaka pati bhee uttkar usakee aeesee prashansa karata haai:
bahut see striayon ne achchhe achchhe kam to kiae haain parantu too un sabhon men shraeshtt haai.
shaebha to joottee aur sundarata vyarth haai, parantu jo sree yahova ka bhy manatee haai, usakee prashansa kee jaaegee.
usake hathon ke parishram ka fal use do, aur usake karyon se sabha men usakee prashansa hogee..
kyonaki aeesa karane se teree ayu baddhegee, aur too adhaik kushal se rahega.
krapa aur sachchai tujh se alag n hone paaen varan unako apane gale ka har banana, aur apanee dayaroopee pattyai par likhna.
aur too parameshvar aur manushy donon ka anugrah paaega, too aati buddhmaian hoga..
usee ko smaran karake sab kam karana, tab ve tere liye seedha marga nikalega.
apanee draashtti men buddhmaian n hona yahova ka bhy manana, aur burai se alag rahana.
aeesa karane se tera shareer bhla changa, aur teree haddiyan pushtt rahengee.
apanee sanpaati ke dara aur apanee boomi kee pahilee upaj de dekar yahova kee praatishtta karana
is prakar tere khtte bhre aur poore rahenge, aur tere rasakundon se naya dakhmadha umandta rahega..
he mere putra, yahova kee shaiksha se munh n modna, aur jab vah tujhe dantte, tab too bura n manana,
kyonaki yahova jis se praem rakhta haai usako danttta haai, jaaise ki bap us bette ko jise vah aadhaik chahata haai..
kya hee dhany haai vah manushy jo buaddh ipaa, aur vah manushy jo samajh praapt kare,
kyonaki buddh ikee praaptai chandee kee praaaptai se badee, aur usaka labh chokhe sone ke labh se bhee uttm haai.
vah moonge se adhaik anamol haai, aur jitanee vastuon kee too lalasa karata haai, un men se koi bhee usake tuly n ttharegee.
usake daahine hath men deegharayu, aur usake baen hath men dhan aur mahima haai.
usake marga manabha haai, aur usake sab marga kushal ke haain.
jo buaddh iko grahan kar lete haai, unake liye vah jeevan ka vraksha banatee haai aur jo usako pakade rahate haai, vah dhany haain..
usee ke gyaan ke dara gaahire sagar foott nikale, aur akashamandl se os ttpakatee haai..
he mere putra, ye baten teree draashtti kee ott n hane paaen khree buddh iddh aur vivek kee raksha kar,
tab in se tujhe jeevan milega, aur ye tere gale ka har banenge.
aur too apane marga par nidr chalega, aur tere panv men ttes n lagegee.
jab too lettega, tab bhy n khaaega, jab too lettega, tab sukh kee neend aaegee.
achanak anevale bhy se n drana, aur jab dushtton par vipaati a pade, tab n ghabarana
kyonaki yahova tujhe sahara diya karega, aur tere panv ko fande men fansane n dega.
jinaka bhla karana chaahiye, yaadi tujh men shaktai rahe, to unaka bhla karane se n rookana..
yaadi tere pas dene ko kuchh ho, to apane padosee se n kahana ki ja kal fir ana, kal maain tujhe doonga.
jab tera padosee tere pas bekhttke rahata haai, tab usake virooddh buree yuktai n bandhana.
jis manushy ne tujh se bura vyavahar n kiya ho, us se akaran mukama khda n karana.
upadravee puroosh ke vishay men dah n karana, n usakee see chal chalana
kyonaki yahova kuttlai se gharana karata haai, parantu vah apana bhed seedho logon par kholata haai..
dushtt ke ghar par yahova ka shaap aur dhaarmiyon ke vasasthan par usakee ashaeesh hotee haai.
ttttha karanevalon se vah nishchay ttttha karata haai aur deenon par anugrah karata haai.
he mere putrae, pita kee shaiksha suno, aur samajh praapt karane men man lagao.
kyonaki maain ne tum ko uttm shaiksha dee haai meree shaiksha ko n chhodo.
dekho, maain bhee apane pita ka putra tha, aur mata ka akela dulara tha,
aur mera pita mujhe yah kahakar sikhata tha, ki tera man mere vachan par laga rahe too meree agyaaon ka palan kar, tab jeevit rahega.
buaddh iko praapt kar, samajh ko bhee praapt kara unako bool n jana, n meree baton ko chhodna.
buaddh iko n chhod, vah teree raksha karegee us se praeeati rak, vah tera pahara degee.
buaddh ishraeshtt haai isaaliye usakee praaptai ke liye yatn kara jo kuchh too praapt kare use praapt to kar parantu samajh kee praaptai ka yatn ghattne n paae.
usakee badai kar, vah tujh ko baddhaegee jab too us se lipatt jaa, tab vah teree mahima karegee.
vah tere sir par shaebhayaman booshan bandhogee aur tujhe sundar mukutt degee..
he mere putra, meree baten sunakar grahan kar, tab too bahut varsha tab jeeavit rahega.
maain ne tujhe buaddh ika marga bataya haai aur seedhaai ke path par chalaya haai.
chalane men tujhe rok ttok n hogee, aur chahe too daude, taubhee ttokar n khaaega.
shaiksha ko pakade rah, use chhod n de usakee raksha kar, kyonki vahee tera jeevan haai.
dushtton kee batt men panv n dharana, aur n bure logon ke marga par chalana.
kyonaki dushtt log yaadi burai n kare, to unako neend naheen atee aur jab tak ve kisee ko ttokar n khailaae, tab tak unhen neend naheen milatee.
ve to dushttta se kamai hui rottee khate, aur upadrav ke dara paya hua dakhmadha peete haain.
parantu dharmiyon kee chal us chamakatee hui jyoti ke saman haai, jisaka prakash dopahar tak adhaik adhaik baddhta rahata haai.
dushtton ka marga ghaer andhakaramay haai ve naheen janate ki ve kis se ttokar khate haain..
he mere putra mere vachan dhyan dharake sun, aur apana kan meree baton par laga.
inako apanee ankhon kee ott n hone de varan apane man men dhaaran kara.
kyonaki jinakon ve praapt hotee haai, ve unake jeevit rahane ka, aur unake sare shareer ke change rahane ka karan hotee haain.
sab se aadhaik apane man kee raksha kara kyonki jeevan ka mool srot vahee haai.
tteddhee bat apane munh se mat bol, aur chalabajee kee baten kahana tujh se door rahe.
teree ankhen samhane hee kee or lagee rahe, aur teree palaken age kee or khulee rahen.
apane panv dharane ke liye marga ko samathr kar, aur tere sab marga tteek rahen.
n to dahinee or muddhna, aur n bain ora apane panv ko burai ke marga par chalane se hatta le..
he mere putra, meree buddh ikee baton par dhyan de, meree samajh kee or kan laga
jis se tera vivek surakshiat bana rahe, aur too gyaan ke vachanon ko thamen rahe.
parantu isaka parinam nagadauna sa kaduva aur dodhaaree talavar sa paaina hota haai.
usake panv mratyu kee or baddhte haain aur usake pag adhaelok tak pahunchate haain..
isaliye use jeevan ka samathr path naheen mil pata usake chalachalan men chanchalata haai, parantu use vah ap naheen janatee..
isaliye ab he mere putrae, meree suno, aur meree baton se munh n modo.
aeesee sree se door hee rah, aur usakee devaddhee ke pas bhee n jana
kaheen aeesa n ho ki too apana yash auron ke hat, aur apana jeevan kroor jan ke vash men kar de
ya paraae teree kamai se apana pett bhre, aur paredashaee manushy tere parishram ka fal apane ghar men rakhen
aur too apane aantaim samay men jab ki tera shareer kshaeen ho jaae tab yah kahakar hay marane lage, ki
maain ne shaiksha se kaaisa baair kiya, aur danttnevale ka kaaisa tiraskar kiya!
maain ne apane gurooon kee baten n manee aur apane sikhanevalon kee or dhyan n lagaya.
maain sabha aur mandlee ke beech men praaya: sab buraiyon men ja pada..
too apane hee kund se panee, aur apane hee koonae se sote ka jal piya karana.
kya tere soton ka panee sadk me, aur tere jal kee dhaara chaukon men bah jane paae?
yah keval tere hee liye rahe, aur tere sang auron ke liye n ho.
