vah misr desh men senaon ke yahova ke liye chinh aur sakshaee ttharega aur jab ve andhor karanevale ke karan yahova kee dohai denge, tab vah unake pas aek uddharakarta aur rakshak bhejega, aur unhen mukt karega.
tab yahova apane ap ko misriyon par pragatt karega aur misree us samay yahova ko pahichanenge aur melabali aur annabali chaddhakar usakee upasana karenge, aur yahova ke liye mannat manakar pooree bhee karenge.
aur yahova misriyon ko marega, aur marega aur changa bhee karega, aur ve yahova kee or firenge aur vah unakee binatee sunakar unako changa karega..
us samay misr se ashshoor jane ka ek rajamarga hoga, aur ashshooree misr men aenge aur misree log ashshoor ko jaenge, aur misree ashshooriyon ke sang milakar aradhana karenge..
us samay israel, misr aur ashshoor teenon milakar prathvee ke liye ashaeesh ka karan honge.
kyonaki senaon ka yahova un teenon ko yah kahakar ashaeesh dega, dhany ho meree praja misr, aur mera rakh hua ashshoor, aur mera nij bhag israaela..
amos ke putra yashaayah ka darshan, jisako us ne yahooda aur yarooshalem ke vishay men ujjaiyah, yotam, ahaj, aur hijaakiyyah nam yahooda ke rajaon ke dinon men paya.
he svarga sun, aur he prathvee kan laga kyonaki yahova kahata haai: maain ne balabachchon ka palan poshan kiya, aur unako baddhaya bhee, parantu unhon ne mujh se balava kiya.
baail to apane malik ko aur gadaha apane svamee kee charanee ko pahichanata haai, parantu israael mujhen naheen janata, meree praja vichar naheen karatee..
hay, yah jati pap se kaaisee bhree haai! yah samaj adharma se kaaisa lada hua haai! is vansh ke log kaaise kukarmee haai, ye ladkebale kaaise bigade huae haain! unhon ne yahova ko chhod diya, unhon ne israael ke pavitra ko tuchchh jana haai! ve paraae banakar door ho gaae haain..
tum balava kar karake kyon adhaik mar khana chahate ho? tumhara sir ghaavon se bhr gaya, aur tumhara day du:kh se bhra haai.
tumhara desh ujada pada haai, tumhare nagar bhsm ho gaae haain tumhare kheton ko paradeshaee log tumhare dekhte hee nigal rahe haain vah paradeshyaien se nash kiae huae desh ke saman ujad haai.
aur siyyon kee bettee dakh kee baree men kee jhopadee kee nain chhod dee gai haai, va kakadee ke khet men kee chhpaariya ya ghaire huae nagar ke saman akelee khdee haai.
yaadi senaon ka yahova hamare thode se logon ko n bacha rakhta, to ham sadom ke saman ho jate, aur amora ke saman ttharate..
he sadom ke nyaiyo, yahova ka vachan suno! he amora kee praja, hamare parameshvar kee shaiksha par kan laga.
yahova yah kahata haai, tumhare bahut se melabali mere kis kam ke haain? maain to meddhon ke homabaaliyon se aur pale huae pashuuon kee charbee se agha gaya hoon
maain bachhdon va bhed ke bachchon va bakaron ke lohoo se prasann naheen hota.. tum jab apane munh mujhe dikhane ke liye ate ho, tab yah kaun chahata haai ki tum mere anganon ko panv se raundo?
vyarth annabali fir mat lao dhoop se mujhe gharana haai. naye chand aur vishraamadin ka manana, aur sabhaon ka prachar karana, yah mujhe bura lagata haai. mahasabha ke sath hee sath anarth kam karana mujh se saha naheen jata.
jab tum meree or hath faailao, tab maain tum se munh faer loonga tum kitanee hee praarthna kyon n karo, taubhee maain tumharee n sunoonga kyonki tumhare hath koon se bhre haain.
apane ko dhaekar paavitra karo: meree ankhon ke samhane se apane bure kamon ko door karo bhvishy men burai karata chhod do,
bhlai karana seekho yatn se nyay karo, upadravee ko sudhaaro anath ka nyay chukao, vidhava ka mukama lado..
yahova kahata haai, ao, ham apas men vadaavivad karen: tumhare pap chahe lal rang ke ho, taubhee ve him kee nain ujale ho jaaenge aur chahe argavanee rang ke ho, taubhee ve un ke saman shvet ho jaaenge.
yaadi tum agyaakaree hokar meree mano,
to is desh ke uttm se uttm padathai khaoge aur yadi tum ne mano aur balava karo, to talavar se mare jaoge yahova ka yahee vachan haai..
jo nagaree satee thee so kyonkar vyabhaichaarin ho gai! vah nyay se bhree thee aur us men dharma paya jata tha, parantu ab us men hatyare hee paae jate haain. teree chandee ghaatu ka maail ho gai,
tere dakhmadha men panee mil gaya haai.
tere hakim hatteele aur choron se mile haain. ve sab ke sab ghoos khanevale aur bhentt ke lalachee haain. ve anath ka nyay naheen karate, aur n vidhava ka mukama apane pas ane dete haain.
is karan prabhu senaon ke yahova, israael ke shaktaiman kee yah vanee haai: suno, maain apane shatrauon ko door karake shaantai paunga, aur apane baairiyon se palatta loonga.
aur maain tum par hath baddhakar tumhara dhaatu ka maail pooree reeati se door karoonga.
aur maain tum men pahile kee nain nyayee aur adi kal ke saman mantraee fir niyukt karoonga. usake bad too dhamrapuree aur satee nagaree kahalaaegee..
siyyon nyay ke dara, aur jo us men firenge ve dharma ke dara chhuda liae jaaenge.
parantu balavaiyon aur papiyon ka aek sang nash hoga, aur jinhon ne yahova ko nyaga haai, unaka ant ho jaaega.
kyonaki jin banjavrakshaen se tum praeeti rakhte the, un se ve lajjait honge, aur jin bariyon se tum prasann rahate the, usake karan tumhare munh kale honge.
kyonaki tum patte murjhaae huae banjavraksha ke, aur bina jal kee baree ke saman ho jaoge.
aur balavan to san aur usaka kam chingaree banega, aur donon aek sath jalenge, aur koi bujhanevala n hoga..
jis varsha men ashshoor ke raja sargon kee agyaa se tartan ne ashadod akar us se yuddh kiya aur usako le bhee liya,
usee varsha yahova ne amos ke putra yashaayah se kaha, jakar apanee kamar ka ttatt khol aur apanee jootiyan utara so us ne vaaisa hee kiya, aur vah nanga aur nange panv ghoomata firata tha.
aur yahova ne kaha, jis prakar mera das yashaayah teen varsha se ughaada aur nange panv chalata aya haai, ki misr aur koosh ke liye chinh aur chamatkar ho,
usee prakar ashshoor ka raja misree aur koosh ke logon ko bandhaua karake desha-nikal karega, kya ladke kya booddhe, sabhon ko bandhauae karake ughaade aur nange panv aur nitamb khule le jaega, jis se misr lajjait ho.
aur samudra ke is par ke basanevale us samay yah kahenge, dekho, jin par ham asha rakhte the or jinake pas ham ashshoor ke raja se bachane ke liye bhagane ko the unakee aeesee dasha ho gai haai. to fir ham log kaaise bachenge?
samudra ke pas ke jangal ke vishay bharee vachana. jaaise dakkhianee prachand bavandr chala ata haai, vah jangal se arthata dravane desh se nikatt a raha haai.
kashtt kee baton ka mujhe darshan dikhaya gaya haai vishvasaghaatee vishvasaghaat karata haai, aur nashak nash karata haai. he aelam, chaddhai kar, he madaai, ghor le usaka sab karahana maain band karata hoon.
is karan meree kaatt imen kaattnai peeda haai mujh ko mano jachcha peeden ho rahee haai maain aeese sankatt men padtr gaya hoon ki kuchh sunai naheen deta, maain aesa ghabara gaya hoon ki kuchh dikhai naheen danta.
mera day dhadkata haai, maain atyant bhyabheet hoo, jis sanjh kee maain batt johata tha use us ne meree thrathrahatt ka karan kar diya haai.
bhojan kee taaiyaree ho rahee haai, paharooae baaittaae ja rahe haai, khana-peena ho raha haai. he hakimo, utto, ddhal men tel malo!
kyonaki prabhu ne mujh se yon kaha haai, jakar aek paharooa khda kar de, aur vah jo kuchh dekhe use bataae.
jab vah savar dekhe jo do-do karake ate ho, aur gadahon aur untton ke savar, tab bahut hee dhyan dekar sune.
aur kya dekhta hoon ki manushyon ka dal aur do-do karake sava chale a rahe haain! aur vah bol utta, gir pada, babul gir pada aur usake devataon ke sab khudee hui mooraten boomi par chakanachoor kar dalee gai haain.
he mere daaen hua, aur mere khalihan ke ann, jo baten maain ne israael ke parameshvar senaon ke yahova se sunee haai, unako maain ne tumhen jata diya haai.
dooma ke vishay bharee vachana. seir men se koi mujhe pukar raha haai, he paharooa, rat ka kya samachar haai? he paharooa, rat kee kya khbar haai?
paharooae ne kaha, bhor hotee haai aur rat bhee. yaadi tum poochhna chahate ho to poochho fir lauttkar ana..
arab ke virooddh bharee vachana. he dadanee battohiyo, tum ko arab ke jangal men rat bitanee padegee.
ve pyase ke pas jal laa, tema desh ke rahanevale rottee lekar bhaganevale se milane ke liye nikal a rahe haain.
kyonaki ve talavaron ke samhane se varan nangee talavar se aur tane huae dhanush se aur ghaer yuddh se bhage haain.
kyonaki prabhu ne mujh se yon kaha haai, majadoor ke vasharen ke anusar aek varsha men kedar ka sara vibhv mittaya jaaega
aur kedar ke dhanudhararee shooraveeron men se thode hee rah jaaenge kyonaki israael ke parameshvar yahova ne aeesa kaha haai..
darshan kee tarai ke vishay men bharee vachana. tumhen kya hua ki tum sab ke sab chhton par chaddh gaae ho,
he kolahal aur udham se bhree prasann nagaree? tujh men jo mare gaae haain ve n to talavar se aur n ladai men mare gaae haain.
tere sab nyayee aek sang bhag gaae aur dhanudharariyon se bandho gaae haain. aur tere jitane shosh paae gaae ve aek sang bandho gaa, ve door bhage the.
is karan maain ne kaha, meree or se munh faer lo ki maain bilak bilakakar roun mere nagar satyanash hone ke shaek men mujhe shaaantai dene ka yatn mat karo..
kyonaki senaon ke prabhu yahova ka ttharaya hua din hoga, jab darshan kee tarai men kolahal aur raunda jana aur bechaainee hogee shaharapanah men surang lagai jaaegee aur dohai ka shabd pahadon tak pahunchega.
aur aelam paaidalon ke dal aur savaron samet tarkash bandho huae haai, aur keer ddhal khole huae haai.
teree uttm uttm taraiyan rathon se bhree hui hongee aur savar faattk ke samhane panti bandhonge. us ne yahooda ka ghoonghatt khol diya haai.
us din too ne van nam bhvan ke asr-shasr ka smaran kiya,
aur too ne daudapur kee shaharapanah kee dararon ko dekha ki ve bahut haai, aur too ne nichale pokhre ke jal ko ikattha kiya.
aur yarooshalem ke gharon ko ginakar shaharapanah ke draddh karane ke liye gharon ko ddha diya.
too ne donon bheeton ke beech purane pokhre ke jal ke liye aek kund khoda. parantu too ne usake karta ko smaran naheen kiya, jis ne praacheenakal se usako tthara rakha tha, aur n usakee or too ne drashtti kee..
parantu kya dekha ki harsha aur anand manaya ja raha haai, gaya-baail ka ghaat aur bhed-bakaree ka vadha kiya ja raha haai, mans khaya aur dakhmadha peeya ja raha haai. aur kahate haai, ao khaaen-peeae, kyonki kal to hamen marana haai.
senaon ke yahova ne mere kan men kaha aur apane man kee bat pragatt kee, nishchay tum logon ke is adharma ka kuchh bhee praayaashchaitt tumharee mratyu tak n ho sakega, senaon ke prabhu yahova ka yahee kahana haai.
senaon ka prabhu yahova yon kahata haai, shobana nam us bhndaree ke pas jo rajagharane ke kam par niyukt haai jakar kah, yahan too kya karata haai?
aur yahan tera kaun haai ki too ne apanee kabar yahan khudavai haai? too apanee kabar unche sthan men khudavata aur apane rahane ka sthan chattan men khudavata haai?
dek, yahova tujh ko badee shaktai se pakadkar bahut door faenk dega.
vah tujhe marodkar gend kee nai lambe chaude desh men faenk dega he apane svamee ke gharane ko lajjait karanevale vahan too marega aur tere vibhv ke rath vaheen rah jaaenge.
maain tujh ko tere sthan par se ddhkel doonga, aur too apane pad se utar diya jayega.
us samay maain hilkaiyah ke putra apane das elyakeem ko bulakar, use tera angarakha pahanaunga,
aur usakee kamar men teree pettee kasakar bandhoonga, aur teree prabhuta usake hath men doonga. aur vah yarooshalem ke rahanevalon aur yahooda ke gharane ka pita ttharega.
aur maain usako draddh sthan men koonttee kee nain gaoonga, aur vah apane pita ke gharane ke liye vibhv ka karan hoga.
aur usake pita se gharane ka sara vibhv, vansh aur santan, sab chhotte-chhotte patra, kya kattore kya suraahiya, sab us par ttangee jaaengee.
senaon ke yahova kee yah vanee haai ki us samay vah koonttee jo draddh sthan men gadee gai thee, vah ddheelee ho jaaegee, aur kattkar girai jaaegee aur us ka bojh gir jaaega, kyonaki yahova ne yah kaha haai.
sor ke vishay bharee vachana. he tashareesh ke jahajon hay, hay, karo kyonki vah ujad gaya vahan n to koi ghar aur n koi sharan ka sthan haai! yah bat unako kitiayon ke desh men se pragatt kee gai haai.
he samudra ke teer ke rahanevalo, jinako samudra ke par janevale seedonee vyapaariyon ne dhan se bhr diya haai, chup raho!
shaeehor ka ann, aur neel nadee ke pas kee upaj mahasagar ke marga se usako minatee thee, kyonki vah aur jatiyon ke liye vyopar ka sthan tha.
he seedon, laajjait ho, kyonki samudra ne arthata samudra ke draddh saian ne yah kaha haai, maain ne n to kabhee janmane kee peeda janee aur n balak ko janm diya, aur n betton ko pala aur n beattyaien ko posa haai.
jab sor ka samachar misr men pahunche, tab ve sunakar sankatt men padenge.
he samudra ke teer ke rahanevalon hay, hay, karo! par hokar tashareesh ko jao.
kya yah tumharee prasannata se bhree hui nagaree haai jo praacheenakal se basee thee, jisake panv use basane ko door le jate the?
sor jo rajaon kee gaee par baaittatee thee, jisake vyoparee haakim the, aur jisake mahajan prathvee bhr men pratishttit the, usake virooddh kis ne aeesee yuaktai kee haai?
senaon ke yahova hee ne aeesee yuktai kee haai ki samast gaurav ke ghamand ko tuchchh kar de aur prathvee ke pratishttiton ka apaman karavaae.
he tashareesh ke nivaasiyon neel nadee kee nai apane desh men faail jao ab kuchh bandhan naheen raha.
us ne apana hath samudra par baddhakar rajyon ko hila diya haai yahova ne kanan ke draddh kilon ke nash karane kee agyaa dee haai.
aur us ne kaha haai, he seedon, he bhrashtt kee hui kumaree, too fir prasann hone kee naheen ut, par hokar kitiayon ke pas ja, parantu vahan bhee tujhe chaain n milega..
kasadiyon ke desh ko dekho, vah jaati ab n rahee ashshoor ne us desh ko jangalee jantuon ka sthan banaya. unhon ne apane gummatt uttaae aur rajabhvanon ko ddha diya, aur usako khndhar kar diya.
he tashareesh ke jahajo, hay, hay, karo, kyonaki tumhara draddhsthan ujad gaya haai.
us samay ek raja ke dinon ke anusar sattr varsha ke beetane par sor veshya kee nain geet gane lagega.
he bisaree hui veshya, veena lekar nagar men ghoom, bhlee bhanati baja, bahut geet ga, jis se log fir tujhe yad karen.
usake vyopar kee praaptai, aur usake chhnaiale kee kamai, yahova ke liye paavitra ki jaegee vah n bhndar men rakhee jaegee n sanchay kee jaegee, kyonki usake vyopar kee praaaptai unheen ke kam men aegee jo yahova ke samhane raha karenge, ki unako bhrapoor bhojan aur chamakeela vasr mile..
suno, yahova prathvee ko nirjan aur sunasan karane par haai, vah usako ulattkar usake rahanevalon ko titar bitar karega.
aur jaaisee yajaman kee vaaisee yajak kee jaaisee das kee vaaisee svamee kee jaaisee dasee kee vaaisee svaminee kee jaaisee lenevale kee vaaisee bechanevale kee jaaisee udhaar denevale kee vaaisee udhaar lenevale kee jaaisee byaj lenevale kee vaaisee byaj denevale kee sabhon kee aek hee dasha hogee.
prathvee shoony aur satyanash ho jaaegee kyonaki yahova hee ne yah kaha haai..
prathvee vilap karegee aur murjhaaegee, jagat kumhalaaega aur murjha jaaega prathvee ke mahan log bhee kumhala jaaenge.
prathvee apane rahanevalon ke karan ashuuddh ho gai haai, kyonki unhon ne vyavastha ka ullanghan kiya aur vidhai ko palatt dala, aur sanatan vacha ko tod diya haai.
is karan prathvee ko shaap grasega aur us men rahanevale doshaee ttharenge aur isee karan prathvee ke nivasee bhsm honge aur thode hee manushy rah jaaenge.
naya dakhmadha jata rahega, dakhlata murjha jaaegee, aur jitane man men anand karate haain sab lambee lambee sans lenge.
dfa ka sukhdai shabd band ho jaaega, veena ka sukhdai shabd shaant ho jaaega.
ve gakar fir dakhmadha n peeaenge peenevale ko maadira kadukee lagegee.
sadkon men log dakhmadha ke liye chillaaenge anand mitt jaaega: desh ka sara harsha jata rahega.
nagar ujad hee ujad rahega, aur usake faattk todkar nash kiae jaaenge.
kyonaki prathvee par desh desh ke logon men aeesa hoga jaaisa ki jalapaiyon ke jhadne ke samay, va dakh todne ke bad koi koi fal rah jate haain..
ve log gala kholakar jayajayakar karenge, aur yahova ke mahatmy ko dekhkar samudra se lalakarenge.
is karan poorva men yahova kee mahima karo, aur samudra ke deepon men israael ke parameshvar yahova ke nam ka gunanuvad karo.
prathvee kee chhor se hamen aeese geet kee dhvani sun padtee haai, ki dharmee kee maahima aur badai ho. parantu maain ne kaha, hay, haya! maain nash ho gaya, nasha! kyonaki vishvasaghaatee vishvasaghaat karate, ve bada hee vishvasaghaat karate haain..
he prathvee ke rahanevalon tumhare liye bhy aur gadha aur fanda haai!
jo koi bhy ke shabd se bhage vah gadhe men girega, aur jo koi gadhe men se nikale vah fande men fansega. kyonaki akash ke jhrokhe khul jaaenge, aur prathvee kee nev dol uttegee. prathvee atyant kampayaman hogee.
vah matavale kee nain bahut dgamagaaegee
aur machan kee nai dolegee vah apane pap ke bojh se dabakar giregee aur fir n uttegee..
us samay aeesa hoga ki yahova akash kee sena ko akash men aur prathvee ke rajaon ko prathvee hee par dand dega.
ve bandhauon kee nai gadhe men ikatthe kiae jaaenge aur bandeegrah men band kiae jaaenge aur bahut dinon ke bad unakee suadhai lee jaaegee.
tab chandrama sankuchit ho jaaega aur soorya laajjait hoga kyonaki senaon ka yahova siyyon parvat par aur yarooshalem men apanee praja ke puraniyon ke samhane pratap ke sath rajy karega..
he yahova, too mera parameshvar haai maain tujhe sarahoonga, maain tere nam ka dhanyavad karoonga kyonki too ne ashcharyakarma kiae haai, too ne praacheenakal se pooree sachchai ke sath yuaktaiyan kee haain.
too ne nagar ko deeh, aur us gaddhvale nagar ko khndhar kar dala haai too ne paradeshaiyon kee rajapuree ko aeesa ujada ki vah nagar naheen raha vah fir kabhee basaya n jaaega.
is karan balavant rajy ke log teree maahima karenge bhyankar anyajatiyon ke nagaron men tera bhy mana jaaega.
kyonaki too sankatt men deenon ke liye gaddh, aur jab bhyanak logon ka jhonka bheet par bauchhar ke saman hota tha, tab too daridraen ke liye unakee shara, aur tapan men chhaya ka sthan hua.
jaaise nirjal desh men badal kee chhaya se tapan ttndee hotee haai veaise hee too paradeshaiyon ka kolahal aur kroor logon ko jayajayakar band karata haai..
aur jo parda sab deshaen ke logon par pada haai, jo ghoonghatt sab anyajaatiyon par lattka hua haai, use vah isee parvat par nash karega.
vah mratyu ko sada ke liye nash karega, aur prabhu yahova sabhon ke mukh par se ansoo ponchh dalega, aur apanee praja kee namadharai saree prathvee par se door karega kyonki yahova ne aeesa kaha haai..
aur us samay yah kaha jaaega, dekho, hamara parameshvar yahee haai ham isee kee batt johate aae haai, ki vah hamara uddhar kare. yahova yahee haai ham usakee batt johate aae haain. ham us se uddhar pakar magan aur anaandait honge.
kyonaki is parvat par yahova ka hath sarvada bana rahega aur moab apane hee sthan men aeesa latada jaaega jaaisa ghoore men pual latada jata haai.
aur vah us men apane hath is prakar faailaaega, jaaise koi taairate huae faailaae parantu vah usake garva ko todega aur usakee chaturai ko nishfal kar dega.
aur usakee unchee unchee aushra draddh shaharapanahon ko vah jhukaaega aur neecha karega, varan boomi par girakar mittee men mila dega..
us samay yahooda desh men yah geet gaya jaega, hamara ek draddh nagar haai uddhar ka kam dene ke liye vah usakee shaharapanah aur gaddh ko niyukt karata haai.
faattkon ko kholo ki sachchai ka palan karanevalee aek dharmee jaati pravesh kare.
jisaka man tujh men dhaeeraj dhare huae haai, usakee too poorn shaaantai ke sath raksha karata haai, kyonki vah tujh par bhrosa rakhta haai.
yahova par sada bhrosa rak, kyonaki prabhu yahova sanatan chattan haai.
vah unche padavale ko jhuka deta, jo nagar unche par basa haai usako vah neeche kar deta. vah usako boomi par girakar mittee men mila deta haai.
dharmee ka marga sachchai haai too jo svayan sachchai haai, too dharmee kee aguvai karata haai.
he yahova, tere nyay ke marga men ham log teree batt johate aae haain tere nam ke smaran kee hamare praanon men lalasa banee rahatee haai.
rat ke samay maain jee se taree lalasa karata hoo, mera sampoorn man se yatn ke sath tujhe ddoonddhta haai. kyonki jab tere nyay ke kam prathvee par pragatt hote haai, tab jagat ke rahanevale dharma kee seekhte haain.
dushtt par chahe daya bhee kee jaae taubhee vah dharma ko n seekhega dharmarajy men bhee vah kuattlaita karega, aur yahova ko mahatmy use soojh n padega..
he yahova, tera hath baddha hua haai, par ve naheen dekhte. parantu ve janenge ki tujhe praja ke liye kaaisee jalan haai, aur lajaaenge.
tere baairee ag se bhsm honge. he yahova, too hamare liye shaantai ttharaaega, ham ne jo kuchh kiya haai use too hee ne hamare liye kiya haai.
he hamare parameshvar yahova, tere sivay aur svamee bhee ham par prabhuta karate the, parantu teree krapa se ham keval tere hee nam ka gunanuvad karenge.
ve mar gaae haai, fir kabhee jeeavit naheen honge unako mare bahut din hua, ve fir naheen uttne ke too ne unaka vichar karake unako aeesa nash kiya ki ve fir smaran men n aaenge.
parantu too ne jati ko baddhaya he yahova, too ne jaati ko baddhaya haai too ne apanee mahima dikhai haai aur us desh ke sab sivanon ko too ne baddhaya haai..
he yahova, du:kh men ve tujhe smaran karate the, jab too unhen tadna deta tha tab ve dabe svar se apane man kee bat tujh par pragatt karate the.
jaaise garbhvatee sree janane ke samay aeentttee aur peedon ke karan chilla utttee haai, ham log bhee, he yahova, tere samhane vaaise hee ho gaae haain.
ham bhee garbhvatee hua, ham bhee aeentte, ham ne mano vayu hee ko janm diya. ham ne desh ke liye koi uddhar ka kam naheen kiya, aur n jagat ke rahanevale utpann huae.
tere mare huae log jeevit honge, murde utt khde honge. he mittee men basanevalo, jagakar jayajayakar karo! kyonki teree os jyoti se utpann hotee haai, aur prathvee murdo ko lautta degee..
he mere logo, ao, apanee apanee kottree men pravesh karake kivadon ko band karo thodee der tak jab tak krodha shaant n ho tab tak apane ko chhpai rakho.
kyonaki dekho, yahova prathvee nivaasiyon ko adharma ka dand dene ke liye apane sthan se chala ata haai, aur prathvee apana koon pragatt karegee aur ghaat kiae huon ko aur aadhaik n chhpai rakhegee..
us samay yahova apanee kadee, badee, aur pod talavar se livyatan nam veg aur tteddhe chalanevale sarpa ko dand dega, aur jo ajagar samudra men rahata haai usako bhee ghaat karega..
us samay ek sundar dakh kee baree hogee, tum usaka yash gana!
mere man men jalajalahatt naheen haai. yadi koi bhanti bhanati ke katteele ped mujh se ladne ko khde karata, to maain un par panv baddhakar unako pooree reeti se bhsm kar deta.
va mere sath mel karane ko ve meree sharan le, ve mere sath mel kar len..
bhavishy men yakoob jad pakadega, aur israael foola-falega, aur usake falon se jagat bhr jaaega..
kya us ne use mara jaaisa us ne usake maranevalon ko mara tha? kya vah ghaat kiya gaya jaaise usake ghaat kiae huae ghaat hue?
jab too ne use nikala, tab socha-vichar kar usako du:kh diya : use ne puravai ke din usako prachand vayu se uda diya haai.
is se yakoob ke adharma ka praayaashchait kiya jaaega aur usake pap ke door hone ka pratifal yah hoga ki ve vedee ke sab patthron ko choona banane ke patthron ke saman chakanachoor karenge, aur ashora aur soorya kee praatimaaen fir khdee n rahengee.
kyonaki gaddhvala nagar nirjan hua haai, vah chhodee hui bastee ke saman nirjan aur jangal ho gaya haai vahan bachhde charenge aur vaheen baaittenge, aur pedon kee daaliyon kee faunagee ko kho lenge.
jab usakee shaakhaaen sookh jaaen tab todee jaaengee aur striayan akar unako todkar jala dengee. kyonki ye log nirbuaddh ihaain isaliye unaka karta un par daya n karega, aur unaka rachanevala un par anugrah n karega..
us samay yahova mahanad se lekar misr ke nale tak apane ann ko fattkega, aur he israealiyon tum ek ek karake ikatthe kiae jaoge.
us samay bada naraasinga foonka jaega, aur jo ashshoor desh men nash ho rahe the aur jo misr desh men barabas basaae huae the ve yarooshalem men akar pavitra parvat par yahova ko dandvata karenge..
ghamand ke mukutt par haya! jo aepraaim ke matavalon ka haai, aur unakee bhdkeelee sundarata par jo murjhanevala fool haai, jo ati upaja tarai ke sire par dakhmadha se matavalon kee haai.
dekho, prabhu ke pas aek balavant aur samarthee haai jo ole kee vashara va ujadnevalee andhaee ya baddh kee prachand dhaar kee nai haai vah usako kattorata se boomi par gira dega.
aur unakee bhdkeelee sundarata ka murjhanevala fool jo aati upaja tarai ke sire par haai, vah graeeshmakal se pahile pake anjeer ke saman hoga, jise dekhnevala dekhte hee hath men le aur nigal jaae..
us samay senaon ka yahova svayan apanee praja ke bache huon ke liye sundar aur pratapee mukutt ttharega
aur jo nyay karane ko baaittte haain unake liye nyay karanevalee atma aur jo chaddhai karate huae shatrauon ko nagar ke faattk se hatta dete haai, unake liye vah bal ttharega..
ye bhee dakhmadha ke karan dgamagate aur maadira se ladkhdate haain yajak aur nabee bhee madira ke karan dgamagate haai, dakhmadha ne unako bhula diya haai, ve madira ke karan ladkhdate aur darshan pate huae bhttke jate, aur nyay men bool karate haain.
kyonaki sab bhojan asan vaman aur mal se bhre haai, koi shuuddh sthan naheen bacha..
vah kisako gyaan sikhaaega, aur kisako apane samachar ka arth samajhaaega? kya unako jo doodha chhudaae huae aur stan se alagaae huae haain? kyonki agyaa par agyaa, agyaa par agyaa,
niyam par niyam, niyam par niyam thoda yaha, thoda vahan..
vah to in logon se paradeshaee hontton aur videshaee bhashaavalon ke dara baten karega
jin se us ne kaha, vishraam isee se milega isee ke dara thke huae ko vishraam do parantu unhon ne sunana n chaha.
isaliye yahova ka vachan unake pas agyaa par agyaa, agyaa par agyaa, niyam par niyam, niyam par niyam haai, thoda yaha, thoda vaha, jis se ve ttokar khakar chitt giren aur ghaayal ho jaae, aur fande men fansakar pakade jaaen..
is karan he ttttha karanevalo, yarooshalemavasee praja ke hakimo, yahova ka vachan suno!
tum ne kaha haai ki ham ne mratyu se vacha bandhaee aur adhaelok se pratigyaa karai haai is karan vipaati jab baddh kee nai baddh aae tab hamare pas n aaegee kyonaki ham ne joott kee sharan lee aur mithya kee ad men chhpai huae haain.
isaliye prabhu yahova yon kahata haai, dekho, maain ne siyyon men nev ka patthr rakha haai, aek parakha hua patthr, kone ka anamol aur aati draddh nev ke yogy patthra: aur jo koi vishvas rakhe vah utavalee n karega.
aur maain nyay kee doree aur dharma ko sahul ttharaunga aur tumhara joott ka sharansthan olon se bah jaaega, aur tumhare chhpaine ka sthan jal se oob jaaega.
tab jo vacha tum ne mratyu se bandhaee haai vah toott jaaegee, aur jo pratigyaa tum ne adhaelok se karai vah n ttharegee jab vipaati baddh kee nai baddh aa, tab tum us men oob hee jaoge.
jab jab vah baddh aa, tab tab vah tum ko le jaaegee vah praati din varan rat din baddha karengee aur is samachar ka sunana hee vyakul hone ka karan hoga.
kyonaki yahova aeesa utt khda hoga jaaisa vah parajeem nam parvat par khda hua aur jaaisa gibon kee tarai men us ne krodha dikhaya tha vah ab fir krodha dikhaaega, jis se vah apana kam kare, jo achambhiat kam haai, aur vah karya kare jo anokha haai.
isaliye ab tum ttttha mat karo, naheen to tumhare bandhan kase jaaenge kyonki maain ne senaon ke prabhu yahova se yah suna haai ki sare desh ka satyanash ttana gaya haai..
kan lagakar meree suno, dhyan dharakar mera vachan suno.
kya hal jotanevala beej bone ke liye lagatar jotata rahata haai? kya vah sada dharatee ko cheerata aur hengata rahata haai?
kya vah usako chauras karake saunfa ko naheen chhtairata, jeere ko naheen bakherata aur gehoon ko panti panati karake aur jab ko usake nij sthan par, aur kattyai gehoon ko khet kee chhor par naheen bota?
kyonaki usaka parameshvar usako tteek tteek kam karana sikhlata aur batalata haai..
danvane kee gadee se to saunfa dai naheen jatee, aur gadee ka pahiya jeere ke upar naheen chalaya jata parantu saunfa chhdee se, aur jeera sontten se jhada jata haai.
rottee ke ann par dayen kee jatee haai, parantu koi usako sada danvata naheen rahata aur n gadee ke paahiye n ghaede us par chalata haai, vah use choor choor naheen karata.
yah bhee senaon ke yahova kee or se niyukt hua haai, vah adabhut yuaktaivala aur mahabuddhmaian haai..
hay, areeael, areeael, hay us nagar par jis men daud chhavanee kiae huae raha! varsha par varsha jadte jao, utsav ke parva apane apane samay par manate jao.
taubhee maain to areeael ko saketee men daloonga, vahan rona peettna rahega, aur vah meree draashtti men sachamuch areeael sa ttharega.
aur maain charon or tere virooddh chhavanee karake tujhe kotton se ghor loonga, aur tere virooddh gaddh bhee banaunga.
tab too girakar boomi men dala jaaega, aur dhool par se bolega, aur teree bat boomi se dhaeemee dhaeemee sunai degee tera bol boomi par se praet ka sa hoga, aur too dhool se gunagunakar bolega..
aur senaon ka yahova achanak badal garajata, boomi ko kampata, aur mahadhvani karata, bavandr aur andhaee chalata, aur nash karanevalee agnai bhdkata hua usake pas aaega.
aur jaatiyon kee saree bheed jo areeael se yuddh karegee, or jitane log usake aur usake gaddh ke virooddh ladenge aur usako saketee men dalenge, ve sab rat ke dekhe huae svapn ke saman ttharenge.
aur jaaisa koi bookha svapan men to dekhta haai ki vah kha raha haai, parantu jagakar dekhta haai ki usaka pett bookha hee haai, va koi pyasa svapan men dekhen kee vah pee raha haai, parantu jagakar dekhta haai ki usaka gala sookha jata haai aur vah pyasa mar raha haai vaaisee hee un sab jatiyon kee bheed kee dasha hogee jo siyyon parvat se yuddh karengee..
tthar jao aur chaakit hoo! ve matavale to haai, parantu dakhmadha se nahee, ve dgamagate to haai, parantu maadira peene se naheen!
yahova ne tum ko bharee neend men dal diya haai aur us ne tumharee nabeeroopee ankhon ko band kar diya haai aur tumhare dashareeroopee siron par parda dala haai.
isaliye sare darshan tumhare liye aek lapettee aur muhar kee hui pustak kee baton ke saman haai, jise koi paddhe-alikhe manushy ko yah kahakar de, ise paddh, aur vah kahe, maain naheen paddh sakata kyonki is par muhar kee hui haai.
tab vahee pustak anapaddhe ko yah kahakar dee jaa, ise paddh, aur vah kahe, maain to anapaddh hoon..
aur prabhu ne kaha, ye log jo munh se mera adar karate huae sameep ate parantu apana man mujh se door rakhte haai, aur jo keval manushyon kee agyaa sun sunakar mera bhy manate haain.
is karan sun, maain inake sath adabhut kam varan ati adabhut aur achambhe ka kam karoonga tab inake buaddhmaianon kee buddh inashtt hogee, aur inake praveenon kee praveenta jatee rahegee..
hay un par jo apanee yuaktai ko yahova se chhpaiane ka bada yatn karate, aur apane kam andhore men karake kahate haai, ham ko kaun dekhta haai? ham ko kaun janata haai?
tumharee kaaisee ulattee samajh haai! kya kumhar mittee ke tuly gina jaaega? kya banai hui vastu apane kartta ke vishay kahe ki us ne mujhe naheen banaya, va rachee hui vastu apane rachanevale ke vishay kahe, ki vah kuchh samajh naheen rakhta?
kya ab thode hee dinon ke beetane par labanon fir faladai baree n ban jaaega, aur faladai baree jangal n ginee jaaegee?
us samay bahire pustak kee baten sunane legenge, aur andho jinhen ab kuchh naheen soojhta, ve dekhne legenge.
namra log yahova ke karan fir anaandait honge, aur daridra manushy israael ke pavitra ke karan magan honge.
kyonaki upadravee fir n rahenge aur ttttha karanevalon ka ant hoga, aur jo anarth karane ke liye jagate rahate haai, jo manushyon ko vachan men fansate haai,
is karan ibraaheem ka chhudanevala yahova, yakoob ke gharane ke vishay yon kahata haai, yakoob ko fir lajjait hona n padega, usaka mukh fir neecha n hoga.
kyonaki jab usake santan mera kam dekhenge, jo maain unake beech men karoonga, tab ve mere nam ko paavitra manenge, aur israael ke parameshvar ko aati bhy manenge.
us samay jinaka man bhttka ho ve buddh ipraapt karenge, aur jo kudkudate haain vah shaiksha grahan karenge..
amos ke putra yashaayah ka vachan, jo us ne yahooda aur yarooshalem ke vishay men darshan men paya..
ant ke dinon men aeesa hoga ki yahova ke bhvan ka parvat sab pahadon par draddh kiya jaaega, aur sab pahaadiyon se aadhaik uncha kiya jaaega aur har jati ke lage dhaara kee nai usakee or chalengen.
aur bahut deshaen ke lage aaenge, aur apas men kahenge: ao, ham yahova ke parvat par chaddhkar, yakoob ke parameshvar ke bhvan men jaaen tab vah hamako apane marga sikhaaega, aur ham usake pathon par chalenge. kyonaki yahova kee vyavastha siyyon se, aur usaka vachan yarooshalem se nikalega.
vah jaati jati ka nyay karega, aur desh desh ke logon ke jhgadon ko mittaaega aur ve apanee talavaren peettkar hal ke faal aur apane bhalon ko hansiya banaaenge tab aek jati doosaree jaati ke virooddh fir talavar n chalaaegee, n log bhvishy men yuddh kee vidha seekhenge..
he yakoob ke gharane, a, ham yahova ke prakash men chalen..
too ne apanee praja yakoob ke gharane ko tyag diya haai, kyonki ve poorviyon ke vyavahar par tan man se chalate aur palishtaiyon kee nai ttona karate haai, aur paradeshaiyon ke sath hath milate haain.
unaka desh chandee aur sone se bhrapoor haai, aur unake rath anaginit haain.
unaka desh mooraton se bhra haai ve apane hathon kee banai hui vastuon ko jinhen unahon ne apanee ungaliyon se sanvara haai, dandvata karate haain.
is se manushy jhukate, aur bade manushy pranam karate haai, is karan unako kshama n kara!
yahova ke bhy ke karan aur usake pratap ke mare chattan men ghaus ja, aur mittee men chhpai ja.
kyonaki adaamiyon kee ghamand bhree ankhen neechee kee jaaengee aur manushyon ka ghamand door kiya jaaega aur us din keval yahova hee unche par virajaman rahega..
aur labanon ke sab devadaron par jo unche aur baden haain
basan ke sab banjavrakshaen para aur sab unche pahadon aur sab unchee pahadiyon para
sab unche gummatton aur sab draddh shaharapanahon para
tashareesh ke sab jahajon aur sab sundar chitrakaree par vah din ata haai.
aur manushy ka garva mittaya jaaega, aur manushyon ka ghamand neecha kiya jaaega aur us din keval yahova hee unche par virajaman rahega.
aur mooraten sab kee sab nashtt ho jaaengee.
aur jab yahova prathvee ke kaampait karane ke liye uttega, tab usake bhy ke karan aur usake pratap ke mare log chattanon kee guufaaon aur boomi ke bilon men ja ghausenge..
us din log apanee chandee-sone kee mooraton ko jinhen unhon ne dandvata karane ke liye banaya tha, chhchoondaron aur chamageedadon ke age faenkenge,
aur jab yahova prathvee ko kaampait karane ke liye uttega tab ve usake bhy ke karan aur usake pratap ke mare chattanon kee dararon or pahaadiyon ke chhedon men ghausenge.
so tum manushy se pare raho jisakee shvas usake nathnon men haai, kyonki usaka mooly haai hee kya?
yahova kee yah vanee haai, hay un balava karanevale ladkon par jo yuaktai to karate parantu meree or se naheen vacha to bandhate parantu mere atma ke sikhaye naheen aur is prakar pap par pap baddhate haain.
ve mujh se bin poochhe misr ko jate haain ki firaun kee raksha men rahe aur misr kee chhaya men sharan len.
isaliye firaun ka sharansthan tumharee lajja ka, aur misr kee chhaya men sharan lena tumharee ninda ka karan hoga.
usake haakim soan men aae to haain aur usake doot ab hanes men pahunche haain.
daakkhian desh ke pashuuon ke vishay bharee vachana. ve apanee dhan sampati ko javan gadahon kee peett par, aur apane khjanon ko untton ke koobadon par lade hua, sankatt aur saketee ke desh men hokar, jahan sinh aur sinhanee, nag aur udnevale tej vishadhar sarpa rahate haai, un logon ke pas ja rahe haain jin se unako labh n hoga.
kyonaki misr kee sahayata vyarth aur nikammee haai, is karan maain ne usako baaittee rahanevalee rahab kaha haai..
ab akar isako unake samhane patthr par khod, aur pustak men lik, ki vah bhvishy ke liye varan sada ke liye sakshaee banee rahe.
kyonaki ve balava karanevale log aur joott bolanevale ladke haain jo yahova kee shaiksha ko sunana naheen chahate.
ve daashairyon se kahate haai, dasharee mat bano aur naabiyon se kahate haai, hamare liye tteek naboovat mat karo ham se chikanee chupadee baten bolo, dhaekha denevalee naboovat karo.
marga se mudo, path se hatto, aur israael ke pavitra ko hamare samhane se door karo.
is karan israael ka paavitra yon kahata haai, tum log jo mere is vachan ko nikamma janate aur andhor aur kuattlaita par bhrosa karake unheen par ttek lagate ho
is karan yah adharma tumhare liye unchee bheet ka tootta hua bhag hoga jo fattkar girane par ho, aur vah achanak pal bhr men toottkar gir padega,
aur kumhar ke bartan kee nai foottkar aeesa chakanachoor hoga ki usake ttukadon ka aek tteekara bhee n milega jis se angettee men se ag lee jaae va haud men se jal nikala jaae..
prabhu yahova, israael ka paavitra yon kahata haai, lautt ane aur shaant rahane men tumhara uddhar haai shaant rahate aur bhrosa rakhne men tumharee veerata haai. parantu tum ne aeesa naheen kiya,
tum ne kaha, nahee, ham to ghaedon par chaddhkar bhagenge, isaaliye tum bhagoge aur yah bhee kaha ki ham tej savaree par chalenge, so tumhara peechha karanevale us se bhee tej honge.
aek hee kee dhamakee se aek hajar bhagenge, aur panch kee dhamakee se tum aeesa bhagoge ki ant men tum pahad kee chottee ke dnde va tteele ke upar kee dhvaja ke saman rah jaoge jo chinh ke liye gade jate haain.
taubhee yahova isaaliye vilamb karata haai ki tum par anugrah kare, aur isaliye unche uttega ki tum par daya kare. kyonki yahova nyayee parameshvar haai kya hee dhany haain ve jo us par asha lagaae rahate haain..
he siyyon ke logon tum yarooshalem men base raho tum fir kabhee n rooge, vah tumharee dohai sunate hee tum par nishchay anugrah karega: vah sunate hee tumharee manega.
aur chahe prabhu tumhen vipaati kee rottee aur du:kh ka jal bhee de, taubhee tumhare upadeshak fir n chhpaie, aur tum apanee ankhon se apane upadeshakon ko dekhte rahoge.
tab tum vah chandee jis se tumharee khudee hui mootiayan maddhee haai, aur vah sona jis se tumharee ddhlee hui mootiayan abooshait haai, ashuuddh karoge. tum unako maaile kuchaaile vasr kee nain faenk doge aur kahoge, door ho.
aur vah tumhare liye jal barasaaega ki tum khet men beej bo sako, aur boomi kee upaj bhee uttm aur bahutayat se hogee. us samay tumhare janavaron ko lambee-chaudee charai milegee.
aur baail aur gadahe jo tumharee khetee ke kam men aaenge, ve soop aur daliya se fattka hua svaadishtt chara khaaenge.
aur us mahasanhar ke samay jab gummatt gir padenge, sab unche unche pahadon aur pahadiyon par naaliyan aur sote paae jaaenge.
us samay yahova apanee praja ke logon ka ghaav bandhoga aur unakee chott changa karega tab chandrama ka prakash soorya ka sa, aur soorya ka prakash sataguna hoga, arthata attvare bhr ka prakash ek din men hoga..
dekho, yahova door se chala ata haai, usaka prakop bhdk utta haai, aur dhooaen ka badal utt raha haai usake hontt krodha se bhre huae aur usakee jeebh bhsm karanevalee ag ke saman haai.
usakee sans aeesee umandnevalee nadee ke saman haai jo gale tak pahunchatee haai vah sab jaatiyon ko nash ke soop se fattkega, aur desh desh ke logon ko bhttkane ke liye unake jabhdon men lagam lagaega..
tab tum paavitra parva kee rat ka sa geet gaoge, aur jaaisa log yahova ke parvat kee or us se milane ko, jo israael kee chattan haai, bansulee bajate huae jate haai, vaaise hee tumhare man men bhee anand hoga.
aur yahova apanee pratapeevanee sunaaega, aur apana krodha bhdkata aur ag kee lau se bhsm karata hua, aur prachand andhaee aur ati vashara aur olon ke sath apana bhujabal dikhaaega.
ashshoor yahova ke shabd kee shaktai se nash ho jaaega, vah use sontte se marega.
aur jab jab yahova usako dand dega, tab tab sath hee dfa aur veena bajengee aur vah hath baddhakar usako lagatar marata rahega.
bahut kal se topet taaiyar kiya gaya haai, vah raja kee ke liye ttharaya gaya haai, vah lamba chauda aur gahira bhee banaya gaya haai, vahan kee chita men ag aur bahut see lakadee haain yahova kee sans jalatee hui gandhak kee dhaara kee nain usako sulagaaegee..
hay un par jo sahayata pane ke liye misr ko jate haain aur ghaedon ka asara karate haain jo rathon par bhrosa rakhte kyonki ve bahut haai, aur savaron par, kyonaki ve ati balavan haai, par israael ke paavitra kee or draashtti naheen karate aur n yahova kee khoj karate haain!
