maain yahova ke karan aati anaandait hounga, mera praan parameshvar ke karan magan rahega kyonaki us ne mujhe uddhar ke vasr paahinaa, aur dharma kee char aeese oddha dee haai jaaise doolha foolon kee mala se apane apako sajata aur dualhain apane gahanon se apana singar karatee haai.
kyonaki jaaise boomi apanee upaj ko ugatee, aur baree men jo kuchh boya jata haai usako vah upajatee haai, vaaise hee prabhu yahova sab jaatiyon ke samhane dhaaarmikata aur dhanyavad ko baddhaaega..
siyyon ke nimitt maain chup n rahoonga, aur yarooshalem ke nimitt maain chaain n loonga, jab tak ki usakee dhaaarmikata prakash kee nain aur usaka uddhar jalate huae paleete ke saman dikhai n de.
jab anyajatiyan tera dharma aur sab raja teree maahima dekhenge aur tera aek naya nam rakha jaaega jo yahova ke mukh se nikalega.
too yahova ke hath men aek shaebhayaman mukutt aur apane pameshvar kee hathelee men rajamukutt ttharegee.
too fir tyagee hui n kahalaaegee, aur teree boomi fir ujadee hui n kahalaaegee parantu too hepseeba aur teree boomi byoola kahalaaegee kyonki yahova tujh se prasann haai, aur teree boomi suhagan hogee.
he yarooshalem, maain ne teree shaharapanah par paharooae baaittaae haain ve dina-rat kabhee chup n rahenge. he yahova ko smaran karanevalo, chup n raho,
aur, jab tak vah yarooshalem ko sthiar karake usakee prashansa prathvee par n faaila de, tab tak use bhee chaain n lene do.
yahova ne apane daahine hath kee aur apanee balavant bhuja kee shapath khai haai: nishchay maain bhavishy men tera ann ab fir tere shatrauon ko khane ke liye n doonga, aur paradeashaiyon ke putra tera naya dakhmadha jisake liye too ne paarishram kiya haai, naheen peene paaenge
keval ve hee, jinhon ne use khtte men rakha ho, us se khakar yahova kee stuati karenge, aur jinhon ne dakhmadha bhndaron men rakha ho, ve hee use mere paavitrasthan ke anganon men peene paaenge..
jao, faattkon men se nikal jao, praja ke liye marga sudhaaro rajamarga sudhaarakar uncha karo, us men ke patthr been beenakar faenk do, desh desh ke logon ke liye jhnda khda karo.
dekho, yahova ne prathvaiee kee chhor tak is agyaa ka prachar kiya haai: siyyon kee bettee se kaho, dek, tera uddharakarta ata haai, dek, jo majadooree usako denee haai vah usake pas haai aur usaka kam usake samane haai.
aur log unako paavitra praja aur yahova ke chhudaae huae kahenge aur tera nam grahan kee hui arthata na-tyagee hui nagaree padega..
yah kaun haai jo aedom desh ke bostra nagar se baainjanee vasr pahine huae chala ata haai, jo aati balavan aur bhdkeela pahirava pahine huae joomata chala ata haai? yah maain hee hoo, jo dharma se bolata aur poora uddhar karane kee shaktai rakhta hoon.
tera pahirava kyon lal haai? aur kya karan haai ki tere vasr haud men dakh raundanevale ke saman haain?
maain ne to akele hee haud men dakhen raundee haai, aur desh ke logon men se kisee ne mera sath naheen diya ha, maain ne apane krodha men akar unhen raunda aur jalakar unhen latada unake lohoo ke chheentte mere vasren par pade haai, is se mera sara pahirava dhabbedar ho gaya haai.
kyonaki palatta lene ka din mere man men tha, aur meree chhudai hui praja ka varsha a pahuncha haai.
maain ne khoja, par koi sahayak n dikhai pada maain ne is se achambha bhee kiya ki koi sambhalanevala naheen tha tab maain ne apane hee bhujabal se uddhar kiya, aur meree jalajalahatt hee ne mujhe samhala.
ha, maain ne apane krodha men akar desh desh ke logon ko latada, apanee jalajalahatt se maain ne unhen matavala kar diya, aur unake lohoo ko boomi par baha diya..
jitana upakar yahova ne ham logon ka kiya arthata israael ke gharane par daya aur atyant karoona karake us ne ham se jitanee bhlai, ki us sab ke anusar maain yahova ke karoonamay kamon ka varnn aur usaka gunanuvad karoonga.
kyonaki us ne kaha, nisndeh ye meree praja ke log haai, aeese ladke haain jo dhaekha nadenge aur vah unaka uddharakarta ho gaya.
unake sare sankatt men us ne bhee kashtt uttaya, aur usake sammukh rahanevale doot ne unaka uddhar kiya praem aur komalata se us ne ap kee unako chhudaya us ne unhen uttaya aur praacheenakal se sada unhen liae fira.
taubhee unhon ne balava kiya aur usake paavitra atma ko kheadit kiya is karan vah palattkar unaka shatra ho gaya, aur svayan un se ladne laga.
tab usake logon ko unake praacheen din arthata moosa ke din smaran aa, ve kahane lage ki jo apanee bhedon ko unake charavahe samet samudra men se nikal laya vah kahan haai? jis ne unake beech apana pavitra atma dala, vah kahan haai?
jis ne apane pratapee bhujabal ko moosa ke dahine hath ke sath kar diya, jis ne unake samhane jal ko do bhag karake apana sada ka nam kar liya,
jo unako gaahire samudra men se le chala jaaisa ghaede ko jangal men vaaise hee unako bhee ttokar n lagee, vah kahan haai?
svarga se, jo tera pavitra aur maahimapoorn vasasthan haai, drashtti kara. teree jalan aur parakram kahan rahe? teree daya aur karoona mujh par se hatt gai haain.
nishchay too hamara pita haai, yadhyapi ibraaheem hamen naheen paahichanata, aur israael hamen grahan naheen karata taubhee, he yahova, too hamara pita aur hamara chhudanevala haai praacheenakal se yahee tera nam haai.
he yahova, too kyon ham ko apane margon se bhttka deta, aur hamare man aeese kattor karata haai ki ham tera bhy naheen manate? apane das, apane nij bhag ke gotraen ke nimitt lautt a.
teree pavitra praja to thode hee kal tak mere paavitrasthan kee aadhaikaree rahee hamare draehiyon ne use latad diya haai.
ham log to aeese ho gaae haai, mano too ne ham par kabhee prabhuta naheen kee, aur unake saman jo kabhee tere n kahalaae..
bhla ho ki too akash ko faadkar utar aae aur pahad tere samhane kanp utte.
jaaise ag jhad-jhnkhad ko jala detee va jal ko ubalatee haai, usee reeti se too apane shatrauon par apana nam aeesa pragatt kar ki jati jati ke log tere pratap se kanp utten!
jab too ne aeese bhyanak kam kiae jo hamaree asha se bhee baddhkar the, tab too utar aya, pahad tere pratap se kanp utte.
kyonaki praacheenakal hee se tujhe chhod koi aur aeesa parameshvar n to kabhee dekha gaya aur n kal se usakee charcha sunee gai jo apanee batt johanevalon ke liye kam kare.
ham to sab ke sab ashuuddh manushy ke se haai, aur hamare dharma ke kam sab ke sab maaile chithdon ke saman haain. ham sab ke sab patte kee nain murjha jate haai, aur hamare adharma ke kamon ne hamen vayu kee nain uda diya haai.
koi bhee tujh se sahayata lene ke liye chaukasee karata haai ki tujh se lipatta rahe kyonaki hamare adharma ke kamon ke karan too ne ham se apana munh chhpai liya haai, aur hamen hamaree buraiyon ke vash men chhod diya haai..
taubhee, he yahova, too hamar pita haai dek, ham to mittee haai, aur too hamara kumhar haai ham sab ke sab tere hath ke kam haain.
isaliye he yahova, atyant krodhait n ho, aur anantakal tak hamare adharma ko smaran n rakh. vichar karake dek, ham teree binatee karate haai, ham sab teree praja haain.
dek, tere paavitra nagar jangal ho gaa, siyyon sunasan ho gaya haai, yarooshalem ujad gaya haai.
hamara paavitra aur shaebhayaman maandair, jis men hamare poorvaj teree stuti karate the, ag se jalaya gaya, aur hamaree manabhavanee vastuaen sab nashtt ho gai haain.
he yahova, kya in baton ke hote bhee too apane ko roke rahega? kya too ham logon ko is atyant durdasha men rahane dega?
jo mujh ko poochhte bhee n the ve mere khojee haain jo mujhe ddoonddhte bhee n the unhon ne mujhe pa liya, aur jo jaati meree naheen kahalai thee, us se bhee maain kahata hoo, dek, maain upaasthiat hoon.
maain aek hatteelee jati ke logon kee or din bhr hath faailaae raha, jo apanee yuktaiyon ke anusar bure margon men chalate haain.
aeese lo, jo mere samhane hee bariyon men baali chaddha chaddhakar aur intton par dhoop jala jalakar, mujhe lagatar krodha dilate haain.
ye kabra ke beech baaittte aur chhpai huae sthanon men rat bitate jo sooar ka mans khate, aur gharaanait vastuon ka ras apane bartanon men rakhte
jo kahate haai, hatt ja, mere nikatt mat a, kyonaki maain tujh se paavitra hoon. ye meree nak men dhoonaen v us ag ke saman haain jo din bhr jalatee rahatee haai.
dekho, yah bat mere samhane likhee hui haai: maain chup n rahoonga, maain nishchay badala doonga varan tumhare aur tumhare purakhaon ke bhee adharma ke kamon ka badala tumharee god men bhr doonga.
kyonaki unhon ne pahadon par dhoop jalaya aur pahadiyon par meree ninda kee haai, isaliye maain yahova kahata hoo, ki, unake pichhle kamon ke badale ko maain inakee god men taulakar doonga..
yahova yon kahata haai, jis bhanati dakh ke kisee guchchhe men jab naya dakhmadha bhr ata haai, tab log kahate haai, use nash mat kar, kyonaki us men ashaeesh haai usee bhanti maain apane dason ke nimitt aeesa karoonga ki sabhon ko nash n karoonga.
maain yakoob men se aek vansha, aur yahooda men se apane parvaton ka aek vaaris utpann karoonga mere chune huae usake varis honge, aur mere das vahan nivas karenge.
meree praja jo mujhe ddoonddhtee haai, usakee bhend-bakaariyan to shaaron men charengee, aur usake gaya-baail akor nam tarai men vishraam karenge.
parantu tum jo yahova ko tyag dete aur mere paavitra parvat ko bool jate ho, jo bhagy devata ke liye menj par bhojan kee vastuaen sajate aur bhavee devee ke liye masala mila hua dakhmadha bhr dete ho
maain tumhen gin ginakar talavar ka kaur banaunga, aur tum sab ghaat hone ke liye jhukoge kyonaki, jab maain ne tumhen bulaya tum ne uttr n diya, jab maain bola, tab tum ne meree n sunee varan jo mujhe bura lagata haai vahee tum ne nit kiya, aur jis se maain aprasann hota hoo, usee ko tum ne apanaya..
dekho, mere das harsha ke mare jayajayakar karenge, parantu tum shaek se chillaoge aur khed ke mare hay hay, karoge.
mere chune huae log tumharee upama de dekar shaap denge, aur prabhu yahova tujh ko nash karega parantu apane dason ka doosara nam rakhega.
tab sare desh men jo koi apane ko dhany kahega vah sachche parameshvar ka nam lekar apane ko dhany kahega, aur jo koi desh men shapath khaae vah sachche parameshvar ke nam se shapath khaaega kyonaki pichhla kashtt door ho gaya aur vah meree ankhon se chhpai gaya haai..
kyonaki dekho, maain naya akash aur nai prathvee utpann karane par hoo, aur pahilee baten smaran n rahengee aur soch vichar men bhee n aaengee.
isaliye jo maain utpann karane par hoo, usake karan tum haashairt ho aur sada sarvada magan raho kyonaki dekho, maain yarooshalem ko magan aur usakee praja ko anandait banaunga.
maain ap yarooshalem ke karan magan, aur apanee praja ke hetu hashairt hoonga us men fir rone va chillane ka shabd n sunai padega.
us men fir n to thode din ka bachcha, aur n aeesa booddha jata rahega jis ne apanee ayu pooree n kee ho kyonki jo ladkapan men maranevala haai vah sau varsha ka hokar marega, parantu papee sau varsha ka hokar shraapit ttharega.
ve ghar banakar un men basenge ve dakh kee bariyan lagakar unaka fal khaaenge.
aeesa naheen hoga ki ve banaaen aur doosara base va ve lagaae, aur doosara khaae kyonki meree praja kee ayu vrakshaen kee see hogee, aur mere chune huae apane kamon ka poora labh uttaaenge.
unaka paarishram vyarth n hoga, n unake balak ghabarahatt ke liye utpann honge kyonaki ve yahova ke dhany logon ka vansh ttharenge, aur unake balabachche un se alag n honge.
bheadiya aur memna aek sang chara karenge, aur sinh baail kee nai boosa khaaega aur sarpa ka ahar mittee hee rahega. mere sare paavitra parvat par n to koi kisee ko du:kh dega aur n koi kisee kee haani karega, yahova ka yahee vachan haai..
yahova yon kahata haai, akash mera sinhasan aur prathvee mere charanon kee chaukee haai tum mere liye kaaisa bhvan banaoge, aur mere vishraam ka kaun sa sthan hoga?
yahova kee yah vanee haai, ye sab vastuaen mere hee hath kee banai hui haai, so ye sab meree hee haain. parantu maain usee kee or drashtti karoonga jo dee aur kheadit man ka ho, aur mera vachan sunakar thrathrata ho..
baail ka bali karanevala manushy ke mar dalanevale ke saman haai jo bhed ke chaddhanevala haai vah usake saman haai jo kutte ka gala kattta haai jo annabali chaddhata haai vah mano sooar ka lohoo chaddhanevale ke saman haai aur, jo loban jalata haai, vah usake saman haai jo moorat ko dhany kahata haai. in sabhon ne apana apana marga chun liya haai, aur ghainaunee vastuon se unake man prasann hate haain.
isaliye maain bhee unake liye du:kh kee baten nikaloonga, aur jin baton se ve drate haain unheen ko un par launga kyonaki jab maain ne unhen bulaya, tab koi n bola, aur jab maain ne un se baten kee, tab unhon ne meree n sunee parantu jo meree draashtti men bura tha vahee ve karate rahe, aur jis se maain aprasann hota tha usee ko unhon ne apanaya.. tum jo yahova ka vachan sunakar thrathrate ho yahova ka yah vachan suno:
tumhare bhai jo tum se baair rakhte aur mere nam ke nimitt tum ko alag kar dete haain unhon ne kaha haai, yahova kee maahima to baddhe, jis se ham tumhara anand dekhte paaen parantu unheen ko laajjait hona padega..
suno, nagar se kolahal kee dhoom, mandair se aek shabd, sunai deta haai! vah yahova ka shabd haai, vah apane shatrauon ko unakee karanee ka fal de raha haai!
usakee peedaen uttane se pahale hee us ne janma diya usako peedaen hone se paahile hee us se betta janma.
aeesee bat kis ne kabhee sunee? kis ne kabhee aeesee baten dekhee? kya desh aek hee din men utpann ho sakata haai? kya aek jati kshan matra men hee utpann ho sakatee haai? kyonki siyyon kee peedaaen uttee hee theen ki us se santan utpann ho gaae.
yahova kahata haai, kya maain use janmane ke samay tak pahunchakar n janmaun? tera parameshvar kahata haai, maain jo garbh deta hoon kya maain kokh band karoon?
he yarooshalem se sab praem rakhnevalo, usake sath anand karo aur usake karan magan ho he usake vishay sab vilap karanevalo usake sath haashairt ho!
jis se tum usake shaaantairoopee stan se doodha pee peekar trapt ho aur doodha peekar usakee mahima kee bahutayat se atyant sukhee ho..
kyonaki yahova yon kahata haai, dekho, maain usakee or shaantai ko nadee kee nai, aur anyajaatiyon ke dhan ko nadee kee baddh ke saman baha doonga aur tum us se peeoge, tum usakee god men uttaae jaoge aur usake ghauttnon par kudaae jaoge.
jis prakar mata apane putra ko shaantai detee haai, vaais hee maain bhee tumhen shaaantai dunga tum ko yarooshalem hee men shaantai milegee.
tum yah dekhoge aur prafaullait hoge tumharee haddiyan ghaas kee nain haree bhree hongee aur yahova ka hath usake dason ke liye pragatt hoga, aur, usake shatrauon ke upar usaka krodha bhdkega..
kyonaki dekho, yahova ag ke sath aaega, aur usake rath bavandr ke saman honge, jis se vah apane krodha ko jalajalahatt ke sath aur apanee chitaunee ko bhsm karanevalee ag kee lapatt men pragatt kare.
kyonaki yahova sab praaanaiyon ka nyay ag se aur apanee talavar se karega aur yahova ke mare huae bahut honge..
jo log apane ko isaliye paavitra aur shuuddh karate haain ki bariyon men jaaen aur kisee ke peechhe khde hokar sooar va choohe ka mans aur aur gharaanait vastuen khate haai, ve aek hee sang nash ho jaaenge, yahova kee yahee vanee haai..
aur maain un se aek chinh pragatt karoonga aur unake bache huon ko maain un anyajaatiyon ke pas bhejoonga jinhon ne n to mera samachar suna haai aur n meree maahima dekhee haai, arthata tashareeashaiyon aur dhanudhararee pooliyon aur loodiyon ke pas, aur tabaaliyon aur yoonaaniyon aur door deepavasiyon ke pas bhee bhej doonga aur ve anyajaatiyon men meree mahima ka varnn karenge.
aur jaaise israaelee log annabaali ko shuuddh patra men dharakar yahova ke bhvan men le ate haai, vaaise hee ve tumhare sab bhaiyon ko ghaedo, ratho, palaayie, khchcharon aur sadniyon par chaddha chaddhakar mere paavitra parvat yarooshalem par yahova kee bhentt ke liye le aaenge, yahova ka yahee vachan haai.
aur un men se maain kitane logon ko yajak aur leveey pad ke liye bhee chun loonga..
kyeanki jis prakar naya akash aur nai prathvee, jo maain banane par hoo, mere sammukh banee rahegee, usee prakar tumhara vansh aur tumhara nam bhee bana rahega yahova kee yahee vanee haai.
fir aeesa hoga ki aek naye chand se doosare naye chand ke din tak aur aek vishraam din se doosare vishraam din tak samast praanee mere samhane dandvata karane ko aya karenge yahova ka yahee vachan haai..
tab ve nikalakar un logon kee lothon par jinhon ne mujh se balava kiya draashtti dalenge kyonaki un men pade huae keede kabhee n marenge, unakee as kabhee n bujhegee, aur sare manushyon ko un se atyant gharana hogee..
jis varsha ujjaiyyah raja mara, maain ne prabhu ko bahut hee unche sinhasan par virajaman dekha aur usake vasr ke ghor se maandair bhr gaya.
us se unche par sarap dikhai die unake chh: chh: pankh the do pankhon se ve apane munh ko ddhanpe the aur do se apane panvon ko, aur do se ud rahe the.
aur ve aek doosare se pukar pukarakar kah rahe the: senaon ka yahova paavitra, paavitra, paavitra haai saree prathvee usake tej se bhrapoor haai.
aur pukaranevale ke shabd se devaddhiyon kee neven dol uttee, aur bhvan dhoonae se bhr gaya.
tab maain ne kaha, haya! haya! maain nash hooa kyonaki maain ashuuddh honttvala manushy hoo, aur ashuuddh honttvale manushyon ke beech men rahata hoon kyonaki maain ne senaon ke yahova maharajadhairaj ko apanee ankhon se dekha haai!
aur us ne us se mere munh ko chookar kaha, dek, is ne tere hontton ko choo liya haai, isaaliy tera adharma door ho gaya aur tere pap kshama ho gaae.
tab maain ne prabhu ka yah vachan suna, maain kis ko bhenjoo, aur hamaree or se kaun jaaega? tab maain ne kaha, maain yahan hoon! mujhe bhej
us ne kaha, ja, aur in logon se kah, sunate hee raho, parantu n samajho dekhte hee raho, parantu n boojho.
too in logon ke man ko motte aur unake kanon ko bharee kar, aur unakee ankhon ko band kara aeesa n ho ki ve ankhon se dekhe, aur kanon se sune, aur man se boojhe, aur man firaven aur change ho jaaen.
tab maain ne poochha, he prabhu kab taka? us ne kaha, jab tak nagar n ujade aur un men koi rah n jaa, aur gharon men koi manushy n rah jaa, aur desh ujad aur sunasan ho jaa,
aur yahova manushyon ko us men se door kar de, aur desh ke bahut se sthan nirjan ho jaaen.
chahe usake nivaasiyon ka dasavan ansh bhee rah jaa, taubhee vah nash kiya jaaega, paranatu jaaise chhotte va bade banjavraksha ko katt dalane par bhee usaka toontt bana rahata haai, vaaise hee pavitra vansh usaka toontt ttharega..
yahooda ka raja ahaj jo yotam ka putra aur ujjaiyyah ka pota tha, usake dinon men aram ke raja raseen aur israael ke raja ramalyah ke putra pekah ne yarooshalem se ladne ke liye chaddhai kee, parantu yuddh karake un se kuchh ban n pada
jab daud ke gharane ko yah samachar mila ki araamiyon ne aepraaiamiyon se saandhi kee haai, tab usaka aur praja ka bhee man aeesa kanp utta jaaise van ke vraksha vayu chalane se kanp jate haain.
tab yahova ne yashaayah se kaha, apane putra shaaryashoob ko lekar dhaeabiyon ke khet kee sadk se uparalee pokhre kee nalee ke sire par ahaj se bhentt karane ke liye ja,
aur us se kah, savadhaan aur shaant ho aur un donon dhoonan nikalatee lukattyaien se arthata raseen aur araamiyon ke bhdke huae kop se, aur ramalyah ke putra se mat dr, aur n tera man kachcha ho.
kyanaki araamiyon aur ramalyah ke putra samet aepraaimiyon ne yah kahakar tere virooddh buree yuktai ttanee haai ki ao,
ham yahooda par chaddhai karake usako ghabara de, aur usako apane vash men lakar tabel ke putra ko raja niyukt kar den.
isaliye prabhu yahova ne yah kaha haai ki yah yuktai n to safal hogee aur n pooree.
kyeanki aram ka sir damishk, or damishk ka sir raseen haai. fir aepraaim ka sir shaemaron aur shaemaron ka sir ramalyah ka putra haai.
paainsatt varsha ke bheetar aepraaim ka bal itana toott jaaega ki vah jati banee n rahegee. yadi tum log is bat kee prateeati n karo to nishchay tum sthiar n rahoge..
fir yahova ne ahaj se kaha,
ahaj ne kaha, maain naheen mangane ka, aur maain yahova kee pareeksha naheen karoonga.
tab us ne kaha, he daud ke gharane suno! kya tum manushyon ko ukata dena chhottee bat samajhkar ab mere parameshvar ko bhee ukata doge?
is karan prabhu ap hee tum ko aek chinh dega. suno, aek kumaree garbhvatee hogee aur putra janegee, aur usaka nam immanooael rakhegee.
aur jab tak vah bure ko tyagana aur bhle ko grahan karana n jane tab tak vah makkhn aur madha khaaega.
kyonaki us se pahile ki vah ladka bure ko tyagana aur bhle ko grahan karana jane, vah desh jisake donon rajaon se too ghabara raha haai nirjan ho jaaega.
yahova tujh par, teree praja par aur tere pita ke gharane par aeese dinon ko le aaega ki jab se aepraaim yahooda se alag ho gaya, tab ve vaaise din kabhee naheen aae -- arthata ashshoor ke raja ke din ..
us samay yahova un makkhiayon ko jo misr kee nadiyon ke siron par rahatee haai, aur un madhaumaakkhiayon ko jo ashshoor desh men rahatee haai, seettee bajakar bulaega.
aur ve sab kee sab akar is desh ke pahadee nalon me, aur chattanon kee dararon me, aur sab bhttkattaiyon aur sab charaiyon par baaitt jaaengee..
usee samay prabhu mahanad ke paravale ashshoor ke rajaroopee bhade ke choore se sir aur panvon ke ronen moondega, us se daddhee bhee pooree mund jaegee..
us samay aeesa hoga ki manushy keval ek kalor aur do bhedon ko palega
aur ve itana doodha dengee ki vah makkhn khaya karega kyonaki jitane is desh men rah jaaenge vah sab makkhn aur madha khaya karenge..
us samay jin jin sthanen men hajar ttukade chandee kee hajar dakhlataen haai, un sab sthanen men katteele hee katteele ped honge.
un sabhon par katteele pedon ke dr ke mare koi n jaega, ve gaye baailon ke charane ke, aur bhed bakaariyon ke raundane ke liye honge..
fir yahova ne mujh se kaha, aek badee paattyai lekar us par sadhaaran aksharon se yah likh: mahesharalalhashabaj ke liye.
aur maain vishvasayogy purooshaen ko arthata uriyyah yajak aur jeberekyah ke putra jakaryah ko is bat kee sakshaee karoonga.
aur maain apanee patnee ke pas gaya, aur vah garbhvatee hui aur usake putra utpann hua. tab yahova ne mujh se kaha, usaka nam mahesharalalhashabaj rakh
kyonaki is se pahile ki vah ladka bapoo aur ma pukaran jane, daamishk aur shaemaron donon kee dhana-sampati loottkar ashshoor ka raja apane desh ko bhejega..
yahova ne fir mujh se doosaree bar kaha,
isaliye ki log shaeeloh ke dhaeere dhaeere bahanevale sote ko nikamma janate haai, aur raseen aur ramalyah ke putra ke sang aeka karake anand karate haai,
is karan sun, prabhu un par us prabal aur gaahire mahanad ko, arthata ashshoor ke raja ko usake sare pratap ke sath chaddha laaega aur vah unake sab nalon ko bhr dega aur sare kadadon se chhlakakar bahega
aur vah yahooda par bhee chaddh aaega, aur baddhte baddhte us par chaddhega aur gale tak pahunchega aur he immanuel, tera samast desh usake pankhon ke faailane se ddhnp jaaega..
he logo, halla karo to karo, parantu tumhara satyanash ho jaaega. he prathvee ke door door desh ke sab logon kan lagakar suno, apanee apanee kamar kaso to kaso, parantu tumhare ttukade ttukade kiae jaaenge apanee kamar kaso to kaso, parantu tumhara satyanash ho jaaega.
tum yuaktai karo to karo, parantu vah nishfal ho jaaegee, tum kuchh bhee kaho, parantu tumhara kaha hua ttharega nahee, kyonki parameshvar hamare sang haai..
kyonaki yahova draddhta ke sath mujh se bola aur in logon kee see chal chalane ko mujhe mana kiya,
aur kaha, jis bat ko yah log rajadraeh kahe, usako tum rajadraeh n kahana, aur jis bat se ve drate haain us se tum n drana aur n bhy khana.
senaon ke yahova hee ko paavitra janana usee ka dr manana, aur usee ka bhy rakhna.
aur vah sharansthan hoga, parantu israael ke dono gharanon ke liye ttokar ka patthr aur ttes kee chattan, aur yarooshalem ke nivaasiyon ke liye fanda aur jal hoga.
aur bahut se log ttokar khaaenge ve girenge aur chakanachoor honge ve fande men fasenge aur pakade jaaenge.
maain us yahova kee batt johata rahoonga jo apane munkh ko yakoob ke gharane se chhpaiaye haai, aur maain usee par asha lagaae rahoonga.
dek, maain aur jo ladke yahova ne mujhe saunpe haai, usee senaon ke yahova kee or se jo siyyon parvat par nivas kiae rahata haai israaeliyon ke liye chinh aur chamatkar haain.
jab log tum se kahen ki ojhaon aur ttonhon ke pas jakar poochho jo gunagunate aur fausafausate haai, tab tum yah kahana ki kya praja ko apane parameshvar hee ke pas jakar n poochhna chaahiye? kya jeevaton ke liye mudorn se poochhna chaahiye?
vyavastha aur chitaunee hee kee charcha kiya karo! yadi ve log is vachanon ke anusar n bolen to nishchay unake liye pau n fattegee
ve is desh men kleashait aur bookhe firate rahenge aur jab ve bookhe honge, tab ve krodha men akar apane raja aur apane parameshvar ko shaap denge, aur apana mukh upar akash kee or uttaaenge
tab ve prathvee kee or draashtti karenge parantu unhen saketee aur andhiayara arthata sankatt bhra andhakar hee dekh padega aur ve ghaer andhakar men ddhkel diae jaaenge..
taubhee sankatt-bhra andhakar jata rahega. pahile to us ne jabooloon aur naptalee ke deshaen ka apaman kiya, parantu antaim dinon men tal kee or yaradan ke par kee anyajatiyon ke galeel ko mahima dega.
jo log aandhiayare men chal rahe the unhon ne bada ujiyala dekha aur jo log ghaer andhakar se bhre huae mratyu ke desh men rahate the, un par jyoti chamakee.
too ne jaati ko baddhaya, too ne usako bahut anand diya ve tere samhane kattnee ke samay ka sa anand karate haai, aur aeese magan haain jaaise log loott banttne ke samay magan rahate haain.
kyonaki too ne usakee gardan par ke bharee jooae aur usake bahange ke bans, us par andhor karanevale kee lattee, in sabhon ko aeesa tod diya haai jese midhaaniyon ke din men kiya tha.
kyonaki yuddh men ladnevale sipaahiyon ke joote aur lohoo men lathde huae kapade sab ag ka kaur ho jaaenge.
kyeanki hamare liye aek balak utpann hua, hamen aek putra diya gaya haai aur prabhuta usake kandho par hogee, aur usaka nam adabhut yuaktai karanevala parakramee parameshvar, anantakal ka pita, aur shaantai ka rajakumar rakha jaaega.
usakee prabhuta sarvada baddhtee rahegee, aur usakee shaantai ka ant n hoga, isaliye vaa uisako daud kee rajagaeepar is samay se lekar sarvada ke liye nyay aur dharma ke dara sthiar kiae or sanbhale rahega. senaon ke yahova kee dhaun ke dara yah ho jaega..
aur saree praja ko, aepraaiamiyon aur shaemaronavasiyon ko maloom ho jaaega jo garva aur kattorata se bolate haain: intten to gir gai haai,
parantu ham gaddhen huae patthron se ghar banaaenge goolar ke vraksha to katt gaae haain parantu ham unakee santee devadaron se kam lenge.
is karan yahova un par raseen ke baairiyon ko prabal karega,
aur unake shatrauon ko arthata pahile aram ko aur tab palishtaiyon ko ubharega, aur ve munh kholakar israaeliyon ko nigal lenge. itane par bhee usaka krodha shaant naheen hua aur usaka hath ab tak baddha hua haai..
taubhee ye log apane maranevale kee or naheen fire aur n senaon ke yahova kee khoj karate haain.
is karan yahova israael men se sir aur poonchh ko, khjoor kee daliyon aur sarakande ko, aek hee din men katt dalega.
puraniya aur praatishttit puroosh to sir haai, aur joottee baten sikhanevala nabee poonchh haai
kyonaki jo in logon kee aguvai karate haain ve inako bhttka dete haai, aur jinakee aguvai hotee haai ve nash ho jate haain.
is karan prabhu n to inake javanon se prasann hoga, aur n inake anath balakon aur vidhavaon par daya karega kyonki har aek ke mukh se moorkhta kee baten nikalatee haain. itane par bhee usaka krodha shaant naheen hua aur usaka hath ab tak baddha hua haai..
kyonaki dushttta ag kee nai dhadhakatee haai, vah unttkattaron aur kantton ko bhsm karatee haai, varan vah ghane van kee jhaadiyon men ag lagatee haai aur vah dhauna men chakara chakarakar upar kee or utttee haai.
senaon ke yahova ke rosh ke mare yah desh jalaya gaya haai, aur ye log ag kee indhan ke saman haain ve apas men aek doosare se daya ka vyavahar naheen karate.
ve daahinee or se bhojanavastu chheenakar bhee bookhe rahate, aur bayen or se khakar bhee trapt naheen hote un men se pratyek manushy apanee apanee banhon ka mans khata haai,
manashsho aepraaim ko aur aepraaim manashsho ko khata haai, aur ve donon milakar yahooda ke virooddh haain itane par bhee usaka krodha shaant naheen hua, aur usaka hath ab tak baddha hua haai..
yahova yon kahata haai, he israaael ke gharane jo vachan yahova tum se kahata haai use suno.
anyajatiyon ko chal mat seekho, n unakee nai akash ke chinhon se vismait ho, isaaliye ki anyajaati log un se vismait hote haain.
log usako sone-chandee se sajate aur hathaide se keel ttonk ttonkakar duddh karate haain ki vah hila-dul n sake.
ve khradakar tad ke ped ke saman gol banai jatee haai, par bol naheen sakateen unhen uttaae firana padta haai, kyonki ve chal naheen sakateen. un se mat dro, kyonaki, n to ve kuchh bura kar sakatee haain aur n kuchh bhla.
he yahova, tere saman koi naheen haai too mahan haai, aur tera nam parakram men bada haai.
he sab jaatiyon ke raja, tujh se kaun n drega? kyonaki yah tere yogy haai anyajatiyon ke sare buddhimanon me, aur unake sare rajyon men tere saman koi naheen haai.
parantu ve pashu sareekhe nire moorkh haain moottairyon se kya shaikshaa? ve to katt hee haain !
pattar banai hui chandee tashash se lai jatee haai, aur ufaaj se sona. ve kareegar aur sunar ke hathon kee kareegaree haain unake paahirave neele aur baainjanee rang ke vasr haain un men jo kuchh haai vah nipun kareegaron kee kareegaree hee haai.
parantu yahova vastav men parameshvar haai jeeavit parameshvar aur sada ka raja vahee haai. usake prakop se prathvee kanpatee haai, aur jaati jati ke log usake krodha ko sah naheen sakate.
tum un se yah kahana, ye devata jinhon ne akash aur prathvee ko naheen banaya ve prathvee ke upar se aur akash ke neeche se nashtt ho jaaenge.
usee ne prathvee ko apanee samarth se banaya, us ne jagat ko apanee buaddhi se sthiar kiya, aur akash ko apanee praveenta se tan diya haai.
jab vah bolata haai tab akash men jal ka bada shabd hota haai, aur prathvee kee chhor se vah kuhare ko uttata haai. vah vashara ke liye bijalee chamakata, aur apane bhndar men se pavan chalata haai.
sab manushy pashu sareekhe gyaanarahit haain apanee khodee hui mooraton ke karan sab sunaron kee asha tootttee haai kyonaki unakee ddhalee hui mooraten joottee haai, aur un men sans hee naheen haai.
ve vyarth aur tttthe hee ke yogy haain jab unake dand ka samay aaega tab ve nash ho jaaengeen.
parantu yakoob ka nij bhag unake saman naheen haai, kyonaki vah to sab ka srajanahar haai, aur israaael usake nij bhag ka gotra haai senaon ka yahova usaka nam haai.
he ghore huae nagar kee rahanevalee, apanee gattree boomi par se utta !
mujh par hay ! mera ghaav changa hone ka naheen. fir maain ne socha, yah to rog hee haai, isaliye mujh ko ise sahana chahiye.
mera tamboo lootta gaya, aur sab raassaiyan toott gai haain mere ladkebale mere pas se chale gaa, aur naheen haain ab koi naheen raha jo mere tamboo ko tane aur meree kanaten khdee kare.
kyonaki charavahe pashu sareekhe haai, aur ve yahova ko naheen pukarate isee karan ve buddhi se naheen chalate, aur unakee sab bheden titara-abitar ho gai haain.
sun, aek shabd sunai deta haai ! dek, vah a raha haai ! uttar disha se bada hullad mach raha haai taaki yahooda ke nagaron ko ujadkar geedadon ka sthan bana de.
he yahova, maain jan gaya hoo, ki manushy ka marga usake vash men naheen haai, manushy chalata to he, parantu usake dg usake adhaeen naheen haain.
he yahova, meree tadna kar, par nyay se krodha men akar nahee, kaheen aeesa n ho ki maain nash ho jaun.
jo jaati tujhe naheen janatee, aur jo tujh se praarthna naheen karate, unheen par apanee jalajalahatt undela kyonaki unhon ne yakoob ko nigal liya, varan, use khakar ant kar diya haai, aur usake nivasasthan ko ujad diya haai.
yahova ka yah vachan yirmayah ke pas pahuncha
is vacha ke vachan suno, aur yahooda ke purushaen aur yarooshalem ke rahanevalon se kaho.
un se kaho, israael ka parameshvar yahova yon kahata haai, sraaapit haai vah manushy, jo is vacha ke vachan n mane
jise maain ne tumhare purakhaon ke sath lohe kee bhtthee arthata misra desh men se nikalane ke samay, yah kahake bandhaee thee, meree suno, aur jitanee agyaaaen maain tumhen deta hoo un sabhon ka palan karo. is se tum meree praja ttharoge, aur maain tumhara parameshvar ttharoonga
aur jo shapath maain ne tumhare pitaron se khi thee ki jis desh men doodha aur madha kee dhaaraaen bahatee haai, use maain tum ko doonga, use pooree karoonga aur dekho, vah pooree hui haai. yah sunakar maain ne kaha, he yahova, aeesa hee ho.
tab yahova ne mujh se kaha, ye sab vachan yahood ke nagaron aur yarooshalem kee sadkon men prachar karake kah, is vacha ke vachan suno aur usake anusar chalo.
kyonaki jis samay se maain tumhare purakhaon ko misra desh se chhuda le aya tab se aj ke din tak unako draddhta se chitata aya hoo, meree bat suno.
fir yahova ne mujh se kaha, yahoodiyon aur yarooshalem ke nivaasiyon men vidraeh paya gaya haai.
jaaise inake purakha mere vachan sunane se inakar karate the, vese hee ye bhee unake adhaman ka anusaran karake doosare devataon ke peechhe chalate aur unakee upasana karate haain israaael aur yahooda ke gharanon ne us vaacha ko jo maain ne unake poorvajon se bandhaee thee, tod diya haai.
isaliye yahova yon kahata haai, dek, maain in par aeesee vipaattai dalane par hoo jis se ye bach n sakenge aur chahe ye meree dohai den taubhee maain inakee n sunoonga.
us samay sarooshalem aur yahooda ke nagaron ke nivasee un devataon kee dohai denge jinake liye ve dhoop jalate haai, parantu ve unakee vipaattai ke samay unako kabhee n bacha sakenge.
he yahooda, jitane tere nagar haain utane hee tere devata bhee haain aur yarooshalem ke nivaasiyon ne har aek sadk men us lajjapoorn bal kee veadiyan bana banakar usake liye dhoop jalaya haai.
isaliye too meree is praja ke liye praarthna n karana, n koi in logon ke liye unche svar se binatee kare, kyonaki jis samay ye apanee vipaattai ke mare meree dohai denge, tab maain unakee n sunoonga.
meree pirya ko mere ghar men kya kam haai? us ne to bahuton ke sath kukarma kiya, aur teree pavitrata pooree reeti se jatee rahee haai. jab too burai karatee haai, tab pusann hotee haai.
yahova ne tujh ko haree, manohar, sundar falavalee jalapai to kaha tha, parantu us ne bade hullad ke shabd hote hee us men ag lagai gai, aur usakee daaliyan tod dalee gai.
senaon ka yahova, jis ne tujhe lagaya, us ne tujh par vipaattai dalane ke liye kaha haai isaka karan israaael aur yahooda ke gharanon kee yah burai haai ki unhon ne mujhe ris dilane ke liye bal ke nimitt dhoop jalaya.
yahova ne mujhe bataya aur yah bat mujhe maloom ho gai kyonki yahova hee ne unakee yuktaiyan mujh par pragatt keen.
maain to vadha honevale bhed ke bachche ke saman anajan tha. maain n janata tha ki ve log meree haani kee yuktaiyan yah kahakar karate haai, ao, ham fal samet is vraksha ko ukhad de, aur jeeviton ke beech men se katt dale, tab isaka nam tak fir smaran n rahe.
parantu, ab he senaon ke yahova, he dhama nyayee, he antakaran kee baton ke gyaata, too unaka palatta le aur mujhe dikha, kyonaki maain ne apana mukama tere hath men chhod diya haai.
isaliye yahova ne mujh se kaha, anatot ke log jo tere praan ke khojee haain aur yah kahate haain ki too yahova ka nam lekar bhavishyadanee n kar, naheen to hamare hathon se marega.
isaliye senaon ka yahova unake vishay yon kahata haai, maain unako dand doonga unake javan talavar se, aur unake ladke-ladkiyan bookhon marenge
aur un men se koi bhee n bachega. maain anatot ke logon par yah vipaattai daloonga unake dand ka din anevala haai.
too unako bota aur ve jad bhee pakadte ve baddhte aur falate bhee haain too unake munh ke nikatt haai parantu unake manon se door haai.
he yahova too mujhe janata haai too mujhe dekhta haai, aur too ne mere man kee pareeksha karake dekha ki maain teree or kis prakar rahata hoo. jaaise bhed-bakaariyan ghaat hone ke liye jhund men se nikalee jatee haai, vaaise hee unako bhee nikal le aur vadha ke din ke liye taaiyar kara.
kab tak desh vilap karata rahega, aur sare maaidan kee ghaas sookhee rahegee? desh ke nivaasiyon kee burai ke karan pashuu-pakshaee sab nash ho gaae haai, kyonki un logon ne kaha, vah hamare ant ko n dekhega.
too jo pyadon hee ke sang daudkar thk gaya haai to ghodon ke sang kyonkar barabaree kar sakega? aur yadhypi too shaaantai ke is desh men nidr haai, parantu yaradan ke asapas ke dhane jangal men too kya karega?
kyonaki tere bhai aur tere gharane ke logon ne bhee tera vishvasaghaat kiya haai ve tere peechhe lalakarate haai, yadi ve tujh se meettee baten bhee kahe, taubhee unakee prateeti n karana.
maain ne apana ghar chhod diya, apana nij bhag maain ne tyag diya haai maain ne apanee praanapirya ko shatrauon ke vash men kar diya haai.
kyonaki mera nij bhag mere dekhne men van ke sinh ke saman ho gaya aur mere viruddh garaja haai is karan maain ne us se baair kiya haai.
kya mera nij bhag meree draashtti men chitteevale shaikaree pakshaee ke saman naheen haai? kya shaikaree pakshaee charon or se use ghore huae haain? jao sab jangalee pashuuon ko ikattha karo unako lao ki kha jaaen.
bahut se charavahon ne meree dakh kee baree ko bigad kar diya, unhon ne mere bhag ko latada, varan mere manohar bhag ke khet ko sunasan jangal bana diya haai.
unhon ne usako ujad diya vah ujadkar mere samhane vilap kar raha haai. sara desh ujad gaya haai, taubhee koi naheen sochata.
jangal ke sab munde tteelon par nashak chaddh aae haain kyonaki yahova kee talavar desh ke aek chhor se lekar doosaree chhor tak nigalatee jatee haai kisee manushy ko shaanantai naheen milatee.
unhon ne gehoon to boya, parantu katteele ped katte, unhon ne kashtt to uttaya, parantu us se kuchh labh n hua. yahova ke krodha ke bhdkane ke karan tum apane kheton kee upaj ke vishay men laajjait ho.
mere dushtt padosee us bhag par hath lagate haai, jisaka bhagee maain ne apanee praja israaael ko banaya haai. unake vishy yahova yon kahata haai ki maain unako unakee boomi men se ukhad daloonga, aur yahooda ke gharane ko bhee unake beech men se ukhdoonga.
aur yaadi ve meree praja kee chal seekhkar mere hee nam kee saugandha, yahova ke jeevan kee saugandha, khane lage, jis prakar se unhon ne meree praja ko bal kee saugandha khana sikhlaya tha, tab meree praja ke beech unaka bhee vansh baddhega.
parantu yadi ve n mane, to maain us jaati ko aeesa ukhadoonga ki vah fir kabhee n pananpegee, yahova kee yahee vanee haai.
yahova ne mujh se yon kaha, jakar sanee kee aek pettee mol le, use kamar men bandha aur jal men mat bheegane de.
tab maain ne aek pettee mol lekar yahova ke vachan ke anusar apanee kamar men bandha lee.
tab toosaree bar yahova ka yah vachan mere pas pahuncha ki
jo pettee too ne mol lekar kaatt imen kas lee haai, use parat ke teer par le ja aur vahan use kadade par kee aek darar men chhpai de.
yahova kee is agyaa ke anusar maain ne usako parat ke teer par le jakar chhpai diya.
bahut dinon ke bad yahova ne mujh se kaha, ut, fir parat ke pas ja, aur jis pettee ko maain ne tujhe vahan chhpaiane kee agyaa dee use vahan se le le.
tab maain parat ke pas gaya or khodakar jis sthan men maain ne pettee ko chhpaiaya tha, vahan se usako nikal liya. aur dekho, pettee bigad gai thee vah kisee kam kee n rahee.
tab yahova ka yah vachan mere pas pahucha, yahova yon kahata haai,
isee prakar se maain yahoodiyon ka garva, aur yarooshalem ka bada garva nashtt kar doonga.
is dushtt jati ke log jo mere vachan sunane se inakar karate haain jo apane man ke hatt par chalate, doosare devataon ke peechhe chalakar unakee upasana karate or unako dandvata karate haai, ve is pettee ke saman ho jaaenge jo kisee kam kee naheen rahee.
yahova kee yah vanee haai ki jis prakar se pettee manushy kee kamar men kasee jatee haai, usee prakar se maain ne israaael ke sare gharane aur yahooda ke sare gharane ko apanee kaatt imen bandha liya tha ki ve meree praja banen aur mere nam aur keettair aur shaebha ka karan ho, parantu unhon ne n mana.
isaliye too un se yah vachan kah, israaael ka parameshvar yahova yon kahata haai, dakhmadha ke sab kuppe dakhmadha se bhr diae jaaenge. tab ve tujh se kahenge, kya ham naheen janate ki dakhmadha ke sab kuppe dakhmadha se bhr diae jaaenge?
tab too un se kahana, yahova yon kahata haai, dekho, maain is desh ke sab rahanevalon ko, vishosh karake daudavansh kee gaee par virajaman raja aur yajak aur bhavishyadvkta aadi yarooshalem ke sab nivaasiyon ko apanee koparoopee madira pilakar achet kar doonga.
tab maain unhen aek doosare se ttkara doonga arthata bap ko bette se, aur bette ko bap se, yahova kee yah vanee haai. maain un par komalata naheen dikhaunga, n taras khunga aur n daya karake unako nashtt hone se bachaunga.
apane parameshvar yahova kee badai karo, is se paahile ki vah andhakar laae aur tumhare panv andhore pahadon par ttokar khaae, aur jab tum prakash ka asara dekho, tab vah usako mratyu kee chhaya se badal aur use ghaer andhakar bana de.
aur yaadi tum ise n suno, to maain akele men tumhare garva ke karan rounga, aur meree ankhon se ansuon kee dhaara bahatee rahegee, kyonki yahova kee bheden bandhaua kar lee gai haain.
raja aur rajamata se kah, neeche baaitt jao, kyonaki tumhare siron ke shaebhayaman mukutt utar liae gaae haain.
daakkhian desh ke nagar ghore gaae haai, koi unhen bacha n sakega sampoorn yahoodee jati bandee ho gai haai, vah pooree reeti se bandhauai men chalee gai haai.
apanee okhen uttakar unako dekh jo uttar disha se a rahe haain. vah sundar jhund jo tujhe saunpa gaya tha kahan haai?
jab vah tere un mitraen ko tere upar pradhaan ttharaaega jinhen too ne apanee hani karane kee shaiksha dee haai, tab too kya kahegee? kya us samay tujhe jachcha kee see peedaaen n uttengee?
aur yaadi too apane man men soche ki ye baten kis karan mujh par padee haai, to tere bade adharma ke karan tera anchal uttaya gaya haai aur teree aediyan baariyai se nangee kee gai haain.
kya habashaee apana chamada, va cheeta apane dhabbe badal sakata haai? yadi ve aeesa kar sake, to too bhee, jo burai karana seekh gai haai, bhlai kar sakegee.
is karan maain unako aeesa titara-abitar karoonga, jaaisa boosa jangal ke pavan se titara-abitar kiya jata haai.
yahova kee yah vanee haai, tera hissa aur mujh se ttharaya hua tera bhag yahee haai, kyonaki too ne mujhe boolakar joott par bhrosa rakha haai.
isaliye maain bhee tera anchal tere munh tak uttaunga, tab teree laj janee jaaegee.
vyabhaichar aur chochala aur chhnaialapan aadi tere ghainaune kam jo too ne maaidan aur tteelon par kiae haai, ve sab maain ne dekhe haain. he yarooshalem, tujh par hay ! too apane ap ko kab tak shuuddh n karegee? aur kitane din tak too banee rahegee?
yahooda vilap karata aur faattkon men log shaek ka pahirava pahine huae boomi par udas baaitte haain aur yarooshalem kee chillahatt akash tak pahunch gai haai.
aur unake bade log unake chhotte logon ko panee ke liye bhejate haain ve gadhon par akar panee naheen pate isaliye choochhe bartan liae huae ghar lautt jate haain ve lajjait aur nirash hokar sir ddhanp lete haain.
desh men panee n barasane se boomi men darar pad gaae haai, is karan kisan log nirash hokar sir ddhanp lete haain.
haarinee bhee maaidan men bachcha janakar chhod jatee haai kyonaki haree ghaas naheen milatee.
jangalee gadahe bhee munde tteelon par khde huae geedadon kee nai hanfate haain unakee ankhen dhaundhala jatee haain kyonaki hariyalee kuchh bhee naheen haai.
he yahova, hamare adharma ke kam hamare viruddh sakshaee de rahe haai, ham tera sang chhodkar bahut door bhttk gaae haai, aur ham ne tere viruddh pap kiya haai taubhee, too apane nam ke nimitt kuchh kara.
he israaael ke adhaar, sankatt ke samay usaka bachanevala too hee haai, too kyon is desh men paradeshaee kee nai haai? too kyon us battohee ke saman haai jo rat bhr rahane ke liye kaheen ttkaita ho?
too kyon aek vismait purush ya aeese veer ke saman haai jo bacha n sake? taubhee he yahova too hamare beech men haai, aur ham tere kahalate haain isaliye hamako n taja.
yahova ne in logon ke vishay yon kaha inako aeesa bhttkana achchha lagata haai ye kukarma men chalane se naheen ruke isaaliye yahova in se prasann naheen haai, vah inaka adharma smaran karega aur unake pap ka dand dega.
fir yahova ne mujh se kaha, is praja kee bhlai ke liye praarthna mat kara.
chahe ve upavas bhee kare, taubhee maain inakee duhai n sunoonga, aur chahe ve homabali aur annabali chaddhaae, taubhee maain un se prasann n hounga maain talavar, mahangee aur maree ke dara inaka ant kar daloonga.
tab maain ne kaha, hay, prabhu yahova, dek, bhvishyadvkta in se kahate haain ki n to tum par talavar chalegee aur n mahangee hogee, yahova tum ko is sthan men sada kee shaantai dega.
aur yahova ne mujh se kaha, ye bhvishyadvkta mera nam lekar joottee bhavishyadanee karate haai, maain ne unako n to bheja aur n kuchh agyaa dee aur n un se koi bhee bat kahee. ve tum logon se darshan ka jootta dava karake apane hee man se vyarth aur dhaekhe kee bhavishyadanee karate haain.
is karan jo bhvishyadvkta mere bina bheje mera nam lekar bhvishyadanee karate haain ki us desh men n to talavar chalegee aur n mahangee hogee, unake vishay yahova yon kahata haai, ki, ve bhvishyadvkta ap talavar aur mahangee ke dara nash kiae jaaenge.
aur jin logon se ve bhavishyadanee kahate haai, ve mahangee aur talavar ke dara mar jane par is prakar yarooshalem kee sadkon men faenk diae jaaenge, ki n to unaka, n unakee striayon ka aur n unake bette-bettyaien ka koi mittee denevala rahega. kyonki maain unakee burai unheen ke upar undeloonga.
too un se yah bat kah, meree okhon se din rat ansoo lagatar bahate rahe, ve n ruken kyonki mere logon kee kunvaree bettee bahut hee kuchalee gai aur ghaayal hui haai.
yaadi maain maaidan men jau, to dekho, talavar ke mare huae pade haain ! aur yaadi maain nagar ke bheetar au, to dekho, bookh se adhmooae pade haain ! kyonaki bhvishyadvkta aur yajak desh men kamai karate firate aur samajh naheen rakhte haain.
he yahova, ham apanee dushttta aur apane purakhaon ke adharma ko bhee man lete haai, kyonki ham ne tere viruddh pap kiya haai.
apane nam ke nimitt hamen n ttukara apane tejomay sinhasan ka apaman n kara jo vacha too ne hamare sath bandhae, use smaran kar aur use n tod.
kya anyajaatiyon kee mooraton men se koi vashara kar sakata haai? kya akash jhadiyan laga sakata haai? he hamare parameshvar yahova, kya too hee in sab baton ka karanevala naheen haai? ham tera hee asara dekhte rahenge, kyonaki in saree vastuon ka srajanahar too hee haai.
fir yahova ne mujh se kaha, yaadi moosa aur shamooael bhee mere samhane khde hote, taubhee mera man in logon kee or n firata. inako mere samhane se nikal do ki ve nikal jaaen!
aur yaadi ve tujh se poochhen ki ham kahan nikal jaaen? to kahana ki yahova yon kahata haai, jo maranevale haai, ve marane ko chale jaae, jo talavar se maranevale haai, ve talavar se marane ko jo akal se maranevale haai, ve akal se marane ko, aur jo bandhauae honevale haai, ve bandhauai men chale jaaeen.
maain unake viruddh char prakar ke vinash ttharaunga mar dalane ke liye talavar, faad dalane ke liye kutte, noch dalane ke liye akash ke pakshae, aur faadkar khane ke liye maaidan ke hinsak jantu, yahova kee yah vanee haai.
yah hijaakiyyah ke putra, yahooda ke raja manashsho ke un kamon ke karan hoga jo us ne yarooshalem men kiae haai, aur maain unhen aeesa karoonga ki ve prathvee ke rajy rajy men mare mare firenge.
he yarooshalem, tujh par kaun taras khaaega, aur kaun tere liye shaek karega? kaun tera kushal poochhne ko teree or mudega?
yahova kee yah vanee haai ki too mujh ko tyagakar peechhe hatt gai haai, isaaliye maain tujh par hath baddhakar tera nash karoonga kyonki, maain taras khate khate ukata gaya hoo.
maain ne unako desh ke faattkon men soop se fattk diya haai unhon ne kumarga ko naheen chhoda, is karan maain ne apanee praja ko nirvash kar diya, aur nash bhee kiya haai.
unakee vidhavaae mere dekhne men samudra kee baloo ke kinakon se adhaik ho gai haain unake javanon kee mataon ke viruddh dupaharee hee ko maain ne lutteron ko ttharaya haai maain ne unako achanak sankatt men dal diya aur ghabara diya haai.
he meree mata, mujh par hay, ki too ne mujh aeese manushy ko utpann kiya jo sansar bhr se jhgada aur vadaavivad karanevala tthara haai ! n to maain ne vyaj ke liye rupaye dia, aur n kisee se udhaar liae haai, taubhee log mujhe kosate haain.
yahova ne kaha, nishchay maain teree bhlai ke liye tujhe draddh karoonga vipaattai aur kashtt ke samay maain shatra se bhee teree binatee karaunga.
kya koi peetal va loha, uttar disha ka loha tod sakata haai?
tere sab papon ke karan jo sarvatra desh men huae haain maain teree dhana-sampattai aur khjane, bina dam diae lutt jane doonga.
maain aeesa karoonga ki vah shatrauon ke hath aeese desh men chala jaaega jise too naheen janatee haai, kyonaki mere krodha kee ag bhdk uttee haai, aur vah tum ko jalaaegee.
he yahova, too to janata haai mujhe smaran kar aur meree sudhai lekar mere satanevalon se mera palatta le. too dhaeeraj ke sath krodha karanevala haai, isaliye mujhe n utta le tere hee nimitt meree namadharai hui haai.
jab tere vachan mere pas pahunche, tab maain ne unhen mano kha liya, aur tere vachan mere man ke harsha aur anand ka karan hue kyonki, he senaon ke parameshvar yahova, maain tera kahalata hoo.
teree chhaya mujh par iui maain man bahalanevalon ke beech baaittkar prasann naheen hua tere hath ke dabav se maain akela baaitta, kyonaki too ne mujhe krodha se bhr diya tha.
meree peeda kyon lagatar banee rahatee haai? meree chott kee kyon koi aushaadhai naheen haai? kya too sachamuch mere liye dhaekha denevalee nadee aur sookhnevale jal ke saman hoga?
yah sunakar yahova ne yon kaha, yadi too fire, to maain firase tujhe apane samhane khda karoonga. yaadi too anamol ko kahe aur nikamme ko n kahe, tab too mere mukh ke saman hoga. ve log teree or firenge, parantu too unakee or n firana.
aur maain tujh ko un logon ke samhane peetal kee draddh shaharapanah banaunga ve tujh se ladenge, parantu tujh par prabal n honge, kyonaki maain tujhe bachane aur tera uddhar karane ke liye tere sath hoo, yahova kee yah vanee haai. maain tujhe dushtt logon ke hath se bachaunga,
aur upadravee logon ke panje se chhuda loonga.
yahova ka yah vachan mere pas pahuncha,
is sthan men vivah karake bette-bettyaian mat janma.
kyonaki jo bette-beattyaian is sthn men utpann hon aur jo mataaen unhen janen aur jo pita unhen is desh men janmaae,
unake vishay yahova yon kahata haai, ve buree buree beemaariyon se marenge. unake liye koi chhatee n peettega, n unako mittee dega ve boomi ke upar khad kee nai pade rahenge. ve talavar aur mahangee se mar mittenge, aur unakee lothen akash ke pakshiayon aur maaidan ke pashuuon ka ahar hongee.
yahova ne kaha, jis ghar men ronapeettna ho us men n jana, n chhatee peettne ke liye kaheen jana aur n in logon ke liye shaek karana kyonki yahova kee yah vanee haai ki maain ne apanee shaantai aur karuna aur daya in logon par se utta lee haai.
is karan is desh ke chhotte-bade sab marenge, n to inako mittee dee jaaegee, n log chhatee peettenge, n apana shareer cheerenge, aur n sir mundaaenge. inake liye koi shaek karanevalon ko rottee n battenge ki shaek men unhen shaantai den
too jevanar ke ghar men inake sath khane-peene ke liye n jana.
kyonaki senaon ka yahova, israaael ka parameshvar yon kahata haai, dek, tum logon ke dekhte aur tumhare hee dinon men maain aeesa karoonga ki is sthan men n to harsha aur n anand ka shabd sunai padega, n dulhe aur n dualhain ka shabda.
aur jab too in logon se ye sab baten kahe, aur ve tujh se poochhen ki yahova ne hamare upar yah saree badee vipaattai dalane ke liye kyon kaha haai? hamara adharma kya haai aur ham ne apane parameshvar yahova ke viruddh kaun sa pap kiya haai?
to too in logon se kahana, yahova kee yah vanee haai, kyonki tumhare purakha mujhe tyagakar doosare devataon ke peechhe chale, aur unakee upasana karake unako dandvata kee, aur mujh ko tyag diya aur meree vyavastha ka palan naheen kiya,
or jitanee burai tumhare purakhaon ne kee thee, us se bhee adhaik tum karate ho, kyonki tum apane bure man ke hatt par chalate ho aur meree naheen sunate
is karan maain tum ko is desh se ukhadkar aeese desh men faenk doonga, jisako n to tum janate ho aur n tumhare purakha janate the aur vahan tum rata-din doosare devataon kee upasana karate rahoge, kyonaki vahan maain tum par kuchh anugrah n karoonga.
fir yahova kee yah vanee hui, dekho, aeese din anevale haain jin men fir yah n kaha jaaega ki yahova jo israaaeliyon ko misra desh se chhuda le aya usake jeevan kee saugandha,
varan yah kaha jaaega ki yahova jo israaaeliyon ko uttar ke desh se aur un sab deshaen se jahan us ne unako barabas kar diya tha chhuda le aya, usake jeevan kee saugandha. kyonki maain unako unake nij desh men jo maain ne unake poorvajon ko diya tha, lautta le aunga.
dekho, yahova kee yah vanee haai ki maai bahut se machhuon ko bulava bhejoonga ki ve in logon ko pakad le, aur, fir maain bahut se bahealiyon ko bulava bhejoonga ki ve inako aher karake sab pahadon aur pahaadiyon par se aur chattanon kee dararon men se nikalen.
kyonaki unaka poora chala-chalan meree ankhon ke samhane pragatt haai vah meree draashtti se chhpai naheen haai, n unaka adharma meree akhon se gupt haai. so maain unake adharma aur pap ka doona dand doonga,
he yahova, he mere bal aur draddh gaddh, sankatt ke samay mere sharansthan, jaatijaati ke log prathvee kee chahunor se tere pas akar kahenge, nishchay hamare purakha joottee, vyarth aur nishfal vastuon ko apanate aae haain.
kya manushy ishvaron ko banaae? nahee, ve ishvar naheen ho sakate !
is kara, aek is bar, maain in logon ko apana bhujabal aur parakram dikhaunga, aur ve janenge ki mera nam yahova haai.
yahooda ka pap lohe kee ttankee aur heere kee nok se likha hua haai vah unake dayaroopee pattyai aur unakee vediyon ke seengon par bhee khuda hua haai.
unakee veadiyan aur ashora nam deaviyan jo hare pedon ke pas aur unche tteelon ke upar haai, ve unake ladkon ko bhee smaran rahatee haain.
he mere parvat, too jo maaidan men haai, teree dhana-sampaattai aur bhndar maain tere pap ke karan lutt jane doonga, aur tere pooja ke unche sthan bhee jo tere desh men paae jate haain.
too apane hee dosh ke karan apane us bhag ka aadhaikaree n rahane paaega jo maain ne tujhe diya haai, aur maain aeesa karoonga ki too anajane desh men apane shatrauon kee seva karega, kyonki too ne mere krodha kee ag aeesee bhdkai jo sarvada jalatee rahegee.
yahova yon kahata haai, sraaapit haai vah purush jo manushy par bhrosa rakhta haai, aur usaka sahara leta haai, jisaka man yahova se bhttk jata haai.
vah nirjal desh ke adhamooae ped ke saman hoga aur kabhee bhlai n dekhega. vah nirjal aur nirjan tatha lonachhai boomi par basega.
dhany haai vah purush jo yahova par bhrosa rakhta haai, jis ne parameshvar ko apana adhaar mana ho.
vah us vraksha ke saman hoga jo nadee ke teer par laga ho aur usakee jad jal ke pas faailee ho jab ghaam hoga tab usako n lagega, usake patte hare rahenge, aur sookhe varsha men bhee unake vishay men kuchh chinta n hogee, kyonki vah tab bhee falata rahega.
man to sab vastuon se adhaik dhaekh denevala hota haai, us men asadhy rog laga haai usaka bhed kaun samajh sakata haai?
maain yahova man kee khojata aur day ko janchata hoo taaki pratyek jan ko usakee chala-chalan ke anusar arthata usake kamon ka fal doon.
jo anyay se dhan battorata haai vah us teetar ke saman hota haai jo doosaree chidiya ke diae huae andon ko setee haai, usakee adhaee ayu men hee vah us dhan ko chhod jata haai, aur ant men vah mooddh hee ttharata haai.
hamara paavitra aradhanalay aadi se unche sthan par rakhe huae aek tejomay sinhasan ke saman haai.
he yahova, he israaael ke adhaar, jitane tujhe chhod dete haain ve sab laajjait honge jo tujh se bhttk jate haain unake nam boomi hee par likhe jaaenge, kyonaki unhon ne bahate jal ke sote yahova ko tyag diya haai.
he yahova mujhe changa kar, tab maain changa ho jaunga mujhe bacha, tab maain bach jaunga kyonaki maain teree hee stuati karata hoo.
sun, ve mujh se kahate haai, yahova ka vachan kahan raha? vah abhee poora ho jaae !
parantu too mera hal janata haai, maain ne tere peechhe chalate huae utavalee karake charavahe ka kam naheen chhoda n maain ne us anevalee vipaattai ke din kee lalasa kee haai jo kuchh maain bola vah tujh par pragatt tha.
he yahova, meree asha toottne n de, mere satanevalon hee kee asha tootte unheen ko vismait kara parantu mujhe nirasha se bacha un par vipaattai dal aur unako chakanachoor kar de !
yahova ne mujh se yon kaha, jakar sadar faattk men khda ho jis se yahooda ke raja varan yarooshalem ke sab rahanevale bheetara-bahar aya jaya karate haain
aur un se kah, he yahooda ke rajao aur sab yahoodiyo, he yarooshalem ke sab nivaasiyo, aur sab logo jo in faattkon men se hokar bheetar jate ho, yahova ka vachan suno.
yahova yon kahata haai, savadhaan raho, vishraam ke din koi bojh mat uttao aur n koi bojh yarooshalem ke faattkon ke bheetar le ao.
vishraam ke din apane apane ghar se bhee koi bojh bahar mat leo aur n kisee reeati ka kam kaj karo, varan us agyaa ke anusar jo maain ne tumhare purakhaon ko dee thee, vishraam ke din ko pavitra mana karo.
parantu unhon ne n suna aur n kan lagaya, parantu isake vipareet hatt kiya ki n sunen aur tadna se bhee n manen.
parantu yadi tum sachamuch meree suno, yahova kee yah vanee haai, aur vishraam ke din is nagar ke faattkon ke bheetar koi bojh n le ao aur vishraamadin ko pavitra mano, aur us men kisee reeati ka kam kaj n karo,
tab to daud kee gaee par virajaman raja, rathon aur ghaedon par chaddhe huae haakim aur yahooda ke log aur yarooshalem ke nivasee is nagar ke faattkon se hokar pravesh kiya karenge aur yah nagar sarvada basa rahega.
aur log homabaali, melabali annabali, loban aur dhanyavadabali liae huae yahooda ke nagaron se aur yarooshalem ke asapas se, binyameen ke desh aur neeche ke desh se, pahadee desh aur dakkhian desh se, yahova ke bhvan men aya karenge.
yahova kee or se yah vachan yirmayah ke pas pahuncha, uttkar kumhar ke ghar ja,
aur vahan maain tujhe apane vachan sunavaunga.
so maain kumhar ke ghar gaya aur kya dekha ki vah chak par kuchh bana raha haai !
aur jo mittee ka basan vah bana raha tha vah bigad gaya, tab us ne usee ka doosara basan apanee samajh ke anusar bana diya.
tab yahova ka yah vachan mere pas pahuncha, he israaael ke gharane,
yahova kee yah vanee haai ki is kumhar kee nai tumhare sath kya maain bhee kam naheen kar sakata? dek, jaaisa mittee kumhar ke hath men rahatee haai, vaaisa hee he israaael ke gharane, tum bhee mere hath men ho.
jab maain kisee jaati va rajy ke vishay kahoon ki use ukhadoonga va ddha doonga athva nash karoonga,
tab yaadi us jati ke log jisake vishay maain ne kah bat kahee ho apanee burai se fire, to maain us vipaattai ke vishay jo maain ne un par dalane ko ttana ho pachhtaunga.
aur jab maain kisee jaati va rajy ke vishay kahoon ki maain use banaunga aur ropoonga
tab yaadi ve us kam ko karen jo meree drashtti men bura haai aur meree bat n mane, to maain us bhlai ke vishy jise maain ne unake liye karane ko kaha ho, pachhtaunga.
isaliye ab too yahooda aur yarooshalem ke nichaasiyoen se yah kah, yahova yon kahata haai, dekho, maain tumharee haani kee yuktai aur tumhare viruddh prabandha kar raha hoo. isaaliye tum apane apane bure marga se firo aur apana apana chalachalan aur kam sudhaaro.
parantu ve kahate haai, aeesa naheen hone ka, ham to apanee hee kalpanaon ke anusar chalenge aur apane bure man ke hatt par bane rahenge.
is karan prabhu yahova yon kahata haai, anyajaatiyon se poochh ki aeesee baten kya kabhee kisee ke sunane men ai haai? israaael kee kumaree ne jo kam kiya haai usake sunane se rom rom khde ho jate haain.
kya labanon ka him jo chattan par se maaidan men bahata haai band ho sakata haai? kya vah ttnda jal jo door se bahata haai kabhee sookh sakata haai?
parantu meree praja mujhe bool gai haai ve nikammee vastuon ke liye dhoop jalate haain unhon ne apane praacheenakal ke magan men ttokar khai haai, aur pagadandiyon aur behad magan men bhttk gaae haain.
is se unaka desh aeesa ujad ho gaya haai ki log us par sada talee bajate rahenge aur jo koi usake pas se chale vah chaakit hoga aur sir hilaaega.
maain unako puravai se udakar shatra ke samhane se titara-abitar kar doonga. unakee vipaattai ke din maain unako munh naheen parantu peett dikhaunga.
tab ve kahane lage, chalo, yirmayah ke viruddh yuaktai kare, kyonki n yajak se vyavastha, n gyaanee se sammati, n bhavishyadvkta se vachan door honge. ao, ham usakee koi bat pakadkar usako nash karaaen aur fir usakee kisee bat par dhyan n den.
he yahova, meree or dhyan de, aur jo log mere sath jhgadte haain unakee baten suna.
kya bhlai ke badale men burai ka vyavahar kiya jaae? too is bat ka smaran kar ki maain unakee bhlai ke liye tere samhane praarthna karane ko khda hua jis se teree jalajalahatt un par se utar jaa, aur ab unhon ne mere praan lene ke liye gadha khoda haai.
jab too un par achanak shatraudal chaddhaa, tab unake gharon se chillahatt sunai de ! kyonki unhon ne mere liye gadha khoda aur mere fansane ko fande lagaae haain.
he yahova, too unakee sab yuaktaiyan janata haai jo ve meree mratyu ke liye karate haain. is karan too unake is adharma ko n ddhanp, n unake pap ko apane samhane se mitta. ve tere dekhte hee ttokar khakar gir jaae, apane krodha men akar un se isee prakar ka vyavahar kara.
yahova ne yon kaha, too jakar kumhar se mittee kee banai hui aek surahee mol le, aur praja ke kuchh puraniyon men se aur yajakon men se bhee kuchh praacheenon ko sath lekar,
hinnomiyon kee tarai kee or us faattk ke nikatt chala ja jahan tteekare faenk diae jate haain aur jo vachan maain kahoo, use vahan prachar kara.
too yah kahana, he yahooda ke rajao aur yarooshalem ke sab nivaasiyo, yahova ka vachan suno. israaael ka parameshvar senaon ka yahova yon kahata haai, is sthan par maain aeesee vipaattai dalane par hoo ki jo koi usaka samachar sune, us par sannatta chha jaaega.
kyonaki yahan ke logon ne mujhe tyag diya, aur is sthan men doosare devataon ke liye jinako n to ve janate haai, aur n unake purakha va yahooda ke purane raja janate the dhoop jalaya haai aur isako paraya kar diya haai aur unhon ne is sthan ko nidashaen ke lohoo se bhr diya,
aur bal kee pooja ke unche sthanon ko banakar apane ladkebalon ko bal ke liye hom kar diya, yadhypi maain ne kabhee bhee jisakee agyaa naheen dee, n usakee charcha kee aur n vah kabhee mere man men aya.
is karan yahova kee yah vanee haai ki aeese din ate haain ki yah sthan fir topet va hinnomiyon kee tarai n kahalaaega, varan ghaat hee kee tarai kahalaaega.
aur maain is nagar ko aeesa ujad doonga ki log ise dekhkar drenge jo koi isake pas se hokar jaae vah isakee sab vipaattaiyon ke karan chakit hoga aur ghabaraaega.
aur ghair jane aur us saketee ke samay jis men unake praan ke shatra unhen dal denge, maain unake bette-beattyaien ka mans unhen khailaunga aur aek doosare ka bhee mans khailaunga.
tab too us surahee ko un manushyon ke samhane tod dena jo tere sang jaaenge,
aur un se kahana, senaon ka yahova yon kahata haai ki jis prakar yah mittee ka basan jo toott gaya ki fir banaya n ja sake, isee prakar maain is desh ke logon ko aur is nagar ko tod daloonga. aur topet nam tarai men itanee kabraen hongee ki kabra ke liye aur sthan n rahega.
yahova kee yah vanee haai ki maain is sthan aur isake rahanevalon ke sath aeesa hee kam karoonga, maain is nagar ko topet ke saman bana doonga.
aur yarooshalem ke ghar aur yahooda ke rajaon ke bhvan, jinakee chhton par akash kee saree sena ke liye dhoop jalaya gaya, aur any devataon ke liye tapavan diya gaya haai, ve sab topet ke saman ashuuddh ho jaaenge.
tab yirmayah topet se lauttkar, jahan yahova ne use bhvishyadanee karane ko bheja tha, yahova ke bhvan ke angan men khda hua, aur sab logon se kahane laga
israaael ka parameshvar senaon ka yahova yon kahata he, dekho, sab ganvon samet is nagar par vah saree vipaattai dalana chahata hoo jo maain ne is par lane ko kaha haai, kyonaki unhon ne hatt karake mere vachan ko naheen mana haai.
hilkaiyyah ka putra yirmayah jo binyameen desh ke anatot men rahanevale yajakon men se tha, usee ke ye vachan haain.
yahova ka vachan usake pas amon ke putra yahooda ke raja yoshaiyyah ke dinon men usake rajy ke terahaven varsha men pahuncha.
isake bad yoshaiyyah ke putra yahooda ke raja yahoyakeem ke dinon me, aur yoshaiyyah ke putra yahooda ke raja sidaakiyyah ke rajy ke gyarahaven varsha ke ant tak bhee pragatt hota raha jab tak usee varsha ke panchaven maheene men yarooshalem ke nivasee bandhauai men n chale gaae.
tab yahova ka yah vachan mere pas pahuncha,
garbh men rachane se pahile hee maain ne tujh par chitt lagaya, aur utpann hone se pahile hee maain ne tujhe aabhaishok kiya maain ne tujhe jaatiyon ka bhavishyadvkta ttharaya.
tab maain ne kaha, hay, prabhu yahova ! dek, maain to bolana hee naheen janata, kyonaki maain ladka hee hoo.
parantu yahova ne mujh se kaha, mat kah ki maain ladka hoo kyonki jis kisee ke pas maain tujhe bhejoon vahan too jaaega, aur jo kuchh maain tujhe aja doon vahee too kahega.
too unake mukh ko dekhkar mat dr, kyonki tujhe chhudane ke liye maain tere sath hoo, yahova kee yahee vanee haai.
tab yahova ne hath baddhakar mere munh ko chhua aur yahova ne mujh se kaha, dek, maain ne apane vachan tere munh men dal diye haain.
sun, maain ne aj ke din tujhe jaatiyon aur rajyon par aadhaikaree ttharaya haai anhen girane aur ddha dene ke liye, nash karane aur katt dalane ke liye, ya unhen banane aur ropane ke liye.
aur yahova ka yah vachan mere pas pahuncha, he yirmayah, tujhe kya dikhai padta haai? maain ne kaha, mujhe badam kee aek tthanee dikhai padtee haai.
tab yahova ne mujh se kaha, tujhe tteek dikhai padta haai, kyonki maain apane vachan ko poora karane ke liye jagrat hoo.
fir yahova ka vachan doosaree bar mere pas pahancha, aur us ne poochha, tujhe kya dikhai padta haai? maain ne kaha, mujhe ubalata hua aek handa dikhai padta haai jisaka munh uttar disha kee or se haai.
yahova kee yah vanee haai, maain uttar disha ke rajyon aur kulon ko bulaunga aur ve akar yarooshalem ke faattkon men aur usake charon or kee shaharapanah, aur yahooda ke aur sab nagaron ke samhane apana apana sinhasan lagaaenge.
aur unakee saree burai ke karan maain un par dand kee agyaa doonga kyonaki unhon ne mujhe tyagakar doosare devataon ke liye dhoop jalaya aur apanee banai hui vastuon ko dandvata kiya haai.
isaliye too apanee kamar kasakar utt aur jo kuchh kahane kee maain tujhe agyaa doon vahee un se kaha. too unake mukh ko dekhkar n ghabarana, aeesa n ho ki maain tujhe unake samhane ghabara doon.
kyonaki sun, maain ne aj tujhe is sare desh aur yahood ke rajao, hakimo, aur yajakon aur sadhaaran logon ke virud gaddhvala nagar, aur lohe ka khmbha, aur peetal kee shaharapanah banaya haai.
ve tujh se ladenge to sahee, parantu tujh par prabal n honge, kyonaki bachane ke liye maain tere sath hoo, yahova kee yahee vanee haai.
jab yirmayah yah bhvishyadanee kar raha tha, tab immer ka putra pashahoor ne jo yajak aur yahova ke bhvan ka pradhaan rakhvala tha, vah sab suna.
so pashahoor ne yirmayah bhvishyadvkta ko mara aur use us katt men dal diya jo yahova ke bhvan ke upar binyameen ke faattk ke pas haai.
kyonaki yahova ne yon kaha haai, dek, maain tujhe tere liye aur tere sab mitraen ke liye bhee bhy ka karan ttharaunga. ve apane shatrauon kee talavar se tere dekhte hee vadha kiae jaaenge. aur maain sab yahoodiyon ko babul ke raja ke vash men kar doonga vah unako bandhaua karake babul men le jaaega, aur talavar se mar dalega.
fir maain is nagar ke sare dhan ko aur is men kee kamai aur sab anamol vastuon ko aur yahooda ke rajaon ka jitana rakha hua dhan haai, us sab ko unake shatrauon ke vash men kar doonga aur ve usako loottkar apana kar lenge aur babul men le jaaenge.
aur, he pashahoor, too un sab samet jo tere ghar men rahate haain bandhauai men chala jaaega apane un mitraen samet jin se too ne joottee bhvishyadanee kee, too babul men jaaega aur vaheen marega, aur vaheen tujhe aur unhen bhee mittee dee jaaegee.
he yahova, too ne mujhe dhaekha diya, aur maain ne dhaekha khaya too mujh se balavant haai, is karan too mujh par prabal ho gaya. din bhr meree hansee hotee haai sab koi mujh se ttttha karate haain.
kyonaki jab maain baten karata hoo, tab maain jor se pukar pukarakar lalakarata hoo ki upadrav aur utpat hua, han utpat ! kyonki yahova ka vachan din bhr mere liye ninda aur ttttha ka karan hota rahata haai.
yaadi maain kahoo, maain usakee charcha n karoonga n usake nam se boloonga, to mere day kee aeesee dasha hogee mano meree haddiyon men dhadhakatee hui ag ho, aur maain apane ko rokate rokate thk gaya par mujh se raha naheen jata.
maain ne bahuton ke munh se apana apavad suna haai. charon or bhy hee bhy haai ! meree jan pahachan ke sab jo mere ttokar khane kee batt johate haai, ve kahate haai, usake dosh batao, tab ham unakee charcha faaila denge. kadaachit vah dhaekha khaa, to ham us par prabal hokar, us se badala lenge.
parantu yahova mere sath haai, vah bhyankar veer ke saman haai is karan mere satanevale prabal n honge, ve ttokar khakar girenge. ve buaddhi se kam naheen karate, isaliye unhen bahut lajjait hona padega. unaka apaman sadaaiv bana rahega aur kabhee boola n jaaega.
he senaon ke yahova, he dhaarmiyon ke parakhnevale aur day aur man ke gyaata, jo badala too un se lega, use maain dekoo, kyonki maain ne apana mukama tere upar chhod diya haai.
yahova ke liye gao yahova kee stuati karo ! kyonki vah daridra jan ke praan ko kukaarmiyon ke hath se bachata haai.
sraapit ho vah din jis men maain utpann hua ! jis din meree mata ne mujh ko janm diya vah dhany n ho !
sraapit ho vah jan jis ne mere pita ko yah samachar dekar usako bahut anandait kiya ki tere ladka utpann hua haai.
us jan kee dasha un nagaron kee see ho jinhen yahova ne bin daya ddha diya use savere to chillahatt aur dopahar ko yuddh kee lalakar sunai diya kare,
kyonaki us ne mujhe garbh hee men n mar dala ki meree mata ka garbhashay hee meree kabra hotee, aur maain usee men sada pada rahata.
maain kyon utpat aur shaek bhogane ke liye janma aur ki apane jeevan men paarishram aur ducha dekoo, aur upane din namadharai men vyateet karoon?
yah vachan yahova kee or se yirmayah ke pas us samay pahuncha jab sidaakiyyah raja ne usake pas maalkaiyyah ke putra pashahoor aur maseyah yajak ke putra sapanyah ke hath se yah kahala bheja ki,
hamare liye yahova se pooch, kyonaki babul ka raja nabookadanessar hamare viruddh yuddh kar raha haai kadachit yahova ham se apane sab ashcharyakaman ke anusar aeesa vyavahar kare ki vah hamare pas se utt jaae.
tab yirmayah ne un se kaha, tum sidaakiyyah se yon kaho, israaael ka parameshvar yahova yon kahata haai,
dekho, yuddh ke jo hathaiyar tumhare hathon men haai, jin se tum babul ke raja aur shaharapanah ke bahar ghoranevale kasadiyon se lad rahe ho, unako maain lauttakar is nagar ke beech men ikattha karoonga
