isaliye israaael ka parameshvar senaon ka yahova yon kahata haai, rekab ke putra yonadab ke vansh men sada aeesa jan paya jaaega jo mere sammukh khda rahe.
fir yoshaiyyah ke putra yahooda ke raja yahoyakeem ke rajy ke chauthe baras men yahova kee or se yah vachan yirmayah ke pas pahuncha,
aek pustak lekar jitane vachan maain ne tujh se yoshaiyyah ke dinon se lekar arthata jab maain tujh se baten karane laga us samay se aj ke din tak israaael aur yahooda aur sab jatiyon ke vishay men kahe haai, sab ko us men likh.
kya jane yahooda ka gharana us saree vipaattai ka samachar sunakar jo maain un par dalane kee kalpana kar raha hoo apanee buree chal se fire aur maain unake adharma aur pap ko kshama karoon.
fir yirmayah ne barook ko agyaa dee aur kaha, maain to bandha hua hoo, maain yahova ke bhvan men naheen ja sakata.
so tu upavas ke din yahova ke bhvan men jakar usake jo vachan too ne mujh se sunakar likhe haai, pustak men se logon ko paddhkar sunana, aur jitane yahoodee log apane apane nagaron se aaenge, unako bhee paddhkar sunana.
kya jane ve yahova se gidgidakar praarthna karen aur apanee apanee buree chal se firen kyonki jo krodha aur jalajalahatt yahova ne apanee is praja par bhdkane ko kaha haai, vah badee haai.
yirmayah bhvishyadvkta kee is agyaa ke anusar neriyyah ke putra barook ne, yahova ke bhvan men us pustak men se usake vachan paddhkar sunaae.
aur yoshaiyyah ke putra yahooda ke raja yahoyakeem ke rajy ke panchaven baras ke nauven maheene men yarooshalem men jitane log the, aur yahooda ke nagaron se jitane log yarooshalem men aae the, unhon ne yahova ke samhane upavas karane ka prachar kiya.
tab barook ne yahova ke bhvan men sab logon ko shaapan ke putra gamaryah jo pradhaan tha, usakee kottree men jo upar ke angan men yahova ke bhvan ke naye faattk ke pas thee, yirmayah ke sab vachan pustak men se paddh sunaae.
tab shaapan ke putra gamaryah ke bette meekayah ne yahova ke sare vachan pustak men se sune.
aur vah rajabhvan ke pradhaan kee kottree men utar gaya, aur kya dekha ki vahan aeleeshama pradhaan aur shamayah ka putra dalayah aur ababor ka putra aelanatan aur shaapan ka putra gamaryah aur hananyah ka putra sidaakiyyah aur sab hakim baaitte huae haain.
aur meekayah ne jitane vachan us samay sune, jab barook ne pustak men se logon ko paddh sunaae the, ve sab varnn kiae.
unhen sunakar sab haakimon ne yahoodee kee jo natanyah ka putra or sholemyah ka pota aur kooshaee ka parapota tha, barook ke pas yah kahane ko bheja, ki jis pustak men se too ne sab logon ko paddh sunaya he, use apane hath men leta a. so neriyyah ka putra barook vah pustak hath men liae huae unake pas aya.
tab unhon ne us se kaha, ab baaitt ja aur hamen yah paddhkar suna. tab barook ne unako paddhkar suna diya.
jab ve un sab vachanon ko sun chuke, tab thrathrate huae aek doosare ko dekhne lage aur unhon ne barook se kaha, ham nishchay raja se in sab vachanon ka varnn karenge.
fir unhon ne barook se kaha, ham se kah, kya too ne ye sab vachan usake mukh se sunakar likhe?
barook ne un se kaha, vah ye sab vachan apane mukh se mujhe sunata gaya or maain inhen pustak men syahee se likhta gaya.
tab haakimon ne barook se kaha, ja, too apane apako aur yirmayah ko chhpai, aur koi n janane paae ki tum kahan ho.
tab ve pustak ko aeleeshama pradhaan kee kottree men rakhkar raja ke pas angan men aae aur raja ko ve sab vachan kah sunaae.
tab raja ne yahoodee ko pustak le ane ke liye bheja, us ne use aeleeshaama pradhaan kee kottree men se lekar raja ko aur jo haakim raja ke as pas khde the unako bhee paddh sunaya.
raja shaeetakal ke bhvan men baaitta hua tha, kyonaki nauvan maheena tha aur usake samhane angeettee jal rahee thee.
jab yahoodee teen char prashtt paddh chuka, tab us ne use chakoo se katta aur jo ag angeettee men thee us men faenk diya so angeettee kee ag men pooree poostak jalakar bhsm ho gai.
parantu n koi dra aur n kisee ne apane kapade faade, arthata n to raja ne aur n usake kamrachaariyon men se kisee ne aeesa kiya, jinhon ne ve sab vachan sune the.
aelanatan, aur dalayah, aur gamaryah ne to raja se binatee bhee kee thee ki pustak ko n jalaa, parantu us ne unakee aek n sunee.
jab raja ne un vachanon kee pustak ko jo barook ne yirmayah ke mukh se sun sunakar likhee thee, jala diya, tab yahova ka yah vachan yirmayah ke pas pahuncha ki
fir aek aur pustak lekar us men yahooda ke raja yahoyakeem kee jalai hai paahilee pustak ke sab vachan likh de.
aur yahooda ke raja yahoyakeem ke vishay men kah ki yahova yon kahata haai, too ne us pustak ko yah kahakar jala diya haai ki too ne us men yah kyon likha haai ki babul ka raja nishchay akar is desh ko nash karega, aur us men n to manushy ko chhodega aur n pashu ko.
isaliye yahova yahooda ke raja yahoyakeem ke vishay men yon kahata haai, ki usaka koi daud kee gaee par virajaman n rahega aur usakee loth aeesee faenk dee jaaegee ki din ko dhaam men or rat ko pale men padee rahegee.
aur maain usako aur usake vansh aur karmachariyon ko unake adharma ka dand doonga aur jitanee vipaattai maain ne un par aur yarooshalem ke nivaasiyon aur yahooda ke sab logon par dalane ko kaha haai, aur jisako unhon ne sach naheen mana, un sab ko maain un par daloonga.
tab yirmayah ne doosaree pustak lekar neriyyah ke putra barook lekhk ko dee, aur jo pustak yahooda ke raja yahoyakeem ne ag men jala dee thee, us men ke sab vachanon ko barook ne yirmayah ke mukh se sun sunakar us men likh diae aur un vachanon men unake saman aur bhee bahut see baten baddha dee gai.
aur yahoyakeem ke putra konyah ke sthan par yoshaiyyah ka putra sidaakiyyah rajy karane laga, kyonki babul ke raja nabookadanessar ne usee ko yahooda desh men raja ttharaya tha.
parantu n to us ne, n usake karmachariyon ne, aur n sadhaaran logon ne yahova ke vachanon ko mana jo us ne yirmayah bhvishyadvkta ke dara kaha tha.
us samay yirmayah bandeegrah men n dala gaya tha, or logon ke beech aya jaya karata tha.
