aur sidaakiyyah ke rajy ke gyarahaven varsha ke chauthe maheene ke nauven din ko us nagar kee shaharapanah todee gai.
so jab yarooshalem le liya gaya, tab nergalasareser, aur samagarnabo, aur khejon ka pradhaan sarsakeem, aur magon ka pradhaan nergalasareser adi, babul ke raja ke sab hakim beech ke faattk men pravesh karake baaitt gaae.
jab yahooda ke raja sidaakiyyah aur sab yodaon ne unhen dekha tab rat hee rat raja kee baree ke marga se donon bheeton ke beech ke faattk se hokar nagar se nikalakar bhag chale aur araba ka marga liya.
tab babul ke raja ne sidaakiyyah ke putraen ko usakee ankhon ke samhane ribala men ghaat kiya aur sab kuleen yahoodiyon ko bhee ghaat kiya.
us ne sidaakiyyah kee ankhon ko faudva dala aur usako babul le jane ke liye beadiyon se jakadva rakha.
kasadiyon ne rajabhvan aur praja ke gharon ko ag lagakar foonk diya, or yarooshalem kee shaharapanah ko ddha diya.
tab jalladon ka pradhaan naboojaradan praja ke bache huon ko jo nagar men rah gaae the, aur jo log usake pas bhag aae the unako arthata praja men se jitane rah gaae un sab ko bandhaua karake babul ko le gaya.
parantu praja men se jo aeese kangal the jinake pas kuchh n tha, unako jalladon ka pradhaan naboojaradan yahooda desh men chhod gaya, aur jate samay unako dakh kee baariyan aur khet de diae.
babul ke raja nagookadanessar ne jalladon ke pradhaan naboojaradan ko yirmayah ke vishay men yah agyaa dee,
ki usako lekar us par krapadraashtti banaae rakhna aur usakee kuchh hani n karana jaaisa vah tujh se kahe vaaisa hee us se vyavahar karana.
so jalladon ke pradhaan naboojaradan aur khejon ke pradhaan naboosajaban aur magon ke pradhaan nergalasareser jyotishaiyon ke saradar,
aur babul ke raja ke sab pradhaanon ne, logon ko bhejakar yirmayah ko pahare ke angan men se bulava liya aur gadalyah ko jo aheekam ka putra aur shaapan ka pota tha saunp diya ki vah use ghar pahunchaae. tab se vah logon ke sath rahane laga.
jab yirmayah pahare ke angan men kaaid tha, tab yahova ka yah vachan usake pas pahuncha,
parantu yahova kee yah vanee haai ki us samay maain tujhe bachaunga, aur jin manushyon se too bhy khata haai, too unake vash men naheen kiya jaaega.
kyonaki maain tujhe, nishchay bachaunga, aur too talavar se n marega, tera praan bacha rahega, yahova kee yah vanee haai. yah is karan hoga, ki too ne mujh par bhrosa rakha haai.
ve kahate haai, yadi koi apanee patnee ko tyag de, aur vah usake pas se jakar doosare purush kee ho jaa, to vah pahila kya usake pas fir jaaega? kya vah desh aati ashuuddh n ho jaaega? yahova kee yah vanee haai ki too ne bahut se praemiyon ke sath vyabhaichar kiya haai, kya too ab meree or firegee?
munde tteelon kee or ankhen uttakar dekh ! aeesa kaun sa sthan haai jahan too ne kukarma n kiya ho? magan men too aeesee baaittee jaaise aek arabee jangal men. too ne desh ko apane vyabhaichar se ashuuddh kar diya haai.
isee karan jhadiyan aur barasat kee pichhlee vashara naheen hotee taubhee tera matha veshya ka sa haai, too lajjait hona hee naheen janatee.
kya too ab mujhe pukarakar kahegee, he mere pita, too hee meree javanee ka sathee haai?
kya vah man men sada krodha rakhe rahega? kya vah usako sada banaae rahega? too ne aeesa kaha to haai, parantu too ne bure kam prabalata ke sath kiae haain.
fir yoshaiyyah raja ke dinon men yahova ne mujh se yah bhee kaha, kya too ne dekha ki bhttkanevalee israaael ne kya kiya haai? us ne sab unche pahadon par aur sab hare pedon ke tale ja jakar vyaabhaichar kiya haai.
tab maain ne sova, jab ye sab kam vah kar chuke tab meree or firegee parantu vah n firee, aur usakee vishvasaghaatee bahin yahooda ne yah dekha.
fir maain ne dekha, jab maain ne bhttkanevalee israaael ko usake vyabhaichar karane ke karan tyagakar use tyagapatra de diya taubhee usakee vishvasaghaatee bahin yahooda n dree, varan jakar vah bhee vyabhaichaarinee ban gai.
usake nirlajja-vyabhaichaarinee hone ke karan desh bhee ashuuddh ho gaya, us ne patthr aur katt ke sath bhee vyabhaichar kiya.
itane par bhee usakee vishvasaghaatee bahin yahooda poorn man se meree or naheen firee, parantu kapatt se, yahova kee yahee vanee haai.
aur yahova ne mujh se kaha, bhttkanevalee israaael, vishvasaghaaatin yahooda se kam doshaee nikalee haai.
too jakar uttar disha men ye baten prachar kar, yahova kee yah vanee haai, he bhttkanevalee israaael lautt a, maain tujh par krodha kee drashtti n karoonga kyonki yahova kee yah vanee haai, maain karunamay hoo maain sarvada krodha n rakhe rahoonga.
keval apana yah adharma man le ki too apane parameshvar yahova se fir gai aur sab hare pedon ke tale idhar udhar doosaron ke pas gai, aur meree baton ko naheen mana, yahova kee yah vanee haai.
he bhttkanevale ladko lautt ao, kyonki maain tumhara svamee hoo yahova kee yah vanee haai. tumhare pratyek nagar peechhe aek, aur pratyek kul peechhe do ko lekar maain siyyon men pahuncha doonga.
aur maain tumhen apane man ke anukool charavahe doonga, jo gyaan aur buaddhi se tumhen charaaenge.
un dinon men jab tum is desh men baddho, aur foolo-falo, tab log fir aeesa n kahenge, yahova kee vacha ka sandooka yahova kee yah bhee vanee he. usaka vichar bhee unake man men n aega, n log usake n rahane se chinta karenge aur n usakee marammat hogee.
un dinon men yahooda ka gharana israael ke gharane ke sath chalega aur ve donon milakar uttar ke desh se is desh men aenge jise maain ne unake poorvajon ko nij bhag karake diya tha.
maain ne socha tha, maain kaaise tujhe ladkon men ginakar vah manabhavana desh doon jo sab jatiyon ke deshaen ka shairomanai haai. aur maain ne socha ki too mujhe pita kahegee, aur mujh se fir n bhttkegee.
is men to sandeh naheen ki jaaise vishvasaghaatee sree apane piry se man faer letee haai, vaaise hee he israaael ke gharane, too mujh se fir gaya haai, yahova kee yahee vanee haai.
munde tteelon par se israaaeliyon ke rone aur gidgidane ka shabd sunai de raha haai, kyonki ve tteddhee chal chalate rahe haain aur apane parameshvar yahova ko bool gaae haain.
he bhttkanevale ladko, lautt ao, maain tumhara bhttkana sudhaar doonga. dek, ham tere pas aae haain kyonaki too hee hamara parameshvar yahova haai.
nishkhy pahadon aur pahadiyon par ka kolahal vyarth hee haai. israaael ka uddhar nishchay hamare parameshvar yahova hee ke dara haai.
parantu hamaree javanee hee se us badanamee kee vastu ne hamare purakhaon kee kamai arthata unakee bhed-bakaree aur gaya-baail aur unake bette-beattyaien ko nigal liya haai.
ham laajjait hokar lett jaae, aur hamara sankoch hamaree oddhnee ban jaae kyonaki hamare purakha aur ham bhee yuva avastha se lekar aj ke din tak apane parameshvar yahova ke viruddh pap karate aae haain aur ham ne apane parameshvar yahova kee baton ko naheen mana haai.
jab jalladon ke pradhaan naboojaradan ne yirmayah ko rama men un sab yarooshalemee aur yahoodee bandhauon ke beech hathkadiyon se bandha hua pakar jo babul jane ko the chhuda liya, usake bad yahova ka vachan usake pas pahuncha.
jalladon ke pradhaan naboojaradan ne yirmayah ko us samay apane pas bula liya, or kaha, is sthan par yah jo vipaattai padee haai vah tere parameshvar yahova kee kahee hui thee.
or jaaisa yahova ne kaha tha vaaisa hee us ne poora bhee kiya haai. tum logon ne jo yahova ke virud pap kiya or usakee agyaa naheen manee, is karan tumharee yah dasha hui haai.
vah vaheen tha ki naboojaradan ne fir us se kaha, gadalyah jo aheekam ka putra aur shaapan ka pota haai, jisako babul ke raja ne yahooda ke nagaron par aadhaikaree ttharaya haai, usake pas lautt ja aur usake sang logon ke beech rah, va jahan kaheen tujhe jana tteek jan pade vaheen chala ja. so jalladon ke pradhaan ne usako seedha aur kuchh dravy bhee dekar vida kiya.
tab yirmayah aheekam ke putra gadalyah ke pas mispa ko gaya, aur vahan un logon ke beech jo desh men rah gaae the, rahane laga.
yodaon ke jo dal dihat men the, jab unake sab pradhaanon ne apane janon samet suna ki babul ke raja ne aheekam ke putra gadalyah ko desh ka aadhaikaree ttharaya haai, aur desh ke jin kangal logon ko vah babul ko naheen le gaya, kya purusha, kya sre, kya balabachche, un sabhon ko use saunp diya haai,
tab natanyah ka putra ishmaael, kareh ke putra yohanan, yonatan aur tanhooset ka putra sarayah, aepaai natopavasee ke putra aur kisee makavasee ka putra yajanyah apane janon samet gadalyah ke pas mispa men aae.
aur gadalyah jo aheekam ka putra aur shaapan ka pota tha, us ne un se aur unake janon se shapath khakar kaha, kasaadiyon ke adhaeen rahane se mat dro. isee desh men rahate huae babul ke raja ke adhaeen raho tab numhara bhla hoga.
maain to iseealiye mispa men rahata hoon ki jo kasadee log hamare yahan aae, unake samhane haajir hua karoon parantu tum dakhmadha aur dhoopakal ke fal aur tel ko battorake apane baratanon men rakho aur apane liae huae nagaron men base raho.
fir jab moaabiyo, ammoniyo, aedomiyon aur any sab jatiyon ke beech rahanevale sab yahoodiyon ne suna ki babul ke raja ne yahoodiyon men se kuchh logon ko bacha liya aur un par gadalyah ko jo aheekam ka putra aur shaapan ka pota haai adhaikaree niyukt kiya haai,
tab sab yahoodee jin jin sthanon men titara-abitar ho gaae the, vahan se lauttkar yahooda desh ke mispa nagar men gadalyah ke pas, aur bahut dakhmadha aur dhoopakal ke fal battorane lage.
tab kareh ka putra yohanan aur maaidan men rahanevale yodaon ke sab dalon ke pradhaan mispa men gadalyah ke pas akar kahane lage, kya too janata haai
ki ammoniyon ke raja balees ne natatyah ke putra ishmaael ko tujhe jan se marane ke liye bheja haai? parantu aheekam ke putra gadalyah ne unakee prateeati n kee.
fir kareh ke putra yohanan ne gadalyah se mispa men chhpaikar kaha, mujhe jakar natanyah ke putra ishmaael ko mar dalane de or koi ise n janega. vah kyon tujhe mar dale, aur jitane yahoodee log tere pas ikatthe huae haain ve kyon titara-abitar ho jaaen aur bache huae yahoodee kyon nash hon?
yaheekam ke putra gadalyah ne kareh ke putra yohanan se kaha, aeesa kam mat kar, too ishmaael ke vishay men joott bolata haai.
aur sataven maheene men aeesa hua ki ishmaael jo natanyah ka putra aur aeleeshaama ka pota aur rajavansh ka aur raja ke pradhaan purushaen men se tha, so das jan sang lekar mispa men aheekam ke putra gadalyah ke pas aya. vahan mispa men unhon ne aek sang bhojan kiya.
tab natanyah ke putra ishmaael aur usake sang ke das janon ne uttkar gadalyah ko, jo aheekam ka putra aur shapan ka pota tha, or jise babul ke raja ne desh ka adhaikaree ttharaya tha, use talavar se aeesa mara ki vah mar gaya.
aur ishmaael ne gadalyah ke sang jitane yahoodee mispa men the, aur jo kasadee yoda vahan mile, un sabhon ko mar dala.
gadalyah ke mar dalane ke doosare din jab koi ise n janata tha,
tab shakem aur shaeelo aur shaemaron se assee purush daddhee mudaa, vasr faade, shareer cheere huae aur hath men annabali aur loban liae hua, yahova ke bhvan men jane ko ate dikhai diae.
jab ve us nagar men aae tab natanyah ke putra ishmaael ne apane sangee janon samet unako ghaat karake gadhe men faenk diya.
parantu un men se das manushy ishmaael se kahane lage, ham ko n mara kyonaki hamare pas maaidan men rakha hua gehoo, jav, tel aur madha haai. so us ne unhen chhod diya aur unake bhaiyon ke sath naheen mara.
jis gadhe men ishmaael n un logon kee sab lothen jinhen us ne mara tha, gadalyah kee loth ke pas faenk dee thee, yah vahee gadha haai jise asa raja ne israaael ke raja basha ke dr ke mare khudavaya tha, usako natanyah ke putra ishmaael ne mare huon se bhr diya.
tab jo log mispa men bache huae the, arthata rajakumaariyan aur jitane aur log mispa men rah gaae the jinhen jalladon ke pradhaan naboojaradan ne aheekam ke putra gadalyah ko saunp diya tha, un sabhon ko natanyah ka putra ishmaael bandhaua karake ammoniyon ke pas le jane ko chala.
jab kareh ke putra yohanan ne aur yodaon ke dalon ke un sab pradhaanon ne jo usake sang the, suna, ki natanyah ke putra ishmaael ne yah sab burai kee haai,
tab ve sab janon ko lekar natanyah ke putra ishmaael se ladne ko nikale aur usako us bade jalashay ke pas paya jo gibon men haai.
kareh ke putra yohanan ko, aur dalon ke sab pradhaanon ko dekhkar jo usake sang the, ishmaael ke sath jo log the, ve sab anaandait hue.
aur jitane logon ko ishmaael mispa se bandhaua karake liae jata tha, ve palattkar kareh ke putra yohanan ke pas chale aae.
parantu natanyah ka putra ishmaael att purush samet yohanan ke hath se bachakar ammoniyon ke pas chala gaya.
tab praja men se jitane bach gaae the, arthata jin yodao, striayo, balabachchon aur khojon ko kareh ka putra yohanan, aheekam ke putra gadalyah ke mispa men mare jane ke bad natanyah ke putra ishmaael ke pas se chhudakar gibon se faer le aya tha, unako vah apane sab sangee dalon ke pradhaanon samet lekar chal diya.
aur betalehem ke nikatt jo kimham kee saray haai, us men ve isaaliye ttkai gaae ki misra men jaaen.
kyonaki ve kasaadiyon se drate the isaka karan yah tha ki aheekam ka putra gadalyah jise babul ke raja ne desh ka adhaikaree ttharaya tha, use natanyah ke putra ishmaael ne mar dala tha.
hamaree binatee grahan karake apane parameshvar yahova se ham sab bache huon ke liye praarthna kar, kyonaki too apanee ankhon se dekh raha haai ki ham jo pahale bahut the, ab thode hee bach gaae haain.
isaliye praarthna kar ki tera parameshvar yahova ham ko bataae ki ham kis marga se chale, aur kaun sa kam karen?
so yirmayah bhvishyadvkta ne un se kaha, maain ne tumharee sunee haai dekho, maain tumhare vachanon ke anusar tumhare parameshvar yahova se praarthna karoonga or jo uttar yahova tumhare liye dega maain tum ko bataunga maain tum se koi bat n chhpaiaunga.
tab unhon ne yirmayah se kaha, yaadi tera parameshvar yahova tere dara hamare pas koi vachan pahunchaae aur ham usake anusar n kare, to yahova hamare beech men sachcha aur vishvasayogy sakshaee tthare.
chahe vah bhlee bat ho, chahe buree, taubhee ham apane parameshvar yahova kee agyaa, jisake pas ham tujhe bhejate haai, manenge, kyonaki jab ham apane parameshvar yahova kee bat manen tab hamara bhla ho.
das din ke beetane par yahova ka vachan yirmayah ke pas pahuncha.
tab us ne kareh ke putra yohanan ko, usake sath ke dalon ke pradhaanon ko, aur chhotte se lekar bade tak jitane log the, un sabhon ko bulakar un se kaha,
israaael ka parameshvar yahova, jisake pas tum ne mujh ko isaaliye bheja ki maain tumharee binatee usake age kah sunau, vah yon kahata haai,
yaadi tum isee desh men rah jao, tab to maain tum ko nash naheen karoonga varan banaae rakoonga aur tumhen n ukhaoonga, varan rope rakoonga kyonaki tumharee jo haani maain ne kee haai us se maain pachhtata hoo.
tum babul ke raja se drate ho, so us se mat dro yahova kee yah vanee haai, us se mat dro, kyonaki maain tumharee raksha karane aur tum ko usake hath se bachane ke liye tumhare sath hoo.
maain tum par daya karoonga, ki vah bhee tum par daya karake tum ko tumharee boomi par fir se basa dega.
parantu yadi tum yah kahakar ki ham is desh men n rahenge apane parameshvar yahova kee bat n mano, aur kaho ki ham to misra desh jakar vaheen rahenge,
kyonaki vahan n ham yud dekhenge, n naraasinge ka shabd sunenge aur n ham ko bhojan kee dhattee hoga, to, he bache huae yahoodiyo, yahova ka yah vachan suno
israaael ka parameshvar senaon ka yahova yon kahata haai, ki yadi tum sachamuch misra kee or jane ka munh karo, aur vahan rahane ke liye jao,
to aeesa hoga ki jis talavar se tum drate ho, vahee vahan misra desh men tum ko ja legee, aur jis mahangee ka bhy tum khate ho, vah misra men tumhara peechha n chhodegee aur vaheen tum maroge.
jitane manushy misra men rahane ke liye usakee or munh kare, ve sab talavar, mahangee aur maree se marenge, aur jo vipaattai maain unake beech daloonga, us se koi bacha n rahega.
he bache huae yahoodiyo, yahova ne tumhare vishay men kaha haai, misra men mat jao. tum nishchay jano ki maain ne aj tum ko chitakar yah bat bata dee haai.
kyonaki jab tum ne mujh ko yah kahakar apane parameshvar yahova ke pas bhej diya ki hamare nimitt hamare parameshvar yahova se praarthna kar aur jo kuchh hamara parameshvar yahova kahe usasee ke anusar ham ko bata aur ham vaaisa hee karenge, tab tum jan boojhke apane hee ko dhaekha dete the.
dekho, maain aj tum ko bataae deta hoo, parantu, aur jo kuchh tumhare parameshvar yahova ne tum se kahane ke liye mujh ko bheja haai, us men se tum koi bat naheen manate.
ab tum nishchay jano, ki jis sthan men tum paradeshaee hoke rahane kee ichchha karate ho, us men tum talavar, mahangee aur maree se mar jaoge.
jab yirmayah unake parameshvar yahova ke ve sab vachan kah chuka, jinake kahane ke liye us ne usako un sab logon ke pas bheja tha,
tab hoshaaya ke putra ajaryaah aur kareh ke putra yohanan aur sab abhaimanee purushaen ne yirmayah se kaha, too joott bolata haai. hamare parameshvar yahova ne tujhe yah kahane ke liye naheen bheja ki misra men rahane ke liye mat jao
parantu neriyyah ka putra barook tujh ko hamare virud usakata haai ki ham kasaadiyon ke hath men paden aur ve ham ko mar dalen va bandhaua karake babul ko le jaaen.
so kareh ka putra yohanan aur dalon ke sab pradhaanon aur sab logon ne yahova kee yah agyaa n manee ki ve yahooda ke desh men hee rahen.
aur kareh ka putra yohanan aur dalon ke aur sab pradhaan un sab yahoodiyon ko jo anyajatiyon ke beech titarabitar ho gaae the, aur un men se lauttkar yahooda desh men rahane lage the, ve unako le gaae--
purusha, sre, balabachche, rajakumaariya, aur jitane praaanaiyon ko jalladon ke pradhaan naboojaradan ne gadalyah ko jo aheekam ka putra aur shaapan ka mota tha, saunp diya tha, unako aur yirmayah bhvishyadvkta aur neariyyah ke putra barook ko ve le gaae
aur yahova kee agyaa n manakar ve misra desh men tahapanhes nagar tak a gaae.
tab yahova ka yah vachan tahapanhes men yirmayah ke pas pahuncha
apane hath se bade patthr le, aur yahoodee purushaen ke samhane us itt ke chabootare men jo tahapanhes men firaun ke bhvan ke dar ke pas haai, choona faer ke chhpai de,
vah ake misra desh ko marega, tab jo maranevale hon ve mratyu ke vash me, jo bandhauae honevale hon ve bandhauai me, aur jo talavar ke liye hen ve talavar ke vash men kar diae jaaenge.
maain misra ke devalayon men ag lagaunga aur vah unhen faunkava dega aur bandhauai men le jaaega aur jaaisa koi charavaha apana vasr oddhta haai, vaaisa hee vah misra desh ko samett lega aur tab bekhttke chala jaaega.
vah misra desh ke sooryagrah ke khmbhon ko tudva dalega aur misra ke devalayon ko ag lagakar foonkava dega.
jitane yahoodee log misra desh men migdol, tahapanhes aur nop nagaron aur patraes desh men rahate the, unake vishay yirmayah ke pas yah vachan pahuncha,
israaael ka parameshvar, senaon ka yahova yon kahata haai ki jo vipaattai maain yarooshalem aur yahooda ke sab nagaron par dal chuka hoo, vah sab tum logon ne dekhee haai. dekho, ve aj ke din kaaise ujade huae aur nirjan haai,
kyonaki unake nivaasiyon ne vah burai kee jis se unhon ne mujhe ris dilai thee ve jakar doosare devataon ke liye dhoop jalate the aur unakee upasana karate the, jinhen n to tum aur n tumhare purakha janate the.
taubhee maain apane sab das bhavishyadvktaon ko bade yatn se yah kahane ke liye tumhare pas bhejata raha ki yah gharaanait kam mat karo, jis se maain gharana rakhta hoo.
par unhon ne meree n sunee aur n meree or kan lagaya ki apanee burai se firen aur doosare devataon ke liye dhoom n jalaaen.
is karan meree jalajalahatt aur kop kee ag yahooda ke nagaron aur yarooshalem kee sadkon par bhdk gai aur ve aj ke din tak ujad aur sunasan pade haain.
ab yahova, senaon ka parameshvar, jo israaael ka parameshvar haai, yon kahata haai, tum log kyon apanee yah badee hani karate ho, ki kya purusha, kya sre, kya balak, kya doodhaapiuva bachcha, tum sab yahooda ke beech se nash kiae jao, aur koi n rahe?
kyonaki is misra desh men jahan tum paradeshaee hokar rahane ke liye aae ho, tum apane kamon ke dara, arthata doosare devataon ke liye dhoop jalakar mujhe ris dilate ho jis se tum nash ho jaoge or prathvee bhr kee sab jaatiyon ke log tumharee jati kee namadharai karenge aur tumharee upama dekar shaap diya karenge.
jo jo buraiyan tumhare purakha, yahooda ke raja aur unakee striaya, aur tumharee striaya, varan tum ap yahooda desh aur yarooshalem kee sadkon men karate the, kya use tum bool gaae ho?
aj ke din tak unaka man choor naheen hua or n ve drate haain aur n meree us vyavastha aur un vidhaiyon par chalate haain jo maain ne tumhare poorvajon ko aur tum ko bhee sunavai haain.
is karan israaael ka parameshvar, senaon ka yahova, yon kahata haai, dekho, maain tumhare virud hokar tumharee haani karoonga, taaki sab yahoodiyon ka ant kar doon.
aur bache huae yahoodee jo hatt karake misra desh men akar rahane lage haai, ve sab mitt jaaenge is misra desh men chhotte se lekar bade tak ve talavar aur mahangee ke dara marak mitt jaaenge aur log unhen kosenge aur chaakit honge aur unakee upama dekar shaap diya karenge aur ninda bhee karenge.
ki jo bache huae yahoodee misra desh men paradeshaee hokar rahane ke liye aae haai, yadhyapi ve yahooda desh men rahane ke liye lauttne kee badee aabhailasha rakhte haai, taubhee un men se aek bhee bachakar vahan n lauttne paaega keval kuchh hee bhage huon ko chhod koi bhee vahan n lauttne paaega.
tab misra desh ke patraes men rahanevale jitane purush janate the ki unakee striayan doosare devataon ke liye dhoop jalatee haai, aur jitanee striayan badee mandlee men pas khdee thee, un sabhon ne yirmayah ko yah uttar diya,
jo vachan too ne ham ko yahova ke nam se sunaya haai, usako ham naheen sunane kee.
jo jo mannaten ham man chuke haain unhen ham nishchay pooree karengee, ham svarga kee ranee ke liye dhoop jalaaenge aur tapavan denge, jaaise ki hamare purakha log aur ham bhee apane rajaon aur aur hakimon samet yahooda ke nagaron men aur yarooshalem kee sadkon men karate the kyonaki us samay ham pett bhrake khate aur bhle change rahate aur kisee vipaattai men naheen padte the.
parantu jab se ham ne svarga kee ranee ke liye dhoop jalana aur tapavan dena chhod diya, tab se ham ko sab vastuon kee ghattee haai aur ham talavar aur mahangee ke dara mitt chale haain.
aur striayon ne kaha, jab ham svarga kee ranee ke liye dhoop jalateen aur chandraakar rottyaian banakar tapavan detee thee, tab apane apane pati ke bin jane aeesa naheen karatee theen.
tab yirmayah ne, kya sre, kya purusha, jitane logon ne yah uttar diya, un sab se kaha,
tumhare purakha aur tum jo apane rajaon aur hakimon aur logon samet yahooda desh ke nagaron aur yarooshalem kee sadkon men dhoop jalate the, kya vah yahova ke dhyan men naheen aya?
kya us ne usako smaran n kiya? so jab yahova tumhare bure aur sab gharanait kamon ko aur aadhaik n sah saka, tab tumhara desh ujadkar nirjan aur sunasan ho gaya, yahan tak ki log usakee upama dekar shaap diya karate haai, jaaise ki aj hota haai.
kyonaki tum dhoop jalakar yahova ke virud pap karate aur usakee naheen sunate the, aur usakee vyavastha aur vidhaiyon aur chitauaniyon ke anusar naheen chale, is karan yah vipaattai tum par a padee haai, jaaise ki aj haai.
fir yirmayah ne un sab logon se aur un sab striayon se kaha, he sare misra desh men rahanevale yahoodiyo, yahova ka vachan suno
israaael ka parameshvar, senaon ka yahova, yon kahata haai, ki tum ne aur tumharee striayon ne mannaten manee aur yah kahakar unhen pooree karate ho ki ham ne svarga kee ranee ke liye dhoop jalane aur tapavan dene kee jo jo mannaten manee haain unhen ham avashy hee pooree karenge aur tum ne apane hathon se aeesa hee kiya. so ab tuum apanee apanee mannaton ko manakar pooree karo !
parantu he misra desh men rahanevale sare yahoodiyo yahova ka vachan suno suno, maain ne apane bade nam kee shapath khai haai ki ab poore misra desh men koi yahoodee manushy mera nam lekar fir kabhee yah n kahane paaega ki prabhu yahova ke jeevan kee saugandha.
suno, ab maain unakee bhlai nahee, hani hee kee chinta karoonga so misra desh men rahanevale sab yahoodee, talavar aur mahangee ke dara mittkar nash ho jaaenge jab tak ki unaka sarvanash n ho jaae.
is bat ka maain yah chinh deta hoo, yahova kee yah vanee haai, ki maain tumhen isee sthan men dand doonga, jis se tum jan loge ki tumharee haani karane men mere vachan nishchay poore honge.
yahova yon kahata he, dekho, jaaisa maain ne yahooda ke raja sidaakiyyah ko usake shatra arthata usake praan ke khojee babul ke raja nabookadanessar ke hath men kar diya, vaaise hee maain misra ke raja firaun hopra ko bhee usake shatrauon ke, arthata usake praan ke khojiyon ke hath men kar doonga.
yoshaiyyah ke putra yahooda ke raja yahoyakeem ke rajy ke chauthe varsha me, jab neriyyah ka putra barook yirmayah bhvishyadvkta se bhavishyadanee ke ye vachan sunakar pustak men likh chuka tha,
tab us ne us se yah vachan kaha, ki israaael ka parameshvar yahova,tujh se yon kahata haai,
he barook, too ne kaha, hay mujh par ! kyonaki yahova ne mujhe dukh par dukh diya haai maain karahate karahate thk gaya aur mujhe kuchh chaain naheen milata.
too yon kah, yahova yon kahata haai, ki dek, is sare desh ko jise maain ne banaya tha, use maain ap ddha doonga, aur jin ko maain ne ropa tha, unhen svayan ukhad faenkoonga.
isaliye sun, kya too apane liye badai khoj raha haai? use mat khoja kyonki yahova kee yah vanee haai, ki maain sare manushyon par vipaattai daloonga parantu jahan kaheen too jaaega vahan maain tera praan bachakar tujhe jeeavit rakoonga.
anyajatiyon ke vishay yahova ka jo vachan yirmayah bhvishyadvkta ke pas pahuncha, vah yah haai.
misra ke vishaya. misra ke raja firaun niko kee sena jo parat mahanad ke teer par karkameesh men thee, aur jise babul ke raja nabookadanessar ne yoshaiyyah ke putra yahooda ke raja yahoyakeem ke rajy ke chauthe varsha men jeet liya tha,
us sena ke vishaya--ddhalen aur fariyan taaiyar karake ladne ko nikatt chale ao.
ghaedon ko jutavao aur he savaro, ghaedon par chaddhkar ttop paahine huae khde ho jao bhalon ko paaina karo, jhlaimon ko paahin lo !
