nishchay yahova ke kop ke karan yarooshalem aur yahooda kee aeesee dasha hui ki ant men us ne unako apane samhane se door kar diya. aur sidaakiyyah ne babul ke raja se balava kiya.
aur usake rajay ke nauven varsha ke dasaven maheene ke dasaven din ko babul ke raja nabookadanessar ne apanee saree sena lekar yarooshalem par chaddhai kee, aur us ne usake pas chhavanee karake usake charon or kila banaya.
yon nagar ghora gaya, aur sidaakiyyah raja ke gyarahaven varsha tak ghaira raha.
chauthe maheene ke nauven din se nagar men mahangee yahan tak baddh gai, ki logon ke liye kuchh rottee n rahee.
tab nagar kee shaharapanah men darar kee gai, aur donon bheeton ke beech jo faattk raja kee baree ke nikatt tha, us se sab yoda bhagakar rat hee rat nagar se nikal gaa, aur araba ka marga liya. us samay kasadee log nagar ko ghore huae the.
parantu unakee sena ne raja ka peechha kiya, aur usako yareeho ke pas ke araba men ja pakada tab usakee saree sena usake pas se titara-abitar ho gai.
so ve raja ko pakadkar hamat desh ke ribala men babul ke raja ke pas le gaa, aur vahan us ne usake dand kee agyaa dee.
fir babul ke raja ne sidaakiyyah kee ankhon ko faudva dala, aur usako bediyon se jakadkar babul tak le gaya, aur usako bandeegrah men dal diya. so vah mratyu ke din tak vaheen raha.
fir usee varsha arthata babul ke raja nabookadanessar ke rajy ke unneesaven varsha ke panchaven maheene ke dasaven din ko jalladon ka pradhaan naboojaradan jo babul ke raja ke sammukh khda rahata tha yarooshalem men aya.
aur us ne yahova ke bhvan aur rajabhvan aur yarooshalem ke sab bade bade gharon ko ag lagavakar faunkava diya.
aur kasadiyon kee saree sena ne jo jalladon ke pradhaan ke sang thee, yarooshalem ke charon or kee sab shaharapanah ko ddha disha.
aur jalladon ka pradhaan naboojaradan kangal logon men se kitanon ko, aur jo log nagar men rah gaae the, aur jo log babul ke raja ke pas bhag gaae the, aur jo kareegar rah gaae the, un sab ko bandhaua karake le gaya.
aur yahova ke bhvan men jo peetal ke khmbhe the, aur kuarsiyon aur peetal ke hauj jo yahova ke bhvan men the, un sabhon ko kasadee log lodkar unaka peetal babul ko le gaae.
aur handiyo, faavaadiyo, kaainchiyo, kattoro, ghoopadano, nidan peetal ke aur sab patraen ko, jin se log seva tthal karate the, ve le gaae.
aur tasalo, karachho, kattoriyo, hanadiyo, deevatto, dhoopadano, aur kattoron men se jo kuchh sone ka tha, unake sone ko, aur jo kuchh chandee ka tha unakee chandee ko bhee jalladon ka pradhaan le gaya.
donon khmbhe, aek hauj aur peetal ke barahon baail jo payon ke neeche the, in sab ko to sulaaiman raja ne yahova ke bhvan ke liye banavaya tha, aur in sab ka peetal taul se bahar tha.
jo khmbhe the, un men se aek aek kee unchai attarah hat, aur ghora barah hat, aur mottai char angul kee thee, aur ve khokhle the.
aek aek kee kanganee peetal kee thee, aur aek aek kanganee kee unchai panch hath kee thee aur us par charon or jo jalee aur anar bane the ve sab peetal ke the.
kangaaniyon ke charon alangon par chhyaianave anar bane the, aur jalee ke upar charon or aek sau anar the.
aur jalladon ke pradhaan ne sarayah mahayajak aur usake neeche ke sapanyah yajak, aur teenon devaddheedaron ko pakad liya
aur nagar men se us ne aek khoja pakad liya, jo yodaon ke upar tthara tha aur jo purush raja ke sammukh raha karate the, un men se sat jan jo nagar men mile aur senapaati ka munshaee jo sadhaaran logon ko sena men bhratee karata tha aur sadhaaran logon men se satt purush jo nagar men mile,
in sab ko jalladon ka pradhaan naboojaradan ribala men babul ke raja ke pas le gaya.
tab babul ke raja ne unhen hamat desh ke ribala men aeesa mara ki ve mar gaae.
yo yahoodee apane desh se bandhauae hokar chale gaae. jin logon ko nabookadanessar bandhaua karake le gaya, so ye haai, arthta usake rajy ke sataven varsha men teen hajar teis yahoodee
fir apane rajy ke attarahaven varsha men nabookadanessar yarooshalem se att sau battees praanaieeyon ko bandhaua karake le gaya
fir nabookadanessar ke rajy ke teisaven varsha men jalladon ka pradhaan naboojaradan sat sau paaintalees yahoodee janon ko bandhauae karake le gaya sab praanee milakar char hajar chhsau huae.
fir yahooda ke raja yahoyakeen kee bandhauai ke saainteesaven varsha men arthata jis varsha babul ka raja aebeelamarodak rajagaee par virajaman hua, usee ke barahaven maheene ke pacheesaven din ko us ne yahooda ke raja yahoyakeen ko bandeegrah se nikalakar bada pad diya
aur us se madhaur madhaur vachan kahakar, jo raja usake sath babul men bandhauae the, unake sinhasanon se usake sinhasan ko adhaeek uncha kiya.
aur usake bandeegrah ke vasr badal diae aur vah jeevan bhr nity raja ke sammukh bhojan karata raha
aur praati din ke khrcha ke liye babul ke raja ke yahan se usako nity kuchh milane ka prabandha hua. yah prabandha usakee mratyu ke din tak usake jeevan bhr lagatar bana raha.
yarooshalem kee sadkon men idhar udhar daudkar dekho ! usake chaukon men ddoonddho yadi koi aeesa mil sake jo tyay se kam kare aur sachchai ka khojee ho to maain usaka pap kshama karoonga.
yadhymi usake nivasee yahova ke jeevan kee shapath bhee khaae, taubhee nishchay ve joottee shapath khate haain.
he yahova, kya teree draashtti sachchai par naheen haai? too ne unako dukh diya, parantu ve shaeakit naheen huae too ne unako nash kiya, parantu unhon ne tadna se bhee naheen mana. unhon ne apana man chattan se bhee adhaik kattor kiya haai unhon ne pashchattap karane se inakar kiya haai.
fir maain ne socha, ye log to kadgal aur abodha hee haain kyonaki ye yahova ka marga aur apane parameshvar ka niyam naheen janate.
isaliye maain bade logon ke pas jakar unako sunaunga kyonki ve to yahova ka marga aur apane parameshvar ka niyam janate haain. parantu un sabhon ne milakar jooae ko tod diya haai aur bandhanon ko khol dala haai.
is karan van men se aek sinh akar unahen mar dalega, nirjal desh ka aek bhediya unako nash karega. aur aek cheeta unake nagaron ke pas ghaat lagaae rahega, aur jo koi un men se nikale vah faada jaaega kyonki unake aparadha bahut baddh gaae haain aur ve mujh se bahut hee door hatt gaae haain.
ve khailaae-pilaae be-lagam ghodon ke saman ho gaa, ve apane apane padosee kee sree par hinaahinane lage.
kya maain aeese kamon ka unhen dand n doon? yahova kee yah vanee haai kya maain aeesee jati se apana palatta n loon?
shaharapanah par chaddhke usaka nash to karo, taubhee usaka ant mat kar dalo usakee jad rahane do parantu usakee daliyon ko todkar faenk do, kyonki ve yahova kee naheen haain.
yahova kee yah vanee haai ki israaael aur yahooda ke gharanon ne mujh se bada vishvasaghaat kiya haai.
bhavishyadvkta hava ho jaaenge un men ishvar ka vachan naheen haai. unake sath aeesa hee kiya jaaega !
is karan senaon ka parameshvar yahova yon kahata haai, ye log jo aeesa kahate haai, isaaliye dek, maain apana vachan tere munh men ag, aur is praja ko katt banaunga, aur vah unako bhsm karegee.
yahova kee yah vanee haai, he israaael ke gharane, dek, maain tumhare viruddh door se aeesee jaati ko chaddha launga jo samath aur praacheen haai, usakee bhasha tum n samajhoge, aur n yah janoge ki ve log kya kah rahe haain.
unaka tarkash khulee kabra haai aur ve sab ke sab shooraveer haain.
tumhare pakke khet aur bhojanavastuaen jo tumhare bette-beattyaien ke khane ke liye haain unhen ve kha jaaenge. ve tumharee bhead-bakaariyon aur gaya-baailon ko kha dalenge ve tumharee dakhon aur anjeeron ko kha jaaenge aur jin gaddhvale nagaron par tum bhrosa rakhte ho unhen ve talavar ke bal se nash kar denge.
taubhee, yahova kee yah vanee haai, un dinon men bhee maain tumhara ant n kar daloonga.
aur jab tum poochhoge ki hamare parameshvar yahova ne ham se ye sab kam kis liye kiae haai, tab tum un se kahana, jis prakar se tum ne mujh ko tyagakar apane desh men doosare devataon kee seva kee haai, usee prakar se tum ko paraye desh men paradeshaiyon kee seva karanee padegee.
yakoob ke gharane men yah prachar karo, aur yahooda men yah sunao
he moorkh aur nirbuaddhi logo, tum jo ankhen rahate huae naheen dekhte, jo kan rahate huae naheen sunate, yah suno.
yahova kee yah vanee haai, kya tum log mera bhy naheen manate? kya tum mere sammukh naheen thrathrate? maain ne baloo ko samudra ka sivana ttharakar yug yug ka aeesa bandha ttharaya ki vah use landha n sake aur chahe usakee laharen bhee utte, taubhee ve prabal n ho sake, ya jab ve garajen taubhee usako n landha saken.
par is praja ka hatteela aur balava karanevala man haai inhon ne balava kiya aur door ho gaae haain.
ve man men itana bhee naheen sochate ki hamara parameshvar yahova to barasat ke arambh aur ant donon samayon ka jal samay par barasata haai, aur kattnee ke niyat saptahon ko hamare liye rakhta haai, isaaliye ham usaka bhy manen.
parantu tumhare adharma ke kamon hee ke karan ve ruk gaa, aur tumhare papon hee ke karan tumharee bhlai naheen hotee.
meree praja men dushtt log paae jate haain jaaise chideemar tak men rahate haai, vaaise hee ve bhee ghaat lagaae rahate haain. ve fanda lagakar manushyon ko apane vash men kar lete haain.
jaaisa pinjada chidiyon se bhra ho, vaaise hee unake ghar chhl se bhre rahate haain isee prakar ve baddh gaae aur dhanee ho gaae haain.
ve motte aur chikane ho gaae haain. bure kamon men ve seema ko landha gaae haain ve nyay, vishosh karake anathon ka nyay naheen chukate is se unaka kam safal naheen hota ve kangalon ka haka bhee naheen dilate.
isaliye, yahova kee yah vanee haai, kya maain in baton ka dand n doon? kya maain aeesee jaati se palatta n loon?
desh men aeesa kam hota haai jis se chakit aur romanchit hona chaahiye.
bhachishyadvkta joottmoott bhavishyadanee karate haain aur yajak unake sahare se prabhuta karate haain meree praja ko yah bhata bhee haai, parantu ant ke samay tum kya karoge?
he binyameeaniyo, yarooshalem men se apana apana saman lekar bhago ! takoa men naraasinga foonko, aur bethkkerem par jhnda uncha karo kyonki uttar kee disha se anevalee vipaattai badee aur vinash lanevalee haai.
siyyon kee sundar aur sukumar bettee ko maain nash karane par hoo.
charavahe apanee apanee bhed-bakaariyan sang liae huae us par chaddhkar usake charon or apane tamboo khde karenge, ve apane apane pas kee ghaas chara lenge.
ao, usake viruddh yuddh kee taaiyaree karo utto, ham do pahar ko chaddhai karen ! hay, hay, din ddhlata jata haai, aur sanjh kee parachhai lambee ho chalee haai !
utto, ham rat hee rat chaddhai karen aur usake mahalon ko ddha den.
senaon ka yahova tum se kahata haai, vraksha katt kattkar yarooshalem ke virud damadama bandhae ! yah vahee nagar haai jo dand ke yogy haai is men andhor hee anadhor bhra hua haai.
he yarooshalem, tadna se hee man le, naheen to too mere man se bhee utar jaaegee aur, maain tujh ko ujadkar nirjan kar daloonga.
senaon ka yahova yon kahata haai, israaael ke sab bache huae dakhlata kee nai ddoonddhkar tode jaaenge dakhke todnevale kee nai us lata kee daaliyon par fir apana hath laga.
maain kis se boloon aur kisako chitakar kahoon ki ve manen? dek, ye uncha sunate haai, ve dhyan bhee naheen de sakate dek, yahova ke vachan kee ve ninda karate aur use naheen chahate haain.
un logon ke ghar aur khet aur striayan sab auron ko ho jaengeen kyonki maain is desh ke rahanevalon par hath baddhaunga, yahova kee yahee vanee haai.
kyonaki un men chhotte se lekar bade tak sab ke sab lalachee haain aur kya bhavishyadvkta kya yajak sab ke sab chhl se kam karate haain.
ve, shaantai haai, shaantai, aeesa kah kahakar meree praja ke ghaav ko upar hee upar changa karate haai, parantu shaantai kuchh bhee naheen.
kya ve kabhee apane gharanait kamon ke karan lajjait hue? nahee, ve kuchh bhee lajjait naheen huae ve laajjait hona janate hee naheen is karan jab aur log neeche gire, tab ve bhee girenge, aur jab maain unako dand dene lagoonga, tab ve ttokar khakar girenge, yahova ka yahee vachan haai.
yahova yon bhee kahata haai, sadkon par khde hokar dekho, aur poochho ki praacheenakal ka achchha marga kaun sa haai, usee men chalo, aur tum apane apane man men chaain paoge. par unhon ne kaha, ham us par n chalenge.
maain ne tumhare liye paharuae baaittakar kaha, narasinge ka shabd dhyan se sunana ! par unhon ne kaha, ham n sunenge.
isaliye, he jaatiyo, suno, aur he mandlee, dek, ki in logon men kya ho raha haai.
he prathvee, suna dek, ki maain is jaati par vah vipaattai le aunga jo unakee kalpanaon ka fal haai, kyonaki inhon ne mere vachanon par dhyan naheen lagaya, aur meree shaiksha ko inhon ne nikammee jana haai.
mere liye jo loban shaba se, aur sugandhiat narakatt jo door desh se ata haai, isaka kya prayojan haai? tumhare homabaliyon se maain prasann naheen hoo, aur n tumhare melabali mujhe meette lagate haain.
is karan yahova ne yon kaha haai, dekho, maain is praja ke age ttokar khaunga, aur bap aur betta, padosee aur mitra, sab ke sab ttokar khakar nash honge.
yahova yon kahata haai, dekho, uttar se varan prathvee kee chhor se aek badee jati ke log is desh ke virodha men ubhare jaaenge.
ve dhanush aur bachh dhaaran kiae huae aaenge, ve kroor aur nirday haai, aur jab ve bolate haain tab mano samudra garajata haai ve ghaedon par chaddhe huae aaenge, he siyyon, ve veer kee nai sashasr hokar tujh par chaddhai karenge.
isaka samachar sunate hee hamare hath ddheele pad gaae haain ham sankatt men pade haain jachcha kee see peeda ham ko uttee haai.
maaidan men mat nikalo, marga men bhee n chalo kyonaki vahan shatra kee talavar aur charon or bhy dekh padta haai.
he meree praja kamar men ttatt bandha, aur rakh men lott jaaisa aekalaute putra ke liye vilap hota haai vaaisa hee bada shaekamay vilap kara kyonki nash karanevala ham par achanak a padega.
maain ne isaaliye tujhe apanee praja ke beech gummatt va gaddh tthara diya ki too unakee chal parakhe aur jan le.
ve sab bahut hee hattee haai, ve lutarai karate firate haain un sabhon kee chal bigadee haai, ve nira tamba aur loha hee haain.
ghaunkanee jal gai, shaeesha ag men jal gaya ddhalanevale ne vyarth hee ddhala haai kyonki bure log naheen nikale gaae.
unaka nam khottee chandee padega, kyonaki yahova ne unako khotta paya haai.
jo vachan yahova kee or se yirmayah ke pas pahuncha vah yah haai
yahova ke bhvan ke faattk men khda ho, aur yah vachan prachar kar, or kah, he sab yahoodiyo, tum jo yahova ko dandvata karane ke liye in faattkon se pravesh karate ho, yahova ka vachan suno.
senaon ka yahova jo israaael ka parameshvar haai, yon kahata haai, apanee apanee chal aur kam sudhaaro, tab maain tum ko is sthan men base rahane doonga.
tum log yah kahakar joottee baton par bhrosa mat rakho, ki yahee yahova ka maandair haai yahee yahova ka mandair, yahova ka maandaira.
yaadi tum sachamuch apanee apanee chal aur kam sudhaaro, aur sachamuch manushya-manushy ke beech nyay karo,
paradeshaee aur anath aur vidhava par andhor n karo is sthan men nidash kee hatya n karo, aur doosare devataon ke peechhe n chalo jis se tumharee haani hotee haai,
to maain tum ko is nagar me, aur is desh men jo maain ne tumhare poorvajon ko diya tha, yug yug ke liye rahane doonga.
tum jo choree, hatya aur vyaabhaichar karate, joottee shapath khate, bal devata ke liye dhoop jalate, aur doosare devataon ke peechhe jinhen tum pahile naheen janate the chalate ho,
to kya yah uchit haai ki tum is bhvan men ao jo mera kahalata haai, aur mere samhane khde hokar yah kaho ki ham isaaliye choott gaae haain ki ye sab gharaanait kam karen?
mera jo sthan shaeelo men tha, jahan maain ne paahile apane nam ka nivas ttharaya tha, vahan jakar dekho ki maain ne apanee praja israaael kee burai ke karan usakee kya dasha kar dee haai?
ab yahova kee yah vanee haai, ki tum jo ye sab kam karate aae ho, aur yadhypi maain tum se bade yatn se baten karata raha hoo, taubhee tum ne naheen suna, aur tumhen bulata aya parantu tum naheen bole,
isaliye yah bhvan jo mera kahalata haai, jis par tum bhrosa rakhte ho, aur yah sthan jo maain ne tum ko aur tumhare poorvajon ko diya tha, isakee dasha maain shaeelo kee see kar doonga.
aur jaaisa maain ne tumhare sab bhaiyon ko arthat sare aepraaiamiyon ko apane samhane se door kar diya haai, vaaisa hee tum ko bhee door kar doonga.
is praja ke liye too praarthna mat kar, n in logon ke liye unche svar se pukar n mujh se binatee kar, kyonaki maain teree naheen sunoonga.
kya too naheen dekhta ki ye log yahooda ke nagaron aur yarooshalem kee sadkon men kya kar rahe haain?
