us samay maain aeesa karoonga ki yahooda ke nagaron aur yarooshalem kee sadkon men n to harsha aur anand ka shabd sun padega, aur n dulhe va dulhain ka kyonki desh ujad hee ujad ho jaega.
yahova kee yah vanee haai, us samay yahooda ke rajao, hakimo, yajako, bhvishyadvktaon aur yarooshalem ke rahanevalon kee haaddiyan kabraen men se nikalakar,
soorya, chandrama aur akash ke sare ganon ke samhane faailai jaaengee kyonki ve unheen se praem rakhte, unheen kee seva karate, unheen ke peechhe chalate, aur unheen ke pas jaya karate aur unheen ko dandvata karate the aur n ve ikatthee kee jaaengee n kabra men rakhee jaaengee ve boomi ke upar khad ke saman padee rahengee.
tab is bure kul ke bache huae log un sab sthanon men jis men maain ne unhen nikal diya haai, jeevan se mratyu hee ko aadhaik chahenge, senaon ke yahova kee yahee vanee haai.
too un se yah bhee kah, yahova yon kahata haai ki jab manushy girate haain to kya fir naheen uttte?
maain ne dhyan dekar suna, parantu ye tteek naheen bolate in men se kisee ne apanee burai se pachhtakar naheen kaha, hay ! maain ne yah kya kiya haai? jaaisa ghaeda ladai men veg se daudta haai, vaaise hee in men se har aek jan apanee hee daud men daudta haai.
tum kyonkar kah sakate ho ki ham buddhiman haai, aur yahova kee dee hui vyapastha hamare sath haai? parantu unake shaastriayon ne usaka jootta vivaran likhkar usako joott bana diya haai.
buaddhiman laajjait ho gaa, ve vismait huae aur pakade gaae dekho, unhon ne yahova ke vachan ko nikamma jana haai, un men buaddhi kahan rahee?
is karan maain unakee striayon ko doosare purushaen ko aur unake khet doosare aadhaikaariyon ke vash men kar doonga, kyonaki chhotte se lekar bade tak ve sab ke sab lalachee haain kya bhavishyadvkta kya yajak, ve sab ke chhl se kam karate haain.
unhon ne, shaantai haai, shaantai aeesa kah kahakar meree praja ke ghaav ko upar hee upar changa kiya, parantu shaaantai kuchh bhee naheen haai.
kaya ve gharaanait kam karake lajjait hue? nahee, ve kuchh bhee lajjait naheen hua, ve laajjait hona janate hee naheen. is karan jab aur log neeche gire, tab ve bhee girenge jab unake dand ka samay aaega, tab ve bhee ttokar khakar girenge, yahova ka yahee vachan haai.
yahova kee sah bhee vanree haai, maain un sabhon ka ant kar doonga. n to unakee dakhlataon men dakh pai jaaengee, aur n anjeer ke praksha men anjeer varan unake patte bhee sookh jaaenge, aur jo kuchh maain ne unhen diya haai vah unake pas se jata rahega.
ham kyon chupa-chap baaitte haain? ao, ham chalakar gaddhvale nagaron men ikatthe nash ho jaaen kyonki hamara parameshvar yahova ham ko nash karana chahata haai, aur hamen vish peene ko diya haai kyonki ham ne yahova ke viruddh pap kiya haai.
ham shaantai kee batt johate the, parantu kuchh kalyan naheen mila, aur changai kee asha karate the, parantu ghabarana hee pada haai.
unake ghaedon ka faurrana dan se sun padta haai, aur balavant ghaedon ke hinaahinane ke shabd se sara desh kanp utta haai. unhon ne akar hamare desh ko aur jo kuchh us men haai, aur hamare nagar ko nivaasiyon samet nash kiya haai.
kyonaki dekho, maain tumhare beech men aeese sanp aur nag bhejoonga jin par mantra n chalega, aur ve tum ko dsenge, yahova kee yahee vanee haai.
hay ! hay ! is shaek kee dasha men mujhe shaaantai kahan se milegee? mera day bheetar hee bheetar tadpata haai !
mujhe apane logon kee chillahatt door ke desh se sunai detee haai kya yahova siyyon men naheen haain? kya usaka raja us men naheen? unhon ne kyon mujh ko apanee khodee hui mooraton aur paradesh kee vyarth vastuon ke dara kyon krodha dilaya haai?
kattnee ka samay beet gaya, fal todne kee tu bhee samapt ho gai, aur hamara uddhar naheen hua.
apane logon ke dukh se maain bhee dukhait hua, maain shaek ka paahirava pahine aati achambhe men ooba hoo.
kya gilad desh men kuchh balasan kee aushaadhai naheen? kya us men koi vaaidh naheen? yaadi haai, to mere logon ke ghaav kyon change naheen hue?
bhla hota, ki mera sir jal hee jal, aur meree ankhen asuon ka sota hotee, ki maain rat din apane mare huae logon ke liye rota rahata.
bhla hota ki mujhe jangal men battohiyon ka koi ttkaiab milata ki maain apane logon ko chhodkar vaheen chala jata ! kyonaki ve sab vyaabhaicharee haai, ve vishvasaghaaatiyon ka samaj haain.
apanee apanee jeebh ko ve dhanush kee nai joott holane ke liye taaiyar karate haai, aur desh men balavant to ho gaa, parantu sachchai ke liye naheen ve burai par burai baddhate jate haai, aur ve mujh ko janate hee nahee, yahova kee yahee vanee haai.
apane apane sangee se chaukas raho, apane bhai par bhee bhrosa n rakho kyonki sab bhai nishchay adnga marenge, aur har aek padosee lutarai karate firenge.
ve aek doosare ko ttgenge aur sach naheen bolenge unhon ne joott hee bolana seekha haai aur kuttlaita hee men paarishram karate haain.
tera nivas chhl ke beech haai chhl hee ke karan ve mera gyaan naheen chahate, yahova kee yahee vanee haai.
isaliye senaon ka yahova yon kahata haai, dek, maain unako tapakar parakoonga, kyonaki apanee praja ke karan maain un se aur kya kar sakata hoon?
unakee jeebh kal ke teer ke saman bedhanevalee haai, us se chhl kee baten nikalatee haain ve munh se to ek doosare se mel kee bat bolate haain par man hee man ek doosare kee ghaat men lage rahate haain.
kya maain aeesee baton ka dand n doon? yahova kee sah vanee haai, kya maain aeesee jati se apana palatta n loon?
maain pahadon ke liye ro utoonga aur shaek ka geet gaunga, aur jangal kee charaiyon ke liye vilap ka geet gaunga, kyonki ve aeese jal gaae haain ki koi un men se hokar naheen chalata, aur un men ddhor ka shabd bhee naheen sunai padta pashuu-pakshaee sab bhag gaae haain.
maain yarooshalem ko deeh hee deeh karake geedadon ka sthan banaunga aur yahooda ke nagaron ko aeesa ujad doonga ki un men koi n basega.
jo buaddhiman murush ho vah isaka bhed samajh le, aur jis ne yahova ke mukh se isaka karan suna ho vah bata de. desh ka nash kyon hua? kyon vah jangal kee nai aeesa jal gaya ki us men se hokar koi naheen chalata?
aur yahova ne kaha, kyonki unhon ne meree vyavastha ko jo maain ne unake age rakhee thee chhod diya aur n meree bat manee aur n usake anusar chale haai,
aur maain un logon ko aeesee jatiyon men titar bitar karoonga jinhen n to ve n unake purakha janate the aur jab tak unaka ant n ho jaae tab tak meree or se talavar unake peechhe padegee.
senaon ka yahova yon kahata haai, socho, aur vilap karanevaliyon ko bulao buddhiman striayon ko batalava bhejo
ve fauta karake ham logon ke liye shaek ka geet gaaen ki hamaree ankhon se ansoo bah chalen aur hamaree palaken jal bahaae.
siyyon se shaek ka yah geet sun padta haai, ham kaaise nash ho gaae ! ham kyon lajja men pad gaae haai, kyonki ham ko apana desh chhodna pada aur hamare ghar gira diae gaae haain.
isaliye, he striayo, yahova ka yah vachan suno, aur usakee yah agyaa mano tum apanee apanee bettyaien ko shaek ka geet, aur apanee apanee padosinon ko vilap ka geet sikhao.
kyonaki mratyu hamaree khaidkiyon se hokar hamare mahalon men ghaus ai haai, ki, hamaree sadkon men bachchon ko aur chaukon men javanon ko mitta de.
too kah, yahova yon kahata haai, manushyon kee lothen aeesee padee rahengee jaaisa khad khet ke upar, aur pooliyan kattnevale ke peechhe padee rahatee haai, aur unaka koi uttanevala n hoga.
yahova yon kahata haai, buddhiman apanee buaddhi par ghamand n kare, n veer apanee veerata par, t dhanee apane dhan par ghamand kare
parantu jo ghamand kare vah isee bat par ghamand kare, ki vah mujhe janata aur samajhta he, ki maain hee vah yahova hoo, jo prathvee par karuna, nyay aur dharma ke kam karata haai kyonaki maain inheen baton se prasann rahata hoo.
dekho, yahova kee yah vanee haai ki aeese din anevale haain ki jinaka khtana hua ho, unako khtanarahiton ke saman dand doonga,
arthata misiryo, yahoodiyo, aedomiyo, ammoniyo, moaabiyon ko, aur un reagistan ke nivaasiyon ke saman jo apane gal ke balon ko munda dalate haain kyonaki ye sab jatiyen to khtanarahit haai, aur israaael ka sara gharana bhee man men khtanaraahit haai.
jo nagaree logon se bhrapoor thee vah ab kaaisee akelee baaittee hui haai ! vah kyon aek vidhava ke saman ban gai? vah jo jatiyon kee draashtti men mahan aur praanton men ranee thee, ab kyon kar denevalee ho gai haai.
rat ko vah foott foott kar rotee haai, usake ansoo galon par ddhlakate haain usake sab yaron men se ab koi use shaaantai naheen deta usake sab mitraen ne us se vishvasaghaat kiya, aur usake shatra ban gaae haain.
yahooda dukh aur kattnai dasatv se bachane ke liye paradesh chalee gai parantu anyajatiyon men rahatee hui vah chaain naheen patee usake sab khdednevalon ne usakee saketee men use pakad liya haai.
siyyon ke marga vilap kar rahe haai, kyonki niyat pavan men koi naheen ata haai usake sab faattk sunasan pade haai, usake yajak karahate haain usakee kumaariyan shaekit haai, aur vah ap kattnai dukh bhog rahee haai.
usake draehee pradhaan ho gaa, usake shatra unnati kar rahe haai, kyonki yahova ne usake bahut se aparadhaen ke karan use dukh diya haai usake balabachchon ko shatra hank hank kar bandhauai men le gae.
siyyon kee putraee ka sara pratap jata raha haai. usake hakim aeese haarinon ke saman ho gaae haain jo kuchh charai naheen pate ve khdednevalon ke samhane se balaheen hokar bhagate haain.
yarooshalem ne, in dakh bhre aur sankatt ke dinon me, jab usake log draeahiyon ke hath men pade aur usaka koi yahayak n raha, tab apanee sab manabhavanee vastuon ko jo praacheenakal se usakee thee, smaran kiya haai. usake draeahiyon ne usako ujada dekhkar tttthon men udaya haai.
yarooshalem ne bada pap kiya, isaliye vah ashuuddh sree see ho gai haai jitane usaka adar karate the ve usaka niradar karate haai, kyonki unhon ne usakee nangai dekhee haai ha, vah karahatee hui munh faer letee haai.
usakee ashuuddhata usake vasr par haai us ne apane ant ka smaran n rakha isaaliye vah bhyankar reeti se girai gai, aur koi use shaantai naieen deta haai. he yahova, mere dukh par drashtti kar, kyonaki shatra mere viruddh safal hua haai !
draehiyon ne usakee sab manabhavanee vastuon par hath baddhaya haai ha, anyajaatiyon ko, jinake vishay men too ne agyaa dee thee ki ve teree sabha men bhagee n hone paaengee, unako us ne tere pavitrasthan men ghausa hua dekha haai.
usake sab nivasee karahate huae bhojanavastu ddoonddh rahe haain unhon ne apana praan bachan ke liaee apanee manabhavanee vastuen bechakar bhojan mol liya haai. he yahova, drashtti kar, aur dhyan se dek, kyonaki maain tuchchh ho gai hoo.
he sab battohiyo, kya tumhen is bat kee kuchh bhee chinta naheen? drashtti karake dekho, kya mere dukh se baddhkar koi aur peeda haai jo yahova ne apane krodha ke din mujh par dal dee haai?
us ne upar se meree haaddiyon men ag lagai haai, aur ve us se bhsm ho gai us ne mere paairon ke liye jal lagaya, aur mujh ko ulatta faer diya haai us ne aeesa kiya ki maain tyagee hui see aur rog se lagatar nirbal rahatee hoo.
us ne jooae kee rassaiyon kee nai mere aparadhaen ko apane hath se kasa haai us ne unhen battkar meree gardan par chaddhaya, aur mera bal ghatta diya haai jinaka maain samhana bhee naheen kar sakatee, unheen ke vash men yahova ne mujhe kar diya haai.
yahova ne mere sab parakramee purushaen ko tuchchh jana us ne niyat parva ka prachar karake logon ko mere viruddh bulaya ki mere javanon ko pees dalen yahooda kee kumaree kanya ko yahova ne mano kolhoo men pera haai.
in baton ke karan maain rotee hoo meree ankhon se ansoo kee dhaara bahatee rahatee haai kyonki jis shaaantaidata ke karan mera jee hara bhra ho jata tha, vah mujh se door ho gaya mere ladkebale akele ho gaa, kyonki shatra prabal hua haai.
siyyon hath faailaae huae haai, use koi shaaantai naheen deta yahova ne yakoob ke vishay men yah agyaa dee haai ki usake charon or ke nivasee usake draehee ho jaaen yarooshalem unake beech ashuuddh sree ke saman ho gai haai.
yahova sachchai par haai, kyonaki maain ne usakee agyaa ka ullanghan kiya haai he sab logo, suno, aur meree peeda ko dekho ! mere kumar aur kumariyan bandhauai men chalee gai haain.
unhon ne suna haai ki maain karahatee hoo, parantu koi mujhe shaantai naheen deta. mere sab shatrauon ne meree vipaattai ka samachar suna haai ve is se hashairt ho gaae ki too hee ne yah kiya haai. parantu jis din kee charcha too ne prachar karake sunai haai usako too dikha, tab ve bhee mere saman ho jaenge.
unakee saree dushttta kee or draashtti kara aur jaaisa mere sare aparadhaen ke karan too ne mujhe dand diya, vaaisa hee unako bhee dand de kyonki maain bahut hee karahatee hoo, aur mera day rog se nirbal ho gaya haai.
yahova ne siyyon kee putraee ko kis prakar apane kop ke badalon se ddhanp diya haai ! us ne israaael kee shaebha ko akash se dharatee par pattk diya aur kop ke din apane panvon kee chaukee ko smaran naheen kiya.
yahova ne yakoob kee sab baastaiyon ko nitturata se nashtt kiya haai us ne rosh men akar yahooda kee putraee ke draddh gaddhon ko ddhakar mittee men mila diya haai us ne hakimon samet rajy ko apavitra ttharaya haai.
us ne krodha men akar israael ke seeng ko jad se katt dala haai us ne shatra ke samhane unakee sahayata karane se apana daahina hath kheench liya he us ne charon or bhsm karatee hui lau kee nai yakoob ko jala diya haai.
us ne shatra banakar dhanush chaddhaya, aur vaairee banakar daahina hath baddhaae huae khda haai aur jitane dekhne men manabhavane the, un sab ko us ne ghaat kiya siyyon kee putraee ke tamboo par us ne ag kee nai apanee jalajalahatt bhdka dee haai.
yahova shatra ban gaya, us ne israaael ko nigal liya usake sare bhvanon ko us ne mitta diya, aur usake draddh gaddhon ko nashtt kar dala haai aur yahooda kee putraee ka dona-peettna bahut baddhay haai.
us ne apana mandp baree ke machan kee nai achanak gira diya, apane milapasthan ko us ne nash kiya haai yahova ne siyyon men niyat varvar aur vishraamadin donon ko bhula diya haai, aur apane bhdke huae kop se raja aur sajak donon ka tiraskar kiya haai.
yahova ne apanee vedee man se utar dee, aur apana kaavitrasthan apaman ke sath taj diya haai usake bhvanon kee bheeton ko us ne shatrauon ke vash men kar diya yahova ke bhvan men unhon ne aeesa kolahal machaya ki mano niyat varsha ka din ho.
yahova ne siyyon kee kumaree kee shaharapanah tod dalane ko ttana tha us ne doree dalee aur apana hath use nash karane se naheen kheencha us ne kile aur shaharapanah donon se vilap karavaya, ve donon aek sath giraae gaae haain.
usake faattk boomi men dhay gaae haai, unake bedon ko us ne todkar nash kiya. usake raja aur hakim anyajaatiyon men rahane ke karan vyavastharaahit ho gaae haai, aur usake bhvishyadvkta yahova se darshan naheen pate haain.
siyyon kee putraee ke puraniye boomi par chupachap baaitte haain unhon ne apane sir par dhool udai aur ttatt ka faentta bandha haai yarooshalem kee koomaariyon ne apana apana sir boomi tak jhukaya haai.
meree ankhen ansoo bahate bahate rah gai haain meree antadiyan aeenttee jatee haain mere logon kee putraee ke vinash ke karan mera kaleja fatt gaya haai, kyonki bachche varan doodhaapiuve bachche bhee nagar ke chaukon me moochchhirt hote haain.
ve apanee apanee mata se rokar kahate haai, ann aur dakhmadha kahan haain? ve nagar ke chaukon men ghaayal kiae huae manushy kee nai moochchhirt hokar apane praan apanee apanee mata kee god men chhodte haain.
he yarooshalem kee putrae, maain tujh se kya kahoon? maain teree upama kis se doon? he siyyon kee kumaree kanya, maain kaun see vastu tere saman ttharakar tujhe shaantai doon? kyonki tera dukh samudra sa apar haai tujhe kaun changa kar sakata haai?
tere bhvishyadvktaon ne darshan ka dava karake tujh se vyarth aur moorkhta kee baten kahee haain unhon ne tera adharma pragatt naheen kiya, naheen to teree vradhauai n hone patee parantu unhon ne tujhe vyarth ke aur jootte vachan bataae. jo tere liye desh se nikal diae jane ka karan hue.
sab battohee tujh par talee bajate haain ve yarooshalem kee putraee par yah kahakar talee bajate aur sir hilate haai, kya yah vahee nagaree haai jise paramasundaree aur saree prathvee ke harsha ka karan kahate the?
tere sab shatrauon ne tujh par munh pasara haai, ve talee bajate aur dant peesate haai, ve kahate haai, ham use nigal gaae haain ! jis din kee batt ham johate the, vah yahee haai, vah ham ko mil gaya, ham usako dekh chuke haain !
yahova ne jo kuchh ttana tha vahee kiya bhee haai, jo vachan vah praacheenakal se kahata aya haai vahee us ne poora bhee kiya haai us ne nitturata se tujhe ddha diya haai, us ne shatrauon ko tujh par anandait kiya, aur tere draeahiyon ke seeng ko uncha kiya he.
ve prabhu kee or tan man se pukarate haain ! he siyyon kee kumaree kee shaharapanaha, apane ansoo rat din nadee kee nai bahatee rah ! taanik bhee vishraam n le, n teree ankh kee putalee chaain le !
rat ke har pahar ke arambh men uttkar chillaya kar ! prabhu ke sammukh apane man kee baton ko ghaara kee nai undel ! tere balabachche jo har aek sadk ke sire par bookh ke karan moochchhirt ho rahe haai, unake praan ke nimitt apane hath usakee or faaila.
he yahova draashtti kar, aur dhyan se dekh ki too ne yah sab dukh kis ko diya haai? kya striayan apana fal arthata apanee god ke bachchon ko kha dalen? he prabhu, kya yajak aur bhvishyadvkta tere pavitrasthan men ghaat kiae jaaen?
sadkon men ladke aur booddhe donon boomi par pade haain meree kumariyan aur javan log talavar se gir gaae haain too ne kop karane ke din unhen ghaat kiya too ne nitturata ke sath unaka vadha kiya haai.
too ne mere bhy ke karanon ke niyat parva kee bheed ke saman charon or se bulaya haai aur yahova ke kop ke din n to koi bhag nikala aur n koi bach raha haai jin ko maain ne god men liya aur pala-posakar baddhaya tha, mere shatra ne unaka ant kar dala haai.
usake rosh kee chhdee se dukh bhoganevala purush maain hee hoon
vah mujhe le jakar ujiyale men nahee, andhiayare hee men chalata haai
usaka hath din bhr mere hee viruddh uttta rahata haai.
us ne mera mans aur chamada gala diya haai, aur meree haaddiyon ko tod diya haai
us ne mujhe bahut din ke mare huae logon ke saman andhore sthanon men basa diya haai.
maain chilla chillake dohai deta hoo, taubhee vah meree praarthta naheen sunata
mere magan ko us ne gaddhe huae patthron se rok rakha haai, meree dgaron ko us ne tteddhee kar diya haai.
vah mere liye ghaat men baaitte huae reechh aur ghaat lagaae huae sinh ke saman haai
us ne mujhe mere magan se bhula diya, aur mujhe faad dala us ne mujh ko ujad diya haai.
us ne dhanush chaddhakar mujhe apane teer ka nishaana banaya haai.
us ne apanee teeron se mere day ko bedha diya haai
sab log mujh par hansate haain aur din bhr mujh par ddhalakar gaeet gate haai,
us ne mujhe kattnai dukh se bhr diya, aur nagadauna pilakar trapt kiya haai.
us ne mere danton ko kankaree se tod dala, aur mujhe rakh se ddhanp diya haai
aur mujh ko man se utarakar kushal se raahit kiya haai maain kalyan bool gaya hoo
isaliaee maain ne kaha, mera bal nash hua, aur meree ash jo yahova par thee, vah toott gai haai.
mera dukh aur mara mara firana, mera nagadaune aura-aur vish ka peena smaran kar !
maain unheen par sochata rahata hoo, is se mera praan ddhla jata haai.
parantu maain yah smaran karata hoo, iseealiye mujhe aasha haai
ham mitt naheen gaae yah yahova kee mahakaruna ka fal haai, kyonaki usakee daya amar haai.
praati bhor vah nai hotee rahatee haai teree sachchai mahan haai.
mere man ne kaha, yahova mera bhag haai, is karan maain us men asha rakoonga.
jo yahova kee batt johate aur usake pas jate haai, unake liye yahova bhla haai.
yahova se uddhar pane kee asha rakhkar chupachap rahana bhla haai.
purush ke liye javanee men jooa uttana bhla haai.
vah yah janakar akela chupachap rahe, ki parameshvar hee ne us par yah bojh dala haai
vah apana munh dhool men rakhe, kaya jane is men kuchh asha ho
vah apana gal apane maranevale kee or faere, aur namadharai sahata rahe.
kyonaki prabhu man se sarvada utare naheen rahata,
chahe vah dukh bhee de, taubhee apanee karuna kee bahutayat ke karan vah daya bhee karata haai
kyonaki vah manushyon ko apane man se n to dabata haai aur n dukh deta haai.
prathvee bhr ke bandhauon ko panv ke tale daalit karana,
aur kisee manushy ka mukama bigadna, in teen kamon ko yahova dekh naheen sakata.
yaadi yahova ne agyaa n dee ho, tab kaun haai ki vachan kahe aur vah poora ho jaae?
so jeeavit manushy kyon kudkudaae? aur purush apane pap ke dand ko kyon bura mane?
ham apane chalachalan ko dhyan se parakhe, aur yahova kee or firen !
ham svargavasee parameshvar kee or man lagaaen aur hath faailaaen aur kahen
ham ne to aparadha aur balava kiya haai, aur too ne kshama naheen kiya.
tera kop ham par haai, too hamare peechhe pada haai, too ne bina taras khaae ghaat kiya haai.
too ne apane ko megha se ghor liya haai ki tujh tak praarthna n pahunch sake.
too ne ham ko jaati jati ke logon ke beech men kooda-karkatt sa ttharaya haai.
hamare sab shatrauon ne ham par apana apana munh faailaya haai
bhy aur gadha, ujad aur vinasha, ham par a pade haain
meree ankhon se meree praja kee putraee ke vinash ke karan jal kee dhaaraaen bah rahee haai.
meree ankh se lagatar ansoo bahate rahenge,
jab tak yahova svarga se meree or n dekhe
apanee nagaree kee sab striayon ka hal dekhne par mera dukh baddhta haai.
jo vyarth mere shatra bane haai, unhon ne nirdayata se chidiya ke saman mera aher kiya haai
