usee din maain ne un se yah bhee shapath khai, ki maain tum ko misra desh se nikalakar ek desh men pahunchaunga, jise maain ne tumhare liye chun liya haai vah sab deshaen ka shairomanai haai, aur us men doodha aur madha kee dharaen bahatee haain.
