jaaise dakuon ke dal kisee kee ghaat men baaittte haai, vaaise hee yajakon ka dal shakem ke marga men vadha karata haai, varan unhon ne mahapap bhee kiya haai.
israael ke gharane men maain ne roaen khde hone ka karan dekha haai us men aepraaim ka chhnaiala aur israael kee ashuuddhta pai jatee haai..
aur he yahooda, jab maain apanee praja ko bandhauai se lautta le aunga, us samay ke liye tere nimitt bhee badala ttharaya hua haai..
jab maain israael ko changa karata hoon tab aepraaim ka adharma aur shaemaron kee buraiyan pragatt ho jatee haain ve chhl se kam karate haai, chor bheetar ghausata, aur dakuon ka dal bahar chheen leta haai.
