is prakar raja ne praja kee binatee n manee isaka karan yah haai, ki jo vachan yahova ne shaeelovasee aahiyyah ke dara nabat ke putra yarobam se kaha tha, usako poora karane ke liye parameshvar ne aeesa hee ttharaya tha.
jab sab israaaeliyon ne dekha ki raja hamaree naheen sunata, tab ve bole ki daud ke sath hamara kya ansha? hamara to yishau ke putra men koi bhag naheen haai. he israaaeliyo, apane apane dere ko chale jao. ab he daud, apane hee gharane kee chinta kara.
tab sab israaaelee apane dere ko chale gaae. keval jitane israaaelee yahooda ke nagaron men base huae the, unheen par rahoobiyam rajy karata raha.
tab raja rahoobiyam ne hadoram ko jo sab begaron par aadhaikaree tha bhej diya, aur israaaeliyon ne usako patthravah kiya aur vah mar gaya. tab rahoobiyam fauta se apane rath par chaddhkar, yarooshalem ko bhag gaya.
yon israaael daud ke gharane se fir gaya aur aj tak fira hua haai.
jab rahoobiyam yarooshalem ko aya, tab us ne yahooda aur binyameen ke gharane ko jo milakar aek lakh assee hajar achchhe yoddha the ikattha kiya, ki israaael ke sath yuddh karen jis se rajy rahoobiyam ke vash men fir a jaae.
tab yahova ka yah vachan parameshvar ke bhkt shamayah ke pas pahuncha,
ki yahooda ke raja sulaaiman ke putra rahoobiyam se aur yahooda aur binyameen ke sab israaaeliyon se kah,
yahova yon kahata haai, ki apane bhaiyon par chaddhai karake yuddh n karo. tum apane apane ghar lautt jao, kyonki yah bat meree hee or se hui haai. yahova ke ye vachan manakar, ve yarobam par bina chaddhai kiae lautt gaae.
so rahoobiyam yarooshalem men rahane laga, aur yahooda men bachav ke liye ye nagar draddh kia,
arthata betalehem, aetam, takoa,
betsoor, soko, adullama.
gat, maresha, jeepa.
adoraaim, lakeesha, ajeka.
sora, ayyalot aur hebraen jo yahooda aur binyameen men haai, draddh kiya.
aur us ne draddh nagaron ko aur bhee draddh karake un men pradhaan ttharaa, aur bhoejan vastu aur tel aur dakhmadha ke bhndar rakhva diae.
fir aek aek nagar men us ne ddhalen aur bhale rakhvakar unako atyant draddh kar diya. yahooda aur binyameen to usake the.
aur sare israaael ke yajak aur leveey bhee apane sab desh se uttkar usake pas gaae.
yon leveey apanee charaiyon aur nij boomi chhodkar, yahooda aur yarooshalem men aa, kyonki yarobam aur usake putraen ne unako nikal diya tha ki ve yahova ke liye yajak ka kam n karen.
aur us ne unche sthanon aur bakaron aur apane banaae huae bachhdon ke liye, apanee or se yajak tthara liae.
aur unhon ne yahooda ka rajy sthiar kiya aur sulaaiman ke putra rahoobiyam ko teen varsha tak draddh karaya, kyonaki teen varsha tak ve daud aur sulaaiman kee leek par chalate rahe.
aur rahoobiyam ne aek sree ko byah liya, arthata mahalat ko jisaka pita daud ka putra yareemot aur mata yishau ke putra aeleeab kee bettee abeehaail thee.
aur us se yoosha, shamaryah aur jaham nam putra utpann huae.
aur usake bad us ne abashalom kee bettee maka ko byah liya, aur us se aabiyyah, atte, jeeja aur shalomeet utpann hue.
rahoobiyam ne attarah raaniyan byah leen aur satt rakhealiyan rakhee, aur usake attais bette aur satt beattyaian utpann hui. abashalom kee naatinee maka se vah apanee sab raniyon aur rakheliyon se aadhaik praem rakhta tha
so rahoobiyam ne maka ke bette aabiyyah ko mukhy aur sab bhaiyon men pradhaan is manasa se tthara diya, ki use raja banaae.
aur vah samajh boojhkar kam karata tha, aur us ne apane sab putraen ko alag alag karake yahooda aur binyameen ke sab dashaen ke sab gaddhvale nagaron men tthara diya aur unhen bhojan vastu bahutayat se dee, aur unake liye bahut see striayan ddoonddhee.
parantu jab rahoobiyam ka rajy draddh ho gaya, aur vah ap sthiar ho gaya, tab us ne aur usake sath sare israaael ne yahova kee yyavastha ko tyag diya.
unhon ne jo yahova se vishvasaghaat kiya, us karan raja rahoobiyam ke panchapen varsha men misra ke raja shaeeshak ne,
aur us ne yahooda ke gaddhvale nagaron ko le liya, aur yarooshalem tak aya.
tab shamayah nabee rahoobiyam aur yahooda ke hakimon ke pas jo shaeeshak ke dr ke mare yarooshalem men iatthe huae the, akar kahane laga, yahova yon kahata haai, ki tum ne mujh ko chhod diya haai, isaaliye maain ne tum ko chhodkar shaeeshak ke hath men kar diya haai.
tab israaael ke hakim aur raja deen ho gaa, aur kaha, yahova dhama haai.
jab yahova ne dekha ki ve deen huae haai, tab yahova ka yah vachan shamayah ke pas pahuncha ki ve deen ho gaae haai, maain unako nashtt n karoonga maain unaka kuchh bachav karoonga, aur meree jalajalahatt shaeeshak ke dara yarooshalem par n bhdkegee.
taubhee ve usake adhaeen to rahenge, taaki ve meree aur desh desh ke rajyon kee bhee seva jan len.
tab misra ka raja shaeeshak yarooshalem par chaddhai karake yahova ke bhvan kee anamol vastuaen aur rajabhvan kee anamol vastuen utta le gaya. vah sab kuchh utta le gaya, aur sone kee jo faariyan sulaaiman ne banai thee, unako bhee vah le gaya.
tab raja rahoobiyam ne unake badale peetal kee ddhalen banavai aur unhen paharuon ke pradhaanon ke hath saunp diya, jo rajabhvan ke dar kee rakhvalee karate the.
aur jab jab raja yahova ke bhvan men jata, tab tab paharuae akar unhen utta le chalate, aur fir paharuon kee kottree men lauttakar rakh dete the.
jab rahoobiyam deen hua, tab yahova ka krodha us par se utar gaya, aur us ne usaka poora vinash n kiya aur yahooda men achchhe gun bhee the.
so raja rahoobiyam yarooshalem men draddh hokar rajy karata raha. jab rahoobiyam rajy karane laga, tab aekanalees varsha kee ayu ka tha, aur yarooshalem men arthata us nagar me, jise yahova ne apana nam banaae rakhne ke liye israaael ke sare gotra men se chun liya tha, satrah varsha tak rajy karata raha. usakee mata ka nam nama tha, jo ammonee stree thee.
us ne vah karma kiya jo bura haai, arthata us ne apane man ko yahova kee khoj men n lagaya.
aadi se ant tak rahoobiyam ke kam kya shamayah nabee aur io dasha kee pustakon men vanshaavaliyon kee reeati par naheen likhe haain? rahoobiyam aur yarobam ke beech to ladai sada hotee rahee.
aur rahoobiyam apane purakhaon ke sang so gaya aur daudapur men usako mittee dee gai. aur usaka putra aabiyyah usake sthan par rajy karane laga.
yarobam ke attarahaven varsha men abiyyah yahooda par rajy karane laga.
vah teen varsha tak yarooshalem men rajy karata raha, aur usakee mata ka nam meekayah tha jo gibavasee ureeael kee bettee thee. aur aabiyyah aur yarobam ke beech men ladai hai.
aabiyyah ne to bade yoddhaon ka dal, arthata char lakh chhntte huae purush lekar ladne ke liye panti bandhaai, aur yarobam ne att lakh chhntte huae purush jo aede shooraveer the, lekar usake viruddh panti bandhaai.
tab aabiyyah samaraaim nam pahad par, jo aepraaim ke pahadee desh men haai, khda hokar kahane laga, he yarobam, he sab israaaeliyo, meree suno.
kya tum ko n janana chaahia, ki israaael ke parameshvar yahova ne lonavalee vacha bandhakar daud ko aur usake vansh ko israaael ka rajy sada ke liye de diya haai.
taubhee nabat ka putra yarobam jo daud ke putra sulaaiman ka karmacharee tha, vah apane svamee ke viruddh utta haai.
aur ab tum sochate ho ki ham yahova ke rajy ka samhana karenge, jo daud kee santan ke hath men haai, kyonaki tum sab milakar bada samaj ban gaae ho aur tumhare pas ve sone ke bachhde bhee haain jinhen yarobam ne tumhare devata hone ke liye banavaya.
kya tum ne yahova ke yajakon ko, arthata haroon kee santan aur leaviyon ko nikalakar desh desh ke logon kee nai yajak niyukt naheen kar liae? jo koi aek bachhda aur sat meddhe apana sanskar karane ko le ata, to unaka yajak ho jata haai jo ishvar naheen haai.
parantu ham logon ka parameshvar yahova haai aur ham ne usako naheen tyaga, aur hamare pas yahova kee seva tthal karanevale yajak haroon kee santan aur apane apane kam men lage huae leveey haain.
aur ve nity savere aur sanjh ko yahova ke liye homabaali aur sugandhadrayy ka dhoop jalate haai, aur shooddh mej par bhentt kee rottee sajate aur sone kee deevatt aur usake deepak sanjh-sanjh ko jalate haain ham to apane parameshvar yahova kee agyaaon ko manate rahate haai, parantu tum ne usako tyag diya haai.
aur dekho, hamare sang hamara pradhaan parameshvar haai, aur usake yajak tumhare viruddh sans vandhakar foonkane ko turahiyan liye huae bhee hamare sath haain. he israaaeliyo apane poorvajon ke parameshvar yahova se mat lado, kyonki tum kratarth n hoge.
parantu yarobam ne ghaatakon ko unake peechhe bhej diya, ve to yahooda ke samhane the, aur ghaatak unake peechhe the.
aur jab yahoodiyon ne peechhe ko munh faera, to dekha ki hamare age aur peechhe donon or se ladai honevalee haai tab unhon ne yahova kee dohai dee, aur yajak turahiyon ko foonkane lage.
tab yahoodee purushaen ne jay jayakar kiya, aur jab yahoodee purushaen ne jay jayakar kiya, tab parameshvar ne aabiyyah aur yahooda ke samhane, yarobam aur sare israaaeliyon ko mara.
aur israaaelee yahooda ke samhane se bhage, aur parameshvar ne unhen unake hath men kar diya.
aur aabiyyah aur usakee praja ne unhen badee mar se mara, yahan tak ki israaael men se panch lakh chhntte huae purush mare gaae.
tab aabiyyah ne yarobam ka peechha karake us se betel, yashaana aur aepraen nagaron aur unake ganvon ko le liya.
aur aabiyyah ke jeevan bhr yarobam fir samath n hua nidan yahova ne usako aeesa mara ki vah mar gaya.
parantu abiyyah aur bhee samath ho gaya aur chaudah striayan byah leen jin se bais bette aur solah beattyaian utpann hui.
aur aabiyyah ke kam aur usakee chal chalan, aur usake vachan, io nabee kee katha men likhe haain.
nidan aabiyyah apane purakhaon ke sang so gaya, aur usako daudapur men mittee dee gai aur usaka putra asa usake sthan par rajy karane laga. isake dinon men das varsha tak desh men chaain raha.
aur asa ne vahee kiya jo usake parameshvar yahova kee draashtti men achchha aur tteek tha.
us ne to parai veadiyon ko aur unche sthanon ko door kiya, aur latton ko tudva dala, aur ashora nam mooraton ko tod dala.
aur yahoodiyon ko agyaa dee ki apane poorvajon ke parameshvar yahova kee khoj karen aur yyavastha aur agyaa ko manon.
aur us ne unche sthanon aur soorya kee praatimaon ko yahooda ke sab nagaron men se door kiya, aur usake samhane rajy men chaain raha.
aur us ne yahooda men gaddhvale nagar basaa, kyonki desh men chaain raha. aur un barason men use kisee se ladai n karanee padee kyonaki yahova ne use vishraam diya tha.
us ne yahoodiyon se kaha, ao ham in nagaron ko basaen aur unake charon or shaharapanah, gaddh aur faattkon ke palle aur bede banaen desh ab tak hamare samhane pada haai, kyonki ham ne, apane parameshvar yahova kee khoj kee haai hamane usakee khoj kee aur us ne hamako charon or se vishraam diya haai. tab unhon ne un nagaron ko basaya aur kratarth hue.
fir asa ke pas ddhal aur bachh rakhnevalon kee aek sena thee, arthata yahooda men se to teen lakh purush aur binyameen men se faree rakhnevale aur dhanudhararee do lakh assee hajar ye sab shooraveer the.
aur unake viruddh das lakh purushaen kee sena aur teen sau rath liye huae jerah nam aek kooshaee nikala aur maresha tak a gaya.
tab asa usaka samhana karane ko chala aur maresha ke nikatt sapata nam tarai men yuddh kee panti bandhaee gai.
tab asa ne apane parameshvar yahova kee yon dohai dee, ki he yahova ! jaaise too samath kee sahayata kar sakata haai, vaaise hee shaaktaiheen kee bhee he hamare parameshvar yahova ! hamaree sahayata kar, kyonki hamara bhrosa tujhee par haai aur tere nam ka bhrosa karake ham is bheed ke viruddh aae haain. he yahova, too hamara parameshvar haai manushy tujh par prabal n hone paaega.
tab yahova ne kooshaiyon ko asa aur yahoodiyon ke samhane mara aur kooshaee bhag gaae.
aur asa aur usake sang ke logon ne unaka peechha garar tak kiya, aur itane kooshaee mare gaa, ki ve fir sir n utta sake kyonaki ve yahova aur usakee sena se har gaa, aur yahoodee bahut sa loott le gaae.
aur unhon ne garar ke as pas ke sab nagaron ko mar liya, kyonaki yahova ka bhy unake rahanevalon ke man men sama gaya aur unhon ne un nagaron ko loott liya, kyonaki un men bahut sa dhan tha.
tab parameshvar ka atma oded ke putra ajaryah men sama gaya,
aur vah asa se bhentt karane nikala, aur us se kaha, he asa, aur he sare yahooda aur binyameen meree suno, jab tak tum yahova ke sang rahoge tab tak vah tumhare sang rahega aur yadi tum usakee khoj men lage raho, tab to vah tum se mila karega, parantu yadi tum usako tyag doge to vah bhee tum ko tyag dega.
bahut din israaael bina saty parameshvar ke aur bina sikhanevale yajak ke aur bina byavastha ke raha.
parantu jab jab ve sankatt men padkar israaael ke parameshvar yahova kee or fire aur usako ddoonddha, tab tab vah unako mila.
us samay n to janevale ko kuchh shaanti hotee thee, aur n anevale ko, varan sare desh ke sab nivaasiyon men bada hee kolahal hota tha.
aur jaati se jati aur tagar se nagar choor kiae jate the, kyonaki parameshvar nana prakar ka kashtt dekar unhen ghabara deta tha.
parantu tum log hiyab bandhae aur tumhare hath ddheele n pade, kyonki tumhare kam ka badala milega.
jab asa ne ye vachan aur oded nabee kee naboovat sunee, tab us ne hiyab bandhakar yahooda aur binyameen ke sare desh men se, aur un nagaron men se bhee jo us ne aepraaim ke pahadee desh men le liye the, sab ghainaunee vastuen door kee, aur yahova kee jo vedee yahova ke osare ke samhane thee, usako naye sire se banaya.
aur us ne sare yahooda aur binyameen ko, aur aepraaim, manashsho aur shaimon men se jo log usake sang rahate the, unako ikattha kiya, kyonaki ve yah dekhkar ki usaka parameshvar yahova usake sang rahata haai, israaael men se usake pas bahut se chale aae the.
asa ke rajy ke pandrahaven varsha ke teesare maheene men ve yarooshalem men iatthe hue.
aur usee samay unhon ne us loott men se jo ve le aae the, sat sau baail aur sat hajar bhed-bakaariya, yahova ko bali karake chaddhai.
aur kya bada, kya chhotta, kya stree, kya purusha, jo koi israaael ke parameshvar yahova kee khoj n kare, vah mar dala jaaega.
aur unhon ne jay jayakar ke sath turahiyan aur narasinge bajate huae unche shabd se yahova kee shapath khai.
aur yah shapath khakar sab yahoodee anaandait hua, kyonki unhon ne apane sare man se shapatha khai aur badee aabhailasha se usako ddoonddha aur vah unako mila, aur yahova ne charon or se unhen vishraam diya.
baran asa raja kee mata maka jis ne ashora ke pas rakhne ke liae aek ghainaunee moorat banai, usako us ne rajamata ke pad se utar diya, aur asa ne usakee moorat kattkar pees dalee aur kidraen nale men foonk dee.
unche sthan to israaealiyon men se n ddhaae gaa, taubhee asa ka man jeevan bhr tishkapatt raha.
aur us ne jo sona chandee, aur patra usake pita ne arpan kiae the, aur jo us ne ap arpan kiae the, unako parameshvar ke bhvan men pahancha diya.
aur raja asa ke rajy ke paainteesaven varsha tak fir ladai n hui.
asa ke rajy ke chhtteesaven varsha men israaael ke raja basha ne yahooda par chaddhai kee aur rama ko isaaliye draddh kiya, ki yahooda ke raja asa ke pas koi ane jane n paae.
tab as ne yahova ke bhvan aur rajabhvan ke bhndaron men se chandee-sona nikal daamishkavasee aram ke raja benhadad ke pas doot bhejakar yah kaha,
ki jaaise mere-tere pita ke beech vaaise hee mere-tere beech bhee vacha bandho dekh maain tere pas chandee-sona bhejata hoo, isaaliye a, israaael ke raja basha ke sath kee apanee vacha ko tod de, taki vah mujh se door ho.
benhadad ne raja asa kee yah bat manakar, apane dalon ke pradhaanon se israaaelee nagaron par chaddhai karavakar iyyon, dan, abelmaaim aur naptalee ke sab bhndaravale nagaron ko jeet liya.
yah sunakar basha ne rama ko draddh karana chhod diya, aur apana vah kam band kara diya.
tab raja asa ne poore yahooda desh ko sath liya aur rama ke patthron aur lakadee ko, jin se basa kam karata tha, utta le gaya, aur un se us ne geva, aur mispa ko draddh kiya.
us samay hananee dasha yahooda ke raja asa ke pas jakar kahane laga, too ne jo apane parameshvar yahova par bhrosa nahee rakha varan aram ke raja hee par bhrosa rakha haai, is karan aram ke raja kee sena tere hath se bach gai haai.
kya kooshaiyon aur loobiyon kee sena badee n thee, aur kya us men bahut hee rat, aur savar n thee? taubhee too ne yahova par bhrosa rakha tha, is karan us ne unako tere hath men kar diya.
dek, yahova kee drashtti saree prathvee par isaliye firatee rahatee haai ki jinaka man usakee or nishkamatt rahata haai, unakee sahayata men vah apana samarth dikhaae. toone yah kam moorkhta se kiya haai, isaaliye ab se too ladaiyon me fansa rahega.
tab asa dasha par krodhait hua aur use katt men ttonkava diya, kyonaki vahausakee aeesee bat ke karan us par krodhait tha. aur usee samay se asa praja ke kuchh logon ko peesane bhee laga.
