aur jab yehoo ahab ke gharane ko dand de raha tha, tab usako yahooda ke hakim aur ahajyah ke bhteeje jo ahajyah ke tthaluae the, mile, aur us ne unako ghaat kiya.
jab ahajyah kee mata atalyah ne dekh ki mera putra mar gaya, tab us ne uttkar yahooda ke gharane ke sare rajavansh ko nash kiya.
parantu yahoshavat jo raja kee bettee thee, us ne ahajyah ke putra yoash ko ghaat honevale rajakumaron ke beech se churakar dhaai samet bichhaune rakhne kee kottree men chhpai diya. is prakar raja yahoram kee bettee yahoshavat jo yahoyada yajak kee sree aur ahajyah kee bahin thee, us ne yoash ko atalyah se aeesa chhpai rakha ki vah use mar dalane n pai.
aur vah usake pas parameshvar ke bhvan men chh varsha chhpai raha, itane dinon tak atalyah desh par rajy karatee rahee.
sataven varsha men yahoyada ne hiyab bandhakar yaroham ke putra ajaryah, yahohanan ke putra ishvaael, obed ke putra ajaryah, adayah ke putra maseyah aur jikree ke putra baleeshapat, in shatapatiyon se vacha bandhaee.
tab ve yahooda men ghoomakar yahooda ke sab nagaron men se leaviyon ko aur israaael ke pitaron ke gharanon ke mukhy mukhy purushaen ko ikattha karake yarooshalem ko le aae.
aur us saree maaedlee ne parameshvar ke bhvan men raja ke sath vacha bandhae, aur yahoyada ne un se kaha, suno, yah rajakumar rajy karega jaaise ki yahova ne daud ke vansh ke vishay kaha haai.
to tum aek kam karo, arthata tum yajakon aur leviyon kee aek tihai log jo vishraamadin ko anevale ho, ve darapalee kare,
aur aek tihai log rajabhvan men rahen aur aek tihai log nev ke faattk ke pas rahen aur sab log yahova ke bhvan ke anganon men rahen.
parantu yajakon aur seva tthal karanevale leviyon ko chhod aur koi yahova ke bhvan ke bheetar n ane paae ve to bheetar aae, kyonki ve pavitra haain parantu sab log yahova ke bhvan kee chaukasee karen.
aur leveey log apane apane hath men hathaiyar liye huae raja ke charon or rahen aur jo koi bhvan ke bheetar ghause, vah mar dala jaae. aur tum raja ke ate jate usake sath rahana.
yahoyada yajak kee in sab agyaaon ke anusar leaviyon aur sab yahoodiyon ne kiya. unhon ne vishraamadin ko anevale aur vishraamadin ko janevale donon dalon ke, apane apane janon ko apane sath kar liya, kyonaki yahoyada yajak ne kisee dal ke leaviyon ko vida n kiya th.
tab yahoyada yajak ne shatapaatiyon ko raja daud ke barchhe aur bhale aur ddhalen jo parameshvar ke bhvan men thee, de deen.
fir us ne un sab logon ko apane apane hath men haathaiyar liye huae bhvan ke daakkhianee kone se lekar, uttaree kone tak vedee aur bhvan ke pas raja ke charon or usakee ad karake khda kar diya.
tab unhon ne rajakumar ko bahar la, usake sir par mukutt rakha aur sakshaeepatra dekar use raja banaya aur yahoyada aur usake putraen ne usaka abhaishok kiya, aur log bol utte, raja jeeavit rahe.
jab atalyah ko un logon ka halla, jo daudte aur raja ko sarahate the sun pada, tab vah logon ke pas yahova ke bhvan men gai.
aur us ne kya dekha, ki raja dar ke nikatt khmbhe ke pas khda haai aur raja ke pas pradhaan aur turahee bajanevale khde haai, aur sab log anand kar rahe haain aur turaahiyan baja rahe haain aur gane bajanevale baje bajate aur stuati karate haain. tab atalyah apane vasr faadkar pukarane lagee, rajadraeh, rajadraeh !
tab yahoyada yajak ne dal ke aadhaikaree shatapatiyon ko bahar lakar un se kaha, ki use apanee pantiyon ke beech se nikal le jao aur jo koi usake peechhe chale, vah talavar se mar dala jaae. yajak ne kaha, ki use yahova ke bhvan men n mar dalo.
tab yahoyada ne apane aur saree praja ke aur raja ke beech yahova kee praja hone kee vacha bandhavai.
tab sab logon ne bal ke bhvan ko jakar ddha diya aur usakee veadiyon aur mooraton ko ttukade ttukade kiya, aur mattan nam bal ke yajak ko vediyon ke samhane hee ghaat kiya.
tab yahoyada ne yahova ke bhvan kee seva ke liye un leveey yajakon ko tthara diya, jinhen daud ne yahova ke bhvan par dal dal karake isaaliye ttharaya tha, ki jaaise moosa kee yyavastha men likha haai, vaaise hee ve yahova ko homabali chaddhaya kare, aur daud kee chalai hui vidhai ke anusar anand karen aur gaaen.
aur us ne yahova ke bhvan ke faattkon par darapalon ko isaliye khda kiya, ki jo kisee reeati se ashuuddh ho, vah bheetar jane n paae.
aur vah shatapaatiyon aur raison aur praja par prabhuta karanevalon aur desh ke sab logon ko sath karake raja ko yahova ke bhvan se neeche le gaya aur unche faattk se hokar rajabhvan men aya, aur raja ko rajagaee par baaittaya.
tab sab log anandait huae aur nagar men shaaantai hui. atalyah to talavar se mar hee dalee gai thee.
jab yoash raja hua, tab vah sat varsha ka tha, aur yarooshalem men chalees varsha tak rajy karata raha usakee mata ka nam sibya tha, jo beshorba kee thee.
aur jab tak yahoyada yajak jeeavit raha, tab tak yoash vah kam karata raha jo yahova kee drashtti men tteek haai.
aur yahaseyada ne usake do byah karaae aur us se bette-beattyaian utpann hui.
isake bad yoash ke man men yahova ke bhvan kee marammat karane kee manasa upajee.
tab us ne yajakon aur leaviyon ko ikattha karake kaha, prati varsha yahooda ke nagaron men ja jakar sab israaaeliyon se rupaye liya karo jis se tumhare parameshvar ke bhvan kee marammat ho dekho isakam men fauta karo. taubhee leaviyon ne kuchh fauta n kee.
us dushtt stree atalyah ke betton ne to parameshvar ke bhvan ko tod diya aur yahova ke bhvan kee sab pavitra kee hui vastuen bal devataon ko de dee theen.
aur raja ne aek sandook banane kee agyaa dee aur vah yahova ke bhvan ke faattk ke pas bahar rakha gaya.
tab yahooda aur yarooshalem men yah prachar kiya gaya ki jis chande ka niyam parameshvar ke das moosa ne jangal men israaael men chalaya tha, usake rupaae yahova ke nimitt le ao.
to sab haakim aur praja ke sab log anandait ho rupaae lakar jab tak chanda poora n hua tab tak sandook men dalate gaae.
aur jab jab vah sandook leviyon ke hath se raja ke pradhaanon ke pas pahunchaya jata aur yah jan padta tha ki us men rupaae bahut haai, tab tab raja ke pradhaan aur mahayajak ka naib akar sandook ko khalee karate aur tab use fir usake sthan par rakh dete the. unhon ne pratidin aeesa kiya aur bahut rupaae iattha kiae.
tab raja aur yahoyada ne vah rupaae yahova ke bhvan men kam karanevalon ko de dia, aur unhon ne rajon aur baddhiyon ko yahova ke bhvan ke sudhaarane ke liye, aur loharon aur tttteron ko yahova ke bhvan kee marammat karane ke liye majadooree par rakha.
aur kareegar kam karate gaae aur kam poora hota gaya aur unhon ne parameshvar ka bhvan jaaisa ka taaisa banakar draddh kar diya.
jab unhon ne vah kam nipatta diya, tab ve shosh rupaae raja aur yahoyada ke pas le gaa, aur un se yahova ke bhvan ke liye patra banaae gaa, arthata seva tthal karane aur homabaali chaddhane ke patra aur dhoopadan adi sone chandee ke patra. aur jab tak yahoyada jeeavit raha, tab tak yahova ke bhvan men homabali nity chaddhaae jate the.
parantu yahoyada booddha ho gaya aur deegharayu hokar mar gaya. jab vah mar gaya tab aek sau tees varsha ka tha.
aur daudapur men rajaon ke beech usako mittee dee gai, kyonki us ne israaael men aur parameshvar ke aur usake bhvan ke vishay men bhla kiya tha.
yahoyada ke marane ke bad yahooda ke haakimon ne raja ke pas jakar use dandvat kee, aur raja ne unakee manee.
tab ve apane pitaron ke parameshvar yahova ka bhvan chhodkar ashoron aur mooraton kee upasana karane lage. so unake aeese doshaee hone ke karan parameshvar ka kroedha yahooda aur yarooshalem par bhdka.
taubhee us ne unake pas nabee bheje ki unako yahova ke pas faer laaen aur inhon ne unhen chita diya, parantu unhon ne kan n lagaya.
aur parameshvar ka atma yahoyada yajak ke putra jakaryah men sama gaya, aur vah unche sthn par khda hokar logon se kahane laga, parameshvar yon kahata haai, ki tum yahova kee agyaaon ko kyon ttalate ho? aeesa karake tum bhagyavan naheen ho sakate, dekho, tum ne to yahova ko tyag diya haai, is karan us ne bhee tum ko tyag diya.
tab logon ne us se draeh kee goshttee karake, raja kee agyaa se yahova ke bhvan ke angan men usako patthravah kiya.
yon raja yoash ne vah praeeati boolakar jo yahoyada ne us se kee thee, usake putra ko ghaat kiya. aur marate samay us ne kaha yahova is par draashtti karake isaka lekha le.
taye varsha ke lagate aramiyon kee sena ne us par chaddhai kee, aur yahooda or yarooshalem akar praja men se sab haakimon ko nash kiya aur unaka sab dhan loottkar damishk ke raja ke pas bheja.
aramiyon kee sena thede hee purushaen kee to ai, pantu yahova ne aek bahut badee sena unake hath kar dee, kyonki unhon ne apane pitaro ke parameshva ko tyag diya th. aur yoash ko bhee unhon ne dand diya.
jinhon ne us se rajadraeh kee goshttee kee, ve ye the, arthata ammonin, shaimat ka putra jabad aur shaimirt, moaabin ka putra yahojabada.
usake betton ke vishay aur usake viruddh, jo bade dand kee taboovat hui, usake aur parameshvar ke bhvan ke banane ke vishay ye sab baten rajaon ke vrattant kee pustak men likhee haain. aur usaka putra amasyah usake sthan par raja hua.
jab amasyah rajy karane laga tab vah vachees varsha ka tha, aur yarooshalem men unatees varsha tak rajy karata raha aur usakee mata ka nam yahoaan tha, jo yarooshalem kee thee.
us ne vah kiya jo yahova kee draashtti men tteek haai, parantu khre man se n kiya.
jab rajy usake hath men sthiar ho gaya, tab us ne apane un karmachariyon ko mar dala jinhon ne usake pita raja ko mar dala tha.
parantu us ne unake ladkevalon ko n mara kyonaki us ne yahova kee us agyaa ke anusar kiya, jo moosa kee yyavastha kee pustak men likhee haai, ki putra ke karan pita n mar dala jaa, aur n pita ke karan putra mar dala jaa, jis ne pap kiya ho vahee us pap ke karan mar dala jaae.
aur amasyah ne yahooda ko varan sare yahoodiyon aur binyameeaniyon ko ikattha karake unako, pitaron ke gharanon ke anusar sahasrapaatiyon aur shatapaatiyon ke aadhaikar men ttharaya aur un men se jitanon kee avastha bees varsha kee athva us se adhaik thee, unakee ginatee karake teen lakh bhala chalanevale aur ddhal uttanevale bade bade yoddha paae.
fir us ne aek lakh israaaelee shooraveeron ko bhee aek sau kikkar chandee dekar bulava rakha.
parantu parameshvar ke aek jan ne usake pas akar kaha, he raja israaael kee sena tere sath jane n paae kyonki yahova israaael arthata aepraaim kee kul santan ke sang naheen rahata.
yaadi too jakar purushaarth kare aur yuddh ke liye hiyav vandho, taubhee parameshvar tujhe shatrauon ke samhane giraaega, kyonki sahayata karane aur gira dene donon men parameshvar samath haai.
tab amasyah ne unhen arthata us dal ko jo aepraaim kee or se usake pas aya tha, alag kar diya, ki ve apane sthan ko lautt jaaen. tab unaka krodha yahoodiyo par bahut bhdk utta, aur ve atyant krodhait hokar apane sthan ko lautt gaae.
parantu amasyah hiyab bandhakar apane logon ko le chala, aur lon kee tarai men jakar, das hajar seiriyon ko mar dala.
aur yahooliyon ne das hajar ko bandhaua karake chattan kee chottee par le gaye, aur chattan kee chottee par se gira diya, so ve sab choor choor ho gaae.
parantu us dal ke purush jise amasyah ne lautta diya ki ve usake sath yuddh karane ko n jaae, shomaron se betheron tak yahooda ke sab nagaron par toott pade, aur unake teen hajar nivasee mar dale aur bahut loott le lee.
jab amasyah aedoniyon ka sanhar karake lautt aya, tab us ne seiariyon ke devataon ko le akar apane devata karake khda kiya, aur unheen ke samhane dandvat karane, aur unheen ke liye dhoop jalane laga.
tab yahova ka krodha amasyah par bhdk utta aur us ne usake pas aek nabee bheja jis ne us se kaha, jo devata apane logon ko tere hath se bacha n sake, unakee khoj men too kyon laga haai?
vah us se kah hee raha tha ki us ne us se poochha, kya ham ne tujhe rajamantraee tthara diya haai? chup rah ! kya too mar khana chahata haai? tab vah nabee yah kahakar chup ho gaya, ki mujhe maloom haai ki parameshvar ne tujhe nash karane ko ttana haai, kyonki too ne aeesa kiya haai aur meree sammati naheen manee.
tab yahooda ke raja amasyah ne sammati lekar, israaael ke raja yoash ke pas, jo yehoo ka pota aur yahoahaj ka putra tha, yon kahala bheja, ki a ham aek doosare ka samhana karen.
israaael ke raja yoash ne yahooda ke raja amasyah ke pas yon kahala bheja, ki labanon par kee aek jhdberee ne labanon ke aek devadar ke pas kahala bheja, ki apanee bettee mere bette ko byah de itane men labanon ka koi van pashu pas se chala gaya aur us jhdberee ko daund dala.
too kahata haai, ki maain ne aedomiyon ko jeet liya haai is karan too fool utta aur badai marata haai ! apane ghar men rah ja too apanee haani ke liye yahan kyon hath dalata haai, is se too kya, varan yahooda bhee neecha khaaega.
parantu amasyah ne n mana. yah to parameshvar kee or se hua, ki vah unhen unake shatrauon ke hath kar de, kyonaki ve aedom ke devataon kee khoj men lag gaae the.
tab israaael ke raja yoash ne chaddhai kee aur us ne aur yahooda ke raja amasyah ne yahooda desh ke betashomesh men aek doosare ka samhana kiya.
aur yahooda israaael se har gaya, aur har aek apane apane dere ko bhaga.
tab israaael ke raja yoash ne yahooda ke raja amasyah ko, jo yahoahaj ka pota aur yoash ka putra tha, betashomesh men pakada aur yarooshalem ko le gaya aur yarooshalem kee shaharapanah men se bapraaimee faattk se konevale faattk tak char sau hath gira diae.
aur jitana sona chandee aur jitane patra parameshvar ke bhvan men obededom ke pas mile, aur rajabhvan meen jitana khjana tha, us sab ko aur bandhak logon ko bhee lekar vah shaemaron ko lott gaya.
yahoahaj ke putra israaael ke raja yoash ke marane ke bad yoash ka putra yahooda ka raja amasyah pandrah varsha tak jeevit raha.
aadi se ant tak amasyah ke aur kam, kya yahooda aur israaael ke rajaon ke itihas kee pustak men naheen likhe haain?
jis samay apasyah yahova ke peechhe chalana chhodkar fir gaya tha us samay se yarooshalem men usake viruddh draeh kee goshttee hone lagee, aur vah lakeesh ko bhag gaya. so dooton ne lakeesh tak usaka peechha kar ke, usako vaheen mar dala.
tab vah ghaedon par rakhkar pahunchaya gaya aur use usake purakhaon ke beech yahooda ke nagar men mittee dee gai.
jab raja amasyah apane purakhaon ke sang so gaya tab ujjaiyyah ne aelot nagar ko draddh kar ke yahooda men fir mila liya.
jab ujjaiyyah rajy karane laga, tab vah solah varsha ka tha. aur yarooshalem men bavan varsha tak rajy karata raha, aur usakee mata ka nam yakeelyah tha, jo yarooshalem kee thee.
jaaise usaka pita amasyah, kiya karata tha vaaisa hee usane bhee kiya jo yahova kee draashtti men tteek tha.
aur jakaryah ke dinon men jo parameshvar ke darshan ke vishay samajh rakhta tha, vah parameshvar kee khoj men laga rahata tha aur jab tak vah yahova kee khoj men laga raha, tab tak parameshvar usako bhagyavan kiae raha.
tab us ne jakar palishtaiyon se yuddh kiya, aur gat, yabne aur ashadod kee shaharapanahen gira dee, aur ashadod ke asapas aur palishtaiyon ke beech men nagar basaae.
aur parameshvar ne paalishtaiyon aur goorbalavasee, araabiyon aur mooniyon ke viruddh usakee sahayata kee.
aur ammonee ujjaiyyah ko bhentt dene lage, varan usakee keettair misra ke sivane tak bhee faail gairar, kyonki vah atyant samath ho gaya tha.
fir ujjaiyyah ne yarooshalem men kone ke faattk aur tarai ke faattk aur shaharapanah ke mod par gummatt banavakar draddh kiae.
aur usake bahut janavar the isaaliye us ne jangal men aur neeche ke desh aur chauras desh men gummatt banavaae aur bahut se haud khudavaa, aur pahadon par aur kamrmel men usake kisan aur dakh kee baariyon ke malee the, kyonki vah khetee kisanee karanevala tha.
pitaron ke gharanon ke mukhy mukhy purush jo shooraveer the, unakee pooree ginatee do hajar chh sau thee.
aur unake aadhaikar men teen lakh saddhe sat hajar kee aek badee badee sena thee, jo shatrauon ke viruddh raja kee sahayata karane ko bade bal se yuddh karanevale the.
inake liye arthata pooree sena ke liye ujjaiyyah ne ddhale, bhale, ttop, jhlaim, dhanush aur gofan ke patthr taaiyar kiae.
fir us ne yarooshalem men gummatton aur kangooron par rakhne ko chatur purushaen ke nikale huae yantra bhee banavaae jinake dara teer aur bade bade patthr faenke jate the. aur usakee keettair door door tak faail gai, kyonki use adabhut yahayata yahan tak milee ki vah samath ho gaya.
parantu jab vah samath ho gaya, tab usaka man fool utta aur us ne bigadkar apane parameshvar yahova ka vishvasaghaat kiya, arthata vah dhoop kee vedee par dhoom jalane ko yahova ke mandair men ghaus gaya.
aur ajaryah yajak usake bad bheetar gaya, aur usake sang yahova ke assee yajak bhee jo veer the gaae.
aur unhon ne ujjaiyyah raja ka samhana karake us se kaha, he ujjaiyyah yahova ke liye dhoop jalana tera kam nahee, haroon kee santan arthata un yajakon hee ka kam haai, jo dhoop jalane ko pavitra kiae gaae haain. too pavitrasthan se nikal ja too ne vishvasaghaat kiya haai, yahova parameshvar kee or se yah teree maahima ka karan n hoga.
tab ujjaiyyah dhoop jalane ko dhoopadan hath men liye huae jhunjhla utta. aur vah yajakon par jhunjhla raha tha, ki yajakon ke dekhte dekhte yahova ke bhvan men dhoop kee vedee ke pas hee usake mathe par koddh pragatt hua.
aur ajaryah mahayajak aur sab yajakon ne us par drashtti kee, aur kya dekha ki usake mathe par koddh nikala haai ! tab uthon ne usako vahan se jhttpatt nikal diya, varan yah janakar ki yahova ne mujhe koddhee kar diya haai, us ne ap bahar jane ko utavalee kee.
aur ujjaiyyah raja marane ke din tak koddhee raha, aur koddh ke karan alag aek ghar men rahata tha, vah to yahova ke bhvan men jane n pata tha. aur usaka putra yoetam rajagharane ke kam par niyukt kiya gaya aur vah logon ka nyay bhee karata tha.
aadi se ant tak ujjaiyyah ke aur kamon ka varnn to amos ke putra yashaayah nabee ne likha haai.
nidan ujjaiyyah apane purakhaon ke sang so gaya, aur usako usake purakhaon ke nikatt rajaon ke mittee dene ke khet men mittee dee gai kyonki unhon ne kaha, ki vah koddhee haai. aur usaka putra yotam usake sthan par rajy karane laga.
jab yotam rajy karane laga tab vah pachees varsha ka tha, aur yarooshalem men solah varsha tak rajy karata raha. aur usakee mata ka nam yaroosha tha, jo sadok kee bettee thee.
us ne vah kiya, jo yahova kee draashtti men tteek haai, arthata jaaisa usake pita ujjaiyyah ne kiya tha, tteek vaaisa hee us ne bhee kiya taubhee vah yahova ke maandair men n ghausa. aur praja ke log tab bhee bigadee chal chalate the.
usee ne yahova ke bhvan ke uparavale faattk ko banaya, aur opel kee shaharapanah par bahut kuchh banavaya.
fir us ne yahooda ke pahadee desh men kai nagar draddh kia, aur jangalon men gaddh aur gummatt banaae.
aur vah ammoniyon ke raja se yuddh karake un par prabal ho gaya. usee varsha ammoniyon ne usako sau kikkar chandee, aur das das hajar kor gehoon aur jav diya. aur fir doosare aur teesare varsha men bhee unhon ne use utana hee diya.
yon yotam samath ho gaya, kyonaki vah apane ap ko apane parameshvar yahova ke sammukh janakar seedhaee chal chalata tha.
yotam ke aur kam aur usake sab yuddh aur usakee chal chalan, in sab baton ka varnn israaael aur yahooda ke rajaon ke itihas men likha haai.
jab vah raja hua, tab pachees varsha ka tha aur vah yarooshalem men solah varsha tak rajy karata raha.
jab ahaj rajy karane laga tab vah bees varsha ka tha, aur solah varsha tak yarooshalem men rajy karata raha. aur apane moolapurush daud ke saman kam naheen kiya, jo yahova kee draashtti men tteek tha,
parantu vah israaael ke rajaon kee see chal chala, aur bal devataon kee moortiyan ddhlavakar banai
aur hinnom ke bette kee tarai men dhoooop jalaya, aur un jaatiyon ke ghainaune kamon ke anusar jinhen yahova ne israaaeliyon ke samhane se desh se nikal diya tha, apane ladkebalon ko ag men hom kar diya.
aur unche sthanon par, aur pahaadiyon par, aur sab hare vrakshaen ke tale vah bali chaddhaya aur dhoom jalaya karata tha.
isaliye usake parameshvar yahova ne usako aramiyon ke raja ke hath kar diya, aur ve usako jeetakar, usake bahut se logon ko bandhaua banake damishk ko le gaae. aur vah israaael ke raja ke vash men kar diya gaya, jis ne use badee mar se mara.
aur ramalyah ke putra pekah ne, yahooda men aek hee din men aek lakh bees hajar logon ko jo sab ke sab veer the, ghaat kiya, kyonaki unhon ne apane pitaron ke parameshvar yahova ko tyag diya tha.
aur jikree namak aek aepraaimee veer ne maseyah namak aek rajaputra ko, aur rajabhvan ke pradhaan ajraeekam ko, aur aelakana ko, jo raja ka mantraee tha, mar dala.
aur israaaelee apane bhaiyon men se traiyo, betton aur beattyaien ko milakar do lakh logon ko bandhaua banake, aur unakee bahut loott bhee chheenakar shaeemaron kee or le chale.
aur ab tum ne ttana haai ki yahoodiyon aur yarooshalemiyon ko apane dasa-dasee banakar dabaae rakho. kya tum bhee apane parameshvar yahova ke yahan dashaee naheen ho?
isaliye ab meree suno aur in bandhauon ko jinhen tum apane bhaiyon men se bandhaua banake le aae ho, lautta do, yahova ka krodha to tum par bhdka haai.
