aur israaael ke raja daud aur usake putra sulaaiman donon kee likhee hui vidhaiyon ke anusar, apane apane pitaron ke anusar, apane apane dal men taaiyar raho.
aur tumhare bhai logon ke pitaron ke gharanon ke bhagon ke anusar paavitrasthan men khde raho, arthata unake aek bhag ke liye leaviyon ke aek aek pitar ke gharane ka aek bhag ho.
aur fasah ke pashuuon ko baali karo, aur apane apane ko paavitra karake apane bhaiyon ke liye taaiyaree karo ki ve yahova ke us vachan ke anusar kar sake, jo us ne moosa ke dara kaha tha.
fir yoshaiyyah ne sab logon ko jo vahan upaasthiat the, tees hajar bhedon aur bakaariyon ke bachche aur teen hajar baail diae the ye sab fasah ke baalidanon ke liye raja kee sampattai men se diae gaae the.
aur usake haakimon ne praja ke logo, yajakon aur leviyon ko svechchha -baaliyon ke liye pashu diae. aur hilkaiyyah, jakaryah aur yaheeael nam parameshvar ke bhvan ke pradhaanon ne yajakon ko do hajar chhsau bhed -bakaariyan. aur teen sau baail fasah ke balidanon ke liae diae.
aur konanyah ne aur shamayah aur natanel jo usake bhai the, aur hasabyah, yeeael aur yojabad namak leviyon ke pradhaanon ne leviyon ko panch hajar bhed-bakaariya, aur panch sau baail fasah ke baalidanon ke liye diae.
is prakar upasana kee taaiyaree ho gai, aur raja kee agyaa ke anusar yajak apane apane sthan par, aur leveey apane apane dal men khde huaee.
tab fasah ke pashu baali kiae gaa, aur yajak bali karanevalon ke hath se lohoo ko lekar chhdik dete aur leveey unakee khal utarate gaae.
tab unhon ne homabaali ke pashu isaliye alag kiae ki unhen logon ke pitaron ke gharanon ke bhagon ke anusar de, ki ve unhen yahova ke liye chaddhva den jaaisa ki moosa kee pustak men likha haai aur baailon ko bhee unhon ne vaaisa hee kiya.
tab unhon ne fasah ke pashuuon ka mans vidhai ke anusar ag men boonja, aur paavitra vastuae, hanadyaien aur handon aur thaaliyon men sijha kar foota se logon ko pahuncha diya.
tab unhon ne apane liye aur yajakon ke liye taaiyaree kee, kyonki haroon kee santan ke yajak homabali ke pashu aur charabee rat tak chaddhate rahe, is karan leviyon ne apane liye aur haroon kee santan ke yajakon ke liye taaiyaree kee.
aur asap ke vansh ke gavaaiye, daud, asap, heman aur raja ke dasha yadootoon kee agyaa ke anusar apane apane sthan par rahe, aur darapal aek aek faattk par rahe. unhen apana apana kam chhodna n pada, kyonki unake bhi leaviyon ne unake liye taaiyaree kee.
yon usee din raja yoshaiyyah kee agyaa ke anusar fasah manane aur yahova kee bedee par homabaali chaddhane ke liye yahova kee saree apasana kee taaiyaree kee gai.
jo israaaelee vahan upaasthiat the unhon ne fasah ko usee samay aur akhmeeree rottee ke parva ko sat din tak mana.
is fasah ke barabar shamooael nabee ke dinon se israaael men koi fasah manaya n gaya tha, aur n israaael ke kisee raja ne aeesa manaya, jaaisa yoshaiyyah aur yajako, leviyon aur jitane yahoodee aur israaaelee upasthiat the, unahon ne aur yarooshalem ke nivaasiyon ne manaya.
yah fasah yoshaiyyah ke rajy ke attarahaven varsha men manaya gaya.
isake bad jab yoshaiyyah bhvan ko taaiyar kar chuka, tab misra ke raja nako ne parat ke pas ke kurkameesh nagar se ladne ko chaddhai kee aur yoshaiyyah usaka samhana karane ko gaya.
