aur attven din ko unhon ne mahasabha kee, unhon ne vedee kee pratishtta sat din kee aur pavan ko bhee sat din mana.
nidan sataven maheene ke teisaven din ko us ne praja ke logon ko vida kiya, ki ve apane apane dere ko jaae, aur ve us bhlai ke karan jo yahova ne daud aur sulaaiman aur apanee praja israaael par kee thee anandait the.
yon sulaaiman yahova ke bhvan aur rajabhvan ko bana chuka, aur yahova ke bhvan men aur apane bhvan men jo kuchh us ne banana chaha, us men usaka manorath poora hua.
tab yahova ne rat men usako darshan dekar us se kaha, maain ne teree praarthana sunee aur is sthan ko yagya ke bhvan ke liye apanaya haai.
yaadi maain akash ko aeesa band karoo, ki vashara n ho, va ttiidyon ko desh ujadne kee agyaa doo, va apanee praja men maree faailau,
tab yaadi meree praja ke log jo mere kahalate haai, deen hokar praarthna karen aur mere darshan ke khojee hokar apanee buree chal se fire, to maain svarga men se sunakar unaka pap kshama karoonga aur unake desh ko jyon ka tyon kar doonga.
ab se jo praarthna is sthan men kee jaaegee, us par meree ankhen khulee aur mere kan lage rahenge.
aur ab maain ne is bhvan ko apanaya aur pavitra kiya haai ki mera nam sada ke liye is men bana rahe meree ankhen aur mera man donon nity yaheen lage rahenge.
aur yaadi too apane pita daud kee nai apane ko mere sammukh janakar chalata rahe aur meree sab agyaaon ke anusar kiya kare, aur meree vidhaiyon aur niyamon ko manata rahe,
to maain teree rajagaee ko sthiar rakoonga jaaise ki maain ne tere pita daud ke sath vacha bandhaee thee, ki tere kul men israaael par prabhuta karanevala sada bana rahega.
parantu yadi tum log firo, aur meree vidhaiyon aur agyaaon ko jo maain ne tum ko dee haain tyago, aur jakar paraye devataon kee upasana karo aur unhen dandvat karo,
to maain unako apane desh men se jo maain ne unako diya haai, jad se ukhaoonga aur is bhvan ko jo maain ne apane nam ke liye paavitra kiya haai, apanee drashtti se door karoonga aur aeesa karoonga ki desh desh ke logon ke beech usakee upama aur namadharai chalegee.
aur yah bhvan jo itana vishaal haai, usake pas se ane janevale chaakit hokar poochhenge ki yahova ne is desh aur is bhvan se aeesa kyon kiya haai.
tab log kahenge, ki un logon ne apane pitaron ke parameshvar yahova ko jo unako misra desh se nikal laya tha, tyagakar paraye devataon ko grahan kiya, aur unhen dajhadvat kee aur unakee upasana kee, is karan us ne yah sab vipaattai un par dalee haai.
sulaaiman ko yahova ke bhvan aur apane bhvan ke banane men bees varsha lage.
tab jo nagar hooram ne sulaaiman ko diae the, unhen sulaaiman ne draddh karake un men israaaeliyon ko basaya.
tab sulaaiman soba ke hamat ko jakar, us par jayavant hua.
aur us ne tadamor ko jo jangal men haai, aur hamat ke sab bhndar nagaron ko draddh kiya.
fir us ne uparavale aur neechevale donon bethoron ko shaharapanah aur faattkon aur bedon se draddh kiya.
aur us ne balat ko aur sulaaiman ke jitane bhndar nagar the aur usake rathon aur savaron ke jitane nagar the unako, aur jo kuchh sulaaiman ne yarooshalem, labanon aur apane rajy ke sab desh men banana chaha, un sab ko banaya.
hittaiyo, aemoriyo, parijjaiyo, hiyivayon aur yaboosiyon ke bache huae log jo israaael ke n the,
unake vansh jo unake bad desh men rah gaa, aur jinaka israaealiyon ne ant n kiya tha, un men se to kitanon ko sulaaiman ne begar men rakha aur aj tak unakee vahee dasha haai.
parantu israaaeliyon men se sulaaiman ne apane kam ke liye kisee ko das n banaya, ve to yoddha aur usake haakim, usake saradar aur usake rathen aur savaron ke pradhaan hue.
aur sulaaiman ke saradaron ke pradhaan jo praja ke logon par prabhuta karanevale the, ve addhai sau the.
fir sulaaiman firaun kee bettee ko daudapur men se us bhvan men le aya jo us ne usake liye banaya tha, kyonaki us ne kaha, ki jis jis sthan men yahova ka sandook aya haai, vah pavitra haai, isaaliye meree ranee israaael ke raja daud ke bhvan men n rahane paaegee.
vah moosa kee agyaa ke aur din din ke prayojan ke anusar, arthata vishraam aur naye chand aur praati varsha teen bar ttharaae huae pavan arthata akhmeeree rottee ke payrva, aur attvaron ke payrva, aur jhopadiyon ke payrva men baali chaddhaya karata tha.
aur us ne apane pita daud ke niyam ke anusar yajakon kee sevakai ke liye unake dal ttharaa, aur leaviyon ko unake kamon par ttharaya, ki har aek din ke prayojan ke anusar ve yahova kee stuati aur yajakon ke samhane seva-tthal kiya kare, aur aek aek faattk ke pas darapalon ko dal dal karake tthara diya kyonaki parameshvar ke bhkt daud ne aeesee agyaa dee thee.
aur raja ne bhndaron ya kisee aur bat men yajakon aur leaviyon ke liye jo jo agyaa dee thee, unhonne n ttala.
aur sulaaiman ka sab kam jo us ne yahova ke bhvan kee nev dalane se lekar usake poora karane tak kiya vah tteek hua. nidan yahova ka bhvan poora hua.
aur hooram ne usake pas apane jahajiyon ke dara jahaj aur samudra ke janakar mallah bhej dia, aur unhon ne sulaaiman ke jahaajiyon ke sang opeer ko jakar vahan se saddhe char sau kikkar sona raja sulaaiman ko la diya.
jab shaeeba kee ranee ne sulaaiman kee keeattair sunee, tab vah kaattnai kattnai prashnon se usakee pareeksha karane ke liye yarooshalem ko chalee . vah bahut bharee dal aur masalon aur bahut sone aur manai se lade untt sath liye huae ai, aur sulaaiman ke pas pahunchakar usase apane man kee sab baton ke vishay baten keen.
sulaaiman ne usake sab prashnon ka uttar diya, koi bat sulaaiman kee buaddhi se aeesee bahar n rahee ki vah use n bata sake.
jab shaeeba kee ranee ne sulaaiman kee buaddhimanee aur usaka banaya hua bhvan
aur usakee mej par ka bhojan dekha, aur usake karmacharee kis reeti baaittte aur usake tthaluae kis reeti khde rahate aur kaaise kaaise kapade paahine rahate haai, aur usake pilanevale kaaise haai, aur ve kaaise kapade paahine haai, aur vah kaaisee chaddhai haai jis se vah yahova ke bhvan ko jaya karata haai, jab us ne yah sab dekha, tab vah chakit ho gai.
tab us ne raja se kaha, maain ne tere kamon aur buddhimanee kee jo keettair apane desh men sunee vah sach hee haai.
parantu jab tak maain ne ap hee akar apanee ankhon se yah n dekha, tab tak maain ne unakee prateeti n kee parantu teree buaddhi kee adhaee badai bhee mujhe n batai gai thee too us keeattair se baddhkar haai jo maain ne sunee thee.
dhany haain tere jan, dhany haain tere ye sevak, jo nity tere sammukh upaasthiat rahakar teree buddhi kee baten sunate haain.
dhany haai tera parameshvar yahova, jo tujh se aeesa prasann hua, ki tujhe apanee rajagaee par isaaliye virajaman kiya ki too apane parameshvar yahova kee or se rajy kare tera parameshvar jo israaael se praem karake unhen sada ke liye sthir karana jahata t, usee karan us ne tujhe nyay aur dharma karane ko unaka raja bana diya.
aur us ne raja ko aek sau bees kikkar sona, bahut sa sugandha drayy, aur maanai diae jaaise sugandhadrayy shaeeba kee ranee ne raja sulaaiman ko dia, vaaise dekhne men naheen aae.
fir hooram aur sulaaiman donon ke jahajee jo oshaeer se sona late the, ve chandan kee lakadee aur maanai bhee late the.
aur raja ne chandan kee lakadee se yahova ke bhvan aur rajabhvan ke liye chabootare aur gavaaiyon ke liye veenaaen aur saranagiyan banavai aeesee vastuaen us se paahile yahooda desh men n dekh padee theen
aur shaeeba kee ranee ne jo kuchh chaha vahee raja sulaaiman ne usako usakee ichchha ke anusar diya yah us se aadhaik tha, jo vah raja ke pas le ai thee. tab vah apane janon samet apane desh ko lautt gai.
jo sona prati varsha sulaaiman ke pas pahucha karata tha, usaka taul chh sau chhyaiasatt kikkar tha.
yah us se aadhaik tha jo saudagar aur yyaparee late the aur arab desh ke sab raja aur desh ke adhaipaati bhee sulaaiman ke pas sona chandee late the.
aur raja sulaaiman ne sona gaddhakar do sau badee badee ddhalen banavai aek aek ddhal men chhchhsau shokel gaddha hua sona laga.
fir us ne sona gaddhakar teen sau chhottee ddhalen aur bhee banavai aek aek chhottee ddhal me teen sau shokel sona laga, aur raja ne unako labanonee ban namak bhvan men rakha diya.
aur raja ne hatheedant ka aek bada sinhasan banaya aur chokhe sone se maddhaya.
us sinhasan men chh seeaddhyaian aur sone ka ek pavadan tha ye sab sinhasan se jude the, aur baaittne ke sthan kee donoen alang ttek lagee thee aur donon ttekon ke pas ek ek sinh khda hua bana tha.
aur chhhon seeddhiyon kee donon alang men aek aek sinh khda hua bana tha, ve sab barah hue. kisee rajy men aeesa kabhee n bana.
aur raja sulaaiman ke peene ke sab patra sone ke the, aur labanonee ban namak bhvan ke sab patra bhee chokhe sone ke the sulaaiman ke dinon men chandee ka kuchh hisab n tha.
kyonaki hooram ke jahaajiyon ke sang raja ke tashash ko janevale jahaj the, aur teen teen varsha ke bad ve tashash ke jahaj sona, chandee, hatheedant, bandar aur mor le ate the.
yon raja sulaaiman dhan aur buaddhi men prathvee ke sab rajaon se baddhkar ho gaya.
aur prathvee ke sab raja sulaaiman kee us buaddhi kee baten sunane ko jo parameshvar ne usake man men upajai theen usaka darshan karana chahate the.
aur apane ghodon aur rathon ke liye sulaaiman ke char hajar than aur barah hajar savar bhee the, jinako us ne rathon ke nagaron men aur yarooshalem men raja ke pas tthara rakha.
aur vah mahanad se le paalishtaiyon ke desh aur misra ke sivane tak ke sab rajaon par prabhuta karata tha.
aur raja ne aeesa kiya, ki bahutayat ke karan yarooshalem men chandee ka mooly patthron ka aur devadar ka mooly neeche ke desh ke goolaron ka sa ho gaya.
aur log misra se aur aur sab deshaen se sulaaiman ke liye ghaede late the.
aadi se ant tak sulaaiman ke aur sab kam kya natan nabee kee pustak me, aur shaeelovasee ahiyyah kee taboovat kee pustak me, aur nabat ke putra yarobam ke vishay io dasha ke darshan kee pustak men naheen likhe haain?
aur sulaaiman apane purakhaon ke sang so gaya aur usako usake pita daud ke nagar men mittee dee gai aur usaka putra rahoobiyam usake sthan par raja hua.
maain vahee paulus jo tumhare samhane deen hoo, parantu peett peechhe tumharee or sahas karata hoon tum ko maseeh kee namrata, aur komalata ke karan samajhata hoon.
maain yah binatee karata hoo, ki tumhare samhane mujhe nirbhy hokar sahas karana n pade jaaisa maain kitanon par jo ham ko shareer ke anusar chalanevale samajhte haai, veerata dikhane ka vichar karata hoon.
kyonaki yadhyapi ham shareer men chalate firate haai, taubhee shareer ke anusar naheen ladte.
kyeaaki hamaree ladai ke haathaiyar shaareearik nahee, par gaddhon ko ddha dene ke liye parameshvar ke dara samarthee haain.
so ham kalpanaon ko, aur har aek unchee bat ko, jo parameshvar kee paahichan ke virodha men utttee haai, khndn karate haain aur har aek bhavana ko kaaid karake maseeh ka agyaakaree bana dete haain.
aur taaiyar rahate haain ki jab tumhara agyaa manana poora ho jaa, to har aek prakar ke agyaa n manane ka palatta len.
tum inheen baton ko dakhte ho, jo ankhon ke samhane haai, yadi kisee ka apane par yah bhrosa ho, ki maain maseeh ka hoo, to vah yah bhee jan le, ki jaaisa vah maseeh ka haai, vaaise hee ham bhee haain.
kyonaki yadi maain us aadhaikar ke vishay men aur bhee ghamand dikhau, jo prabhu ne tumhare bigadne ke liye naheen par banane ke liye hamen diya haai, to lajjait n hoonga.
yah maain isaaliye kahata hoo, ki patraiyon ke dara tumhen dranevala n ttharoon.
kyonaki kahate he, ki us kee patraiyan to gambheer aur prabhavashaalee haain parantu jab dekhte haai, to vah deh ka nirbal aur vaktavy men halka jan padta haai.
so jo aeesa kahata haai, ki samajh rakhe, ki jaaise peett peechhe paatraiyon men hamare vachan haai, vaaise hee tumhare samhane hamare kam bhee honge.
kyonaki hamen yah hiyav naheen ki ham apane ap ko un men se aeese kitanon ke sath gine, ya un se apane ko milaae, jo apanee prashansa karate haai, aur apane ap ko apas men nap taulakar aek doosare se milan karake moorkh ttharate haain.
ham to seema se bahar ghamand kadapi n karenge, parantu usee seema tak jo parameshvar ne hamare liye tthara dee haai, aur us men tum bhee a gaae ho aur usee ke anusar ghamand bhee karenge.
kyonaki ham apanee seema se bahar apane ap ko baddhana naheen chahate, jaaise ki tum tak n pahunchane kee dasha men hota, baran maseeh ka susamachar sunate huae tum tak pahunch chuke haain.
aur ham seema se bahar auron ke parishram par ghaman naheen karate parantu hamen asha haai, ki jyon jyon tumhara vishvas baddhta jaaega tyon tyon ham apanee seema ke anusar tumhare karan aur bhee baddhte jaaenge.
ki ham tumhare sivanon se age baddhkar susamachar sunaae, aur yah nahee, ki ham auron kee seema ke bheetar bane banaae kamon par ghamand karen.
paranatu jo ghamand kare, vah prabhu par ghamand karen.
kyonaki jo apanee badai karata haai, vah nahee, parantu jis kee badai prabhu karata haai, vahee grahan kiya jata haai..
yaadi tum meree thodee moorkhta sah lete to kya hee bhla hota ha, meree sah bhee lete ho.
kyonaki maain tumhare vishay me ishvareey dhaun lagaae rahata hoo, isaaliye ki maain ne aek hee puroosh se tumharee bat lagai haai, ki tumhen pavitra kunvaree kee nai maseeh ko saunp doon.
parantu maain drata hoon ki jaaise sanp ne apanee chaturai se havva ko bahakaya, vaaise hee tumhare man us seedhaai aur paavitrata se jo maseeh ke sath honee chahiae kaheen bhrashtt n kiae jaaen.
yaadi koi tumhare pas akar, kisee doosare yeeshu ko prachar kare, jis ka prachar ham ne naheen kiya: ya koi aur atma tumhen mile jo paahile n mila tha ya aur koi susamachar jise tum ne paahile n mana tha, to tumhara sahana tteek hota.
yaadi maain vktavay men anadee hoo, taubhee gyaan men naheen baran ham ne is ko har bat men sab par tumhare liye pragatt kiya haai.
kya is men maain ne kuchh pap kiya ki maain ne tumhen parameshvar ka susamachar sent ment sunaya aur apane ap ko neecha kiya, ki tum unche ho jao?
maain ne aur kaleeasiyaon ko lootta arthata maain ne un se majadooree lee, taaki tumharee seva karoon.
or jab tumhare sath tha, aur mujhe ghattee hui, to maain ne kisee par bhar naheen diya, kyonaki bhaiyon ne, makiduaniya se akar meree ghattee ko paree kee: aur maain ne har bat men apane ap ko tum par bhar hone se roka, aur roke rahoonga.
yaadi maseeh kee sachchai mujh men haai, to akhya desh men koi mujhe is ghamand se n rokega.
kis liye? kya isaaliye ki maain tum se praem naheen rakhta? parameshvar yah janata haai.
kyonaki aeese log jootte praerit, aur chhl se kam karanevale, aur maseeh ke praeariton ka roop dharanevale haain.
aur yah kuchh achambhe kee bat naheen kyonaki shautan ap bhee jyotimarya svargadoot ka roop dhaaran karata haai.
so yaadi usake sevak bhee dharma ke sevakon ka sa roop dhare, to kuchh badee bat naheen parantu un ka ant un ke kamon ke anusar hoga.
maain fir kahata hoo, koi mujhe moorkh n samajhe naheen to moorkh hee samajhkar meree sah lo, taki thoda sa maain bhee ghamand karoon.
is bedhadk ghamand se bolane men jo kuchh maain kahata hoon vah praboo kee agyaa ke anusar naheen par manon moorkhta se hee kahata hoon.
jab ki bahut log shareer ke anusar ghamand karate haai, to maain bhee ghamand karoonga.
tum to samajhdar hokar anand se moorkhon kee sah lete ho.
kyeanki jab tumhen koi das bana leta haai, ya kha jata haai, ya fasa leta haai, ya apane ap ko bada banata haai, ya tumhare munh par thppad marata haai, to tum sah lete ho.
mera kahata anadar kee reeti par haai, mano ki ham nirbal se the parantu jis kisee bat men koi hiyav karata haai maain moorkhta se kahata hoon to maain bhee hiyav karata hoon.
kya ve hee ibraanee haain? maain bhee hoon: kya ve hee ibraaheem ke vansh ke haain? maain bhee hoon: kya ve hee maseeh ke sevak haain?
maain pagal kee nai kahata hoon maain un se baddhkar hoon! aadhaik parishram karane men bar bar kaaid hone men kode khate men bar bar mratyu ke jokhaimon men.
panch bar maain ne yahoodiyon ke hath se untalees untalees kode khaae.
teen bar maain ne benteen khai aek bar patthravah kiya gaya teen bar jahaj jin par maain chaddha tha, toott gaae aek raj din maain ne samudra men katta.
maain bar bar yatraaon men nadiyon ke jokhaimon men dakuon ke jokhaimon men apane jativalon se jokhaimon men anyajaatiyon se jokhaimon men nagaron men ke jakhaimon men jangal ke jokhaimon men samudra ke jakhaimon men jootte bhaiyon ke beech jokhaimon men
paarishram aur kashtt men bar bar jagate rahane men bookh-apiyas men bar bar upavas karate men jade men ughaade rahane men.
aur aur baton ko chhodkar jin ka varnn maain naheen karata sab kaleesiyaon kee chinta pratidin mujhe dabatee haai.
kis kee nirbalata se maain nirbal naheen hota? kis ke ttokar khane se mera jee naheen dukhta?
yaadi ghaman karana avashy haai, to maain apanee nirbalata kee baton par karoonga.
prabhu yeeshu ka parameshvar aur pita jo sada dhany haai, janata haai, ki maain joott naheen bolata.
daamishk men aaritas raja kee or se jo hakim tha, us ne mere pakadne ko daamishiikayon ke nagar par pahara baaitta rakha tha.
aur maain ttokare men khaidkee se hokar bheet par se utara gaya, aur usake hath se bach nikala..
yadhypi ghamand karana to mere liye tteek naheen taubhee karana padta haai so maain prabhu ke diae huae darshanon aur prakashaen kee charcha karoonga.
maain aeese manushy ko janata hoon n jane dehasahit, n jane deharaahit parameshvar hee janata haai.
ki svarga lok par utta liya gaya, aur aesee baten suneen jo kahane kee naheen aur jin ka munh men lana manushy ko uchit naheenn.
aeese manushy par to maain ghamand karoonga, parantu apane par apanee nirbalataon ko chhod, apane vishay men ghamand n karoonga.
kyonaki yadi maain ghamand karana chahoon bhee to moonrkh n hoonga, kyonki sach boloonga tobhee rook jata hoo, aeesa n ho, ki jaaisa koi mujhe dekhta haai, ya mujh se sunata haai, mujhe us se baddhkar samajhe.
aur isaliye ki maain prakashaen kee bahutayat se fool n jau, mere shareer men aek kantta chubhaya gaya arthata shautan ka aek doot ki mujhe ghoose mare taaki maain fool n jaun.
is ke vishay men maain ne prabhu se teen bar binatee kee, ki mujh se yah door ho jaae.
aur us ne mujh se kaha, mera anugrah tere liye bahut haai kyonaki meree samarth nirbalata men siddh hotee haai isaaliye maain bade anand se apanee nirbalataon par ghamand karoonga, ki maseeh kee samarth mujh par chhaya karatee rahe.
maain moorkh to bana, parantu tum hee ne mujh se yah barabas karavaya: tumhen to meree prashansa karanee chaahiae thee, kyonki yadhyapi maain kuchh bhee nahee, taubhee un bade se bade praariton se kisee bat men kam naheen hoon.
praarit ke lakshan bhee tumhare beech sab prakar ke dhaeeraj saahit chinho, aur adabhut kamo, aur samarth ke kamon se dikhaae gaae.
tum koain see bat men aur kaleeasiyon se kam the, keval is men ki maain ne tum par apana bhar n rakha: mera yah anyay kshama karo.
dekho, maain teesaree bar tumhare pas ane ko taaiyar hoo, aur maain tum par koi bhar n rakoonga kyonaki maain tumharee sampati nahee, baran tum hee ko chahata hoon: kyonaki ladke-balon ko mata-pita ke liye dhan battorana n chaahia, par mata-apita ko ladke-balon ke liye.
maain tumharee atmaon ke liye bahut anand se khrcha karoonga, baran ap bhee khrcha ho jaunga: kya jitana baddhkar maain tum se praem rakhta hoo, utana hee ghattkar tum mujh se praem rakhoge?
aeesa ho sakata haai, ki maain ne tum par bojh naheen dala, parantu chaturai se tumhen dhaekha dekar fansa liya.
bhla, jinhen maain ne tumhare pas bheja, kya un men se kisee ke dara maain ne chhl karake tum se kuchh le liya?
maai ne titus ko samajhakar usake sath us bhai ko bheja, to kya teetus ne chhl karake tum se kuchh liya? kya ham aek hee atma ke chalaae n chale? kya aek hee leek par n chale?
tum abhee tak samajh rahe hoge ki ham tumhare samane pratyuttr de rahe haai, ham to parameshvar ko upaasthiat janakar maseeh men bolate haai, aur he piryo, sab baten tumharee unnati hee ke liye kahate haain.
kyonaki mujhe dr haai, kaheen aeesa n ho, ki maain akar jaaise chahata hoo, vaaise tumhen n paun aur mujhe bhee jaaisa tum naheen chahate vaaisa hee pao, ki tum men jhgada, dah, krodha, viradha, ishrya, chugalee, abhaiman aur bakhede hon.
aur mera parameshvar kaheen mere fir se tumhare yahan ane par mujh par dabav dale aur mujhe bahuton ke liye fir shaek karana pade, jinhon ne pahile pap kiya tha, aur us gande kam, aur vyaabhaichar, aur luchapan se, jo unhon ne kiya, man naheen firaya..
ab teesaree bar tumhare pas ata hoon: do ya teen gavahon ke munh se har aek bat ttharai jaaegee.
jaaise jab doosaree bar tumhare sath tha, so vaaise hee ab door rahate huae un logon se jinhon ne pahile pap kiya, aur aur sab logon se ab pahile se kahe deta hoo, ki yadi maain fir aunga, to naheen chhooonga.
tum to is ka praman chahate ho, ki maseeh mujh men bolata haai, jo tumhare liye nirbal naheen parantu tum men samarthee haai.
vah nirbalata ke karan kroos par chaddhaya to gaya, taubhee parameshvar kee samarth se jeevit haai, ham bhee to us men nirbal haain parantu parameshvar kee samarth se jo tumhare liye haai, usake sath jeeaenge.
apane praan ko parakho, ki vishvas men ho ki naheen apane ap ko jancho, kya tum apane vishay men yah naheen janate, ki yeeshu maseeh tum men haai? naheen to tum nikamme nikale ho.
par meree asha haai, ki tum jan loge, ki ham nikamme naheen.
aur ham apane parameshvar se praarthna karate haai, ki tum koi burai n karo isaliye hanee, ki ham khre dekh pade, par isaaliye ki tum bhlai karo, chahe ham nikamme hee ttharen.
kyonaki ham saty ke virodha men kuchh naheen kar sakate, par saty ke liye kar sakate haain.
jab ham nirbal haai, aur tum balavant ho, to ham anandait hote haai, aur yah praarthna bhee karate haai, ki tum siddh ho jao.
is karan maain tumhare peett peechhe ye baten likhta hoo, ki upaasthiat hokar mujhe us aadhaikar ke anusar jise prabhu ne bigadne ke liye naheen par banane ke liye mujhe diya haai, kaddhai se kuchh karana n pade..
aek doosare ko pavitra chumban se namaskar karo.
sab paavitra log tumhen namaskar karate haain.
prabhu yeeshu maseeh ka anugrah aur parameshvar ka praem aur paavitra atma kee sahabhaagita tum sab ke sath hotee rahe..
paulus kee or se jo parameshvar kee ichchha se maseeh yeeshu ka praearit haai, aur bhai teemuathaiyus kee or se parameshvar kee us kaleesiya ke nam jo kuarinthus men haai aur sare akhma ke sab pavitra lagon ke nama..
hamare pita parameshvar aur prabhu yeeshu maseeh kee or se anugrah aur shaaantai milatee rahe..
hamare prabhu yeeshu maseeh ke parameshvar, aur pita ka dhanyavad ho, jo daya ka pita, aur sab prakar kee shaaantai ka parameshvar haai.
vah hamare sab kleshaen men shaaantai deta haai taki ham us shaaantai ke karan jo parameshvar hamen deta haai, unhen bhee shaaantai de sake, jo kisee prakar ke klesh men hon.
kyonaki jaaise maseeh ke dukh ham ko aadhaik hote haai, vaaise hee hamaree shaaantai bhee maseeh ke dara adhaik hatee haai.
aur hamaree asha tumhare vishay men draddh haai kyonaki ham janate haai, ki tum jaaise dukhon ke vaaise hee shaantai ke bhee sahabhagee ho.
he bhaiyo, ham naheen chahate ki tum hamare us klesh se anajan raho, jo aasiya men ham par pada, ki aeese bharee bojh se dab gaae the, jo hamaree samarth se bahar tha, yahan tak ki ham jeevan se bhee hath dhae baaitte the.
baran ham ne apane man men samajh liya tha, ki ham par mratyu kee agyaa ho chukee haai ki ham apana bhrosa n rakhe, baran parameshvar ka jo mare huon ko jilata haai.
usee ne hamen aeesee badee mratyu se bachaya, aur bachaega aur us se hamaree yah asha haai, ki vah age ko bhee bachata rahega.
aur tum bhee milakar praarthna ke dara hamaree sahayata karoge, ki jo baradan bahuton ke dara hamen mila, usake karan bahut log hamaree or se dhanyavad karen..
kyonaki ham apane vivek kee is gavahee par ghamand karate haai, ki jagat men aur vishosh karake tumhare beech hamara chaaritra parameshvar ke yogy aeesee paavitrata aur sachchai saahit tha, jo shaareerik gyaan se nahee, parantu parameshvar ke anugrah ke sath tha.
ham tumhen aur kuchh naheen likhte, keval vah jo tum paddhte ya manate bhee ho, aur mujhe asha haai, ki ant tak bhee manate rahoge.
jaaisa tum men se kitanon ne man liya haai, ki ham tumhare ghamand ka karan haai vaaise tum bhee prabhu yeeshu ke din hamare liye ghamand ka karan ttharoge..
aur is bhrose se maain chahata tha ki pahile tumhare pas aun ki tumhen aek aur dan mile.
aur tumhare pas se hokar maakiduaniya ko jau, aur tum muchhe yahoodiya kee or kud door tak pahunchao.
isaliye maain ne jo yah ichchha kee thee to kya maain ne chanchalata dikhai? ya jo karana chahata hoon kya shareer ke anusar karana chahata hoo, ki maain bat men ha, han bhee karoon
aur naheen naheen bhee karoon? parameshvar sachcha gavah haai, ki hamare us vachan men jo tum se kaha han aur naheen danon pai naheen jateen.
kyonaki parameshvar ka putra yeeshu maseeh jisaka hamare dara arthata mere aur silavanus aur teemuthaiyus ke dara tumhare beech meen prachar hua us men han aur naheen donon n thee parantu, us men han hee han hui.
kyanaki parameshvar kee jitanee pratigyaaaen haai, ve sab usee men han ke sath haain: isaliye usake dara ameen bhee hui, ki hamare dara parameshvar kee maahima ho.
aur jo hamen tumhare sath maseeh men draddh karata haai, aur jis ne hamen aabhaishok kiya vahee parameshvar haai.
jis ne ham par chhap bhee kar dee haai aur bayan men atma ko hamare manon men diya..
maain parameshvar ko gavah karata hoo, ki maai ab tak kurinthus men isaaliye naheen aya, ki mujhe tum par taras ata tha.
yah nahee, ki ham vishvas ke vishay men tum par prabhuta jatana chahate haain parantu tumhare anand men sahayak haain kyonki tum vishvas hee se sthiar rahate ho.
maainne apane man men yahee ttan liya tha ki fir tumhare pas udas hokar n aun.
kyonaki yadi maain tumhen udas karoo, to mujhe anand denevala kaun hoga, keval vahee jis ko maain ne udas kiya?
bade klesha, aur man ke kashtt se, maain ne bahut se ansu baha bahakar tumhen likha, isaliye nahee, ki tum udas ho, parantu isaaliye ki tum us bade praem ko jan lo, jo mujhe tum se haai..
aur yaadi kisee ne udas kiya haai, to mujhe hee naheen baran ki usake sath bahut kadai n karoon kuchh kuchh tum sab ko bhee udas kiya haai.
aeese jan ke liye yah dand jo bhaiyon men se bahuton ne diya, bahut haai.
isaliye is se yah bhla haai ki usaka aparadha kshama karo aur shaantai do, n ho ki aeesa manushy udasee men oob jaae.
is karan maain tum se binatee karata hoo, ki us ko apane praem ka praman do.
kyonaki maain ne isaliye bhee likha tha, ki tumhen parakh loo, ki sab baton ke manane ke liye taaiyar ho, ki naheen.
jis ka tum kuchh kshama karate ho us maain bhee kshama karata hoo, kyonki maain ne bhee jo kuchh kshama kiya haai, yadi kiya ho, to tumhare karan maseeh kee jagah men hokar kshama kiya haai.
ki shautan ka ham par danv n chale, kyonki ham us kee yuktaiyon se anajan naheen.
aur jab maain maseeh ka susamachar, sunane ko traeas men aya, aur prabhu ne mere liye aek dar khol diya.
parantu parameshvar ka dhanyavad ho, jo maseeh men sada ham ko jay ke utsav men liye firata haai, aur apane gyaan ka sugandha hamare dara har jagah faailata haai.
kyonaki ham parameshvar ke nikatt uddhar panevalo, aur nash honevalo, dono ke liye maseeh ke sugandha haain.
kitano ke liye to marane ke nimitt mranyu kee gandha, aur kitano ke liye jeevan ke nimitt jeevan kee sugandha, aur in baton ke yogy kaun haai?
kyonaki ham un bahuton ke saman nahee, jo parameshvar ke vachan men milavatt karate haain parantu man kee sachchai se, aur parameshvar kee or se parameshvar ko upaasthiat janakar maseeh men bolate haain..
kya ham fir apanee badai karane lage? ya hamen kitanon ki nai sifaaarish kee paatraiyan tumhare pas lanee ya tum se lenee haain?
hamaree patraee tum hee ho, jo hamare dayon par likhee hui haai, aur use sab manushy pahichanate aur paddhte haai.
yah pragatt haai, ki tum maseeh kee patraee ho, jis ko ham ne sevakon kee nai likha aur jo siyahee se nahee, parantu jeevate parameshvar ke atma se patthr kee paattyaien par nahee, parantu day kee mans roopee paattyaien par likhee haai.
ham maseeh ke dara parameshvar par aeesa hee bhrosa rakhte haain.
yah nahee, ki ham apane ap se is yogy haai, ki apanee or se kisee bat ka vichar kar saken par hamaree yogyata parameshvar kee or se haai.
jis ne hamen nai vacha ke sevak hone ke yogy bhee kiya, shabd ke sevak naheen baran atma ke kyonaki shabd marata haai, par atma jilata haai.
aur yahad mratyu kee yah vacha jis ke akshar patthron par khod gaae the, yahan tak tejomay hui, ki moosa ke munh par ke tej ke karan jo ghattta bhee jata tha, israael usake munh par draashtti naheen kar sakate the.
to atma kee vacha aur bhee tejomay kyon n hogee?
kyonaki jab doshaee ttharanevalee vacha tejomay thee, to dharmee ttharanevalee vacha aur bhee tejomay kyon n hogee?
aur jo tejomay tha, vah bhee us tej ke karan jo us se baddhkar tejamay tha, kuchh tejomay n tthara.
kyonaki jab vah jo ghattta jata tha tejomay tha, to vah jo sthiar rahega, aur bhee tejomay kyon n hoga?
so aeesee asha rakhkar ham hiyav ke sath bolate haain.
aur moosar kee nain nahee, jis ne apane munh par parada dala tha taki israaelee us ghattnevalee vastu ke ant ko n dekhen.
parantu ve matimand ho gaa, kyonaki aj tak purane niyam ke paddhte samay un ke dayon par vahee parada pada rahata haai par vah maseeh men utt jata haai.
aur aj tak jab kabhee moosa kee pustak paddhee jatee haai, to un ke day par parada pada rahata haai.
prabhu to atma haai: aur jahan kaheen prabhu ka atma haai vahan svatantrata haai.
parantu jab ham sab ke ughaade chehare se prabhu ka pratap is prakar pragatt hota haai, jis prakar darpan me, to prabhu ke dara jo atma haai, ham usee tejasvee roop men ansh ansh kar ke badalate jate haain..
isaliye jab ham par aeesee daya hui, ki hamen yah seva milee, to ham hiyav naheen chhodte.
parantu ham ne lajja ke gupt kamon ko tyag diya, aur n chaturai se chalate, aur n parameshvar ke vachan men milavatt karate haai, parantu saty ko pragatt karake, parameshvar ke samhane har aek manushy ke vivek men apanee bhlai baaittate haain.
parantu yadi hamare susamachar par parada pada haai, to yah nash honevalon hee ke liye pada haai.
aur un aavishvasiyon ke liye, jin kee buddh iko is sansar ke ishvar ne andhaee kar dee haai, taki maseeh jo parameshvar ka praatiroop haai, usake tejomay susamachar ka prakash un par n chamake.
kyonaki ham apane ko nahee, parantu maseeh yeeshu ko prachar karate haai, ki vah prabhu haai aur usake vishay men yah kahate haai, ki ham yeeshu ke karan tumhare sevak haain.
isaliye ki parameshvar hee haai, jis ne kaha, ki andhakar men se jyoti chamake aur vahee hamare dayon men chamaka, ki parameshvar kee mahima kee paahichan kee jyoti yeeshu maseeh ke chehare se prakashaman ho..
parantu mahare pas yah dhan mitthee ke baratanon men rakha haai, ki yah aseem samarth hamaree or se nahee, baran parameshvar hee kee or se tthare.
ham charon or se klesh to bhogate haai, par sankatt men naheen padte niroopay to haai, par nirash naheen hote.
ham yeeshu kee mratyu ko apanee deh men har samay liye firate haain ki yeeshu ka jeevan bhee hamaree deh men pragatt ho.
kyonaki ham jeete jee sarvada yeeshu ke karan mratyu ke hath men saunpe jate haain ki yeeshu ka jeevan bhee hamare maranahar shareer men pragatt ho.
so mratyu to ham par prabhav dalatee haai aur jeevan tum para.
aur isaliye ki ham men vahee vishvas kee atma haai, jis ke vishay me likha haai, ki maain ne vishvas kiya, isaliye maain bola so ham bhee vishvas karate haai, isee liye bolate haain.
kyonaki ham jatane haai, jis ne prabhu yeeshu ko jilaya, vahee hamen bhee yeeshu men bhagee janakar jilaaega, aur tumhare sath apane samhane upaasthiat karega.
kyonaki sab vastuen tumhare liye haai, taki anugrah bahuton ke dara aadhaik hokar parameshvar kee maahima ke liye dhanyavad bhee baddhaae..
isaliye ham hiyav naheen chhodte yadhypi hamara baharee manushyatv nash bhee hota jata haai, taubhee hamara bheetaree manushyatv din pratidin naya hota jata haai.
kyonaki hamara pal bhr ka halka sa klesh hamare liye bahut hee mahatvapoorn aur anant jeevan maahima utpann karata jata haai.
aur ham to dekhee hui vastuon ko naheen parantu anadekhee vastuon ko dekhte rahate haai, kyonki dekhee hui vastuen thode hee din kee haai, parantu anadekhee vastuen sada banee rahatee haain.
kyonaki ham janate haai, ki jab hamara prathvee par ka dera sareekha ghar giraya jaaega to hamen parameshvar kee or se svarga par aek aeesa bhvan milega, jo hathon se bana hua ghar naheen parantu chirasthai haai.
is men to ham kaharate, aur badee lalasa rakhte haain ki apane svargeey ghar ko pahin len.
ki is ke pahinane se ham nange n paae jaaen.
aur ham is dere men rahate huae bojh se dabe kaharate rahate haain kyonaki ham utarana nahee, baran aur paahinana chahate haai, taki vah jo maranahar haai jeevan men oob jaae.
aur jis ne hamen isee bat ke liye taaiyar kiya haai vah parameshvar haai, jis ne hamen bayane men atma bhee diya haai.
so ham sada ddhaddhs bandho rahate haain aur yah janate haain ki jab tak ham deh men rahate haai, tab tak prabhu se alag haain.
kyonaki ham roop ko dekhkar nahee, par vishvas se chalate haain.
isaliye ham ddhaddhs bandho rahate haai, aur deh se alag hokar prabhu ke sath rahana aur bhee uttm samajhte haain.
is karan hamare man kee umang yah haai, ki chahe sath rahe, chahe alag rahen par ham use bhate rahen.
so prabhu ka bhy manakar ham logon ko samajhate haain aur parameshvar par hamara hal pragatt haai aur meree asha yah haai, ki tumhare vivek par bhee pragatt hua hoga.
ham fir bhee apanee badai tumhare samhane naheen karate baran ham apane vishay men tumhen ghamand karane ka avasar dete haai, ki tum unhen uttr de sako, jo man par nahee, baran dikhvattee baton par ghamand karate haain.
yaadi ham besudha haai, to parameshvar ke liye aur yaadi chaaitany haai, to tumhare liye haain.
kyonaki maseeh ka praem hamen vivash kar deta haai isaaliye ki ham yah samajhte haai, ki jab aek sab ke liye mara to sab mar gaae.
aur vah is nimitt sab ke liye mara, ki jo jeevit haai, ve age ko apane liye n jeeaen parantu usake liye jo un ke liye mara aur fir jee utta.
so ab se ham kisee ko shareer ke anusar n samajhenge, aur yaadi ham ne maseeh ko bhee shareer ke anusar jana tha, taubhee ab se us ko aeesa naheen janenge.
so yaadi koi maseeh men haai to vah nai sraashtti haai: puranee baten beet gai haain dekho, ve sab nai ho gain.
aur sab baten parameshvar kee or se haai, jis ne maseeh ke dara apane sath hamara mel milap kee seva hamen saunp dee haai.
arthata parameshvar ne maseeh men hokar apane sath sansar ka mel milap kar liya, aur un ke aparadhaen ka dosh un par naheen lagaya aur us ne mel milap ka vachan hamen saunp diya haai..
so ham maseeh ke rajadoot haain mano parameshvar hamare dara samajhata haai: ham maseeh kee or se nivedan karate haai, ki parameshvar ke sath mel milap kar lo.
jo pap se agyaat tha, usee ko us ne hamare liye pap ttharaya, ki ham us men hokar parameshvar kee dhaarmikata ban jaaen..
kyonaki vah to kahata haai, ki apanee prasannata ke samay maain ne teree sahayata kee: dekho, abhee uddhar ka din haai.
ham kisee bat men ttokar khane ka koi bhee avasar naheen dete, ki hamaree seva par koi dosh n aae.
parantu har bat men parameshvar ke sevakon kee nai apane sadagunon ko pragatt karate haai, bade dhaurya se, kleshaen se, daridrata se, sankatto se.
kode khane se, kaaid hone se, hulladon se, parishram se, jagate rahane se, upavas karane se.
paavitrata se, gyaan se, dhaeeraj se, krapaluta se, paavitra atma se.
sachche praem se, saty ke vachan se, parameshvar kee samarth se dhaaarmikata ke hathaiyaron se jo dahine, baaen haain.
adar aur niradar se, duranam aur sunam se, yadhypi bhramanevalon ke aeese maloom hote haain taubhee sachche haain.
anajanon ke sadrashy haain taubhee praasiddh haain marate huon ke aeese haain aur dekhon jeevit haain marakhanevalon ke sadrash haain parantu praan se mare naheen jate.
shaek karanevale ke saman haai, parantu sarvada anand karate haai, kangalon ke aeese haai, parantu bahuton ko dhanavan bana dete haain aeese haain jaaise hamare pas kuchh naheen taubhee sab kuchh rakhte haain.
he kuarinthiayo, ham ne khulakar tum se baten kee haai, hamara day tumharee or khula hua haai.
tumhare liye hamare man men kuchh saketee nahee, par tumhare hee manon men saketee haai.
par apane ladke-bale janakar tum se kahata hoo, ki tum bhee usake badale men apana day khol do..
aavishvasiyon ke sath asaman jooae men n juto, kyonki dhaaarmikata aur adharma ka kya mel jola? ya jyoti aur andhakar kee kya sangati?
aur maseeh ka baliyal ke sath kya lagava? ya vishvasee ke sath aavishvasee ka kya nata?
aur mooraton ke sath parameshvar ke mandair ka kya sambandha? kyonaki ham to jeevate parameshvar ka mandair haain jaaisa parameshvar ne kaha haai ki maain un men basoonga aur un men chala fira karoonga aur maain un ka parameshvar hoonga, aur ve mere log honge.
isaliye prabhu kahata haai, ki un ke beech men se nikalo aur alag raho aur ashuuddh vastu ko mat chooo, to maain tumhen grahan karoonga.
aur tumhara pita hoonga, aur tum mere bette aur bettyaian hoge: yah sarvashaktaiman prabhu parameshvar ka vachan haai..
hamen apane day men jagah do: ham ne n kisee se anyay kiya, n kisee ko bigada, aur n kisee ko ttga.
maain tumhen doshaee ttharane ke liye yah naheen kahata: kyonki maain paahile hee kah chooka hoo, ki tum hamare day men aeese bas gaae ho ki ham tumhare sath marane jeene ke liye taaiyar haain.
maain tum se bahut hiyav ke sath bol raha hoo, mujhe tum par bada ghamand haai: maain shaantai se bhr gaya hoon apane sare klesh men maain anand se aati bhrapoor rahata hoon..
kyonaki jab ham makiduaniya men aa, tab bhee hamare shareer ko chaain naheen mila, parantu ham charon or se klesh pate the bahar ladaiyan thee, bheetar bhyankar baten thee.
taubhee danon ko shaantai denevale parameshvar ne titus ke ane se ham ko shaaantai dee.
aur n keval usake ane se parantu us kee us shaantai se bhee, jo us ko tumharee or se milee thee aur us ne tumharee lalasa, aur tumhare dukh or mere liye tumharee dhaun ka samachar hamen sunaya, jis se mujhe aur bhee anand hua.
kyoki yadhyapi maain ne apanee patraee se tumhen shaeakit kiya, parantu us se pachhtata naheen jaaisa ki pahile pachhtata tha kyonki maain dekhta hoo, ki us patraee se tumhen shaek to hua parantu vah thodee der ke liye tha.
ab maain anaandait hoon par isaliye naheen ki tum ko shaek pahuncha baran isaliye ki tum ne us shaek ke karan man firaya, kyonki tumhara shaek parameshvar kee ichchha ke anusar tha, ki hamaree or se tumhen kisee bat men haani n pahunche.
kyonaki parameshvara-bhaktai ka shaek aeesa pashchatap utpann karata haai jis ka parinam uddhar haai aur fir us se pachhtana naheen padta: parantu sansaree shaek mratyu utpann karata haai.
so dekho, isee bat se ki tumheen parameshvara-bhktai ka shaek hua tum men kitanee uttejana aur pratyattr aur ris, aur bhy, aur lalasa, aur dhaun aur palaa lene ka vichar utpann hua? tum ne sab prakar se yah siddh kar dikhaya, ki tum is bat men nirdosh ho.
fir maain ne jo tumhare pas likha tha, vah n to usake karan likha, jis ne anyay kiya, aur n usake karan jis par anyay kiya gaya, parantu isaliye ki tumharee uttejana jo hamare liye haai, vah parameshvar ke samhane tum par pragatt ho jaae.
isaliye hamen shaaantai hui aur hamaree is shaantai ke sath titus ke anand ke karan aur bhee anand hua kayonaki usaka jee tum sab ke karan hara bhra ho gaya haai.
aur jab us ko tum sab ke agyaakaree hone ka smaran ata haai, ki kyonkar tum ne drate aur kanpate huae us se bhentt kee to usaka praem tumharee or aur bhee baddhta jata haai.
maain anand karata hoo, ki tumharee or se mujhe har bat men ddhaddhs hota haai..
ab he bhaiyo, ham tumhen parameshvar ke us anugrah ka samachar dete haai, jo makiduaniya kee kaleesiyaon par hua haai.
ki klesh kee badee pareeksha men un ke bade anand aur bharee kangalapan ke baddh jane se un kee udarata bahut baddh gai.
aur unake vishay men meree yah gavahee haai, ki unhon ne apanee samarth bhr baran samarth se bhee bahar man se diya.
aur is dan men aur paavitra logon kee seva men bhagee hone ke anugrah ke vishay men ham se bar bar bahut binatee kee.
aur jaaisee ham ne agyaa kee thee, vaaisee hee nahee, baran unhon ne prabhu ko, fir parameshvar kee ichchha se ham ko bhee apane tai de diya.
isaliye ham ne titus ko samajhaya, ki jesa us ne paahile arambh kiya tha, vaaisa hee tumhare beech men is dan ke kam ko poora bhee kar le.
so jaaise har bat men arthata vishvas, vachan, gyaan aur sab prakar ke yatn me, aur us praem me, jo ham se rakhte ho, baddhte jate ho, vaaise hee is dan ke kam men bhee baddhte jao.
maain agyaa kee reeati par to nahee, parantu aur ke utsah se tumhare praem kee sachchai ko parakhne ke liye kahata hoon.
