isaliye ab yah kam poora karo ki ichchha karane men tum taaiyar the, vaaisa hee apanee apanee poonjee ke anusar poora bhee karo.
kayonaki yadi man kee taaiyaree ho to dan usake anusar grahan bhee hota haai jo usake pas haai n ki usake anusar jo usake pas naheen.
yah naheenkh ki auro ko chaain aur tum ko klesh mile.
