aur aabvaiyon ne nibhj, aur tatrtak ko sthaapit kiya aur sapavamee log apane betton ko adrammelek aur anammelek nam sapavaainm ke devataon ke liye hom karake chaddhane lage.
yon ve yahava ka bhy manate to the, parantu sab prakar ke logon men se unche sthanon ke yajak bhee tthara dete the, jo unche sthanon ke bhvanon men unake liye baali karate the.
ve yahova ka bhy manate to the, parantu un jatiyon kee reeati par, jinake beech se ve nikale gaae the, apane apane devataon kee bhee upasana karate rahe.
aj ke din tak ve apanee pahilee reeatiyon par chalate haai, ve yahova ka bhy naheen manate.
parantu yahova jo tum ko bade bal aur baddhai hui bhuja ke dara miyara desh se nikal le aya, tum usee ka bhy manana, usee ko dandvat karana aur usee ko bali chaddhana.
aur us ne jo jo vidhaiyan aur niyam aur jo yyavastha aur agyaaaen tumhare liye likhee, unhen tum sada chaukasee se manate raho aur paraye devataon ka bhy n manana.
aur jo vacha maain ne tumhare sath bandhaee haai, use n boolana aur paraye devataon ka bhy n manana.
keval apane parameshvar yahova ka bhy panana, vahee tum ko tumhare sab shatrauon ke hath se bachaaega.
taubhee unhon ne n mana, parantu ve apanee paahilee reeati ke anusar karate rahe.
ataaev ve jaatiyan yahova ka bhy manatee to thee, parantu apanee khudee hui mooraton kee upasana bhee karatee rahee, aur jaaise ve karate the vaaise hee unake bette pote bhee aj ke din tak karate haain.
aela ke putra israaael ke raja hosho ke teesare varsha men yahooda ke raja ahaj ka putra hijaakiyyah raja hua.
jaaise usake moolapurush daud ne kiya tha jo yahova kee draashtti men tteek haai vaaisa hee us ne bhee kiya.
us ne unche sthan gira dia, latton ko tod diya, ashora ko katt dala. aur peetal ka jo sanp moosa ne banaya tha, usako us ne is karan choor choor kar diya, ki un dinon tak israaelee usake liye dhoop jalate the aur us ne usaka nam nahushatan rakha.
vah israaael ke parameshvar yahova par bhrosa rakhta tha, aur usake bad yahooda ke sab rajaon men koi usake barabar n hua, aur n us se paahile bhee aeesa koi hua tha.
aur vah yahova se lipatta raha aur usake peechhe chalana n chhoda aur jo agyaaaen yahova ne moosa ko dee thee, unaka vah palan karata raha.
isaliye yahova usake sang raha aur jahan kaheen vah jata tha, vahan usaka kam safal hota tha. aur us ne ashshoor ke raja se balava karake, usakee adhaeenata chhod dee.
us ne paalishtaiyon ko gajjaa aur usake sivanon tak, paharuon ke gummatt aur gaddhvale nagar tak mara.
raja hijaakiyyah ke chauthe varsha men jo aela ke putra israaael ke raja hosho ka satavan varsha tha, ashshoor ke raja shalmaneser ne shaemaron par chaddhai karake use ghor liya.
aur teen varsha ke beetane par unhon ne usako le liya. is prakar hijaakiyyah ke chhttven varsha men jo israaael ke raja hosho ka nauvan varsha tha, shaemaron le liya gaya.
tab ashshoor ka raja israaael ko bandhaua karake ashshoor men le gaya, aur halah men or gojan kee nadee habor ke pas aur madiyon ke nagaron men use basa diya.
isaka karan yah tha, ki unhon ne apane parameshvar yahova kee bat n manee, varan usakee vacha ko toda, aur jitanee agyaaaen yahova ke das moosa ne dee thee, unako ttal diya aur n unako suna aur n unake anusar kiya.
hijaakiyyah raja ke chaudahaven varsha men ashshoor ke raja sanhereeb ne yahooda ke sab gaddhvale nagaron par chaddhai karake unako le liya.
tab yahooda ke raja hijaakiyyah ne ashshoor ke raja ke pas lakeesh ko kahala bheja, ki mujh se aparadha hua, mere pas se lautt ja aur jo bhr too mujh par dalega usako maain uttaunga. to ashshoor ke raj ne yahooda ke raja hijaakiyyah ke liye teen sau kikkar chandee aur tees kikkar lona tthara diya.
tab jitanee chandee yahova ke bhvan aur rajabhvan ke bhndaron men milee, us sab ko hijaakiyyah ne use de diya.
us samay hijaakiyyah ne yahova ke mandair ke kivadon se aur un khmbhon se bhee jin par yahooda ke raja hijaakiyyah ne sona maddha tha, sone ko chheelakar ashshoor ke raja ko de diya.
taubhee ashshoor ke raja ne tatrtan, rabasarees aur rabashaake ko badee sena dekar, lakeesh se yarooshalem ke pas hijaakiyyah raja ke viruddh bhej diya. so ve yarooshalem ko gaae aur vahan pahunchakar upar ke pokhre kee nalee ke pas dhobiyon ke khet kee sadk par jakar khde huae.
aur jab unhon ne raja ko pukara, tab hilaakiyyah ka putra aelyakeem jo rajagharane ke kam par tha, aur shobna jo mantraee tha aur asap ka putra yoah jo iatihas ka likhnevala tha, ye teenon unake pas bahar nikal gaae.
rabashaake ne un se kaha, hijaakiyyah se kaho, ki maharajaadhairaj arthata ashshoor ka raja yon kahata haai, ki too kis par bhrosa karata haai?
too jo kahata haai, ki mere yahan yuddh ke liye yuaktai aur parakram haai, so to keval bat hee bat haai. too kis par bhrosa rakhta haai ki too ne mujh se balava kiya haai?
sun, too to us kuchale huae narakatt arthata misra par bhrosa rakhta haai, us par yadi koi ttek lagaa, to vah usake hath men chubhkar chhedega. misra ka raja firaun apane sab bhrosa rakhnevalon ke liye aeesa hee haai.
fir yadi tum mujh se kaho, ki hamara bhrosa apane parameshvar yahova par haai, to kya yah vahee naheen haai jisake unche sthanon aur vediyon ko hijaakiyyah ne door karake yahooda aur yarooshalem se kaha, ki tum isee vedee ke samhane jo yarooshalem men haai dandvat karana?
to ab mere svamee ashshoor ke raja ke pas muchh bandhak rak, tab maain tujhe do hajar ghaede doonga, kya too un par savar chaddha sakega ki naheen?
fir too mere svamee ke chhotte se chhotte karmacharee ka bhee kaha n man kar kyon rathon aur savaron ke liye misra par bhrosa rakhta haai?
tab hilaakiyyah ke putra aelyakeem aur shobna yoah ne rabashaake se kaha, apane dason se aramee bhasha men baten kar, kyonki ham use samajhte haain aur ham se yahoodee bhasha men shaharapanah par baaitte huae logon ke sunate baten n kara.
rabashaake ne un se kaha, kya mere svamee ne mujhe tumhare svamee hee ke, va tumhare hee pas ye baten kahane ko bheja haai? kya us ne mujhe un logon ke pas naheen bheja, jo shaharapanah par baaitte haai, taki numhare sang unako bhee apanee bishtta khana aur apana mootra peena pade?
tab rabashaake ne khde ho, yahoodee bhasha men unche shabd se kaha, maharajadhairaj arthta ashshoor ke raja kee bat suno.
raja yon kahata haai, ki hijaakiyyah tum ko bhulane n paa, kyonaki vah tumhen mere hath se bacha n sakega.
aur vah tum se yah kahakar yahova par bhrosa karane n paa, ki yahova nishchay ham ko bachaaega aur yah nagar ashshoor ke raja ke vash men n padega.
hijaakiyyah kee mat suno. ashshoor ka raja kahata haai ki bhentt bhejakar mujhe prasann karo aur mere pas nikal ao, aur pratyek apanee apanee dakhlata aur anjeer ke vraksha ke fal khata aur apane apane kund ka panee peeta rahe.
kya aur jatiyon ke devataon ne apane apane desh ko ashshoor ke raja ke hath se kabhee bachaya haai?
hamat aur arpad ke devata kahan rahe? sapavaainm, hena aur iyva ke devata kahan rahe? kya unhon ne shaemaron ko mere hath se bachaya haai,
desh desh ke sab devataon men se aeesa kaun haai, jis ne apane desh ko mere hath se bachaya ho? fir kya yahova yarooshalem ko mere hath se bachaaega.
parantu sab log chup rahe aur usake uttar men aek bat bhee n kahee, kyonaki raja kee aeesee agyaa thee, ki usako uttar n dena.
tab hilaakiyyah ka putra aelyakeem jo rajagharane ke kam par tha, aur shobna jo mantraee tha, aur asap ka putra yoah jo iatihas ka likhnevala tha, apane vasr faade hua, hijaakiyyah ke pas jakar rabashaake kee baten kah sunai.
jab hijaakiyyah raja ne yah suna, tab vah apane vasr faad, ttatt oddhkar yahova ke bhpan men gaya.
aur us ne aelyakeem ko jo rajagharane ke kam par tha, aur shobna mantraee ko, aur yajakon ke puraaniyon ko, jo sab ttatt oddhe huae the, amos ke putra yashaayah bhavishyadvkta ke pas bhej diya.
unhon ne us se kaha, hijaakiyyah yon kahata haai, aj ka din sankat, aur ulahane, aur ninda ka din haai bachche janmane par huae par jachcha ko janm dene ka bal n raha.
kadachit tera parameshvar yahova rabashaake kee sab baten sune, jise usake svamee ashshoor ke raja ne jeevate parameshvar kee ninda karane ko bheja haai, aur jo baten tere parameshvar yahava ne sunee haain unhen dpatte isaaliye too in bache huon ke liye jo rah gaae haain praarthna kara.
jab hijaakiyyah raja ke karmacharee yashaayah ke pas aa,
tab yashaayah ne un se kaha, apane svamee se kaho, yaheva yon kahata haai, ki jo vachan too ne sune haai, jinake dara ashshoor ke raja ke janon ne meree ninda kee haai, unake karan mat dra.
sun, maain usake man men praerana karoonga, ki vah kuchh samachar sunakar apane desh ko lautt jaa, aur maain usako usee ke desh men talavar se marava daloonga.
tab rabashaake ne lauttkar ashshoor ke raja ko libna nagar se yuddh karate paya, kyonki us ne suna tha ki vah lakeesh ke pas se utt gaya haai.
aur jab us ne koosh ke raja tirhaka ke vishy yah suna, ki vah mujh se ladne ko nikala haai, tab us ne hijaakiyyah ke pas dooton ko yah kah kar bheja,
tum yahooda ke raja hijaakiyyah se yon kahana tera parameshvar jisaka too bhrosa karata haai, yah kahakar tujhe dhaekha n dene paa, ki yarooshalem ashshoor ke raja ke vash men n padega.
dek, too ne to suna haai ashshoor ke rajaon ne sab deshaen se kaaisa yyavahar kiya haai unhen satyanash kar diya haai. fir kya too bachega?
gojan aaair haran aur resep aur talassar men rahanevale aedenee, jin jatiyoen ko mere purakhaon ne nash kiya, kya un men se kisee jaati ke devataon ne usako bacha liya?
hamat ka raja, aur arpad ka raja, aur samavaainm nagar ka raja, aur hena aur iyva ke raja ye sab kahan rahe? is patraee ko hijaakiyyah ne dooton ke hath se lekar paddha.
tab yahova ke bhvan men jakar usako yahova ke samhane faaila diya.
aur yahova se yah praarthna kee, ki he israaael ke parameshvar yahova ! he karoobon par virajanevale ! prathvee ke sab rajyon ke upar keval too hee parameshvar haai. akash aur prathvee ko too hee ne banaya haai.
he yahova ! kan lagakar sun, he yahova ankh kholakar dek, aur sanhereeb ke vachanoen ko sun le, jo us ne jeevate parameshvar kee ninda karane ko kahala bheje haain.
he yahova, sach to haai, ki ashshoor ke rajaon ne jatiyon ko aur unake deshaen ko ujada haai.
aur unake devataon ko ag men jhenka haai, kyonaki ve ishvar n the ve manushyon ke banaae huae katt aur patthr hee ke the is karan ve unako nash kar sake.
tab amos ke putra yashaayah ne hijaakiyyah ke pas yah kahala bheja, ki israaael ka parameshvar yahova yon kahata haai, ki jo praarthna too ne ashshoor ke raja sanhereeb ke vishay mujh se kee, use maain ne suna haai.
usake vishay men yahova ne yah vachan kaha haai, ki siyyon kee kumaree kanya tujhe tuchchh janatee aur tujhe tttthon men udatee haai, yarooshalem kee putrae, tujh par sir hilatee haai.
too ne jo namadharai aur ninda kee haai, vah kisakee kee haai? aur too ne jo bada bol bola aur ghamand kiya haai vah kisake viruddh kiya haai? israaael ke paavitra ke viruddh too ne kiya haai !
apane dooton ke dara too ne prabhu kee ninda karake kaha haai, ki vahut se rath lekar maain parvaton kee chottyaien par, varan labanon ke beech tak chaddh aya hoo, aur maain usake unche unche devadaruon aur achchhe achchhe sanovaron ko katt daloonga aur us men jo sab se uncha ttkaine ka sthan hoga us men aur usake van kee faladai bariyon men pravesh karoonga.
