maain to tera baaitta rahana, aur kooch karana, aur lautt ana janata hoo, aur yah bhee ki too mujh par apana krodha bhdkata haai.
is karan ki too mujh par apana krodha bhdkata aur tere aabhaiman kee baten mere kanon men padee haain maain teree nak men apanee nakel dalakar aur tere munh men apana lagam lagakar, jis marga se too aya haai, usee se tujhe lotta doonga.
