kyonaki yarooshalem men se bache huae aur siyyon parvat ke bhage huae log nikalenge. yahova yah kam apanee jalan ke karan karega.
isaliye yahova ashshoor ke raja ke vishay men yon kahata haai ki vah is nagar men pravesh karane, varan is par aek teer bhee marane n paaega, aur n vah ddhal lekar isake samhane ane, va isake viruddh damadama banane paaega.
jis marga se vah aya, usee se vah lautt bhee jaaega, aur is nagar men pravesh n karane paaega, yahova kee yahee vanee haai.
aur maain apane nimitt aur apane das daud ke nimitt is nagar kee raksha karake ise bachaunga.
usee rat men kya hua, ki yahova ke doot ne nikalakar ashshooriyon kee chhavanee men ek lakh pachasee hajar purushaen ko mara, aur bhor ko jab log sabere utte, tab dekha, ki loth hee loth padee haai.
tab ashshoor ka raja sanhereeb chal diya, aur lauttkar neenave men rahane laga.
vahan vah apane devata nisraek ke mandair men dandvat kar raha tha, ki ademmelek aur sareser ne usako talavar se mara, aur ararat desh men bhag gaae. aur usee ka putra aesarhaon usake sthan par rajy karane laga.
ahab ke marane ke bad moab israaael ke viruddh ho gaya.
