tab us ne bheet kee or munh faer, yahova se praarthna karake kaha, he yahova !
maain bintee karata hoo, smaran kar, ki maain sachchai aur khre man se apane ko tere sammukh janakar chalata aya hoo aur jo tujhe achchha tagata haai vahee maain karata aya hoo. tab hijaakiyyah bilak bilak kar roya.
aur aeesa hua ki yashaayah nagar ke beech tak jane bhee n paya tha ki yahova ka yah vachan usake pas pahuncha,
