aeese din anevale haai, jin men jo kuchh tere bhvan men haai, aur jo kuchh tere murakhaon ka rakha hua aj ke din tak bhndaron men haai vah sab babel ko utt jaaega yahova yah kahata haai, ki koi vastu n bachegee.
