abashaalom sab israaaelee logon samet yarooshalem ko aya, aur usake sang aheetopel bhee aya.
jab daud ka mitra aerekee hooshau abashaalom ke pas pahuncha, tab hooshau ne abashaalom se kaha, raja chiranjeev rahe ! raja chiranjeev rahe !
hooshau ne abashaalom se kaha, aeesa nahee jisako yahova aur ve log, kya varan sab israaaelee log chahe, usee ka maain hoo, aur usee ke sang maain rahoonga.
aur fir maain kisakee seva karoon? kya usake putra ke samhane rahakar seva n karoon? jaaisa maain tere pita ke samhane rahakar seva karata tha, vaaisa hee tere samhane rahakar seva karoonga.
tab abashaalom ne aheetopel se kaha, tum log apanee sammaati do, ki kya karana chaahiye?
aheetopel ne abashaalom se kaha, jin rakhealiyon ko tera pita bhvan kee chaukasee karane ko chhod gaya, unake pas too ja aur jab sab israaaelee yah sunenge, ki abashaalom ka pita us se ghain karata haai, tab tere sab sangee hiyav bandhonge.
so usakealiye bhvan kee chht ke upar aek tamboo khda kiya gaya, aur abashaalom samaroot israaael ke dekhte apane pita kee rakheliyon ke pas gaya.
un dinon jo sammaati aheetopel deta tha, vah aeesee hotee thee ki mano koi parameshvar ka vachan poochhleta ho aheetopel chahe daud ko chahe abashalom ko, jo jo sammati deta vah aeesee hee hotee thee.
fir aheetopel ne abashaalom se kaha, mujhe barah hajar purush chhanttne de, aur maain uttkar aj hee rat ko daud ka peechha karoonga.
aur jab vah thakit aur nirbal hoga, tab maain use pakadoonga, aur draunga aur jitane log usake sath haain sab bhagenge. aur maain raja hee ko maroonga,
aur maain sab logon ko tere pas lautta launga jis manushy ka too khojee haai usake milane me samast praja ka milana ho jaaega, aur samast praja kushal kshom se rahegee.
yah bat abashaalom aur sab israaaelee puraniyon ko uchit maloom padee.
fir abashaalom ne kaha, aerekee hooshau ko bhee bula la, aur jo vah kahega ham use bhee sunen.
jab hooshau abashaalom ke pas aya, tab abashaalom ne us se kaha, aheetopel ne to is prakar kee bat kahee haai kya ham usakee bat manen ki nahee? saadi nahee, to too kah de.
hooshau ne abashaalom se kaha, jo sammati aheetopel ne is bar dee vah achchhee naheen.
fir hooshau ne kaha, too to apane pita aur usake janon ko janata haai ki ve shooraveer haai, aur bachcha chheenee hui reechhnee ke saman odhait honge. aur tera pita yoddha haai aur aur logo ke sath rat naheen bitata.
is samay to vah kisee gaddhhe, va kisee doosare sthan men chhpai hoga. jab in men se paahile paahile koi koi mare jaae, tab isake sab sunanevale kahane lagenge, ki abashaalom ke pakshavale har gaae.
tab veer ka day, jo sinh ka sa hota haai, usaka bhee hiyav choott jaaega, samast israaael to janata haai ki tera pita veer haai, aur usake sangee bade yoddha haain.
isaliye meree sammati yah haai ki dan se lekar beshorba tak rahanevale samast israaaelee tere pas samudrateer kee baloo ke kinakon ke saman akatthe kiae jaa, aur too ap hee yuddh ko jaae.
aur yaadi vah kisee nagar men ghausa ho, to sab israaaelee us nagar ke pas raassaiyan le aaenge, aur ham use nale men kheenchenge, yahan tak ki usaka aek chhotta sa patthr bhee n rah jaaega.
tab abashaalom aur sab israaaelee purushaen ne kaha, aerekee hooshau kee bammaati aheetopel kee sammaati se umtam haai. sahova ne to aheetopel kee achchhee sammati ko nishfal karane ke liye ttana tha, ki yah abashaalom hee par vipaattai dale.
tab hooshau ne sadok aur aebyatar yajakon se kaha, aheetopel ne to abashaalom aur israaaelee puraniyon ko is is prakar kee sammati dee aur maain ne is is prakar kee sammati dee haai.
isaliye ab fauta kar daud ke pas kahala bhejo, ki aj rat jangalee ghaatt ke pas n ttharana, avashy par hee ho jana aeesa n ho ki raja aur jitane log usake sang ho, sab nash ho jaaen.
yonatan aur aheemay aenarogel ke pas tthare rahe aur aek laundee jakar unhen sandesha de atee thee, aur ve jakar raja daud ko sandesha dete the kyonki ve kisee ke dekhte nagar men nahee ja sakate the.
aek chhokare ne to unhen dekhkar abashaalom ko bataya parantu ve donon fauta se chale gaa, aur aek bahareemavasee manushy ke ghar pahunchakar jisake angan men kuna tha us men utar gaae.
tab usakee sree ne kapada lekar kunae ke munh par bichhaya, aur usake upar dalar hua ann faaila diya isaliye kuchh maloom n pada.
tab abashaalom ke sevak us ghar men us sree ke pas jakar kahane lage, aheemas aur yonatan kahan haain? sree ne un se kaha, ve to us chhottee nadee ke par gaae. tab unhon ne unhen ddoonddha, aur n pakar yarooshalem ko lautte.
jab ve chale gaa, tab ye kunae men se nikale, aur jakar daud raja ko samachar diya aur daud se kaha, tum log chalo, fauta karake nadee ke par ho jao kyonaki aheetopel ne tumharee hani kee aeesee aeesee sammati dee haai.
tab daud apane sab sanagiyon samet uttkar yaradan par ho gaya aur pah fattne tak un men se aek bhee n rah gaya jo yaradan ke par n ho gaya ho.
jab aheetopel ne dekha ki meree sammaati ke anusar kam naheen hua, tab us ne apane gadahe par kattee kasee, aur apane nagar men jakar apane ghar men gaya. aur apane gharane ke vishay jo jo agyaa denee thee vah dekar apane ko faansee laga lee aur vah mar gaya, aur usake pita ke kaabirstan men use mittee de dee gai.
aur abashaalom ne amasa ko yoab ke sthan par pradhaan senapaati ttharaya. yah amasa aek purush ka putra tha jisaka nam israaaelee yitrae tha, aur vah yoab kee mata, sarooyah kee bahin, abeegal nam nahash kee bettee ke sang soya tha.
aur israaaeliyon ne aur abashaalom ne gilad desh men chhavanee dalee.
jab daud mahanaaim men aya, tab ammoniyon ke rabba ke nivasee nahash ka putra shaebee, aur lodabaravasee ammeeael ka putra makeer, aur rogaleemavasee giladee barjillaai,
charapaiya, tasale mittee ke bartan, gehoo, jav, maaida, lobiya, masoor, chabena,
madha, makkhn, bhedbakariya, aur gay ke dahee ka paneer, daud aur usake sanagiyon ke khane ko yah sochakar le aa, ki jangal men ve log bookhe pyase aur thke mande honge.
tab daud ne apane sang ke logon kee ginatee lee, aur un par sahasrpaati aur shatapati ttharaae.
fir daud ne logon kee aek tihai to yoab ke, aur aek tihai sarooyah ke putra yoab ke bhai abeeshau ke, aur aek tihai gatee itteai ke, aadhaikar men karake yuddh men bhej diya. aur raja ne logon se kaha, maain bhee avashy tumhare sath chaloonga.
logoen ne kaha, too jane n paaega. kyonaki chahe ham bhag jaae, taubhee ve hamaree chinta n karenge varan chahe ham men se adho mare bhee jaae, taubhee ve hamaree chinta n karenge. kyonki hamare sareekhe das hajaar purush haain isaaliye achchha yah haai ki too nagar men se hamaree sahayata karane ko taaiyar rahe.
raja ne un se kaha, jo kuchh tumhen bhaae vahee maain karoonga. aur raja faattk kee aek or khda raha, aur sab log sau sau, aur hajaar, hajaar karake nikalane lage.
aur raja ne yoab, abeeshau, aur itte ko agyaa dee, ki mere nimitt us javan, arthata abashaalom se komalata karana. yah agyaa raja ne abashaalom ke vishay sab pradhaanon ko sab logon ke sunate dee.
so log israaael ka samhala karane ko maaidan men nikale aur aepraaim nam van men yuddh hua.
vahan israaaelee log daud ke janon se har gaa, aur us din aeesa bada sanhar hua ki bees hajar khet aae.
aur yuddh us samast desh men faail gaya aur us din jitane log talavar se mare gaa, un se bhee adhaik van ke karan mar gaae.
sanyog se abashaalom aur daud ke janon kee bhentt ho gai. abashaalom to aek khchchar par chaddha hua ja raha tha, ki khchchar aek bade banj vraksha kee ghanee daaliyon ke neeche se gaya, aur usaka sir us banj vraksha men attk gaya, aur vah adhar men lattka rah gaya, aur usaka khchchar nikal gaya.
isako dekhkar kisee manushy ne yoab ko bataya, ki maain ne abashaalom ko banj vraksha men ttnga hua dekha.
yoab ne batanevale se kaha, too ne yah dekha ! fir kyon use vaheen marake boomi par n gira diya? to maain tujhe das tukade chandee aur aek kattbaind deta.
us manushy ne yoab se kaha, chahe mere hath men hajaar ttukade chandee taulakar diae jaaee, taubhee rajakumar ke viruddh hath n baddhaunga kyonaki ham logon ke sunate raja ne tujhe aur abeeshau aur ittaai ko yah agyaa dee, ki tum men se koi kyon n ho us javan arthata abashaalom ko n chooe.
yaadi maain dhaekha dekar usaka praan leta, to too ap mera virodhaee ho jata, kyonaki raja se koi bat chhpaiee naheen rahatee.
tab yoab ke das hathaiyar ddhonevale javanon ne abashaalom ko ghorake aeesa mara ki vah mar gaya.
fir yoab ne narasinga foonka, aur log inraaael ka peechha karane se lautte kyonki yoab praja ko bachana chahata tha.
tab logon ne abashaalom ko utarake us van ke aek bade gadhe men dal diya, aur us par patthron ka aek bahut bada ddher laga diya aur sab israaaelee apate apane dere ko bhag gaae.
apane jeete jee abashaalom ne yah sochakar ki mere nam ka smaran karanevala koi putra mere naheen haai, apane liye vah latt khdee karai thee jo raja kee tarai men haai aur latt ka apana hee nam rakha, jo aj ke din tak abashaalom kee latt kahalatee haai.
aur sadok ke putra aheemas ne kaha, mujhe daudkar raja ko yah samachar dene de, ki yahova ne nyay karake tujhe tere shatrauon ke hath se bachaya haai.
yoab ne us se kaha, too aj ke din samachar n de doosare din samachar dene paaega, parantu aj samachar n de, isaaliye ki rajakumar mar gaya haai.
tab yoab ne aek kooshaee se kaha jo kuchh too ne dekha haai vah jakar raja ko bata de. to vah kooshaee yoab ko dandvata karake daud gaya.
fir sadok ke putra aheemas ne doosaree bar yoab se kaha, jo ho so ho, parantu mujhe bhee kooshaee ke peechhe daud jane de. yoab ne kaha, he mere bette, tere samachar ka kuchh badala n milega, fir too kyon daud jana chahata haai?
us ne yah kaha, jo ho so ho, parantu mujhe daud jane de. usane us se kaha, daud. tab aheemas dauda, aur tarai se hokar kooshaee ke age baddh gaya.
daud to do faattkon ke beech baaitta tha, ki paharua jo faattk kee chht se hokar shaharapanah par chaddh gaya tha, us ne ankhen uttakar kya dekha, ki aek manushy akela dauda ata haai.
fir paharuae ne aek aur manushy ko daudte huae dekh faattk ke rakhvale ko pukarake kaha, sun, aek aur manushy akela dauda ata haai. raja ne kaha, vah bhee sandesha lata hoga.
paharuae ne kaha, pujhe to aeesa dekh padta haai ki pahale ka daudna sadok ke putra aheemas ka sa haai. raja ne kaha, vah to bhla manushy haai, to bhla sandesh lata hoga.
tab aheemas ne pukarake raja se kaha, kalyan. fir us ne boomi par munh ke bal gir raja ko dandvata karake kaha, tera parameshvar yahova dhany haai, jis ne mere prabhu raja ke viruddh hath uttanevale manushyon ko tere vash men kar diya haai !
raja ne poochha, kya us javan abashaalom ka kalyan haai? aheemas ne kaha, jab yoab ne raja ke karmacharee ko aur tere das ko bhej diya, tab mujhe badee bheed dekh padee, parantu maloom n hua ki kya hua tha.
raja ne kaha hattkar yaheen khda raha. aur vah hattkar khda raha.
tab kooshaee bhee a gaya aur kooshaee kahane laga, mere prabhu raja ke liye samachar haai. yahova ne aj nyay karake tujhe un sabhon ke hath se bachaya haai jo tere viruddh utte the.
raja ne kooshaee se poochha, kya vah javan arthata abashaalom kalyan se haai? kooshaee ne kaha, mere prabhu raja ke shatra, aur jitane teree haani ke liye utte haai, unakee dasha us javan kee see ho.
tab raja bahut ghabaraya, aur faattk ke upar kee attaree par rota hua chaddhne laga aur chalate chalate yon kahata gaya, ki hay mere bette abashaalom ! mere bette, hay ! mere bette abashaalom ! bhla hota ki maain ap teree santee marata, hay ! abashaalom ! mere bette, mere bette !!
tab yoab ko yah samachar mila, ki raja abashaalom ke liye ro raha haai aur vilap kar raha haai.
isaliye us din ka vijay sab logon kee samajh men vilap hee ka karan ban gaya kyonaki logon ne us din suna, ki raja apane bette ke liye kheadit haai.
aur us din log aeesa munh churakar nagar men ghause, jaaisa log yuddh se bhag ane se lajjait hokar munh churate haain.
aur raja munh ddhanpe huae chilla chillakar pukarata raha, ki hay mere bette abashaalom ! hay abashaalom, mere bette, mere bette !
tab yoab ghar men raja ke pas jakar kahane laga, tere karmachariyon ne aj ke din tera, aur tere bette-beattyaien ka aur teree patnaiyon aur rakheliyon ka praan to bachaya haai, parantu too te aj ke din un sabhon ka munh kala kiya haai
isaliye ki too apane baaiariyon se praem aur apane praeamiyon se baair rakhta haai. too ne aj yah pragatt kiya ki tujhe haakimon aur karmachaariyon kee kuchh chinta naheen varan maain ne aj jan liya, ki yadi ham sab aj mare jate aur abashaalom jeevit rahata, to too bahut prasann hota.
isaliye ab uttkar bahar ja, aur apane karmachariyon ko shaantai de taheen to maain yahova kee shapath khakar kahata hoo, ki yadi too bahar n jaaega, to aj rat ko aek manushy bhee tere sang n rahega aur tere bachapan se lekar ab tak jitanee vipaattaiyan tujh par padee haain un sab se yah vipaattai badee hogee.
tab raja uttkar faattk men ja baaitta. aur jab sab logon ko yah bataya gaya, ki raja faattk men baaitta haai tab sab log raja ke samhane aae. aur israaaelee apane apane dere ko bhag gaae the.
aur israaael ke sab gotron men sab log apas men yah kahakar ddhgadte the, ki raja ne hamen hamare shatrauon ke hath se bachaya tha, aur paalishtaiyon ke hath se usee ne hamen chhudaya parantu ab vah abashaalom ke dr ke mare desh chhodkar bhag gaya.
aur abashaalom jisako ham ne apana raja hone ko abhaishok kiya tha, vah yuddh men mar gaya haai. to ab tum kyon chup rahate? aur jaja ko lautta le apane kee charcha kyon naheen karate?
tab raja daud ne sadok aur aebyatar yajakon ke pas kahala bheja, ki yahoodee puraniyon se kaho, ki tum log raja ko bhvan pahunchane ke liye sab se peechhe kyon hote ho jab ki samast israaael kee batacheet raja ke sunane men ai haai, ki usako bhvan men pahunchaae?
fir amasa se yah kaho, ki kya too meree haddee aur mans naheen haai? aur yadi too yoab ke sthan par sada ke liye senapaati n tthare, to parameshvar mujh se vaaisa hee varan us se bhee adhaik kare.
is prakar us ne sab yahoodee purushaen ke man aeese apanee or kheench liya ki manon aek hee purush tha aur unhon ne raja ke pas kahala bheja, ki too apane sab karpachariyon ko sang lekar lautt a.
tab raja lauttkar yaradan tak a gaya aur yahoodee log gilagal tak gaae ki us se milakar use yaradan par le aae.
yahoodiyon ke sang gera ka putra binyameenee shaimee bhee jo bahooreemee tha fauta karake raja daud se bhentt karane ko gaya
usake sang hajaar binyameenee purush the. aur shaaul ke gharane ka karmacharee seeba apane pandrah putraen aur bees dason samet tha, aur ve raja ke samhane yaradan ke par panv paaidal utar gae.
aur aek beda raja ke parivar ko par le ane, aur jis kam men vah use lagane chahe usee men lagane ke liye par gaya. aur jab raja yaradan par jane par tha, tab gera ka putra shaimee usake pavon par girake,
raja se kahane laga, mera prabhu mere dosh ka lekha n kare, aur jis din mera prabhu raja yarooshalem ko chhod aya, us din tere das ne jo kuattlai kam kiya, use aeesa smaran n kar ki raja use apane dhyan men rakhe.
kyonaki tera das janata haai ki maain ne pap kiya dek, aj apane prabhu raja se bhentt karane ke liye yoosufa ke samast ghrane men se maain hee pahila aya hoo.
tab sarooyah ke putra abeeshau ne kaha, shaimee ne jo yahova ke aabhaishaikt ko shaap diya tha, is karan kya usako vadha karana n chaahiye?
fir raja ne shaimee se kaha, tujhe praan dand n milega. aur raja ne us se shapath bhee khai.
tab shaaul ka pota mapeeboshot raja se bhentt karane ko aya us ne raja ke chale jane ke din se usake kushal kshom se fir ane ke din tak n apane pavon ke nakoon katte, aur n apanee daddhee banavai, aur n apane kapade dhaulavaae the.
to jab yarooshalemee raja se milane ko gaa, tab raja ne us se poochha, he mapeeboshot, too mere sang kyon naheen gaya tha?
us ne kaha, he mere prabhu, he raja, mere karmacharee ne mujhe dhaekha diya tha tera das jo pangu haai isaliye tere das ne socha, ki maain gadahe par kattee kasavakar us par chaddh raja ke sath chala jaunga.
aur mere karmacharee ne mere prabhu raja ke samhane meree chugalee khai. parantu mera prabhu raja parameshvar ke doot ke saman haai aur jo kuchh tujhe bhaae vahee kara.
mere pita ka samast gharana teree or se praan dand ke yogy tha parantu too ne apane das ko apanee mej par khanevalon men gina haai. mujhe kya hak haai ki maain raja kee or dohai doon?
raja ne us se kaha, too apanee bat kee charcha kson karata rahata haai? meree agyaa yah haai, ki us boomi ko tum aur seeba donon apas men bantt lo.
mapeeboshot ne raja se kaha, mere prabhu raja jo kushal kshom se apane ghar aya haai, isaaliye seeba hee sab kuchh le le.
tab giladee barjillaai rogaleem se aya, aur raja ke sath yaradan par gaya, ki usako yaradan ke par pahunchaae.
baarjillaai to vraddh purush tha, arthata assee parsha kee ayu ka tha jab tak raja mahanaaim men rahata tha tab tak vah usaka palan poshan karata raha kyonaki vah bahut dhanee tha.
tab raja ne barjillaai se kaha, mere sang par chal, aur maain tujhe yarooshalem men apane pas rakhkar tera palan poshan karoonga.
baarjillaai ne raja se kaha, mujhe kitane din jeevit rahana haai, ki maain raja ke sang yarooshalenm ko jaun?
aj maain assee varsha ka hoo kya maain bhle-bure ka vivek kar sakata hoo? kya tera das jo kuchh khata peeta haai usaka svad paahichan sakata haai? kya mujhe gavaaiyyon va gayikaon ka shabd ab sun padta haai? tera das ab apane prabhu raja ke liye kyon bojh ka karan ho?
tere das raja ke sang yaradan par hee tak jaaega. raja isaka aeesa bada badala mujhe kyon de?
apane das ko lauttne de, ki maain apane hee nagar men apane mata pita ke kaabirstan ke pas maroon. parantu tera das kimham upaasthiat haai mere prabhu raja ke sang vah par jaae aur jaaisa tujhe bhaae vaaiya hee us se vyavahar karana.
raja ne kaha, ha, kimhan mere sang par chalega, aur jaaisa tujhe bhaae vaaisa hee maain us se vyavahar karoonga varan jo kuchh too mujh se chahega vah maain tere liye karoonga.
tab sab log yaradan par gaa, aur raja bhee par hua tab raja ne baarjillaai ko choomakar ashaeervad diya, aur vah apane sthan ko lautt gaya.
tab raja gilgal kee or par gaya, aur usake sang kimham par hua aur sab sahoodee logon ne aur adho israaaelee logon ne raja ko par pahunchaya.
tab sab israaaelee purush raja ke pas aa, aur raja se kahane lage, kya karan haai ki hamare yahoodee bhai tujhe choree se le aa, aur parivar samet raja ko aur usake sab janon ko bhee yaradan par le aae haain?
sab yahoodee purushaen ne israaaelee purushaen ko uttar diya, ki karan yah haai ki raja hamare gotra ka haai. to tum log is bat se kyon roott gaae ho? kya ham ne raja ka diya hua kuchh khaya haai? va us ne hamen kuchh dan diya haai?
shaaul ke marane ke bad, jab daud amaleakiyon ko marakar lautta, aur daud ko sikalag men rahate huae do din ho gaa,
tab teesare din aeesa hua ki chhavanee men se shaaul ke pas se aek purush kapade faade sir par dhoolee dale huae aya. aur jab vah daud ke pas pahuncha, tab boomi par gira aur dandvata kiya.
daud ne us se poochha, too kahan se aya haai? us ne us se kaha, maain israaaelee chhavanee men se bachakar aya hoon.
daud ne us se poochha, vahan kya bat hui? mujhe bata. us ne kaha, yah, ki log ranboomi chhodkar bhag gaa, aur bahut log mare gaae aur shaaul aur usaka putra yonatan bhee mare gaae haain.
daud ne us samachar denevale javan se poochha, ki too kaaise janata haai ki shaaul aur usaka putra yonatan mar gaae?
samachar denevale javan ne kaha, sanyog se maain gilabo pahad par tha to kya dekha, ki shaaul apane bhale kee ttek lagaae huae haai fir maain ne yah bhee dekha ki usaka peechha kiae huae rath aur savar bade veg se daude a rahe haain.
us ne peechhe firakar mujhe dekha, aur mujhe pukara. maain ne kaha,kya agyaa?
us ne mujh se poochha, too kaun haai? maain ne us se kaha, maain to amalekee hoo.
tab maain ne yah nishchay jan liya, ki vah gir jane ke pahachata naheen bach sakata, usake pas khde hokar use mar dala aur maain usake sir ka mukutt aur usake hath ka kangan lekar yahan apane prabhu ke pas aya hoo.
tab daud ne apane kapade pakadkar faade aur jitane purush usake sang the unhon ne bhee vaaisa hee kiya
aur ve shaaul, aur usake putra yonatan, aur yahova kee praja, aur israaael ke gharane ke liye chhatee peettne aur rone lage, aur sanjh tak kuchh n khaya, is karan ki ve talavar se mare gaae the.
fir daud ne us samachar denevale javan se poochha, too kahan ka haai? us ne kaha, maain to paradeshaee ka betta arthata amalekee hoo.
daud ne us se kaha, too yahova ke aabhaishaikt ko nash karane ke liye hath baddhane se kyon naheen dra?
tab daud ne aek javan ko bulakar kaha, nikatt jakar us par prahar kara. tab us ne use aeesa mara ki vah mar gaya.
aur daud ne us se kaha, tera koon tere hee sir par pade kyonki too ne yah kahakar ki maain hee ne yahova ke aabhaishaikt ko mar dala, apane munh se apane hee viruddh sakshaee dee haai.
shaaul aur yonatan ke liye daud ka banaya hua vilapageet tab daud ne shaaul aur usake putra yonatan ke vishay yah vilapageet banaya,
aur yahoodiyon ko yah dhanush nam geet sikhane kee agyaa dee yah yashaar nam pustak men likha hua haai
he israaael, tera shairomanai tere unche sthan par mara gaya. hay, shooraveer kyonkar gir pade haain!
gat men yah n batao, aur n ashkalon kee sadkon men prachar karana n ho ki palishtee striyan anandait ho, n ho ki khtanaraahit logon kee beattyaian garva karane lagen.
he gilabo pahado, tum par n os pade, aur n vashara ho, aur n bhentt ke yogy upajavale khet paae jaaen! kyonki vahan shooraveeron kee ddhalen ashuuddh ho gai. aur shaaul kee ddhal bina tel lagaae rah gai.
joojhe huon ke lohoo bahane se, aur shooraveeron kee charbee khane se, yonatan ka dhanush lautt n jata tha, aur n shaaul kee talavar choochhee fir atee thee.
shaaul aur yonatan jeevanakal men to piry aur manabha the, aur apanee mratyu ke samay alag n hue ve ukab se bhee veg chalanevale, aur sinh se bhee aadhaik parakramee tho.
he israaaelee striyo, shaaul ke liye roo, vah to tumhen lal rang ke vastr paahinakar sukh deta, aur tumhare vastron ke upar sone ke gahane paahinata tha.
hay, yuddh ke beech shooraveer kaaise kam aae ! he yonatan, he unche sthanon par joojhe hua,
he mere bhai yonatan, maain tere karan dukhait hoo too mujhe bahut manabha jan padta tha tera praem mujh par adabhut, varan striyon ke praem se bhee baddhkar tha.
hay, shooraveer kyonkar gir gaa, aur yuddh ke haathaiyar kaaise nash ho gaae haain !
vahan sanyog se shoba nam aek binyameenee tha, vah ochha purush bikree ka putra tha vah naraasinga foonkakar kahane laga, daud men hamara kuchh ansh nahee, aur n yishau ke putra men hamara koi bhag haai he israaaeliyo, apane apane dere ko chale jao !
isaliye sab israaaelee purush daud ke peechhe chalana chhodkar bikree ke putra shoba ke peechhe ho liae parantu sab yahoodee purush yaradan se yarooshalem tak apane raja ke sang lage rahe.
tab daud yarooshalem ko apane bhvan men aya aur raja ne un das rakhealiyon ko, jinhen vah bhvan kee chaukasee karane ko chhod gaya tha, alag aek ghar men rakha, aur unaka palan poshan karata raha, parantu un se sahavas n kiya. isaliye ve apanee apanee mratyu ke din tak vidhavapan kee see dasha men jeevit hee band rahee.
tab amasa yahoodiyon ko bulane gaya parantu usake ttharaae huae samay se adhaik rah gaya.
tab daud ne abeeshau se kaha, ab bikree ka putra shoba abashaalom se bhee hamaree aadhaik hani karega isaaliye too apane prabhu ke logon ko lekar usaka peechha kar, aeesa n ho ki vah gaddhvale nagar pakar hamaree drashtti se chhpai jaae.
tab yoab ke jan, aur karetee aur paletee log, aur sab shooraveer usake peechhe ho liae aur bikree ke putra shoba ka peechha karane ko yarooshalem se nikale.
ve gibon men us bharee patthr ke pas pahunche hee the, ki amasa un se a mila. yoab to yoddha ka vasr faette se kase huae tha, aur us faette men aek talavar usakee kamar par apanee myan men bandhaee hui thee aur jab vah chala, tab vah nikalakar gir padee.
to yoab ne amasa se poochha, he mere bhai, kya too kushal se haai? tab yoab ne apana dahina hath baddhakar amasa ko choomane ke liye usakee daddhee pakadee.
parantu amasa ne us talavar kee kuchh chinta n kee jo yaab ke hath men thee aur us ne use amasa ke pett men bhonk dee, jis se usakee antadiyan nikalakar dharatee par gir padee, aur us ne usako doosaree bar n mara aur vah mar gaya. tab yoab aur usaka bhai abeeshau bikree ke putra shoba ka peechha karane ko chale.
aur usake pas yaab ka aek javan khda hokar kahane laga, jo koi yoab ke paksha aur daud kee or ka ho vah yoab ke peechhe ho le.
usake sadk par se sarakaae jane par, sab log bikree ke putra shoba ka peechha karane ko yoab ke peechhe ho lie.
aur vah sab israaaelee gotron men hokar abel aur betamaka aur beariyon ke desh tak pahuncha aur ve bhee ikatthe hokar usake peechhe ho liae.
tab unhon ne usako betamaka ke abel men ghor liya aur nagar ke samhane aeesa damadama bandha ki vah shaharapanah se satt gaya aur yoab ke sang ke sab log shaharapanah ko girane ke liye dhakka dene lage.
tab aek buaddhiman rootraee ne nagar men se pukara, suno ! suno ! yoab se kaho, ki yahan aa, taki maain us se kuchh baten karoon.
jab yoab usake nikatt gaya, tab sree ne poochha, kya too yoab haai? us ne kaha, ha, maain vahee hoo. fir us ne us se kaha, apanee dasee ke vachan suna. us ne kaha, maain to sun raha hoo.
vah kahane lagee, praacheenakal men to log kaha karate the, ki abel men poochha jaae aur is reeti jhgade ko nipatta dete the.
maain to melaamilapavale aur vishvasayogy israaaeliyon men se hoo parantu too aek pradhan nagar nash karane ka yatn karata haai too yahova ke bhag ko kyon nigal jaaega?
yoab ne uttar dekar kaha, yah mujh se door ho, door, ki maain nigal jaun va nash karoon !
bat aeesee naheen haai. shoba nam aepraaim ke pahadee desh ka aek purush jo bikree ka putra haai, us ne daud raja ke viruddh hath uttaaya haai to tum log keval usee ko saunp do, tab maain nagar ko chhodkar chala jaunga. sree ne yoab se kaha, usaka sir shaharapanah par se tere pas faenk diya jaaega.
tab sree apanee buaddhimanee se sab logon ke pas gai. tab unhon ne bikree ke putra shoba ka sir kattkar yoab ke pas faenk diya. tab yoab ne naraasinga foonka, aur sab log nagar ke pas se alag alag hokar apane apane dere ko gaae. aur yoab yarooshalem ko raja ke pas lautt gaya.
yoab to samast israaaelee sena ke upar pradhaan raha aur yahoyada ka mutra banayah karetiyon aur paletiyon ke upar tha
aur adoram begaron ke upar tha aur aheelood ka putra yahoshaapat itihas ka lekhk tha
aur shaya mantraee tha aur sadok aur aebyatar yajak the
aur yairee ira bhee daud ka aek mantraee tha.
daud ke dinon men lagatar teen baras tak akal pada to daud ne yahova se praarthna kee. yahova ne kaha, yah shaaul aur usake koonee gharane ke karan hua, kyonki us ne giboniyon ko marava dala tha.
tab raja ne giboniyo ko bulakar un se baten keen. gibonee log to israaaeliyon men se naheen the, ve bache huae aemoriyo men se the aur israaaeliyon ne unake sath shapath khai thee, parantu shaaul ko jo israaaeliyon aur yahoodiyon ke diye jalan hui thee, is se us ne unhen mar dasane ke liye yatn kiya tha.
tab daud ne giboniyon se poochha, maain tumhare liye kya karoon? aur kya karake aeesa praayashchait karoo, ki tum yahova ke nij bhag ko ashaeervad de sako?
giboniyon ne us se kaha, hamare aur shaaul va usake gharane ke madhy rupaye paaise ka kuchh jhgada naheen aur n hamara kam haai ki kisee israaaelee ko mar dalen. us ne kaha, jo kuchh tum kaho, vahee maain tumhare liye karoonga.
unhon ne raja se kaha, jis purush ne ham ko nash kar diya, aur hamare viruddh aeesee yuktai dee ki ham aeese satyanash ho jae, ki israael ke desh men age ko n rah sake,
usake vansh ke sat jan hamen saunp diae jae, aur ham unhen yahova ke liye yahova ke chune huae shaaul kee giba nam bastee men faansee denge. raja ne kaha, maain unako saunp doonga.
parantu daud ne aur shaaul ke putra yonatan ne apas men yahova kee shapath khai thee, is karan raja ne yonatan ke putra mapeeboshot ko jo shaaul ka pota tha bacha rakha.
parantu amanee aur mapeeboshot nam, ayya kee bettee rispa ke donon putra jo shaaul se utpann huae the aur haaul kee bettee meekal ke panchon bette, jo vah maholavasee barjillaai ke putra adraeeael kee or se the, inako raja ne pakadvakar
tab ayya kee bettee rispa ne ttatt lekar, kattnee ke arambh se lekar jab tak akash se un par atyant vrashtti n padee, tab tak chattan par use apane neeche bichhaye rahee aur n to din men akash ke pakshiayon ko, aur n rat men banaaile pashuuon ko unhen choone diya.
jab ayya kee beettee shaaul kee rakhelee rispa ke is kam ka samachar aud ko mila,
tab daud ne jakar shaaul aur usake putra yonatan kee haddiyon ko giladee yabesh ke logon se le liya, jinhon ne unhen betashaan ke us chauk se chura liya tha, jahan palishtaiyon ne unhen us din ttanga tha, jab unhon ne shaaul ko gilbo pahad par mar dala tha
to vah vahan se shaaul aur usake putra yonatan kee haaddiyon ko le aya aur faanyee paae huon kee haddiyan bhee ikatthee kee gai.
aur shaaul aur usake putra yonatan kee haddiyan binyameen ke desh ke jela men shaaul ke pita keesh ke kabirstan gadee gai aur daud kee sab agyaaon ke anusar kam hua. aur usake bad parameshvar ne desh ke liye praarthna sun lee.
paalishtaiyon ne dasraaael se fir yuddh kiya, aur daud apane janon samet jakar paalishtaiyon se ladne laga parantu daud thk gaya.
parantu sarooyah ke putra abeeshau ne daud kee sahayata karake us paalishtee ko aesa mara ki vah mar gaya. tab daud ke janon ne shapath khakar us se kaha, too fir hamare sang yuddh ko jane n paaega, aeesa n ho ki tere marane se israaael ka diy bujh jaae.
isake bad paalishtaiyon ke sath gob men fir yuddh hua us samay hooshaai sibbakaai ne rapaivanshaee sap ko mara.
aur gob men paalishtaiyon ke sath fir yuddh hua us men betalehem vasee yarayorageem ke putra aelhanan ne gatee golyat ko mar dala, jisake bachhen kee chhd jolahe kee dongee ke saman thee.
fir gat men bhee yuddh hua, aur vahan aek badee deel ka rapaivanshaee purush tha, jisake aek aek hath panv me, chh chh ungalee, arthata ginatee men chaubees ungaaliyan theen.
jab us ne israaael ko lalakara, tab daud ke bhai shaima ke putra yahonatan ne use mara.
ye hee char gat men us rapai se utpann huae the aur ve daud aur usake janon se mar dale gaae.
aur jis samay yahova ne daud ko usake sab shatrauon aur shaaul ke hath se bachaya tha, tab us ne yahova ke liye is geet ke vachan gaae
us ne kaha, yahova meree chattan, aur mera gaddh, mera chhudanevala,
mera chattanaroopee parameshvar haai, jisaka maain sharanagat hoo, meree ddhal, mera bachanevala seeng, mera uncha gaddh, aur mera sharansthan haai, he mere uddhar katrta, too upadrav se mera uddhar kiya karata haai.
maain yahova ko jo stuati ke yogy haai pukaroonga, aur apane shatrauon se bachaya jaunga.
mratyu ke tarangon ne to mere charon or ghora dala, nastaikapan kee dhaaraon ne mujh ko ghabada diya tha
adhaelok kee rassaiyan mere charon or thee, mratyu ke fande mere samhane the.
apane sankatt men maain ne yahova ko pukara aur apane parameshvar ke sammukh chillaya. aunr us ne meree bat ko apane maandair men se sun liya, aur meree dohai usake kanon men pahunchee.
tab prathvee hil gai aur dol uttee aur akash kee neven kanpakar bahut hee hil gai, kyonaki vah ati krodhait hua tha.
usake nathnon se dhauna nikala, aur usake munh se ag nikalakar bhsm karane lagee jis se koyale dahak utte.
aur vah svarga ko jhukakar neeche utar aya aur usake panvon ke tale ghaer andhakar chhaya tha.
aur vah karoob par savar hokar uda, aur pavan ke pankhon par chaddhkar dikhai diya.
aur us ne apane charon or ke anadhaiyare ko, meghaen ke samooh, aur akash kee kalee ghattaon ko apana mandp banaya.
usake sammukh kee jhlak to usake age age thee, ag ke koyale dahak utte.
yahova akash men se garaja, aur paramapradhaan ne apanee vanee sunai.
us ne teer chala chalakar mere shatrauon ko titar bitar kar diya, aur bijalee gira girakar usako parast kar diya.
tab samudra kee thah dikhai dene lagee, aur jagat kee neven khul gai, yah to yahova kee dantt se, aur usake nathnon kee sans kee jhonk se hua.
us ne upar se hath baddhakar mujhe thanm liya, aur mujhe gahare jal men se kheenchakar bahar nikala.
unhon ne meree vipaattai ke din mera samhana to kiya parantu yahova mera ashray tha.
aur us ne mujhe nikalakar chaude sthan men pahunchaya us ne mujh ko chhudaya, kyonaki vah mujh se prasann tha.
yahova ne mujh se mere dharma ke anusar vyavahar kiya mere kamon kee shuuddhata ke anusar us ne mujhe badala diya.
kyonaki maain yahova ke magan par chalata raha, aur apane parameshvar se munh modkar dushtt n bana.
usake sab niyam to mere samhane bane rahe, aur maain usakee vidhaiyon se hatt n gaya.
isaliye yahova ne mujhe mere dharma ke anusar badala diya, meree us shuuddhata ke anusar jise vah dekhta tha.
dayavant ke sath too apane ko dayavant dikhata khre purush ke sath too apane ko khra dikhata haai
shuuddh ke sath too apane ko shuuddh dikhata aur tteddhe ke sath too tirachha banata haai.
aur deen logon ko to too bachata haai, parantu abhaimaaniyon par draashtti karake unhen neecha karata haai.
he yahova, too hee mera deepak haai, aur yahova mere aandhiayare ko door karake ujiyala kar deta haai.
teree sahayata se maain dal par dhaava karata, apane parameshvar kee sahayata se maain shaharapanah ko faand jata hoo.
ishvar kee gaati khree haai yahova ka vachan taya hua haai vah apane sab sharanagaton kee ddhal haai.
yahova ko chhod kya koi ishvar haai? hamare parameshvar ko chhod kya aur koi chattan haai?
yah vahee ishvar haai, jo mera ati draddh kila haai, vah khre manushy ko apane marga men liae chalata haai.
vah mere paairon ko harinaiyon ke se bana deta haai, aur mujhe unche sthanon par khda karata haai.
vah mere hathon ko yuddh karana sikhata haai, yahan tak ki meree banhen peetal ke dhanush ko jhuka detee haain.
aur too ne mujh ko apane uddhar kee ddhal dee haai, aur teree namrata mujhe baddhatee haai.
too mere paairon ke liye sthan chauda karata haai, aur mere paair naheen fisale.
maain ne apane shatrauon ka peechha karake unhen satyanash kar diya, aur jab tak unaka ant n kiya tab tak n lautta.
aur maain ne unaka ant kiya aur unhen aeesa chhed dala haai ki ve utt naheen sakate varan ve to mere panvon ke neeche gire pade haain.
aur too ne yuddh ke liye meree kamar balavant kee aur mere virodhaiyon ko mere hee samhane parast kar diya.
aur too ne mere shatrauon kee peett mujhe dikhai, taki maain apane baairiyon ko katt daloon.
unhon ne batt to johee, parantu koi bachanevala n mila unhon ne yahova kee bhee batt johee, parantu us ne unako koi uttar n diya.
tab maain ne unako koott koottkar boomi kee dhooli ke saman kar diya, maain ne unhen sadkon aur galee koochon kee keechad ke saman pattkakar charon or faaila diya.
fir too ne muujhe praja ke jhgadon se chhudakar any jatiyon ka pradhaan hone ke liye meree raksha kee jin logon ko maain n janata tha ve bhee mere adhaeen ho jaaenge.
paradeshaee meree chapaloosee karenge ve mera nam sunate hee mere vash men aaenge.
paradeshaee murjhaaenge, aur apane kotton men se thrathrate huae nikalenge.
yahova jeeavit haai meree chattan dhany haai, aur parameshvar jo mere uddhar kee chattan haai, usakee maahima ho.
dhany haai mera palatta lenevala ishvar, jo desh desh ke logon ko mere vash men kar deta haai,
is kara, he yahova, maain jaati jati ke samhane tera dhanyavad karoonga, aur tere nam ka bhjan gaunga.
vah apane ttharaae huae raja ka bada uddhar karata haai, vah apane abhaishaikt daud, aur usake vansh par yuganuyug karuna karata rahega.
daud ke antaim vachan ye haain yishau ke putra kee yah vanee haai, us purush kee vanee haai jo unche par khda kiya gaya, aur yakoob ke parameshvar ka abhaishaikt, aur israaael ka madhaur bhjan ganevala haai
yahova ka atma mujh men hokar bola, aur usee ka vachan mere munh men aya.
vah mano bhor ka prakash hoga jab soorya nikalata haai, aeesa bhor jis men badal n ho, jaaisa vashara ke bad nirmal prakash ke karan boomi se haree haree ghaas ugatee haai.
kya mera gharana ishvar kee draashtti men aeesa naheen haai? us ne to mere sath sada kee aek aeesee vacha bandhaee haai, jo sab baton men tteek kee hui aur attl bhee haai. kyonki chahe vah usako pragatt n kare, taubhee mera poorn uddhar aur poorn aabhailasha ka vishay vahee haai.
parantu ochhe log sab ke sab nikammee jhaadiyon ke saman haain jo hath se pakadee naheen jateen
aur jo purush unako chooae use lohe aur bhale kee chhd se susaajjait hona chaahiye. isaliye ve apane hee sthan men ag se bhsm kar diae jaaenge.
daud ke shooraveeron ke nam ye haain arthata tahakamonee yoshshobyashshobet, jo saradaron men mukhy tha vah aesnee adeeno bhee kahalata tha jis ne aek hee samay men att sau purush mar dale.
usake bad ahohee dodaai ka putra eleeajar tha. vah us samay daud ke sang ke teenon veeron men se tha, jab ki unhon ne yuddh ke liye ekatrait huae paalishtaiyon ko lalakara, aur israaelee purush chale gaae the.
vah kamar bandhakar paalishtaiyon ko tab tak marata raha jab tak usaka hath thk n gaya, aur talavar hath se chipatt n gai aur us din yahova ne badee vijay karai aur jo log usake peechhe ho liae ve keval loottne hee ke liye usake peechhe ho liae.
usake bad age nam ek pahadee ka putra shamma tha. palishtaiyon ne ikatthe hokar ek sthan men dal bandha, jahan masoor ka ek khet tha aur log unake dr ke mare bhage.
tab us ne khet ke madhy men khde hokar use bachaya, aur palishtaiyon ko mar liya aur yahova ne badee vijay dilai.
fir teeson mukhy saradaron men se teen jan kattnee ke dinon men daud ke pas adullam nam gufaa men aa, aur palishtaiyon ka dal rapaim nam tarai men chhavanee kiae huae tha.
us samay daud gaddh men tha aur us samay paalishtaiyon kee chaukee betalehem men thee.
tab daud ne badee abhailasha ke sath kaha, kaun mujhe betalehem ke faattk ke pas ke kuen ka panee pilaaega?
to ve teenon veer palishtaiyon kee chhavanee men toott pade, aur betalehem ke faattk ke kunae se panee bhrake daud ke pas le aae. parantu us ne peene se inakar kiya, aur yahova ke samhane ardha karake undela,
aur kaha, he yahova, mujh se aeesa kam door rahe. kya maain un manushyon ka lohoo peeun jo apane praanon par khelakar gaae the? isaaliye us ne us panee ko peene se inakar kiya. in teen veeron ne to ye hee kam kiae.
aur abeeshau jo sarooyah ke putra yoab ka bhai tha, vah teenon se mukhy tha. us ne apana bhala chalakar teen sau ko mar dala, aur teenon men namee ho gaya.
kya vah teenon se aadhaik pratishttit n tha? aur isee se vah unaka pradhaan ho gaya parantu mukhy teenon ke pad ko n pahuncha.
fir yahoyada ka putra banayah tha, jo kabaselavasee aek bade kam karanevale veer ka putra tha us ne sinh sareekhe do moabiyon ko mar dala. aur barfa ke samay us ne aek gadhe men utarake aek sinh ko mar dala.
fir us ne aek roopavana misraee purush ko mar dala. misraee to hath men bhala liae huae tha parantu banayah aek lattee hee liae huae usake pas gaya, aur misraee ke hath se bhala ko chheenakar usee ke bhale se use ghaat kiya.
aeese aeese kam karake yahoyada ka putra banayah un teenon veeron men namee ho gaya.
vah teeson se adhaik pratishttit to tha, parantu mukhy teenon ke pad ko n pahuncha. usako daud ne apanee nij sabha ka sabhasad niyukt kiya.
fir teeson men yoab ka bhai asahela betalehemee dodo ka putra aelhanan,
herodee shamma, aur aeleeka, peletee heles,
takoi ikkesh ka putra ira,
anatotee abeeaejaer, hooshaai mabunne,
ahohee salmon, natopahee maharaai,
piratonee, banayah, gash ke nalon ke pas rahanevala hiai,
araba ka abeealbon, bahooreemee ajamavet,
shaalabonee aelyahaba, yashon ke vansh men se yonatan,
ahasabaai ka putra aeleepelett maka desh ka, geeloi aheetopel ka putra aeleeam,
kammenlee hesrae, arabee paraai
sobai natan ka putra yigal, gadee banee,
ammonee selek, berotee naharaai ko sarooyah ke putra yoab ka hathaiyar ddhonevala tha,
yeteree ira, aur gareb,
aur hittee uriyyah tha sab milakar saaiaintees the.
aur yahova ka kop israaaeliyon par fir bhdka, aur us ne daud ko inakee hani ke liye yah kahakar ubhara, ki israaael aur yahooda kee ginatee le.
so raja ne yoab senapaati se jo usake pas tha kaha, too dan se beshba tak rahanevale sab israaaelee gotron men idhar udhar ghoom, aur tum log praja kee ginatee lo, taki maain jan loon ki praja kee kitanee ginatee haai.
yoab ne raja se kaha, praja ke log kitane hee kyon n ho, tera parameshvar yahova unako sauguna baddha de, aur mera prabhu raja ise apanee ankhon se dekhne bhee paae parantu, he mere prabhu, he raja, yah bat too kyon chahata haai?
taubhee raja kee agyaa yoab aur senapaatiyon par prabal hui. so yoab aur senapati raja ke sammukh se israaaelee praja kee ginatee lene ko nikal gaae.
unhon ne yaradan par jakar aroer nagar kee daahinee or dere khde kia, jo gad ke nale ke madhy men aur yajer kee or haai.
tab ve gilad men aur tahateemhodashaee nam desh men gaa, fir danyan ko gaa, aur chakkar lagakar seedon men pahunche
tab ve sor nam draddh gaddh, aur hibbaiyon aur kananiyon ke sab nagaron men gaae aur unhon ne yahooda desh kee dakkhian disha men beshonba men daura nipattaya.
