aur log yahova ka sandook bheetar le aa, aur usake sthan me, arthata us tamboo men rakha, jo daud ne usake liye khda karaya tha aur daud ne yahova ke sammukh homabali aur melabali chaddhaae.
jab daud homabali aur melabali chaddha chuka, tab us ne senaon ke yahova ke nam se praja ko ashaeervad diya.
tab us ne samast praja ko, arthata, kya sree kya purusha, samast israaaelee bheed ke logon ko aek aek rottee, aur aek aek ttukada mans, aur kishaamish kee aek aek ttiikaya banttva dee. tab praja ke sab log apane apane ghar chale gaae.
tab daud apane gharane ko ashaeervad dene ke liye lautta. aur shaaul kee bettee meekal daud se milane ko nikalee, aur kahane lagee, aj israaael ka raja jab apana shareer apane karmachariyon kee laundyaien ke samhane aeesa ughaade huae tha, jaaisa koi nikamma apana tan ughaaddhe rahata haai, tab kya hee pratapee dekh padta tha !
daud ne meekal se kaha, yahova, jis ne tere pita aur usake samast gharane kee santee mujh ko chunakar apanee praja israaael ka pradhaan hone ko tthara diya haai, usake sammukh maain ne aeesa khela--aur maain yahova ke sammukh isee prakar khela karoonga.
aur is se bhee maain adhaik tuchchh banoonga, aur apane lekhe neech ttharoonga aur jin launadyaien kee too ne charcha kee ve bhee mera adaraman karengee.
aur shaaul kee bettee meekal ke marane ke din tak usake koi santan n hua.
jab raja apane bhvan men rahata tha, aur yahova ne usako usake charon or ke sab shatrauaun se vishraam diya tha,
tab raja natan nam bhavishyadvkta se kahane laga, dek, maain to devadaru ke bane huae ghar men rahata hoo, parantu parameshvar ka sandook tamboo men rahata haai.
natan ne raja se kaha, jo kuchh tere man men ho use kara kyonki yahova tere sang haai.
usee din rat ko yahova ka yah vachan natan ke pas pahuncha,
ki jakar mere das daud se kah, yahova son kahata haai, ki kya too mere nivas ke liye ghar banavaaega?
jis din se maain israaaliaeyon ko misra se nikal laya aj ke din tak maain kabhee ghar men naheen raha, tamboo ke nivas men aya jaya karata hoo.
jahan jahan maain samast israaaeliyon ke beech firata thai, kya maain ne kaheen israaael ke kisee gotra se, jise maain ne apanee praja israaael kee charavahee karane ko ttharaya ho, aeesee bat kabhee kahee, ki tum ne mere liaee devadaru ka ghar kyon naheen banavaya?
isaliye ab too mere das daud se aeesa kah, ki senaon ka yahova yon kahata haai, ki maain ne to tujhe bhedshaala se, aur bhead-bakaarison ke peechhe peechhe firane se, is manasa se bula liya ki too meree praja israaael ka pradhaan ho jaae.
aur jahan kaheen too aya gaya, vahan vahan maain tere sang raha, aur tere samast shatrauon ko tere samhane se nash kiya haai fir maain tere nam ko prathvee par ke bade bade logon ke namon ke saman mahan kar doonga.
aur maain apanee praja israaael ke liye aek sthan ttharaunga, aur usako sthiar karoonga, ki vah apane hee sthan men basee raheegee, aur kabhee chalayaman n hogee aur kuattlai log use fir dukh n dene paaenge, jaaise ki pahile dinon men karate the,
varan us samay se bhee jab maain apanee praja israaael ke upar nyayee ttharata tha aur maain tujhe tere samast shatrauon se vishraam doonga. aur yahova tujhe yah bhee batata haai ki yahova tera ghar banaae rakhega.
jab teree ayu pooree ho jaaegee, aur too apane purakhaon ke sang so jaaega, tab maain tere nij vansh ko tere peechhe khda karanke usake rajy ko sthiar karoonga.
mere nam ka ghar vahee banavaaega, aur maain usakee rajagaee ko sadaaiv sthiar rakoonga.
maain usaka pita ttharoonga, aur vah mera putra ttharega. yadi vah adharma kare, to maain use manushyon ke yogy dand se, aur adaamiyon ke yogy mar se tadna doonga.
parantu meree karuna us par se aeese n hattegee, jaaise maain ne shaaul par se hattakar usako tere age se door kiya.
varan tera gharana aur tera rajy mere samhane sada attl bana rahega teree gaee sadaaiv banee rahegee.
in sab baton aur is darshan ke anusar natan ne daud ko samajha diya.
parantu taubhee, he prabhu yahova, yah teree drashttee men chhottee see bat hui kyonaki tu ne apane das ke gharane ke vishay age ke bahut dinon tak kee charcha kee haai, aur he prabhu yahova, yah to manushy ka niyam haai !
daud tujh se aur kya kah sakata haai? he prabhu yahava, too to apane das ko janata haai !
is kara, he yahova parameshvar, too mahana haai kyonki jo kuchh ham ne apane kanon se suna haai, usake anusar tere tuly koi nahee, aur n tujhe chhod koi aur parameshvar haai.
fir teree praja israaael ke bhee tuly kaun haai? yah to prathvee bhr men aek hee jaati haai jise parameshvar ne jakar apanee nij praja karane ko chhudaya, isaaliye ki vah apana nam kare, aur tumhare liye bade bade kam kare aur too apanee praja ke samhane, jise too ne misraee aadi jati jati ke logon aur unake devataon se chooda liya, apane desh ke liye bhyanak kam kare.
aur too ne apanee praja israaael ko apanee sada kee praja hone ke liye ttharaya aur he yahova, too ap usaka parameshvar haai.
ab he yahova parameshvar, too ne jo vachan apane das ke aur usake gharane ke vishay diya haai, use sada ke liye sthiar kar, aur apane kahane ke anoosar hee kara
aur yah kar ki log tere nam kee maahima sada kiya kare, ki senaon ka yahova israaael ke upar parameshvar haai aur tere das daud ka gharana tere samhane attl rahe.
kyonaki, he senaon ke yahova, he israaael ke parameshvar, too ne yah kahakar apane das par pragatt kiya haai, ki maain tera ghar banaae rakoonga is karan tere das ko tujh se yah praarthna karane ka hiyav hua haai.
aur ab he prabhu yahova, too hee parameshvar haai, aur tere vachan saty haai, aur too ne apane das ko yah bhlai karane ka vachan diya haai
to ab prasann hokar apane das ke gharane par aeesee ashaeesh de, ki vah tere sammukh sadaaiv bana rahe kyonaki, he prabhu yahova, too ne aeesa hee kaha haai, aur tere das ka gharana tujh se ashaeesh pakar sadaaiv dhany rahe.
isake bad daud ne palishtaiyon ko jeetakar apane adhaeen kar liya, aur daud ne palishtaiyon kee rajadhaanee kee prabhuta unake hath se chheen lee.
fir us ne moaabiyon ko bhee jeeta, aur inako boomi par littakar doree se mapa tab do doree se logon ko mapakar ghaat kiya, aur doree bhr ke logon ko jeeavit chhod diya. tab moabee daud ke adhaeen hokar bhentt le ane lage.
fir jab soba ka raja rahob ka putra hadadejer mahanad ke pas apana rajy fir jyon ka tyon karane ko ja raha tha, tab daud ne usako jeet liya.
aur daud ne us se aek hajar sat sau savar, aur bees hajar pyade chheen liae aur sab rathvale ghaedon ke sum kee nas kattvai, parantu aek sau rathvale ghaede bacha rakhe.
aur jab daamishk ke aramee soba ke raja hadadejer kee sahayata karane ko aa, tab daud ne aramiyon men se bais hajaar purush mare.
tab daud ne damishk men aram ke sipaahiyon kee chauakiyan baaittai is prakar aramee daud ke adhaeen hokar bhentt le ane lage. aur jahan jahan daud jata tha vahan vahan yahova usako jayavant karata tha.
aur hadadejer ke karmachariyon ke pas sone kee jo ddhalen theen unhen daud lekar yarooshalem ko aya.
aur betah aur barautaai nam hadadejer ke nagaron se daud raja bahut sa peetal le aya.
aur jab hamat ke raja toi ne suna ki daud ne hadadejer kee samast sena ko jeet liya haai,
tab toi ne yoram nam apane putra ko daud raja ke pas usaka kushal kshom poochhne, aur use isaliye badhaai dene ko bheja, ki us ne hadadejer se lad kar usako jeet liya tha kyonaki hadadejer toi se lada karata tha. aur yoram chandee, sone aur peetal ke patra liae huae aya.
inako daud raja ne yahova ke liye paavitra karake rakha aur vaaisa hee apane jeetee hui sab jatiyon ke sone chandee se bhee kiya,
arthata aramiyo, moaabiyo, ammaniyo, palishtaiyo, aur amalekiyon ke sone chandee ko, aur rahob ke putra soba ke raja hadadejer kee loott ko bhee rakha.
aur jab daud lomavalee tarai men attarah hajar araamiyon ko marake lautt aya, tab usaka bada nam ho gaya.
fir us ne aedom men sipaahiyon kee chauakiyan baaittai poore aedom men us ne sipaahiyon kee chauakiyan. baaittai, aur sab aedomee daud ke adhaeen ho gaae. aur daud jahan jahan jata tha vahan vahan yahova usako jayavant karata tha.
daud ke karmachaariyon kee namavalee daud to samast israaael par rajy karata tha, aur daud apanee samast praja ke sath nyay aur dharma ke kam karata tha.
aur pradhaan senapaati sarooyah ka putra yoab tha itihas ka likhnevala aheelood ka putra yahoshaapat tha
pradhaan yajak aheetoob ka putra sadok aur aebyatar ka putra aheemelek the mantraee sarayah tha
karetiyo aur paletiyon ka pradhaan yahoyada ka putra banayah tha aur daud ke putra bhee mantraee the.
shaaul ke gharane ka seeba nam aek karmacharee tha, vah daud ke pas bulaya gaya aur jab raja ne us se poochha, kya too seeba haai? tab us ne kaha, ha, tera das vahee haai.
raja ne poochha, kya shaaul ke gharane men se koi ab tak bacha haai, jisako maain parameshvar kee see praeeti dikhaun? seeba ne raja se kaha, ha, yonatan ka aek betta to haai, jo langada haai.
raja ne us se poochha, vah kahan haai? seeba ne raja se kaha, vah to lodabar nagar me, ammeeael ke putra makeer ke ghar men rahata haai.
jab mapeeboshot, jo yonatan ka putra aur shaaul ka pota tha, daud ke pas aya, tab muh ke bal girake dandvata kiya. daud ne kaha, he mapeeboshot ! us ne kaha, tere das ko kya agyaa?
daud ne us se kaha, mat dra tere pita yonatan ke karan maain nishchay tujh ko praeeati dikhaunga, aur tere dada shaaul kee saree booomi tujhe faer doonga aur too meree mej par nity bhojan kiya kara.
us ne dandvata karake kaha, tera das kya haai, ki too mujhe aeese mare kutte kee or draashtti kare?
tab raja ne shaaul ke karmacharee seeba ko bulavakar us se kaha, jo kuchh shaaul aur usake samast gharane ka tha vah maain ne tere svamee ke pote ko de diya haai.
ab se too apane betton aur sevakon samet usakee boomi par khetee karake usakee upaj le aya karana, ki tere svamee ke pote ko bhojan mila kare parantu tere svamee ka pota mapeeboshot meree mej par nity bhojan kiya karega. aur seeba ke to pandrah putra aur bees sevak the.
seeba ne raja se kaha, mera prabhu raja apane das ko jo jo agyaa de, un sabhon ke anusar tera das karega. daud ne kaha, mapeeboshot rajakumaron kee nai meree mej par bhojan kiya kare.
mapeeboshot ke bhee meeka nam aek chhotta betta tha. aur seeba ke ghar men jitane rahate the ve sab mapeeboshot kee seva karate the.
aur mapeeboshot yarooshalem men rahata tha kyonaki vah raja kee mej par nity bhojan kiya karata tha. aur vah donon panvon ka pangula tha.
paulus aur silavanus aur teemuthaiyus kee or se thaissaluneekiyon kee kaleesiya ke nam, jo hamare pita parameshvar aur prabhu yeeshu maseeh men haai..
hamare pita parameshvar aur prabhu yeeshu maseeh men tumhen anugrah aur shaaantai milatee rahe..
he bhaiyo, tumhare vishay men hamen har samay parameshvar ka dhanyavad karana chahia, aur yah uchit bhee haai isaaliye ki tumhara vishvas bahut baddhta jata haai, aur tum sab ko praem apas men bahut hee hota jata haai.
yahan tak ki ham ap parameshvar kee kaleeasiya men tumhare vishay men ghamand karate haai, ki jitane upadrav aur klesh tum sahate ho, un sab men tumhara dhaeeraj aur vishvas pragatt hota haai.
yah parameshvar ke sachche nyay ka spashtt praman haai ki tum parameshvar ke rajy ke yogy ttharo, jis ke liye tum dukh bhee uttate ho.
kyonaki parameshvar ke nikatt yah nyay haai, ki jo tumhen klesh dete haai, unhen badale men klesh de.
aur tumhen jo klesh pate ho, hamare sath chaain de us samay jab ki prabhu yeeshu apane samarthee dooton ke sat, dhadhakatee hui ag men svarga se pragatt hoga.
aur jo parameshvar ko naheen pahachanate, aur hamare prabhu yeeshu ke susamachar ko naheen manate un se palatta lega.
ve prabhu ke samhane se, aur usakee shaaktai ke tej se door hokar anant vinash ka dand paaenge.
yah us din hoga, jab vah apane paavitra logon men mahima pane, aur sab vishvas karanevalon men ashcharya ka karan hone ko aaega kyonaki tum ne hamaree gavahee kee prateeati kee.
isee liye ham sada tumhare nimitt praarthna bhee karate haai, ki hamara parameshvar tumhen is bulahatt ke yogy samajhe, aur bhlai kee har aek ichchha, aur vishvas ke har aek kam ko samarth sahit poora kare.
ki hamare parameshvar aur prabhu yeeshu maseeh ke anugrah ke anusar hamare prabhu yeeshu ka nam tum men maahima paa, aur tum us men..
he bhaiyo, tum apane prabhu yeeshu maseeh ke ane, aur usake pas apane ikatthe hone ke vishay men tum se binatee karate haain.
ki kisee atma, ya vachan, ya patraee ke dara jo ki manon hamaree or se ko, yah samajhkar ki prabhu ka din a pahuncha haai, tumhara man achanak aasthiar n ho jaae aur n tum ghabarao.
kisee reeati se kisee ke dhaekhe men n ana kyonaki vah din n aaega, jab tak dharma ka tyag n ho le, aur vah pap ka puroosh arthata vinash ka putra pragatt n ho.
jo virodha karata haai, aur har aek se jo parameshvar, ya poojy kahalata haai, apane ap ko bada ttharata haai, yahan tak ki vah parameshvar ke mandair men baaittkar apane ap ko parameshvar pragatt karata haai.
kya tumhen smaran nahee, ki jab maain tumhare yahan tha, to tum se ye baten kaha karata tha?
kyonaki adharma ka bhed ab bhee kayrya karata jata haai, par abhee aek rokanevala haai, aur jab tak vah door n ho jaa, vah roke rahega.
tab vah adharmee pragatt hoga, jise prabhu yeeshu apane munh ko faook se mar dalega, aur apane agaman ke tej se bhsm karega.
us adharmee ka ana shautan ke kayrya ke anusar sab prakar kee joottee samarth, aur chinh, aur adabhut kam ke sath.
aur nash honevalon ke liye adharma ke sab prakar ke dhaekhe ke sath hoga kyonaki unhonne saty ke praem ko grahan naheen kiya jis se un ka uddhar hota.
aur jitane log saty kee prateeti naheen karate, varan adharma se prasann hote haai, sab dand paaen..
par he bhaiyo, aur prabhu ke piry logo chahiye ki ham tumhare vishay men sada parameshvar ka dhanyavad karate rahe, ki parameshvar ne adi se tumhen chun liya ki atma ke dara paavitra banakar, aur saty kee prateeti karake uddhar pao.
jis ke liye us ne tumhen hamare susamachar ke dara bulaya, ki tum hamare prabhu yeeshu maseeh kee maahima ko praapt karo.
isaliye, ye bhaiyo, sthiara aur jo jo baten tum ne kya vachan, kya patraee ke dara ham se seekhee haai, unhen thame raho..
hamara prabhu yeeshu maseeh ap hee, aur hamara pita parameshvar jis ne ham se praem rakha, aur anugrah se anant shaaantai aur uttm asha dee haai.
tumhare manon men shaantai de, aur tumhen har aek achchhe kam, aur vachan men draddh kare..
nidan, he bhaiyo, hamare liye praarthna kiya karo, ki prabhu ka vachan aeesa shaeegha faaile, aur maahima paa, jaaisa tum men hua.
aur ham tteddhe aur dushtt manushyon se bache rahen kyonaki har aek men vishvas naheen..
parantu prabhu sachcha haai vah tumhen draddhta se sthiar karega: aur us dushtt se suraakshiat rakhega.
aur hamen prabhu men tumhare upar bhrosa haai, ki jo jo agyaa ham tumhen dete haai, unhen tum manate ho, aur manate bhee rahoge.
parameshvar ke praem aur maseeh ke dhaeeraj kee or prabhu tumhare man kee aguvai kare..
he bhaiyo, ham tumhen apane prabhu yeeshu maseeh ke nam se agyaa dete haain ki har aek aeese bhai se alag raho, jo anuachit chal chalata, aur jo shaiksha us ne ham se pai usake anusar naheen karata.
kyonaki tum ap janate ho, ki kis reeti se hamaree see chal chalanee chahiae kyonaki ham tumhare beech men anuchit chal n chale.
aur kisee kee rottee sent men n khai par paarishram aur kashtt se rat din kam dhandha karate the, ki tum men se kisee par bhar n ho.
yah nahee, ki hamen aadhaikar naheen par isaliye ki apane ap ko tumhare liye adarsha ttharaae, ki tum hamaree see chal chalo.
aur jab ham tumhare yahan the, tab bhee yah agyaa tumhen dete the, ki yadi koi kam karana n chahe, to khane bhee n paae.
ham sunate haai, ki kitane log tumhare beech men anuchit chal chalate haain aur kuchh kam naheen karate, par auron ke kam men hath dala karate haain.
aeeson ko ham prabhu yeeshu maseeh men agyaa dete aur samajhate haai, ki chupachap kam karake apanee hee rottee khaya karen.
aur tum, he bhaiyo, bhlai karane men hiyav n chhodo.
yaadi koi hamaree is patraee kee bat ko n mane, to us par drashtti rakho aur us kee sangaati n karo, jis se vah lajjait ho
taubhee use baairee man samajho par bhai janakar chitao..
ab prabhu jo shaaantai ka sota haai ap hee tumhen sada aur har prakar se shaantai de: prabhu tum sab ke sath rahe..
maain paulus apane hath se namaskar likhta hoon: har patraee men mera yahee chinh haai: maain isee prakar se likhta hoon.
hamare prabhu yeeshu maseeh ka anugrah tum sab par hota rahe..
piry putra teemuathaiyus ke nama.. parameshvar pita aur hamare prabhu maseeh yeeshu kee or se tujhe anugrah aur daya aur shaaantai milatee rahe..
jis parameshvar kee seva maain apane bapadadon kee reeati par shuuddh vivek se karata hoo, usaka dhanyavad ho ki apanee praarthnaon men tujhe lagatar smaran karata hoon.
aur tere ansuon kee suadhai kar karake rat din tujh se bhentt karane kee lalasa rakhta hoon ki anand se bhr jaun.
aur mujhe tere us nishkapatt vishvas kee sudhai atee haai, jo pahile teree nanee lois, aur teree mata yooneeke men thee, aur mujhe nishchay hua haai, ki tum men bhee haai.
isee karan maain tujhe suadhai dilata hoo, ki too parameshvar ke us varadan ko jo mere hath rakhne ke dara tujhe mila haai chamaka de.
isaliye hamare prabhu kee gavahee se, aur mujh se jo usaka kaaidee hoo, lajjait n ho, par us parameshvar kee samarth ke anusar susamachar ke liye mere sath dukh utta.
jis ne hamara uddhar kiya, aur paavitra bulahatt se bulaya, aur yah hamare kamon ke anusar naheen par apanee manasa aur us anugrah ke anusar haai jo maseeh yeeshu men sanatan se ham par hua haai.
par ab hamare uddharakarta maseeh yeeshu ke pragatt hone ke dara prakash hua, jis ne mratyu ka nash kiya, aur jeevan aur amarata ko us susamachar ke dara prakashaman kar diya.
jis ke liye maain pracharak, aur praerit, aur upadeshak bhee tthara.
is karan maain in dukhon ko bhee uttata hoo, par lajata nahee, kyonki maain use jis kee maain ne prateeti kee haai, janata hoon aur mujhe nishchay haai, ki vah meree thatee kee us din tak rakhvalee kar sakata haai.
jo khree baten too ne mujh se sunee haain un ko us vishvas aur praem ke sath jo maseeh yeeshu men haai, apana adarsha banakar rakh.
aur paavitra atma ke dara jo ham men basa hua haai, is achchhee thatee kee rakhvalee kara..
too janata haai, ki asiyavale sab mujh se fir gaae haai, jin men foogilus aur hiramugines haain.
unesifauroos ke gharane par prabhu daya kare, kyonaki us ne bahut bar mere jee ko ttnda kiya, aur meree janjeeron se laajjait n hua.
par jab vah roma men aya, to bade yatn se ddoonddhkar mujh se bhentt kee.
prabhu kare, ki us din us par prabhu kee daya ho. aur jo jo seva us ne iafisus men kee haai unhen bhee too bhlee bhanati janata haai..
isaliye he mere putra, too us anugrah se jo maseeh yeeshu men haai, balavant ho ja.
aur jo baten too ne bahut gavahon ke samhane mujh se sunee haai, unhen vishvasee manushyon ko saunp de jo auron ko bhee sikhane ke yogy hon.
maseeh yeeshu ke achchhe yoddha kee nai mere sath dukh utta.
jab koi yoddha ladai par jata haai, to isaaliye ki apane bhratee karanevale ko prasann kare, apane ap ko sansar ke kamon men naheen fansata
fir akhade men ladnevala yaadi vidhai ke anusar n lade to mukutt naheen pata.
jo grahasth paarishram karata haai, fal ka ansh pahile use milana chahiae.
jo maain kahata hoo, us par dhyan de aur prabhu tujhe sab baton kee samajh dega.
yeeshu maseeh ko smaran rak, jo daud ke vansh se hua, aur mare huon men se jee utta aur yah mare susamachar ke anusar haai.
jis ke liye maain kukarmee kee nai dukh uttata hoo, yahan tak ki kaaid bhee hoon parantu parameshvar ka vachan kaaid naheen.
is karan maain chune huae logon ke liye sab kuchh sahata hoo, ki ve bhee us uddhar ko jo maseeh yeeshu men haain anant mahima ke sath paaen.
yah bat sach haai, ki yadi ham usake sath mar gaae haain to usake sath jeeaenge bhee.
yaadi ham dhaeeraj se sahate rahenge, to usake sath rajy bhee karenge : yadi ham usaka inkar karenge to vah bhee hamara inkar karega.
in baton kee sudhai unhen dila, aur prabhu ke samhane chita de, ki shabdon par tarka-vitarka n kiya kare, jin se kuchh labh naheen hota baran sunanevale bigad jate haain.
apane ap ko parameshvar ka grahanyogy aur aeesa kam karanevala ttharane ka prayatn kar, jo lajjait hone n paa, aur jo saty ke vachan ko tteek reeti se kam men lata ho.
par ashuuddh bakavad se bacha raha kyonaki aeese log aur bhee abhktai men baddhte jaaenge.
aur un ka vachan sade-ghaav kee nain faailata jaaega: huminayus aur filetus unheen men se haain.
jo yah kahakar ki punarootthan ho chuka haai saty se bhttk gaae haai, aur kitanon ke vishvas ko ulatt pulatt kar dete haain.
