parameshvar yahova ne mujhe yah dikhaya, aur maain kya dekhta hoon ki us ne pichhlee ghaas ke ugane ke arambh me ttiiddayan utpann kee aur vah raja kee kattnee ke bad kee pichhlee ghaas theen.
jab ve ghaas kha chukee, tab maain ne kaha, he parameshvar yahova, kshama kara! naheen to yakoob kaaise sthiar rah sakega? vah kitana nirbal haai!
isake vishay men yahova pachhtaya, aur us se kaha, aeesee bat ab n hogee..
parameshvar yahova ne mujhe yah dikhaya : aur kya dekhta hoon ki parameshvar yahova ne ag ke dara mukama ladne ko pukara, aur us ag se mahasagar sookh gaya, aur desh bhee bhsm hua chahata tha.
tab maain ne kaha, he parameshvar yahova, thm ja! naheen to yakoob kaaise sthiar rah sakega? vah kaaisa nirbal haai.
isake vishay men bhee yahova pachhtaya aur parameshvar yahova ne kaha, aeesee bat fir n hogee..
us ne mujhe yah bhee dikhaya: maain ne dekha ki prabhu sahul lagakar banai hui kisee bheet par khda haai, aur usake hath men sahul haai.
aur yahova ne mujh se kaha, he amos, tujhe kya dekh padta haai? maain ne kaha, aek sahula. tab parameshvar ne kaha, dek, maain apanee praja israael ke beech men sahul lagaunga.
maain ab unako n chhooonga. isahak ke unche sthan ujad, aur israael ke paavitrasthan sunasan ho jaaenge, aur maain yarobam ke gharane par talavar kheeche huae chaddhai karoonga..
kyonaki amos yon kahata haai, ki, yarobam talavar se mara jaaega, aur israael apanee boomi par se nishchay banghauai men jaaega..
aur amasyah ne amos se kaha, he dasharee, yahan se nikalakar yahooda desh men bhag ja, aur vaheen rottee khaya kar, aur vaheen bhvishyadanee kiya kara
parantu betel men fir kabhee bhavishyadanee n karana, kyonaki yah raja ka paavitrasthan aur raja-nagar haai.
amos ne uttr dekar amasyah se kaha, maain ne to bhavishyadvkta tha, aur n bhvishyadvkta ka betta maain to gaya-baail ka charavaha, aur goolar ke vrakshaen ka chhanttnehara tha,
aur yahova ne mujhe bhed-bakaariyon ke peechhe peechhe firane se bulakar kaha, ja, meree praja israael se bhvishyadanee kara.
isaliye ab too yahova ka vachan sun, too kahata haai ki israael ke virooddh bhavishyadanee mat kara aur isahak ke gharane ke virooddh bar bar vachan mat suna.
is karan yahova yon kahata haai, teree sree nagar men veshya ho jaaegee, aur tere bette-bettyaian talavar se maree jaaengee, aur teree boomi doree dalakar bantt lee jaaegeen aur too ap ashuuddh desh men marega, aur israael apanee boomi par se nishchay bandhaai men jaaega..
parameshvar yahova ne mujh ko yon dikhaya: ki, dhoopakal ke falon se bhree hui aek ttokaree haai.
aur us ne kaha, he amos, tujhe kya dekh padta haai? maain ne kaha, dhoopakal ke falon se bhree aek ttokaree. tab yahova ne mun se kaha, meree praja israael ka ant a gaya haai maain ab usako aur n chhooonga.
parameshvar yahova kee vanee haai, ki us din rajamandair ke geet hahakar men badal jaaenge, aur lathon ka bada ddher lagega aur sab sthanon men ve chupachap faenk dee jaaengee..
yah suno, tum jo daridraen ko nigalana aur desh ke namra logon ko nash karana chahate ho,
jo kahate ho naya chand kab beetega ki ham ann bech saken? aur vishraamadin kab beetega, ki ham ann ke khtte kholakar aepa ko chhotta aur shokel ko bharee kar de, aur chhl se dandee mare,
ki ham kangalon ke roopaya dekar, aur daaridraen ko aek jodee jootiyan dekar mol le, aur nikamma ann bechen?
yahova, jis par yakoob ko ghamand karana uchit haai, vahee apanee shapath khakar kahata haai, maain tumhare kisee kam ko kibhee n booloonga.
kya is karan boomi n kanpegee? aur kya un par ke sab rahanevale vilap n karenge? yah desh sab ka sab misr kee neel nadee ke saman hoga, jo baddhtee haai, fir laharen maratee, aur ghatt jatee haai..
parameshvar yahova kee yah vanee haai, us samay maain soorya ka dopahar ke samay ast karoonga, aur is desh ko din dupaharee aandhiayara kar doonga.
maain tumhare pavorn ke utsav door karake vilap karaunga, aur tumhare sab geeton ko door karake vilap ke geet gavaunga maain tum sab kee katt imen ttatt bandhaaunga, aur tum sab ke siron ko mundaunga aur aeesa vilap karaunga jaaisa aekalaute ke liye hota haai, aur usaka ant kattnai du:kh ke din ka sa hoga..
aur log yahova ke vachan kee khoj men samudra se samudra tab aur uttr se poorab tak mare mare firenge, parantu usako n paaenge..
us samay sundar kumaariyan aur javan puroosh donon pyas ke mare moorchha khaenge.
jo log samariya ke pap mool devata kee shapath khate haai, aur jo kahate haain ki dan ke devata ke jeevan kee shapat, aur beshorba ke panth kee shapat, ve sab gir padenge, aur fir n uttenge..
maain ne prabhu ko vedee ke upar khda dekha, aur us ne kaha, khmbhe kee kangaaniyon par mar jis se devaaddhiyan hile, aur unako sab logon ke sir par girakar ttukade ttukade kara aur jo nash hone se bache, unhen maain talavar se ghaat karoonga un men se aek bhee n bhag nikalega, aur jo apane ko bachaa, vah bachane n paaega..
kyonaki chahe ve khodakar adhaelok men utar jaae, to vahan se maain hath baddhakar unhen launga chahe ve akash par chaddh jaae, to vahan se maain unhen utar launga.
chahe ve kamrmel men chhpai jaae, parantu vahan bhee maain unhen ddoonddh-ddoonddhkar pakad loonga, aur chahe ve samudra kee thah men meree draashtti se ott ho, vahan bhee maain sarpa ko unhen dsane kee agyaa doonga.
aur chahe shatra unhen hankakar bandhauai men le jaae, vahan bhee maain agyaa dekar talavar se unhen ghaat karaunga aur maain un par bhlai karane ke liye nahee, burai kee karane ke liye draashtti karoonga..
senaon ke parameshvar yahova ke sparsha karane se prathvee pighalatee haai, aur usake sare rahanevale vilap karate haain aur vah sab kee sab misr kee nadee ke saman jo jatee haai, jo baddhtee haai fir laharen maratee, aur ghatt jatee haai.
jo akash men apanee kottriyan banata, aur apane akashamandl kee nev prathvee par dalata, aur samudra ka jal gharatee par baha deta haai, usee ka nam yahova haai..
he israaeliyo, yahova kee yah vanee haai, kya tum mere lekhe kooshaiyon ke saman naheen ho? kya maain israael ko misr desh se aur paalishtaiyon ko kaptor se naheen nikal laya? aur araamiyon ko keer se naheen nikal laya?
dekho, parameshvar yahova kee drashtti is papa-may rajy par lagee haai, aur maain isako dharatee par se nash karoonga taubhee maain pooree reeati se yakoob ke gharane ko nash n karoonga, yahova kee yahee vanee haai.
meree agyaa se israael ka dharana sab jatiyon men aeesa chala jaaega jaaisa ann chalanee men chala jata haai, parantu usaka aek bhee pushtt dana boomi par n girega.
us samay maain daud kee giree hui jhopadee ko khda karoonga, aur usake bade ke nakon ko sudhaaroonga, aur usake khndharon ko fir banaunga, aur jaaisa vah praacheenakal se tha, usako vaaisa hee bana dunga
jis se ve bache huae aedomiyon ko varan sab anyajaatiyon ko jo meree kahalatee haai, apane adhaikar men le, yahova jo yah kam poora karata haai, usakee yahee vanee haai..
yahova kee yah bhee vanee haai, dekho, aeese din ate haai, ki hal jotanevala lavanevale ko aur dakh raundanevala beech bonevale ko ja lega aur pahadon se naya dakhmadha ttpakane lagega, aur sab pahadiyon se bah nikalega.
maain apanee praja israael ke bandhauon ko faer le aunga, aur ve ujade huae nagaron ko sudhaarakar un men basenge ve dakh kee bariyan lagakar dakhmadha peeaenge, aur bageeche lagakar unake fal khaaenge.
maain unhe, unheen kee boomi men bounga, aur ve apanee boomi men se jo maain ne unhen dee haai, fir kabhee ukhade n jaaenge, tumhare parameshvar yahova ka yahee vachan haai..
obadhah ka darshana.. ham logon ne yahova kee or se samachar suna haai, aur aek doot anyajaatiyon men yah kahane ko bheja gaya haai:
utto! ham us se ladne ko utten! maain tujhe jaatiyon men chhotta kar doonga, too bahut tuchchh gina jaega.
he pahadon kee dararon men basanevale, he unche sthan men rahanevale, tere abhaiman ne tujhe dhaekha diya haai too man men kahata haai,
kaun mujhe boomi par utar dega? parantu chahe too ukab kee nain uncha udta ho, varan taragan ke beech apana ghaensala banaae ho, taubhee maain tujhe vahan se neeche giraunga, yahova kee yahee vanee haai..
yaadi chora-dakoo rat ko tere pas ate, hay, too kaaise mitta diya gaya haai! to kya ve churaae huae dhan se trapt hokar chale n jate? aur yaadi dakh ke todnevale tere pas ate, to kya ve kaheen kaheen dakh n chhod jate?
parantu aesav ka dhan kaaise khojakar lootta gaya haai, usaka gupt dhan kaaise pata laga lagakar nikala gaya haai!
jitanon ne tujh se vacha bandhaee thee, un sabhon ne tujhe sivane tak ddhkel diya haai jo log tujh se mel rakhte the, ve tujh ko dhaeka dekar tujh par prabal huae haain ve teree rottee khate haai, ve tere liye fanda lagate haain-- us men kuchh samajh naheen haai.
yahova kee yah vanee haai, kya maain us samay aedom men se buaddhmaianon ko, aur aesav ke pahad men se chaturai ko nash n karoonga?
aur he teman, tere shooraveeron ka man kachcha n ho jaaega, aur yon aesav ke pahad par ka har aek puroosh ghaat hokar nash ho jaaega.
he aesav, aek upadrav ke karan jo too ne apane bhai yakoob par kiya, too lajja se ddhnpega aur sada ke liye nash ho jaaega.
jis din paradeshaee log usakee dhan sampaati chheenakar le gaa, aur birane logon ne usake faattkon se ghausakar yarooshalem par chitthee dalee, us din too bhee un men se aek tha.
tujhe uchit n tha ki meree praja kee vipaati ke din too usake faattk se ghausata, aur usakee vipaati ke din usakee dhan sampati par hath lagata.
tujhe uchit n tha ki tiramuhane par usake bhaganevalon ko mar dalane ke liye khda hota, aur sankatt ke din usake bache huon ko pakadata..
kyonaki saree anyajatiyon par yahova ke din ka ana nikatt haai. jaaisa tu ne kiya haai, vaaisa hee tujh se bhee kiya jaaega, tera vyavahar lauttkar tere hee sir par padega.
jis prakar too ne mere pavitra parvat par piya, usee prakar se saree anyajaatiyan lagatar peetee rahengee, varan ve sudka-sudkakar peeaengee, aur aesee ho jaaengee jaaisee kabhee hui hee naheen.
parantu us samay siyyon parvat par bache huae log rahenge, or vah pavitrasthan ttharega aur yakoob ka gharana apane nij bhagon ka aadhaikaree hoga.
tab yakoob ka gharana ag, aur yoosufa ka gharana lau, aur aesav ka gharana koonttee banega aur ve un men ag lagakar unako bhsm karenge, aur aesav ke gharane ka koi n bachega kyonaki yahova hee ne aeesa kaha haai..
daakkhian desh ke log aesav ke pahad ke aadhaikaree ho jaaenge, aur neeche ke desh ke log palishtaiyon ke aadhaikaree honge aur yahoodee, aepraaim aur samariya ke dihat ko apane bhag men kar lenge, aur binyameen gilad ka aadhaikaree hoga.
israaeliyon ke us dal men se jo lag bandhauai men jakar kananiyon ke beech sarapat tak rahate haai, aur yarooshaleamiyon men se jo log bandhauai men jakar saparad men rahate haai, ve sab dakkhian desh ke nagaron ke adhaikaree ho jaaenge.
aur uddhar karanevale aesav ke pahad ka nyay karane ke liye siyyon parvat par chaddh aaenge, aur rajy yahova hee ka ho jaaega..
yahova ka yah vachan amitaai ke putra yona ke pas pahuncha,
uttkar us bade nagar neenave ko ja, aur usake virooddh prachar kara kyonaki usakee burai meree draashtti men baddh gai haai.
parantu yona yahova ke sammukh se tashareesh ko bhag jane ke liye utta, aur yapo nagar ke jakar tashareesh janevala aek jahaj paya aur bhada dekar us par chaddh gaya ki unake sath hokar yahova ke sammukh se tashareesh ko chala jaae..
tab yahova ne samudra men aek prachand andhaee chalai, aur samudra men badee andhaee uttee, yahan tak ki jahaj toottne par tha.
tab manjhee usake nikatt akar kahane laga, too bharee neend men pada hua kya karata haai? ut, apane devata kee dohai de! sambhv haai ki parameshvar hamaree chinta kare, aur hamara nash n ho..
tab unhon ne apas men kaha, ao, ham chitthee dalakar jan len ki yah vipaati ham par kis ke karan padee haai. tab unhon ne chitthee dalee, aur chitthee yona ke nam par nikalee.
tab unhon ne us se kaha, hamen bata ki kis ke karan yah vipaati ham par padee haai? tera udhym kya haai? aur too kahan se aya haai? too kis desh aur kis jati ka haai?
us ne un se kaha, maain ibraee hoon aur svarga ka parameshvar yahova jis ne jal sthl donon ko banaya haai, usee ka bhy manata hoon.
tab ve nipatt dr gaa, aur us se kahane lage, too ne yah kya kiya haai? ve jan gaae the ki vah yahova ke sammukh se bhag aya haai, kyonki us ne ap hee unako bata diya tha..
tab unhon ne us se poochha, ham tere sath kya karen jis se samudra shaant ho jaae? us samay samudra kee laharen baddhtee hee jatee theen.
us ne un se kaha, mujhe uttakar samudra men faenk do tab samudra shaant pad jaega kyonki maain janata hoo, ki yah bharee andhaee tumhare upar mere hee karan ai haai.
taubhee ve bade yatn se khete rahe ki usako kinare par lagaae, parantu pahunch n sake, kyonaki samudra kee laharen unake virooddh baddhtee hee jatee theen.
tab unhon ne yahova ko pukarakar kaha, he yahova ham binatee karate lae, ki is puroosh ke praan kee santee hamara nash n ho, aur n hamen nirdosh kee hatya ka doshaee tthara kyonki he hayova, jo kuchh teree ichchha thee vahee too ne kiya haai.
tab unhon ne yona ko uttakar samudra men faenk diya aur samudra kee bhyanak laharen thm gain.
tab un manushyon ne yahova ka bahut hee bhy mana, aur usako bhentt chaddhai aur mannaten maneen..
yahova ne aek bada sa magaramachchh ttharaya tha ki yona ko nigal le aur yona us magaramachchh ke pett men teen din aur teen rat pada raha..
tab yona ne usake pett men se apane parameshvar yahova se praarthna karake kaha,
maain ne sankatt men pade huae yahova kee dohai dee, aur us ne meree sun lee haai adhaelok ke udar men se maain chilla utta, aur too ne meree sun lee.
too ne mujhe gahire sagar men samudra kee thah tak dal diya aur maain dhaaraon ke beech men pada tha, teree bhdkai hui sab tarang aur laharen mere upar se bah gain.
maain jal se yahan tak ghaira hua tha ki mere praan nikale jate the gaahira sagar mere charon or tha, aur mere sir men sivar lipatta hua tha.
maain pahadon kee jad tak pahunch gaya tha maain sada ke liye boomi men band ho gaya tha taubhee he mere parameshvar yahova, too ne mere praanon ko gadhe men se uttaya haai.
jab maain moorchha khane laga, tab maain ne yahova ko smaran kiya aur meree praarthna tere pas varan tere pavitra maandair men pahunch gai.
jo log dhaekhe kee vyarth vastuon par man lagate haai, ve apane karoonanidhaan ko chhod dete haain.
parantu maain unche shabd se dhanyavad karake tujhe balidan chaddhaunga jo mannat maain ne manee, usako pooree karoonga. uddhar yahova hee se hota haai.
aur yahova ne magaramachchh ko agyaa dee, aur us ne yona ko sthl par ugal diya..
tab yahova ka yah vachan doosaree bar yona ke pas pahuncha,
uttkar us bade nagar neenave ko ja, aur jo bat maain tujh se kahoonga, usaka us men prachar kara.
tab yona yahova ke vachan ke anusar neenave ko gaya. neenave aek bahut bada lagar tha, vah teen din kee yatra ka tha.
aur yona ne nagar men pravesh karake aek din kee yatra pooree kee, aur yah prachar karata gaya, ab se chalees din ke beetane par neenave ulatt diya jaaega.
tab neenave ke manushyon ne parameshvar ke vachan kee prateeti kee aur upavas ka prachar kiya gaya aur bade se lekar chhotte tak sabhon ne ttatt oddha.
tab yah samachar neenave ke raja ke kan men pahuncha aur us ne sinhasan par se ut, apana rajakeey oddhna utarakar ttatt oddh liya, aur rakh par baaitt gaya.
aur raja ke pradhaanon se sammaati lekar neenave men is agyaa ka ddheenddhora pittvaya, ki kya manushy, kya gaya-baail, kya bhed-bakaree, ya aur pashu, koi kuchh bhee n khaaen ve ne khanae aur n panee peeven.
aur manushy aur pashu donon ttatt oddhe, aur ve parameshvar kee dohai chilla-achilla kar den aur apane kumarga se firen aur us upadrav se, jo ve karate haai, pashchatap karen.
jab parameshvar ne unake kamon ko dekha, ki ve kumarga se fir rahe haai, tab parameshvar ne apanee ichchha badal dee, aur unakee jo haani karane kee ttanee thee, usako n kiya..
yah bat yona ko bahut hee buree lagee, aur usaka krodha bhdka.
aur us ne yahova se yah kahakar praarthna kee, he yahova jab maain apane desh men tha, tab kya maain yahee bat n kahata tha? isee karan maain ne teree agyaa sunate hee tashareesh ko bhag jane ke liye faurtee kee kyonki maain janata tha ki too anugrahakaree aur dayalu parameshvar haai, vilamb se kop karanevala karoonanidhaan haai, aur du:kh dene se prasann naheen hota.
so ab he yahova, mera praan le le kyonaki mere liye jeeavit rahane se marana hee bhla haai.
yahova ne kaha, tera jo krodha bhdka haai, kya vah uchit haai?
is par yona us nagar se nikalakar, usakee poorab or baaitt gaya aur vahan aek chhppar banakar usakee chhaya men baaitta hua yah dekhne laga ki nagar ko kya hoga?
tab yahova parameshvar ne aek rend ka ped lagakar aeesa baddhaya ki yona ke sir par chhaya ho, jis se usaka du:kh door ho. yona us rend ke ped ke karan bahut hee anaandait hua.
bihan ko jab pau fattne lagee, tab parameshvar ne aek keede ko bheja, jis ne rend ka ped aesa katta ki vah sookh gaya.
jab soorya uga, tab parameshvar ne puravai bahakar loo chalai, aur ghaam yona ke sir par aeesa laga ki vah moochrchha khane laga aur us ne yah kahakar mratyu mangee, mere liye jeeavit rahane se marana hee achchha haai.
parameshvar ne yona se kaha, tera krodha, jo rend ke ped ke karan bhdka haai, kya vah uchit haai? us ne kaha, ha, mera jo krodha bhdka haai vah achchha hee haai, varan krodha ke mare marana bhee achchha hota.
tab yahova ne kaha, jis rend ke ped ke liye too ne kuchh paarishram naheen kiya, n usako baddhaya, jo aek hee rat men hua, aur aek hee rat men nash bhee hua us par too ne taras khai haai.
fir yah bada nagar neenave, jis men aek lakh bees hajar se aadhaim manushy haai, jo apane dahine baaen hathon ka bhed naheen paahichanate, aur bahut ghareloo pashu bhee us men rahate haai, to kya maain us par taras n khaun?
yahova ka vachan, jo yahooda ke raja yotam, ahaj aur hijaakiyyah ke dinon men meeka moreshotee ko pahuncha, jis ko us ne shaemaron aur yarooshalem ke vishay men paya..
he jaati-jati ke sab logo, suno! he prathvee too us sab samet jo tujh men haai, dhyan de! aur prabhu yahova tumhare viroodd, varan parameshvar apane paavitra maandair men se tum par sakshaee de.
aur pahad usake neeche gal jaaenge, aur tarai aeese fattengee, jaaise mom ag kee anch se, aur panee jo ghaatt se neeche bahata haai.
yah sab yakoob ke aparadha, aur israael ke gharane ke pap ke karan se hota haai. yakoob ka aparadha kya haai? kya samaariya naheen? aur yahooda ke unche sthan kya haain? kya yarooshalem naheen?
is karan maain samariya ko maaidan ke khet ka ddher kar doonga, aur dakh ka bageecha banaunga aur maain usake patthron ko khdd men luddhka doonga, aur usakee nev ukhad doonga.
usakee sab khudee hui mooraten ttukade ttukade kee jaengee aur jo kuchh us ne chhnaiala karake kamaya haai vah ag se bhsm kiya jaega, aur usakee sab pratimaon ko maain chakanachoor karoonga kyonki chhnaiale hee kee kamai se usane usako sanchay kiya haai, aur vah fir chhnaiale kee see kamai ho jaegee..
is karan maain chhatee peettkar hay, hay, karoonga maain lutta hua sa aur nanga chala fira karoonga maain geedadon kee nai chillaunga, aur shaturmugon kee nain rounga.
kyonaki usaka ghaav asadhy haai aur vipaati yahooda par bhee a padee, varan vah mere jaatibhaiyon par padkar yarooshalem ke faattk tak pahunch gai haai..
gat nagar men isakee charcha mat karo, aur mat roo betaapra men dhooti men lottpott karo.
he shaapeer kee rahanevalee nangee hokar nirlaj chalee ja sanan kee rahanevalee naheen nikal sakatee betasel ke rone peettne ke karan usaka sharansthan tum se le liya jaaega.
kyonaki marot kee rahanevalee to kushal kee batt johate-johate tadp gai haai, kyonki yahova kee or se yarooshalem ke faattk tak vipaati a pahunchee haai.
he lakeesh kee rahanevalee apane rathon men veg chalanevale ghaede jota tujhee se siyyon kee praja ke pap ka arambh hua, kyonki israael ke aparadha tujhee men paae gaae.
is karan too gat ke moreshot ko dan dekar door kar dega akajeeb ke ghar se israael ke raja dhaesha hee khaaenge.
he maresha kee rahanevalee maain fir tujh par aek adhaikaree ttharaunga, aur israael ke pratishttit logon ko adullam men ana padega.
apane dulare ladkon ke liye apana kesh kattvakar sir munda, varan apana poora sir giddh ke saman ganja kar de, kyonaki ve bandhauae hokar tere pas se chale gaae haain.
hay un par, jo bichhaunon par pade huae buraiyon kee kalpana karate aur dushtt karma kee ichchha karate haai, aur balavant hone ke karan bhor ko din nikalate hee ve usako poora karate haain.
ve kheton ka lalach karake unhen chhlee lete haai, aur gharon ka lalach karake unhen bhee le lete haain aur usake gharane samet puroosh par, aur usake nij bhag samet kisee puroosh par andhor aur atyachar kahate haain.
us samay yah atyant shaek ka geet drashttant kee reeati par gaya jaega: ham to sarvanash ho gae vah mere logon ke bhag ko bigadta haai hay, vah use mujh se kitanee door kar deta haai! vah hamare khet balava karanevale ko de deta haai.
is karan tera aeesa koi n ho, jo yahova kee mandlee men chitthee dalakar napane kee doree dale..
bakavasee kaha karate haai, ki bakavas n karo. in baten ke liye n kaha karo aeese logon men se apaman n mittega.
he yakoob ke gharane, kya yah kaha jaae ki yahova ka atma adhaeer ho gaya haai? kya ye kam usee ke kiae huae haain? kya mere vachanon se usaka bhla naheen hota jo seedhaai se chalata haai?
parantu kal kee bat haai ki meree praja shatra banakar mere virooddh uttee haai tum shaant aur bhole-bhale raahiyon ke tan par se chadar chheen lete ho jo ladai ka vichar n karake nidhadk chale jate haain.
meree praja kee striayon ko tum unake sukhdhaamon se nikal dete ho aur unake nanhen bachchon se tum meree dee hui uttm vastuaen sarvada ke liye chheen lete ho.
utto, chale jao! kyonki yah tumhara vishraamasthan naheen haai isaka karan vah ashuuddhta haai jo kaattnai du:kh ke sath tumhara nash karegee.
yaadi koi joottee atma men chalata huae joottee aur vyarth baten kahe aur kahe ki maain tumhen nity dakhmadha aur madira ke liye prachar sunata rahoonga, to vahee in logon ka bhvishyadvkta ttharega..
he yakoob, maain nishchay tum sabhon ko ikattha karoonga maain israael ke bache huon ko nishchay ikattha karoonga aur bosra kee bhedbakariyon kee nain aek sang rakoonga. us jhund kee nain jo achchhee charai men ho, ve manushyon kee bahutayat ke mare kolahal machaaenge.
unake age age bade ka todnevala gaya haai, isaliye ve bhee use tod rahe haai, aur faattk se hokar nikal ja rahe haain unaka raja unake age age gaya arthata yahova unaka saradar aur aguva haai..
aur maain ne kaha, he yakoob ke pradhaano, he israael ke gharane ke nyaiyo, suno! kya nyay ka bhed janana tumhara kam naheen?
tum to bhlai se baair, aur burai se praeeti rakhte ho, mano, tum, logon par se unakee khal, aur unakee haddiyon par se unaka mans udhod lete ho
varan tum mere logon ka mans kha bhee lete, aur unakee khal udhodte ho tum unakee haaddiyon ko handee men pakane ke liye ttukade ttukade karate ho.
yahova ka yah vachan haai ki jo bhvishyadvkta meree praja ko bhttka dete haai, aur jab unhen khane ko milata haai tab shaaantai, shaaantai, pukarate haai, aur yadi koi unake munh men kuchh n de, to usake virooddh yuddh karate ko taaiyar ho jate haain.
is karan tum par aeesee rat aaegee, ki tum ko darshan n milega, aur tum aeese andhakar men padoge ki bhavee n kah sakoge. bhvishyadvktaon ke liye soorya ast hoga, aur din rahate un par andhiayara chha jaaega.
dasharee laajjait honge, aur bhavee kahanevalon ke munh kale honge aur ve sab ke sab apane otton ko isaaliye ddhanpenge ki parameshvar kee or se uttr naheen milata.
parantu maain to yahova kee atma se shaaktai, nyay aur parakram pakar paripoorn hoon ki maain yakoob ko usaka aparadha aur israael ko usaka pap jata sakoon.
he yakoob ke gharane ke pradhaano, he israael ke gharane ke nyayiyo, he nyay se dharana karanevalo aur sab seedhaee baton kee tteddhee-meddhee karanevalo, yah bat suno.
tum siyyon ko hatya karake aur yarooshalem ko kuattlaita karake draddh karate ho.
usake pradhaan ghoos le lekar vichar karate, aur yajak dam le lekar vyavastha dete haai, aur bhvishyadvkta roopaye ke liye bhavee kahate haain taueeaee ve yah kahakar yahova par bhrosa rakhte haai, yahova hamare beech men haai, isaliye koi vipaati ham par n aegee.
isaliye tumhare karan siyyon jotakar khet banaya jaaega, aur yarooshalem deenh hee deenh ho jaaega, aur jis parvat par bhvan bana haai, vah van ke unche sthan sa ho jaaega..
ant ke dinon men aeesa hoga ki yahova ke bhvan ke bhvan ka parvat sab pahadon par draddh kiya jaaega, aur sab pahaadiyon se aadhaik uncha kiya jaaega aur har jati ke log dhaara kee nain usakee or chalenge.
aur bahut jatiyon ke lag jaaenge, aur apas men kahenge, ao, ham yahova ke parvat par chaddhkar, yakoob ke parameshvar ke bhvan men jaaen tab vah ham ko apane marga sikhaaega, aur ham usake pathon par chalenge. kyonaki yahova kee vyavastha siyyon se, aur usaka vachan yarooshalem se nikalega.
vah bahut dekhon ke logon ka nyay karega, aur door door tak kee samarthee jatayon ke jhgadon ko mittaaega so ve apanee talavaren peettkar hal ke faal, aur apane bhalon se hanasiya banaaenge tab aek jati doosaree jaati ke virooddh talavar fir n chalaaegee
aur log age ko yuddh vidha n seekhenge. parantu ve apanee apanee dakhlata aur anjeer ke vraksha tale baaitta karenge, aur koi unako n draaega senaon ke yahova ne yahee vachan diya haai..
sab rajyon ke log to apane apane devata ka nam lekar chalate haai, parantu ham log apane parameshvar yahova ka nam lekar sada sarvada chalate rahenge..
yahova kee yah vanee haai, us samay maain praja ke langadon ko, aur barabas nikale huon ko, aur jin ko maain ne du:kh diya haai un sab ko ikatthe karoonga.
aur langadon ko maain bacha rachoonga, aur door kiae huon ko aek samarthee jaati kar doonga aur yahova un par siyyon parvat ke upar se sada rajy karata rahega..
aur he aeder ke gummat, he siyyon kee pahadee, paahilee prabhuta arthata yarooshalem ka rajy tujhe milega..
he siyyon kee bettee, jachcha sree kee nain peeda uttakar utpann kara kyonaki ab too gaddhee men se nikalakar maaidan men basegee, varan babul tak jaaegee vaheen too chhudai jaaegee, arthata vaheen yahova tujhe tere shatrauon ke vash men se chhuda lega..
aur ab bahut see jatiyan tere virooddh ikatthee hokar tere vishay men kahengee siyyon apaavitra kee jaa, aur ham apanee ankhon se usako niharen.
parantu ve yahova kee kalpanaaen naheen janate, n usakee yuaktai samajhte haai, ki vah unhen aeesa battor lega jaaise khalihan men poole battore jate haain.
he siyyon, utt aur danv kar, maain tere seengon ko lohe ke, aur tere khuon kon peetal ke bana doonga or too bahut see jatiyon ko choorachoor karegee, or unakee kamai yahova ko aur unakee dhana-sampaiti prathvee ke prabhu ke liye arpan karegee..
ab he bahut dalon kee svaminee, dal bandha-bandhakar ikatthee ho, kyonki us ne ham logon ko ghor liya haai ve israael ke nyayee ke gal par sontta marenge.
he betalehem aepraata, yaadi too aeesa chhotta haai ki yahooda ke hajaron men gina naheen jata, taubhee tujh men se mere liye aek puroosh nikalega, jo israaeliyon men prabhuta karanevala hoga aur usaka nikalana praacheenakal se, varan anaadi kal se hota aya haai.
is karan vah unako us samay tak tyage rahega, jab tak jachcha utpann n kare tab israaeliyon ke pas usake bache huae bhai lauttkar un se mil jaaenge.
aur vah khda hokar yahova kee dee hui shaaktai se, aur apane parameshvar yahova ke nam ke pratap se, unakee charavahee karega. aur ve suraakshiat rahenge, kyonki ab vah prathvee kee chhor tak mahana ttharega..
aur vah shaantai ka mool hoga, jab ashshooree hamare desh par chaddhai kare, aur hamare rajabhvanon men panv dhare, tab ham unake virooddh sat charavahe varan att pradhaan manushy khden karenge.
aur ve ashshoor ke desh ko varan paaittav ke sthanon tak nimraed ke desh ke talavar chalakar mar lenge aur jab ashshooree log hamare desh men aae, aur usake sivane ke bheetar panv dhare, tab vahee puroosh ham ko un se bachaaega.
aur yakoob ke bache huae log bahut rajyon ke beech aeesa kam denge, jaaisa yahova kee or se padnevalee os, aur ghaas par kee vashara, jo kisee ke liye naheen ttharatee aur manushyon kee batt naheen johatee.
aur yakoob ke bache huae log jaatiyon men aur desh desh ke logon ke beech aeese honge jaaise vanapashuuon men sinh, va bhed-bakaariyon ke jhundon men javan sinh hota haai, kyonaki jab vah unake beech men se jaa, to latadta aur faadta jaaega, aur koi bacha n sakega.
yahova kee yahee vanee haai, us samay maain tere ghaedon ko tere beech men se nash karoonga aur tere rathon ka vinash karoonga.
or maain tere desh ke nagaron ko bhee nash karoonga, aur tere kilon ko ddha doonga.
aur maain tere tantra-mantra nash karoonga, aur tujh men ttonhe age ko n rahenge.
or maain teree khudee hui moorate, aur teree latte, tere beech men se nash karoonga aur too age ko apane hath kee banai hui vastuon ko dandvata n karega.
aur maain teree ashora nam mooraton ko teree boomi men se ukhad daloonga, aur tere nagaron ka vinash karoonga.
aur maain anyajaatiyon se jo mera kaha naheen manatee, krodha aur jal jalahatt ke sath palatta loonga..
jo bat yahova kahata haai, use suno: uttkar, pahadon ke samhane vadavivad kar, aur tteele bhee teree sunane paaen.
he pahado, aur he prathvee kee attl nev, yahova ka vadaavivad suno, kyonki yahova ka apanee praja ke sath mukama haai, aur vah israael se vadavivad karata haai..
he meree praja, maain ne tera kya kiya, aur kya karake maain ne tujhe ukata diya haai?
mere virooddh sakshaee de! maain to tujhe misr desh se nikal le aya, aur dasatv ke ghar men se tujhe chhuda laya aur teree aguvai karane ko moosa, haroon aur maariyam ko bhej diya.
he meree praja, smaran kar, ki moab ke raja balak ne tere virooddh kaun see yuaktai kee? aur bor ke putra bilam ne usako kya sammati dee? aur shaitiam se gilgal tak kee baton ka smaran kar, jis se too yahova ke dharma ke kam samajh sake..
maain kya lekar yahova ke sammukh au, aur upar rahanevale parameshvar ke samhane jhukoon? kya maain homabaali ke liye aek aek varsha ke bachhde lekar usake sammukh aun?
kya yahova hajaron meddhon se, va tel kee lakhon naadiyon se prasann hoga? kya maain apane aparadha ke praayashchaitt men apane pahilautte ko va apane pap ke badale men apane janmaae huae kisee ko doon?
he manushy, vah tujhe bata chuka haai ki achchha kya haai aur yahova tujh se ise chhod aur kya chahata haai, ki too nyay se kam kare, aur krapa se praeeti rakhe, aur apane parameshvar ke sath namrata se chale?
yahova is nagar ko pukar raha haai, aur sampoorn gyaan, tere nam ka bhy manana haai: rajadand kee, aur jo use denevala haai usakee bat suno!
kya ab tak dushtt ke ghar men dushttta se paya hua dhan aur chhotta aepa gharaanait naheen haai?
kya maain kapatt ka tarajoo aur ghattbaddh ke battkhron kee thailee lekar paavitra tthar sakata hoon?
is karan maain tujhe marate marate bahut hee ghaayal karata hoo, aur tere papon ke karan tujh ko ujad dalata hoon.
too khaaega, parantu trapt n hoga, tera patt jalata hee rahega aur too apanee sampati lekar chalega, parantu n bacha sakega, aur jo kuchh too bacha bhee le, usako maain talavar chalakar luttva doonga.
too boaega, parantu lavega naheen too jalapai ka tel nikalega, parantu lagane n paaega aur dakh raundega, parantu dakhmadha peene n paaega.
kyonaki ve omraee kee vidhaiyon par, aur ahab ke gharane ke sab kamon par chalate haain aur tum unakee yuktaiyon ke anusar chalate ho isaliye maain tujhe ujad doonga, aur is nagar ke rahanevalon par talee bajavaunga, aur tum meree praja kee namadharai sahoge..
hay mujh par ! kyonki maain us jal ke saman ho gaya hoon jo dhoopakal ke fal todne par, va rahee hutt dakh beenane ke samay ke ant men a jaa, mujhe to pakkee anjeeron kee lalasa thee, parantu khane ke liye koi guchchha nahee raha.
bhkt log prathvee par se nash ho gaae haai, aur manushyon men aek bhee seedha naheen jan naheen raha ve sab ke sab hatya ke liye ghaat lagate, aur jal lagakar apane apane bhai ka aher karate haain.
ve apane donon hathon se man lagakar burai karate haain haakim ghoos mangata, aur nyayee ghoos lene ko taaiyar rahata haai, aur rais apane man kee dushttta varnn karata haai isee prakar se ve sab milakar jalasajee karate haain.
un men se jo sab se uttm haai, jo sab se seedha haai, vah kanttevale bade se bhee bura haai. tere paharooon ka kaha hua din, arthata tere dand ka din a gaya haai. ab ve shaeegha chaunadhaiya jaenge.
mitra par vishvas mat karo, paramaamitra par bhee bhrosa mat rakho varan apanee arddhagin se bhee sanbhlakar bolana.
kyonaki putra pita ka apaman karata, aur bettee mata ke, aur patoh sas ke virooddh utttee haai manushy ke shatra usake ghar hee ke log hote haain.
parantu maain yahova kee or takata rahoonga, maain apane uddharakarta parameshvar kee batt johata rahoonga mera parameshvar meree sunega..
maain ne yahova ke virooddh pap kiya haai, is karan maain us samay tak usake krodha ko sahata rahoonga jab tak ki vah mera mukama ladkar mera nyay n chukaaega. us samay vah mujhe ujiyale men nikal le aaega, aur maain usaka dharma dekoonga.
tab meree baaiarin jo mujh se yah kahatee haai ki tera parameshvar yahova kahan raha, vah bhee use dekhegee aur lajja se munh ddhanpegee. maain apanee ankhon se use dekoonga tab vah sadkon kee keech kee nain latadee jaaegee..
tere badon ke bandhane ke din usakee seema baddhai jaaegee.
us din ashshoor se, aur misr aur mahanad ke beech ke, aur samudra-samudra aur pahad-pahad ke beech men deshaen se log tere pas anege.
taubhee yah desh apane rahanevalon ke kamon ke karan ujad hee rahega..
too lattee liye huae apanee praja kee charavahee kar, arthata apane nij bhag kee bhed-bakaariyon kee, jo kamrmel ke van men alag baaitttee haai ve poorvakal kee nain bashaan aur gilad men chara karen..
jaaise ki misr desh se tere nikal ane ke dinon me, vaaisee hee ab maain usako adabhut kam dikhaunga.
anyajatiyan dekhkar apane sare parakram ke vishay men lajaaengee ve apane munh ko hath se chhpaiaaengee, aur unake kan bahire ho jaaenge.
ve sarpa kee nain mittee chattengee, aur boomi par renganevale jantuon kee bhanati apane bilon men se kanpatee hui nikalengee he hamare parameshvar yahova ke pas thrathratee hui aaengee, aur ve tujh se drengee..
tere saman aeesa parameshvar kahan haai jo adharma ko kshama kare aur apane nij bhag ke bache huon ke aparadha ko ddhanp de? vah apane krodha ko sada banaae naheen rahata, kyonaki vah karoona se praeeati rakhta haai.
vah fir ham par daya karega, aur hamare adharma ke kamon ko latad dalega. too unake sab papon ko gaahire samudra men dal dega.
too yakoob ke vishay men vah sachchai, aur ibraaheem ke vishay men vah karoona pooree karega, jis kee shapath too praachaeenakal ke dinon se lekar ab tak hamare pitaron se khata aya haai..
neenave ke vishay men bharee vachana. aelkoshaee nahoom ke darshan kee pustaka..
yahova jal uttnevala aur badala lenevala ishvar haai yahova badala lenevala aur jalajalahatt karanevala haai yahova apane draehiyon se badala leta haai, aur apane shatrauon ka pap naheen boolata.
yahova vilamb se krodha karanevala aur bada shaaktaiman haai vah doshaee ko kisee prakar nirdosh n ttharaaega.. yahova bavandr aur andhaee men hokar chalata haai, aur badal usake panvon kee dhooli haai.
usake ghaudkane se mahanad sookh jate haai, aur samudra bhee nirjal ho jata haai bashaan aur kammarail kumhalate aur labanon kee hariyalee jatee rahatee haai.
usake sparsha se pahad kanp uttte haain aur pahadiyan gal jatee haain usake pratap se prathvee varan sara sansar apane sab rahanevalon samet thrathra uttta haai..
usake krodha ka samhana kaun kar sakata haai? aur jab usaka krodha bhdkata haai, tab kaun tthar sakata haai? usakee jalajalahatt ag kee nain bhdk jatee haai, aur chattanen usakee shaktai se fatt fattkar giratee haain.
parantu vah umadtee hui dhaara se usake sthan ka ant kar dega, aur apane shatrauon ko khdedkar andhakar men bhga dega.
tum yahova ke virooddh kya kalpana kar rahe ho? vah tumhara ant kar dega vipaati doosaree bar padne n paaegee.
kyeanki chahe ve kantton se ulajhe huae ho, aur madira ke nasho men choor bhee ho, taubhee ve sookhee koonttee kee nain bhsm kiae jaaenge.
tujh men se aek nikala haai, jo yahova ke virooddh kalpana karata aur neechata kee yuktai bandhata haai..
yahova yon kahata haai, chahe ve sab prakar ke samarthee ho, aur bahut bhee ho, taubhee pooree reeati se katte jaaenge aur shoony ho jaaenge. maain ne tujhe du:kh diya haai, parantu fir n doonga.
kyonaki ab maain usaka jooa teree gardan par se utarakar tod daloonga, aur tera bandhan faad daloonga..
yahova ne tere vishay men yah agyaa dee haai ki age ko tera vansh n chale maain tere devalayon men se ddhlee aur gaddhee hui mooraton ko katt daloonga, maain tere liye kabar khodoonga, kyonki too neech haai..
dekho, pahadon par shuubhsamachar ka sunanevala aur shaaantai ka prachar karanevala a raha haai! ab he yahooda, apane parva man, aur apanee mannaten pooree kar, kyonaki vah ochha fir kabhee tere beech men hokar n chalega, aur pooree reeti se nash hua haai..
satyanash karanevala tere virooddh chaddh aya haai. gaddh ko draddh kara marga dekhta hua chaukas raha apanee kamar kasa apana bal baddha de..
yahova yakoob kee badai israael kee badai ke saman jyon kee tyon kar raha haai, kyonaki ujadnevalon ne unako ujad diya haai aur dakhlata kee daliyon ko nash kiya haai..
rath sadkon men bahut veg se hanke jate haain ve paleeton ke saman dikhain dete haai, aur unaka veg bijalee ka sa haai.
vah apane shooraveeron ko smaran karata haai ve chalate chalate ttokar khate haai, ve shaharapanah kee or faurtee se jate haai, aur katt ka gummatt taaiyar kiya jata haai.
naharon ke dar khul jate haai, aur rajabhvan galakar baaitta jata haai.
huseb nangee karake bandhauvai men le lee jaaegee, aur usakee dasiyan chhatee peetttee hui pindukon kee nain vilap karengee.
neenave jab se banee haai, tab se talab ke saman haai, taubhee ve bhage jate haai, aur khde ho khde ho, aeesa pukare jane par bhee koi munh naheen faerata.
chandee ko lootto, sone ko lootto, usake rakhe huae dhan kee bahutayat, aur vibhv kee sab prakar kee manabhavanee samagraee ka kuchh pariman naheen..
vah khalee, choochheen aur soonee ho gai haai! man kachcha ho gaya, aur panv kanpate haain aur un sabhon ki kattyaien men badee peeda uttee, aur sabhon ke mukh ka rang ud gaya haai!
sinhon kee vah mand, aur javan sinh ke akhett ka vah sthan kahan raha jis men sinh aur sinhanee apane bachchon samet bekhttke firate the?
sinh to apane danvarooon ke liye bahut aher ko faadta tha, aur apanee sinhaniyon ke liye aher ka gala ghaentt ghaenttkar le jata tha, aur apanee gufaaon aur mandon ko aher se bhr leta tha..
senaon ke yahova kee yah vanee haai, maain tere virooddh hoo, aur usake rathon ko bhsm karake dhaunaen men uda doonga, aur usake javan sinh sareekhe veer talavar se mare jaaenge maain tere aher ko prathvee par se nash karoonga, aur tere dooton ka bol fir suna n jaaega..
hay us hatyaree nagaree par, vah to chhl aur loott ke dhan se bhree hui haai loott kam naheen hotee haai.
kodo kee fattkar aur paahiyon kee ghadghadahatt ho rahee haai ghaede koodate-faandate aur rath uchhlate chalate haain.
savar chaddhai karate, talavaren aur bhale bijalee kee nain chamakate haai, mare huon kee bahutayat aur lothon ka bada ddher haai mudorn kee kuchh ginatee nahee, log murdon se ttokar kha khakar chalate haain!
yah sab us aati sundar veshya, aur nipun ttonahin ke chhnaiale ke dara jaati-jati ke logon ko, aur ttone ke dara kula-kul ke logon ko bech dalatee haai..
senaon ke yahova kee yah vanee haai, maain tere virooddh hoo, aur tere vasr ko uttakar, tujhe jati-jati ke samhane nangee aur rajya-rajy ke samhane neecha dikhaunga.
maain tujh par ghainaunee vastuen faenkakar tujhe tuchchh kar doonga, aur sab se teree hansee karaunga.
aur jitane tujhe dekhenge, sab tere pas se bhagakar kahenge, neenave nash ho gai kaun usake karan vilap kare? ham usake liye shaantai denevala kahan se ddoonddhkar le aaen?
kya too amon nagaree se baddhkar haai, jo naharon ke beech basee thee, aur usake liye kila aur shaharapanah ka kam deta tha?
koosh aur misree usako anaginit bal dete the, poot aur loobee tere sahayak the..
too bhee matavalee hogee, too ghabara jaaegee too bhee shatra ke dr ke mare sharan ka sthan ddoonddhegee.
