shaalateeael ke putra yahooda ke adhaipaati jaroobbabel, aur yahosadak ke putra yahoshoo mahayajak aur sab bache huae logon se yah bat kah,
tum men se kaun haai, jis ne is bhvan kee paahilee maahima dekhee haai? ab tum ise kaaisee dasha men dekhte ho? kya yah sach naheen ki yah tumharee draashtti men us pahile kee apeksha kuchh bhee achchha naheen haai?
taubhee, ab yahova kee yah vanee haai, he jaroobbabel, hiyav bandha aur he yahosadak ke putra yahoshoo mahayajak, hiyav bandha aur yahova kee yah bhee vanee haai ki he desh ke sab logo hiyav bandhakar kam karo, kyonaki maain tumhare sang hoo, senaon ke yahova kee yahee vanee haai.
tumhare misr se nikalane ke samay jo vacha maain ne tum se bandhaee thee, usee vacha ke anusar mera atma tumhare beech men bana haai isaaliye tum mat dro.
kyonaki senaon ka yahova yon kahata haai, ab thodee hee der bakee haai ki maain akash aur prathvee aur samudra aur sthl sab ko kampait karoonga.
aushra maai. saree jaatiyon ko kampakapaunga, aur saree jaatiyon kee manabhavanee vastuaen aaengee aur maain is bhvan ko apanee mahima ke tej se bhr doonga, senaon ke yahova ka yahee vachan haai.
chandee to meree haai, aur sona bhee mera hee haai, senaon ke yahova kee yahee vanee haai.
is bhvan kee pichhlee mahima isakee paahilee maahima se badee hogee, senaon ke yahova ka yahee vachan haai, aur is sthan men maain shaantai doonga, senaon ke yahova kee yahee vanee haai..
dara ke doosare varsha ke nauven maheene ke chaubeesave din ko, yahova ka yah vachan haggaai bhavishyadvkta ke pas pahuncha,
senaon ka yahova yon kahata haai: yajakon se is bat kee vyavastha pooch,
yaadi koi apane vasr ke anchal se rottee va pakaae huae bhojan va dakhmadha va tel va kisee prakar ke bhojan ko chhua, to kya vah bhojan pavitra ttharega? yajakon ne uttr diya, naheen.
fir haggaai ne poochha, yadi koi jan manushy kee loth ke karan ashuuddh hokar aeesee kisee vastu ko chhua, to kya vah ashuuddh ttharegee? yajakon ne uttr diya, han ashuuddh ttharegee.
fir haggaai ne kaha, yahova kee yahee vanee haai, ki meree draashtti men yah praja aur yah jaati vaaisee hee haai, aur inake sab kam bhee vaaise haain aur jo kuchh ve vahan chaddhate haai, vah bhee ashuuddh haai
ab socha-avichar karo ki aj se pahile arthata jab yahova ke maandair men patthr par patthr rakha hee naheen gaya tha,
un dinon men jab koi ann ke bees napuon kee asha se jata, tab das hee pata tha, aur jab koi dakhras ke kund ke pas is asha se jata ki pachas bartan bhr nikale, tab bees hee nikalate the.
maain ne tumharee saree khetee ko loo aur garooi aur olon se mara, taubhee tum meree or n fire, yahova kee yahee vanee haai.
ab socha-avichar karo, ki aj se pahile arthata jis din yahova ke mandair kee nev dalee gai, us din se lekar nauven maheene ke isee chaubeesaven din tak kya dasha thee? isaka socha-vichar karo.
kya ab tak beech khtte men haai? ab tak dakhlata aur anjeer aur anar aur jalapai ke vraksha naheen fale, parantu aj ke din se maain tum ko ashaeesh deta rahoonga..
usee maheene ke chaubeesaven din ko doosaree bar yahova ka yah vachan haggaai ke pas pahuncha, yahooda ke adhaipaati jaroobbabel se yon kaha:
maain akash aur prathvee donon ko kampaunga,
senaon ke yahova kee yahee vanee haai, us din, he shaalateeael ke putra mere das jaroobbabel, maain tujhe lekar angoottee ke saman rakoonga, yahova kee yahee vanee haai kyonki maain ne tujhee ko chun liya haai, senaon ke yahova kee yahee vanee haai..
barasat ke ant men yahova se vashara mango, yahova se jo bijalee chamakata haai, aur vah unako vashara dega aur har aek ke khet men haariyalee upajaaega.
kyonaki grahadevata anarth bat kahate aur bhavee kahanevale jootta darshan dekhte aur jootte svapan sunate, aur vyarth shaaantai dete haain. is karan log bhed-bakaariyon kee nain bhttk gaae aur charavahe n hone ke karan durdasha men pade haain..
mera krodha charavahon par bhdka haai, aur maain un bakaron ko dand doonga kyonaki senaon ka yahova apane jhund arthata yahooda ke gharane ka hal dekhne ka aaega, aur ladai men unako apana shttpushtt ghaeda sa banaaega.
aur ve aeese veeron ke saman honge jo ladai men apane baairiyon ko sadkon ke keech kee nain raundate hon ve ladenge, kyonki yahova unake sang rahega, is karan ve veerata se ladenge aur savaron kee asha toottegee..
maain yahooda ke gharane ko parakramee karoonga, aur yoosufa ke gharane ka uddhar karoonga. aur mujhe un par daya ai haai, is karan maain unhen lautta lakar unheen ke desh men basaunga, aur ve aeese honge, manon maain ne unako man se naheen utara maain unaka parameshvar yahova hoo, isaaliye unakee sun loonga.
aepraaimee log veer ke saman honge, aur unaka man aeesa anaandait hoga jaaise dakhmadha se hota haai. yah dekhkar unake ladkebalen anand karenge aur unaka man yahova ke karan magan hoga..
maain seenttee bajakar unako ikattha karoonga, kyonaki maain unaka chhudanevala hoo, aur ve aeese baddhenge jaaise pahale baddhe the.
yadhypi maain unhen jaati-jati ke logon ke beech chhtairaunga taubhee ve door door deshaen men mujhe smaran karenge, aur apane balakon samet jeevit lautt aaenge.
maain unahen misr desh se lautta launga, aur ashshoor se ikattha karoonga, aur gilad aur labanon ke deshaen men le akar itana baddhaunga ki vahan unakee samai n hogee.
vah us kashttdai samudra men se hokar usakee laharen dabata hua jaaega aur neel nadee ka sab gaahira jal sookh jaaega. aur ashshoor ka ghamand toda jaaega aur misr ka rajadand jata rahega.
maain unhen yahova dara parakramee karoonga, aur ve usake nam se chalen firenge, yahova kee yahee vanee haai..
he labanon, ag ko rasta de ki vah akar tere devadaron ko bhsm kare!
he sanaubaro, hay, hay, karo! kyonaki devadar gir gaya haai aur bade se bade vraksha nash ho gaae haain! he basha ke banj vrakshae, hay, hay, karo! kyonaki agamy van katta gaya haai!
charavahon ke hahakar ka shabd ho raha haai, kyonaki unaka vibhv nash ho gaya haai! javan sinhon ka garajana sunai deta haai, kyonaki yaradan ke teer ka ghana van nash kiya gaya haai!
mere parameshvar yahova ne yah agyaa dee: ghaat hanevalee bhed-bakaariyon ka charavaha ho ja.
unake mol lenevale unhen ghaat karane par bhee apane ko doshaee naheen janate, aur unake bechanevale kahate haai, yahova dhany haai, ham dhanee ho gaae haain aur unake charavahe un par kuchh daya naheen karate.
yahova kee yah vanee haai, maain is desh ke rahanevalon par fir daya n karoonga. dekho, maain manushyon ko aek doosare ke hath me, aur unake raja ke hath men pakadva doonga aur ve is desh ko nash karenge, aur maain usake rahanevalon ko unake vash se n chhudaunga..
so maain ghaat honevalee bhed-bakaariyon ko aur vishosh karake un men se jo deen theen unako charane laga. aur maain ne do lattyaian leen aek ka nam maain ne anugrah rakha, aur doosaree ka nam aekata. inako liye huae maain un bhed-bakaariyon ko charane laga.
aur maain ne unake teenon charavahon ko aek maheene men nash kar diya, parantu maain unake karan adhaeer tha, aur ve mujhe se gharana karatee theen.
tab maain ne un se kaha, maain tum ko n charaunga. tum men se jo mare vah mare, aur jo nash ho vah nash ho, aur jo bachee rahen ve aek doosare ka mans khaaen.
aur maain ne apanee vah lattee tod dalee, jisaka nam anugrah tha, ki jo vacha maain ne sab anyajaatiyon ke sath bandhaee thee use tooon.
vah usee din todee gai, aur is se deen bhed-bakaariyan jo mujhe takatee thee, unhon ne jan liya ki yah yahova ka vachan haai.
tab maain ne un se kaha, yaadi tum ko achchha lage to meree majadooree do, aur naheen to mat do. tab unhon ne meree majadooree men chandee ke tees ttukade taul diae.
tab yahova ne mujh se kaha, inhen kumhar ke age faenk de, yah kya hee bharee dam haai jo unhon ne mera ttharaya haai? tab maain ne chandee ke un tees ttukadon ko lekar yahova ke ghar men kumhar ke age faenk diya.
tab maain ne apanee doosaree lattee jis ka nam aekata tha, isaaliye tod dalee ki maain us bhaichare ke nate ko tod daloon jo yahooda aur israael ke beech men haai..
tab yahova ne mujh se kaha, ab too mooddh charavahe ke haathaiyar le le.
kyonaki maain is desh men aek aeesa charavaha ttharaunga, jo khoi hui ko n ddoonddhega, n titara-abitar ko ikatthee karenga, n ghaayalon ko changa karega, n jo bhlee changee haain unaka palana-poshan karega, varan mottyaien ka mans khaaega aur unake khuron ko faad dalega.
hay us nikamme charavahe par jo bhed-bakaariyon ko chhod jata haai! usakee banh, aur dahinee ankh donon par talavar lagegee, tab usakee banh sookh jaaegee aur usakee dahinee ankh foott jaaegee..
dekho, maain yarooshalem ko charon or kee sab jaatiyon ke liye ladkhda dene ke mad ka kattora tthara doonga aur jab yarooshalem ghor liya jaaega tab yahooda kee dasha bhee aeesee hee hogee.
aur us samay prathvee kee saree jaatiyan yarooshalem ke virooddh ikatthee hongee, tab maain usako itana bharee patthr banaunga, ki jo usako uttaaenge ve bahut hee ghaayal honge.
yahova kee yah vanee haai, us samay maain har aek ghaede ka ghabara doonga, aur usake savar ko dhaayal karoonga. parantu maain yahooda ke gharane par krapadrashtti rakoonga, jab maain anyajatiyon ke sab ghaedon ko andha kar daloonga.
us samay maain yahooda ke adhaipaatiyon ko aeesa kar doonga, jaaisee lakadee ke ddher men ag bhree angettee va poole men jalatee hui mashaal hotee haai, arthata ve daahine banae charon or ke sab logon ko bhsm kar dalenge aur yarooshalem jahan ab basee haai, vaheen basee rahegee, yarooshalem men..
aur he yahova paahile yahooda ke tambuon ka uddhar karega, kaheen aeesa n ho ki daud ka gharana aur yarooshalem ke nivasee apane apane vibhv ke karan yahooda ke virooddh baddhai maren.
us samay yahova yarooshalem ke nivaasiyon ko mano ddhal se bacha lega, aur us sakay un men se jo ttokar khanevala ho vah daud ke saman hoga aur daud ka gharana parameshvar ke saman hoga, arthata yahova ke us doot ke saman jo unake age age chalata tha.
aur us samay maain un sab jaatiyon ko nash karane ka yatn karoonga jo yarooshalem par chaddhai karengee..
aur maain daud ke gharane aur yarooshalem ke nivaasiyon par apana anugrah karanevalee aur praarthna sikhanevalee atma undeloonga, tab ve mujhe takenge arthata jise unhon ne bedha haai, aur usake liye aeese roaenge jaaise aekalaute putra ke liye rote-peettte haai, aur aeesa bharee shaek karenge, jaaisa pahilautte ke liye karate haain.
us samay yarooshalem men itana rona-peettna hoga jaaisa maagion kee tarai men hadadirmmon men hua tha.
sare desh men vilap hoga, har aek parivar men alag alaga arthata daud ke gharane ka paarivar alag, aur unakee striayan alaga natan ke gharane ka paarivar alag, aur unakee striayan alaga
levee ke gharane ka parivar alag aur unakee striayan alaga shaimiyon ka paarivar alaga aur unakee striayan alaga
aur jitane parivar rah gaae hon har aek paarivar alag aur unakee striayan bhee alag alaga
usee samay daud ke gharane aur yarooshalem ke nivaasiyon ke liye pap aur maalinata dhaene ke nimitt ek bahata hua sota hoga..
aur senaon ke yahova kee yah vanee haai, ki us samay maain is desh me se moorto ke nam mitta daloonga, aur ve fir smaran men n rahengee aur maain bhavishyadvktaon aur ashuuddh atma ko is desh men se nikal doonga.
aur yaadi koi fir bhvishyadaanee kare, to usake mata-pita, jin se vah utpann hua, us se kahenge, too jeevit n bachega, kyonaki too ne yahova ke nam se joott kaha haai so jab vah bhavishyadanee kare, tab usake mata-apita jin se vah utpann hua usako bedha dalenge.
us samay har ek bhvishyadvkta bhavishyavanee karate huae apane apane darshan se lajjait honge, aur dhaekha dene ke liye kambal ka vasr n paahinenge,
varantu vah kahega, maain bhavishyadvkta nahee, kisan hoon kyonaki ladkapan hee se maain auron ka das hoon.
tab us se yah poochha jaaega, teree chhatee par ye ghaav kaaise hua, tab vah kahega, ye ve hee haain jo mere praemiyon ke ghar men mujhe lage haain..
senaon ke yahova kee yah vanee haai, he talavar, mere ttharaae huae charavahe ke virooddh arthata jo puroosh mera svajati haai, usake virooddh chala. too us charavahe ko kat, tab bhed-bakaariyan titara-abitar ho jaaengee aur bachchon par maain apane hath baddhaunga.
yahova kee yah bhee vanee haai, ki is desh ke sare nivaasiyon kee do tihai mar dalee jaaegaee aur bachee hui tihai us men banee rahegee.
us tihai ko maain ag men dalakar aeesa nirmal karoonga, jaaisa roopa nirmal kiya jata haai, aur aeesa jachoonga jaaisa sona jancha jata haai. ve mujh se praarthna kiya karenge, aur maain unakee sunoonga. maain unake vishay men kahoonga, ye meree praja haai, aur ve mere vishay men kahenge, yahova hamara parameshvar haai..
suno, yahova ka aek aeesa din aneval haai jis men tera dhan loottkar tere beech men bantt liya jaaega.
kyonaki maain sab jaatiyon ko yarooshalem se ladne ke liye ikattha karoonga, aur vah nagar le liya nagara. aur ghar lootte jaaenge aur striayan bhrashtt kee jaaengee nagar ke adho log bandhauvai men jaaenge, parantu praja ke shosh log nagar hee men rahane paaenge.
tab yahova nikalakar un jaatiyon se aeesa ladega jaaisa vah sangraam ke din men lada tha.
aur us samay vah jalapai ke parvat par panv dharega, jo poorab or yarooshalem ke samhane haai tab jalapai ka parvat poorab se lekar paachchhim tak beechobeech se fattkar bahut bada khdd ho jaaega tab adha parvat uttr kee or aur adha dakkhian kee or hatt jaaega.
tab tum mere banaae huae us khdd asel tak pahunchega, varan tum aeese bhagoge jaaise us bhuidaul ke dr se bhage the jo yahooda ke raja ujjaiyah ke dinon men hua tha. tab mera parameshvar yahova aaega, aur sab paavitra log usake sath honge..
us samay kuchh ujiyala n rahega, kyonaki jyotigan simatt jaenge.
aur lagatar aek hee din hoga jise yahova hee janata haai, n to din hoga, aur n rat hogee, parantu sanjh ke samay ujiyala hoga..
us samay yarooshalem se bahata hua jal foott nikalega usakee ek shaakha poorab ke tal aur doosaree pachchhim ke samudra kee or bahegee, aur dhoop ke dinon men aur jade ke dinon men bhee barabar bahatee rahengee..
geba se lekar yarooshalem kee dakkhian or ke rimmon tak sab boomi araba ke saman ho jaaegee. parantu vah unchee hokar binyameen ke faattk se lekar paahile faattk ke sthan tak, aur konevale faattk tak, aur hananel ke gummatt se lekar raja ke dakhrasakundon tak apane sthan men basegee.
aur log us men basenge kyonki fir satyanash ka shaap n hoga aur yarooshalem bekhttke basee rahegee.
aur us samay yahova kee or se un men badee ghabarahatt paaittegee, aur ve aek doosare par apane apane hath uttaaenge.
yahooda bhee yarooshalem men ladega, aur sona, chandee, vasr adi charon or kee sab jaatiyon kee dhan sampaati us men battoree jaaegee.
aur ghaede, khchchar, untt aur gadahe varan jitane pashu unakee chhavaniyon men honge ve bhee aeesee hee beemaree se mare jaaenge..
tab jine log yarooshalem par chaddhnevalee sab jaatiyon men se bache rahenge, ve praati varsha raja ko arthata senaon ke yahova ko dandvata karane, aur jhopaadiyon ka parva manane ke liye yarooshalem ko jaya karenge.
aur prathvee ke kulon men se jo log yarooshalem men raja, arthata senaon ke yahova ko dandvat karane ke liye n jaaenge, unake yahan vashara n hogee.
aur yaadi misr ka kul vahan n aa, to kya un par vah maree n padegee jis se yahova un jatiyon ko marega jo jhopadiyon ka parva manane ke liye n jaaenge?
yah misr ka aur un sab jatiyon ka pap ttharega, jo jhopaadiyon ka parva manane ke liye n jaaenge.
us samay ghaedon kee ghanttyaien par bhee yah likha rahega, yahova ke liye paavitra. aur yahova ke bhvan ki hanadiyan un kattoron ke tuly pavitra ttharengee, jo vedee ke samhane rahate haain.
varan yarooshalem men aur yahooda desh men sab handiyan senaon ke yahova ke liye paavitra ttharengee, aur sab melabaali karanevale a akar un handyaien men mans sijhaya karenge. aur sab senaon ke yahova ke bhvan men fir koi vyoparee n paya jaaega..
dara ke rajy ke doosare varsha ke attven maheene men jakaryah bhavishyadvkta ke pas jo berekyah ka putra aur io ka pota tha, yahova ka yah vachan pahuncha:
yahova tum logon ke purakhaon se bahut hee krodhait hua tha.
isaliye too in logon se kah, senaon ka yahova yon kahata haai: tum meree or firo, senaon ke yahova kee yahee vanee haai, tab maain tumharee or firoonga, senaon ke yahova ka yahee vachan haai.
apane purakhaon ke saman n bano, un se to agale bhavishyadvkta yah pukar pukarakar kahate the ki senaon ka yahova yon kahata haai, apane bure margon se, aur apane bure kamon se firo parantu unhon ne n to suna, aur n meree or dhyan diya, yahova kee yahee vanee haai.
tumhare purakha kahan rahe? aur bhvishyadvkta kya sada jeeavit rahate haain?
parantu mere vachan aur meree agyaaaen jin ko maain ne apane das naabiyon ko diya tha, kya ve tumhare purakhaon par pooree n hui? tab unhon ne man firaya aur kaha, senaon ke yahova ne hamare chalachalan aur kamon ke anusar ham se jaaisa vyavahar karane ko kaha tha, vaaisa hee us ne ham ko badala diya haai..
dara ke doosare varsha ke shabat nam gyarahaven maheene ke chaubeesaven din ko jakaryah nabee ke pas jo berekyah ka putra aur io ka pota tha, yahova ka vachan yon pahuncha:
maain ne rat ko svapn men kya dekha ki aek puroosh lal ghaede par chaddha hua un menhadiyon ke beech khda haai jo neeche sthan men haai, aur usake peechhe lal aur surang aur shvet ghaede bhee khde haain.
tab maain ne kaha, he mere prabhu ye kaun haain? tab jo doot mujh se baten karata tha, us ne mujh se kaha, maain tujhe bataunga ki ye kaun haain.
fir jo puroosh menhadiyon ke beech khda tha, us ne kaha, yah ve haain jin ko yahova ne prathvee par saair arthata dhoomane ke liye bheja haai.
tab unhon ne yahova ke us doot se jo menhadiyon ke beech khda tha, kaha, ham ne prathvee par saair kiya haai, aur kya dekha ki saree prathvee men shaantai aur chaain haai.
tab yahova ke doot ne kaha, he senaon ke yahova, too jo yarooshalem aur yahooda ke nagaron par sattr varsha se krodhait haai, so too un par kab tak daya n karega?
aur yahova ne uttr men us doot se jo mujh se baten karata tha, achchhee achchhee aur shaaantai kee baten kaheen.
tab jo doot mujh se baten karata tha, us ne mujh se kaha, too pukarakar kah ki senaon ka yahova yon kahata haai, mujhe yarooshalem aur siyyon ke liye badee jalan hui haai.
aur jo jaatiyan sukh se rahatee haai, un se maain krodhait hoon kyonki maain ne to thoda se krodha kiya tha, parantu unhon ne vipaati ko baddha diya.
is karan yahova yon kahata haai, ab maain daya karake yarooshalem ko lautt aya hoon mera bhvan us men banega, aur yarooshalem par napane kee doree dalee jaaegee, senaon ke yahova kee yahee vanee haai.
fir yah bhee pukarakar kah ki senaon ka yahova yon kahata haai, mere nagar fir uttm vastuon se bhr jaaenge, aur yahova fir siyyon ko shaaantai dega aur yarooshalem ko fir apana ttharaaega..
fir maain ne jo ankhen uttai, to kya dekha ki char seeng haain.
fir yahova ne mujhe char lohar dikhaae.
fir maain ne ankhen uttain to kya dekha, ki hath men napane kee doree liae huae aek puroosh haai.
tab maain ne us se poochha, too kahan jata haai? us ne mujh se kaha, yarooshalem ko napane jata hoon ki dekoon usakee chaudai kitanee, aur lambai kitanee haai.
tab maain ne kya dekha, ki jo doot mujh se baten karata tha vah chala gaya, aur doosara doot us se milane ke liye akar,
us se kahata haai, daudkar us javan se kah, yarooshalem manushyon aur gharaailoo pashuuon kee bahutayat ke mare shaharapanah ke bahar bahar bhee basegee.
aur yahova kee yah vanee haai, ki maain ap usake charon or ag kee se shaharapanah ttharoonga, aur usake beech men tejomay hokar dikhai doonga..
yahova kee yah vanee haai, dekho, suno uttr ke desh men se bhag jao, kyonki maain ne tum ko akash kee charon vayuon ke saman titar bitar kiya haai.
he babulavalee jaati ke sang rahanevalee, siyyon ko bachakar nikal bhaga!
kyonaki senaon ka yahova yon kahata haai, us tel ke pragatt hone ke bad us ne mujhe un jatiyon ke pas bheja haai jo tumhen lootttee thee, kyonki jo tum ko choota haai, vah meree ankh kee putalee hee ko choota haai.
dekho, maain apana hath un par uttaunga, tab ve unheen se lootte jaaenge jo unake das huae the. tab tum janoge ki senaon ke yahova ne mujhe bheja haai.
he siyyon, unche svar se ga aur anand kar, kyonaki dek, maain akar tere beech men nivas karoonga, yahova kee yahee vanee haai.
us samay bahut see jaatiyan yahova se mil jaengee, aur meree praja ho jaengee aur maain tere beech men bas karoonga,
aur too janegee ki senaon ke yahova ne mujhe tere pas bhej diya haai. aur yahova yahooda ko paavitra desh men apana bhag kar lega, aur yarooshalem ko fir apana ttharaaega..
he sab praanaiyon! yahova ke samhane chupake raho kyonki vah jagakar apane pavitra nivasasthan se nikala haai..
fir us ne yahoshoo mahayajak ko yahova ke doot ke samhane khda hua mujhe dikhaya, aur shautan usakee daahinee or usaka virodha karane ko khda tha.
tab yahova ne shautan se kaha, he shautan yahova tujh ko ghaudke! yahova jo yarooshalem ko apana leta haai, vahee tujhe ghaudke! kya yah ag se nikalee hui lukattee see naheen haai?
us samay yahoshoo to doot ke samhane maaila vasr paahine huae khda tha.
tab doot ne un se jo samhane khde the kaha, isake ye maaile vasr utaro. fir us ne us se kaha, dek, maain ne tera adharma door kiya haai, aur maain tujhe sundar vasr paahina deta hoon.
tab maain ne kaha, isake sir par aek shuuddh pagadee rakhee jaae. aur unhon ne usake sir par yajak ke yogy shuuddh pagadee rakhee, aur usako vasr pahinaae us samay yahova ka doot pas khda raha..
tab yahova ke doot ne yahoshoo ko chitakar kaha,
senaon ka yahova tujh se yon kahata haai: yadi too mere magorn par chale, aur jo kuchh maain ne tujhe saunp diya haai usakee raksha kare, to too mere bhvan ka nyayee, aur mere anganon ka rakshak hoga aur maain tujh ko inake beech men ane jane doonga jo pas khde haain.
he yaheashoo mahayajak, too sun le, aur tere bhaibandha jo tere samhane khde haain ve bhee sune, kyonki ve manushy shuubh shakun haain: suno, maain apane das shaakh ko pragatt karoonga.
