yahooda ne vishvasaghaat kiya haai, aur israael men aur yarooshalem men gharaanait kam kiya gaya haai kyonaki yahooda ne birane devata kee kanya se vivah karake yahova ke paavitra sthan ko jo usaka piry haai, apaavitra kiya haai.
jo puroosh aeesa kam kare, usake tambuon men se yakoob ka parameshvar usake ghar ke rakshak aur senaon ke yahova kee bhentt chaddhanevale ko yahooda se katt dalega!
fir tum ne yah doosara kam kiya haai ki tum ne yahova kee vedee ko ronevalon aur ahen bhranevalon ke ansuon se bhaigo diya haai, yahan tak ki vah tumharee bhentt kee or drashtti tak naheen karata, aur n prasann hokar usako tumhare hath se grahan karata haai. tum poochhte ho, aeesa kyon?
isaliye, kyonaki yahova tere aur teree us javanee kee sanaginee aur byahee hui sree ke beech sakshaee hua tha jis ka too ne vishvasaghaat kiya haai.
kya us ne aek hee ko naheen banaya jab ki aur atmaaen usake pas theen? or aek hee ko kyon banaya? isaaliye ki vah parameshvar ke yogy santan chahata haai. isaaliye tum apanee atma ke vishay men chaukas raho, aur tum men se koi apaneee javanee kee sree se vishvasaghaat n kare.
kyonaki israael ka parameshvar yahova yah kahata haai, ki maain sree-tyag se gharana karata hoo, aur us se bhee jo apane vasr ko upadrav se ddhanpata haai. isaliye tum apanee atma ke vishay men chaukas raho aur vishvasaghaat mat karo, senaon ke yahova ka yahee vachan haai..
tum logon ne apanee baton se yahova ko ukata diya haai. taubhee poochhte ho, ki ham ne kis bate men use ukata diya? is me, ki tum kahate ho ki jo koi bura karata haai, vah yahova kee draashtti men achchha lagata haai, aur vah aeese logon se prasann rahata haai, aur yah, ki nyayee parameshvar kahan haai?
dekho, maain apane doot ko bhejata hoo, aur vah marga ko mere age sudhaarega, aur prabhu, jise tum ddoonddhte ho, vah achanak apane maandair men a jaaega han vacha ka vah doot, jise tum chahate ho, suno, vah ata haai, senaon ke yahova ka yahee vachan haai.
vah roope ka tanevala aur shuuddh karanevala banega, aur leviyon ko shuuddh karega aur unako sone roope kee nain nirmal karega, tab ve yahova kee bhentt dharma se chaddhaaenge.
tab yahooda aur yarooshalem kee bhentt yahova ko aeesee bhaaegee, jaaisee paahile dinon men aur praacheenakal men bhavatee thee..
tab maain nyay karane ko tumhare nikatt aunga aur ttonho, aur vyaabhaichaariyo, aur joottee kiriya khanevalon ke viroodd, aur jo majadoor kee majadooree ko dabate, aur vidhava aur anathon par andhor karate, aur paradeshaee ka nyay bigadte, aur mera bhy naheen manate, un sabhon ke virooddh maain turant sakshaee doonga, senaon ke yahova ka yahee vachan haai..
apane purakhaon ke dinon se tum log meree vidhaiyon se hattte aae ho, or unaka palan naheen karate. tum meree or firo, tab maain bhee tumharee or firoonga, senaon ke yahova ka yahee vachan haai parantu tum poochhte ho, ham kis bat men firen?
kya manushy parameshvar ko dhaekha de sakata haai? dekho, tum mujh ko dhaekha dete ho, aur taubhee poochhte ho ki ham ne kis bat men tujhe lootta haai? dashamansh aur uttane kee bhentton men.
tum par bharee shaap pada haai, kyonki tum mujhe loottte ho varan saree jati aeesa karatee haai.
sare dashamansh bhndar men le ao ki mere bhvan men bhojanavastu rahe aur senaon ka yahova yah kahata haai, ki aeesa karake mujhe parakho ki maain akash ke jhrokhe tumhare liye kholakar tumhare upar aparampar ashaeesh kee vashara karata hoon ki naheen.
maain tumhare liye nash karanevale ko aeesa ghaudkoonga ki vah tumharee boomi kee upaj nash n karega, aur tumharee dakhlataon ke fal kachche n girenge, senaon ke yahova ka yahee vachan haai..
tab saree jatiyan tum ko dhany kahengee, kyonaki tumhara desh manohar desh hoga, senaon ke yahova ka yahee vachan haai..
yahova yah kahata haai, tum ne mere virooddh ddhttiai kee baten kahee haain. parantu tum poochhte ho, ham ne tere virooddh men kya kaha haai?
tum ne kaha haai ki parameshvar kee seva karanee vyarth haai. ham ne jo usake bataae huae kamon ko poora kiya aur senaon ke yahova ke dr ke mare shaek ka paahirava pahine huae chale haai, is se kya labh hua?
ab se ham aabhaimanee logon ko dhany kahate haain kyonki duracharee to safal ban gaae haai, varan ve parameshvar kee pareeksha karane par bhee bach gaae haain..
tab yahova ka bhy mananevalon ne apas men baten kee, aur yahova dhyan dhar kar unakee sunata tha aur jo yahova ka bhy manate aur usake nam ka samman karate the, unake smaran ke nimitt usake samhane aek pustak likhee jatee thee.
senaon ka yahova yah kahata haai, ki jo din maain ne ttharaya haai, us din ve log mere varan mere nij bhag ttharenge, aur maai un se aeesee komalata karoonga jaaisee koi apane seva karanevale putra se kare.
tab tum firakar dharmee aur dushtt ka bhed, arthata jo parameshvar kee seva karata haai, aur jo usakee seva naheen karata, un donon ko bhed pahichan sakoge..
kyonaki dekho, vah dhadhakate bhtthe ka sa din ata haai, jab sab abhaimanee aur sab duracharee log anaj kee koonttee ban jaaenge aur us anevale din men ve aeese bhsm ho jaaenge ki unaka pata tak n rahega, senaon ke yahova ka yahee vachan haai.
parantu tumhare liye jo mere nam ka bhy manate ho, dharma ka soorya uday hoga, aur usakee kiranon ke dara tum change ho jaoge aur tum nikalakar pale huae bachhdon kee nai koodoge aur faandoge.
tab tum dushtton ko latad daloge, arthatamere us ttharaae huae din men ve tumhare panvon ke neeche kee rakh ban jaaenge, senaon ke yahova ka yahee vachan haai..
mere das moosa kee vyavastha arthata jo jo vidhai aur niyam maain ne sare israaeliyon ke liye usako horeb men diae the, unako smaran rakho..
dekho, yahova ke us bade aur bhyanak din ke ane se paahile, maain tumhare pas aeliyyah nabee ko bhejoonga.
aur vah mata pita ke man ko unake putraen kee or, aur putraen ke man ko unake mata-pita kee or faerega aeesa n ho ki maain akar prathvee ko satyanash karoon..
mujh praacheen kee or se us piry gayus ke nam, jis se maain sachcha praem rakhta hoon..
he piry, meree yah praarthna haai ki jaaise too atmaik unnati kar raha haai, vaaise hee too sab baton me unnaati kare, aur bhla changa rahe.
kyonaki jab bhaiyon ne akar, tere us saty kee gavahee dee, jis par too sachamuch chalata haai, to maain bahut hee anandait hua.
mujhe is se baddhkar aur koi anand nahee, ki maain sunoo, ki mere ladke-bale saty par chalate haain.
he piry, jo kuchh too un bhaiyon ke sath karata haai, jo paradeshaee bhee haai, use vishvasee kee nai karata haai.
unhon ne mandlee ke samhane tere praem kee gavahee dee thee: yaadi too unhen us prakar vida karega jis prakar parameshvar ke logon ke liye uchit haai to achchha karega.
kyonaki ve us nam ke liye nikale haai, aur anyajaatiyon se kuchh naheen lete.
maain ne mandlee ko kuchh likha tha par diyuatraifaes jo un men bada banana chahata haai, hamen grahan naheen karata.
so jab maain aunga, to usake kamon kee jo vah kar raha haai suadhai dilaunga, ki vah hamare vishay men buree buree baten bakata haai aur is par bhee santosh n karake ap hee bhaiyon ko grahan naheen karata, aur unhen jo grahan karana chahate haai, mana karata haai: aur mandlee se nikal deta haai.
he piry, burai ke nahee, par bhlai ke anuyayee ho, jo bhlai karata haai, vah parameshvar kee or se haai par jo burai karata haai, us ne parameshvar ko naheen dekha.
demetraiyus ke vishay men sab ne baran saty ne bhee ap hee gavahee dee: aushra ham bhee gavahee dete haai, aur too janata haai, ki hamaree gavahee sachcha haai..
par mujhe asha haai ki tujh se shaeegha bhentt karoonga: tab ham amhane samhane batacheet karenge: tujhe shaaantai milatee rahe. yahan ke mitra tujhe namaskar karate haain: vahan ke mitraen ke nam le lekar namaskar kah dena..
fir us ne apane barah chelon ko pas bulakar, unhen ashuuddh atmaon par adhaikar diya, ki unhen nikalen aur sab prakar kee beemariyon aur sab prakar kee durbalataon ko door karen..
aur barah praeariton ke nam ye haain: paahila shamaun, jo pataras kahalata haai, aur usaka bhai andairyasa jabdee ka putra yakoob, aur usaka bhai yoohanna
firaalippus aur bara-tulmaai thoma aur mahasool lenevala mattee, halafaai ka putra yakoob aur taai.
shamaun kananee, aur yahooda iskaariyotee, jis ne use pakadva bhee diya..
in barahon ko yeeshu ne yah agyaa dekar bheja ki anyajaatiyon kee or n jana, aur samariyon ke kisee nagar men pravesh n karana.
parantu israael ke gharane hee kee khoi hui bhedon ke pas jana.
aur chalate chalate prachar kar kaho ki svarga ka rajy nikatt a gaya haai.
beemaron ko changa karo: mare huon ko jilao: koddhiyon ko shuuddh karo: dushttatmaon ko nikalo: tum ne sentament paya haai, sentament do.
apane pattukon men n to sona, aur n roopa, aur n tanba rakhna.
marga ke liye n jholee rakho, n do kurate, n joote aur n lattee lo, kyonki majadoor ko usaka bhojan milana chahiae.
jis kisee nagar ya ganv men jao to pata lagao ki vahan kaun yogy haai? aur jab tak vahan se n nikalo, usee ke yahan raho.
aur ghar men pravesh karate huae us ko ashaeesh dena.
yaadi us ghar ke log yogy honge to tumhara kalyan un par pahunchega parantu yaadi ve yogay n hon to tumhara kalyan tumhare pas lautt aaega.
aur jo koi tumhen grahan n kare, aur tumharee baten n sune, us ghar ya us nagar se nikalate huae apane panvon kee dhool jhad dalo.
maain tum se sach kahata hoo, ki nyay ke din us nagar kee dasha se sadom aur amora ke desh kee dasha aadhaik sahane yogy hogee..
dekho, maain tumhen bhedon kee nai bhediyon ke beech men bhejata hoon so sanpon kee nai buaddhmaian aur kabootaron kee nai bhole bano.
parantu logon se savadhaan raho, kyonaki ve tumhen mahasabhaon men saupenge, aur apanee panchayat men tumhen kode marenge.
tum mere liye haakimon or rajaon ke samhane un par, aur anyajatiyon par gavah hone ke liye pahunchaae jaoge.
jab ve tumhen pakadvaaenge to yah chinta n karata, ki ham kis reeti se ya kya kahenge: kyonki jo kuchh tum ko kahana hoga, vah usee ghadee tumhen bata diya jaaega.
kyonaki bolanevale tum naheen ho parantu tumhare pita ka atma tum men bolata haai.
bhai, bhai ko aur pita putra ko, ghaat ke liye saunpenge, aur ladkebale mata-apita ke virodha men uttkar unhen marava dalenge.
mere nam ke karan sab log tum se baair karenge, par jo ant tak dhaeeraj dhare rahega usee ka uddhar hoga.
jab ve tumhen aek nagar men sataae, to doosare ko bhag jana. maain tum se sach kahata hoo, tum israael ke sab nagaron men n fir chukoge ki manushy ka putra a jaaega..
chele ka guroo ke, aur das ka svamee ke barabar hona hee bahut haai jab unhon ne ghar ke svamee ko shautan kaha to usake gharavalon ko kyon n kahenge?
so un se mat drana, kyonaki kuchh ddhpa nahee, jo khola n jaaega aur n kuchh chhpai haai, jo jana n jaaega.
jo maain tum se andhiayare me kahata hoo, use ujiyale men kaho aur jo kanon kan sunate ho, use kotton par se prachar karo.
jo shareer ko ghaat karate haai, par atma ko ghaat naheen kar sakate, un se mat drana par usee se dro, jo atma aur shareer donon ko narak men nash kar sakata haai.
kya paaise me do gauraaiye naheen bikatee? taubhee tumhare pita kee ichchha ke bina un men se aek bhee boomi par naheen gir sakatee.
isaliye, dro naheen tum bahut gauraaiyon se baddhkar ho.
jo koi manushyon ke samhane mujhe man lega, use maain bhee svargeey pita ke samhane man loonga.
par jo koi manushyon ke samhane mera inkar karega us se maain bhee apane svargeey pita ke samhane inkar karoonga.
yah n samajho, ki maain prathvee par milap karane ko aya hoon maain milap karane ko nahee, par talavar chalavane aya hoon.
maain to aya hoo, ki manushy ko usak pita se, aur bettee ko us kee man se, aur bahoo ko us kee sas se alag kar doon.
manushy ke baairee usak ghar hee ke log honge.
jo mata ya pita ko mujh se aadhaik piry janata haai, vah mere yogy naheen aur jo betta ya bettee ko mujh se aadhaik piry janata haai, vah mere yogy naheen.
aur jo apana kroos lekar mere peechhe n chale vah mere yogy naheen.
jo apane praan bachata haai, vah use khoaega aur jo mere karan apana praan khota haai, vah use paaega.
jo tumhen grahan karata haai, vah mujhe grahan karata haai aur jo mujhe grahan karata haai, vah mere bhejanevale ko grahan karata haai.
jo bhavishyadvkta ko bhavishyadvkta janakar grahan kare, vah bhavishyadvkta ka badala paaega aur jo dharmee janakar dharmee ko grahan kare, vah dharmee ka badala paaega.
jo koi in chhotton men se aek ko chela janakar keval aek kattora ttnda panee pilaa, maain tum se sach kahata hoo, vah kisee reeati se apana pratifal n khoaega..
jab yeeshu apane barah chelon ko agyaa de chuka, to vah un ke nagaron men upadesh aur prachar karane ko vahan se chala gaya..
yoohanna ne bandeegrah men maseeh ke kamon ka samachar sunakar apane chelon ko us se yah poochhne bheja.
ki kya anevala too hee haai: ya ham doosare kee batt johen?
yeeshu ne uttr diya, ki jo kuchh tum sunate ho aur dekhte ho, vah sab jakar yoohanna se kah do.
ki andho dekhte haain aur langade chalate firate haain koddhee shuuddh kiae jate haain aur bahire sunate haai, murde jilaae jate haain aur kangalon ko susamachar sunaya jata haai.
aur dhany haai vah, jo mere karan ttokar n khaae.
jab ve vahan se chal dia, to yeeshu yoohanna ke vishay men logon se kahane laga tum jangal men kya dekhte gaae the? kya hava se hilate huae sarakande ko?
fir tum kya dekhne gaae the? dekho, jo komal vasr pahinate haai, ve rajabhvanon men rahate haain.
to fir kyon gaae the? kya kisee bhavishyadvkta ko dekhne ko? han maain tum se kahata hoo, baran bhavishyadvkta se bhee bade ko.
yah vahee haai, jis ke vishay men likha haai, ki dekh maain apane doot ko tere age bhejata hoo, jo tere age tera marga taaiyar karega.
maain tum se sach kahata hoo, ki jo striayon se janme haai, un men se yoohanna bapatisma denevalon se koi bada naheen hua par jo svarga ke rajy men chhotte se chhotta haai vah us se bada haai.
yoohanna tak sare bhavishyadvkta aur vyavastha bhavishyadvvanee karate rahe.
aur chaho to mano, aeliyyah jo anevala tha, vah yahee haai.
jis ke sunane ke kan ho, vah sun le.
maain is samay ke logon kee upama kis se doon? ve un balakon ke saman haai, jo bajaron men baaitte huae aek doosare se pukarakar kahate haain.
ki ham ne tumhare liye bansalee bajai, aur tum n nache ham ne vilap kiya, aur tum ne chhatee naheen peettee.
kyonaki yoohanna n khata aya aur n peeta, aur ve kahate haain ki us men dushttatma haai.
tab vah un nagaron ko ulahana dene laga, jin men us ne bahutere samarth ke kam kiae the kyonki unhon ne apana man naheen firaya tha.
hay, khurajeena hay, baaitasaaida jo samarth ke kam tum men kiae gaa, yaadi ve soor aur saaida men kiae jate, to ttatt oddhkar, aur rakh men baaittkar, ve kab se man fira lete.
parantu maain tum se kahata hoon ki nyay ke din tumharee dasha se soor aur saaida kee dasha adhaik sahane yogy hogee.
aur he kafaranahoom, kya too svarga tak uncha kiya jaaega? too to adhaelok tak neeche jaaega jo samarth ke kam tujh men kiae gaae haai, yaadi sadom men kiae jate, to vah aj tak bana rahata.
par maain tum se kahata hoo, ki nyay ke din teree dasha se sadom ke desh kee dasha aadhaik sahane yogy hogee.
usee samay yeeshu ne kaha, he pita, svarga aur prathvee ke prabhu maain tera dhanyavad karata hoo, ki too ne in baton ko gyaaaniyon aur samajhdaron se chhpai dakha, aur balakon par pragatt kiya haai.
ha, he pita, kyonaki tujhe yahee achchha laga.
mere pita ne mujhe sab kuchh saunpa haai, aur koi putra ko naheen janata, keval pita aur koi pita ko naheen janata, keval putra aur vah jis par putra use pragatt karana chahe.
he sab paarishram karanevalon aur bojh se dabe logo, mere pas ao maain tumhen vishraam doonga.
mera jooa apane upar utta lo aur mujh se seekho kyonaki maain namra aur man men dee hoon: aur tum apane man men vishraam paoge.
kyonaki mera jooa sahaj aur mera bojh halka haai..
us samay yeeshu sabt ke din kheton men se hokar ja raha tha, aur usake chelon ko bookh lagee, so ve balen tod todkar khane lage.
fareesiyon ne yah dekhkar us se kaha, dekh tere chele vah kam kar rahe haai, jo sabt ke din karana uchit naheen.
us ne un se kaha kya tum ne naheen paddha, ki daud ne, jab vah aur usake sathee bookhe huae to kya kiya?
vah kyonkar parameshvar ke ghar men gaya, aur bhentt kee rottyaian khai, jinhen khana n to use aur usake saathaiyon ko, par keval yajakon ko uchit tha?
ya tum ne vyavastha men naheen paddha, ki yajak sabt ke din mandair men sabt ke din ke vidhai ko todne par bhee nirdosh ttharate haain.
par maain tum se kahata hoo, ki yahan vah haai, jo mandair se bhee bada haai.
yaadi tum is ka arth janate ki maain daya se prasann hoo, balidan se nahee, to tum nirdosh ko doshaee n ttharate.
manushy ka putra to sabt ke din ka bhee prabhu haai..
vahan se chalakar vah un kee sabha ke ghar men aya.
aur dekho, aek manushy tha, jis ka hath sookha hua tha aur unhon ne us par dosh lagane ke liey us se poochha, ki kya sabt ke din changa karana uchit haai?
us ne un se kaha tum men aeesa kaun haai, jis kee ek bhed ho, aur vah sabt ke din gadhe men gir jaa, to vah use pakadkar n nikale?
us ne baddhaya, aur vah fir doosare hath kee nai achchha ho gaya.
tab fareesiyon ne bahar jakar usake virodha men sammati kee, ki use kis prakar nash karen?
yah janakar yeeshu vahan se chala gaya aur bahut lage usake peechhe ho liye aur us ne sab ko changa kiya.
aur unhen chitaya, ki mujhe pragatt n karana.
ki jo vachan yashaayah bhvishyadvkta ke dara kaha gaya tha, vah poora ho.
ki dekho, yah mera sevak haai, jise maain ne chuna haai mera piry, jis se mera man prasann haai: maain apana atma us par daloonga aur vah anyajaatiyon ko nyay ka samachar dega.
vah n jhgada karega, aur n dhoom machaaega aur n bajaron men koi usaka shabd sunega.
aur anyajatiyan usake nam par asha rakhengee.
tab log aek andho-goonge ko jis men dushttatma thee, usake pas laae aur us ne use achchha kiya aur vah goonga bolane aur dekhne laga.
is par sab log chaakit hokar kahane lage, yah kya daud kee santan ka haai?
parantu fareeasiyon ne yah sunakar kaha, yah to dushttatmaon ke saradar shautan kee sahayata ke bina dushttatmaon ko naheen nikalata.
us ne un ke man kee bat janakar un se kaha jis kisee rajy men foott hotee haai, vah ujad jata haai, aur koi nagar ya gharana jis men foott hotee haai, bana n rahega.
aur yaadi shautan hee shautan ko nikale, to vah apana hee virodhaee ho gaya haai fir usaka rajy kyonkar bana rahega?
bhla, yadi maain shautan kee sahayata se dushttatmaon ko nikalata hoo, to tumhare vansh kis kee sahayata se nikalate haain? isaliye ve hee tumhara nyay chukaaenge.
par yaadi maain parameshvar ke atma kee sahayata se dushttatmaon ko nikalata hoo, to parameshvar ka rajy tumhare pas a pahuncha haai.
ya kyonkar koi manushy kisee balavant ke ghar men ghausakar usaka mal loott sakata haai jab tak ki pahile us balavant ko n bandha le? aur tab vah usaka ghar loott lega.
jo mere sath nahee, vah mere virodha men haai aur jo mere sath naheen battorata, vah bithrata haai.
isaliye maain tum se kahata hoo, ki manushy ka sab prakar ka pap aur ninda kshama kee jaaegee, par atma kee ninda kshama n kee jaaegee.
jo koi manushy ke putra ke virodha men koi bat kahega, usaka yah aparadha kshama kiya jaaega, parantu jo koi pavitraatma ke virodha men kuchh kahega, usaka aparadha n to is lok men aur n paralok men kshama kiya jaaega.
yaadi ped ko achchha kaho, to usake fal ko bhee achchha kaho ya ped ko nikamma kaho kyonki ped fal hee se pahachana jata haai.
he sanp ke bachcho, tum bure hokar kyonkar achchhee baten kah sakate ho? kyonki jo man men bhra haai, vahee munh par ata haai.
bhla, manushy man ke bhle bhndar se bhlee baten nikalata haai aur bura manushy bure bhndar se buree baten nikalata haai.
aur maai tum se kahata hoo, ki jo jo nikammee baten manushy kahenge, nyay ke din har aek bat ka lekha denge.
kyonaki too apanee baton ke karan nirdosh aur apanee baton hee ke karan doshaee ttharaya jaaega..
is par kitane shaaastriayon aur fareeasiyon ne us se kaha, he guro, ham tujh se aek chinh dekhna chahate haain.
us ne unhen uttr diya, ki is yug ke bure aur vyabhaicharee log chinh ddoonddhte haain parantu yoonus bhvishyadvkta ke chinh ko chhod koi aur chinh un ko n diya jaega.
yoonus teen raj din jal jantu ke pett men raha, vaaise hee manushy ka putra teen rat din prathvee ke bheetar rahega.
neenave ke log nyay ke din is yug ke logon ke sath uttkar unhen doshaee ttharaaenge, kyonki unhon ne yoonus ka prachar sunakar, man firaya aur dekho, yahan vah haai jo yoonus se bada haai.
jab ashuuddh atma manushy men se nikal jatee haai, to sookhee jagahon men vishraam ddoonddhtee firatee haai, aur patee naheen.
tab kahatee haai, ki maain apane usee ghar men jahan se nikalee thee, lautt jaungee, aur akar use soona, jhada-buhara aur saja sajaya patee haai.
tab vah jakar apane se aur buree sat atmaon ko apane sath le atee haai, aur ve us men paaittkar vahan vas karatee haai, aur us manushy kee pichhlee dasha paahile se bhee buree ho jatee haai is yug ke bure logon kee dasha bhee aeesee hee hogee.
jab vah bheed se baten kar hee raha tha, to dekho, us kee mata aur bhai bahar khde the, aur us se baten karana chahate the.
kisee ne us se kaha dekh teree mata aur tere bhai bahar khde haai, aur tujh se baten karana chahate haain.
yah sun us ne kahanevale ko uttr diya kaun haai meree mata?
aur kaun haai mere bhai? aur apane chelon kee or apana hath baddha kar kaha dekho, meree mata aur mere bhai ye haain.
kyonaki jo koi mere svargeey pita kee ichchha par chale, vahee mera bhai aur baahin aur mata haai..
aur usake pas aeesee badee bheed ikatthee hui ki vah nav par chaddh gaya, aur saree bheed kinare par khdee rahee.
aur us ne un se drashttanton men bahut see baten kahee, ki dekho, aek bonevala beej bone nikala.
bote samay kuchh beej marga ke kinare gire aur paakshiayon ne akar unhen chug liya.
kuchh patthreelee boomi par gire, jahan unhen bahut mittee n milee aur gaharee mittee n milane ke karan ve jald ug aae.
par sooraj nikalane par ve jal gaa, aur jad n pakadne se sookh gaae.
kuchh jhaadiyon men gire, aur jhaadiyon ne baddhkar unhen daba dala.
par kuchh achchhee boomi par gire, aur fal laa, koi sau guna, koi satt guna, koi tees guna.
jis ke kan hon vah sun le..
aur chelon ne pas akar us se kaha, too un se drashttanton men kyon baten karata haai?
us ne uttr diya, ki tum ko svarga ke rajy ke bhedon kee samajh dee gai haai, par un ko naheen.
kyonaki jis ke pas haai, use diya jaaega aur usake pas bahut ho jaaega par jis ke pas kuchh naheen haai, us se jo kuchh usake pas haai, vah bhee le liya jaaega.
maain un se drashttanton men isaaliye baten karata hoo, ki ve dekhte huae naheen dekhte aur sunate huae naheen sunate aur naheen samajhte.
aur un ke vishay men yashaayah kee yah bhvishyadvvanee pooree hotee haai, ki tum kanon se to sunoge, par samajhoge naheen aur ankhon se to dekhoge, par tumhen n soojhega.
kyonaki in logon ka man motta ho gaya haai, aur ve kanon se uncha sunate haain aur unhon ne apanee ankhen moond leen haain kaheen aeesa n ho ki ve ankhon se dekhe, aur kanon se sunen aur man se samajhe, aur fir jaae, aur maain unhen changa karoon.
par dhany haai tumharee ankhe, ki ve dekhtee haain aur tumhare kan, ki ve sunate haain.
kyonaki maain tum se sach kahata hoo, ki bahut se bhavishyadvktaon ne aur dharmiyon ne chaha ki jo baten tum dekhte ho, dekhen par n dekheen aur jo baten tum sunate ho, sune, par n suneen.
so tum banevale ka drashttant suno.
jo koi rajy ka vachan sunakar naheen samajhta, usake man men jo kuchh boya gaya tha, use vah dushtt akar chheen le jata haai yah vahee haai, jo marga ke kinare boya gaya tha.
aur jo patthreelee boomi par boya gaya, yah vah haai, jo vachan sunakar turant anand ke sath man leta haai.
par apane men jad n rakhne ke karan vah thode hee din ka haai, aur jab vachan ke karan klesh ya upadrav hota haai, to turant ttokar khata haai.
jo achchhee boomi men boya gaya, yah vah haai, jo vachan ko sunakar samajhta haai, aur fal lata haai koi sau guna, koi satt guna, koi tees guna.
us ne unhen ek aur drashttant diya ki svarga ka rajy us manushy ke saman haai jis ne apane khet men achchha beej boya.
par jab log so rahe the to usaka baairee akar gehoon ke beech jangalee beej bokar chala gaya.
jab ankur nikale aur balen lagee, to jangalee dane bhee dikhai diae.
is par grahasth ke dason ne akar us se kaha, he svamee, kya too ne apane khet men achchha beej n boya tha? fir jangatee dane ke paudho us men kahan se aae?
