us ne kaha, aeesa nahee, n ho ki jangatee dane ke paudho battorate huae un ke sath gehoon bhee ukhad lo.
kattnee tak donon ko aek sath baddhne do, aur kattnee ke samay maain kattnevalon se kahoonga paahile jangalee dane ke paudho battorakar jalane ke liye un ke gatthe bandha lo, aur gehoon ko mere khtte men ikattha karo..
us ne unhen ek aur drashttant diya ki svarga ka rajy rai ke ek dane ke saman haai, jise kisee manushy ne lekar apane khet men bo diya.
us ne ek aur drashttant unhen sunaya ki svarga ka rajy khmeer ke saman haai jis ko kisee sree ne lekar teen paseree atte men mila diya aur hote hote vah sab khmeer ho gaya..
ye sab baten yeeshu ne drashttanton men logon se kahee, aur bina drashttant vah un se kuchh n kahata tha.
ki jo vachan bhavishyadvkta ke dara kaha gaya tha, vah poora ho ki maain drashttant kahane ko apana munh kholoonga: maain un baton ko jo jagat kee utpati se gupt rahee haain pragatt karoonga..
tab vah bheed ko chhodkar ghar men aya, aur usake chelon ne usake pas akar kaha, khet ke jangalee dane ka drashttant hamen samajha de.
us ne un ko uttr diya, ki achchhe beej ka bonevala manushy ka putra haai.
khet sansar haai, achchha beej rajy ke santan, aur jangalee beej dushtt ke santan haain.
jis baairee ne un ko boya vah shautan haai kattnee jagat ka ant haai: aur kattnevale svargadoot haain.
so jaaise jangalee dane battore jate aur jalaae jate haain vaaisa hee jagat ke ant men hoga.
manushy ka putra apane svargadooton ko bhejega, aur ve usake rajy men se sab ttokar ke karanon ko aur kukarma karanevalon ko ikattha karenge.
aur unhen ag ke kund men dalenge, vahan rona aur dant peesana hoga.
us samay dharmee apane pita ke rajy men soorya kee nai chamakenge jis ke kan hon vah sun le..
svarga ka rajy khet men chhpai huae dhan ke saman haai, jise kisee manushy ne pakar chhpai diya, aur mare anand ke jakar aur apana sab kuchh bechakar us khet ko mol liya..
fir svarga ka rajy aek vyoparee ke saman haai jo achchhe motiyon kee khoj men tha.
jab use aek bahumooly motee mila to us ne jakar apana sab kuchh bech dala aur use mol le liya..
fir svarga ka rajy us bade jal ke saman haai, jo samudra men dala gaya, aur har prakar kee machhaliyon ko samett laya.
aur jab bhr gaya, to us ko kinare par kheench laa, aur baaittkar achchhee achchhee to baratanon men ikattha kiya aur nikammee, nikammeen faenk dee.
jagat ke ant men aeesa hee hoga: svargadoot akar dushtton ko dharmiyon se alag karenge, aur unhen ag ke kund men dalenge.
vahan rona aur dant peesana hoga.
kya tum ne ye sab baten samajheen?
jab yeeshu ne sab drashttant kah chuka, to vahan se chala gaya.
aur apane desh men akar un kee sabha men unhen aeesa upadesh dene laga ki ve chakit hokar kahane lage ki is ko yah gyaan aur samarth ke kam kahan se mile?
kya yah baddhi ka betta naheen? aur kya is kee mata ka nam mariyam aur is ke bhaiyon ke nam yakoob aur yoosufa aur shamaun aur yahooda naheen?
aur kya is kee sab bahinen hamare beech men naheen rahatee? fir is ko yah sab kahan se mila?
so unhon ne usake karan ttokar khai, par yeeshu ne un se kaha, bhvishyadvkta apane desh aur apane ghar ko chhod aur kaheen niradar naheen hota.
aur us ne vahan un ke avishvas ke karan bahut samarth ke kam naheen kiae..
us samay chauthai desh ke raja herodes ne yeeshu kee charcha sunee.
aur apane sevakon se kaha, yah yoohanna bapatisma denevala haai: vah mare huon men se jee utta haai, isee liye us se samarth ke kam pragatt hote haain.
kyonaki herodes ne apane bhai filippus kee patnee herodiyas ke kara, yoohanna ko pakadkar bandha, aur jelakhane men dal diya tha.
kyonaki yoohanna ne us se kaha tha, ki is ko rakhna tujhe uchit naheen haai.
par jab herodes ka janm din aya, to herodiyas kee bettee ne utsav men nach dikhakar herodes ko khush kiya.
isaliye us ne shapath khakar vachan diya, ki jo kuchh too mangegee, maain tujhe doonga.
vah apanee mata kee uskai hui bolee, yoohanna bapaatisma denevale ka sir thal men yaheen mujhe mangava de.
raja dukhait hua, par apanee shapath ke, aur sath baaittnevalon ke kara, agyaa dee, ki de diya jaae.
aur jelakhane men logon ko bhejakar yoohanna ka sir kattva diya.
aur usaka sir thal men laya gaya, aur ladkee ko diya gaya aur vah us ko apanee man ke pas le gai.
aur usake chelon ne akar aur us kee loth ko le jakar gaddh diya aur jakar yeeshu ko samachar diya..
jab yeeshu ne yah suna, to nav par chaddhkar vahan se kisee sunasan jagah aekant men chala gaya aur log yah sunakar nagar nagar se paaidal usake peechhe ho liae.
us ne nikalakar badee bheed dekhee aur un par taras khaya aur us ne un ke beemaron ko changa kiya.
jab sanjh hui, to usake chelon ne usake pas akar kaha yah to sunasan jagah haai aur der ho rahee haai, logon ko vida kiya jaae ki ve bastaiyon men jakar apane liye bhojan mol len.
yeeshu ne un se kaha un ka jana avashyak naheen! tum hee inhen khane ko do.
unhon ne us se kaha yahan hamare pas panch rottee aur do machhliyon ko chhod aur kuchh naheen haai.
us ne kaha, un ko yahan mere pas le ao.
tab us ne logon ko ghaas par baaittne ko kaha, aur un panch rottyaien aur do machhliyon ko liya aur svarga kee or dekhkar dhanyavad kiya aur rottyaian tod todkar chelon ko dee, aur chelon ne logon ko.
aur sab khakar trapt ho gaa, aur unhon ne bache huae ttukadon se bhree hui barah ttokaariyan uttai.
aur khanevale striayon aur balakon ko chhodkar panch hajar purooshaen ke attkal the..
aur us ne turant apane chelon ko barabas nav par chaddhaya, ki ve us se pahile par chale jaae, jab tak ki vah logon ko vida kare.
