aur vah rat ke chauthe pahar jheel par chalate huae un ke pas aya.
chele us ko jheel par chalate huae dekhkar ghabara gaae! aur kahane lage, vah boot haai aur dar ke mare chilla utte.
yeeshu ne turant un se baten kee, aur kaha ddhaddhs bandhae maain hoon dro mata.
pataras ne us ko uttr diya, he prabhu, yadi too hee haai, to mujhe apane pas panee par chalakar ane kee agyaa de.
us ne kaha, a: tab pataras nav par se utarakar yeeshu ke pas jane ko panee par chalane laga.
par hava ko dekhkar dr gaya, aur jab oobane laga, to chillakar kaha he prabhu, mujhe bacha.
yeeshu ne turant hath baddhakar use tham liya, aur us se kaha, he alpa-avishvasee, too ne kyon sandeh kiya?
jab ve nav par chaddh gaa, to hava thm gai.
is par jo nav par the, unhon ne use dandvat karake kaha sachamuch too parameshvar ka putra haai..
ve par utarakar gannesarat desh men pahunche.
aur vahan ke logon ne use pahachanakar as pas ke sare desh men kahala bheja, aur sab beemaron ko usake pas laae.
tab yarooshalem se kitane fareesee aur shaasree yeeshu ke pas akar kahane lage.
tere chele puraniyon kee reeton ko kyon ttalate haai, ki bina hath dhaeae rottee khate haain?
us ne un ko uttr diya, ki tum bhee apanee reeton ke karan kyon parameshvar kee agyaa ttalate ho?
kyonaki parameshvar ne kaha tha, ki apane pita aur apanee mata ka adar karana: aur jo koi pita ya mata ko bura kahe, vah mar dala jaae.
par tum kahate ho, ki yadi koi apane pita ya mata se kahe, ki jo kuchh tujhe mujh se labh pahunch sakata tha, vah parameshvar ko bhentt chaddhai ja chukee.
to vah apane pita ka adar n kare, so tum ne apanee reeton ke karan parameshvar ka vachan ttal diya.
he kapattyaie, yashaayah ne tumhare vishay men yah bhavishyadanee tteek kee.
ki ye log hotton se to mera adar karate haai, par un ka man mujh se door rahata haai.
aur ye vyarth meree upasana karate haai, kyonki manushy kee vidhaiyon ko dhamorpadesh karake sikhate haain.
aur us ne logon ko apane pas bulakar un se kaha, suno aur samajho.
