un ko jane do ve andho marga dikhanevale haain: aur andha yadi andho ko marga dikhaa, to donon gadhe men gir padenge.
yah sunakar, pataras ne us se kaha, yah drashttant hamen samajha de.
us ne kaha, kya tum bhee ab tak na samajh ho?
kya naheen samajhte, ki jo kuchh munh men jata, vah pett men padta haai, aur sandas men nikal jata haai?
kyonaki kuchinta, hatya, parasreegaman, vyaabhaichar, choree, joottee gavahee aur ninda man hee se nikalatee haai.
