tab chelon ne aekant men yeeshu ke pas akar kaha ham ise kyon naheen nikal sake?
us ne un se kaha, apane vishvas kee ghattee ke karan: kyonaki maain tum se sach kahata hoo, yadi tumhara vishvas rai ke dane ke barabar bhee ho, to is pahad se kah sakoge, ki yahan se sarakakar vahan chala ja, to vah chala jaega aur koi bat tumhare liye anhonee n hogee.
jab ve galeel men the, to yeeshu ne un se kaha manushy ka putra manushyon ke hath men pakadvaya jaaega.
aur ve use mar dalenge, aur vah teesare din jee uttega.
is par ve bahut udas huae..
jab ve kafaranahoom men pahunche, to maandair ke liye kar lenevalon ne pataras ke pas akar poochha, ki kya tumhara guroo mandair ka kar naheen deta? us ne kaha, han deta to haai.
jab vah ghar men aya, to yeeshu ne usake poochhne se pahile us se kaha, he shamaun too kya samajhta haai? prathvee ke raja mahasool ya kar kin se lete haain? apane putraen se ya parayon se? pataras ne un se kaha, parayon se.
taubhee isaaliye ki ham unhen ttokar n khailaae, too jheel ke kinare jakar bansee dal, aur jo machhlee pahile nikale, use le to tujhe usaka munh kholane par aek sikka milega, usee ko lekar mere aur apane badale unhen de dena..
usee ghadee chele yeeshu ke pas akar poochhne lage, ki svarga ke rajy men bada kaun haai?
is par us ne aek balak ko pas bulakar un ke beech men khda kiya.
aur kaha, maain tum se sach kahata hoo, yadi tum n firo aur balakon ke saman n bano, to svarga ke rajy men pravesh karane naheen paoge.
jo koi apane ap ko is balak ke saman chhotta karega, vah svarga ke rajy men bada hoga.
aur jo koi mere nam se aek aeese balak ko grahan karata haai vah mujhe grahan karata haai.
par jo koi in chhotton men se jo mujh par vishvas karate haain aek ko ttokar khailaa, usake liye bhla hota, ki badee chakkee ka patt usake gale men lattkaya jata, aur vah gaahire samudra men dubaya jata.
ttokaron ke karan sansar par haya! ttokaron ka lagana avashy haai par hay us manushy par jis ke dara ttokar lagatee haai.
yaadi tera hath ya tera panv tujhe ttokar khailaa, to kattkar faenk de ttunda ya langada hokar jeevan men pravesh karana tere liye is se bhla haai, ki do hath ya do panv rahate huae too anant ag men dala jaae.
aur yaadi teree ankh tujhe ttokar khailaa, to use nikalakar faenk de.
kana hokar jeevan men pravesh karana tere liye is se bhla haai, ki do ankh rahate huae too narak kee ag men dala jaae.
dekho, tum in chhotton men se kisee ko tuchchh n janana kyonaki maain tum se kahata hoo, ki svarga men un ke doot mere svargeey pita ka munh sada dekhte haain.
tum kya samajhte ho? yaadi kisee manushy kee sau bheden ho, aur un men se aek bhttk jaa, to kya ninnanave ko chhodkar, aur pahadon par jakar, us bhttkee hui ko n ddoonddhega?
aur yaadi aeesa ho ki use paa, to maain tum se sach kahata hoo, ki vah un ninnanave bhedon ke liye jo bhttkee naheen theen itana anand naheen karega, jitana ki is bhed ke liye karega.
yaadi tera bhai tera aparadha kare, to ja aur akele men batacheet karake use samajha yadi vah teree sune to too ne apane bhai ko pa liya.
aur yaadi vah n sune, to aur aek do jan ko apane sath le ja, ki har aek bat do ya teen gavahon ke munh se ttharai jaae.
yaadi vah un kee bhee n mane, to kaleeasiya se kah de, parantu yadi vah kaleeasiya kee bhee n mane, to too use anyajaati aur mahasool lenevale ke aeesa jana.
maain tum se sach kahata hoo, jo kuchh tum prathvee par bandhaege, vah svarga par bandhoga aur jo kuchh tum prathvee par khologe, vah svarga par khulega.
fir maain tum se kahata hoo, yadi tum men se do jan prathvee par kisee bat ke liye jise ve mange, aek man ke ho, to vah mere pita kee or se svarga men haai un ke liye ho jaaegee.
kyonaki jahan do ya teen mere nam par ikatthe hote haain vahan maain un ke beech men hota hoon..
tab pataras ne pas akar, us se kaha, he prabhu, yaadi mera bhai aparadha karata rahe, to maain kitanee bar use kshama karoo, kya sat bar taka?
yeeshu ne us se kaha, maain tujh se yah naheen kahata, ki sat bar, baran sat bar ke sattr gune taka.
isaliye svarga ka rajy us raja ke saman haai, jis ne apane dason se lekha lena chaha.
jab vah lekha lene laga, to aek jan usake samhane laya gaya jo das hajar tode dhaarata tha.
jab ki chukane ko usake pas kuchh n tha, to usake svamee ne kaha, ki yah aur is kee patnee aur ladkebale aur jo kuchh is ka haai sab becha jaa, aur vah karja chuka diya jaae.
is par us das ne girakar use pranam kiya, aur kaha he svamee, dhaeeraj dhar, maain sab kuchh bhr doonga.
tab us das ke svamee ne taras khakar use chhod diya, aur usaka dhaar kshama kiya.
parantu jab vah das bahar nikala, to usake sangee dason men se aek us ko mila, jo usake sau deenar dhaarata tha us ne use pakadkar usaka gala ghaentta, aur kaha jo kuchh too dhaarata haai bhr de.
is par usaka sangee das girakar, us se binatee karane laga ki dhaeeraj dhar maain sab bhr doonga.
usake sangee das yah jo hua tha dekhkar bahut udas hua, aur jakar apane svamee ko poora hal bata diya.
tab usake svamee ne us ko bulakar us se kaha, he dushtt das, too ne jo mujh se binatee kee, to maain ne to tera vah poora karja kshama kiya.
so jaaisa maain ne tujh par daya kee, vaaise hee kya tujhe bhee apane sangee das par daya karana naheen chaahiae tha?
aur usake svamee ne krodha men akar use dand denevalon ke hath men saunp diya, ki jab tak vah sab karja bhr n de, tab tak un ke hath men rahe.
isee prakar yaadi tum men se har aek apane bhai ko man se kshama n karega, to mera pita jo svarga men haai, tum se bhee vaaisa hee karega..
jab yeeshu ye baten kah chuka, to galeel se chala gaya aur yahoodiya ke desh men yaradan ke par aya.
aur badee bheed usake peechhe ho lee, aur us ne unhen vahan changa kiya..
tab fareesee us kee pareeksha karane ke liye pas akar kahane lage, kya har aek karan se apanee patnee ko tyagana uchit haai?
us ne uttr diya, kya tum ne naheen paddha, ki jis ne unhen banaya, us ne arambh se nar aur naree banakar kaha.
ki is karan manushy apane mata pita se alag hokar apanee patnee ke sath rahega aur ve donon aek tan honge?
so v ab do nahee, parantu aek tan haain: isaliye jise parameshvar ne joda haai, use manushy alag n kare.
unhon ne us se kaha, fir moosa ne kyon yah ttharaya, ki tyagapatra dekar use chhod de?
us ne un se kaha, moosa ne tumhare man kee kattorata ke karan tumhen apanee patnee ko chhod dene kee agyaa dee, parantu arambh men aeesa naheen tha.
chelon ne us se kaha, yaadi puroosh ka sree ke sath aeesa sambandha haai, to byah karana achchha naheen.
us ne un se kaha, sab yah vachan grahan naheen kar sakate, keval ve jin ko yah dan diya gaya haai.
kyonaki kuchh napunsak aeese haain jo mata ke garbh hee se aeese janmen aur kuchh nanpusak aeese haai, jinhen manushy ne napunsak banaya: aur kuchh napunsak aese haai, jinhon ne svarga ke rajy ke liye apane ap ko napunsak banaya haai, jo is ko grahan kar sakata haai, vah grahan kare.
tab log balakon ko usake pas laa, ki vah un par hath rakhe aur praarthna kare par chelon ne unhen dantta.
yeeshu ne kaha, balakon ko mere pas ane do: aur unhen mana n karo, kyonki svarga ka rajy aeeson hee ka haai.
aur vah un par hath rakhkar, vahan se chala gaya.
aur dekho, aek manushy ne pas akar us se kaha, he guroo maain kaun sa bhla kam karoo, ki anant jeevan paun?
us ne us se kaha, too mujh se bhlai ke vishay men kyon poochhta haai? bhla to ek hee haai par yadi too jeevan men pravesh karana chahata haai, to agyaaon ko mana kara.
us ne us se kaha, kaun see agyaaen? yeeshu ne kaha, yah ki hatya n karana, vyabhaichar n karana, choree n karana, joottee gavahee n dena.
apane pita aur apanee mata ka adar karana, aur apane padosee se apane saman praem rakhna.
us javan ne us se kaha, in sab ko to maain ne mana haai ab mujh men kis bat kee ghattee haai?
yeeshu ne us se kaha, yaadi too siddh hona chahata haai to ja, apana mal bechakar kangalon ko de aur tujhe svarga men dhan milega aur akar mere peechhe ho le.
parantu vah javan yah bat sun udas hokar chala gaya, kyonaki vah bahut dhanee tha..
tab yeeshu ne apane chelon se kaha, maain tum se sach kahata hoo, ki dhanavan ka svarga ke rajy men pravesh karana kaattnai haai.
fir tum se kahata hoo, ki parameshvar ke rajy men dhanavan ke pravesh karane se untt ka sooi ke nake men se nikal jana sahaj haai.
yah sunakar, chelon ne bahut chakit hokar kaha, fir kis ka uddhar ho sakata haai?
is par pataras ne us se kaha, ki dek, ham to sab kuchh chhod ke tere peechhe ho liye haain: to hamen kya milega?
yeeshu ne un se kaha, maain tum se sach kahata hoo, ki nai utpaati se jab manushy ka putra apanee maahima ke sihansan par baaittega, to tum bhee jo mere peechhe ho liye ho, barah sinhasanon par baaittkar israael ke barah gotraen ka nyay karoge.
aur jis kisee ne gharon ya bhaiyon ya bahinon ya pita ya mata ya ladkebalon ya kheton ko mere nam ke liye chhod diya haai, us ko sau guna milega: aur vah anant jeevan ka aadhaikaree hoga.
parantu bahutere jo paahile haai, pichhle honge aur jo pichhle haai, pahile honge..
ibraaheem kee santan, daud kee santan, yeeshu maseeh kee vanshaavalee.
ibraaheem se isahak utpann hua isahak se yakoob utpann hua aur yakoob se yahooda aur usake bhai utpann hue.
yahooda se firis, aur yahooda aur tamar se jorah utpann hue aur firis se hisron utpann hua, aur hisron se aeram utpann hua.
aur aeram se ammeenadab utpann hua aur ammeenadab se nahashaen aur nahashaen se salamon utpann hua.
aur salamon aur rahab se boaj utpann hua. aur boaj aur root se obed utpann hua aur obed se yishau utpann hua.
aur yishau se daud raja utpann hua..
aur daud se sulaaiman us sree se utpann hua jo pahile uriyyah kee patnee thee.
aur sulaaiman se rahabam utpann hua aur rahabam se aabiyyah utpann hua aur aabiyyah se asa utpann hua aur asa se yahoshafaat utpann hua aur yahoshaafaat se yoram utpann hua, aur yoram se ujjaiyah utpann hua.
aur hijikiyyah se manaashshiah utpann hua. aur manaashshiah se amon utpann hua aur amon se yoshaiyyah utpann hua.
aur bandee hokar babool jane ke samay men yoshaiyyah se yakunyah, aur us ke bhai utpann huae..
bandee hokar babul pahunchaae jane ke bad yakunyah se shaalaatiael utpann hua aur shaalatiael se jaroobbabil utpann hua.
aur jaroobbabil se abeehood utpann hua, aur abeehood se ilyakeem utpann hua aur ilyakeem se ajor utpann hua.
aur ajor se sadok utpann hua aur sadok se akheem utpann hua aur akheem se ileehood utpann hua.
aur ileehood se iliyajar utpann hua aur ialiyajar se mattan utpann hua aur mattan se yakoob utpann hua.
aur yakoob se yoosufa utpann hua jo mariyam ka paati tha jis se yeeshu jo maseeh kahalata haai utpann hua..
ibraaheem se daud tak sab chaudah peeddhee hui aur daud se babul ko bandee hokar pahunchaae jane tak chaudah peeddhee aur bandee hokar babul ko pahunchaae jane ke samay se lekar maseeh tak chaudah peeddhee hui..
ab yeeshu maseeh ka janm is prakar se hua, ki jab us kee mata maariyam kee manganee yoosufa ke sath ho gai, to un ke ikatthe hone ke pahile se vah paavitra atma kee or se garbhvatee pai gai.
so usake paati yoosufa ne jo dharmee tha aur use badanam karana naheen chahata tha, use chupake se tyag dene kee manasa kee.
jab vah in baton ke soch hee men tha to prabhu ka svargadoot use svapn men dikhai dekar kahane laga he yoosufa daud kee santan, too apanee patnee mariyam ko apane yahan le ane se mat dra kyonki jo usake garbh men haai, vah pavitra atma kee or se haai.
vah putra janegee aur too usaka nam yeeshu rakhna kyonaki vah apane logon ka un ke papon se udar karega.
yah sab kuchh isaliye hua ki jo vachan prabhu ne bhvishyadvkta ke dara kaha tha vah poora ho.
ki, dekho aek kunvaree garbhvatee hogee aur aek putra janegee aur usaka nam immanuel rakha jaaega jis ka arth yah haai parameshvar hamare sath.
so yoosufa neend se jagakar prabhu ke doot kee agyaa anusar apanee patnee ko apane yahan le aya.
aur jab tak vah putra n janee tab tak vah usake pas n gaya: aur us ne usaka nam yeeshu rakha..
svarga ka rajy kisee grahasth ke saman haai, jo sabere nikala, ki apane dakh kee baree men majadooron ko lagaae.
fir pahar aek din chaddhe, nikalakar, aur auron ko bajar men bekar khde dekhkar,
un se kaha, tum bhee dakh kee baree men jao, aur jo kuchh tteek haai, tumhen doonga so ve bhee gae.
fir us ne doosare aur teesare pahar ke nikatt nikalakar vaaisa hee kiya.
aur aek ghantta din rahe fir nikalakar auron ko khde paya, aur un se kaha tu kyon yahan din bhr bekar khde rahe? unhon ne us se kaha, isaliye, ki kisee ne hamen majadooree par naheen lagaya.
us ne un se kaha, tum bhee da,a kee baree men jao.
sanjh ko dakh baree ke svamee ne apane bhndaree se kaha, majadooron ko bulakar pichhlon se lekar paahilon tak unhen majadooree de de.
so jab ve aa, jo ghantta bhr din rahe lagaae gaae the, to unhen aek aek deenar mila.
jo paahile aa, unhon ne yah samajha, ki hamen aadhaik milega parantu unhen bhee aek hee aek deenar mila.
jab mila, to vah grahasth par kudkuda ke kahane lage.
ki in pichhlon ne aek hee ghantta kam kiya, aur too ne unhen hamare barabar kar diya, jinhon ne din bhr ka bhar uttaya aur ghaam saha?
us ne un men se ek ko uttr diya, ki he mitra, maain tujh se kuchh anyay naheen karata kya too ne mujh se ek deenar n ttharaya?
kya uchit naheen ki man apane mal se jo chahoon so karoon? kya too mere bhle hone ke karan buree drashtti se dekhta haai?
isee reeti se jo pichhle haai, vah pahile honge, aur jo paahile haai, ve pichhle honge..
yeeshu yarooshalem ko jate huae barah chelon ko aekant men le gaya, aur marga men un se kahane laga.
ki dekho, ham yarooshalem ko jate haain aur manushy ka putra mahayajakon aur shaaastriayon ke hath pakadvaya jaaega aur ve us ko ghaat ke yogy ttharaaenge.
aur us ko anyajatiyon ke hath sonpenge, ki ve use tttthon men udaae, aur kode mare, aur kroos par chaddhaae, aur vah teesare din jilaya jaaega..
jab jabdee ke putraen kee mata ne apane putraen ke sath usake pas akar pranam kiya, aur us se kuchh mangane lagee.
us ne us se kaha, too kya chahatee haai? vah us se bolee, yah kah, ki mere ye do putra tere rajy men ek tere daahine aur ek tere baen baaitten.
yeeshu ne uttr diya, tum naheen janate ki kya mangate ho? jo kattora maain peene par hoo, kya tum pee sakate ho? unhon ne us se kaha, pee sakate haain.
us ne un se kaha, tum mera kattora to peeoge par apane daahine baen kisee ko bittana mera kam nahee, par jin ke liye mere pita kee or se taaiyar kiya gaya, unhen ke liye haai.
yah sunakar, dason chele un donon bhaiyon par kruddh huae.
yeeshu ne unhen pas bulakar kaha, tum janate ho, ki any jaatiyon ke haakim un par prabhuta karate haain aur jo bade haai, ve un par adhaikar jatate haain.
parantu tum men aeesa n hoga parantu jo koi tum men bada hona chahe, vah tumhara sevak bane.
aur jo tum men pradhaan hona chahe vah tumhara das bane.
jaaise ki manushy ka putra, vah isaliye naheen aya ki us kee seva tthal kii jaa, parantu isaaliye aya ki ap seva tthal kare aur bahuton kee chhudautee ke liye apane praan de..
jab ve yareeho se nikal rahe the, to aek badee bheed usake peechhe ho lee.
aur dekho, do andho, jo sadkar ke kinare baaitte the, yah sunakar ki yeeshu ja raha haai, pukarakar kahane lage ki he prabhu, daud kee santan, ham par daya kara.
logon ne unhen dantta, ki chup rahe, par ve aur bhee chillakar bole, he prabhu, daud kee santan, ham par daya kara.
tab yeeshu ne khde hokar, unhen bulaya, aur kaha
yeeshu ne taras khakar un kee ankhe chooi, aur ve turant dekhne lage aur usake peechhe ho liae..
jab ve yarooshalem ke nikatt pahunche aur jaaitoon pahad par baaitafage ke pas aa, to yeeshu ne do chelon ko yah kahakar bheja.
ki apane samhane ke ganv men jao, vahan panhuchate hee aek gadahee bandhaee hui, aur usake sath bachcha tumhen milega unhen kholakar, mere pas le ao.
yaadi tum men se koi kuchh kahe, to kaho, ki prabhu ko in ka prayojan haai: tab vah turant unhen bhej dega.
yah isaliye hua, ki jo vachan bhavishyadvkta ke dara kaha gaya tha, vah poora ho
ki siyyon kee bettee se kaho, dek, tera raja tere pas ata haai vah namra haai aur gadahe par baaitta haai baran ladoo ke bachche para.
chelon ne jakar, jaaisa yeeshu ne un se kaha tha, vaaisa hee kiya.
aur gadahee aur bachche ko lakar, un par apane kapade dale, aur vah un par baaitt gaya.
aur bahutere logon ne apane kapade marga men bichhaa, aur aur logon ne pedon se daaliyan kattkar marga men bichhai.
aur jo bheed age age jatee aur peechhe peechhe chalee atee thee, pukar pukar kar kahatee thee, ki daud kee santan ko hoshaana dhany haai vah jo prabhu ke nam se ata haai, akash men hoshaana.
logon ne kaha, yah galeel ke nasarat ka bhvishyadvkta yeeshu haai..
yeeshu ne parameshvar ke mandair men jakar, un sab ko, jo mandair men len den kar rahe the, nikal diya aur sarrafaon ke peeddhe aur kabootaron ke bechanevalon kee chauakiyan ulatt deen.
aur un se kaha, likha haai, ki mera ghar praarthna ka ghar kahalaaega parantu tum use dakuon kee khoh banate ho.
aur andho aur langade, maandair men usake pas laa, aur us ne unhen changa kiya.
parantu jab mahayajakon aur shaaastriayon ne in adabhut kamon ko, jo us ne kia, aur ladkon ko maandair men daud kee santan ko hoshaana pukarate huae dekha, to krodhait hokar us se kahane lage, kya too sunata haai ki ye kya kahate haain?
yeeshu ne un se kaha, han kya tum ne yah kabhee naheen paddha, ki balakon aur doodha peete bachchon ke munh se tu ne stuati siddh karai?
tab vah unhen chhodkar nagar ke bahar baaitaaniyyah ko gaya, or vahana rat bitai..
bhor ko jab vah nagar ko lautt raha tha, to use bookh lagee.
aur anjeer ke ped sadk ke kinare dekhkar vah usake pas gaya, aur paton ko chhod us men aur kuchh n pakar us se kaha, ab se tujh men fir kabhee fal n lage aur anjeer ka ped turant sukh gaya.
yah dekhkar chelon ne achambha kiya, aur kaha, yah anjeer ka ped kyonkar turant sookh gaya?
yeeshu ne un ko uttr diya, ki maain tum se sach kahata hoon yaadi tum vishvas rakho, aur sandeh n karo to n keval yah karoge, jo is anjeer ke ped se kiya gaya haai parantu yadi is pahad se bhee kahoge, ki ukhd jo aur samudra men ja pad, to yah ho jaaega.
aur jo kuchh tum praarthna men vishvas se mangoge vah sab tum ko milega..
vah maandair men jakar upadesh kar raha tha, ki mahayajakon aur logon ke puraniyon ne usake pas akar poochha, too ye kam kis ke adhaikar se karata haai? aur tujhe yah aadhaikar kis ne diya haai?
yeeshu ne un ko uttr diya, ki maain bhee tum se aek bat poochhta hoon yadi vah mujhe bataoge, to maain bhee tumhen bataunga ki ye kam kis adhaikar se karata hoon.
yoohanna ka bapaatisma kahan se tha? svarga kee or se ya manushyon kee or se tha? tab ve apas men vivad karane lage, ki yadi ham kahen svarga kee or se, to vah hame se kahega, fir tum ne us kee prateeati kyon n kee?
aur yaadi kahen manushyon kee or se to hamen bheed ka dr haai kyonaki ve sab yuhanna ko bhvishyadvkta janate haain.
so unhon ne yeeshu ko uttr diya, ki ham naheen janate us ne bhee un se kaha, to maain bhee tumhen naheen batata, ki ye kam kis adhaikar se karata hoon.
tum kya samajhte ho? kisee manushy ke do putra the us ne pahile ke pas jakar kaha he putra aj dakh kee baree men kam kara.
us ne uttr diya, maain naheen jaunga, parantu peechhe pachhta kar gaya.
in donon men se kis ne pita kee ichchha pooree kee? unhon ne kaha, pahile ne: yeeshu ne un se kaha, maain tum se sach kahata hoo, ki mahasool lenevale aur veshya tum se pahile parameshvar ke rajy men pravesh karate haain.
kyonaki yoohanna dharma ke marga se tumhare pas aya, aur tum ne us kee prateeti n kee: par mahasool lenevalon aur veshyaon ne us kee prateeati kee: aur tum yah dekhkar peechhe bhee n pachhtaae ki us kee prateeati kar lete..
aek aur drashttant suno: aek grahasth tha, jis ne dakh kee baree lagai aur usake charon or bada bandhaa aur us me ras ka kund khoda aur gummatt banaya aur kisanon ko usaka tteeka dekar paradesh chala gaya.
jab fal ka samay nikatt aya, to us ne apane dason ko usaka fal lene ke liye kisanon ke pas bheja.
par kisanon ne usake dason ko pakad ke, kisee ko peetta, aur kisee ko mar dala aur kisee ko patthravah kiya.
fir us ne aur dason ko bheja, jo pahilon se aadhaik the aur unhon ne un se bhee vaaisa hee kiya.
ant men us ne apane putra ko un ke pas yah kahakar bheja, ki ve mere putra ka adar karenge.
parantu kisanon ne putra ko dekhkar apas men kaha, yah to vaaris haai, ao, use mar dalen: aur us kee meeras le len.
aur unhon ne use pakada aur dakh kee baree se bahar nikalakar mar dala.
unhonne us se kaha, vah un bure logon ko buree reeati se nash karega aur dakh kee baree ka tteeka aur kisanon ko dega, jo samay par use fal diya karenge.
yeeshu ne un se kaha, kya tum ne kabhee paavitra shaasr men yah naheen paddha, ki jis patthr ko rajaamistriayon ne nikamma ttharaya tha, vahee kone ke sire ka patthr ho gaya?
yah prabhu kee or se hua, aur hamare dekhte men adabhut haai, isaaliye maain tum se kahata hoo, ki parameshvar ka rajy tum se le liya jaaega aur aeesee jaati ko jo usaka fal laa, diya jaaega.
jo is patthr par girega, vah chakanachoor ho jaaega: aur jis par vah girega, us ko pees dalega.
mahayajak aur fareesee usake drashttanton ko sunakar samajh gaa, ki vah hamare vishay men kahata haai.
aur unhon ne use pakadna chaha, parantu logon se dr gaae kyonki ve use bhavishyadvkta janate the..
is par yeeshu fir un se drashttanton men kahane laga.
svarga ka rajy us raja ke saman haai, jis ne apane putra ka byah kiya.
aur us ne apane dason ko bheja, ki nevatahaariyon ko byah ke bhoj men bulaaen parantu unhon ne ana n chaha.
fir us ne aur dason ko yah kahakar bheja, ki nevatahaariyon se kaho, dekho maain bhoj taaiyar kar chuka hoo, aur mere baail aur pale huae pashu mare gaae haain: aur sab kuchh taaiyar haai byah ke bhoj men ao.
parantu ve beparavai karake chal diae: koi apane khet ko, koi apane byopar ko.
auron ne jo bach rahe the usake dason ko pakadkar un ka anadar kiya aur mar dala.
raja ne krodha kiya, aur apanee sena bhejakar un hatyaron ko nash kiya, aur un ke nagar foonk diya.
tab us ne apane dason se kaha, byah ka bhoj to taaiyar haai, parantu nevataharee yogy n tthare.
isaliye chaurahon men jao, aur jitane log tumhen mile, sab ko byah ke bhoj men bula lao.
so un dason ne sadkon par jakar kya bure, kya bhle, jitane mile, sab ko ikatthe kiya aur byah ka ghar jevanaharon se bhr gaya.
jab raja jevanaharon ke dekhne ko bheetar aya to us ne vahan aek manushy ko dekha, jo byah ka vasr naheen paahine tha.
us ne usase poochha he mitra too byah ka vasr paahine bina yahan kyon a gaya? usaka munh band ho gaya.
tab raja ne sevakon se kaha, is ke hath panv bandhakar use bahar aandhiayare men dal do, vahan rona, aur dant peesana hoga.
kyonaki bulaae huae to bahut parantu chune huae thode haain..
so unhon ne apane chelon ko herodiyon ke sath usake pas yah kahane ko bheja, ki he guroo ham janate haai, ki too sachcha haai aur parameshvar ka marga sachchai se sikhata haai aur kisee kee parava naheen karata, kyonki too manushyon ka munh dekhkar baten nahee karata.
is liye hamen bata too kya samajhta haai? kaaisar ko kar dena uchit haai, ki naheen.
yeeshu ne un kee dushttta janakar kaha, he kapaattyaien mujhe kyon parakhte ho?
kar ka sikka mujhe dikhao: tab ve usake pas aek deenar le aae.
us ne, un se poochha, yah mootira aur nam kis ka haai?
unhon ne us se kaha, kaaisar ka tab us ne, un se kaha jo kaaisar ka haai, vah kaaisar ko aur jo parameshvar ka haai, vah parameshvar ko do.
yah sunakar unhon ne achambha kiya, aur use chhodkar chale gaae..
usee din sadookee jo kahate haain ki mare huon ka punarootthan haai hee naheen usake pas aa, aur us se poochha.
ab hamare yahan sat bhai the paahila byah karake mar gaya aur santan n hone ke karan apanee patnee ko apane bhai ke liye chhod gaya.
isee prakar doosare aur teesare ne bhee kiya, aur saton tak yahee hua.
sab ke bad vah sree bhee mar gai.
so jee uttne par, vah un saton men se kis kee patnee hogee? kyonaki vah sab kee patnee ho chukee thee.
yeeshu ne unhen uttr diya, ki tum pavitra shaasr aur parameshvar kee samarth naheen janate is karan bool men pad gaae ho.
kyonaki jee uttne par byah shaadee n hogee parantu ve svarga men parameshvar ke dooton kee nai honge.
parantu mare huon ke jee uttne ke vishay men kya tum ne yah vachan naheen paddha jo parameshvar ne tum se kaha.
ki maain ibraaheem ka parameshvar, aur isahak ka parameshvar, aur yakoob ka parameshvar hoon? vah to mare huon ka nahee, parantu jeevaton ka parameshvar haai.
yah sunakar log usake upadesh se chakit hue.
jab fareesiyon ne suna, ki us ne sadookiyon ka munh band kar diya to ve ikatthe huae.
aur un men se aek vyavasthapak ne parakhne ke liye, us se poochha.
he guroo vyavastha men kaun see agyaa badee haai?
us ne us se kaha, too parameshvar apane prabhu se apane sare man aur apane sare praan aur apanee saree buaddh ike sath praem rakh.
badee aur mukhy agyaa to yahee haai.
aur usee ke saman yah doosaree bhee haai, ki too apane padosee se apane saman praem rakh.
ye hee do agyaaaen saree vyavastha aur bhvishyadvktaon ka adhaar haai..
jab fareesee ikatthe the, to yeeshu ne un se poochha.
ki maseeh ke vishay men tum kya samajhte ho? vah kis ka santan haai? unhon ne us se kaha, daud ka.
us ne un se poochha, to daud atma men hokar use prabhu kyon kahata haai?
ki prabhu ne, mere prabhu se kaha mere daahine baait, jab tak ki maain tere baaiariyon ko tere panvon ke neeche n kar doon.
bhla, jab daud use prabhu kahata haai, to vah usaka putra kyonkar tthara?
tab yeeshu ne bheed se aur apane chelon se kaha.
shaasree aur fareesee moosa kee gaee par baaitte haain.
isaliye ve tum se jo kuchh kahen vah karana, aur manana parantu un ke se kam mat karana kyonaki ve kahate to haain par karate naheen.
ve aek aeese bharee bojh ko jin ko uttana kattnai haai, bandhakar unhen manushyon ke kandhaen par rakhte haain parantu ap unhen apanee ungalee se bhee sarakana naheen chahate .
ve apane sab kam logon ko dikhane ke liye karate haain: ve apane taveejon ko chaude karate, aur apane vasren kee koren baddhate haain.
jevanaron men mukhy mukhy jagahe, aur sabha men mukhy mukhy asana.
aur bajaron men namaskar aur manushy men rabbee kahalana unhen bhata haai.
aur prathvee par kisee ko apana pita n kahana, kayonki tumhara aek hee pita haai, jo svarga men haai.
aur svamee bhee n kahalana, kyonaki tumhara aek hee svamee haai, arthata maseeha.
jo tum men bada ho, vah tumhara sevak bane.
jo koi apane ap ko bada banaaega, vah chhotta kiya jaaega: aur jo koi apane ap ko chhotta banaaega, vah bada kiya jaaega..
he kapattee shaastriayon aur fareeasiyon tum par haya! tum manushyon ke virodha men svarga ke rajy ka dar band karate ho, n to ap hee us men pravesh karate ho aur n us men pravesh karanevalon ko pravesh karane dete ho..
he kapattee shaastriayon aur fareeasiyon tum par haya! tum aek jan ko apane mat men lane ke liye sare jal aur thl men firate ho, aur jab vah mat men a jata haai, to use apane se doona narakeey bana dete ho..
he andho aguvo, tum par hay, jo kahate ho ki yadi koi maandair kee shapath khaae to kuchh nahee, parantu yaadi koi maandair ke sone kee saugandha khaae to us se bandha jaaega.
he moorkho, , aur andhae, kaun bada haai, sona ya vah mandair jis se sona paavitra hota haai?
fir kahate ho ki yadi koi vedee kee shapath khaae to kuchh nahee, parantu jo bhentt us par haai, yaadi koi us kee shapath khaae to bandha jaaega.
he andhae, kaun bada haai, bhentt ya vedee: jis se bhentt paavitra hota haai?
isaliye jo vedee kee shapath khata haai, vah us kee, aur jo kuchh us par haai, us kee bhee shapath khata haai.
aur jo maandair kee shapath khata haai, vah us kee aur us men rahanevalon kee bhee shapath khata haai.
aur jo svarga kee shapath khata haai, vah parameshvar ke sihansan kee aur us par baaittnevale kee bhee shapath khata haai..
he kapattee shaastriayo, aur fareeasiyo, tum par haya tum podeene aur saunfa aur jeere ka dasavan ansh dete ho, parantu tum ne vyavastha kee gambheer baton ko chhod diya haai chahiye tha ki inhen bhee karate rahate, aur unhen bhee n chhodte.
he andho aguvo, tum machchhd ko to chhan dalate ho, parantu untt ko nigal jate ho.
he kapattee shaastriayo, aur fareeasiyo, tum par hay, tum kattore aur thalee ko upar upar se to manjate ho parantu ve bheetar andhor asanyam se bhre huae haain.
he andho fareesee, paahile kattore aur thalee ko bheetar se manj ki ve bahar se bhee svachchh hon..
he kapattee shaastriayo, aur fareeasiyo, tum par haya tum choona firee hui kabraen ke saman ho jo upar se to sundar dikhai detee haai, parantu bheetar murdon kee haddiyon aur sab prakar kee malinata se bhree haain.
isee reeti se tum bhee upar se manushyon ko dharmee dikhai dete ho, parantu bheetar kapatt aur adharma se bhre huae ho..
he kapattee shaastriayo, aur fareeasiyo, tum par haya tum bhavishyadvktaon kee kabraen sanvarate aur dharmiyon kee kabraen banate ho.
aur kahate ho, ki yadi ham apane bapadadon ke dinon men hote to bhvishyadvktaon kee hatya men un ke sajhee n hote.
is se to tum apane par ap hee gavahee dete ho, ki tum bhvishyadvktaon ke ghaatakon kee santan ho.
he sanpo, he karaaiton ke bachcho, tum narak ke dand se kyonkar bachoge?
isaliye dekho, maain tumhare pas bhvishyadvktaon aur buddhmaianon aur shaaastriayon ko bhejata hoon aur tum un men se kitanon ko mar daloge, aur kroos par chaddhaoge aur kitanon ko apanee sabhaon men kode maroge, aur aek nagar se doosare nagar men khdedte firoge.
jis se dharmee haabil se lekar birikyah ke putra jakarayah tak, jise tum ne maandair aur vedee ke beech men mar dala tha, jitane dharmiyon ka lohoo prathvee par bahaya gaya haai, vah sab tumhare sir par padega.
maain tum se sach kahata hoo, ye sab baten is samay ke logon par a padengee..
he yarooshalem, he yarooshalema too jo bhavishyadvktaon ko mar dalata haai, aur jo tere pas bheje gaa, unhen patthravah karata haai, kitanee hee bar maain ne chaha ki jaaise murgee apane bachchon ko apane pankhon ke neeche ikatthe karatee haai, vaaise hee maain bhee tere balakon ko ikatthe kar loo, parantu tum ne n chaha.
dekho, tumhara ghar tumhare liye ujad chhoda jata haai.
jab yeeshu mandair se nikalakar ja raha tha, to usake chele us ko maandair kee rachana dikhane ke liye us ke pas aae.
us ne un se kaha, kya tum yah sab naheen dekhte? maain tum se sach kahata hoo, yahan patthr par patthr bhee n choottega, jo ddhaya n jaega.
aur jab vah jaaitoon pahad par baaitta tha, to chelon ne alag usake pas akar kaha, ham se kah ki ye baten kab hongee? aur tere ane ka, aur jagat ke ant ka kya chinh hoga?
yeeshu ne un ko uttr diya, savadhaan raho! koi tumhen n bhramane paae.
kyonaki bahut se aeese honge jo mere nam se akar kahenge, ki maain maseeh hoon: aur bahuton ko bhramaaenge.
tum ladaiyon aur ladaiyon kee charcha sunoge dekho ghabara n jana kyonaki in ka hona avashy haai, parantu us samay ant n hoga.
kyonaki jati par jati, aur rajy par rajy chaddhai karega, aur jagah jagah akal padenge, aur bhuidol honge.
ye sab baten peedaon ka arambh hongee.
tab ve klesh dilane ke liye tumhen pakadvaaenge, aur tumhen mar dalenge aur mere nam ke karan sab jatiyon ke log tum se baair rakhenge.
tab bahutere ttokar khaaenge, aur aek doosare se baair rakhenge.
aur bahut se jootte bhvishyadvkta utt khde honge, aur bahuton ko bhramaaenge.
aur adharma ke baddhne se bahuton ka praem ttnda ho jaaega.
parantu jo ant tak dhaeeraj dhare rahega, usee ka uddhar hoga.
aur rajy ka yah susamachar sare jagat men prachar kiya jaaega, ki sab jatiyon par gavahee ho, tab ant a jaaega..
so jab tum us ujadnevalee gharanait vastu ko jis kee charcha daaniyyel bhvishyadvkta ke dara hui thee, paavitra sthan men khdee hui dekho, jo paddhe, vah samajhe .
tab jo yahoodiya men hon ve pahadon par bhag jaaen.
jo kotte par ho, vah apane ghar men se saman lene ko n utare.
aur jo khet men ho, vah apana kapada lene ko peechhe n lautte.
un dinon men jo garbhvatee aur doodha pilatee hongee, un ke liye hay, haya.
aur praarthna karo ki tumhen jade men ya sabt ke din bhagana n pade.
kyonaki us samay aeesa bharee klesh hoga, jaaisa jagat ke arambh se n ab tak hua, aur n kabhee hoga.
aur yaadi ve din ghattaae n jate, to koi praanee n bachata parantu chune huon ke karan ve din ghattaae jaaenge.
us samay yadi koi tum se kahe, ki dekho, maseeh yahan haain! ya vahan haai to prateeati n karana.
dekho, maain ne paahile se tum se yah sab kuchh kah diya haai.
isaliye yaadi ve tum se kahe, dekho, vah jangal men haai, to bahar n nikal jana dekho, vah kottriyon men haai, to prateeati n karana.
kyonaki jaaise bijalee poorva se nikalakar paashchaim tak chamakatee jatee haai, vaaisa hee manushy ke putra ka bhee ana hoga.
jahan loth ho, vaheen giddh ikatthe honge..
un dinon ke klesh ke bad turant soorya aandhiayara ho jaega, aur chand ka prakash jata rahega, aur tare akash se gir padenge aur akash kee shaktaiyan hilai jaengee.
aur vah turahee ke bade shabd ke sat, apane dooton ko bhejega, aur ve akash ke is chhor se us chhor tak, charon disha se usake chune huon ko ikatthe karenge.
anjeer ke ped se yah drashttant seekho: jab us kee dalee komal ho jatee aur patte nikalane lagate haai, to tum jan lete ho, ki graeeshm kal nikatt haai.
isee reeti se jab tum in sab baton ko dekho, to jan lo, ki vah nikatt haai, baran dar par haai.
maain tum se sach kahata hoo, ki jabatab ye sab baten pooree n ho le, tab tak yah peeddhee jatee n rahegee.
akash aur prathvee ttl jaaenge, parantu meree baten kabhee n ttlengee.
us din aur us ghadee ke vishay men koi naheen janata, n svarga ke doot, aur n putra, parantu keval pita.
jaaise nooh ke din the, vaaisa hee manushy ke putra ka ana bhee hoga.
kyonaki jaaise jala-pralay se pahile ke dinon me, jis din tak ki nooh jahaj par n chaddha, us din tak log khate-peete the, aur un men byah shaadee hotee thee.
aur jab tak jala-pralay akar un sab ko baha n le gaya, tab tak un ko kuchh bhee maloom n pada vaaise hee manushy ke putra ka ana bhee hoga.
us samay do jan khet men honge, ek le liya jaega aur doosara chhod diya jaega.
do striayan chakkee peesatee rahengee, aek le lee jaaegee, aur doosaree chhod dee jaaegee.
isaliye jagate raho, kyonki tum naheen janate ki tumhara prabhu kis din aaega.
parantu yah jan lo ki yadi ghar ka svamee janata hota ki chor kis pahar aaega, to jagata rahata aur apane ghar men sengha lagane n deta.
isaliye tum bhee taaiyar raho, kyonki jis ghadee ke vishay men tum sochate bhee naheen ho, usee ghadee manushy ka putra a jaaega.
so vah vishvasayogy aur buaddhmaian das kaun haai, jise svamee ne apane naukar chakaron par saradar ttharaya, ki samay par unhen bhojan de?
dhany haai, vah das, jise usaka svamee akar aeesa kee karate paae.
maain tum se sach kahata hoon vah use apanee saree sanpati par saradar ttharaaega.
parantu yadi vah dushtt das sochane lage, ki mere svamee ke ane men der haai.
aur apane sathee dason ko peettne lage, aur piyakkadon ke sath khaae peeae.
to us das ka svamee aeese din aaega, jab vah us kee batt n johata ho.
aur aeesee ghadee ki vah n janata ho, aur use bharee tadna dekar, usaka bhag kapattyaien ke sath ttharaaega: vahan rona aur dant peesana hoga..
tab svarga ka rajy un das kunvariyon ke saman hoga jo apanee mashaalen lekar doolhe se bhentt karane ko nikaleen.
un men panch moorkh aur panch samajhdar theen.
moorkhon ne apanee mashaalen to lee, parantu apane sath tel naheen liya.
jab dulhe ke ane men der hui, to ve sab unghane lagee, aur so gai.
adhaee rat ko dhoom machae, ki dekho, doolha a raha haai, us se bhentt karane ke liye chalo.
tab ve sab kunvaariyan uttkar apanee apanee mashalen tteek karane lageen.
aur moorkhon ne samajhdaron se kaha, apane tel men se kuchh hamen bhee do, kyonki hamaree mashaalen bujhee jatee haain.
jab ve mol lene ko ja rahee thee, to doolha a pahuncha, aur jo taaiyar thee, ve usake sath byah ke ghar men chaleen gai aur dar band kiya gaya.
isake bad ve doosaree kunvariyan bhee akar kahane lagee, he svamee, he svamee, hamare liye dar khol de.
us ne uttr diya, ki maain tum se sach kahata hoo, maain tumhen naheen janata.
isaliye jagate raho, kyonki tum n us din ko janate ho, n us ghadee ko..
kyonaki yah us manushy kee see dasha haai jis ne paradesh ko jate samay apane dason ko bulakar, apanee sanpaati un ko saunp dee.
us ne ek ko panch tod, doosare ko do, aur teesare ko eka arthata har ek ko us kee samarth ke anusar diya, aur tab paradesh chala gaya.
tab jis ko panch tode mile the, us ne turant jakar un se len den kiya, aur panch tode aur kamaae.
isee reeti se jis ko do mile the, us ne bhee do aur kamaae.
parantu jis ko aek mila tha, us ne jakar mittee khodee, aur apane svamee ke roopaye chhpai diae.
bahut dinon ke bad un dason ka svamee akar un se lekha lene laga.
jis ko panch tode mile the, us ne panch tode aur lakar kaha he svamee, too ne mujhe panch tode saunpe the, dekh maain ne panch tode aur kamaae haain.
usake svamee ne usase kaha, dhany haai achchhe aur vishvasayogy das, too thode men vishvasayogy raha maain tujhe bahut vastuon ka adhaikaree banaunga apane svamee ke anand men sambhagee ho.
aur jis ko do tode mile the, us ne bhee akar kaha he svamee too ne mujhe do tode saunpen the, dek, maain ne do tode aur kamaaen.
usake svamee ne us se kaha, dhany he achchhe aur vishvasayogy das, too thode men vishvasayogy raha, maain tujhe bahut vastuon ka adhaikaree banaunga apane svamee ke anand men sambhagee ho.
tab jis ko aek toda mila tha, us ne akar kaha he svamee, maain tujhe janata tha, ki too kattor manushy haai, aur jahan naheen chheettta vahan se battorata haai.
so maain dr gaya aur jakar tera toda mittee men chhpai diya dek, jo tera haai, vah yah haai.
usake svamee ne use uttr diya, ki he dushtt aur alasee dasa jab yah too janata tha, ki jahan maain ne naheen boya vahan se kattta hoon aur jahan maain ne naheen chheetta vahan se battorata hoon.
to tujhe chahiae tha, ki mera roopaya sarrafaon ko de deta, tab maain akar apana dhan byaj samet le leta.
isaliye vah toda us se le lo, aur jis ke pas das tode haai, us ko de do.
kyonaki jis kisee ke pas haai, use aur diya jaaega aushra usake pas bahut ho jaaega: parantu jis ke pas naheen haai, us se vah bhee jo usake pas haai, le liya jaaega.
aur is nikamme das ko bahar ke andhore men dal do, jahan rona aushra dant peesana hoga.
jab manushy ka putra apanee mahima men aaega, aur sab svarga doot usake sath aaenge to vah apanee mahima ke sihansan par virajaman hoga.
aur sab jaatiyan usake samhane ikatthee kee jaaengee aur jaaisa charavaha bhedon ko bakariyon se alag kar deta haai, vaaisa hee vah unhen aek doosare se alag karega.
aur vah bhedon ko apanee daahinee or aur bakariyon ko bai aur khdee karega.
tab raja apanee dahinee or valon se kahega, he mere pita ke dhany logo, ao, us rajy ke adhaikaree ho jao, jo jagat ke adi se tumhare liye taaiyar kiya hua haai.
maain nanga tha, tum ne mujhe kapade pahinaae maain beemar tha, tum ne meree sudhai lee, maain bandeegrah men tha, tum mujh se milane aae.
tab dharmee us ko uttr denge ki he prabhu, ham ne kab tujhe bookha dekha aur sikhaya? ya piyasa dekha, aur pilaya?
ham ne kab tujhe paradeshaee dekha aur apane ghar men ttharaya ya nanga dekha, aur kapade paahinaae?
tab raja unhen uttr dega maain tum se sach kahata hoo, ki tum ne jo mere in chhotte se chhotte bhaiyon men se kisee aek ke sath kiya, vah mere hee sath kiya.
tab vah bain or valon se kahega, he sraapit logo, mere samhane se us anant ag men chale jao, jo shautan aur usake dooton ke liye taaiyar kee gai haai.
kyonaki maain bookha tha, aur tum ne mujhe khane ko naheen diya, maain piyasa tha, aur tum ne mujhe panee naheen pilaya.
maain paradeshaee tha, aur tum ne mujhe apane ghar men naheen ttharaya maain nanga tha, aur tum ne mujhe kapade naheen pahinaae beemar aur bandeegrah men tha, aur tum ne meree sudhai n lee.
tab ve uttr denge, ki he prabhu, ham ne tujhe kab bookha, ya piyasa, ya paradeshae, ya nanga, ya beemar, ya bandeegrah men dekha, aur teree seva tthal n kee?
tab vah unhen uttr dega, maain tum se sach kahata hoon ki tum ne jo in chhotte se chhotton men se kisee aek ke sath naheen kiya, vah mere sath bhee naheen kiya.
aur yah anant dand bhogenge parantu dharmee anant jeevan men pravesh karenge.
jab yeeshu ye sab baten kah chuka, to apane chelon se kahane laga.
tum janate ho, ki do din ke bad fasah ka pavrva hoga aur manushy ka putra kroos par chaddhaae jane ke liye pakadvaya jaaega.
tab mahayajak aur praja ke puraniae kaifaa nam mahayajak ke angan men ikatthe huae.
aur apas men vichar karane lage ki yeeshu ko chht se pakadkar mar dalen.
parantu ve kahate the, ki pavrva ke samay naheen kaheen aeesa n ho ki logon men balava mach jaae.
jab yeeshu baaitaniyyah men shamaun koddhee ke ghar men tha.
to aek sree sangamaramar ke patra men bahumol itra lekar usake pas ai, aur jab vah bhojan karane baaitta tha, to usake sir par undel diya.
yah dekhkar, usake chele risayaae aur kahane lage, is ka kyon satyanash kiya gaya?
yah to achchhe dam par bikakar kangalon ko bantta ja sakata tha.
yah janakar yeeshu ne un se kaha, sree ko kyon satate ho? us ne mere sath bhlai kee haai.
kangal tumhare sath sada rahate haai, parantu maain tumhare sath sadaaiv n rahoonga.
us ne meree deh par jo yah itra undela haai, vah mere gaddhe jane ke liye kiya haai
maain tum se sach kahata hoo, ki sare jagat men jahan kaheen yah susamachar prachar kiya jaaega, vahan usake is kam ka varnn bhee usake smaran men kiya jaaega.
tab yahooda iskariyotee nam barah chelon men se aek ne mahayajakon ke pas jakar kaha.
yaadi maain use tumhare hath pakadva doo, to mujhe kya doge? unhon ne use tees chandee ke sikke taulakar de diae.
aur vah usee samay se use pakadvane ka avasar ddoonddhne laga..
akhmeeree rottee ke pavrva ke paahile din, chele yeeshu ke pas akar poochhne lage too kahan chahata haai ki ham tere liye fasah khane kee taaiyaree karen?
us ne kaha, nagar men faulane ke pas jakar us se kaho, ki guroo kahata haai, ki mera samay nikatt haai, maain apane chelon ke sath tere yahan pavrva manaunga.
so chelon ne yeeshu kee agyaa manee, aur fasah taaiyar kiya.
jab ve kha rahe the, to us ne kaha, maain tum se sach kahata hoo, ki tum men se aek mujhe pakadvaaega.
is par ve bahut udas hua, aur har aek us se poochhne laga, he guro, kya vah maain hoon?
manushy ka putra to jaaisa usake vishay men likha haai, jata hee haai parantu us manushy ke liye shaek haai jis ke dara manushy ka putra pakadvaya jata haai: yadi us manushy ka janm n hota, to usake liye bhla hota.
tab usake pakadvanevale yahooda ne kaha ki he rabbee, kya vah maain hoon?
us ne us se kaha, too kah chuka: jab ve kha rahe the, to yeeshu ne rottee lee, aur ashaeesh mangakar todee, aur chelon ko dekar kaha, lo, khao yah meree deh haai.
fir us ne kattora lekar, dhanyavad kiya, aur unhen dekar kaha, tum sab is men se peeo.
kyonaki yah vacha ka mera vah lohoo haai, jo bahuton ke liye papon kee kshama ke nimitt bahaya jata haai.
maain tum se kahata hoo, ki dakh ka yah ras us din tak kabhee n peeunga, jab tak tumhare sath apane pita ke rajy men naya n peeun..
fir ve bhjan gakar jaaitoon pahad par gaae..
tab yeeshu ne un se kaha tum sab aj hee rat ko mere vishay men ttokar khaoge kyonki likha haai, ki maain charavahe ko maroonga aur jhund kee bheden tittr bittr ho jaaengee.
parantu maain apane jee uttne ke bad tum se pahale galeel ko jaunga.
is par pataras ne us se kaha, yadi sab tere vishay men ttokar khaaen to khaae, parantu maain kabhee bhee ttokar n khaunga.
yeeshu ne us se kaha, maain tum se sach kahata hoo, ki aj hee raj ko murga ke bang dene se paahile, too teen bar mujh se mukar jaaega.
pataras ne us se kaha, yadi mujhe tere sath marana bhee ho, taubhee, maain tujh se kabhee n mukaroonga: aur aeesa hee sab chelon ne bhee kaha..
tab yeeshu ne apane chelon ke sath gatasamanee nam aek sthan men aya aur apane chelon se kahane laga ki yaheen baaitte rahana, jab tak ki maain vahan jakar praarthna karoon.
aur vah pataras aur jabdee ke donon putraen ko sath le gaya, aur udas aur vyakul hone laga.
tab us ne un se kaha mera jee bahut udas haai, yahan tak ki mere praan nikala chahate: tum yaheen ttharo, aur mere sath jagate raho.
fir vah thoda aur age baddhkar munh ke bal gira, aur yah praarthna karane laga, ki he mere pita, yaadi ho sake, to yah kattora mujh se ttl jaae taubhee jaaisa maain chahata hoon vaaisa nahee, parantu jaaisa too chahata haai vaaisa hee ho.
fir chelon ke pas akar unhen sote paya, aur pataras se kaha kya tum mere sath aek ghadee bhee n jag sake?
jagate raho, aur praarthna karate raho, ki tum pareeksha men n pado: atma to taaiyar haai, parantu shareer durbal haai.
fir us ne doosaree bar jakar yah praarthna kee ki he mere pita, yaadi yah mere peeae bina naheen hatt sakata to teree ichchha pooree ho.
tab us ne akar unhen fir sote paya, kyonki un kee ankhen neend se bhree theen.
aur unhen chhodkar fir chala gaya, aur vahee bat fir kahakar, teesaree bar praarthna kee.
tab us ne chelon ke pas akar un se kaha ab sote raho, aur vishraam karo: dekho, ghadee a pahunchee haai, aur manushy ka putra papiyon ke hath pakadvaya jata haai.
utto, chalen dekho, mera pakadvanevala nikatt a pahuncha haai..
vah yah kah hee raha tha, ki dekho yahooda jo barahon men se aek tha, aya, aur usake sath mahayajakon aur logon ke puraaniyon kee or se badee bheed, talavaren aur laattyaian liae huae ai.
usake pakadvanevale ne unhen yah pata diya tha ki jis ko maain choom loon vahee haai use pakad lena.
aur turant yeeshu ke pas akar kaha he rabbee namaskara aur us ko bahut chooma.
yeeshu ne us se kaha he mitra, jis kam ke liye too aya haai, use kar le. tab unhon ne pas akar yeeshu par hath dale, aur use pakad liya.
tab yeeshu ne us se kaha apanee talavar kattee men rakh le kyonki jo talavar chalate haai, ve sab talavar se nash kiae jaaenge.
parantu pavitra shaasr kee baten ki aeesa hee hona avashy haai, kyonkar pooree hongee?
usee ghadee yeeshu ne bheed se kaha kya tum talavaren aur laattyaian lekar mujhe dakoo ke saman pakadne ke liye nikale ho? maain har din mandair men baaittkar upadesh diya karata tha, aur tum ne mujhe naheen pakada.
parantu yah sab isaaliye hua haai, ki bhvishyadvktaon ke vachan ke poore hon: tab sab chelen use chhodkar bhag gaae..
aur yeeshu ke pakadnevale us ko kaifaa nam mahayajak ke pas le gaa, jahan shaasree aur puraaniae ikatthe huae the.
aur pataras door se usake peechhe peechhe mahayajak ke angan tak gaya, aur bheetar jakar ant dekhne ko pyadon ke sath baaitt gaya.
mahayajak aur saree mahasabha yeeshu ko mar dalane ke liye usake virodha men joottee gavahee kee khoj men the.
parantu bahut se jootte gavahon ke ane par bhee n pai.
ant men do janon ne akar kaha, ki us ne kaha haai ki maain parameshvar ke maandair ko ddha sakata hoon aur use teen din men bana sakata hoon.
tab mahayajak ne khde hokar us se kaha, kya too koi uttr naheen deta? ye log tere virodha men kya gavahee dete haain? parantu yeeshu chup raha: mahayajak ne us se kaha.
maain tujhe jeevate parameshvar kee shapath deta hoo, ki yadi too parameshvar ka putra maseeh haai, to ham se kah de.
yeeshu ne us se kaha too ne ap hee kah diya: baran maain tum se yah bhee kahata hoo, ki ab se tum manushy ke putra ko sarvashaaktaiman kee daahinee or baaitte, aur akash ke badalon par ate dekhoge.
tab mahayajak ne apane vasr faadkar kaha, is ne parameshvar kee ninda kee haai, ab hamen gavahon ka kya prayojana?
dekho, tum ne abhee yah ninda sunee haai! tum kya samajhte ho? unhon ne uttr diya, yah vadha hone ke yogy haai.
tab unhon ne us se munh par tooka, aur use ghoonse mare, auron ne thppad mar ke kaha.
he maseeh, ham se bhavishyadvvanee karake kaha: ki kis ne tujhe mara?
aur pataras bahar angan men baaitta hua tha: ki aek laundee ne usake pas akar kaha too bhee yeeshu galeelee ke sath tha.
us ne sab ke samhane yah kah kar inkar kiya aur kaha, maain naheen janata too kya kah rahee haai.
jab vah bahar devaddhee men chala gaya, to doosaree ne use dekhkar un se jo vahan the kaha yah bhee to yeeshu nasaree ke sath tha.
us ne shapath khakar fir inkar kiya ki maain us manushy ko naheen janata.
thodee der ke bad, jo vahan khde the, unhon ne pataras ke pas akar us se kaha, sachamuch too bhee un men se aek haai kyonki teree bolee tera bhed khol detee haai.
tab vah dhaikkar dene aur shapath khane laga, ki maain us manushy ko naheen janata aur turant murga ne bang dee.
tab pataras ko yeeshu kee kahee hui bat smaran ai kee murga ke bang dene se pahile too teen bar mera inkar karega aur vah bahar jakar foott foott kar rone laga..
jab bhor hui, to sab mahayajakon aur logon ke puraniyon ne yeeshu ke mar dalane kee sammati kee.
aur unhon ne use bandha aur le jakar peelatus haakim ke hath men saunp diya..
jab usake pakadvanevale yahooda ne dekha ki vah doshaee ttharaya gaya haai to vah pachhtaya aur ve tees chandee ke sikke mahayajakon aur puraaniyon ke pas faer laya.
aur kaha, maain ne nirdoshaee ko ghaat ke liye pakadvakar pap kiya haai? unhon ne kaha, hamen kya? too hee jana.
tab vah un sikkon ko mandair men faenkakar chala gaya, aur jakar apane ap ko faansee dee.
mahayajakon ne un sikkon ko lekar kaha, inhen bhndar men rakhna uchit nahee, kyonki yah lohoo ka dam haai.
tab jo vachan yirmayah bhvishyadvkta ke dara kaha gaya tha vah poora hua ki unhon ne ve tees sikke arthata us ttharaae huae mooly ko jise israael kee santan men se kitanon ne ttharaya tha le liae.
aur jaaise prabhu ne mujhe agyaa dee thee vaaise hee unhen kumhar ke khet ke mooly men de diya..
jab yeeshu hakim ke samhane khda tha, to haakim ne us se poochha ki kya too yahoodiyon ka raja haai? yeeshu ne us se kaha, too ap hee kah raha haai.
jab mahayajak aur puraaniae us par dosh laga rahe the, to us ne kuchh uttr naheen diya.
is par peelatus ne us se kaha: kya too naheen sunata, ki ye tere virodha men kitanee gavaahiyan de rahe haain?
parantu us ne us ko aek bat ka bhee uttr naheen diya, yahan tak ki hakim ko bada ashcharya hua.
aur haakim kee yah reeti thee, ki us pavrva men logon ke liye kisee aek bandhauae ko jise ve chahate the, chhod deta tha.
us samay baraabba nam unheen men ka ek namee bandhaua tha.
so jab ve ikatthe hua, to peelatus ne un se kaha tum kis ko chahate ho, ki maain tumhare liye chhod doon? baraabba ko, ya yeeshu ko jo maseeh kahalata haai?
kyonaki vah janata tha ki unhon ne use dah se pakadvaya haai.
jab vah nyay kee gaee par baaitta hua tha to us kee patnee ne use kahala bheja, ki too us dharmee ke mamale men hath n dalana kyonki maain ne aj svapn men usake karan bahut dukh uttaya haai.
mahayajakon aur puraniyon ne logon ko ubhara, ki ve baraabba ko mang le, aur yeeshu ko nash karaaen.
haakim ne un se poochha, ki in donon men se kis ko chahate ho, ki tumhare liye chhod doon? unhon ne kaha baraabba ko.
