unhon ne pitt milaya hua dakhras use peene ko diya, parantu us ne chakhkar peena n chaha.
tab unhon ne use kroos par chaddhaya aur chitthiyan dalakar usake kapade bantt liae.
aur vahan baaittkar usaka pahara dene lage.
aur usaka doshapatra, usake sir ke upar lagaya, ki yah yahoodiyon ka raja yeeshu haai.
aur yah kahate the, ki he mandair ke ddhanevale aur teen din men bananevale, apane ap ko to bacha yaadi too parameshvar ka putra haai, to kroos par se utar a.
