isee prakar dakoo bhee jo usake sath krooson par chaddhaae gaae the us kee ninda karate the..
dopahar se lekar teesare pahar tak us sare desh men andhora chhaya raha.
teesare pahar ke nikatt yeeshu ne bade shabd se pukarakar kaha, aelee, aelee, lama shabaktanee? arthata he mere parameshvar, he mere parameshvar, too ne mujhe kyon chhod diya?
jo vahan khde the, un men se kitanon ne yah sunakar kaha, vah to aeliyyah ko pukarata haai.
un men se ek turant dauda, aur spanj lekar sirake men duboya, aur sarakande par rakhkar use chusaya.
