isaliye khet ke svamee se binatee karo ki vah apane khet kattne ke liye majadoor bhej de..
fir vah vahan se uttkar yahoodiya ke sivanon men aur yaradan ke par aya, aur bheed usake pas fir ikatthee ho gai, aur vah apanee reeati ke anusar unhen fir upadesh dene laga.
tab fareesiyon ne usake pas akar us kee pareeksha karane ko us se poochha, kya yah uchit haai, ki puroosh apanee patnee ko tyage?
