yeeshu ne charon aur dekhkar apane chelon se kaha, dhanavanon ko parameshvar ke rajy men pravesh karana kaaisa kaattnai haai!
chele us kee baton se achambhiat hua, is par yeeshu ne fir un ko uttr diya, he balako, jo dhan par bhrosa rakhte haai, un ke liye parameshvar ke rajy men pravesh karana kaaisa kattnai haai!
ve bahut hee chakit hokar apas men kahane lage to fir kis ka uddhar ho sakata haai.
yeeshu ne un kee or dekhkar kaha, manushyon se to yah naheen ho sakata, parantu parameshvar se ho sakata haai kyonaki parameshvar se sab kuchh ho sakata haai.
pataras us se kahane laga, ki dek, ham to sab kuchh chhodkar tere peechhe ho liye haain.
yeeshu ne kaha, maain tum se sach kahata hoo, ki aeesa koi nahee, jis ne mere aur susamachar ke liye ghar ya bhaiyon ya baahinon ya mata ya pita ya ladke-balon ya kheton ko chhod diya ho.
aur ab is samay sau guna n paa, gharon aur bhaiyon aur baahinon aur mataon aur ladke-balon aur kheton ko par upadrav ke sath aur paralok men anant jeevana.
par bahutere jo pahile haai, pichhle honge aur jo pichhle haai, ve pahile honge.
aur ve yarooshalem ko jate huae marga men the, aur yeeshu un ke age age ja raha tha: aur ve achambha karane lage aur jo usake peechhe peechhe chalate the drane lage, tab vah fir un barahon ko lekar un se ve baten kahane laga, jo us par anevalee theen.
ki dekho, ham yarooshalem ko jate haai, aur manushy ka putra mahayajakon aur shaastriayon ke hath pakadvaya jaaega, aur ve us ko ghaat ke yogy ttharaaenge, aur anyajatiyon ke hath men saunpenge.
tab jabadee ke putra yakoob aur yoohanna ne usake pas akar kaha, he guro, ham chahate haai, ki jo kuchh ham tujh se mange, vahee too hamare liye kare.
us ne un se kaha, tum kya chahate ho ki maain tumhare liye karoon?
unhon ne us se kaha, ki hamen yah de, ki teree maahima men ham men se ek tere dahine aur doosara tere banae baaitte.
yeeshu n un se kaha, tum naheen janate, ki kya mangate ho? jo kattora maain peene par hoo, kya pee sakate ho? aur jo bapatisma maain lene par hoo, kya le sakate ho?
unhon ne us se kaha, ham se ho sakata haai: yeeshu ne un se kaha: jo kattora maain peene par hoo, tum peeonge aur jo bapatisma maain lene par hoo, use loge.
par jin ke liye taaiyar kiya gaya haai, unhen chhod aur kisee ko apane daahine aur apane baaen bittana mera kam naheen.
yah sunakar dason yakoob aur yoohanna par risiyane lage.
aur yeeshu ne un ko pas bula kar un se kaha, tum janate ho, ki jo anyajaatiyon ke haakim samajhe jate haai, ve un par prabhuta karate haain aur un men jo baden haai, un par adhaikar jatate haain.
par tum men aeesa naheen haai, baran jo koi tum men bada hona chahe vah tumhara sevak bane.
aur jo koi tum men pradhaan hona chahe, vah sab ka das bane.
kyonaki manushy ka putra isaliye naheen aya, ki us kee seva ahal kee jaa, par isaaliye aya, ki ap seva tthal kare, aur bahuton kee chhudautee ke liye apana praan de..
