is par yeeshu ne us se kaha too kya chahata haai ki maain tere liye karoon? andho ne us se kaha, he rabbee, yah ki maain dekhne lagoon.
yeeshu ne us se kaha chala ja, tere vishvas ne tujhe changa kar diya haai: aur vah turant dekhne laga, aur marga men usake peechhe ho liya..
jab ve yarooshalem ke nikatt jaaitoon pahad par baaitafage aur baaitaniyyah ke pas aa, to us ne apane chelon men se do ko yah kahakar bheja.
