aur bahuton ne apane kapade marga men bichhaae aur auron ne kheton men se daaliyan katt katt kar faaila deen.
aur jo usake age age jate aur peechhe peechhe chale ate the, pukar pukar kar kahate jate the, ki hoshaana dhany haai vah jo prabhu ke nam se ata haai.
hamare pita daud ka rajy jo a raha haai dhany haai: akash men hoshaana..
aur vah yarooshalem pahunchakar mandair men aya, aur charon or sab vastuon ko dekhkar barahon ke sath baaitaaniyyah gaya kyonaki sanjh ho gai thee..
