maain tum se sach kahata hoon ki jo koi is pahad se kahe ki too ukhd ja, aur samudra men ja pad, aur apane man men sandeh n kare, varan prateeti kare, ki jo kahata hoon vah ho jaaega, to usake liye vahee hoga.
isaliye maain tum se kahata hoo, ki jo kuchh tum praarthna karake mangon to prateeti kar lo ki tumhen mil gaya, aur tumhare liye ho jaaega.
