parameshvar mare huon ka nahee, varan jeevaton ka parameshvar haai: so tum badee bool men pade ho..
aur shaastriayon men se aek ne akar unhen vivad karate suna, aur yah janakar ki us ne unhen achchhee reeti se uttr diya us se poochha, sab se mukhy agyaa kaun see haai?
