shaasree ne us se kaha he guro, bahut tteeka! too ne sach kaha, ki vah aek hee haai, aur use chhod aur koi naheen.
aur us se sare man aur saree buaddh iddh aur sare praan aur saree shaktai ke sath praem rakhna aur padosee se apane saman praem rakhna, sare homon aur balidanon se baddhkar haai.
jab yeeshu ne dekha ki us ne samajh se uttr diya, to us se kaha too parameshvar ke rajy se door naheen: aur kisee ko fir us se kuchh poochhne ka sahas n hua..
fir yeeshu ne maandair men upadesh karate huae yah kaha, ki shaasree kyonkar kahate haai, ki maseeh daud ka putra haai?
daud ne apahee pavitra atma men hokar kaha haai, ki prabhu ne mere prabhu se kaha mere daahine baait, jab tak ki maain tere baaiariyon ko tere panvon kee peeddhee n kar doon.
daud to ap hee use prabhu kahata haai, fir vah usaka putra kahan se tthara? aur bheed ke log us kee anand se sunate the..
us ne apane upadesh men un se kaha, shaastriayon se chaukas raho, jo lambe vasr paahine huae firana.
