kyonaki manushy ka putra to, jaaisa usake vishay men likha haai, jata hee haai parantu us manushy par hay jis ke dara manushy ka putra pakadvaya jata haai! yadi us manushy ka janm hee n hotakh to usake liye bhla hota..
