yoohanna aya, jo jangal men bapatisma deta, aur papon kee kshama ke liye manafirav ke bapatisma ka prachar karata tha.
aur sare yahoodiya desh ke, aur yarooshalem ke sab rahanevale nikalakar usake pas gaa, aur apane papon ko manakar yaradan nadee men us se bapaatisma liya.
yoohanna untt ke rom ka vasr pahine aur apanee kamar men chamaden ka pattuka bandho rahata tha or ttiiddayan aur van madha khaya karata tha.
aur yah prachar karata tha, ki mere bad vah ane vala haai, jo mujh se shaktaiman haai maain is yogy naheen ki jhukakar usake jooton ka bandha kholoon.
maain ne to tumhen panee se bapatisma diya haai par vah tumhen paavitra atma se bapatisma dega..
un dinon men yeeshu ne galeel ke nasarat se akar, yaradan men yoohanna se bapaatisma liya.
aur jab vah panee se nikalakar upar aya, to turant us ne akash ko khulate aur atma ko kabootar kee nain apane upar utarate dekha.
aur yah akashavanee hai, ki too mera piry putra haai, tujh se maain prasann hoon..
tab atma ne turant us ko jangal kee or bheja.
aur jangal men chalees din tak shautan ne us kee pareeksha kee aur vah van pashuuon ke sath raha aur svargadoot un kee seva karate rahe..
yoohanna ke pakadvaae jane ke bad yeeshu ne galeel men akar parameshvar ke rajy ka susamachar prachar kiya.
aur kaha, samay poora hua haai, aur parameshvar ka rajy nikatt a gaya haai man firao aur susamachar par vishvas karo..
galeel kee jheel ke kinare kinare jate hua, us ne shamaun aur usake bhai aandairyas ko jheel men jal dalate dekha kyonaki ve machhuve the.
aur yeeshu ne un se kaha mere peechhe chale ao maain tum ko manushyon ke machhuve banaunga.
ve turant jalon ko chhodkar usake peechhe ho liae.
aur kuchh age baddhkar, us ne jabadee ke putra yakoob, aur usake bhai yahoonna ko, nav par jalon ko sudhaarate dekha.
aur ve kafaranahoom men aa, aur vah turant sabt ke din sabha ke ghar men jakar upadesh karane laga.
aur log usake upadesh se chakit hue kyonki vah unhen shaaastriayon kee nain nahee, parantu aadhaikaree kee nai upadesh deta tha.
aur usee samay, un kee sabha ke ghar men aek manushy tha, jis men aek ashuuddh atma thee.
us ne chillakar kaha, he yeeshu nasaree, hamen tujh se kya kama? kya too hamen nash karane aya haai? maain tujhe janata hoo, too kaun haai? parameshvar ka paavitra jana!
yeeshu ne use danttkar kaha, chup raha aur us men se nikal ja.
tab ashuuddh atma us ko marodkar, aur bade shabd se chillakar us men se nikal gai.
is par sab log ashcharya karate huae apas men vada-vivad karane lage ki yah kya bat haai? yah to koi naya upadesh haai! vah adhaikar ke sath ashuuddh atmaon ko bhee agyaa deta haai, aur ve us kee agyaa manatee haain.
so usaka nam turant galeel ke as pas ke sare desh men har jagah faail gaya..
aur shamaun kee sas jvar se peeadit thee, aur unhon ne turant usake vishay men us se kaha.
tab us ne pas jakar usaka hath pakad ke use uttaya aur usaka jvar us par se utar gaya, aur vah un kee seva-tthal karane lagee..
sandhya ke samay jab soorya oob gaya to log sab beemaron ko aur unhen jin men dushttatma bheen usake pas laae.
aur sara nagar dar par ikattha hua.
aur us ne bahuton ko jo nana prakar kee beemariyon se dukhee the, changa kiya aur bahut se dushttatmaon ko nikala aur dushttatmaon ko bolane n diya, kyonaki ve use pahachanatee theen..
aur bhor ko din nikalane se bahut pahile, vah uttkar nikala, aur aek jangalee sthan men gaya aur vahan praarthna karane laga.
tab shamaun aur usake sathee us kee khoj men gaae.
jab vah mila, to us se kaha ki sab log tujhe ddoonddh rahe haain.
us n un se kaha, ao ham or kaheen as pas kee baastaiyon men jae, ki maain vahan bhee prachar karoo, kyonki maai. isee liye nikala hoon.
so vah sare galeel men un kee sabhaon men ja jakar prachar karata aur dushttatmaon ko nikalata raha..
aur aek koddhee ne usake pas akar, us se binatee kee, aur usake samhane ghauttne ttekakar, us se kaha yadi too chahe to mujhe shuuddh kar sakata haai.
us ne us par taras khakar hath baddhaya, aur use chookar kaha maain chahata hoon too shuuddh ho ja.
aur turant usaka koddh jata raha, aur vah shuuddh ho gaya.
tab us ne use chitakar turant vida kiya.
aur us se kaha, dek, kisee se kuchh mat kahana, parantu jakar apane ap ko yajak ko dikha, aur apane shuuddh hone ke vishay men jo kuchh moosa ne ttharaya haai use bhentt chaddha, ki un par gavahee ho.
parantu vah bahar jakar is bat ko bahut prachar karane aur yahan tak faailane laga, ki yeeshu fir khullamakhulla nagar men n ja saka, parantu bahar jangalee sthanon men raha aushra chahunor se lage usake pas ate rahe..
kai din ke bad vah fir kafaranahoom men aya aur suna gaya, ki vah ghar men haai.
fir itane log ikatthe hua, ki dar ke pas bhee jagah naheen milee aur vah unhen vachan suna raha tha.
aur log aek jhole ke mare huae ko char manushyon se uttvakar usake pas le aae.
parantu jab ve bheed ke karan usake nikatt n panhuch sake, to unhon ne us chht ko jis ke neeche vah tha, khol diya aur jab use udhod chuke, to us khatt ko jis par jhole ka mara hua pada tha, lattka diya.
yeeshu n, un ka vishvas dekhkar, us jhole ke mare huae se kaha he putra, tere pap kshama hue.
ki yah manushy kyon aeesa kahata haai? yah to parameshvar kee ninda karata haai, parameshvar ko chhod aur kon pap kshama kar sakata haai?
yeeshu ne turant apanee atma men jan liya, ki ve apane apane man men aeesa vichar kar rahe haai, aur un se kaha, tum apane apane man men yah vichar kyon kar rahe ho?
sahaj kya haai? kya jhole ke mare se yah kahata ki tere pap kshama hua, ya yah kahana, ki utt apanee khatt utta kar chal fira?
parantu jis se tum jan lo ki manushy ke putra ko prathvee par pap kshama karane ka bhee adhaikar haai us ne us jhole ke mare huae se kaha.
maain tujh se kahata hoon ut, apanee khatt uttakar apane ghar chala ja.
aur vah utta, aur turant khatt uttakar aur sab ke samhane se nikalakar chala gaya, is par sab chaakit hua, aur parameshvar kee badai karake kahane lage, ki ham ne aeesa kabhee naheen dekha..
vah fir nikalakar jheel ke kinare gaya, aur saree bheed usake pas ai, aur vah unhen upadesh dene laga.
aur vah uttkar, usake peechhe ho liya: aur vah usake ghar men bhojan karane baaitte kyonki ve bahut se the, aur usake peechhe ho liye the.
aur shaastriayon aur fareeasiyon ne yah dekhkar, ki vah to papiyon aur chungee lenevalon ke sath bhojan kar raha haai, usak chelon se kaha vah to chungee lenevalon aur paapiyon ke sath khata pita haai!!
yeeshu ne yah sunakar, un se kaha, bhle changon ko vaaidh kee avashyakata nahee, parantu beemaron ko haai: maain dhaarmiyon ko nahee, parantu paapiyon ko bulane aya hoon..
yoohanna ke chele, aur fareesee upavas karate the so unhon ne akar us se yah kaha ki yoohanna ke chele aur fareeasiyon ke chele kyon upavas rakhte haain? parantu tere chele upavas naheen rakhte.
yeeshu ne un se kaha, jab tak dulha baratiyon ke sath dahata haai kya ve upavas kar sakate haain? so jab tak doolha un ke sath haai, tab tak ve upavas naheen kar sakate.
parantu ve din aaenge, ki doolha un se alag kiya jaaega us samay ve upavas karenge.
kore kapade ka paaiband purane pahiravan par koi naheen lagata naheen to vah paaiband us men se kuchh kheench lega, arthata naya, purane se, aur vah aur fatt jaaega.
naye dakhras ko puranee mashakon men koi naheen rakhta, naheen to dakhras mashkon ko faad dega, aur dakhras aur mashken donon nashtt ho jaaengee parantu dakh ka naya ras nai mashkon men bhra jata haai..
aur aeesa hua ki vah sabt ke din kheton men se hokar ja raha tha aur usake chele chalate huae balen todne lage.
tab fareesiyon ne us se kaha, dekh ye sabt ke din vah kam kyon karate haain jo uchit naheen?
us ne un se kaha, kya tum ne kabhee naheen paddha, ki jab daud ko avashyakata hui aur jab vah aur usake sathee bookhe hua, tab us ne kya kiya tha?
us ne kyonkar abiyatar mahayajak ke samay, parameshvar ke bhvan men jakar, bhentt kee rottyaian khai, jisaka khana yajakon ko chhod aur kisee ko bhee uchit nahee, aur apane sathaiyon ko bhee deen?
aur us ne un se kaha sabt ka din manushy ke liye banaya gaya haai, n ki manushy sabt ke din ke liye.
isaliye manushy ka putra sabt ke din ka bhee svamee haai..
aur vah aradhanalay men fir gaya aur vahan aek manushy tha, jas ka hath sookh gaya tha.
aur ve us par dosh lagane ke liye us kee ghaat men lage huae the, ki dekhe, vah sabt ke din men use changa karata haai ki naheen.
us ne sookhe hathvale manushy se kaha beech men khda ho.
aur un se kaha kya sabt ke din bhla karana uchit haai ya bura karata, praan ko bachana ya marana? par ve chup rahe.
aur us ne un ke man kee kattorata se udas hokar, un ko krodha se charon or dekha, aur us manushy se kaha, apana hath baddha us ne baddhaya, aur usaka hath achchha ho gaya.
tab fareesee bahar jakar turant herodiyon ke sath usake virodha men sammati karane lage, ki use kis prakar nash karen..
aur yeeshu apane chelon ke sath jheel kee or chala gaya: aur galeel se aek badee bheed usake peechhe ho lee.
aur yahoodiya, aur yarooshalem aur idoomiya se, aur yaradan ke par, aur soor aur saaida ke asapas se aek badee bheed yah sunakar, ki vah kaaise achambhe ke kam karata haai, usake pas ai.
kyonaki us ne bahuton ko changa kiya tha isaliye jitane loge rog se graasit the, use choone ke liye us par gire padte the.
aur ashuuddh atmanae bhee, jab use dekhtee thee, to usake age gir padtee thee, aur chillakar kahatee theen ki too parameshvar ka putra haai.
aur us ne unhen bahut chitaya, ki mujhe pragatt n karana..
fir vah pahad par chaddh gaya, aur jinhen vah chahata tha unhen apane pas bulaya aur ve usake pas chale aae.
tab us ne barah purooshaen ko niyukt kiya, ki ve usake sath sath rahe, aur vah unhen bheje, ki prachar karen.
aur dushttatmaon ke nikalane ka aadhaikar rakhen.
aur jabadee ka putra yakoob, aur yakoob ka bhai yoohanna, jinaka nam us ne booanaragis, arthata garjan ke putra rakha.
aur aandairyas, aur filippus, aur baratulmaai, aur mattee, aur thoma, aur halafai ka putra yakooba aur taee, aur shamaun kananee.
aur yahooda iskariyotee, jis ne use pakadva bhee diya..
aur vah ghar men aya: aur aeesee bheed ikatthee ho gai, ki ve rottee bhee n kha sake.
jab usake kuttumbaiyon ne yah suna, to use pakadne ke liye nikale kyonki kahate the, ki usaka chitt ttkaiane naheen haai.
aur shaasree jo yarooshalem se aae the, yah kahate the, ki us men shautan haai, aur yah bhee, ki vah dushttatmaon ke saradar kee sahayata se dushttatmaon ko nikalata haai.
aur vah unhen pas bulakar, un se dushttanton men kahane laga shautan kyonkar shautan ko nikal sakata haai?
aur yaadi kisee rajy men foott pade, to vah rajy kyonkar sthiar rah sakata haai?
aur yaadi kisee ghar men foott pade, to vah ghar kyonkar sthiar rah sakega?
aur yaadi shautan apana hee virodhaee hokar apane men foott dale, to vah kyonkar bana rah sakata haai? usaka to ant hee ho jata haai.
kintu koi manushy kisee balavant ke ghar men ghausakar usaka mal loott naheen sakata, jab tak ki vah pahile us balavant ko n bandha le aur tab usake ghar ko loott lega.
maain tum se sach kahata hoo, ki manushyon kee santan ke sab pap aur ninda jo ve karate haai, kshama kee jaaegee.
parantu jo koi paavitraatma ke virooddh ninda kare, vah kabhee bhee kshama n kiya jaaega: varan vah anant pap ka aparadhaee ttharata haai.
kyonaki ve yah kahate the, ki us men ashuuddh atma haai..
aur us kee mata aur usake bhai aa, aur bahar khde hokar use bulava bheja.
aur bheed usake asapas baaittee thee, aur unhon ne us se kaha dek, teree mata aur tere bhai bahar tujhe ddoonddhte haain.
us ne unhen uttr diya, ki meree mata aur mere bhai kaun haain?
aur un par jo usake as pas baaitte the, draashtti karake kaha, dekho, meree mata aur mere bhai yah haain.
kyonaki jo koi parameshvar kee ichchha par chale, vahee mere bhai, aur baahin aur mata haai..
vah fir jheel ke kinare upadesh dene laga: aur aeesee badee bheed usake pas ikatthee ho gai, ki vah jheel men aek nav par chaddhkar baaitt gaya aur saree bheed boomi par jheel ke kinare khdee rahee.
aur vah unhen drashttanton men bahut see baten sikhane lage, aur apane upadesh men un se kaha.
suno: dekho, aek bonevala, beej bane ke liye nikala!
aur bote samay kuchh to marga ke kinare gira aur paakshiayon ne akar use chug liya.
aur jab soorya nikala, to jal gaya, aur jad n pakadne ke karan sookh gaya.
aur kuchh to jhaadiyon men gira, aur jhaadiyon ne baddhkar use daba liya, aur vah fal n laya.
parantu kuchh achchhee boomi par gira aur vah uga, aur baddhkar falavant hua aur koi tees guna, koi satt guna aur koi sau guna fal laya.
aur us ne kaha jis ke pas sunane ke liye kan hon vah sun le..
jab vah akela rah gaya, to usake sathaiyon ne un barah samet us se in drashttanton ke vishay men poochha.
isaliye ki ve dekhte huae dekhen aur unhen sujhai n pade aur sunate huae sunen bhee aur n samajhen aeesa n ho ki ve fire, aur kshama kiae jaaen.
fir us ne un se kaha kya tum yah drashttant naheen samajhte? to fir aur sab drashttanton ko kyonkar samajhoge?
banevala vachan bota haai.
jo marga ke kinare ke haain jahan vachan boya jata haai, ye ve haai, ki jab unhon ne suna, to shautan turant akar vachan ko jo un men boya gaya tha, utta le jata haai.
aur vaaise hee jo patthreelee boomi par boae jate haai, ye ve haai, ki jo vachan ko sunakar turant anand se grahan kar lete haain.
parantu apane bheetar jad n rakhte ke karan ve thode bhee dinon ke liye rahate haain is ke bad jab vachan ke karan un par klesh ya upadrav hota haai, to ve turant ttokar khate haain.
aur jo jhaadyaien men boae gaae ye ve haain jinhon ne vachan suna.
aur sansar kee chinta, aur dhan ka dhaekha, aur aur vastuon ka lobh un men samakar vachan ko daba deta haai. aur vah nishfal rah jata haai.
aur jo achchhee boomi men boae gaa, ye ve haai, jo vachan sunakar grahan karate aur fal late haai, koi tees guna, koi satt guna, aur koi sau guna..
aur us ne un se kaha kya diye ko isaliye late haain ki paaimane ya khatt ke niche rakha jaae? kya isaliye nahee, ki deevatt par rakha jaae?
kyonaki koi vastu chhpaiee nahee, parantu isaliye ki pragatt ho jaae
aur n kuchh gupt haai par isaliye ki pragatt ho jaae. yaadi kisee ke sunane ke kan ho, to sun le.
fir us ne un se kaha chaukas raho, ki kya sunate ho? jis nap se tum napate ho usee se tumhare liye bhee napa jaaega, aur tum ko aadhaik diy jaaega.
kyonaki jis ke pas haai, us ko diya jaaega parantu jis ke pas naheen haai us se vah bhee jo usake pas haai le liya jaaega..
fir us ne kaha parameshvar ka rajay aeesa haai, jaaise koi manushy boomi par beej chheentte.
aur rat ko soa, aur din ko jage aur vah beech aeese uge aur baddhe ki vah n jane.
prathvee ap se ap fal latee haai pali ankur, tab bal, aur tab balon men taaiyar dana.
parantu jab dana pak jata haai, tab vah turant hansiya lagata haai, kyonki kattnee a pahunchee haai..
fir us ne kaha, ham parameshvar ke rajy kee upama kis se de, aur kis drashttant se usaka varnn karen?
vah rai ke dane ke saman haain ki jab boomi men boya jata haai to boomi ke sab beejon se chhotta hota haai.
parantu jab boya gaya, to ugakar sab sag pat se bada ho jata haai, aur usakee aeesee badee daaliyan nikalatee haai, ki akash ke pakshaee usakee chhaya men basera kar sakate haain..
aur vah unhen is prakar ke bahut se drashttant de dekar un kee samajh ke anusar vachan sunata tha.
aur bina drashttant kahe un se kuchh bhee naheen kahata tha parantu aekant men vah apane nij chelon ko sab baton ka arth batata tha..
usee din jab sanjh hui, to us ne un se kaha ao, ham par chale,.
tab badee andhaee ai, aur laharen nav par yahan tak lagee, ki vah ab panee se bhree jatee thee.
aur vah ap pichhle bhag men gaee par so raha tha tab unhon ne use jagakar us se kaha he guro, kya tujhe chinta nahee, ki ham nash huae jate haain?
tab us ne uttkar andhaee ko dantta, aur panee se kaha shaant rah, thm ja : aur andhaee thm gai aur bada chaain ho gaya.
aur un se kaha tum kyon drate ho? kya tumhen ab tak vishvas naheen?
aur ve jheel ke par giraseniyon ke desh men pahunche.
aur jab vah nav par se utara to turant aek manushy jis men ashuuddh atma thee kabraen se nikalakar use mila.
vah kabraen men raha karata tha. aur koi use sankalon se bhee n bandha sakata tha.
kyonaki vah bar bar bediyon aur sankalon se bandha gaya tha, par us ne sakalon ko tod diya, aur beadiyon ke ttukade ttukade kar diae the, aur koi use vash men naheen kar sakata tha.
vah lagatar rata-adin kabraen aur pahado men chillata, aur apane ko patthron se ghaayal karata tha.
vah yeeshu ko door hee se dekhkar dauda, aur use pranam kiya.
aur unche shabd se chillakar kaha he yeeshu, paramapradhaan parameshvar ke putra, mujhe tujh se kya kama? maain tune parameshvar kee shapath deta hoo, ki mujhe peeda n de.
kyonaki us ne us se kaha tha, he ashuuddh atma, is manushy men se nikal a.
us ne us se poochha tera kaya nam haai? us ne us se kaha mera nam sena haai kyonki ham bahut haain.
aur us ne us se bahut binatee kee, hamen is desh se bahar n bheja.
vahan pahad par sooaron ka aek bada jhund char raha tha.
aur unhon ne us se binatee karake kaha, ki hamen un sooaron men bhej de, ki ham un ke bheetar jaaen.
so us ne unhen agyaa dee aur ashuuddh atma nikalakar sooaron ke bheetar paaitt gai aur jhun, jo koi do hajar ka tha, kadade par se jhpattkar jheel men ja pada, aur oob mara.
aur un ke charavahon ne bhagakar nagar aur ganvon men samachar sunaya.
aur jo hua tha, log use dekhne aae. aur yeeshu ke pas akar, ve us men sena samai thee, kapade paahine aur sachet baaitte dekhkar, dr gaae.
aur dekhnevalon ne usaka jis men dushttatmaaen thee, aur sooaron ka poora hal, un ko kah sunaya.
aur ve us se binatee kar ke kahane lage, ki hamare sivanon se chala ja.
aur jab vah nav par chaddhne laga, to vah jis men pahile dushttatmaaen thee, us se binatee karane laga, ki mujhe apane sath rahane de.
parantu us ne use agyaa n dee, aur us se kaha, apane ghar jakar apane logon ko bata, ki tujh par daya karake prabhu ne tere liye kaaise bade kam kiae haain.
vah jakar dikapulis men is bat ka prachar karane laga, ki yeeshu ne mere liye kaaise bade kam kiae aur sab achambha karate the..
jab yeeshu fir nav se par gaya, to aek badee bheed usake pas ikatthee ho gai aur vah jheel ke kinare tha.
aur yair nam aradhanalay ke saradaron men se aek aya, aur use dekhkar, usake panvon par gira.
aur us ne yah kahakar bahut binatee kee, ki meree chhottee bettee marane par haai: too akar us par hath rak, ki vah changee hokar jeeavit rahe.
tab vah usake sath chala aur badee bheed usake peede ho lee, yahan tak ki log us par gire padte the..
aur aek sre, jis ko barah varsha se lohoo bahane ka rog tha.
yeeshu kee charcha sunakar, bheed men usake peechhe se ai, aur usake vasr ko choo liya.
kyonaki vah kahatee thee, yadi maain usake vasr hee ko choo loongee, to changee ho jaungaha.
aur turant usaka lohoo bahana band ho gaya aur us ne apanee deh men jan liya, ki maain us beemaree se achchhee ho gai.
usake chelon ne us se kaha too dekhta haai, ki bheed tujh par giree padtee haai, aur too kahata haai ki kis ne mujhe chhua?
tab us ne use dekhne ke liye jis ne yah kam kiya tha, charon or drashtti kee.
tab vah sree yah janakar, ki meree kaaisee bhlai hui haai, dratee aur kanpatee hui ai, aur usake panvon par girakar, us se sab hal sach sach kah diya.
us ne us se kaha putraee tere vishvas ne tujhe changa kiya haai: kushal se ja, aur apanee is beemaree se bachee raha..
vah yah kah hee raha tha, ki aradhanalay ke saradar ke ghar se logon ne akar kaha, ki teree bettee to mar gai ab guroo ko kyon dukh deta haai?
jo bat ve kah rahe the, us ko yeeshu ne anasunee karake, aradhanalay ke saradar se kaha mat dra keval vishvas rakh.
aur us ne pataras aur yakoob aur yakoob ke bhai yoohanna ko chhod, aur kisee ko apane sath ane n diya.
aur aradhanalay ke saradar ke ghar men pahunchakar, us ne logon ko bahut rote aur chillate dekha.
tab us ne bheetar jakar us se kaha, tum kyon halla machate aur rote ho? ladkee maree nahee, parantu so rahee haai.
ve us kee hansee karane lage, parantu us ne sab ko nikalakar ladkee ke matapita aur apane saathaiyon ko lekar, bheetar janha ladkee padee thee, gaya.
aur ladkee ka hath pakadkar us se kaha, 'taleeta koomeen jis ka arth yah haai ki 'he ladkee, maain tujh se kahata hoo, uttn.
aur ladkee turant uttkar chalane firane lagee kyonaki vah barah varsha kee thee. aur is par log bahut chaakit ho gaae.
