kyonaki har aek jan ag se namakeen kiya jaaega.
namak achchha haai, par yaadi namak kee namakeenee jatee rahe, to use kis se svaadit karoge? apane men namak rakho, aur apas men mel milap se raho..
aur in baton ke bad prabhu ne sattr aur manushy niyukt kiae aur jis jis nagar aur jagah ko vah ap jane par tha, vahan unhen do do karake apane age bheja.
aur us ne un se kaha pakke khet bahut haain parantu majadoor thode haain: isaliye khet ke svamee se binatee karo, ki vah apane khet kattne ko majadoor bhej de.
jao dekhon maain tumhen bhedon kee nain bheadyaien ke beech men bhejata hoon.
isaliye n battua, n jholee, n joote lo aur n marga men kisee ko namaskar karo.
jis kisee ghar men jao, pahile kaho, ki is ghar par kalyan ho.
yaadi vahan koi kalyan ke yogy hoga to tumhara kalyan us par ttharega, naheen to tumhare pas lautt aaega.
usee ghar men raho, aur jo kuchh un se mile, vahee khao peeo, kyonki majadoor ko apanee majadooree milanee chahie: ghar ghar n firana.
aur jis nagar men jao, aur vahan ke log tumhen utare, to to kuchh tumhare samhane rakha jaae vahee khao.
vahan ke beemaron ko changa karo: aur un se kaho, ki parameshvar ka rajy tumhare nikatt a pahuncha haai.
parantu jis nagar men jao, aur vahan ke log tumhen grahan n kare, to usake bajaron men jakar kaho.
ki tumhare nagar kee dhool bhee, jo hamare panvon men lagee haai, ham tumhare samhane jhad dete haai, taubhee yah jan lo, ki parameshvar ka rajy tumhare nikatt a pahuncha haai.
maain tum se kahata hoo, ki us din us nagar kee dasha se sadom kee dasha sahane yogy hogee.
hay khurajeen ! hay baaitasaaida ! jo samarth ke kam tum men kiae gaa, yaadi ve soor aur saaida men kiae jate, to ttatt oddhkar aur rakh men baaittkar ve kab ke man firate.
parantu nyay ke din tumharee dasha se soor aur saaida kee dasha sahane yogy hogee.
aur he kafaranahoom, kya too svarga tak uncha kiya jaaega? too to adhaelok tak neeche jaaega.
jo tumharee sunata haai, vah meree sunata haai, aur jo tumhen tuchchh janata haai, vah mujhe tuchchh janata haai aur jo mujhe tuchchh janata haai, vah mere bhejanevale ko tuchchh janata haai.
us ne un se kaha maain shautan ko bijalee kee nai svarga se gira hua dekh raha tha.
dekho, maaine tumhe sanpon aur bichchhuon ko raundane ka, aur shatra kee saree samarth par adhaikar diya haai aur kisee vastu se tumhen kuchh haani n hogee.
taubhee is se anaandait mat ho, ki atma tumhare vash men haai, parantu is se anandait ho ki tumhare nam svarga par likhe haain..
mere pita ne mujhe sab kuchh saunp diya haai aur koi naheen janata ki putra kaun haai keval pita aur pita kaun haai yah bhee koi naheen janata, keval putra ke aur vah jis par putra use prakatt karana chahe.
aur chelon kee or firakar nirale men kaha, dhany haain ve ankhe, jo ye bate jo tum dekhte ho dekhtee haain.
kyonaki maain tum se kahata hoo, ki bahut se bhavishyadvktaon aur rajaon ne chaha, ki jo baten tum dekhte ho dekhen par n dekheen aur jo baten tum sunate ho sune, par n suneen..
aur dekho, aek vyavasthapak utta aur yah kahakar, us kee pareeksha karane laga ki he guro, anant jeevan ka varis hone ke liye maain kya karoon?
us ne us se kaha ki vyavastha men kya likha haai? too kaaise paddhta haai?
us ne uttr diya, ki too prabhu apane parameshvar se apane sare man aur apane sare praan aur apanee saree shaaktai aur apanee saree buaddh ike sath praem rakh aur apane padosee se apane saman praem rakh.
us ne us se kaha, too ne tteek uttr diya haai, yahee kara: to too jeevit rahega.
parantu us ne apanee tain dharmee ttharane kee ichchha se yeeshu se poochha, to mera padosee kaun haai?
yeeshu ne uttr diya ki aek manushy yarooshalem se yareeho ko ja raha tha, ki dakuon ne ghorakar usake kapade utar lia, aur marapeettkar use adhamooa chhodkar chale gaae.
aur aeesa hua ki usee marga se aek yajak ja raha tha: parantu use dekh ke katarakar chala gaya.
isee reeti se aek levee us jagah par aya, vah bhee use dekh ke katarakar chala gaya.
parantu aek samaree yatraee vahan a nikala, aur use dekhkar taras khaya.
aur usake pas akar aur usake ghaavon par tel aur dakhras dalakar pattiyan bandhae, aur apanee savaree par chaddhakar saray men le gaya, aur us kee seva tthal kee.
doosare din us ne do dinar nikalakar bhattyaiare ko dia, aur kaha is kee seva tthal karana, aur jo kuchh tera aur lagega, vah maain lauttne par tujhe bhr doonga.
ab meree samajh men jo dakuon men ghair gaya tha, in teenon men se usaka padosee kaun tthara?
us ne kaha, vahee jis ne us par taras khaya: yeeshu ne us se kaha, ja, too bhee aeesa hee kara..
fir jab ve ja rahe the, to vah aee ganv men gaya, aur martha nam aek sree ne use apane ghar men utara.
aur maariyam nam us kee aek baahin thee vah prabhu ke panvon ke pas baaittkar usaka vachan sunatee thee.
par martha seva karate karate ghabara gai aur usake pas akar kahane lagee he prabhu, kya tujhe kuchh bhee soch naheen ki meree baahin ne mujhe seva karane ke liye akelee hee chhod diya haai? so us se kah, ki meree sahayata kare.
prabhu ne use uttr diya, martha, he martha too bahut baton ke liye chinta karatee aur ghabaratee haai.
parantu aek bat avashy haai, aur us uttm bhag ko mariyam ne chun liya haai: jo us se chheena n jaaega..
fir vah kisee jagah praarthna kar raha tha: aur jab vah praarthna kar chuka, to usake chelon men se aek ne us se kaha he prabhu, jaaise yoohanna ne apane chelon ko praarthna karana sikhlaya vaaise hee hamen bhee too sikha de.
us ne un se kaha jab tum praarthna karo, to kaho he pita, tera nam pavitra mana jaa, tera rajy ae.
hamaree din bhr kee rottee har din hamen diya kara.
aur hamare papon ko kshama kar, kyonki ham bhee apane har aek aparadhaee ko kshama karate haai, aur hamen pareeksha men n la..
kyonaki aek yatraee mitra mere pas aya haai, aur usake age rakhne ke liye mere pas kuchh naheen haai.
aur vah bheetar se uttr de, ki mujhe dukh n de ab to dar band haai, aur mere balak mere pas bichhaune par haai, isaaliye maain uttkar tujhe de naheen sakata?
maain tum se kahata hoo, yadi usaka mitra hone par bhee use uttkar n de, taubhee usake lajja chhodkar mangane ke karan use jitanee avashyakata ho utanee uttkar dega.
aur maain tum se kahata hoon ki mango, to tumhen diya jaaega ddoonddhon to tum paoge khttkhttao, to tumhare liye khola jaaega.
tum men se aeesa kaun pita hoga, ki jab usaka putra rottee mange, to use patthr de: ya machhlee mange, to machhlee ke badale use sanp de?
ya anda mange to use bichchoo de?
so jab tum bure hokar apane ladkebalon ko achchhee vastuaee dena janate ho, to svargeey pita apane manganevalon ko pavitra atma kyon n dega..
fir us ne aek goongee dushttatma ko nikala: jab dushttatma nikal gai, to goonga bolane laga aur logon ne achambha kiya.
parantu un men se kitanon ne kaha, yah to shautan nam dushttatmaon ke pradhaan kee sahayata se dushttatmaon ko nikalata haai.
auron ne us kee pareeksha karane ke liye us se akash ka aek chinh manga.
parantu us ne, un ke man kee baten janakar, un se kaha jis jis rajy men foott hotee haai, vah rajy ujad jata haai: aur jis ghar men foott hotee haai, vah nash ho jata haai.
aur yaadi shautan apana hee virodhaee ho jaa, to usaka rajy kyonkar bana rahega? kyonaki tum mere vishay men to kahate ho, ki yah shautan kee sahayata se dushttatma nikalata haai.
bhla yadi maain shautan kee sahayata se dushttatmaon ko nikalata hoo, to tumharee santan kis kee sahayata se nikalate haain? isaliye ve hee tumhara nyay chukaaenge.
parantu yadi maain parameshvar kee samarth se dushttatmaon ko nikalata hoo, to parameshvar ka rajy tumhare pas a pahuncha.
jab balavant manushy hathaiyar bandho huae apane ghar kee rakhvalee karata haai, to us kee sanpati bachee rahatee haai.
par jab us se baddhkar koi aur balavant chaddhai karake use jeet leta haai, to usake ve haathaiyar jin par usaka bhrosa tha, chheen leta haai aur us kee sanpaati loottkar bantt deta haai.
jo mere sath naheen battorata vah bithrata haai.
jab ashuuddh atma manushy men se nikal jatee haai to sookhee jagahon men vishraam ddoonddhtee firatee haai aur jab naheen patee to kahatee haai ki maain apane usee ghar men jahan se nikalee thee lautt jaungee.
aushra akar use jhada-buhara aur saja-sajaya patee haai.
tab vah akar apane se aur buree sat atmaon ko apane sath le atee haai, aur ve us men paaittkar vas karatee haai, aur us manushy kee pichhlee dasha paahile se bhee buree ho jatee haai..
jab vah ye baten kah hee raha tha to bheed men se kisee sree ne unche shabd se kaha, dhany vah garbh jis men too raha aur ve stan, jo too ne choose.
us ne kaha, han parantu dhany ve haai, jo parameshvar ka vachan sunate aur manate haain..
jab badee bheed ikatthee hotee jatee thee to vah kahane laga ki is yug ke log bure haain ve chinh ddoonddhte haain par yoonus ke chinh ko chhod koi aur chinh unhen n diya jaaega.
jaaisa yoonus neenave ke logon ke liye chinh tthara, vaaisa hee manushy ka putra bhee is yug ke logon ke liye ttharega.
daakkhian kee ranee nyay ke din is samay ke manushyon ke sath uttkar, unhen doshaee ttharaaegee, kyonaki vah sulaaiman ka gyaan sunane ko prathvee kee chhor se ai, aur dekho yahan vah haai jo sulaaiman se bhee bada haai.
neenave ke log nyay ke din is samay ke logon ke sath khde hokar, unhen doshaee ttharaaenge kyonaki unhon ne yoonus ka prachar sunakar man firaya aur dekho, yahan vah haai, jo yoonus se bhee bada haai..
koi manushy deeya bar ke talaghare me, ya paaimane ke neeche naheen rakhta, parantu deevatt par rakhta haai ki bheetar anevale ujiyala paaen.
tere shareer ka deeya teree ankh haai, isaliye jab teree ankh nirmal haai, to tera sara shareer bhee ujiyala haai parantu jab vah buree haai, to tera shareer bhee andhora haai.
isaliye yaadi tera sara shareer ujiyala ho, or usaka koi bhag andhora n rahe, to sab ka sab aeesa uliyala hoga, jaaisa us samay hota haai, jab deeya apanee chamak se tujhe ujala deta haai..
jab vah baten kar raha tha, to kisee fareesee ne us se binatee kee, ki mere yahan bhejan kara aur vah bheetar jakar bhojan karane baaitta.
fareesee ne yah dekhkar achambha diya ki us ne bhojan karane se paahile snan naheen kiya.
prabhu ne us se kaha, he fareesiyo, tum kattore aur thalee ko upar upar to manjate ho, parantu tumhare bheetar andhor aur dushttta bhree haai.
he nirbuaddhyaie, jis ne bahar ka bhag banaya, kya us ne bheetar ka bhag naheen banaya?
par he fareesiyo, tum par hay ! tum podeene aur sudab ka, aur sab bhanati ke saga-pat ka dasavan ansh dete ho, parantu nyay ko aur parameshvar ke praem ko ttal dete ho: chahiae to tha ki inhen bhee karate rahate aur unhen bhee n chhodte.
he fareesiyo, tum par hay ! tum aradhanalayon men mukhy mukhy asan aur bajaron men namaskar chahate ho.
hay tum par ! kyonki tum un chhpaiee kabraen ke saman ho, jin par log chalate haai, parantu naheen janate..
tab aek vyavasthapak ne us ko uttr diya, ki he guro, in baton ke kahane se too hamaree ninda karata haai.
us ne kaha he vyavasthapako, tum par bhee hay ! tum aeese bojh jin ko uttana kattnai haai, manushyon par ladate ho parantu tum ap un bojhon ko apanee ek ungalee se bhee naheen choote.
hay tum par ! tum un bhvishyadvktaon kee kabraen banate ho, jinhen tumhare bapa-dadon ne mar dala tha.
so tum gavah ho, aur apane bapa-dadon ke kamon men sammat ho kyonaki unhon ne to unhen mar dala aur tum un kee kabraen banate ho.
isaliye parameshvar kee buaddh ine bhee kaha haai, ki maain un ke pas bhavishyadvktaon aur praeariton ko bhejoongee: aur ve un men se kitanon ko mar dalenge, aur kitanon ko sataaenge.
taaki jitane bhvishyadvktaon ka lohoo jagat kee utpati se bahaya gaya haai, sab ka lekha, is yug ke logon se liya jaae.
habeel kee hatya se lekar jakarayah kee hatya tak jo vedee aur maandair ke beech men ghaat kiya gaya: maain tum se sach kahata hoon usaka lekha isee samay ke logon se liya jaaega.
hay tum vyavasthapakon par ! ki tum ne gyaan kee kunjee le to lee, parantu tum ne apahee pravesh naheen kiya, aur pravesh karanevalon ko bhee rok diya.
jab vah vahan se nikala, to shaasree aur fareesee bahut peechhe pad gaae aur chhedne lage, ki vah bahut see baton kee charcha kare.
aur us kee ghaat men lage rahe, ki usake munh kee koi bat pakaden..
itane men jab hajaron kee bheed lag gai, yahan tak ki aek doosare par gire padte the, to vah sab se paahile apane chelon se kahane laga, ki fareeasiyon ke kapattroopee khmeer se chaukas rahana.
kuchh ddhpa nahee, jo khola n jaaega aur n kuchh chhpai haai, jo jana n jaaega.
isaliye jo kuchh tum ne andhore men kaha haai, vah ujane men suna jaaega: aur jo tum ne kottariyon men kanon kan kaha haai, vah kotton par prachar kiya jaaega.
parantu maain tum se jo mere mitra ho kahata hoo, ki jo shareer ko ghaat karate haain parantu usake peechhe aur kuchh naheen kar sakate un se mat dro.
maain tumhen chitata hoon ki tumhen kis se drana chahia, ghaat karate ke bad jis ko narak men dalane ka aadhaikar haai, usee se dro : baran maain tum se kahata hoon usee se dro.
kya do paaise kee panch gauraaiyan naheen bikatee? taubhee parameshvar un men se aek ko bhee naheen boolata.
baran tumhare sir ke sab bal bhee gine huae haai, so dro nahee, tum bahut gauraaiyon se baddhkar ho.
maain tum se kahata hoon jo koi manushyon ke samhane mujhe man lega use manushy ka putra bhee parameshvar ke svargadooton ke samahane man lega.
parantu jo manushyon ke samhane mujhe inkar kare usaka parameshvar ke svargadooton ke samhane inkar kiya jaaega.
jo koi manushy ke putra ke virodha men koi bat kahe, usaka vah aparadha kshama kiya jaaega.
kyonaki pavitra atma usee ghadee tumhen sikha dega, ki kya kahana chaahiae..
fir bheed men se aek ne us se kaha, he guro, mere bhai se kah, ki pita kee sanpaati mujhe bantt de.
us ne us se kaha he manushy, kis ne mujhe tumhara nyayee ya banttnevala niyukt kiya haai?
aur us ne un se kaha, chaukas raho, aur har prakar ke lobh se apane ap ko bachaae rakho: kyonki kisee ka jeevan us kee sanpati kee bahutayat se naheen hota.
us ne un se ek drashttant kaha, ki kisee dhanavan kee boomi men badee upaj hui.
tab vah apane man men vichar karane laga, ki maain kya karoo, kyonki mere yahan jagah nahee, jahan apanee upaj ityadi rakoon.
aur vahan apana sab ann aur sanpaati rakoonga: aur apane praan se kahoonga, ki praa, tere pas bahut vasharen ke liye bahut sanpati rakhee haai chaain kar, kha, pee, sukh se raha.
parantu parameshvar ne us se kaha he moorkh, isee rat tera praan tujh se le liya jaaega: tab jo kuchh too ne ikattha kiya haai, vah kis ka hoga?
aeesa hee vah manushy bhee haai jo apane liye dhan battorata haai, parantu parameshvar kee drashtti men dhanee naheen..
fir us ne apane chelon se kaha isaaliye maain tum se kahata hoo, apane praan kee chinta n karo, ki ham kya khaaenge n apane shareer kee ki kya paahinenge.
kyonaki bhojan se praa, aur vasr se shareer baddhkar haai.
kauvon par dhyan do ve n bote haai, n kattte n un ke bhndar aur n khtta hota haai taubhee parameshvar unhen palata haai tumhara mooly paakshiayon se kaheen aadhaik haai.
tum men se aeesa kaun haai, jo chinta karane se apanee avastha men aeek ghadee bhee bada sakata haai?
isaliye yaadi tum sab se chhotta kam bhee naheen kar sakate, to aur baton ke liye kyon chinta karate ho?
sosanon ke pedon par dhyan karo ki ve kaaise baddhte haain ve n parishram karate, n katate haain: taubhee maain tum se kahata hoo, ki sulaaiman bhee, apane sare vibhv me, un men se kisee aek ke saman vasr paahine huae n tha.
isaliye yaadi parameshvar maaidan kee ghaas ko jo aj haai, aur kar bhad men jhonkee jaaegee, aeesa paahinata haai to he alp vishvasiyo, vah tumhen kyon n pahinaaega?
aur tum is bat kee khoj men n raho, ki kya khaaenge aur kya peeaenge, aur n sandeh karo.
kyonaki sansar kee jatiyan in sab vastuon kee khoj men rahatee haain: aur tumhara pita janata haai, ki tumhen in vastuon kee avashyakata haai.
parantu usake rajy kee khoj men raho, to ye vastuaeen bhee tumhen mil jaaengee.
he chhotte jhun, mat dra kyonaki tumhare pita ko yah bhaya haai, ki tumhen rajy de.
apanee sanpaati bechakar dan kar do aur apane liye aeese battuae banao, jo purane naheen hote, arthata svarga par aeesa dhan ikattha karo jo ghattta naheen aur jis ke nikatt chor naheen jata, aur keeda naheen bigadta.
kyonaki jahan tumhara dhan haai, vahan tumhara man bhee laga rahega..
tumharee kamaren bandhaee rahe, aur tumhare deeye jalate rahen.
aur tum un manushyon ke saman bano, jo apane svamee kee batt dekh rahe ho, ki vah byah se kab lauttega ki jab vah akar dar khttkhttaa, ate turant usake khol den.
dhany haain ve das, jinhen svamee akar jagate paae maain tum se sach kahata hoo, ki vah kamar bandha kar unhen bhojan karane ko baaittaaega, aur pas akar un kee seva karega.
yaadi vah rat ke doosare pahar ya teesare pahar men akar unhen jagate paa, to ve das dhany haain.
parantu tum yah jan rakho, ki yadi ghar ka svamee janata, ki chor kis ghadee aaega, to jagata rahata, aur apane ghar men sengha lagane n deta.
tum bhee taaiyar raho kyonki jis ghadee tum sochate bhee nahee, us ghadee manushy ka putra a javega.
prabhu ne kaha vah vishvasayogy aur buaddhmaian bhndaree kaun haai, jis ka svamee use naukar chakaron par saradar ttharaae ki unhen samay par seedha de.
dhany haai vah das, jise usaka svamee akar aeesa hee karate paae.
maain tum se sach kahata hoon vah use apanee sab sanpaati par saradar ttharaaega.
parantu yadi vah das sochane lage, ki mera svamee ane men der kar raha haai, aur dason aur daasiyon ko marane peettne aur khane peene aur piyakkad hone lage.
to us das ka svamee aeese din ki vah us kee batt jahata n rahe, aur aeesee ghadee jise vah janata n ho aaega, aur use bharee tadna dekar usaka bhag avishvasiyon ke sath ttharaaega.
aur vah das jo apane svamee kee ichchha janata tha, aur taaiyar n raha aur n us kee ichchha ke anusar chala bahut mar khaaega.
parantu jo naheen janakar mar khane ke yogy kam kare vah thodee mar khaaega, isaaliye jise bahut diya gaya haai, us se bahut manga jaaega, aur jise bahut saunpa gaya haai, us se bahut mangengen..
mujhe to aek bapaatisma leta haai aur jab tak vah n ho le tab tak maain kaaisee saketee men rahoonga?
kya tum samajhte ho ki maain prathvee par milap karane aya hoon? maain kahata hoon nahee, baran alag karane aya hoon.
kyonaki ab se aek ghar men panch jan apas men virodha rakhenge, teen do se do teen se.
pita putra se, aur putra pita se virodha rakhega man bettee se, aur bettee man se, sas bahoo se, aur bahoo sas se virodha rakhegee..
aur us ne bheed se bhee kaha, jab badal ko pachchhim se uttte dekhte ho, to turant kahate ho, ki vashara hogee aur aeesa hee hota haai.
aur jab daakkhiana chalatee dakhte ho to kahate ho, ki looh chalegee, aur aeesa hee hota haai.
he kapattyaie, tum dharatee aur akash ke roop men bhed kar sakate ho, parantu is yug ke vishay men kyon bhed karana naheen janate?
aur tum ap hee nirny kyon naheen kar lete, ki uchit kya haai?
jab too apane mui ke sath haakim ke pas ja raha haai, to marga hee men us se choottne ka yatn kar le aeesa n ho, ki vah tujhe nyayee ke pas kheench le jaa, aur nyayee tujhe pyade ko saunpe aur pyada tujhe bandeegrah men dal de.
maain tum se kahata hoo, ki jab tak too damadee damadee bhr n dega tab tak vahan se choottne n paaega..
us samay kuchh log a pahunche, aur us se un galeeliyon kee charcha karane lage, jin ka lohoo peelatus ne un hee ke baalidanon ke sath milaya tha.
yah sun us ne un se uttr men yah kaha, kya tum samajhte ho, ki ye galeelee, aur sab galeealiyon se papee the ki un par aeesee vipaati padee?
maain tum se kahata hoo, ki naheen parantu yaadi tum man n firaoge to tum sab bhee isee reeti se nash hoge.
ya kya tum samajhte ho, ki ve attarah jan jin par shaeeloh ka gummatt gira, aur ve dab kar mar gaae: yarooshalem ke aur sab rahanevalon se aadhaik aparadhaee the?
maain tum se kahata hoo, ki naheen parantu yaadi tum man n firaoge to tum bhee sab isee reeti se nash hoge.
fir us ne yah drashttant bhee kaha, ki kisee kee angoor kee baree men aek anjeer ka ped laga hua tha: vah us men fal ddoonddhne aya, parantu n paya.
tab us ne baree ke rakhvale se kaha, dekh teen varsha se maain is anjeer ke ped men fal ddoonddhne ata hoo, parantu naheen pata, ise katt dal ki yah boomi ko bhee kyon roke rahe.
us ne us ko uttr diya, ki he svamee, ise is varsha to aur rahane de ki maain is ke charo or khodakar khad daloon.
so age ko fale to bhla, naheen to use katt dalana.
sabt ke din vah aek aradhanalay men upadesh kar raha tha..
aur dekho, aek sree thee, jise attarah varsha se aek durbal karanevalee dushttatma lagee thee, aur vah kubadee ho gai thee, aur kisee reeati se seedhaee naheen ho sakatee thee.
tab us ne us par hath rakhe, aur vah turant seedhaee ho gai, aur parameshvar kee badai karane lagee.
isaliye ki yeeshu ne sabt ke din use achchha kiya tha, aradhanalay ka saradar risiyakar logon se kahane laga, chh: din haai, jin men kam karana chahia, so un hee dinon men akar change hoo parantu sabt ke din men naheen.
yah sun kar prabhu ne uttr dekar kaha he kapattyaie, kya sabt ke din tum men se har aek apane baail ya gadahe ko than se kholakar panee pilane naheen le jata?
aur kya uchit n tha, ki yah sree jo ibraaheem kee bettee haai jise shautan ne attarah varsha se bandha rakha tha, sabt ke din is bandhan se chhudai jatee?
jab us ne ye baten kahee, to usake sab virodhaee lajjait ho gaa, aur saree bheed un maahima ke kamon se jo vah karata tha, anaandait hui..
fir us ne kaha, parameshvar ka rajy kis ke saman haai? aur maain us kee upama kis se doon?
vah rai ke aek dane ke saman haai, jise kisee manushy ne lekar apanee baree men boya: aur vah baddhkar ped ho gaya aur akash ke paakshiayon ne us kee daliyon par basera kiya.
us ne fir kaha maain parameshvar ke rajy ki upama kis se doon?
vah nagar nagar, aur ganv ganv hokar upadesh karata hua yarooshalem kee or ja raha tha.
aur kisee ne us se poochha he prabhu, kya uddhar panevale thode haain?
us ne un se kaha saket dar se pravesh karane ka yatn karo, kyonaki maain tum se kahata hoo, ki bahutere pravesh karana chahenge, aur n kar sakenge.
jab ghar ka svamee uttkar dar band kar chuka ho, aur tum bahar khde huae dar khttkhttakar kahane lago, he prabhu, hamare liye khol de, aur vah uttr de ki maain tumhen naheen janata, tum kahan ke ho?
tab tum kahane lagoge, ki ham ne tere samhane khaya peeya aur too ne hamare bajaron men upadesh kiya.
parantu vah kahega, maain tum se kahata hoo, maain naheen janata tum kahan ke ho, he kukarma karanevalo, tum sab mujh se dur ho.
vahan rona aur dant peesana hoga: jab tum ibraaheem aur isahak aur yakoob aur sab bhvishyadvktaon ko parameshvar ke rajy men baaitte, aur apane ap ko bahar nikale huae dekhoge.
aur poorva aur paachchhima uttr aur dakkhian se log akar parameshvar ke rajy ke bhoj men bhagee honge.
aur dekho, kitane pichhle haain ve prathm honge, aur kitane jo prathm haai, ve pichhle honge..
usee ghadee kitane fareeasiyo ne akar us se kaha, yahan se nikalakar chala ja kyonki herodes tujhe mar dalana chahata haai.
us ne un se kaha jakar us lomadee se kah do, ki dekh maain aj aur kal dushttatmaon ko nikalata aur bimaron ko changa karata hoon aur teesare din poora karoonga.
taubhee mujhe aj aur kal aur parason chalana avashy haai, kyonki ho nahee sakata ki koi bhavishyadvkta yarooshalem ke bahar mara jaae.
he yarooshalem ! he yarooshalem ! too jo bhavishyadvktaon ko mar dalatee haai, aur jo tere pas bheje gaae unhen patthravah karatee haai kitanee bar maain ne yah chaha, ki jaaise murgee apane bachchon ko apane pankho ke neeche ikatthe karatee haai, vaaise hee maain bhee tere balakon ko ikatthe karoo, par tum ne yah n chaha.
dekho, tumhara ghar tumhare liye ujad chhoda jata haai, aur maain tum se kahata hoon jab tak tum ne kahoge, ki dhany haai vah, jo prabhu ke nam se ata haai, tab tak tum mujhe fir kabhee n dekhoge..
fir vah sabt ke din fareeasiyon ke saradaron men se kisee ke ghar men rottee khane gaya: aur ve us kee ghaat men the.
aur dekho, aek manushy usake samhane tha, jise jalandhar ka rog tha.
is par yeeshu ne vyavasthapakon aur fareeasiyon se kaha kya sabt ke din achchha karana uchit haai, ki naheen? parantu ve chupachap rahe.
tab us ne use hath laga kar changa kiya, aur jane diya.
aur un se kaha ki tum men se aeesa kaun haai, jis ka gadaha ya baail kuaen men gir jaae aur vah sabt ke din use turant bahar n nikal le?
ve in baton ka kuchh uttr n de sake..
jab koi tujhe byah men bulaa, to mukhy jagah men n baaittna, kaheen aeesa n ho, ki us ne tujh se bhee kisee bade ko nevata diya ho.
aur jis ne tujhe aur use donon ko nevata diya haai: akar tujh se kahe, ki is ko jagah de, aur tab tujhe lajjait hokar sab se neechee jagah men baaittna pade.
par jab too bulaya jaa, to sab se neechee jagah ja baait, ki jab vah, jis ne tujhe nevata diya haai aa, to tujh se kahe ki he mitra, age baddhkar baaitt tab tere sath baaittnevalon ke samhane teree badai hogee.
aur jo koi apane ap ko bada banaaega, vah chhotta kiya jaaega aur jo koi apane ap ko chhotta banaaega, vah bada kiya jaaega..
tab us ne apane nevata denevale se bhee kaha, jab too din ka ya rat ka bhoj kare, to apane mitraen ya bhaiyon ya kuttuambaiyon ya dhanavan padosiyon ko n bula, kaheen aeesa n ho, ki ve bhee tujhe nevata de, aur tera badala ho jaae.
parantu jab too bhoj kare, to kangalo, ttundo, langadon aur andhaen ko bula.
tab too dhany hoga, kyonaki un ke pas tujhe badala dene ko kuchh nahee, parantu tujhe dharmiyon ke jee uttne par is ka praatifal milega.
usake sath bhojan karanevalon men se ek ne ye baten sunakar us se kaha, dhany haai vah, jo parameshvar ke rajy men rottee khaegaa.
us ne us se kaha kisee manushy ne badee jevanar kee aur bahuton ko bulaya.
par ve sab ke sab kshama mangane lage, pahile ne us se kaha, maain ne khet mol liya haai aur avashy haai ki use dekoon: maain tujh se binatee karata hoo, mujhe kshama kara de.
doosare ne kaha, maain ne panch jode baail mol liae haain: aur unhen parakhne jata hoon : maain tujh se binatee karata hoo, mujhe kshama kara de.
aek aur ne kaha maai ne byah kiya haai, isaaliye maain naheen a sakata.
us das ne akar apane svamee ko ye baten kah sunai, tab ghar ke svamee ne krodha men akar apane das se kaha, nagar ke bajaron aur galiyon men turant jakar kangalo, ttundo, langadon aur andhaen ko yahan le ao.
das ne fir kaha he svamee, jaaise too ne kaha tha, vaaise hee kiya gaya haai fir bhee jagah haai.
svamee ne das se kaha, sadkon par aur badon kee or jakar logon ko barabas le hee a taaki mera ghar bhr jaae.
kyonaki maain tum se kahata hoo, ki un nevate huon men se koi meree jevanar ko n chakhega.
aur jab badee bheed usake sath ja rahee thee, to us ne peechhe firakar un se kaha.
yaadi koi mere pas aa, aur apane pita aur mata aur patnee aur ladkebalon aur bhaiyon aur baahinon baran apane praan ko bhee aapiry n jane, to vah mera chela naheen ho sakata.
aur jo koi apana kroos n uttaae aur mere peechhe n aae vah bhee mera chela naheen ho sakata.
tum men se kaun haai ki gaddh banana chahata ho, aur paahile baaittkar khrcha n jode, ki poora karane kee bisat mere pas haai ki naheen?
kaheen aeesa n ho, ki jab nev dalakar taaiyar n kar sake, to sab dekhnevale yah kahakar use tttthon men udane lagen.
ki yah manushy banane to laga, par taaiyar n kar saka?
ya kaun aeesa raja haai, ki doosare raja se yuddh karane jata ho, aur paahile baaittkar vichar n kar le ki jo bees hajar lekar usaka samhana kar sakata hoo, ki naheen?
naheen to usake door rahate hee, vah dooton ko bhejakar milap karana chahega.
isee reeti se tum men se jo koi apana sab kuchh tyag n de, to vah mera chela naheen ho sakata.
namak to achchha haai, parantu yadi namak ka svad bigad jaa, to vah kis vastu se svaadishtt kiya jaaega.
vah n to boomi ke aur n khad ke liye kam men ata haai: use to log bahar faenk dete haain: jis ke sunane ke kan hon vah sun le..
sab chungee lenevale aur papee usake pas aya karate the taki us kee sunen.
tab us ne un se yah drashttant kaha.
tum men se kaun haai jis kee sau bheden ho, aur un men se aek kho jaae to ninnanave ko jangal men chhodkar, us khoi hui ko jab tak mil n jaae khojata n rahe?
aur jab mil jatee haai, tab vah bade anand se use kandho par utta leta haai.
aur ghar men akar mitraen aur padosiyon ko ikatthe karake kahata haai, mere sath anand karo, kyonki meree khoi hui bhed mil gai haai.
maain tum se kahata hoon ki isee reeati se aek man firanevale papee ke vishay men bhee svarga men itana hee anand hoga, jitana ki ninnanave aeese dharmiyon ke vishay naheen hota, jinhen man firane kee avashyakata naheen..
ya kaun aeesee sree hogee, jis ke pas das sikke ho, aur un men se aek kho jaae to vah deeya barakar aur ghar jhad buharakar jab tak mil n jaa, jee lagakar khojatee n rahe?
aur jab mil jata haai, to vah apane sakhaiyon aur padosiniyon ko ikatthee karake kahatee haai, ki mere sath anand karo, kyonki mera khoya hua sikka mil gaya haai.
maain tum se kahata hoon ki isee reeati se aek man firanevale papee ke vishay men parameshvar ke svargadooton ke samhane anand hota haai..
fir us ne kaha, kisee manushy ke do putra the.
un men se chhuttke ne pita se kaha ki he pita sanpaati men se jo bhag mera ho, vah mujhe de deejie. us ne un ko apanee sanpaati bantt dee.
jab vah sab kuchh khrcha kar chuka, to us desh men bada akal pada, aur vah kangal ho gaya.
aur vah us desh ke nivaasiyon men se aek ke yahana jo pada : us ne use apane kheton men sooar charane ke liye bheja.
aur vah chahata tha, ki un faliyon se jinhen sooar khate the apana pett bhre aur use koi kuchh naheen deta tha.
jab vah apane ape men aya, tab kahane laga, ki mere pita ke kitane hee majadooron ko bhojan se aadhaik rottee milatee haai, aur maain yahan bookha mar rahan hoon.
maain ab uttkar apane pita ke pas jaunga aur us se kahoonga ki pita jee maain ne svarga ke virodha men aur teree draashtti men pap kiya haai.
ab is yogy naheen raha ki tera putra kahalau, mujhe apane aek majadoor kee nain rakh le.
tab vah uttkar, apane pita ke pas chala: vah abhee door hee tha, ki usake pita ne use dekhkar taras khaya, aur daudkar use gale lagaya, aur bahut chooma.
putra n us se kaha pita jee, maain ne svarga ke virodha men aur teree draashtti men pap kiya haai aur ab is yogy naheen raha, ki tera putra kahalaun.
parantu pita ne apane dason se kaha jhtt achchhe se achchha vasr nikalakar use pahinao, aur usake hath men angoottee, aur panvon men jootiyan paahinao.
aur pala hua bachhda lakar maro taki ham khanae aur anand manaven.
kyonaki mera yah putra mar gaya tha, fir jee gaya haai : kho gay tha, ab mil gaya haai: aur ve anand karane lage.
parantu usaka jetta putra khet men tha : aur jab vah ate huae ghar ke nikatt pahuncha, to us ne gane bajane aur nachane ka shabd suna.
aur us ne aek das ko bulakar poochha yah kya ho raha haai?
us ne us se kaha, tera bhai aya haai aur tere pita ne pala hua bachhda kattvaya haai, isaaliye ki use bhla changa paya haai.
yah sunakar vah krodha se bhr gaya, aur bheetar jana n chaha : parantu usaka pita bahar akar use manane laga.
us ne pita ko uttr diya, ki dekh maain itane varsha se taree seva kar raha hoo, aur kabhee bhee teree agyaa naheen ttalee, taubhee too ne mujhe kabhee ek bakaree ka bachcha bhee n diya, ki maain apane mitraen ke sath anand karata.
parantu jab tera yah putra, jis ne teree sanpaati veshyaon men uda dee haai, aya, to usake liye too ne pala hua bachhda kattvaya.
us ne us se kaha putra, too sarvada mere sath haai aur jo kuchh mera haai vah sab tera hee haai.
fir us ne chelon se bhee kaha kisee dhanavan ka aek bhndaree tha, aur logon ne usake samhane us par yah dosh lagaya ki yah teree sab sanpaati udaae deta haai.
so us ne use bulakar kaha, yah kya haai jo maai tere vishay men sun raha hoon? apane bhndareepan ka lekha de kyonaki too age ko bhndaree naheen rah sakata.
tab bhndaree sochane laga, ki ab maain kya karoon? kyonki mera svamee ab bhndaree ka kam mujh se chheen le raha haai: mittee to mujh se khodee naheen jatee: aur bheekh mangane se mujhe lajja atee haai.
maain saman gaya, ki kya karoonga: taki jab maain bhndaree ke kam se chhudaya jaun to log mujhe apane gharon men le len.
aur us ne apane svamee ke denadaro men se aek aek ko bulakar pahile se poochha, ki tujh par mere svamee ka kya ata haai?
us ne kaha, sau man tela tab us ne us se kaha, ki apanee khata-bahee le aur baaittkar turant pachas likh de.
fir doosare se poochha tujh par kya ata haai? us ne kaha, sau man gehoon tab us ne us se kaha apanee khata-bahee lekar assee likh de.
svamee ne us adharmee bhndaree ko saraha, ki us ne chaturai se kam kiya haai kyonki is sansar ke log apane samay ke logon kee reeti vyavaharon men jyoti ke logon se aadhaik chatur haain.
aur maain tum se kahata hoo, ki adharman ke dhan se apane liye mitra bana lo taki jab vah jata rahe, to ve tumhen anant nivason men le len.
jo thode se thode men sachcha haai, vah bahut men bhee sachcha haai: aur jo thode se thode men adharmee haai, vah bahut men bhee adharmee haai.
isaliye jab tum adharma ke dhan men sachche n tthare, to sachcha tumhen kaun saunpega.
koi das do svaamiyon kee seva naheen kar sakata: kyonaki vah to aek se baair aur doosare se praem rakhega ya aek se mil rahega aur doosare ko tuchchh janega: tum parameshvar aur dhan donon kee seva naheen kar sakate..
fareesee jo lobhee the, ye sab baten sunakar use tttthon men udane lage.
us ne un se kaha tum to manushyon ke samhane apane ap ko dharmee ttharate ho: parantu parameshvar tumhare man ko janata haai, kyonaki jo vastu manushyon kee draashtti men mahan haai, vah parameshvar ke nikatt gharanait haai.
vyavastha aur bhavishyadvkta yoohanna tak rahe, us samay se parameshvar ke rajy ka susamachar sunaya ja raha haai, aur har koi us men prabalata se pravesh karata haai.
akash aur prathvee ka ttl jana vyavastha ke aek bindu ke mitt jane se sahaj haai.
jo koi apanee patnee ko tyagakar doosaree se byah karata haai, vah vyaabhaichar karata haai, aur jo koi aeesee tyagee hui sree se byah karata haai, vah bhee vyabhaichar karata haai.
aek dhanavan manushy tha jo baainjanee kapade aur malamal pahinata aur prati din sukh-vilas aur dhooma-dhaam ke sath rahata tha.
aur lajar nam ka aek kangal ghaavon se bhra hua us kee devaddhee par chhod diya jata tha.
aur vah chahata tha, ki dhanavan kee mej par kee joottn se apana pett bhre baran kutte bhee akar usake ghaavon ko chattte the.
aur aeesa hua ki vah kangal mar gaya, aur svargadooton ne use lekar ibraaheem kee god men pahunchaya aur vah dhanavan bhee mara aur gada gaya.
aur adhaelok men us ne peeda men pade huae apanee ankhen uttai, aur door se ibraaheem kee god men lajar ko dekha.
aur us ne pukar kar kaha, he pita ibraaheem, mujh par day karake lajar ko bhej de, taki vah apanee ungulee ka sira panee men bhaigokar meree jeebh ko ttndee kare, kyonki maain is jvaala men tadp raha hoon.
parantu ibraaheem ne kaha he putra smaran kar, ki too apane jeevan men achchhee vastuaen le chuka haai, aur vaaise hee lajar buree vastuaen: parantu ab vah yahan shaaantai pa raha haai, aur too tadp raha haai.
aur in sab baton ko chhod hamare aur tumhare beech aek bharee gadha ttharaya gaya haai ki jo yahan se us par tumhare pas jana chahe, ve n ja sake, aur n koi vahan se is par hamare pas a sake.
us ne kaha to he pita maain tujh se binatee karata hoo, ki too use mere pita ke ghar bheja.
kyonaki mere panch bhai haai, vah un ke samhane in baton kee gavahee de, aeesa n ho ki ve bhee is peeda kee jagah men aaen.
ibraaheem ne us se kaha, un ke pas to moosa aur bhavishyadvktaon kee pustaken haai, ve un kee sunen.
us ne us se kaha, ki jab ve moosa aur bhvishyadvktaon kee naheen sunate, to yaadi mare huon men se koi bhee jee utte taubhee us kee naheen manenge..
fir us ne apane chelon se kaha ho naheen sakata ki ttokaren n lage, parantu hay, us manushy par jis ke karan ve atee haai!
jo in chhotton men se kisee aek ko ttokar khailata haai, usake liye yah bhla hota, ki chakkee ka patt usake gale men lattkaya jata, aur vah samudra men dal diya jata.
sachet raho yaadi tera bhai aparadha kare to use samajha, aur yaadi pachhtaae to use kshama kara.
yaadi din bhr men vah sat bar tera aparadha kare aur saton bar tere pas fir akar kahe, ki maain pachhtata hoo, to use kshama kara..
tab praeriton ne prabhu se kaha, hamara vishvas baddha.
prabhu ne kaha ki yadi tum ko rai ke dane ke barabar bhee vishvas hota, to tum is toot ke ped se kahate ki jad se ukhdkar samudra men lag ja, to vah tumharee man leta.
par tum men se aeesa kaun haai, jis ka das hal jotata, ya bhenden charata ho, aur jab vah khet se aa, to us se kahe turant akar bhojan karane baaitt?
aur yah n kahe, ki mera khana taaiyar kara: aur jab tak maain khaun-peeun tab tak kamar bandhakar meree seva kara is ke bad too bhee kha pee lena.
kya vah us das ka nihora manega, ki us ne ve hee kam kiae jis kee agyaa dee gai thee?
isee reeti se tum bhee, jab un sab kamon ko kar chuko jis kee agyaa tumhen dee gai thee, to kaha, ham nikamme das haain ki jo hamen karana chaahiae tha vahee kiya haai..
aur aeesa hua ki vah yarooshalem ko jate huae samariya aur galeel ke beech se hokar jo raha tha.
aur unhon ne door khde hokar, unche shabd se kaha, he yeeshu, he svamee, ham par daya kara.
us ne unhen dekhkar kaha, jao aur apane tai yajakon ko dikhao aur jate hee jate ve shuuddh ho gae.
tab un men se aek yah dekhkar ki maain changa ho gaya hoo, unche shabd se parameshvar kee badai karata hua lautta.
aur yeeshu ke panvon par munh ke bal girakar, usaka dhanyavad karane laga aur vah samaree tha.
is par yeeshu ne kaha, kya dason shuuddh n huae to fir ve nau kahan haain?
kya is paradeshaee ko chhod koi aur n nikala, jo parameshvar kee badai karata?
tab us ne us se kaha uttkar chala ja tere vishvas ne tujhe changa kiya haai..
jab fareesiyon ne us se poochha, ki parameshvar ka rajy kab aaega? to us ne un ko uttr diya, ki pameshvar ka rajy pragatt roop men naheen ata.
aur log yah n kahenge, ki dekho, yahan haai, ya vahan haai, kyonaki dekho, parameshvar ka rajy tumhare beech men haai..
aur us ne chelon se kaha ve din aaenge, jin men tum manushy ke putra ke dinon men se aek din ko dekhna chahoge, aur naheen dekhne paoge.
log tum se kahenge, dekho, vahan haai, ya dekho yahan haai parantu tum chale n jana aur n un ke peechhe ho lena.
kyonaki jaaise bijalee akash kee aek or se kaundhakar akash kee doosaree or chamakatee haai, vaaise hee manushy ka putra bhee apane din men pragatt hoga.
parantu pahile avashy haai, ki vah bahut dukh uttaa, aur is yug ke log use tuchchh ttharaaen.
jaaisa nooh ke dinon men hua tha, vaaisa hee manushy ke putra ke dinon men bhee hoga.
jis din tak nooh jahaj par n chaddha, us din tak log khate-peete the, aur un men byaha-shaadee hotee theee tab jala-pralay ne akar un sab ko nash kiya.
aur jaaisa loot ke dinon men hua tha, ki log khate-peete lena-den karate, ped lagate aur ghar banate the.
manushy ke putra ke pragatt hone ke din bhee aeesa hee hoga.
us din jo kotte par ho aur usaka saman ghar men ho, vah use lene ko n utare, aur vaaise hee jo khet men ho vah peechhe n lautte.
loot kee patnee ko smaran rakho.
jo koi apana praan bachana chahe vah use khoaega, aur jo koi use khoae vah use jeevit rakhega.
maain tum se kahata hoo, us rat ko manushy aek khatt par honge, aek le liya jaaega, aur doosara chhod diya jaaega.
do striayan aek sath chakkee peesatee hongee, aek le lee jaaegee, aur doosaree chhod dee jaaegee.
do jan khet men honge aek le liya jaaega aur doosara chhoda jaaega.
yah sun unhon ne us se poochha, he prabhu yah kahan hoga? us ne un se kaha, jahan loth haai, vahan giddh ikatthe honge..
fir us ne is ke vishay men ki nity praarthna karana aur hiyav n chhodna chaahiae un se yah drashttant kaha.
ki kisee nagar men aek nyayee rahata tha jo n parameshvar se drata th aur n kisee manushy kee paravah karata tha.
aur usee nagar men aek vidhava bhee rahatee thee: jo usake pas a akar kaha karatee thee, ki mera nyay chukakar mujhe mui se bacha.
us ne kitane samay tak to n mana parantu ant men man men vicharakar kaha, yadhyapi maain n parameshvar se drata, aur n manushyon kee kuchh paravah karata hoon.
taubhee yah vidhava mujhe satatee rahatee haai, isaaliye maain usaka nyay chukaunga kaheen aeesa n ho ki ghadee ghadee akar ant ko mera nak men dam kare.
so kya parameshr apane chune huon ka nyay n chukaaega, jo rata-adin us kee duhai dete rahate aur kya vah un ke vishay men den karega?
maain tum se kahata hoon vah turant un ka nyay chukaaega taubhee manushy ka putra jab aaega, to kya vah prathvee par vishvas paaega?
aur us ne kitano se jo apane upar bhrosa rakhte the, ki ham dharmee haai, aur auron ko tuchchh janate the, yah drashttant kaha.
ki do manushy mandair men praarthna karane ke liye gaae aek fareesee tha aur doosara chungee lenevala.
fareesee khda hokar apane man men yon praarthna karane laga, ki he parameshvar, maain tera dhanyavad karata hoo, ki maain aur manushyon kee nai andhor karanevala, anyayee aur vyaabhaicharee nahee, aur n is chungee lenevale ke saman hoon.
maain saptah men do bar upavas karata hoon maain apanee sab kamai ka dasavan ansh bhee deta hoon.
parantu chungee lenevale ne door khde hokar, svarga kee or ankh uttana bhee n chaha, baran apanee chhatee peett-peettkar kaha he parameshvar mujh papee par daya kara.
maain tum se kahata hoo, ki vah doosara naheen parantu yahee manushy dharmee ttharaya jakar apane ghar gaya kyonaki jo koi apane ap ko bada banaaega, vah chhotta kiya jaaega aur jo apane ap ko chhotta banaaega, vah bada kiya jaaega..
fir log apane bachchon ko bhee usake pas lane lage, ki vah un par hath rakhe aur chelon ne dekhkar unhen dantta.
yeeshu n bachchon ko pas bulakar kaha, balakon ko mere pas ane do, aur unhen mana n karo: kyonaki parameshvar ka rajy aeeson kee ka haai.
maain tum se sach kahata hoo, ki jo koi paramashevar ke rajy ko balak kee nai grahan n karega vah us men kabhee pravesh karane n paaega..
kisee saradar ne us se poochha, he uttm guro, anantajeevan ka adhaikaree hone ke liye maain kya karoon?
yeeshu ne us se kaha too mujhe uttm kyon kahata haai? koi uttm nahee, keval aek, arthata parameshvara.
too agyaaon ko to janata haai, ki vyaabhaichar n karana, joottee gavahee n dena, apane pita aur apanee mata ka adar karana.
us ne kaha, maain to in sab ko ladkapan hee se manata aya hoon.
vah yah sunakar bahut udas hua, kyonki vah bada dhanee tha.
yeeshu ne use dekhkar kaha dhanavanon ka parameshvar ke rajy men pravesh karana kaaisa kattnai haai?
parameshvar ke rajy men dhanavan ke pravesh karane se untt ka sooi ke nake men se nikal jana sahaj haai.
aur sunanevalon ne kaha, to fir kis ka uddhar ho sakata haai?
us ne kaha jo manushy se naheen ho sakata, vah parameshvar se ho sakata haai.
pataras ne kaha dek, ham to ghar bar chhodkar tere peechhe ho liye haain.
us ne un se kaha maain tum se sach kahata hoo, ki aeesa koi naheen jis ne parameshvar ke rajy ke liye ghar ya patnee ya bhaiyon ya mata pita ya ladke-balon ko chhod diya ho.
aur is samay kai guna adhaik n paae aur paralok men anant jeevana..
fir us ne barahon ko sath lekar un se kaha dekho, ham yarooshalem ko jate haai, aur jitanee baten manushy ke putra ke liye bhavishyadvktaon ke dara likhee gai haain ve sab pooree hongee.
kyonaki vah anyajaatiyon ke hath men saunpa jaaega, aur ve use tttthon men udaaenge aur usaka apaman karenge, aur us par tookenge.
aur use kode marenge, aur ghaat karenge, aur vah teesare din jee uttega.
aur unhon ne in baton men se koi bat n samajhee: aur yah bat un men chhpaiee rahee, aur jo kaha gaya tha vah un kee samajh men n aya..
jab vah yareeho ke nikatt pahuncha, to aek andha sadk ke kinare baaitta hua bheekh mang raha tha.
aur vah bheed ke chalane kee ahatt sunakar poochhne laga, yah kya ho raha haai?
tab us ne pukar ke kaha, he yeeshu daud kee santan, mujh par daya kara.
jo age jate the, ve use danttne lage ki chup rahe: parantu vah aur bhee chillane laga, ki he daud kee santan, mujh par daya kara.
tab yeeshu ne khde hokar agyaa dee ki use mere pas lao, aur jab vah nikatt aya, to us ne us se yah poochha.
too kya chahata haai, ki maain tere liye karoon? us ne kaha he prabhu yah ki maain dekhne lagoon.
yeeshu ne kaha dekhne lag, tere vishvas ne tujhe achchha kar diya haai.
aur vah turant dekhne laga aur parameshvar kee badai karata hua usake peechhe ho liya, aur sab logon ne dekhkar parameshvar kee stuati kee..
vah yareeho men pravesh karake ja raha tha.
aur dekho, jakkai nam aek manushy tha jo chungee lenevalon ka saradar aur dhanee tha.
vah yeeshu ko dekhna chahata tha ki vah kon sa haai? parantu bheed ke karan dekh n sakata tha. kyonaki vah natta tha.
tab us ko dekhne ke liye vah age daudkar aek goolar k ped par chaddh gaya, kyonaki vah usee marga se jane vala tha.
jab yeeshu us jagah pahuncha, to upar draashtti kar ke us se kaha he jakkai jhtt utar a kyonaki aj mujhe tere ghar men rahana avashy haai.
vah turant utarakar anand se use apane ghar ko le gaya.
yah dekhkar sab loge kudkudakar kahane lage, vah to aek papee manushy ke yahan ja utara haai.
jakkai ne khde hokar prabhu se kaha he prabhu, dekh maain apanee adhaee sampati kangalon ko deta hoo, aur yadi kisee ka kuchh bhee anyay karake le liya haai to use chauguna faer deta hoon.
kyonaki manushy ka putra khoae huon ko ddoonddhne aur un ka uddhar karane aya haai..
jab ve ye baten sun rahe the, to us ne aek drashttant kaha, isaliye ki vah yarooshalem ke nikatt tha, aur ve samajhte the, ki parameshvar ka rajy abhee pragatt hua chahata haai.
so us ne kaha, aek dhanee manushy door desh ko chala taki rajapad pakar fir aae.
aushra us ne apane dason men se das ko bulakar unhen das muharen dee, aur un se kaha, mere lautt ane tak lena-den karana.
parantu usake nagar ke rahanevale us se baair rakhte the, aur usake peechhe dooton ke dara kahala bheja, ki ham naheen chahate, ki yah ham par rajy kare.
jab vah rajapad pakar lautt aya, to aeesa hua ki us ne apane dason ko jinhen rokad dee thee, apane pas bulavaya taaki maloom kare ki unhon ne lena-den se kya kya kamaya.
tab paahile ne akar kaha, he svamee tere mohar se das aur moharen kamai haain.
us ne us se kaha dhany he uttm das, tujhe dhany haai, too bahut hee thode men vishvasee nikala ab das nagaron ka adhaikar rakh.
doosare ne akar kaha he svamee teree mohar se panch aur moharen kamai haain.
us ne kaha, ki too bhee panch nagaron par haakim ho ja.
teesare ne akar kaha he svamee dek, teree mohar yah haai, jise maain ne angochhe men bandha rakhee.
kyonaki maain tujh se drata tha, isaliye ki too kattor manushy haai: jo too ne naheen rakha use utta leta haai, aur jo too ne naheen boya, use kattta haai.
us ne us se kaha he dushtt das, maain tere hee munh se tujhe doshaee ttharata hoon: too mujhe janata tha ki kattor manushy hoo, jo maain ne naheen rakha use utta leta, aur jo maain ne naheen boya, use kattta hoon.
to too ne mere roopaye kottee men kyon naheen rakh dia, ki maain akar byaj samet le leta?
aur jo log nikatt khde the, us ne un se kaha, vah mohar us se le lo, aur jis ke pas das moharen haain use de do.
maain tum se kahata hoo, ki jis ke pas haai, use diya jaaega aur jis ke pas nahee, us se vah bhee jo usake pas haai le liya jaaega.
parantu mere un baairiyon ko jo naheen chahate the ki maain un par rajy karoo, un ko yahan lakar mere samane ghaat karo..
ye baten kahakar vah yarooshalem kee or un ke age age chala..
aur jab vah jaaitoon nam pahad par baaitafage aur baaitaniyah ke pas pahuncha, to us ne apane chelon men se do ko yah kahake bheja.
ki samhane ke ganv men jao, aur us men pahunchate hee aek gadahee ka bachcha jis par kabhee koi savar naheen hua, bandha hua tumhen milega, use kholakar lao.
aur yaadi koi tum se poochhe, ki kyon kholate ho, to yah kah dena, ki prabhu ko is ka prayojan haai.
jo bheje gaae the unhon ne jakar jaaisa us ne un se kaha tha, vaaisa hee paya.
jab ve gadahe ke bachche ko khol rahe the, to usake malikon ne un se poochha is bachche ko kyon kholate ho?
unhon ne kaha, prabhu ko is ka prayojan haai.
ve us ko yeeshu ke pas le aae aur apane kapade us bachche par dalakar yeeshu ko us par savar kiya.
jab vah ja raha tha, to ve apane kapade marga men bichhate jate the.
aur nikatt ate huae jab vah jaaitoon pahad kee ddhlan par pahuncha, to chelon kee saree mandlee un sab samarth ke kamon ke karan jo unhon ne dekhe the, anaandait hokar bade shabd se parameshvar kee stuati karane lagee.
ki dhany haai vah raja, jo prabhu ke nam se ata haai svarga men shaantai aur akash mandl men mahima ho.
us ne uttr diya, ki tum men se kahata hoo, yadi ye chup rahe, to patthr chilla uttenge..
jab vah nikatt aya to nagar ko dekhkar us par roya.
aur kaha, kya hee bhla hota, ki too ha, too hee, isee din men kushal kee baten janata, parantu ab ve teree ankhon se chhpai gai haain.
kyonaki ve din tujh par aaenge ki tere baairee morcha bandhakar tujhe ghor lenge, aur charon or se tujhe dabaaenge.
aur tujhe aur tere balakon ko jo tujh men haai, mittee men milaaenge, aur tujh men patthr par patthr bhee n chhodenge kyonki too ne vah avasar jab tujh par krapa draashtti kee gai n pahichana..
tab vah maandair men jakar bechanevalon ko bahar nikalane laga.
aur un se kaha, likha haai ki mera ghar praarthna ka ghar hoga: parantu tum ne use dakuon kee khoh bana diya haai..
aur vah praati din mandair men upadesh karata tha: aur mahayajak aur shaasree aur loagon ke rais use nash karane ka avasar ddoonddhte the.
parantu koi upay n nikal sake ki yah kis prakar karen kyonki sab log badee chah se us kee sunate the.
isaliye ki bahuton ne un baton ko jo hamare beech men hotee haain iatihas likhne men hath lagaya haai.
jaaisa ki unhon ne jo pahile hee se in baton ke dekhnevale aur vachan ke sevak the ham tak pahunchaya.
isaliye he shraeeman thaiyuafilus mujhe bhee yah uchit maloom hua ki un sab baton ka sampoorn hal arambh se tteek tteek janch karake unhen tere liye kramanusar likoon.
ki too yah jan le, ki ye baten jinakee too ne shaiksha pai haai, kaaisee attl haain..
yahoodiyon ke raja herodes ke samay aabiyyah ke dal men jakarayah nam ka aek yajak tha, aur us kee patnee haroon ke vansh kee thee, jis ka nam ileeashaiba tha.
aur ve donon parameshvar ke samhane dharmee the: aur prabhu kee saree agyaaon aur vidhaiyon par nirdosh chalanevale the. un ke koi santan n thee,
kyonaki ileeashaiba banjh thee, aur ve donon booddhe the..
to yajakon kee reeati ke anusar usake nam par chitthee nikalee, ki prabhu ke maandair men jakar dhoop jalaae.
aur dhoop jalane ke samay logon kee saree mandlee bahar praarthna kar rahee thee.
ki prabhu ka aek svargadoot dhoop kee vedee kee dahinee or khda hua us ko dikhai diya.
aur jakarayah dekhkar ghabaraya aur us par bada bhy chha gaya.
parantu svargadoot ne us se kaha, he jakarayah, bhyabheet n ho kyonki teree praarthna sun lee gai haai aur teree patnee ileeashaiba se tere liye aek putra utpann hoga, aur too usaka nam yoohanna rakhna.
aur tujhe anand aur harsha hoga: aur bahut log usake janm ke karan anandait honge.
kyonaki vah prabhu ke samhane mahan hoga aur dakhras aur madira kabhee n piaega aur apanee mata ke garbh hee se pavitra atma se paaripoorn ho jaaega.
aur israaeliyon men se bahuteron ko un ke prabhu parameshvar kee or faerega.
vah aeliyyah kee atma aur samarth men ho kar usake age age chalega, ki pitaron ka man ladkebalon kee or faer de aur agyaa n mananevalon ko dhaarmiyon kee samajh par laae aur prabhu ke liye aek yogy praja taaiyar kare.
jakarayah ne svargadoot se poochha yah maain kaaise janoon? kyonki maain to booddha hoon aur meree patnee bhee booddhee ho gai haai.
svargadoot ne us ko uttr diya, ki maain jibraail hoo, jo parameshvar ke samhane khda rahata hoon aur maain tujh se baten karane aur tujhe yah susamachar sunane ko bheja gaya hoon.
aur dekh jis din tak ye baten pooree n ho le, us din tak too maun rahega, aur bol n sakega, isaliye ki too ne meree baton kee jo apane samay par pooree hongee, prateeti n kee.
jab vah bahar aya, to un se bol n saka: so ve jan gaa, ki us ne mandair men koi darshan paya haai aur v un se sanket karata raha, aur goonga rah gaya.
jab us kee seva ke din poore hua, to vah apane ghar chala gaya..
in dinon ke bad us kee patnee ileeshaiba garbhvatee hui aur panch maheene tak apane ap ko yah kah ke chhpaiaae rakha.
ki manushyon men mera apaman door karane ke liye prabhu ne in dinon men krapadraashtti karake mere liye aeesa kiya haai..
chhttven maheene men parameshvar kee or se jibraail svargadoot galeel ke nasarat nagar men aek kunvaree ke pas bheja gaya.
jis kee manganee yoosufa nam daud ke gharane ke aek puroosh se hui thee: us kunvaree ka nam mariyam tha.
aur svargadoot ne usake pas bheetar akar kaha anand aur jay teree ho, jis par ishvar ka anugrah hua haai, prabhu tere sath haai.
vah us vachan se bahut ghabara gai, aur sochane lagee, ki yah kis prakar ka aabhaivadan haai?
svargadoot ne us se kaha, he mariyama bhyabheet n ho, kyonaki parameshvar ka anugrah tujh par hua haai.
aur dek, too garbhvatee hogee, aur tere aek putra utpann hoga too usaka nam yeeshu rakhna.
vah mahan hoga aur paramapradhaan ka putra kahalaaega aur prabhu parameshvar usake pita daud ka sinhasan us ko dega.
aur vah yakoob ke gharane par sada rajy karega aur usake rajy ka ant n hoga.
maariyam ne svargadoot se kaha, yah kyonkar hoga? maain to puroosh ko janatee hee naheen.
svargadoot ne us ko uttr diya ki pavitra atma tujh par utarega, aur paramapradhaan kee samarth tujh par chhaya karegee isaaliye vah paavitra jo utpann honevala haai, parameshvar ka putra kahalaaega.
aur dek, aur teree kuttumbainee ileeshaiba ke bhee buddhape men putra honevala haai, yah usaka, jo banjh kahalatee thee chhttvan maheena haai.
kyonaki jo vachan parameshvar kee or se hota haai vah prabhavaraahit naheen hota.
maariyam ne kaha, dek, maain prabhu kee dasee hoo, mujhe tere vachan ke anusar ho: tab svargadoot usake pas se chala gaya..
aur jakarayah ke ghar men jakar ileeshaiba ko namaskar kiya.
jyonhee ileeashaiba ne maariyam ka namaskar suna, tyonhee bachcha usake pett men uchhla, aur ileeashaiba paavitra atma se paaripoorn ho gai.
aur us ne bade shabd se pukar kar kaha, too striayon men dhany haai, aur tere pett ka fal dhany haai.
aur yah anugrah mujhe kahan se hua, ki mere prabhu kee mata mere pas ai?
aur dekh jyonhee tere namaskar ka shabd mere kanon men pada tyonhee bachcha mere pett men anand se uchhl pada.
aur dhany haai, vah jis ne vishvas kiya ki jo baten prabhu kee or se us se kahee gai, ve pooree hongee.
tab maariyam ne kaha, mera praan prabhu kee badai karata haai.
aur meree atma mere uddhar karanevale parameshvar se anaandait hui.
kyonaki us ne apanee dasee kee deenata par draashtti kee haai, isaliye dekho, ab se sab yug yug ke log mujhe dhany kahenge.
kyonaki us shaktaiman ne mere liye bade bade kam kiae haai, aur usaka nam pavitra haai.
aur us kee daya un par, jo us se drate haai, peeddhee se peeddhee tak banee rahatee haai.
us ne balavanon ko sinhasanon se gira diya aur deenon ko uncha kiya.
us ne bookhon ko achchhee vastuon se trapt kiya, aur dhanavanon ko choochhe hath nikal diya.
us ne apane sevak israel ko sambhal liya.
ki apanee us daya ko smaran kare, jo ibraaheem aur usake vansh par sada rahegee, jaaisa us ne hamare bapa-dadon se kaha tha.
maariyam lagabhg teen maheene usake sath rahakar apane ghar lott gai..
tab ileeshaiba ke janane ka samay poora hua, aur v putra janee.
usake padosiyon aur kuttumbaiyon ne yah sun kar, ki prabhu ne us par badee daya kee haai, usake sath anandait hue.
aur aeesa hua ki attven din ve balak ka khtana karane aae aur usaka nam usake pita ke nam par jakarayah rakhne lage.
aur us kee mata ne uttr diya ki naheen baran usaka nam yoohanna rakha jaae.
aur unhon ne us se kaha, tere kuttumb men kisee ka yah nam naheen.
tab unhon ne usake pita se sanket karake poochha.
ki too usaka nam kya rakhna chahata haai? aur us ne likhne kee pattee mangakar likh diya, ki usaka nam yoohanna haai: aur sabhon ne achambha kiya.
tab usaka munh aur jeebh turant khul gai aur vah bolane aur parameshvar ka dhanyavad karane laga.
aur usake as pas ke sab rahanevalon par bhy chha gaya aur un sab baton kee charcha yahoodaya ke sare pahadee desh men faail gai.
aur sab sunanevalon ne apane apane man men vichar karake kaha, yah balak kaaisa hoga kyonki prabhu ka hath usake sath tha..
aur usaka pita jakarayah pavitra atma se paaripoorn ho gaya, aur bhvishyadvvanee karane laga.
ki prabhu israael ka parameshvar dhany ho, ki us ne apane logon par draashtti kee aur un ka chhuttkara kiya haai.
or apane sevak daud ke gharane men hamare liye aek uddhar ka seeng nikala.
arthata hamare shatrauon se, aur hamare sab baaiariyon ke hath se hamara uddhar kiya haai.
ki hamare bapa-dadon par daya karake apanee paavitra vacha ka smaran kare.
aur vah shapath jo us ne hamare pita ibraaheem se khai thee.
ki vah hamen yah dega, ki ham apane shatrauon ke hath se chhuttkara.
usake samhane pavitrata aur dhaaarmikata se jeevan bhr nidr rahakar us kee seva karate rahen.
aur too he balak, paramapradhaan ka bhvishyadvkta kahalaaega, kyonki too prabhu ke marga taaiyar karane ke liye usake age age chalega,
ki usake logon ko uddhar ka gyaan de, jo un ke papon kee kshama se praapt hota haai.
yah hamare parameshvar kee usee badee karoona se hoga jis ke karan upar se ham par bhor ka prakash uday hoga.
ki andhakar aur mratyu kee chhaya men baaittnevalon ko jyoti de, aur hamare panvon ko kushal ke marga men seedho chalaae..
aur vah balak baddhta aur atma men balavant hota gaya, aur israael par pragatt hone ke din tak jangalon men raha.
aur kahane lage, ki hamen bata, too in kamon ko kis adhaikar se karata haai, aur vah kaun haai, jis ne tujhe yah aadhaikar diya haai?
us ne un ko uttr diya, ki maain bhee tum men se ek bat poochhta hoon mujhe batao.
yoohanna ka bapatisma svarga kee or se tha ya manushyon kee or se tha?
tab ve apas men kahane lage, ki yadi ham kahen svarga kee or se, to vah kahega fir tum ne us kee prateeati kyon n kee?
aur yaadi ham kahe, manushyon kee or se, to sab log hamen patthravah karenge, kyonaki ve sachamuch janate haai, ki yoohanna bhvishyadvkata tha.
so unhon ne uttr diya, ham naheen janate, ki vah kis kee or se tha.
yeeshu ne un se kaha, to maain bhee tum ko naheen batata, ki maain ye kam kis adhaikar se karata hoon.
tab vah logon se yah drashttant kahane laga, ki kisee manushy ne dakh kee baree lagai, aur kisanon ko usaka tteka de diya aur bahut dinon ke liye paredash chala gaya.
samay par us ne kisanon ke pas aek das ko bheja, ki ve dakh kee baree ke kuchh falon ka bhag use de, par kisanon ne use peettkar choochhe hath lautta diya.
fir us ne aek aur das ko bheja, or unhon ne use bhee peettkar aur usaka apaman karake choochhe hath lautta diya.
fir us ne teesara bheja, aur unhon ne use bhee ghaayal karake nikal diya.
tab dakh kee baree ke svamee ne kaha, maain kya karoon? maain apane piry putra ko bhejoonga kya jane ve usaka adar karen.
jab kisanon ne use dekha to apas men vichar karane lage, ki yah to varis haai ao, ham use mar dale, ki miras hamaree ho jaae.
aur unhon ne use dakh kee baree se bahar nikalakar mar dala: isaaliye dakh kee baree ka svamee un ke sath kya karega?
vah akar un kisanon ko nash karega, aur dakh kee baree auron ko saunpega : yah sunakar unhon ne kaha, parameshvar aeesa n kare.
us ne un kee or dekhkar kaha fir yah kya, likha haai, ki jis patthr ko rajaamistriayon ne nikamma ttharaya tha, vahee kone ka sira ho gaya.
jo koi us patthr par girega vah chakanachoor ho jaaega, aur jis par vah girega, use vah pees dalega..
usee ghadee shaaastriayon aur mahayajakon ne use pakadna chaha, kyonki samajh gaa, ki us ne ham par yah drashttant kaha, parantu ve logon se dre.
aur ve us kee tak men lage aur bhediye bheje, ki dharma ka bhesh dharakar us kee koi n koi bat pakade, ki use haakim ke hath aur adhaikar men saunp den.
kya hamen kaaisar ko kar dena uchit haai, ki naheen.
us ne un kee chaturai ko tadkar un se kaha ek deenar mujhe dikhao.
is par kis kee mootira aur nam haai? unhon ne kaha, kaaisar ka.
us ne un se kaha to jo kaaisar ka haai, vah kaaisar ko do aur jo parameshvar ka haai, vah parameshvar ko do.
ve logoen ke samhane us bat ko pakad n sake, baran usake uttr se achaambhiat hokar chup rah gaae.
fir sadookee jo kahate haai, ki mare huon ka jee uttna haai hee nahee, un men se kitanon ne usake pas akar poochha.
ki he guro, moosa ne hamare liye yah likha haai, ki yadi kisee ka bhai apanee patnee ke rahate huae bina santan mar jaa, to usaka bhai us kee patnee ko byah le, aur apane bhai ke liye vansh utpann kare.
so sat bhai the, pahila bhai byah karake bina santan mar gaya.
fir doosare aur teesare ne bhee us sree ko byah liya.
sab ke peechhe vah sree bhee mar gai.
so jee uttne par vah un men se kis kee patnee hogee, kyonaki vah saton kee patnee ho chukee thee.
yeeshu ne un se kaha ki is yug ke santanon men to byah shaadee hotee haai.
par jo log is yogy ttharenge, ki us yug ko aur mare huon men se jee uttna praapt kare, un men byah shaadee n hogee.
ve fir marane ke bhee naheen kyonki ve svargadooton ke saman honge, aur jee uttne ke santan hone se parameshvar ke bhee santan honge.
parantu is bat ko ki mare huae jee uttte haai, moosa n bhee jhadee kee katha men pragatt kee haai, ki vah prabhu ko ibraaheem ka parameshvar, aur isahak ka parameshvar, aur yakoob ka paramashevar kahata haai.
parameshvar to muradon ka naheen parantu jeevaton ka parameshvar haai: kyonki usake nikatt sab jeeavit haain.
tab yah sunakar shaastriayon men se kitanon ne kaha, ki he guro, too ne achchha kaha.
aur unhen fir us se kuchh aur poochhne ka hiyav n hua..
fir us ne un se poochha, maseeh ko daud ka santan kyonkar kahate haain.
daud ap bhjanasanhita kee pustak men kahata haai, ki prabhu ne mere prabhu se kaha.
mere dahine baait, jab tak ki maain teere baairiyon ko tere panvon ke tale n kar doon.
daud to use prabhu kahata haai to fir vah us kee santan kyonkar tthara?
jab sab log sun rahe the, to us ne apane chelon se kaha.
shaastriayon se chaukas raho, jin ko lambe lambe vasr paahine huae firana bhla haai, aur jinhen bajaron men namaskar, aur sabhaon men mukhy asan aur jevanaron men mukhy sthan piry lagate haain.
ve vidhavaon ke ghar kha jate haai, aur dikhane ke liye badee der tak praarthna karate rahate haain: ye bahut hee dand paaenge..
fir us ne ankh uttakar dhanavanon ko apana apana dan bhndar men dalate dekha.
aur us ne aek kangal vidhava ko bhee us men do damaadiyan dalate dekha.
tab us ne kaha maain tum se sach kahata hoon ki is kangal vidhava ne sab se baddhkar dala haai.
kyonaki un sab ne apanee baddhtee men se dan men kuchh dala haai, parantu is ne apanee ghattee men se apanee saree jeevika dal dee haai..
ve din aaenge, jin men yah sab jo tum dekhte ho, un men se yahan kisee patthr par patthr bhee n choottega, jo ddhaya n jaaega.
unhon ne us se poochha, he guro, yah sab kab hoga? aur ye baten jab pooree hone par hongee, to us samay ka kya chinh hoga?
us ne kaha chaukas raho, ki bhramaae n jao, kyonaki bahutere mere nam se akar kahenge, ki maain vahee hoon aur yah bhee ki samay nikatt a pahuncha haai: tum un ke peechhe n chale jana.
aur jab tum ladaiyon aur balavon kee charcha suno, to ghabara n jana kyonaki in ka pahile hona avashy haai parantu us samay turant ant n hoga.
tab us ne un se kaha, ki jati par jati aur rajy par rajy chaddhai karega.
aur baden baden booidol honge, aur jagah jagah akal aur maariyan padengee, aur akash men bhyankar baten aur bade bade chinh pragatt honge.
parantu in sab baton se paahile ve mere nam ke karan tumhen pakadenge, aur sataaenge, aur panchayaton men saupenge, aur bandeegrah me dlavaaenge, aur rajaon aur haakimon ke samhane le jaaenge.
par yah tumhare liye gavahee dene ka avasar ho jaaega.
kyonaki maain tumhen aeesa bol aur buddh idoonga, ki tumhare sab virodhaee samhana ya khndn n kar sakenge.
aur tumhare mata pita aur bhai aur kuttumb, aur mitra bhee tumhen pakadvaaenge yahan tak ki tum men se kitanon ko marava dalenge.
aur mere nam ke karan sab log tum se baair karenge.
parantu tumhare sir ka aek bal bhee banka n hoga.
apane dhaeeraj se tum apane praanon ko bachaae rakhoge..
jab tum yarooshalem ko senaon se ghaira hua dekho, to jan lena ki usaka ujad jana nikatt haai.
tab jo yahoodiya men hon vah pahadon par bhag jaae, aur jo yarooshalem ke bheetar hon ve bahar nikal jaaen aur jo gavon men ho ve us men n janae.
kyonaki yah palatta lene ke aeese din honge, jin men likhee hui sab baten pooree ho jaaengee.
un dinon men jo garbhvatee aur doodha pilatee hongee, un ke liye hay, hay, kyonaki desh men bada klesh aur in logon par badee apaati hogee.
ve talavar ke kaur ho jaaenge, aur sab deshaen ke logon men bandhauae hokar pahunchaae jaaenge, aur jab tak any jaatiyon ka samay poora n ho, tab tak yarooshalem any jaatiyon se raunda jaaega.
aur sooraj aur chand aur taron men chinh dikhai denge, aur prathvee par, desh desh ke logon ko sankatt hoga kyonaki ve samudra ke garajane aur laharon ke kolahal se ghabara jaaenge.
aur bhy ke karan aur sansar par anevalee ghattnaon kee bantt dekhte dekhte logon ke jee men jee n rahega kyonaki akash kee shaktaiyon hilai jaaengee.
tab ve manushy ke putra ko samarth aur badee mahima ke sath badal par ate dekhenge.
jab ye baten hone lage, to seedho hokar apane sir upar uttana kyonaki tumhara chhuttkara nikatt hoga..
us ne un se ek drashttant bhee kaha ki anjeer ke ped aur sab pedon ko dekho.
jyonahi un kee konpalen nikalatee haai, to tum dekhkar ap hee jan lete ho, ki graeeshmakal nikatt haai.
isee reeti se jab tum ye baten hote dekho, tab jan lo ki parameshvar ka rajy nikatt haai.
maain tum se sach kahata hoo, ki jab tak ye sab baten n ho le, tab tak is peeddhee ka kadaapi ant n hoga.
akash aur prathvee ttl jaaenge, parantu meree baten kabhee n ttlengee..
isaliye savadhaan raho, aeesa n ho ki tumhare man khumar aur matavalepan, aur is jeevan kee chintaon se sust ho jaae, aur vah din tum par fande kee nai achanak a pade.
kyonaki vah saree prathvee ke sab rahanevalon par isee prakar a padega.
aur vah din ko mandair men upadesh karata tha aur rat ko bahar jakar jaaitoon nam pahad par raha karata tha.
aur bhor ko tadke sab log us kee sunane ke liye maandair men usake pas aya karate the.
akhmeeree rottee ka pavrva jo fasah kahalata haai, nikatt tha.
aur mahayajak aur shaasree is bat kee khoj men the ki us ko kyonkar mar dale, par ve logon se drate the..
aur shautan yahooda men samaya, jo iskaariyotee kahalata aur barah chelon men gina jata tha.
us ne jakar mahayajakon aur paharooon ke saradaron ke sath batacheet kee, ki us ko kis prakar un ke hath pakadvae.
ve anandait hua, aur use roopaye dene ka vachan diya.
tab akhmeeree rottee ke pavrva ka din aya, jis men fasah ka memna balee karana avashy tha.
aur yeeshu ne pataras aur yoohanna ko yah kahakar bheja, ki jakar hamare khane ke liye fasah taaiyar karo.
unhon ne us se poochha, too kahan chahata haai, ki ham taaiyar karen?
us ne un se kaha dekho, nagar men pravesh karate hee ek manushy jal ka ghada uttaae huae tumhen milega, jis ghar men vah jae tum usake peechhe chale jana.
aur us ghar ke svamee se kaho, ki guroo tujh se kahata haai ki vah pahunashaala kahan haai jis men maain apane chelon ke sath fasah khaun?
vah tumhen aek sajee sajai badee attaree dikha dega vahan taaiyaree karana.
unhon ne jakar, jaaisa us ne un se kaha tha, vaaisa hee paya, aur fasah taaiyar kiya..
jab ghadee pahunchee, to vah praearitoen ke sath bhojan karane baaitta.
aur us ne un se kaha mujhe badee lalasa thee, ki dukh-bhogane se paahile yah fasah tumhare sath khaun.
kyonaki maain tum se kahata hoo, ki jab tak vah parameshvar ke rajy men poora n ho tab tak maain use kabhee n khaunga.
tab us ne kattora lekar dhanyavad kiya, aur kaha, is ko lo aur apas men bantt lo.
kyonaki maain tum se kahata hoo, ki jab tak parameshvar ka rajy n aae tab tak maain dakh ras ab se kabhee n peeunga.
fir us ne rottee lee, aur dhanyavad karake todee, aur un ko yah kahate huae dee, ki yah meree deh haai, jo tumhare liye dee jatee haai: mere smaran ke liye yahee kiya karo.
isee reeti se us ne biyaree ke bad kattora mere us lohoo men jo tumhare liye bahaya jata haai nai vacha haai.
par dekho, mere pakadvanevale ka hath mere sath mej par haai.
kyonaki manushy ka putra to jaaisa usake liye ttharaya gaya jata hee haai, par hay us manushy par, jis ke dara vah pakadvaya jata haai!
tab ve apas men poochh pachh karane lage, ki ham men se kaun haai, jo yah kam karega?
un men yah vada-avivad bhee hua ki ham men se kaun bada samajha jata haai?
us ne un se kaha, anyajaatiyon ke raja un par prabhuta karate haain aur jo un par adhaikar rakhte haai, ve upakarak kahalate haain.
parantu tum aeese n hona varan jo tum men bada haai, vah chhotte kee nai aur jo pradhaan haai, vah sevak kee nai bane.
kyonaki bada kaun haai vah jo bhojan par baaitta ya vah jo seva karata haai? kya vah naheen jo bhojan par baaitta haai? par maain tumhare beech men sevak kee nain hoon.
parantu tum vah ho, jo meree pareekshaaon men lagatar mere sath rahe.
vaaise hee maain bhee tumhare liye ttharata hoo, taki tum mere rajy men meree mej par khao-apio baran sinhasanon par baaittkar israael ke barah gotraen ka nyay karo.
shamaun, he shamaun, dek, shautan ne tum logon ko mang liya haai ki genhoon kee nai fattke.
parantu maain ne tere liye binatee kee, ki tera vishvas jata n rahe: aur jab too fire, to apane bhaiyon ko sthiar karana.
us ne us se kaha he prabhu, maain tere sath bandeegrah jane, varan marane ko bhee taaiyar hoon.
us ne kaha he pataras maain tujh se kahata hoo, ki aj murga bang dega jab tak too teen bar mera inkar n kar lega ki maain use naheen janata..
aur us ne un se kaha, ki jab maain ne tumhen battua, aur jholee, aur joote bina bheja tha, to kya tum ko kisee vastu kee ghattee hui thee? unhon ne kaha kisee vastu kee naheen.
kyonaki maain tum se kahata hoo, ki yah jo likha haai, ki vah aparadhaiyon ke sath gina gaya, usaka mujh men poora hona avashy haai kyonki mere vishay kee baten pooree hon par haain.
unhon ne kaha he prabhu, dek, yahan do talavaren haain: us ne un se kaha bahut haain..
tab vah bahar nikalakar apanee reeati ke anusar jaaitoon ke pahad par gaya, aur chele usake peechhe ho liae.
us jagah pahunchakar us ne un se kaha praarthna karo, ki tum pareeksha men n pado.
aur vah ap un se alag aek ddhela faenkane ke ttppe bhr gaya, aur ghauttne ttekakar praarthna karane laga.
ki he pita yaadi too chahe to is kattore ko mere pas se hatta le, taubhee meree naheen parantu teree hee ichchha pooree ho.
tab svarga se aek doot us ko dikhai diya jo use samarth deta tha.
aur vah atyant sankatt men vyakul hokar aur bhee day vedana se praarthna karane laga aur usaka paseena mano lohoo kee badee badee boondon kee nai boomi par gir raha tha.
tab vah praarthna se utta aur apane chelon ke pas akar unhen udasee ke mare sota paya aur un se kaha, kyon sote ho?
utto, praarthna karo, ki pareeksha men n pado..
vah yah kah hee raha tha, ki dekho aek bheed ai, aur un barahon men se aek jis ka nam yahooda tha unake age age a raha tha, vah yeeshu ke pas aya, ki usaka chooma le.
yeeshu ne us se kaha, he yahooda, kya too chooma lekar manushy ke putra ko pakadvata haai?
usake saathaiyon ne jab dekha ki kya honevala haai, to kha he prabhu, kya ham talavar chalaen?
aur un men se aek ne mahayajak ke das par chalakar usaka dahina kan uda diya.
is par yeeshu ne kaha ab bas karo : aur usaka kan chookar use achchha kiya.
tab yeeshu ne mahayajakon aur maandair ke paharooon ke saradaron aur puraaniyon se, jo us par chaddh aae the, kaha kya tum mujhe dakoo janakar talavaren aur lattyaian liae huae nikale ho?
jab maain mandair men har din tumhare sath tha, to tum ne mujh par hath n dala par yah tumharee ghadee haai, aur andhakar ka adhaikar haai..
fir ve use pakadkar le chale, aur mahayajak ke ghar men laae aur pataras door hee door usake peechhe peechhe chalata tha.
aur jab ve angan men ag sulagakar ikatthe baaitte, to pataras bhee un ke beech men baaitt gaya.
aur aek laundee use ag ke ujiyale men baaitte dekhkar aur us kee or takakar kahane lagee, yah bhee to usake sath tha.
paranatu us ne yah kahakar inkar kiya, ki he naree, maain use naheen janata.
thodee der bad kisee aur ne use dekhkar kaha, too bhee to unheen men se haai: pataras ne kaha he manushy maain naheen hoon.
koi ghantte bhr ke bad aek aur manushy draddhta se kahane laga, nishchay yah bhee to usake sath tha kyonki yah galeelee haai.
tab prabhu ne ghoomakar pataras kee or dekha, aur pataras ko prabhu kee vah bat yad ai jo us ne kahee thee, ki aj murga ke bang dene se paahile, too teen bar mera inkar karega.
aur vah bahar nikalakar foott foott kar rone laga..
jo manushy yeeshu ko pakade huae the, ve use tttthon men udakar peettne lage.
aur us kee ankhe ddhanpakar us se poochha, ki bhvishyadanee karake bata ki tujhe kisane mara.
aur unhon ne bahut see aur bhee ninda kee baten usake virodha men kaheen..
yaadi too maseeh haai, to ham se kah de! us ne un se kaha, yaadi maain tum se kahoon to prateeti n karoge.
aur yaadi poonchoo, to uttr n doge.
paranatu ab se manushy ka putra sarvashaaktaiman parameshvar kee daahinee aur baaitta rahega.
is par sab ne kaha, to kya too parameshvar ka putra haai? us ne un se kaha tum ap hee kahate ho, kyonki maain hoon.
tab unhon ne kaha ab hamen gavahee ka kya prayojan haai kyonaki ham ne ap hee usake munh se sun liya haai..
tab saree sabha uttkar use peelatus ke pas le gai.
aur ve yah kahakar us par dosh lagane lage, ki ham ne ise logon ko bahakate aur kaaisar ko kar dene se mana karate, aur apane ap ko maseeh raja kahate huae suna haai.
peelatus ne us se poochha, kya too yahoodiyon ka raja haai? us ne use uttr diya, ki too ap hee kah raha haai.
tab peelatus ne mahayajakon aur logon se kaha, maain is manushy men kuchh dosh naheen pata.
par ve aur bhee draddhta se kahane lage, yah galeel se lekar yahan tak sare yahoodiya men upadesh de de kar logon ko usakata haai.
yah sunakar peelatus ne poochha, kya yah manushy galeelee haai?
aur yah janakar ki vah herodes kee riyasat ka haai, use herodes ke pas bhej diya, kyonaki un dinon men vah bhee yarooshalem men tha..
herodes yeeshu ko dekhkar bahut hee prasann hua, kyonaki vah bahut dinon se us ko dekhna chahata tha: isaliye ki usake vishay men suna tha, aur usaka kuchh chinh dekhne kee asha rakhta tha.
vah us ne bahuteree baten poochhta raha, par us ne us ko kuchh bhee uttr n diya.
aur mahayajak aur shaasree khde huae tan man se us par dosh lagate rahe.
tab herodes ne apane sipaahiyon ke sath usaka apaman karake tttthon men udaya, aur bhdkeela vasr paahinakar use peelatus ke pas lautta diya.
usee din peelatus aur herodes mitra ho gae. isake pahile ve ek doosare ke baairee the..
peelatus ne mahayajakon aur saradaron aur logon ko bulakar un se kaha.
tum is manushy ko logon ka bahakanevala ttharakar mere pas laae ho, aur dekho, maain ne tumhare samhane us kee janch kee, par jin baton ka tum us par dosh lagate ho, un baton ke vishay men maain ne us men kuchh bhee dosh naheen paya haai.
n herodes ne, kyonki us ne use hamare pas lautta diya haai: aur dekho, us se aeesa kuchh naheen hua ki vah mratyu ke dand ke yogy ttharaya jaae.
isaliye maain use pittvakar chhod deta hoon.
tab sab milakar chilla utte, ki is ka kam tamam kar, aur hamare liye baraabba ko chhod de.
yahee kisee balave ke karan jo nagar men hua tha, aur hatya ke karan bandeegrah men dala gaya tha.
par peelatus ne yeeshu ko chhodne kee ichchha se logon ko fir samajhaya.
us ne teesaree bar un se kaha kyon us ne kaun see burai kee haai? maain ne us men mratyu dand ke yogy kortt bat naheen pai! isaaliye maain use pittvakar chhod deta hoon.
parantu ve chilla-achillakar peechhe pad gaa, ki vah kroos par chaddhaya jaa, aur un ka chillana prabal hua.
so peelatus ne agyaa dee, ki un kee binanee ke anusar kiya jaae.
aur us ne us manushy ko jo balave aur hatya ke karan bandeegrah men dala gaya tha, aur jise ve mangate the, chhod diya aur yeeshu ko un kee ichchha ke anusar saunp diya..
aur logon kee badee bheed usake peechhe ho lee: aur bahut see striayan bhee, jo usake liye chhatee-peetttee aur vilap karatee theen.
yeeshu ne un kee or firakar kaha he yarooshalem kee putraiyo, mere liye mat roo parantu apane aur apane balakon ke liye roo.
kyonaki dekho, ve din ate haai, jin men kahenge, dhany haain ve jo banjh haai, aur ve garbh jo n jane aur ve stan jinhon ne doodha n pilaya.
us samay ve pahadon se kahane lagenge, ki ham par giro, aur tteelon se ki hamen ddhap lo.
kyonaki jab ve hare ped ke sath aeesa karate haai, to sookhe ke sath kya kuchh n kiya jaaega?
ve aur do manushyon ko bhgyaee jo kukarmee the usake sath ghaat karane ko le chale..
jab ve us jagah jise khopadee kahate haain pahunche, to unhon ne vahan use aur un kukaarmiyon ko bhee aek ko daahinee aur aur doosare ko bain aur krooson par chaddhaya.
tab yeeshu ne kaha he pita, inhen kshama kar, kyonaki ye janate naheen ki kya kar rahen haain? aur unhon ne chitthiyan dalakar usake kapade bantt liae.
log khde khde dekh rahe the, aur saradar bhee ttttha kar karake kahate the, ki is ne auron ko bachaya, yaadi yah parameshvar ka maseeh haai, aur usaka chuna hua haai, to apane ap ko bacha le.
sipahee bhee pas akar aur siraka dekar usaka ttttha karake kahate the.
yaadi too yahoodiyon ka raja haai, to apane ap ko bacha.
aur usake upar aek patra bhee laga tha, ki yah yahoodiyon ka raja haai.
jo kukarmee lattkaae gaae the, un men se aek ne us kee ninda karake kaha kya too maseeh naheen? to fir apane ap ko aur hamen bacha.
is par doosare ne use danttkar kaha, kya too parameshvar se bhee naheen drata? too bhee to vahee dand pa raha haai.
aur ham to nyayanusar dand pa rahe haai, kyonki ham apane kamon ka tteek fal pa rahe haain par is ne koi anuchit kam naheen kiya.
tab us ne kaha he yeeshu, jab too apane rajy men aa, to meree suadhai lena.
us ne us se kaha, maain tujh se sach kahata hoon ki aj hee too mere sath svargalok men hoga..
aur lagabhg do pahar se teesare pahar tak sare desh men aandhiayara chhaya raha.
aur soorya ka ujiyala jata raha, aur mandair ka parada beech men fatt gaya.
aur yeeshu ne bade shabd se pukar kar kaha he pita, maain apanee atma tere hathon men saunpata hoon: aur yah kahakar praan chhod diae.
soobedar ne, jo kuchh hua tha dekhkar, parameshvar kee badai kee, aur kaha nishchay yah manushy dharmee tha.
aur bheed jo yah dekhne ko ikatthee hui bhee, is ghattna ko, dekhkar chhatee-peetttee hui lautt gai.
aur usake sab jan pahachan, aur jo striayan galeel se usake pas ai thee, door khdee hui yah sab dekh rahee theen..
aur dekho yoosufa nam aek mantraee jo sajjan aur dharmee puroosh tha.
aur un ke vichar aur un ke is kam se prasann n tha aur vaa yaihoodiyon ke nagar arimateeya ka rahanevala aur parameshvar ke rajy kee batt johanevala tha.
aur use utarakar chadar men lapetta, aur aek kabra men rakha, jo chattan men khodee hui thee aur us men koi kabhee n rakha gaya tha.
vah taaiyaree ka din tha, aur sabt ka din arambh hone par tha.
aur un striayon ne jo usake sath galeel se ai thee, peechhe peechhe jakar us kabra ko dekha, aur yah bhee ki us kee loth kis reeti se rakhee gai haai.
parantu saptah ke pahile din bade bhor ko ve un sugaandhiat vastuon ko jo unhon ne taaiyar kee thee, le kar kabra par ain.
aur unhon ne patthr ko kabra par se luddhka hua paya.
aur bheetar jakar prabhu yeeshu kee loth n pai.
jab ve is bat se bhauchakkee ho rahee theen to dekho, do puroosh jhlakate vasr pahine huae un ke pas a khde hue.
jab ve dr gai, aur dharatee kee or munh jhukaae raheen to unhon ne us ne kaha tum jeevate ko mare huon men kyon ddoonddhtee ho?
vah yahan nahee, parantu jee utta haai smaran karo ki us ne galeel men rahate huae tum se kaha tha.
ki avashy haai, ki manushy ka putra paapiyon ke hath men pakadvaya jaa, aur kroos par chaddhaya jaae aur teesare din jee utte.
tab us kee baten un ko smaran ain.
aur kabra se lauttkar unhon ne un gyarahon ko, aur, aur sab ko, ye baten kah sunai.
jinhon ne praeariton se ye baten kahee, ve mariyam magadaleenee aur yoanna aur yakoob kee mata mariyam aur un ke sath kee aur striayan bhee theen.
parantu un kee baten unahen kahanee see samajh padee, aur unhon ne un kee prateeati n kee.
tab pataras uttkar kabra par daud gaya, aur jhukakar keval kapade pade dekhe, aur jo hua tha, us se achambha karata hua, apane ghar chala gaya..
dekho, usee din un men se do jan immaus nam aek ganv ko ja rahe the, jo yarooshalem se koi sat meel kee dooree par tha.
aur ve in sab baton par jo huin thee, apas men batacheet karate ja rahe the.
aur jab ve apas men batacheet aur poochhtachh kar rahe the, to yeeshu ap pas akar un ke sath ho liya.
paranatu un kee ankhe aeesee band kar dee gain thee, ki use paahichan n sake.
us ne un se poochha ye kya baten haai, jo tum chalate chalate apas men karate ho? ve udas se khde rah gae.
yah sunakar, unamen se klaiyupas nam aek vyaaktai ne kaha kya too yarooshalem men akela paradeshaee haai jo naheen janata, ki in dinon men us men kya hua haai?
us ne un se poochha kaun see baten? unhon ne us se kaha yeeshu nasaree ke vishay men jo parameshvar aur sab logon ke nikatt kam aur vachan men samarthee bhvishyadvkta tha.
aur mahayajakon aur hamare saradaron ne use pakadva diya, ki us par mratyu kee agyaa dee jaae aur use kroos par chaddhvaya.
parantu hamen asha thee, ki yahee israel ko chhuttkara dega, aur in sab baton ke sivay is ghattna ko huae teesara din haai.
aur ham men se kai striayon ne bhee hamen ashcharya men dal diya haai, jo bhor ko kabra par gai theen.
aur jab us kee loth n pai, to yah kahatee hui ai, ki ham ne svargadooton ka darshan paya, jinhon ne kaha ki vah jeevit haai.
tab hamare saathaiyon men se kai aek kabra par gaa, aur jaaisa striayon ne kaha tha, vaaisa hee paya parantu us ko n dekha.
tab us ne un se kaha he nirbuaddhyaie, aur bhvishyadvktaon kee sab baton par vishvas karane men mandamaatiyon!
kya avashy n tha, ki maseeh ye dukh uttakar apanee maahima men pravesh kare?
itane men ve us ganv ke pas pahunche, jahan ve ja rahe the, aur usake ddhng se aeesa jan pada, ki vah age bada chahata haai.
parantu unhon ne yah kahakar use roka, ki hamare sath raha kyonaki sandhya ho chalee haai aur din ab bahut ddhl gaya haai. tab vah un ke sath rahane ke liye bheetar gaya.
tab un kee ankhe khul gain aur unhon ne use pahachan liya, aur vah un kee ankhon se chhpai gaya.
unhon ne apas men kaha jab vah marga men ham se baten karata tha, aur paavitra shasr ka arth hamen samajhata tha, to kya hamare man men uttejana n utpann hui?
ve usee ghadee uttkar yarooshalem ko lautt gaa, aur un gyarahon aur un ke saathaiyon ko ikatthe paya.
ve kahate the, prabhu sachamuch jee utta haai, aur shamaun ko dikhai diya haai.
tab unhon ne marga kee baten unhen bata deen aur yah bhee ki unhon ne use rottee todte samay kyonkar pahachana..
ve ye baten kah hee rahe the, ki vah ap hee un ke beech men a khda hua aur un se kaha, tumhen shantai mile.
parantu ve ghabara gaa, aur dr gaa, aur samajhe, ki ham kisee boot ko dekhte haain.
us ne un se kaha kyon ghabarate ho? aur tumhare man men kyon sandeh uttte haain?
mere hath aur mere panv ko dekho, ki maain vaheen hoon mujhe chookar dekho kyonki atma ke haddee mans naheen hota jaaisa mujh men dekhte ho.
yah kahakar us ne unahen apane hath panv dikhaae.
jab anand ke mare un ko prateeati n hui, aur ashcharya karate the, to us ne un se poochha kya yahan tumhare pas kuchh bhojan haai?
unhon ne use boonee machhlee ka ttukada diya.
us ne lekar un ke samhane khaya.
fir us ne un se kaha, ye meree ve baten haai, jo maain ne tumhare sath rahate hua, tum se kahee thee, ki avashy haai, ki jitanee baten moosa kee vyavastha aur bhavishyadvktaon aur bhjanon kee pustakon me, mere vishay men likhee haai, sab pooree hon.
tab us ne paavitra shaasr boojhne ke liye un kee samajh khol dee.
aur un se kaha, yon likha haai ki maseeh du:kh uttaaega, aur teesare din mare huon men se jee uttega.
aur yarooshalem se lekar sab jaatiyon men man firav ka aur papon kee kshama ka prachar, usee ke nam se kiya jaaega.
tum in sab baten ke gavah ho.
aur dekho, jis kee pratigyaa mere pita ne kee haai, maain us ko tum par utaroonga aur jab tak svarga men samarth n pao, tab tak tum isee nagar men tthare raho..
tab vah unhen baaitaaniyyah tak bahar le gaya, aur apane hath uttakar unhen ashaeesh dee.
aur unhen ashaeesh dete huae vah un se alag ho gaya aur svarga se utta liya gaya.
aur ve us ko dandvata karake bade anand se yarooshalem ko lautt gaae.
aur lagatar maandair men upaasthiat hokar parameshvar kee stuati kiya karate the..
un dinon men augoostus kaaisar kee or se agyaa nikalee, ki sare jagat ke logon ke nam likhe jaen.
yah paahilee nam likhai us samay hui, jab kvairiniyus sooriya ka haakim tha.
aur sab log nam likhvane ke liye apane apane nagar ko gaae.
so yoosufa bhee isaliye ki vah daud ke gharane aur vansh ka tha, galeel ke nasarat nagar se yahoodiya men daud ke nagar baaitalaham ko gaya.
us ke vahan rahate huae usake janane ke din poore hue.
aur us desh men kitane gaderiye the, jo rat ko maaidan men rahakar apane jhund ka pahara dete the.
aur prabhu ka aek doot un ke pas a khda hua aur prabhu ka tej un ke charon or chamaka, aur ve bahut dr gaae.
tab svargadoot ne un se kaha, mat dro kyonaki dekho maain tumhen bade anand ka susamachar sunata hoon jo sab logon ke liye hoga.
ki aj daud ke nagar men tumhare liye aek uddharakarta janma haai, aur yahee maseeh prabhu haai.
aur is ka tumhare liye yah pata haai, ki tum aek balak ko kapade me lipatta hua aur charanee men pada paoge.
tab aekaaek us svargadoot ke sath svargadooton ka dal parameshvar kee stuti karate huae aur yah kahate dikhai diya.
ki akash men parameshvar kee mahima aur prathvee par un manushyon men jinase vah prasann haai shaaantai ho..
jab svargadoot un ke pas se svarga ko chale gaa, to gadeariyon ne apas men kaha, ao, ham baaitalaham jakar yah bat jo hui haai, aur jise prabhu ne hamen bataya haai, dekhen.
aur unhon ne turant jakar mariyam aur yoosufa ko aur charanee men us balak ko pada dekha.
inhen dekhkar unhon ne vah bat jo is balak ke vishay men un se kahee gai thee, pragatt kee.
aur sab sunanevalon ne un baton se jo gadriyon ne un se kaheen ashcharya kiya.
parantu mariyam ye sab baten apane man men rakhkar sochatee rahee.
aur gadriye jaaisa un se kaha gaya tha, vaaisa hee sab sunakar aur dekhkar parameshvar kee maahima aur stuti karate huae lautt gaae..
jab att din poore hua, aur usake khtane ka samay aya, to usaka nam yeeshu rakha gaya, jo svargadoot ne usake pett men ane se pahile kaha tha.
aur jab moosa ko vyavastha ke anusar un ke shuuddh hone ke din poore huae to ve use yarooshalem men le gaa, ki prabhu ke samane laaen.
jaaisa ki prabhu kee vyavastha men likha haai ki har aek pahilautta prabhu ke liye paavitra ttharega.
aur prabhu kee vyavastha ke vachan ke anusar pandukon ka aek joda, ya kabootar ke do bachche la kar baalidan karen.
aur dekho, yarooshalem men shamaun nam aek manushy tha, aur vah manushy dharmee aur bhkt tha aur israael kee shaantai kee batt joh raha tha, aur paavitra atma us par tha.
aur paavitra atma se us ko chitavanee hui thee, ki jab tak too prabhu ke maseeh ko dekh ne lega, tak tak mratyu ko n dekhega.
aur vah atma ke sikhane se mandair men aya aur jab mata-apita us balak yeeshu ko bheetar laa, ki usake liye vyavastha kee reeati ke anusar karen.
to us ne use apanee god men liya aur parameshvar ka dhanyavad karake kaha,
he svamee, ab too apane das ko apane vachan ke anusar shaaantai se vida karata haai.
kyonaki meree ankho ne tere uddhar ko dekh liya haai.
jise too ne sab deshaen ke logon ke samhane taaiyar kiya haai.
ki vah any jaatiyon ko prakash dene ke liye jyoti, aur tere nij log israael kee maahima ho.
aur usaka pita aur us kee mata in baton se jo usake vishay men kahee jatee thee, ashcharya karate the.
tab shamaun ne un ko ashaeesh dekar, us kee mata mariyam se kaha dek, vah to israael men bahuton ke girane, aur uttne ke liye, aur aek aeesa chinh hone ke liye ttharaya gaya haai, jis ke virodha men baten kee jaaegeen --
varan tera praan bhee talavar se var par chhdai jaaega-- is se bahut dayon ke vichar pragatt honge.
aur vah us ghadee vahan akar prabhu ka dhanyavad karane lagee, aur un sabhon se, jo yarooshalem ke chhuttkare kee batt johate the, usake vishay men baten karane lagee.
aur jab ve prabhu kee vyavastha ke anusar sab kuchh nipatta chuke to galeel men apane nagar nasarat ko fir chale gaae..
aur balak baddhta, aur balavant hota, aur buaddh ise paaripoorn hota gaya aur parameshvar ka anugrah us par tha.
usake mata-apita praati varsha fasah ke pabrba men yarooshalem ko jaya karate the.
jab vah barah varsha ka hua, to ve pabrba kee reeti ke anusar yarooshalem ko gaae.
aur jab ve un dinon ko poora karake lauttne lage, to vah ladka yeeshu yarooshalem men rah gaya aur yah usake mata-pita naheen janate the.
ve yah samajhkar, ki vah aur yatraiyon ke sath hoga, aek din ka padav nikal gaae: aur use apane kuttumbaiyon aur janapahachanon men ddoonddhne lage.
par jab naheen mila, to ddoonddhte-ddoonddhte yarooshalem ko fir lautt gaae.
aur teen din ke bad unhon ne use maandair men upadeshakon ke beech men baaitte, un kee sunate aur un se prashn karate huae paya.
aur jitane us kee sun rahe the, ve sab us kee samajh aur usake uttron se chakit the.
tab ve use dekhkar chakit huae aur us kee mata ne us se kaha he putra, too ne ham se kyon aeesa vyavahar kiya? dek, tera pita aur maain kuddhte huae tujhe ddoonddhte the.
us ne un se kaha tum mujhe kyon ddoonddhte the? kya naheen janate the, ki mujhe apane pita ke bhvan men hona avashy haai?
parantu jo bat us ne un se kahee, unhon ne use naheen samajha.
tab vah un ke sath gaya, aur nasarat men aya, aur un ke vash men raha aur us kee mata ne ye sab baten apane man men rakheen..
aur yeeshu buddh iddh aur deela-daul men aur parameshvar aur manushyon ke anugrah men baddhta gaya..
tibiriyus kaaisar ke rajy ke pandrahaven varsha men jab puantaiyus peelatus yahoodiya ka haakim tha, aur galeel men herodes nam chauthai ka itooraaiya, aur trakhoneetis me, usaka bhai filippus, aur aabilene men lisaaniyas chauthai ke raja the.
aur jab hanna aur kaaifaa mahayajak the, us samay parameshvar ka vachan jangal men jakarayah ke putra yoohanna ke pas pahuncha.
aur vah yaradan ke as pas ke sare desh men akar, papon kee kshama ke liye man firav ke bapatisma ka prachar karane laga.
jaaise yashaayah bhvishyadvkta ke kahe huae vachanon kee pustak men likha haai, ki jangal men aek pukaranevale ka shabd ho raha he ki prabhu ka marga taaiyar karo, us kee sadken seedhaee banao.
har aek ghaattee bhr dee jaaegee, aur har aek pahad aur tteela neecha kiya jaaega aur jo tteddha haai seedha, aur jo uncha neecha haai vah chauras marga banega.
aur har praanee parameshvar ke uddhar ko dekhega..
jo bheed kee bheed us se bapatisma lene ko nikal kar atee thee, un se vah kahata tha he sanp ke bachcho, tumhen kis ne jata diya, ki anevale krodha se bhago.
so man firav ke yogy fal lao: aur apane apane man men yah n socho, ki hamara pita ibraaheem haai kyonaki maain tum se kahata hoo, ki parameshvar in patthron se ibraaheem ke liye santan utpann kar sakata haai.
aur ab hee kulhada pedon kee jad par dhara haai, isaaliye jo jo ped achchha fal naheen lata, vah katta aur ag men jhonka jata haai.
aur logon ne us se poochha, to ham kya karen?
us ne unahen utar diya, ki jis ke pas do kurate hon? vah usake sath jis ke pas naheen haain bantt de aur jis ke pas bhojan ho, vah bhee aeesa hee kare.
aur mahasool lenevale bhee bapatisma lene aa, aur us se poochha, ki he guro, ham kya karen?
us ne un se kaha, jo tumhare liye ttharaya gaya haai, us se adhaik n lena.
aur sipaahiyon ne bhee us se yah poochha, ham kya karen? us ne un se kaha, kisee par upadrav n karana, aur n jootta dosh lagana, aur apanee majadooree par santosh karana..
usaka soop, usake hath men haai aur vah apana khlihan achchhee tarah se safa karega aur gehoon ko apane khtte men ikattha karega, parantu boosee ko us ag men jo bujhne kee naheen jala dega..
so vah bahut see shaiksha de dekar logon ko susamachar sunata raha.
parantu us ne chauthai desh ke raja herodes ko usake bhai filippus kee patnee herodiyas ke vishay, aur sab kukamorn ke vishay men jo us ne kiae the, ulahana diya.
isaliye herodes ne un sab se baddhkar yah kukarma bhee kiya, ki yoohanna ko bandeegrah men dal diya..
jab sab logon ne bapaatisma liya, aur yeeshu bhee bapaatisma lekar praarthna kar raha tha, to akash khul gaya.
aur paavitra atma shaareearik roop men kabootar kee nai us par utara, aur yah akashavanee hui, ki too mera piry putra haai, maain tujh se prasann hoon..
jab yeeshu ap upadesh karane laga, jo lagabhg tees varsha kee ayu ka tha aur jaaisa samajha jata tha yoosufa ka putra tha aur v aelee ka.
