aur vah inosh ka, aur vah shot ka, aur vah adam ka, aur vah parameshvar ka tha..
fir yeeshu paavitraatma se bhra hua, yaradan se lautta aur chalees din tak atma ke sikhane se jangal men firata raha aur shautan us kee pareeksha karata raha.
un dinon men us ne kuchh n khaya aur jab ve din poore ho gaa, to use bookh lagee.
aur shautan ne us se kaha yaadi too parameshvar ka putra haai, to is patthr se kah, ki rottee ban jaae
yeeshu ne use uttr diya ki likha haai, manushy keval rottee se jeevit n rahega.
tab shautan use le gaya aur us ko pal bhr men jagat ke sare rajy dikhaae.
aur us se kaha maain yah sab aadhaikar, aur in ka vibhv tujhe doonga, kyonaki vah mujhe saunpa gaya haai: aur jise chahata hoo, usee ko de deta hoon.
yeeshu ne use uttr diya likha haai ki too prabhu apane parameshvar ko pranam kara aur keval usee kee upasana kara.
kyonaki likha haai, ki vah tere vishay men apane svargadooton ko agyaa dega, ki ve teree raksha karen.
aur ve tujhe hathon hath utta lenge aeesa n ho ki tere panv men patthr se ttes lage.
yeeshu ne us ko uttr diya yah bhee kaha gaya haai, ki too prabhu apane parameshvar kee pareeksha n karana.
jab shautan sab pareeksha kar chuka, tab kuchh samay ke liye usake pas se chala gaya..
fir yeeshu atma kee samarth se bhra hua galeel ko lautta, aur us kee charcha as pas ke sare desh men faail gai.
aur vah un hee aradhanalayon men upadesh karata raha, aur sab us kee badai karate the..
aur vah nasarat men aya jahan pala posa gaya tha aur apanee reeti ke anusar sabt ke din aradhanalay men ja kar paddhne ke liye khda hua.
yashaayah bhvishyadvkta kee pustak use dee gai, aur us ne pustak kholakar, vah jagah nikalee jahan yah likha tha.
ki prabhu ka atma mujh par haai, isaaliye ki us ne kangalon ko susamachar sunane ke liye mera abhaishok kiya haai, aur mujhe isaliye bheja haai, ki bandhauon ko chhuttkare ka aur andhaen ko drashtti pane ka susamachar prachar karoon aur kuchale huon ko chhudaun.
aur prabhu ke prasann rahane ke varsha ka prachar karoon.
tab us ne pustak band karake sevak ke hath men de dee, aur baaitt gaya: aur aradhanalay ke sab logon kee ankh us par lagee thee.
tab vah un se kahane laga, ki aj hee yah lekh tumhare samhane poora hua haai.
aur sab ne use saraha, aur jo anugrah kee baten usake munh se nikalatee theee, un se achambha kiya aur kahane lage kya yah yoosufa ka putra naheen?
us ne us se kaha tum mujh par yah kahavat avashy kahoge, ki he vaaidh, apane ap ko achchha kara! jo kuchh ham ne suna haai ki kafaranahoom men kiya gaya haai use yahan apane desh men bhee kara.
aur us ne kaha maain tum se sach kahata hoo, koi bhavishyadvkta apane desh men mana-samman naheen pata.
aur maain tum se sach kahata hoo, ki aeliyyah ke dinon men jab saddhe teen varsha tak akash band raha, yahan tak ki sare desh men bada akal pada, to israael men bahut see vidhavaaen theen.
par aeliyyah un men se kisee ke pas naheen bheja gaya, keval saaida ke sarafat men aek vidhava ke pasa.
aur ileesha bhavishyadvkta ke samay israael men bahut se koddhee the, par naman soorayanee ko chhod un men se kai shuuddh naheen kiya gaya.
ye baten sunate hee jitane aradhanalay men the, sab krodha se bhr gaae.
aur uttkar use nagar se bahar nikala, aur jis pahad par un ka nagar basa hua tha, us kee chottee par le chale, ki use vahan se neeche gira den.
par vah un ke beech men se nikalakar chala gaya..
fir vah galeel ke kafaranahoom nagar men gaya, aur sabt ke din logon ko upadesh de raha tha.
ve us ke upadesh se chakit ho gaae kyonki usaka vachan aadhaikar saahit tha.
aradhanalay men aek manushy tha, jis men ashuuddh atma thee.
vah unche shabd se chilla utta, he yeeshu nasaree, hamen tujh se kya kama? kya too hamen nash karane aya haai? maain tujhe janata hoon too kaun haai? too parameshvar ka pavitra jan haai.
yeeshu ne use danttkar kaha, chup raha: aur us men se nikal ja: tab dushttatma use beech men pattkakar bina haani pahunchaae us men se nikal gai.
is par sab ko achambha hua, aur ve apas men baten karake kahane lage, yah kaaisa vachan haai? ki vah adhaikar aur samarth ke sath ashuuddh atmaon ko agyaa deta haai, aur ve nikal jatee haain.
vah aradhanalay men se uttkar shamaun ke ghar men gaya aur shamaun kee sas ko jvar chaddha hua tha, aur unhon ne usake liye us se binatee kee.
us ne usake nikatt khde hokar jvar ko dantta aur vah us par se utar gaya aur vah turant uttkar un kee seva tthal karane lagee..
aur dushttatma chillatee aur yah kahatee hui ki too parameshvar ka putra haai, bahuton men se nikal gai par vah unhen danttta aur bolane naheen deta tha, kyonaki ve janate the, ki yah maseeh haai..
jab din hua to vah nikalakar aek jangalee jagah men gaya, aur bheed kee bheed use ddoonddhtee hui usake pas ai, aur use rokane lagee, ki hamare pas se n ja.
parantu us ne un se kaha mujhe aur aur nagaron men bhee parameshvar ke rajy ka susamachar sunana avashy haai, kyonaki maain isee liye bheja gaya hoon..
aur vah galeel ke aradhanalayon men prachar karata raha..
jab bheed us par giree padtee thee, aur parameshvar ka vachan sunatee thee, aur vah gannesarat kee jheel ke kinare par khda tha, to aeesa hua.
ki us ne jheel ke kinare do naven lagee hui dekhee, aur machhuve un par se utarakar jal dhae rahe the.
un navon men se ek par jo shamaun kee thee, chaddhkar, us ne us se binatee kee, ki kinare se thoda hatta le chale, tab vah baaittkar logon ko nav par se upadesh dene laga.
jab ve baten kar chuka, to shamaun se kaha, gaahire men le chal, aur machhaliyan pakadne ke liye apane jal dalo.
shamaun ne usako uttr diya, ki he svamee, ham ne saree rat mihanat kee aur kuchh n pakada taubhee tere kahane se jal daloonga.
jab unhon ne aeesa kiya, to bahut machhaliyan ghor laa, aur un ke jal fattne lage.
is par unhon ne apane saathaiyon ko jo doosaree nav par the, sanket kiya, ki akar hamaree sahayata karo: aur unhon ne akar, dono nav yahan tak bhr leen ki ve oobane lageen.
yah dekhkar shamaun pataras yeeshu ke panvon par gira, aur kaha he prabhu, mere pas se ja, kyonki maain papee manushy hoon.
kyonaki itanee machhaliyon ke pakade jane se use aur usake sathaiyon ko bahut achambha hua.
aur vaaise hee jabadee ke putra yakoob aur yoohanna ko bhee, jo shamaun ke sahabhagee the, achambha hua: tab yeeshu ne shamaun se kaha, mat dra: ab se too manushyon ko jeevata pakada karega.
aur v navon ko kinare par le aae aur sab kuchh chhodkar usake peechhe ho liae..
jab vah kisee nagar men tha, to dekho, vahan koddh se bhra hua aek manushy tha, aur vah yeeshu ko dekhkar munh ke bal gira, aur binatee kee ki he prabhu yaadi too chahe ho mujhe shuuddh kar sakata haai.
us ne hath baddhakar use chooa aur kaha maain chahata hoon too shuuddh ho ja: aur usaka koddh turant jata raha.
tab us ne use chitaya, ki kisee se n kah, parantu jake apane ap ko yajak ko dikha, aur apane shuuddh hone ke vishay men jo kuchh moosa ne chaddhava ttharaya haai use chaddha ki un par gavahee ho.
parantu us kee charcha aur bhee faailatee gai, aur bheed kee bheed us kee sunane ke liye aur apanee bimaariyon se change hone ke liye ikatthee hui.
parantu vah jangalon men alag jakar praarthna kiya karata tha..
aur aek din hua ki vah upadesh de raha tha, aur fareesee aur vyavasthapak vahan baaitte huae the, jo galeel aur yahoodiya ke har aek ganv se, aur yarooshalem se aae the aur changa karane ke liye prabhu kee samarth usake sath thee.
aur dekho kai log aek manushy ko jo jhole ka mara hua tha, khatt par laa, aur ve use bheetar le jane aur yeeshu ke samhane rakhne ka upay ddoonddh rahe the.
aur jab bheed ke karan use bheetar n le ja sake to unhon ne kotte par chaddh kar aur khpraail hattakar, use khatt samet beech men yeeshu ke samhane utara diya.
us ne un ka vishvas dekhkar us se kaha he manushy, tere pap kshama hue.
tab shaasree aur fareesee vivad karane lage, ki yah kaun haai, jo parameshvar kee ninda karata haai? parameshvar ka chhod kaun papon kee kshama kar sakata haai?
yeeshu ne un ke man kee baten janakar, un se kaha ki tum apane manon men kya vivad kar rahe ho?
parantu isaaliye ki tum jano ki manushy ke putra ko prathvee par pap kshama karane ka bhee adhaikar haai us ne us jhole ke mare huae se kaha, maain tujh se kahata hoo, utt aur apanee khatt uttakar apane ghar chala ja.
vah turant un ke samhane utta, aur jis par vah pada tha use uttakar, parameshvar kee badai karata hua apane ghar chala gaya.
tab sab chaakit huae aur parameshvar kee badai karane lage, aur bahut drakar kahane lage, ki aj ham ne anokhee baten dekhee haain..
tab vah sab kuchh chhodkar utta, aur usake peechhe ho liya.
aur levee ne apane ghar men usake liye badee javanar kee aur chungee lenevalon kee aur auron kee jo usake sath bhojan karane baaitte the aek badee bheed thee.
aur fareesee aur un ke shaasree us ke chelon se yah kahakar kudkudane lage, ki tum chungee lenevalon aur paapiyon ke sath kyon khate-peete ho?
yeeshu ne un ko uttr diya ki vaaidh bhle changon ke liye nahee, parantu beemaron ke liye avashy haai.
maain dharmiyon ko nahee, parantu paapiyon ko man firane ke liye bulane aya hoon.
aur unhon ne us se kaha, yoohanna ke chele to barabar upavas rakhte aur praarthna kiya karate haai, aur vaaise hee fareeasiyon ke bhee, parantu tere chele to khate peete haain!
yeeshu ne un se kaha kya tum baraatiyon se jab tak doolha un ke sath rahe, upavas karenge.
parantu ve din aaenge, jin men doolha un se alag kiya jaaega, tab ve un dinon men upavas karenge.
us ne ek aur drashttant bhee un se kaha ki koi manushy naye pahiravan men se faadkar purane paahiravan men paaiband naheen lagata, naheen to naya fatt jaega aur vah paaiband purane men mel bhee naheen khaega.
aur koi naya dakhras puranee mashakon men nahee bhrata, naheen to naya dakhras mashakon ko faadkar bah jaaega, aur mashaken bhee nash ho jaaengee.
parantu naya dakhras nai mashakon men bhrana chahiye.
koi manushy purana dakhras peekar naya naheen chahata kyonaki vah kahata haai, ki purana hee achchha haai..
fir sabt ke din vah kheton men se hokar ja raha tha, aur usake chele balen tod todkar, aur hathon se mal mal kar khate jate the.
tab fareesiyon men se kai aek kahane lage, tum vah kam kyon karate ho jo sabt ke din karana uchit naheen?
yeeshu ne un ka uttr diya kya tum ne yah naheen paddha, ki daud ne jab vah aur usake sathee bookhe the to kya kiya?
vah kyonkar parameshvar ke ghar men gaya, aur bhentt kee rottyaian lekar khai, jinhen khana yajakon ko chhod aur kisee ko uchit nahanee, aur apane sathaiyon ko bhee dee?
aur us ne un se kaha manushy ka putra sabt ke din ka bhee prabhu haai.
aur aeesa hua ki kisee aur sabt ke din ko vah aradhanalay men jakar upadesh karane laga aur vahan aek manushy tha, jis ka dahina hath sookha tha.
shaasree aur fareesee us par dosh lagane ka avasar pane ke liye us kee tak men the, ki dekhen ki vah sabt ke din changa karata haai ki naheen.
parantu vah un ke vichar janata tha isaliye usane sookhe hathvale manushy se kaha ut, beech men khda ho: vah utt khda hua.
yeeshu ne un se kaha maain tum se yah poochhta hoon ki sabt ke din kya uchit haai, bhla karan ya bura karana praan ko bachana ya nash karana?
aur us ne charon or un sabhon ko dekhkar us manushy se kaha apana hath baddha: us ne aeesa hee kiya, aur usaka hath fir changa ho gaya.
parantu ve ape se bahar hokar apas men vivad karane lage ki ham yeeshu ke sath kya karen?
aur un dinon men vah pahad par praarthna karane ko nikala, aur parameshvar se praarthna karane men saree rat bitai.
jab din hua, to us ne apane chelon ko bulakar un men se barah chun lia, aur un ko praerit kaha.
aur mattee aur thoma aur halafai ka putra yakoob aur shamaun jo jelotes kahalata haai.
aur yakoob ka betta yahooda aur yahooda isakariyotee, jo usaka pakadvanevala bana.
tab vah un ke sath utarakar chauras jagah men khda hua, aur usake chelon kee badee bheed, aur sare yahoodiya aur yarooshalem aur soor aur saaida ke samudra ke kinare se bahutere log, jo us kee sunane aur apanee beemaariyon se changa hone ke liy usake pas aae the, vahan the.
aur ashuuddh atmaon ke sataae huae log bhee achchhe kiae jate the.
tab us ne apane chelon kee or dekhkar kaha dhany ho tum, jo deen ho, kyonaki parameshvar ka rajy tumhara haai.
dhany ho tum, jo ab bookhe ho kyonaki trapt kiae jaoge dhany ho tum, jo ab rote ho, kyonaki hansoge.
dhany ho tum, jab manushy ke putra ke karan log tum se baair karenge, aur tumhen nikal denge, aur tumharee ninda karenge, aur tumhara nam bura janakar katt denge.
us din anaandait hokar uchhlana, kyonki dekho, tumhare liye svarga men bada praatifal haai: un ke bapa-dade bhvishyadvktaon ke sath bhee vaaisa hee kiya karate the.
parantu hay tum para jo dhanavan ho, kyonaki tum apanee shaaantai pa chuke.
parantu hay tum para jo ab trapt ho, kyonki bookhe hoge: hay, tum para jo ab hansate ho, kyonki shaek karoge aur rooge.
hay, tum para jab sab manushy tumhen bhla kahe, kyonki un ke bapa-dade jootte bhvishyadvktaon ke sath bhee aeesa hee kiya karate the..
parantu maain tum sunanevalon se kahata hoo, ki apane shatrauon se praem rakho jo tum se baair kare, un ka bhla karo.
jo tumhen srap de, un ko ashaeesh do: jo tumhara apaman kare, un ke liye praarthna karo.
jo tere aek gal par thppad mare us kee or doosara bhee faer de aur jo teree dohar chheen le, us ko kurata lene se bhee n roka.
jo koi tujh se mange, use de aur jo teree vastu chheen le, us se n manga.
aur jaaisa tum chahate ho ki log tumhare sath kare, tum bhee un ke sath vaaisa hee karo.
yaadi tum apane praem rakhnevalon ke sath praem rakho, to tumharee kya badai? kyonki papee bhee apane praem rakhnevalon ke sath praem rakhte haain.
aur yaadi tum apane bhlai karanevalon hee ke sath bhlai karate ho, to tumharee kya badai? kyonaki papee bhee aeesa hee karate haain.
aur yaadi tum use udhaar do, jin se fir pane kee asha rakhte ho, to tumharee kya badai? kyonaki papee paapiyon ko udhaar dete haai, ki utana hee fir paaen.
baran apane shatrauon se praem rakho, aur bhlai karo: aur fir pane kee as n rakhkar udhaar do aur tumhare liye bada fal hoga aur tum paramapradhaan ke santan ttharoge, kyonki vah un par jo dhanyavad naheen karate aur buron par bhee krapalu haai.
jaaisa tumhara pita dayavant haai, vaaise hee tum bhee dayavant bano.
dosh mat lagao to tum par bhee dosh naheen lagaya jaaega: doshaee n ttharao, to tum bhee doshaee naheen ttharaae jaoge: kshama karo, to tumharee bhee kshama kee jaaegee.
diya karo, to tumhen bhee diya jaaega: log poora nam daba dabakar aur hila hilakar aur ubhrata hua tumharee god men dalenge, kyonki jis nam se tum napate ho, usee se tumhare liye bhee napa jaaega..
fir us ne un se aek drashttant kaha kya andha, andho ko marga bata sakata haai? kya dono gadhe men naheen girenge?
chela apane guroo se bada nahee, parantu jo koi siddh hoga, vah apane guroo ke saman hoga.
too apane bhai kee ankh ke tinake ko kyon dekhta haai, aur apanee hee ankh ka lattha tujhe naheen soojhta?
aur jab too apanee hee ankh ka lattha naheen dekhta, to apane bhai se kyonkar kah sakata haai, he bhai, tthar ja teree ankh se tinake ko nikal doon? he kapattee, paahile apanee ankh se lattha nikal, tab jo tinaka tere bhai kee ankh men haai, bhlee bhanti dekhkar nikal sakega.
koi achchha ped nahee, jo nikamma fal laa, aur n to koi nikamma ped haai, jo achchha fal laae.
