kyonaki vah hamaree jati se praem rakhta haai, aur usee ne hamare aradhanalay ko banaya haai.
yeeshu un ke sath sath chala, par jab vah ghar se door n tha, to soobedar ne sake pas kai mitraen ke dara kahala bheja, ki he prabhu dukh n utta, kyonaki maain is yogy nahee, ki too meree chht ke tale aae.
isee karan maain ne apane ap ko is yogy bhee n samajha, ki tere pas au, par vachan hee kah de to mera sevak changa ho jaaega.
maain bhee paradhaeen manushy hoon aur sipahee mere hath men haai, aur jab aek ko kahata hoo, ja, to vah jata haai, aur doosare se kahata hoon ki a, to ata haai aur apane kisee das ko ki yah kar, to vah use karata haai.
yah sunakar yeeshu ne achambha kiya, aur us ne munh faerakar us bheed se jo usake peechhe a rahee thee kaha, maain tum se kahatah hoo, ki maain ne israael men bhee aeesa vishvas naheen paya.
aur bheje huae logon ne ghar lauttkar, us das ko changa paya..
thode din ke bad vah nain nam ke aek nagar ko gaya, aur usake chele, aur badee bheed usake sath ja rahee thee.
jab vah nagar ke faattk ke pas pahuncha, to dekho, log aek murade ko bahar liae ja rahe the jo apanee man ka aekalauta putra tha, aur vah vidhava thee: aur nagar ke bahut se log usake sath the.
use dekh kar prabhu ko taras aya, aur us ne kaha mat ro.
