usake chelon ne kaha, dek, ab to too kholakar kahata haai, aur koi drashttant naheen kahata.
ab ham jan gaa, ki too sab kuchh janata haai, aur tujhe prayojan nahee, ki koi tujh se poochhe, is se ham prateeti karate haai, ki too parameshvar se nikala haai.
yah sun yeeshu ne un se kaha, kya tum ab prateeati karate ho?
maain ne ye baten tum se isaliye kahee haai, ki tumhen mujh men shaaantai mile sansar men tumhen klesh hota haai, parantu ddhaddhs bandhae, maain ne sansar ko jeen liya haai..
yeeshu ne ye baten kaheen aur apanee ankhe akash kee or uttakar kaha, he pita, vah ghadee a pahunchee, apane putra kee maahima kar, ki putra bhee teree mahima kare.
kyonaki too ne us ka sab praaanaiyon par aadhaikar diya, ki jinhen too ne us ko diya haai, un sab ko vah anant jeevan de.
aur anant jeevan yah haai, ki ve tujh advait sachche parameshvar ko aur yeeshu maseeh ko, jise too ne bheja haai, jane.
jo kam too ne mujhe karane ko diya tha, use poora karake maain ne prathvee par teree mahima kee haai.
aur ab, he pita, too apane sath meree mahima us maahima se kar jo jagat ke hone se paahile, meree tere sath thee.
maain ne tera nam un manushyon par pragatt kiya jinhen too ne jagat men se mujhe diya: ve tere the aur too ne unhen mujhe diya aur unhon ne tere vachan ko man liya haai.
ab ve jan gaae haai, ki jo kuchh too ne mujhe diya haai, sab teree or se haai.
kyonaki jo baten too ne mujhe pahuncha dee, maain ne unhen unako pahuncha diya aur unhon ne un ko grahan kiya: aur sach sach jan liya haai, ki maain teree or se nikala hoo, aur prateeati kar lee haai ki too hee ne mujhe bheja.
maain un ke liye binatee karata hoo, sansar ke liye binatee naheen karata hoon parantu unheen ke liye jinhen too ne mujhe diya haai, kyonki ve tere haain.
aur jo kuchh mera haai vah sab tera haai aur jo tera haai vah mera haai vah sab tera haai aur jo tera haai, vah mera haai aur in se meree maahima pragatt hui haai.
maain age ko jagat men n rahoonga, parantu ye jagat men rahenge, aur maain tere pas ata hoon he paavitra pita, apane us nam se jo too ne mujhe diya haai, un kee raksha kar, ki ve hamaree nai aek hon.
jab maai. un ke sath tha, to maain ne tere us nam se, jo too ne mujhe diya haai, un kee raksha kee, maain ne un kee chaukasee kee aur vinash ke putra ko chhod un men se kai nash n hua, isaaliye ki pavitra shaasr kee bat pooree ho.
parantu ab maain tere pas ata hoo, aur ye baten jagat men kahata hoo, ki ve mera anand apane men poora paaen.
maain ne tera vachan unhen pahuncha diya haai, aur sansar ne un se baair kiya, kyonaki jaaisa maain sansar ka nahee, vaaise hee ve bhee sansar ke naheen.
maain yah binatee naheen karata, ki too unhen jagat se utta le, parantu yah ki too unhen us dushtt se bachaae rakh.
jaaise maain sansar ka nahee, vaaise hee ve bhee sansar ke naheen.
saty ke dara unhen paavitra kara: tera vachan saty haai.
jaaise too ne jagat men mujhe bheja, vaaise hee maain ne bhee unhen jagat men bheja.
aur un ke liye maain apane ap ko pavitra karata hoon taki ve bhee saty ke dara pavitra kiae jaaen.
jaaisa too he pita mujh men haai, aur maain tujh men hoo, vaaise hee ve bhee ham men ho, isaaliye ki jagat prateeti kare, ki too hee ne mujhe bheja.
aur vah maahima jo too ne mujhe dee, maain ne unhen dee haai ki ve vaaise hee aek hon jaaise kee ham aek haain.
maain un men aur too mujh men ki ve siddh hokar aek ho jaae, aur jagat jane ki too hee ne mujhe bheja, aur jaaisa too ne mujh se praem rakha, vaaisa hee un se praem rakha.
he pita, maai. chahata hoon ki jinhen too ne mujhe diya haai, jahan maain hoo, vahan ve bhee mere sath hon ki ve meree us maahima ko dekhen jo too ne mujhe dee haai, kyonki too ne jagat kee utpaati se pahile mujh se praem rakha.
he dhaarmik pita, sansar ne mujhe naheen jana, parantu maain ne tujhe jana aur inhon ne bhee jana ki too hee ne mujhe bheja.
aur maain ne tera nam un ko bataya aur batata rahoonga ki jo praem tujh ko mujh se tha, vah un men rahe aur maain un men rahoon..
yeeshu ye baten kahakar apane chelon ke sath kidraen ke nale ke par gaya, vahan aek baree thee, jis men vah aur usake chele gaae.
aur usaka pakadvanevala yahooda bhee vah jagah janata tha, kyonki yeeshu apane chelon ke sath vahan jaya karata tha.
tab yeeshu un sab baton ko jo us par anevalee thee, janakar nikala, aur un se kahane laga, kise ddoonddhte ho?
unhon ne usako uttr diya, yeeshu nasaree ko: yeeshu ne un se kaha, maain hee hoon: aur usaka pakadvanevala yahooda bhee un ke sath khda tha.
usake yah kahate hee, ki maain hoo, ve peechhe hattkar boomi par gir pade.
tab us ne fir un se poochha, tum kis ko ddoonddhte ho.
ve bole, yeeshu nasaree ko. yeeshu ne uttr diya, maain to tum se kah chuka hoon ki maain hee hoo, yadi mujhe ddoonddhte ho to inhen jane do.
yai isaliye hua, ki vah vachan poora ho, jo us ne kaha tha ki jinhen too ne mujhe diya, un men se maain ne aek ko bhee n khoya.
shamaun pataras ne talavar, jo usake pas thee, kheenchee aur mahayajak ke das par chalakar, usaka daahina kan uda diya, us das ka nam malakhus tha.
tab yeeshu ne pataras se kaha, apanee talavar kattee men rakh: jo kattora pita ne mujhe diya haai kya maain use n peeun?
tab sipaahiyon aur un ke soobedar aur yahoodiyon ke pyadon ne yeeshu ko pakadkar bandha liya.
aur paahile use hanna ke pas le gaae kyonki vah us varsha ke mahayajak kaifaa ka sasur tha.
yah vahee kaifaa tha, jis ne yahoodiyon ko salah dee thee ki hamare logon ke liye aek puroosh ka marana achchha haai.
shamaun pataras aur aek aur chela bhee yeeshu ke peechhe ho liae: yah chela mahayajak ka jana pahachana tha aur yeeshu ke sath mahayajak ke angat men gaya.
parantu pataras dar par khda raha, tab vah doosara chela jo mahayajak ka jana pahachana tha, bahar nikala, aur darapalin se kahakar, pataras ko bheetar le aya.
us dasee ne jo darapalin thee, pataras se kaha, kya too bhee is manushy ke chelon men se haai? us ne kaha, maain naheen hoon.
das aur pyade jade ke karan koaele dhadhakakar khde tap rahe the aur pataras bhee un ke sath khda tap raha tha..
tak mahayajak ne yeeshu se usake chelon ke vishay men aur usake upadesh ke vishay men poochha.
yeeshu ne us ko uttr diya, ki maain ne jagat se kholakar baten kee maain ne sabhaon aur aradhanalay men jahan sab yahoodee ikatthe hua karate haain sada upadesh kiya aur gupt men kuchh bhee naheen kaha.
too mujh se kyon poochhta haai? sunanevalon se poochh: ki maain ne un se kya kaha? dekh ve janate haain ki maain ne kya kya kaha?
tab us ne yah kaha, to pyadon men se aek ne jo pas khda tha, yeeshu ko thppad marakar kaha, kya too mahayajak ko is prakar uttr deta haai.
yeeshu ne use uttr diya, yaadi maain ne bura kaha, to us burai par gavahee de parantu yadi bhla kaha, to mujhe kyon marata haai?
hanna ne use bandho huae kaifaa mahayajak ke pas bhej diya..
mahayajak ke dason men se aek jo usake kuttumb men se tha, jisaka kan pataras ne katt dala tha, bola, kya maain ne tujhe usake sath baree men n dekha tha?
pataras fir inkar kar gaya aur turant murga ne bang dee..
aur ve yeeshu ko kaifaa ke pas se kile ko le gaae aur bhor ka samay tha, parantu ve ap kile ke bheetar n gaae taaki ashuuddh n hon parantu fasah kha saken.
tab peelatus un ke pas bahar nikal aya aur kaha, tum is manushy par kis bat kee naliya karate ho?
unhon ne us ko uttr diya, ki yadi vah kukarmee n hota to ham use tere hath n saunpate.
peelatus ne un se kaha, tum hee ise le jakar apanee vyavastha ke anusar usaka nyay karo: yahoodayon ne us se kaha, hamen adhaikar naheen ki kisee ka praan len.
yah isaliye hua, ki yeeshu kee vah bat pooree ho jo us ne yah pata dete huae kahee thee, ki usaka marana kaaisa hoga..
yeeshu ne uttr diya, kya too yah bat apanee or se kahata haai ya auron ne mere vishay men tujh se kahee?
peelatus ne uttr diya, kya maain yahoodee hoon? teree hee jaati aur mahayajakon ne tujhe mere hath saunpa, too ne kya kiya haai?
yeeshu ne uttr diya, ki mera rajy is jagat ka nahee, yadi mera rajy is jagat ka hota, to mere sevak ladte, ki maain yahoodiyon ke hath saunpa n jata: parantu ab mera rajy yahan ka naheen.
peelatus ne us se kaha, ki too kahata haai, kyonaki maain raja hoon maain ne isaliye janm liya, aur isaliye jagat men aya hoon ki saty par gavahee doon jo koi saty ka haai, vah mera shabd sunata haai.
peelatus ne us se kaha, saty kya haai? aur yah kahakar vah fir yahoodiyon ke pas nikal gaya aur un se kaha, maain to us men kuchh dosh naheen pata.
par tumharee yah reeti haai ki maain fasah men tumhare liye aek vyaktai ko chhod doon so kya tum chahate ho, ki maain tumhare liye yahoodiyon ke raja ko chhod doon?
tab unhon ne fir chillakar kaha, ise naheen parantu hamare liye baraabba ko chhod de aur baraabba dakoo tha..
is par peelatus ne yeeshu ko lekar kode lagavaae.
aur sipaahiyon ne kantton ka mukutt goonthkar usake sir par rakha, aur use baainjanee vasr paahinaya.
aur usake pas a akar kahane lage, he yahoodiyon ke raja, pranama! aur use thppad mare.
tak peelatus ne fir bahar nikalakar logon se kaha, dekho, maain use tumhare pas fir bahar lata hoon taki tum jano ki maain kuchh bhee dosh naheen pata.
tak yeeshu kantton ka mukutt aur baainjanee vasr pahine huae bahar nikala aur peelatus ne un se kaha, dekho, yah puroosha.
jab mahayajakon aur pyadon ne use dekha, to chillakar kaha, ki use kroos par chaddha, kroos par : peelatus ne un se kaha, tum hee use lekar kroos par chaddhao kyonaki maain us men dosh naheen pata.
yahoodiyon ne us ko uttr diya, ki hamaree bhee vyavastha haai aur us vyavastha ke anusar vah mare jane ke yogy haai kyonaki us ne apane ap ko parameshvar ka putra banaya.
jab peelatus ne yah bat sunee to aur bhee dr gaya.
aur fir kile ke bheetar gaya aur yeeshu se kaha, too kahan ka haai? parantu yeeshu ne use kuchh bhee uttr n diya.
peelatus ne us se kaha, mujh se kyon naheen bolata? kya too naheen janata ki tujhe chhod dene ka aadhaikar mujhe haai aur tujhe kroos par chaddhane ka bhee mujhe adhaikar haai.
yeeshu ne uttr diya, ki yadi tujhe upar se n diya jata, to tera mujh par kuchh aadhaikar n hota isaliye jis ne mujhe tere hadha pakadvaya haai, usaka pap aadhaik haai.
is se peelatus ne use chhod dena chaha, parantu yahoodayon ne chilla chillakar kaha, yadi too is ko chhod dega to teree bhaktai kaaisar kee or naheen jo koi apane ap ko raja banata haai vah kaaisar ka samhana karata haai.
ye baten sunakar peelatus yeeshu ko bahar laya aur us jagah aek chabootara tha jo ibraanee men gabbata kahalata haai, aur nyay asan par baaitta.
yah fasah kee taaiyaree ka din tha aur chhtte ghantte ke lagabhg tha: tab us ne yahoodiyon se kaha, dekho, yahee haai, tumhara raja!
parantu ve chillaae ki le ja! le ja! use kroos par chaddha: peelatus ne un se kaha, kya maain tumhare raja ko kroos par chaddhaun? mahayajakon ne uttr diya, ki kaaisar ko chhod hamara aur koi raja naheen.
tab ve yeeshu ko le gaae. aur vah apana kroos uttaae huae us sthan tak bahar gaya, jo khopadee ka sthan kahalata haai aur ibraanee men gulaguta.
vahan unhon ne use aur usake sath aur do manushyon ko kroos par chaddhaya, aek ko idhar aur aek ko udhar, aur beech men yeeshu ko.
aur peelatus ne aek dosha-patra likhkar kroos par laga diya aur us men yah likha hua tha, yeeshu nasaree yahoodiyon ka raja.
yah dosha-patra bahut yahoodiyon ne paddha kyonaki vah sthan jahan yeeshu kroos par chaddhaya gaya tha nagar ke pas tha aur patra ibraanee aur lateenee aur yoonanee men likha hua tha.
tab yahoodiyon ke mahayajakon ne peelatus se kaha, yahoodiyon ka raja mat likh parantu yah ki us ne kaha, maain yahoodiyon ka raja hoon.
peelatus ne uttr diya, ki maain ne jo likh diya, vah likh diya..
yah isaliye hua, ki pavitra shaasr kee bat pooree ho ki unhon ne mere kapade apas men bantt liye aur mere vasr par chitthee dalee: so sipaahiyon ne aeesa hee kiya.
parantu yeeshu ke kroos ke pas us kee mata aur us kee mata kee bahin mariyam, klopas kee patnee aur mariyam magadaleenee khdee thee.
yeeshu ne apanee mata se kaha he naree, dek, yah tera putra haai.
tab us chele se kaha, yah teree mata haai, aur usee samay se vah chela, use apane ghar le gaya..
is ke bad yeeshu ne yah janakar ki ab sab kuchh ho chuka isaliye ki pavitra shaasr kee bat pooree ho kaha, maain pyasa hoon.
vahan aek sirake se bhra hua bartan dhara tha, so unhon ne sirake ke bhaigoae huae ispanj ko joofae par rakhkar usake munh se lagaya.
jab yeeshu ne vah siraka liya, to kaha poora hua aur sir jhukakar praan tyag diae..
aur isaliye ki vah taaiyaree ka din tha, yahoodiyon ne peelatus se binatee kee ki un kee ttange tod dee jaaen aur ve utare jaaen taaki sabt ke din ve krooson par n rahe, kyonki vah sabt ka din bada din tha.
so sipaahiyon ne akar pahile kee ttangen todeen tab doosare kee bhee, jo usake sath krooson par chaddhaae gaae the.
parantu jab yeeshu ke pas akar dekha ki vah mar chuka haai, to us kee ttangen n todeen.
parantu sipaahiyon men se aek ne barachhe se usaka panjar bedha aur us men se turant lohoo aur panee nikala.
jis ne yah dekha, usee ne gavahee dee haai, aur us kee gavahee sachchee haai aur vah janata haai, ki sach kahata haai ki tum bhee vishvas karo.
ye baten isaaliye huin ki pavitra shaasr kee yah bat pooree ho ki us kee koi haddee todee n jaaegee.
fir aek aur sthan par yah likha haai, ki jise unhon ne bedha haai, us par draashtti karenge..
in baton ke bad aramatiyah ke yoosufa ne, jo yeeshu ka chela tha, parantu yahoodiyon ke dr se is bat ko chhpaiaae rakhta tha, peelatus se binatee kee, ki maain yeeshu kee loth ko le jau, aur peelatus ne us kee binatee sunee, aur vah akar us kee loth le gaya.
nikudemus bhee jo paahile yeeshu ke pas rat ko gaya tha pachas ser ke lagabhg mila hua gandharas aur aelava le aya.
tab unhon ne yeeshu kee loth ko liya aur yahoodiyon ke gadne kee reeati ke anusar use sugandha dravy ke sath kafan men lapetta.
us sthan par jahan yeeshu kroos par chaddhaya gaya tha, ek baree thee aur us baree men ek nai kabra thee jis men kabhee koi n rakha gaya tha.
so yahoodiyon kee taaiyaree ke din ke kara, unhon ne yeeshu ko usee men rakha, kyonaki vah kabra nikatt thee..
aadi men vachan tha, aur vachan parameshvar ke sath tha, aur vachan parameshvar tha.
yahee adi men parameshvar ke sath tha.
sab kuchh usee ke dara utpann hua aur jo kuchh utpann hua haai, us men se koi bhee vastu usake bina utpann n hui.
us men jeevan tha aur vah jeevan munashyon kee jyoti thee.
aek manushy parameshvar kee or se a upasthiat hua jis ka nam yoohanna tha.
yah gavahee dene aya, ki jyoti kee gavahee de, taki sab usake dara vishvas laaen.
vah ap to vah jyoti n tha, parantu us jyoti kee gavahee dene ke liye aya tha.
sachchee jyoti jo har aek manushy ko prakaashait karatee haai, jagat men anevalee thee.
vah jagat men tha, aur jagat usake dara utpann hua, aur jagat ne use naheen paahichana.
parantu jitanon ne use grahan kiya, us ne unhen parameshvar ke santan hone ka adhaikar diya, arthata unhen jo usake nam par vishvas rakhte haain.
ve n to lohoo se, n shareer kee ichchha se, n manushy kee ichchha se, parantu parameshvar se utpann huae haain.
aur vachan dehadhaaree hua aur anugrah aur sachchai se paripoorn hokar hamare beech men dera kiya, aur ham ne us kee aeesee mahima dekhee, jaaisee pita ke aekalaute kee mahima.
yoohanna ne usake vishay men gavahee dee, aur pukarakar kaha, ki yah vahee haai, jis ka maain ne varnn kiya, ki jo mere bad a raha haai, vah mujh se baddhkar haai kyonaki vah mujh se pahile tha.
kyonaki us kee paripoornta se ham sab ne praapt kiya arthata anugrah par anugraha.
isaliye ki vyavastha to moosa ke dara dee gai parantu anugrah, aur sachchai yeeshu maseeh ke dara pahunchee.
parameshvar ko kisee ne kabhee naheen dekha, aekalauta putra jo pita kee god men haai, usee ne use pragatt kiya..
yoohanna kee gavahee yah haai, ki jab yahoodiyon ne yarooshalem se yajakon aur leveeyon ko us se yah poochhne ke liye bheja, ki too kaun haai?
to us ne yah man liya, aur inkar naheen kiya parantu man liya ki maain maseeh naheen hoon.
tab unhon ne us se poochha, to fir kaun haai? kya too aeliyyah haai? us ne kaha, maain naheen hoon: to kya too vah bhavishyadvkta haai? us ne uttr diya, ki naheen.
tab unhon ne us se poochha, fir too haai kauna? taaki ham apane bhejanevalon ko uttr den too apane vishay men kya kahata haai?
us ne kaha, maain jaaisa yashaayah bhvishyadvkta ne kaha haai, jangal men ek pukaranevale ka shabd hoon ki tum prabhu ka marga seedha karo.
ye fareesiyon kee or se bheje gaae the.
unhon ne us se yah prashn poochha, ki yadi too n maseeh haai, aur n eliyyah, aur n vah bhvishyadvkta haai, to fir bapaatisma kyon deta haai?
yoohanna ne un ko uttr diya, ki maain to jal se bapatisma deta hoon parantu tumhare beech men aek vyaktai khda haai, jise tum naheen janate.
arthata mere bad anevala haai, jis kee jootee ka bandha maain kholane ke yogy naheen.
ye baten yaradan ke par baaitaniyyah men hui, jahan yoohanna bapaatisma deta tha.
