aur maain ne dekha, aur gavahee dee haai, ki yahee parameshvar ka putra haai..
doosare din fir yoohanna aur usake chelon men se do jan khde huae the.
tab ve donon chele us kee sunakar yeeshu ke peechhe ho liae.
