tab vah daudee aur shamaun pataras aur us doosare chele ke pas jis se yeeshu praem rakhta tha akar kaha, ve prabhu ko kabra men se nikal le gaae haain aur ham naheen janatee, ki use kahan rakh diya haai.
tab pataras aur vah doosara chela nikalakar kabra kee or chale.
aur donon sath sath daud rahe the, parantu doosara chela pataras se age baddhkar kabra par pahile pahuncha.
aur jhukakar kapade pade dekhe: taubhee vah bheetar n gaya.
tab shamaun pataras usake peechhe peechhe pahuncha aur kabra ke bheetar gaya aur kapade pade dekhe.
aur vah angochha jo usake sir se bandha hua tha, kapadon ke sath pada hua naheen parantu alag aek jagah lapetta hua dekha.
tab doosara chela bhee jo kabra par pahile pahuncha tha, bheetar gaya aur dekhkar vishvas kiya.
ve to ab tak paavitra shaasr kee vah bat n samajhte the, ki use mare huon men se jee uttna hoga.
tab ye chele apane ghar lautt gaae.
parantu mariyam rotee hui kabra ke pas hee bahar khdee rahee aur rote rote kabra kee or jhukakar,
do svargadooton ko ujjavat kapade pahine huae aek ko sirahane aur doosare ko paaitane baaitte dekha, jahan yeeshu kee loth padee thee.
unhon ne us se kaha, he naree, too kyon rotee haai? us ne un se kaha, ve mare prabhu ko utta le gaae aur maain naheen janatee ki use kahan rakha haai.
yah kahakar vah peechhe firee aur yeeshu ko khde dekha aur n pahachana ki yah yeeshu haai.
yeeshu ne us se kaha, he naree too kyon rotee haai? jis ko ddoonddhtee haai? us ne malee samajhkar us se kaha, he maharaj, yadi too ne use utta liya haai to mujh se kah ki use kahan rakha haai aur maain use le jaungee.
yeeshu ne us se kaha, mujhe mat choo kyonki maain ab tak pita ke pas upar naheen gaya, parantu mere bhaiyon ke pas jakar un se kah de, ki maain apane pita, aur tumhare parameshvar ke pas upar jata hoon.
maariyam magadaleenee ne jakar chelon ko bataya, ki maain ne prabhu ko dekha aur us ne mujh se baten kaheen..
usee din jo saptah ka pahila din tha, sandhya ke samay jab vahan ke dar jahan chele the, yahoodiyon ke dr ke mare band the, tab yeeshu aya aur beech men khda hokar un se kaha, tumhen shaantai mile.
yeeshu ne fir un se kaha, tumhen shaantai mile jaaise pita ne mujhe bheja haai, vaaise hee maain bhee tumhen bhejata hoon.
yah kahakar us ne un par foonka aur un se kaha, paavitra atma lo.
jin ke pap tum kshama karo ve un ke liye kshama kiae gaae haain jin ke tum rakho, ve rakhe gaae haain..
parantu barahon men se aek vyaaktai arthata thoma jo didumus kahalata haai, jab yeeshu aya to un ke sath n tha.
jab aur chele us se kahane lage ki ham ne prabhu ko dekha haai: tab us ne un se kaha, jab tak maain us ke hathon men keelon ke chhed n dekh loo, aur keelon ke chhedon men apanee ungalee n dal loo, tab tak maain prateeti naheen karoonga..
att din ke bad us ke chele fir ghar ke bheetar the, aur thoma un ke sath tha, aur dar band the, tab yeeshu ne akar aur beech men khda hokar kaha, tumhen shaantai mile.
tab us ne thoma se kaha, apanee ungalee yahan lakar mere panjar men dal aur aavishvasee naheen parantu vishvasee ho.
yah sun thoma ne uttr diya, he mere prabhu, he mere parameshvara!
yeeshu ne us se kaha, too ne to mujhe dekhkar vishvas kiya haai, dhany haain ve jinhon ne bina dekhe vishvas kiya..
yeeshu ne aur bhee bahut chinh chelon ke samhane dikhaa, jo is pustak men likhe naheen gaae.
parantu ye isaaliye likhe gaae haai, ki tum vishvas karo, ki yeeshu hee parameshvar ka putra maseeh haai: aur vishvas karake usake nam se jeevan pao..
in baton ke bad yeeshu ne apane ap ko tibiriyas jheel ke kinare chelon par pragatt kiya aur is reeati se pragatt kiya.
shamaun pataras aur thoma jo didumus kahalata haai, aur galeel ke kana nagar ka natanaael aur jabadee ke putra, aur usake chelon men se do aur jan ikatthe the.
shamaun pataras ne un se kaha, maain machhlee pakadne jata hoon: unhon ne us se kaha, ham bhee tere sath chalate haain: so ve nikalakar nav par chaddhe, parantu us rat kuchh n pakada.
bhor hote hee yeeshu kinare par khda hua taubhee chelon ne n pahachana ki yah yeeshu haai.
tab yeeshu ne un se kaha, he balako, kya tumhare pas kuchh khane ko haai? unhon ne uttr diya ki naheen.
us ne un se kaha, nav kee dahinee or jal dalo, to paoge, tab unhon ne jal dala, aur ab machhliyon kee bahutayat ke karan use kheench n sake.
isaliye us chele ne jis se yeeshu praem rakhta tha pataras se kaha, yah to prabhu haai: shamaun pataras ne yah sunakar ki prabhu haai, kamar men angarakha kas liya, kyonaki vah nanga tha, aur jheel men kood pada.
parantu aur chele dongee par machhliyon se bhra hua jal kheenchate huae aa, kyonki ve kinare se adhaik door nahee, koi do sau hath par the.
jab kinare par utare, to unhon ne koaele kee ag, aur us r machhlee rakhee hui, aur rottee dekhee.
yeeshu ne un se kaha, jo machhliyan tum ne abhee pakadee haai, un men se kuchh lao.
shamaun pataras ne dongee par chaddhkar aek sau tirman badee machhliyon se bhra hua jal kinare par kheencha, aur itanee machhaliyan hone par bhee jan n fatta.
yeeshu ne un se kaha, ki ao, bhojan karo aur chelon men se kisee ko hiyav n hua, ki us se poochhe, ki too kaun haai?
yeeshu aya, aur rottee lekar unhen dee, aur vaaise hee machhlee bhee.
yah teesaree bar haai, ki yeeshu ne mare huon men se jee uttne ke bad chelon ko darshan diae..
bhojan karane ke bad yeeshu ne shamaun pataras se kaha, he shamaun, yoohanna ke putra, kya too in se baddhkar mujh se praem rakhta haai? us ne us se kaha, han prabhu too to janata haai, ki maain tujh se praeeti rakhta hoon: us ne us se kaha, mere memanon ko chara.
us ne teesaree bar us se kaha, he shamaun, yoohanna ke putra, kya too mujh se praeeati rakhta haai? pataras udas hua, ki us ne use teesaree bar aeesa kaha ki kya too mujh se praeeti rakhta haai? aur us se kaha, he prabhu, too to sab kuchh janata haai: too yah janata haai ki maain tujh se praeeti rakhta hoon: yeeshu ne us se kaha, meree bhedon ko chara.
maain tujh se sach sach kahata hoo, jab too javan tha, to apanee kamar bandhakar jahan chahata tha, vahan firata tha parantu jab too booddha hoga, to apane hath lambe karega, aur doosara teree kamar bandhakar jahan too n chahega vahan tujhe le jaaega.
pataras ne firakar us chele ko peechhe ate dekha, jis se yeeshu praem rakhta tha, aur jis ne bhojan ke samay us kee chhatee kee aur jhukakar poochha he prabhu, tera pakadvanevala kaun haai?
use dekhkar pataras ne yeeshu se kaha, he prabhu, is ka kya hal hoga?
yeeshu ne us se kaha, yaadi maain chahoon ki vah mere ane tak tthara rahe, to tujhe kya? too mere peechhe ho le.
isaliye bhaiyon men yah bat faail gai, ki vah chela n marega taubhee yeeshu ne us se yah naheen kaha, ki yah n marega, parantu yah ki yadi maain chahoon ki yah mere ane tak tthara rahe, to tujhe is se kya?
yah vahee chela haai, jo in baton kee gavahee deta haai aur jis ne in baton ko likha haai aur ham janate haai, ki us kee gavahee sachchee haai.
aur bhee bahut se kam haai, jo yeeshu ne kiae yaadi ve aek aek karake likhe jate, to maain samajhta hoo, ki pustaken jo likhee jateen ve jagat men bhee n samateen..
fir us se kaha, maain tum se sach sach kahata hoon ki tum svarga ko khula hua, aur parameshvar ke svargadooton ko upar jate aur manushy ke putra ke upar utarate dekhoge..
fir teesare din galeel ke kana men kisee ka byah tha, aur yeeshu kee mata bhee vahan thee.
aur yeeshu aur usake chele bhee us byah men nevate gaae the.
jab dakhras ghatt gaya, to yeeshu kee mata ne us se kaha, ki un ke pas dakhras naheen raha.
yeeshu ne us se kaha, he maahila mujhe tujh se kya kama? abhee mera samay naheen aya.
us kee mata ne sevakon se kaha, jo kud vah tum se kahe, vahee karana.
vahan yahoodiyon ke shuuddh karane kee reeti ke anusar patthr ke chh: mattke dhare the, ji men do do, teen teen man samata tha.
yeeshu ne un se kaha, ab nikalakar bhoj ke pradhaan ke pas le jao.
ve le gaa, jab bhoj ke pradhaan ne vah panee chakha, jo dakhras ban gaya tha, aur naheen janata tha, ki vah kahan se aya he, parantu jin sevakon ne panee nikala tha, ve janate the to bhoj ke pradhaan ne doolhe ko bulakar, us se kaha.
har aek manushy paahile achchha dakhras deta haai aur jab log peekar chhk jate haai, tab madhyam deta haai parantu too ne achchha dakhras ab tak rakh chhoda haai.
yeeshu ne galeel ke kana men apana yah pahila chinh dikhakar apanee mahima pragatt kee aur usake chelon ne us par vishvas kiya..
is ke bad vah aur us kee mata aur usake bhai aur usake chele kafaranahoom ko gaae aur vahan kuchh din rahe..
yahoodiyon ka fasah ka pabrba nikatt tha aur yeeshu yarooshalem ko gaya.
aur us ne maandair men baail aur bhed aur kabootar ke bechanevalon or sarrafaon ko baaitte huae paya.
aur raassaiyon ka koda banakar, sab bhedon aur baailon ko mandair se nikal diya, aur sarrafaon ke paaise bithra dia, aur peeddhon ko ulatt diya.
aur kabootar bechanevalon se kaha inhen yahan se le jao: mere pita ke bhvan ko vyopar ka ghar mat banao.
tab usake chelon ko smaran aya ki likha haai, 'tere ghar kee dhaun mujhe kha jaaegeen.
is par yahoodiyon ne us se kaha, too jo yah karata haai to hamen kaun sa chinh dikhata he?
yeeshu ne un ko uttr diya ki is mandair ko ddha do, aur maain use teen din men khda kar doonga.
yahoodiyon ne kaha is mandair ke banane men chhyaialees varsha lage he, aur kya too use teen din men khda kar dega?
parantu us ne apanee deh ke mandair ke vishay men kaha tha.
jab vah yarooshalem men fasah ke samay pabrba men tha, to bahuton ne un chinhon ko jo vah dikhata tha dekhkar usake nam par vishvas kiya.
aur use prayojan n tha, ki manushy ke vishay men koi gavahee de, kyonki vah ap janata tha, ki manushy ke man men kya haai?
fareesiyon men se neekudemus nam aek manushy tha, jo yahoodiyon ka saradar tha.
us ne rat ko yeeshu ke pas akar us se kaha, he rabbee, ham janate haai, ki too parameshvar kee are se guroo ho kar aya haai kyonaki koi in chinhon ko jo too dikhata haai, yaadi parameshvar usake sath n ho, to naheen dikha sakata.
yeeshu ne us ko uttr diya ki maain tujh se sach sach kahata hoo, yadi koi naye sire se n janmen to parameshvar ka rajy dekh naheen sakata.
neekudemus ne us se kaha, manushy jab booddha ho gaya, to kyonkar janm le sakata haai?
yeeshu ne uttr diya, ki maain tujh se sach sach kahata hoon jab tak koi manushy jal aur atma se n janme to vah parameshvar ke rajy men pravesh naheen kar sakata.
kyonaki jo shareer se janma haai, vah shareer haai aur jo atma se janma haai, vah atma haai.
achambha n kar, ki maain ne tujh se kaha ki tumhen naye sire se janm lena avashy haai.
hava jidhar chahatee haai udhar chalatee haai, aur too usaka shabd sunata haai, parantu naheen janata, ki vah kahan se atee aur kidhar ko jatee haai? jo koi atma se janma haai vah aeesa hee haai.
neekudemus ne us ko uttr diya ki ye baten kyonkar ho sakatee haain?
yah sunakar yeeshu ne us se kaha too israaeliyon ka guroo ho kar bhee kya in baton ko naheen samajhta.
maain tujh se sach sach kahata hoon ki ham jo janate haai, vah kahate haai, aur jise ham ne dekha haai us kee gavahee dete haai, aur tum hamaree gavahee grahan naheen karate.
jab maain ne tum se prathvee kee baten kahee, aur tum prateeati naheen karate, to yaadi maain tum se svarga kee baten kahoo, to fir kyonkar prateeti karoge?
aur koi svarga par naheen chaddha, keval vaheen jo svarga se utara, arthata manushy ka putra jo svarga men haai.
aur jis reeti se moosa ne jangal men sanp ko unche par chaddhaya, usee reeati se avashy haai ki manushy ka putra bhee unche par chaddhaya jaae.
taaki jo koi vishvas kare us men anant jeevan paae..
kyonaki parameshvar ne jagat se aeesa praem rakha ki us ne apana aekalauta putra de diya, taaki jo koi us par vishvas kare, vah nash n ho, parantu anant jeevan paae.
parameshvar ne apane putra ko jagat men isaliye naheen bheja, ki jagat par dand kee agyaa de parantu isaaliye ki jagat usake dara uddhar paae.
jo us par vishvas karata haai, us par dand kee agyaa naheen hotee, parantu jo us par vishvas naheen karata, vah doshaee tthara chuka isaliye ki us ne parameshvar ke aekalaute putra ke nam par vishvas naheen kiya.
aur dand kee agyaa ka karan yah haai ki jyoti jagat men ai haai, aur manushyon ne andhakar ko jyoti se adhaik piry jana kyonki un ke kam bure the.
kyonaki jo koi burai karata haai, vah jyoti se baair rakhta haai, aur jyoti ke nikatt naheen ata, aeesa n ho ki usake kamon par dosh lagaya jaae.
parantu jo sachchai par chalata haaikh vah jyoti ke nikatt ata haai, taaki usake kam pragatt ho, ki vah parameshvar kee or se kiae gaae haain.
is ke bad yeeshu aur usake chele yahoodiya desh men aae aur vah vahan un ke sathr rahakar bapaatisma dene laga.
aur yoohanna bhee shaalema ke nikatt aeenon men bapaatisma deta tha. kyonaki vahan bahut jal tha aur log akar bapatisma lete the.
kyonaki yoohanna us samay tak jelakhane men naheen dala gaya tha.
vahan yoohanna ke chelon ka kisee yahoodee ke sath shuuddh ike vishay men vada-avivad hua.
aur unhon ne yoohanna ke pas akar us se kaha, he rabbee, jo vyaktai yaradan ke par tere sath tha, aur jis kee too ne gavahee dee haai dek, vah bapatisma deta haai, aur sab usake pas ate haain.
yoohanna ne uttr diya, jab tak manushy ko svarga se n diya jaae tab tak vah kuchh naheen pa sakata.
avashy haai ki vah baddhe aur maain ghatoon..
jo upar se ata haai, vah sarvottm haai, jo prathvee se ata haai vah prathvee ka haai aur prathvee kee hee baten kahata haai: jo svarga se ata haai, vah sab ke upar haai.
jo kuchh us ne dekha, aur suna haai, usee kee gavahee deta haai aur koi us kee gavahee grahan naheen karata.
jis ne us kee gavahee grahan kar lee us ne is bat par chhap de dee ki parameshvar sachcha haai.
kyonaki jise parameshvar ne bheja haai, vah parameshvar kee baten kahata haai: kyonaki vah atma nap napakar naheen deta.
pita putra se praem rakhta haai, aur us ne sab vastuen usake hath men de dee haain.
jo putra par vishvas karata haai, anant jeevan usaka haai parantu jo putra kee naheen manata, vah jeevan ko naheen dekhega, parantu parameshvar ka krodha us par rahata haai..
fir jab prabhu ko maloom hua, ki fareeasiyon ne suna haai, ki yeeshu yoohanna se aadhaik chele banata, aur unhen bapatisma deta haai.
yadhypi yeeshu ap naheen baran usake chele bapaatisma dete the.
tab yahoodiya ko chhodkar fir galeel ko chala gaya.
aur us ko samariya se hokar jana avashy tha.
so vah sookhar nam samariya ke aek nagar tak aya, jo us boomi ke pas haai, jis yakoob ne apane putra yoosufa ko diya tha.
aur yakoob ka kooan bhee vaheen tha so yeeshu marga ka thka hua us kooaen par yonhee baaitt gaya, aur yah bat chhtte ghantte ke lagabhg hui.
itane men aek samaree sree jal bhrane ko ai: yeeshu ne us se kaha, mujhe panee pila.
kyonaki usake chele to nagar men bhojan mol lene ko gaae the.
us samaree sree ne us se kaha, too yahoodee hokar mujh samaree sree se panee kyon mangata haai? kyonaki yahoodee samariyon ke sath kisee prakar ka vyavahar naheen rakhte.
yeeshu ne uttr diya, yaadi too parameshvar ke baradan ko janatee, aur yah bhee janatee ki vah kaun haai jo tujh se kahata haai mujhe panee pila to too us se mangatee, aur vah tujhe jeevan ka jal deta.
sree ne us se kaha, he prabhu, tere pas jal bhrane ko to kuchh haai bhee nahee, aur kooan gahira haai: to fir vah jeevan ka jal tere pas kaha se aya?
kya too hamare pita yakoob se bada haai, jis ne hamen yah kooan diya aur apahee apane santan, aur apane ddharon samet us men se peeya?
yeeshu ne us ko uttr diya, ki jo koi yah jal peeaega vah fir piyasa hoga.
parantu jo koi us jal men se peeaega jo maain use doonga, vah fir anantakal tak piyasa n hoga: baran jo jal maain use doonga, vah us men aek sota ban jaaega jo anant jeevan ke liye umadta rahega.
saee ne us se kaha, he prabhu, vah jal mujhe de taaki maain pyasee n houn aur n jal bhrane ko itanee door aun.
yeeshu ne us se kaha, ja, apane paati ko yahan bula la.
sree ne uttr diya, ki maain bina paati kee hoon: yeeshu ne us se kaha, too tteek kahatee haai ki maain bina paati kee hoon.
kyonaki too panch paati kar chukee haai, aur jis ke pas too ab haai vah bhee tera paati naheen yah too ne sach kaha haai.
sree ne us se kaha, he prabhu, mujhe gyaat hota haai ki too bhvishyadvkta haai.
hamare bapadadon ne usee pahad par bhjan kiya: aur tum kahate ho ki vah jagah jahan bhjan karana chaahiae yarooshalem men haai.
yeeshu ne us se kaha, he naree, meree bat kee prateeti kar ki vah samay ata haai ki tum n to is pahad par pita ka bhjan karoge n yarooshalem men.
tum jise naheen janate, usaka bhjan karate ho aur ham jise janate haain usaka bhjan karate haain kyonaki uddhar yahoodiyon men se haai.
sree ne us se kaha, maain janatee hoon ki maseeh jo kheestus kahalata haai, anevala haai jab vah aaega, to hamen sab baten bata dega.
yeeshu ne us se kaha, maain jo tujh se bol raha hoo, vahee hoon..
itane men usake chele a gaa, aur achambha karane lage, ki vah sree se baten kar raha haai taubhee kisee ne n kaha, ki too kya chahata haai? ya kis liye us se baten karata haai.
tab sree apana ghada chhodkar nagar men chalee gai, aur logon se kahane lagee.
ao, aek manushy ko dekho, jis ne sab kuchh jo maain ne kiya mujhe bata diya: kaheen yah to maseeh naheen haai?
so ve nagar se nikalakar usake pas ane lage.
itane men usake chele yeeshu se yah binatee karane lage, ki he rabbee, kuchh kha le.
parantu us ne un se kaha, mere pas khane ke liye aeesa bhojan haai jise tum naheen janate.
tab chelon ne apas men kaha, kya koi usake liye kuchh khane ko laya haai?
yeeshu ne un se kaha, mera bhojan yah haai, ki apane bhejanevale kee ichchha ke anusar chaloon aur usaka kam poora karoon.
kya tum naheen kahate, ki kattnee hone men ab bhee char maheene pade haain? dekho, maain tum se kahata hoo, apanee ankhe uttakar kheton par draashtti dalo, ki ve kattnee ke liye pak chuke haain.
aur kattnevala majadooree pata, aur anant jeevan ke liye fal battorata haai taaki bonevala aur kattnevala donon milakar anand karen.
kyonaki is par yah kahavat tteek baaitttee haai ki banevala aur haai aur kattnevala aura.
maain ne tumhen vah khet kattne ke liye bheja, jis men tum ne parishram naheen kiya: auron ne parishram kiya aur tum un ke paarishram ke fal men bhagee hue..
aur us nagar ke bahut samariyon ne us sree ke kahane se, jis ne yah gavahee dee thee, ki us ne sab kuchh jo maain ne kiya haai, mujhe bata diya, vishvas kiya.
tab jab ye samaree usake pas aa, to us se binatee karane lage, ki hamare yahan raha: so vah vahan do din tak raha.
aur usake vachan ke karan aur bhee bahuteron ne vishvas kiya.
aur us sree se kaha, ab ham tere kahane kee se vishvas naheen karate kyonaki ham ne ap hee sun liya, aur janate haain ki yahee sachamuch men jagat ka uddharakarta haai..
fir un do dinon ke bad vah vahan se kooch karake galeel ko gaya.
kyonaki yeeshu ne ap hee sakshaee dee, ki bhvishyadvkta apane desh men adar naheen pata.
jab vah galeel men aya, to galeelee anand ke sath us se mile kyonaki jitane kam us ne yarooshalem men pabrba ke samay kiae the, unhon ne un sab ko dekha tha, kyonaki ve bhee pabrba men gaae the..
tab vah fir galeel ke kana men aya, jahan us ne panee ko dakh ras banaya tha: aur raja ka karmacharee tha jis ka putra kafaranahoom men beemar tha.
vah yah sunakar ki yeeshu yahoodiya se galeel men a gaya haai, usake pas gaya aur us se binatee karane laga ki chalakar mere putra ko changa kar de: kyonki vah marane par tha.
yeeshu ne us se kaha, jab tak tum chinh aur adabhut kam n dekhoge tab tak kadaapi vishvas n karoge.
raja ke karmacharee ne us se kaha he prabhu, mere balak kee mratyu hone ke pahile chala.
yeeshu ne us se kaha, ja, tera putra jeeavit haai: us manushy ne yeeshu kee kahee hui bat kee prateeati kee, aur chala gaya.
vah marga men ja raha tha, ki usake das us se a mile aur kahane lage ki tera ladka jeeavit haai.
us n un se poochha ki kis ghadee vah achda hone laga? unhon ne us se kaha, kal sataven ghantte men usaka jvar utar gaya.
yah doosara ashcharyakarma tha, jo yeeshu ne yahoodiya se galeel men akar dikhaya..
yarooshalem men bhed-faattk ke pas aek kund haai jo ibraanee bhasha men betahasada kahalata haai, aur usake panch osare haainn.
in men bahut se beemar, andho, langade aur sookhe angavale panee ke hilane kee asha men pade rahate the.
kyonaki niyuaktai samay par parameshvar ke svargadoot kund men utarakar panee ko hilaya karate the: panee hilate hee jo koi paahile utarata vah changa ho jata tha chahe usakee koi beemaree kyon n ho.
vahan aek manushy tha, jo adtees varsha se beemaree men pada tha.
yeeshu ne use pada hua dekhkar aur janakar ki vah bahut dinon se is dasha men pada haai, us se poochha, kya too changa hona chahata haai?
us beemar ne us ko uttr diya, ki he prabhu, mere pas koi manushy nahee, ki jab panee hilaya jaa, to mujhe kund men utare parantu mere pahunchate pahunchate doosara mujh se paahile utar padta haai.
yeeshu ne us se kaha, ut, apanee khatt uttakar chal fira.
vah manushy turant changa ho gaya, aur apanee khatt uttakar chalane firane laga.
vah sabt ka din tha. isaaliye yahoodee us se, jo changa hua tha, kahane lage, ki aj to sabt ka din haai, tujhe khatt uttanee uchitt naheen.
us ne unhen uttr diya, ki jis ne mujhe changa kiya, usee ne mujh se kaha, apanee khatt uttakar chal fira.
unhon ne us se poochha vah kaun manushy haai jis ne tujh se kaha, khatt uttakar chal fira?
parantu jo changa ho gaya tha, vah naheen janata tha vah kaun haai kyonaki us jagah men bheed hone ke karan yeeshu vahan se hatt gaya tha.
in baton ke bad vah yeeshu ko maandair men mila, tab us n us se kaha, dek, too to changa ho gaya haai fir se pap mat karana, aeesa n ho ki is se koi bharee vipaati tujh par a pade.
us manushy ne jakar yahoodiyon se kah diya, ki jis ne mujhe changa kiya, vah yeeshu haai.
is karan yahoodee yeeshu ko satane lage, kyonaki vah aeese aeese kam sabt ke din karata tha.
is par yeeshu ne un se kaha, ki mera pita ab tak kam karata haai, aur maain bhee kam karata hoon.
is karan yahoodee aur bhee aadhaik usake mar dalane ka prayatn karane lage, ki vah n keval sabt ke din kee vidhai ko todta, parantu parameshvar ko apana pita kah kar, apane ap ko parameshvar ke tuly ttharata tha..
is par yeeshu ne un se kaha, maain tum se sach sach kahata hoo, putra ap se kuchh naheen kar sakata, keval vah jo pita ko karate dekhta haai, kyonki jin jin kamon ko vah karata haai unhen putra bhee usee reeati se karata haai.
kyonaki pita putra se praeeati rakhta haai aur jo jo kam vah ap karata haai, vah sab use dikhata haai aur vah in se bhee bade kam use dikhaaega, taaki tum achambha karo.
kyoki jaaisa pita mare huon ko uttata aur jilata haai, vaaisa hee putra bhee jinhen chahata haai unhen jilata haai.
aur pita kisee ka nyay bhee naheen karata, parantu nyay karane ka sab kam putra ko saunp diya haai.
isaliye ki sab log jaaise pita ka adar karate haain vaaise hee putra ka bhee adar karen: jo putra ka adar naheen karata, vah pita ka jis ne use bheja haai, adar naheen karata.
maain tum se sach sach kahata hoo, jo mera vachan sunakar mere bhejanevale kee prateeti karata haai, anant jeevan usaka haai, aur us par dand kee agyaa naheen hotee parantu vah mratyu se par hokar jeevan men pravesh kar chuka haai.
maain tum se sach sach kahata hoo, vah samay ata haai, aur ab haai, jis men mratak parameshvar ke putra ka shabd sunenge, aur jo sunenge ve jeeaenge.
kyonaki jis reeti se pita apane ap men jeevan rakhta haai, usee reeti se us ne putra ko bhee yah aadhaikar diya haai ki apane ap men jeevan rakhe.
baran use nyay karane ka bhee adhaikar diya haai, isaaliye ki vah manushy ka putra haai.
is se achambha mat karo, kyonaki vah samay ata haai, ki jitane kabraen men haai, usaka shabd sunakar nikalenge.
maain apane ap se kuchh naheen kar sakata jaaisa sunata hoo, vaaisa nyay karata hoo, aur mera nyay sachcha haai kyonaki maain apanee ichchha nahee, parantu apane bhejanevale kee ichchha chahata hoon.
yaadi maain ap hee apanee gavahee doon to meree gavahee sachchee naheen.
tum ne yoohanna se puchhvaya aur us ne sachchai kee gavahee dee haai.
parantu maain apane vishay men manushy kee gavahee naheen chahata taubhee maain ye baten isaliye kahata hoo, ki tumhen uddhar mile.
vah jo jalata aur chamakata hua deepak tha aur tumhen kuchh der tak us kee jyoti me, magan hona achchha laga.
parantu mere pas jo gavahee haai vah yoohanna kee gavahee se badee haai: kyonki jo kam pita ne mujhe poora karane ko saunpa haai arthata yahee kam jo maain karata hoo, ve mere gavah haai, ki pita ne mujhe bheja haai.
aur pita jis ne mujhe bheja haai, usee ne meree gavahee dee haai: tum ne n kabhee usaka shabd suna, aur n usaka roop dekha haai.
aur usake vachan ko man men sthiar naheen rakhte kyonki jise us ne bheja us kee prateeati naheen karate.
tum paavitra shaasr men ddoonddhte ho, kyonaki samajhte ho ki us men anant jeevan tumhen milata haai, aur yah vahee haai, jo meree gavahee deta haai.
fir bhee tum jeevan pane ke liye mere pas ana naheen chahate.
maain manushyon se adar naheen chahata.
parantu maain tumhen janata hoo, ki tum men parameshvar ka praem naheen.
maain apane pita ke nam se aya hoo, aur tum mujhe grahan naheen karate yaadi koi aur apane hee nam se aa, to use grahan kar loge.
tum jo aek doosare se adar chahate ho aur vah adar jo advait parameshvar kee or se haai, naheen chahate, kisee prakar vishvas kar sakate ho?
yah n samajho, ki maain pita ke samhane tum par dosh lagaunga: tum par dosh laganevala to haai, arthata moosa jis par tum ne bhrosa rakha haai.
kyonaki yadi tum moosa kee prateeati karate, to meree bhee prateeti karate, isaaliye ki us ne mere vishay men likha haai.
parantu yadi tum us kee likhee hui baton kee prateeti naheen karate, to meree baton kee kyonkar prateeati karoge..
in baton ke bad yeeshu galeel kee jheel arthata tibiriyas kee jheel ke pas gaya.
aur aek badee bheed usake peechhe ho lee kayonaki jo ashcharya karma vah beemaron par dikhata tha ve un ko dekhte the.
tab yeeshu pahad par chaddhkar apane chelon ke sath vahan baaitta.
aur yahoodiyon ke fasah ke pabrba nikatt tha.
tab yeeshu ne apanee ankhe uttakar aek badee bheed ko apane pas ate dekha, aur filippus se kaha, ki ham in ke bhojan ke liye kahan se rottee mol laaen?
parantu us ne yah bat use parakhne ke liye kahee kyonki vah ap janata tha ki maain kya karoonga.
filippus ne us ko uttr diya, ki do sau deenar kee rottee un ke liye pooree bhee n hongee ki un men se har aek ko thodee thodee mil jaae.
usake chelon men se shamaun pataras ke bhai andairyas ne us se kaha.
yahan aek ladka haai jis ke pas jav kee panch rottee aur do machhaliyan haain parantu itane logon ke liye ve kya haain.
yeeshu ne kaha, ki logon ko baaitta do. us jagah bahut ghaas thee: tab ve log jo ginatee men lagabhg panch hajar ke the, baaitt gaae:
tab yeeshu ne rottyaian lee, aur dhanyavad karake baaittnevalon ko bantt dee: aur vaaise hee machhliyon men se jitanee ve chahate the bantt diya.
so unhon ne battora, aur jav kee panch rottyaien ke ttukade jo khanevalon se bach rahe the un kee barah ttokariyan bhreen.
tab jo ashcharya karma us ne kar dikhaya use ve log dekhkar kahane lage ki vah bhvishyadvkta jo jagat men anevala tha nishchay yahee haai.
yeeshu yah janakar ki ve mujhe raja banane ke liye akar pakadna chahate haai, fir pahad par akela chala gaya.
aur nav par chaddhkar jheel ke par kafaranahoom ko jane lage: us samay andhora ho gaya tha, aur yeeshu abhee tak un ke pas naheen aya tha.
aur andhaee ke karan jheel men lahare uttne lageen.
so jab ve khete khete teen char meel ke lagabhg nikal gaa, to unhon ne yeeshu ko jheel par chalate, aur nav ke nikatt ate dekha, aur dr gaae.
parantu us ne un se kaha, ki maain hoon dro mata.
so ve use nav par chaddha lene ke liye taaiyar huae aur turant vah nav ke sthan par ja pahunchee jahan vah jate the.
doosare din us bheed ne, jo jheel ke par khdee thee, yah dekha, ki yahan aek ko chhodkar aur koi chhottee nav n thee, aur yeeshu apane chelon ke sath us nav par n chaddha, parantu keval usake chele chale gaae the.
taubhee aur chhottee naven tibiriyas se us jagah ke nikatt ai, jahan unhon ne prabhu ke dhanyavad karane ke bad rottee khai thee.
so jab bheed ne dekha, ki yahan n yeeshu haai, aur n usake chele, to ve bhee chhottee chhottee navon par chaddh ke yeeshu ko ddoonddhte huae kafaranahoom ko pahunche.
aur jheel ke par us se milakar kaha, he rabbee, too yahan kab aya?
yeeshu ne unhen uttr diya, ki maain tum se sach sach kahata hoo, tum mujhe isaliye naheen ddoonddhte ho ki tum ne achaambhiat kam dekhe, parantu isaliye ki tum rottyaian khakar trapt huae.
nashaman bhojan ke liye paarishram n karo, parantu us bhojan ke liye jo anant jeevan tak ttharata haai, jise manushy ka putra tumhen dega, kyonaki pita, arthata parameshvar ne usee par chhap kar dee haai.
unhon ne us se kaha, parameshvar ke kayrya karane ke liye ham kya karen?
yeeshu ne unhen uttr diya parameshvar ka kayrya yah haai, ki tum us par, jise us ne bheja haai, vishvas karo.
tab unhon ne us se kaha, fir too kaun ka chinh dikhata haai ki ham use dekhkar teree prateeati kare, too kaun sa kam dikhata haai?
hamare bapadadon ne jangal men manna khaya jaaisa likha haai ki us ne unhen khane ke liye svarga se rottee dee.
yeeshu ne un se kaha, maain tum se sach sach kahata hoon ki moosa ne tumhen vah rottee svarga se n dee, parantu mera pita tumhen sachchee rottee svarga se deta haai.
kyoki parameshvar kee rottee vahee haai, jo svarga se utarakar jagat ko jeevan detee haai.
tab unhon ne us se kaha, he prabhu, yah rottee hamen sarvada diya kara.
yeeshu ne un se kaha, jeevan kee rottee maain hoon: jo mere pas aaega vah kabhee bookha n hoga aur jo mujh par vishvas karega, vah kabhee piyasa n hoga.
parantu maain ne tum se kaha, ki tum ne mujhe dekh bhee liya haai, tobhee vishvas naheen karate.
jo kuchh pita mujhe deta haai vah sab mere pas aaega, use maain kabhee n nikaloonga.
kyonaki maain apanee ichchha nahee, baran apane bhejanevale kee ichchha pooree karane ke liye svarga se utara hoon.
aur mere bhejanevale kee ichchha yah haai ki jo kuchh us ne mujhe diya haai, us men se maain kuchh n khoun parantu use antim din fir jila uttaun.
kyonaki mere pita kee ichchha yah haai, ki jo koi putra ko dekhe, aur us par vishvas kare, vah anant jeevan paae aur maain use anatim din fir jila uttaunga.
so yahoodee us par kudkudane lage, isaliye ki us ne kaha tha ki jo rottee svarga se utaree, vah maain hoon.
yeeshu ne un ko uttr diya, ki apas men mat kudkudao.
koi mere pas naheen a sakata, jab tak pita, jis ne mujhe bheja haai, use kheench n le aur maain us ko antim din fir jila uttaunga.
bhavishyadvktaon ke lekhon men yah likha haai, ki ve sab parameshvar kee or se sikhaae huae honge. jis kisee ne pita se suna aur seekha haai, vah mere pas ata haai.
yah nahee, ki kisee ne pita ko dekha parantu jo parameshvar kee or se haai, keval usee ne pita ko dekha haai.
jeevan kee rottee maain hoon.
tumhare bapadadon ne jangal men manna khaya aur mar gaae.
yah vah rottee haai jo svarga se utaratee haai taaki manushy us men se khaae aur n mare.
jeevan kee rottee jo svarga se utaree maain hoon. yadi koi is rottee men se khaa, to sarvada jeeavit rahega aur jo rottee maain jagat ke jeevan ke liye doonga, vah mera mans haai.
is par yahoodee yah kahakar apas men jhgadne lage, ki yah manushy kyonkar hamen apana mans khane ko de sakata haai?
yeeshu ne un se kaha maain tum se sach sach kahata hoon jab tak manushy ke putra ka mans n khao, aur usaka lohoo n peeo, tum men jeevan naheen.
jo mera mans khata, aur mera lohoo peeta he, anant jeevan usee ka haai, aur maain antim din fir use jila uttaunga.
kyonaki mera mans vastav men khane kee vastu haai aur mera lohoo vastav men peen kee vastu haai.
jo mera mans khata aur mera lohoo peeta haai, vah mujh men sthiar bana rahata haai, aur maain us men.
jaaisa jeevate pita ne mujhe bheja aur maain pita ke karan jeevit hoon vaaisa hee vah bhee jo mujhe khaaega mere karan jeevit rahega.
jo rottee svarga se utaree yahee haai, bapadadon ke saman naheen ki khaya, aur mar gaae: jo koi yah rottee khaaega, vah sarvada jeevit rahega.
ye baten us ne kafaranahoom ke aek aradhanalay men upadesh dete samay kaheen.
isaliye usake chelon men se bahuton ne yah sunakar kaha, ki yah bat nagavar haai ise kaun sun sakata haai?
yeeshu ne apane man men yah jan kar ki mere chele apas men is bat par kudkudate haai, un se poochha, kya is bat se tumhen ttokar lagatee haai?
aur yaadi tum manushy ke putra ko jahan vah pahile tha, vahan upar jate dekhoge, to kya hoga?
atma to jeevanadayak haai, shareer se kuchh labh naheen: jo baten maain ne tum se kaheen haain ve atma haai, aur jeevan bhee haain.
parantu tum men se kitane aeese haain jo vishvas naheen karate: kyonaki yeeshu to paahile hee se janata tha ki jo vishvas naheen karate, ve kaun haain? aur kaun mujhe pakadvaaega.
aur us ne kaha, isee liye maain ne tum se kaha tha ki jab tak kisee ko pita kee or yah baradan n diya jaae tak tak vah mere pas naheen a sakata.
is par usake chelon men se bahutere ultte fir gaae aur usake bad usake sath n chale.
tab yeeshu ne un barahon se kaha, kya tum bhee chale jana chahate ho?
shamaun pataras ne us ko uttr diya, ki he prabhu ham kis ke pas jaaen? anant jeevan kee baten to tere hee pas haain.
aur ham ne vishvas kiya, aur jan gaae haai, ki parameshvar ka pavitra jan too hee haai.
yeeshu ne unhen uttr diya, kya maain ne tum barahon ko naheen chun liya? taubhee tum men se aek vyaaktai shautan haai.
yah us ne shamaun iskariyotee ke putra yahoodah ke vishay men kaha, kyoenaki yahee jo un barahon men se tha, use pakadvane ko tha..
aur yahoodiyon ka mandpon ka pabrba nikatt tha.
isaliye usake bhaiyon ne us se kaha, yahan se kooch karake yahoodiya men chala ja, ki jo kam too karata haai, unhen tere chele bhee dekhen.
kyonankai aeesa koi n hoga jo prasiddh hona chahe, aur chhpaikar kam kare: yadi too yah kam karata haai, to apane tai jagat par pragatt kara.
kyonaki usake bhai bhee us par vishvas naheen karate the.
tab yeeshu ne un se kaha, mera samay abhee naheen aya parantu tumhare liye sab samay haai.
tum pabrba men jao: maain abhee is pabrba men naheen jata kyonki abhee tak mera samay poora naheen hua.
vah un se ye baten kahakar galeel hee men rah gaya..
parantu jab usake bhai pabrba men chale gaa, to vah ap hee pragatt men nahee, parantu manon gupt hokar gaya.
to yahoodee pabrba men use yah kahakar ddoonddhne lage ki vah kahan haai?
aur logon men usake vishay chupake chupake bahut see baten huin: kitane kahate the vah bhla manushy haai: aur kitane kahate the nahee, vah logon ko bhramata haai.
