tab yeeshu ne fir logon se kaha, jagat kee jyoti maain hoon jo mere peechhe ho lega, vah andhakar men n chalega, parantu jeevan kee jyoti paaega.
fareesiyon ne us se kaha too apanee gavahee ap deta haai teree gavahee tteek naheen.
yeeshu ne un ko uttr diya ki yadi maain apanee gavahee ap deta hoo, taubhee meree gavahee tteek haai, kyonaki maain janata hoo, ki maain kahan se aya hoon aur kahan ko jata hoon? parantu tum naheen janate ki maain kahan se ata hoon ya kahan ko jata hoon.
tum shareer ke anusar nyay karate ho maain kisee ka nyay naheen karata.
aur tumharee vyavastha men bhee likha haai ki do janon kee gavahee milakar tteek hotee haai.
aek to maain ap apanee gavahee deta hoo, aur doosara pita meree gavahee deta haai jis ne mujhe bheja.
unhon ne us se kaha, tera pita kahan haai? yeeshu ne uttr diya, ki n tum mujhe janate, to mere pita ko bhee janate.
ye baten us ne mandair men upadesh dete huae bhndar ghar men kahee, aur kisee ne use n pakada kyonki usaka samay ab tak naheen aya tha..
us ne fir un se kaha, maain jata hoon aur tum mujhe ddoonddhoge aur apane ap men maroge: jahan maain jata hoo, vahan tum naheen a sakate.
is par yahoodiyon ne kaha, kya vah apane ap ko mar dalega, jo kahata haai ki jahan maain jata hoon vahan tum naheen a sakate?
us ne un se kaha, tum neeche ke ho, maain upar ka hoon tum sansar ke ho, maain sansar ka naheen.
isaliye maain ne tum se kaha, ki tum apane papon men maroge kyonaki yadi tum vishvas n karoge ki maain vaheen hoo, to apane papon men maroge.
unhon ne us se kaha, too kaun haai? yeeshu ne un se kaha, vahee hoon jo praarambh se tum se kahata aya hoon.
tumhare vishay men mujhe bahut kuchh kahana aur nirny karana haai parantu mera bhejanevala sachcha haai aur jo maain ne us se suna he, vahee jagat se kahaha hoon.
ve n samajhe ki ham se pita ke vishay men kahata haai.
tab yeeshu ne kaha, ki jab tum manushy ke putra ko unche par chaddhaoge, to janoge ki maain vahee hoo, aur apane ap se kuchh naheen karata, parantu jaaise pita ne mujhe sikhaya, vaaise hee ye baten kahata hoon.
aur mera bhejanevala mere sath haai us ne mujhe akela naheen chhoda kyonki maain sarvada vahee kam karata hoo, jis se vah prasann hota haai.
vah ye baten kah hee raha tha, ki bahuteron ne us par vishvas kiya..
tab yeeshu ne un yahoodiyon se jinhon ne un kee prateeati kee thee, kaha, yaadi tum mere vachan men bane rahoge, to sachamuch mere chele ttharoge.
aur saty ko janoge, aur saty tumhen svatantra karega.
unhon ne us ko uttr diya ki ham to ibraaheem ke vansh se haain aur kabhee kisee ke das naheen hue fir too kyonkar kahata haai, ki tum svatantra ho jaoge?
yeeshu ne un ko uttr diya maain tum se sach sach kahata hoon ki jo koi pap karata haai, vah pap ka das haai.
aur das sada ghar men naheen rahata putra sada rahata haai.
so yaadi putra tumhen svatantra karega, to sachamuch tum svatantra ho jaoge.
maain janata hoon ki tum ibraaheem ke vansh se ho taubhee mera vachan tumhare day men jagah naheen pata, isaaliye tum mujhe mar dalana chahate ho.
unhon ne un ko uttr diya, ki hamara pita to ibraaheem haai: yeeshu ne un se kaha yaadi tum ibraaheem ke santan hote, to ibraaheem ke saman kam karate.
parantu ab tum mujh aeese manushy ko mar dalana chahate ho, jis ne tumhen vah saty vachan bataya jo parameshvar se suna, yah to ibraaheem ne naheen kiya tha.
tum apane pita ke saman kam karate ho: unhon ne us se kaha, ham vyabhaichar se naheen janme hamara aek pita haai arthata parameshvara.
yeeshu ne un se kaha yaadi parameshvar tumhara pita hota, to tum mujh se praem rakhte kyonaki maain parameshvar men se nikal kar aya hoon maain ap se naheen aya, parantu usee ne mujhe bheja.
tum meree bat kyon naheen samajhte? isaliye ki mera vachan sun naheen sakate.
tum apane pita shautan se ho, aur apane pita kee lalasaon ko poora karana chahate ho. vah to arambh se hatyara haai, aur saty par sthiar n raha, kyonaki saty us men haai hee naheen: jab vah joott bolata, to apane svabhav hee se bolata haai kyonaki vah jootta haai, baran joott ka pita haai.
parantu maain jo sach bolata hoo, iseealiye tum meree prateeati naheen karate.
tum men se kaun mujhe papee ttharata haai? aur yaadi maain sach bolata hoo, to tum meree prateeti kyon naheen karate?
yah sun yahoodiyon ne us se kaha kya ham tteek naheen kahate, ki too samaree haai, aur tujh men dushttatma haai?
yeeshu ne uttr diya, ki mujh men dushttatma naheen parantu maain apane pita ka adar karata hoo, aur tum mera niradar karate ho.
parantu maain apanee praatishtta naheen chahata, ha, aek to haai jo chahata haai, aur nyay karata haai.
maain tum se sach sach kahata hoo, ki yadi koi vyaktai mere vachan par chalega, to vah anant kal tak mratyu ko n dekhega.
yahoodiyon ne us se kaha, ki ab ham ne jan liya ki tujh men dushttatma haai: ibraaheem mar gaya, aur bhavishyadvkta bhee mar gaae haain aur too kahata haai, ki yadi koi mere vachan par chalega to vah anant kal tak mratyu ka svad n chakhega.
hamara pita ibraaheem to mar gaya, kya too us se bada haai? aur bhavishyadvkta bhee mar gaa, too apane ap ko kya ttharata haai.
yeeshu ne uttr diya yaadi maain ap apanee maahima karoo, to meree maahima kuchh nahee, parantu meree mahima karanevala mera pita haai, jise tum kahate ho, ki vah hamara parameshvar haai.
aur tum ne to use naheen jana: parantu maain use janata hoon aur yaadi kahoon ki maain use naheen janata, to maain tumharee nain jootta ttharoonga: parantu maain use janata, aur usake vachan par chalata hoon.
tumhara pita ibraaheem mera din dekhne kee asha se bahut magan tha aur us ne dekha, aur anand kiya.
yahoodiyon ne us se kaha, ab tak too pachas varsha ka naheen fir bhee too ne ibraaheem ko dekha haai?
yeeshu ne un se kaha maain tum se sach sach kahata hoon ki pahile isake ki ibraaheem utpann hua maain hoon.
tab unhon ne use marane ke liye patthr uttaa, parantu yeeshu chhpaikar maandair se nikal gaya..
fir jate huae us ne aek manushy ko dekha, jo janm ka andha tha.
aur usake chelon ne us se poochha, he rabbee, kis ne pap kiya tha ki yah andha janma, is manushy ne, ya usake mata pita ne?
yeeshu ne uttr diya, ki n to is ne pap kiya tha, n is ke mata pita ne: parantu yah isaaliye hua, ki parameshvar ke kam us men pragatt hon.
jis ne mujhe bheja haai hamen usake kam din hee din men karana avashy haai: vah rat anevalee haai jis men koi kam naheen kar sakata.
jab tak maain jangal men hoo, tab tak jagat kee jyoti hoon.
yah kahakar us ne boomi par tooka aur us took se mittee sanee, aur vah mittee us andho kee ankhon par lagakara.
us se kaha ja shaeeloh ke kund men dhae le, jis ka arth bheja hua haai so us ne jakar dhaeya, aur dekhta hua lautt aya.
tab padosee aur jinhon ne pihale use bheekh mangate dekha tha, kahane lage kya yah vahee nahee, jo baaitta bheekh manga karata tha?
tab ve us se poochhne lage, teree ankhen kyonkar khul gai?
us ne uttr diya, ki yeeshu nam ek vyaktai ne mittee sanee, aur meree ankhon par lagakar mujh se kaha, ki shaeeloh men jakar dhae le so maain gaya, aur dhaekar dekhne laga.
unhon ne us se poochha vah kahan haai? us ne kaha maain naheen janata..
log use jo pahile andha tha fareesiyon ke pas le gaae.
jis din yeeshu ne mittee sanakar us kee ankhe kholee thee vah sabt ka din tha.
fir fareeasiyon ne bhee us se poochha teree ankhen kis reeti se khul gai? us n eun se kaha us ne meree ankho par mittee lagai, fir maain ne dhae liya, aur ab dekhta hoon.
is par kai fareesee kahane lage yah manushy parameshvar kee or se nahee, kyonki vah sabt ka din naheen manata. auron ne kaha, papee manushy kyonkar aeese chinh dikha sakata haai? so un men foott padee.
unhon ne us andho se fir kaha, us ne jo teree ankhe kholee, too usake vishay men kya kahata haai? us ne kaha, yah bhvishyadvkta haai.
parantu yahoodiyon ko vishvas n hua ki yah andha tha aur ab dekhta haai jab tak unhon ne usake mata-pita ko jis kee ankhe khul gai thee, bulakara.
usake mata-apita ne uttr diya ham to janate haain ki yah hamara putra haai, aur andha janma tha.
parantu ham yah naheen janate haain ki ab kyonkar dekhta haai aur n yah janate haai, ki kis ne us kee ankhe kholeen vah sayana haai usee se poochh lo vah apane vishay men ap kah dega.
ye baten usake mata-pita ne isaliye kaheen kyonki ve yahoodiyon se drate the kyoki yahoodee aeka kar chuke the, ki yadi koi kahe ki vah maseeh haai, to aradhanalay se nikala jaae.
isee karan usake mata-apita ne kaha, ki vah sayana haai usee se poochh lo.
tab unhon ne us manushy ko jo andha tha doosaree bar bulakar us se kaha, parameshvar kee stuti kara ham to janate haain ki vah manushy papee haai.
us ne uttr diya: maain naheen janata ki vah papee haai ya naheen: maain ek bat janata hoon ki maain andha tha aur ab dekhta hoon.
unhon ne us se fir kaha, ki us ne tere sath kya kiya? aur kis terah teree ankhen kholee?
us ne un se kaha maain to tum se kah chuka, aur tum ne ne suna ab doosaree bar kyon sunana chahate ho? kya tum bhee usake chele hona chahate ho?
tab ve use bura-bhla kahakar bole, too hee usaka chela haai ham to moosa ke chele haain.
ham janate haain ki parameshvar ne moosa se baten keen parantu is manushy ko naheen janate kee kahan ka haai.
us ne un ko uttr diya yah to achambhe kee bat haai ki tum naheen janate kee kahan ka haai taubhee us ne meree ankhen khol deen.
ham janate haain ki parameshvar papiyon kee naheen sunata parantu yaadi koi parameshvar ka bhkt ho, aur us kee ichchha par chalata haai, to vah us kee sunata haai.
jagat ke arambh se yah kabhee sunane men naheen aya, ki kisee ne bhee janm ke andho kee ankhe kholee hon.
yaadi yah vyaaktai parameshvar kee or se n hota, to kuchh bhee naheen kar sakata.
unhon ne us ko uttr diya, ki too to bilakul papon men janma haai, too hamen kya sikhata haai? aur unhon ne use bahar nikal diya..
yeeshu ne suna, ki unhon ne use bahar nikal diya haai aur jab use bhentt hui to kaha, ki kya too parameshvar ke putra par vishvas karata haai?
us ne uttr diya, ki he prabhu vah kaun haai ki maain us par vishvas karoon?
yeeshu ne us se kaha, too ne use dekha bhee haai aur jo tere sath baten kar raha haai vahee haai.
us ne kaha, he prabhu, maain vishvas karata hoon: aur use dandvat kiya.
jo fareesee usake sath the, unhon ne ye baten sun kar us se kaha, kya ham bhee andho haain?
yeeshu ne un se kaha, yaadi tum andho hote to papee n ttharate parantu ab kahate ho, ki ham dekhte haai, isaaliye tumhara pap bana rahata haai..
kaaisaariya men kuranealiyus nam aeek manushy tha, jo italiyanee nam palattn ka soobedar tha.
vah bhkt tha, aur apane sare gharane samet parameshvar se drata tha, aur yahoodee lagon ko bahut dan deta, aur barabar parameshvar se praarthna karata tha.
us ne din ke teesare pahar ke nikatt darshan men spashtt roop se dekha, ki parameshvar ka ek svargadoot mere pas bheetar akar kahata haai ki he kuraneliyusa.
us ne use dhyan se dekha aur drakar kaha he prabhu kya haai? us ne us se kaha, teree praarthnaen aur tere dan smaran ke liye parameshvar ke samhane pahunche haain.
aur ab yafaa men manushy bhejakar shamaun ko, jo pataras kahalata haai, bulava le.
vah shamaun chamade ke dhandha karanevale ke yahan pahun haai, jis ka ghar samudra ke kinare haain.
jab vah svargadoot jis ne us se baten kee theen chala gaya, to us ne do sevak, aur jo usake pas upasthiat raha karate the un men se aek bhkt sipahee ko bulaya.
aur unhen sab baten batakar yafaa ko bheja..
aur use bookh lagee, aur kuchh khana chahata tha parantu jab ve taaiyar kar rahe the, to vah besudha ho gaya.
aur us ne dekha, ki akash khul gaya aur aek patra badee chadar ke saman charon konon se lattkata hua, pathvee kee or utar raha haai.
jis men prathvee ke sab prakar ke chaupaae aur renganevale jantu aur akash ke pakshaee the.
aur use aek aeesa shabd sunai diya, ki he pataras ut, mar ke kha.
parantu pataras ne kaha, naheen prabhu, kadapi naheen kyonki maain ne kabhee koi apavitra ya ashuuddh vastu naheen khai haai.
fir doosaree bar use shabd sunai diya, ki jo kuchh parameshvar ne shuuddh ttharaya haai, use too ashuuddh mat kaha.
teen bar aeesa hee hua tab turant vah patra akash par utta liya gaya..
jab pataras apane man men dubadha kar raha tha, ki yah darshan jo maain ne dekha kya haai, to dekho, ve manushy jinhen kuraneliyus ne bheja tha, shamaun ke ghar ka pata lagakar devaddhee par a khde huae.
aur pukarakar poochhne lage, kya shamaun jo pataras kahalata haai, yaheen pahun haai?
pataras jo us darshan par soch hee raha tha, ki atma ne us se kaha, dek, teen manushy teree khoj men haain.
so uttkar neeche ja, aur bekhttke un ke sath ho le kyonaki maain hee ne unhen bheja haai.
tab pataras ne utarakar un manushyon se kaha dekho, jisakee khoj tum kar rahe ho, vah maain hee hoon tumhare ane ka kya karan haai?
unhon ne kaha kuraneliyus soobedar jo dharmee aur parameshvar se dranevala aur saree yahoodee jaati men sunamee manushy haai, us ne ek paavitra svargadoot se yah chitavanee pai haai, ki tujhe apane ghar bulakar tujh se vachan sune.
tab us ne unhen bheetar bulakar un kee pahunai kee.. aur doosare din, vah unake sath gaya aur yafaa ke bhaiyon men se kai usake sath ho liae.
doosare din ve kaaisariya men pahunche, aur kuraneliyus apane kuttumbaiyon aur piry mitraen ko ikatthe karake un kee batt joh raha tha.
jab pataras bheetar a raha tha, to kuranealiyus ne us se bhentt kee, aur panvon padke pranam kiya.
parantu pataras ne use uttakar kaha, khda ho, maain bhee to manushy hoon.
aur usake sath batacheet karata hua bheetar gaya, aur bahut se logon ko ikatthe dekhkara.
isee liye maain jab bulaya gaya to bina kuchh kahe chala aya: ab maain poochhta hoon ki mujhe kis kam ke liye bulaya gaya haai?
kuranealiyus ne kaha ki is ghadee poore char din hua, ki maain apane ghar men teesare pahar ko praarthna kar raha tha ki dekho, aek puroosh chamakeela vasr paahine hua, mere samhane a khda hua.
aur kahane laga, he kuraneliyus, teree praarthna sun lee gai, aur tere dan parameshvar ke samhane smaran kiae gaae haain.
is liye kisee ko yafaa bhejakar shamaun ko jo pataras kahalata haai, bula vah samudra ke kinare shamaun chamade ke dhandha karanevale ke ghar men pahun haai.
tab maain ne turant tere pas log bheje, aur too ne bhla kiya, jo a gaya: ab ham sab yahan parameshvar ke samhane haai, taki jo kuchh parameshvar ne tujh se kaha haai use sunen.
tab pataras ne munh kholakar kaha
ab mujhe nishchay hua, ki parameshvar kisee ka paksha naheen karata, baran har jati men jo us se drata aur dharma ke kam karata haai, vah use bhata haai.
jo vachan us ne israaeliyon ke pas bheja, jab ki us ne yeeshu maseeh ke dara jo sab ka prabhu haai shaantai ka susamachar sunaya.
vah bat tum janate ho jo yoohanna ke bapatisma ke prachar ke bad galeel se arambh karake sare yahoodiya men faail gai.
ki parameshvar ne kis reeti se yeeshu nasaree ko paavitra atma aur samarth se aabhaishok kiya: vah bhlai karata, aur sab ko jo shautan ke sataae huae the, achchha karata fira kyonaki parameshvar usake sath tha.
aur ham un sab kamon ke gavah haain jo us ne yahoodiya ke desh aur yarooshalem men bhee kia, aur unhon ne use katt par lattkakar mar dala.
sab logon ko naheen baran un gavahon ko jinhen parameshvar ne pahile se chun liya tha, arthata hamako jinhon ne usake mare huon men se jee uttne ke bad usake sath khaya peeya.
aur us ne hamen agyaa dee, ki logon men prachar karo aur gavahee do, ki yah vahee haai jise parameshvar ne jeevaton aur mare huon ka nyayee ttharaya haai.
us kee sab bhavishyadvkta gavahee dete he, ki jo koi us par vishvas karega, us ko usake nam ke dara papon kee kshama milegee..
pataras ye baten kah hee raha tha, ki pavitra atma vachan ke sab sunanevalon par utar aya.
aur jitane khtana kiae huae vishvasee pataras ke sath aae the, ve sab chaakit huae ki anyajaatiyon par bhee paavitra atma ka dan undela gaya haai.
kyonaki unhon ne unhen bhanati bhanati kee bhasha bolate aur parameshvar kee badai karate suna.
is par pataras ne kaha kya koi jal kee rok kar sakata haai, ki ye bapaatisma n paae, jinhon ne hamaree nai paavitra atma paya haai?
aur us ne agyaa dee ki unhen yeeshu maseeh ne nam men bapaatisma diya jaae: tab unhon ne us se binatee kee ki kuchh din hamare sath raha..
aur praeriton aur bhaiyon ne jo yahoodiya men the suna, ki anyajaatiyon ne bhee parameshvar ka vachan man liya haai.
aur jab pataras yarooshalem men aya, to khtana kiae huae log us se vada-avivad karane lage.
ki too ne khtanaraahit logon ke yahan jakar un se sath khaya.
tab pataras ne unhen arambh se kramanusar kah sunaya
ki maain yafaa nagar men praarthna kar raha tha, aur besudha hokar aek darshan dekha, ki aek patra, badee chadar ke saman charon konon se lattkaya hua, akash se utarakar mere pas aya.
jab maain ne us par dhyan kiya, to prathvee ke chaupaae aur banapashu aur renganevale jantu aur akash ke pakshaee dekhe.
aur yah shabd bhee suna ki he pataras utt mar aur kha.
maain ne kaha, naheen prabhu, nahee, kyonki koi apavitra ya ashuuddh vastu mere munh men kabhee naheen gai.
is ke uttr men akash se doosaree bar shabd hua, ki jo kuchh parameshvar ne shuuddh ttharaya haai, use ashuuddh mat kaha.
aur dekho, turant teen manushy jo kaaisariya se mere pas bheje gaae the, us ghar par jis men ham the, a khde hue.
tab atma ne mujh se un ke sath bekhttke ho lene ko kaha, aur ye chh: bhai bhee mere sath ho liae aur ham us manushy ke ghar men gaae.
aur us ne bataya, ki maain ne aek svargadoot ko apane ghar men khda dekha, jis ne mujh se kaha, ki yafaa men manushy bhejakar shamaun ko jo pataras kahalata haai, bulava le.
vah tum se aeesee baten kahega, jin ke dara too aur tera sara gharana udar paaega.
jab maain baten karane laga, to pavitra atma un par usee reeti se utara, jis reeti se arambh men ham par utara tha.
tab mujhe prabhu ka vah vachan smaran aya jo us ne kaha ki yoohanna ne to panee se bapatisma diya, parantu tum pavitra atma se bapatisma paoge.
so jab ki parameshvar ne unhen bhee vahee dan diya, jo hamen prabhu yeeshu maseeh par vishvas karane se mila tha to maain kaun tha jo parameshvar ko rok sakata?
yah sunakar, ve chup rahe, aur parameshvar kee badai karake kahane lage, tak to parameshvar ne anyajatiyon ko bhee jeevan ke liye man firav ka dan diya haai..
so jo log us klesh ke mare jo staifanus ke karan pada tha, tittr bittr ho gaae the, ve firate firate faeeneeke aur kupraus aur antakiya men pahunche parantu yahoodiyon ko chhod kisee aur ko vachan n sunate the.
parantu un men se kitane kuprausee aur kurenee the, jo antaakiya men akar yunaaniyon ko bhee prabhu yeeshu ka susamachar kee baten sunane lage.
aur prabhu ka hath un par tha, aur bahut log vishvas karake prabhu kee or fire.
tab un kee charcha yarooshalem kee kaleesiya ke sunane men ai, aur unhon ne baranabas ko antaakiya bheja.
kyonaki vah aek bhla manushy tha aur paavitra atma se paaripoorn tha: aur aur bahut se log prabhu men a mile.
tab vah shaaul ko ddoonddhne ke liye tarasus ko chala gaya.
aur jab un se mila to use antakiya men laya, aur aeesa hua ki ve aek varsha tak kaleesiya ke sath milate aur bahut logon ko upadesh dete rahe, aur chele sab se pahile antaakiya hee men maseehee kahalaae..
unheen dinon men kai bhvishyadvkta yarooshalem se antakiya men ae.
un men se agabus nam ek ne khde hokar atma kee praerana se yah bataya, ki sare jagat men bada akal padega, aur vah akal klaudiyus ke samay men pada.
tab chelon ne ttharaya, ki har aek apanee apanee poonjee ke anusar yahoodiya men rahanevale bhaiyon kee seva ke liye kuchh bheje.
aur unhon ne aeesa hee kiya aur baranabas aur shaaul ke hath praacheenon ke pas kuchh bhej diya..
us samay herodes raja ne kaleesiya ke kai ek vyaaktaiyon ko dukh dene ke liye un par hath dale.
us ne yoohanna ke bhai yakoob ko talavar se marava dala.
aur jab us ne dekha, ki yahoodee log is se anandait hote haai, to us ne pataras ko bhee pakad liya: ve din akhmeeree rottee ke din the.
aur us ne use pakad ke bandeegrah men dala, aur rakhvalee ke liye, char char sipaahiyon ke char paharon men rakha: is manasa se ki fasah ke bad use logon ke samhane laae.
so bandeegrah men pataras kee rakhvalee ho rahee thee parantu kaleesiya usake liye lau lagakar parameshvar se praarthna kar rahee thee.
aur jab herodes use un ke samhane lane ko tha, to usee rat pataras do janjeeron se bandha hua, do sipaahiyon ke beech men so raha tha: aur paharooae dar par bandeegrah kee rakhvalee kar rahe the.
to dekho, prabhu ka aek svargadoot a khda hua: aur us kottree men jyoti chamakee: aur us ne pataras kee pasalee par hath mar ke use jagaya, aur kaha ut, fauratee kar, aur usake hath se janjeeren khulakar gir padeen.
tab svargadoot ne us se kaha kamar bandha, aur apane joote paahin le: us ne vaaisa hee kiya, fir us ne us se kaha apana vasr pahinakar mere peechhe ho le.
vah nikalakar usake peechhe ho liya parantu yah n janata tha, ki jo kuchh svargadoot kar raha haai, vah sachamuch haai, baran yah samajha, ki maain darshan dekh raha hoon.
tab pataras ne sachet hokar kaha ab maain ne sach jan liya ki prabhu ne apana svargadoot bhejakar mujhe herodes ke hath se chhuda liya, aur yahoodiyon kee saree asha tod dee.
aur yah sochakar, vah us yoohanna kee mata maariyam ke ghar aya, jo marakus kahalata haai vahan bahut log ikatthe hokar praarthna kar rahe the.
jab us ne faattk kee khaidkee khttkhttai to roode nam aek dasee sunane ko ai.
aur pataras ka shabd pahachanakar, us ne anand ke mare faattk n khola parantu daudkar bheetar gai, aur bataya ki pataras dar par khda haai.
unhon ne us se kaha too pagal haai, parantu vah draddhta se bolee, ki aeesa hee haai: tab unhon ne kaha, usaka svargadoot hoga.
parantu pataras khttkhttata hee raha: so unhon ne khaidkee kholee, aur use dekhkar chaakit ho gaae.
tab us ne unhen hath se saain kiya, ki chup rahen aur un ko bataya, ki prabhu kis reeti se mujhe bandeegrah se nikal laya haai: fir kaha, ki yakoob aur bhaiyon ko yah bat kah dena tab nikalakar doosaree jagah chala gaya.
bhor ko sipaahiyon men badee halachal hone lagee, ki pataras kya hua.
jab herodes ne us kee khoj kee, aur n paya to paharooon kee janch karake agyaa dee ki ve mar dale jaaen aur vah yahoodiya ko chhodkar kaaisaariya men ja raha.
aur vah soor aur saaida ke logon se bahut aprasann tha so ve aek chitt hokar usake pas aae aur balastus ko, jo raja ka aek karmacharee tha, manakar mel karata chaha kyonaki raja ke desh se un ke desh ka palan poshan hota tha.
aur ttharaae huae din herodes rajavasr paahinakar sinhasan par baaitta aur un ko vyakhyan dene laga.
aur log pukar utte, ki yah to manushy ka naheen parameshvar ka shabd haai.
usee kshan prabhu ke ek svargadoot ne turant use mara, kyonaki us ne paramashevar kee mahima nahee kee aur vah keede padke mar gaya..
jab baranabas aur shaaul apanee seva pooree kar chuke, to yoohanna ko jo marakus kahalata haai sath lekar yarooshalem se lautte..
antaakiya kee kaleesiya men kitane bhvishyadvkta aur upadeshak the arthata baranabas aur shamaun jo neegar kahalata haai aur lookiyus kurenee, aur desh kee chauthai ke raja herodes ka doodhabhai manahem aur shaaula.
jab ve upavas saahit prabhu kee upasana kar rahe tha, to paavitra atma ne kaha mere nimitt baranabas aur shaaul ko us kam ke liye alag karo jis ke liye maain ne unhen bulaya haai.
tab unhon ne upavas aur praarthna karake aur un par hath rakhkar unhen vida kiya..
so ve paavitra atma ke bheje huae silookiya ko gaae aur vahan se jahaj par chaddhkar kupraus ko chale.
aur salamees men pahunchakar, parameshvar ka vachan yahoodiyon kee aradhanalayon men sunaya aur yoohanna un ka sevak tha.
aur us sare ttapoo men hote hua, pafaus tak pahunche: vahan unhen bara-yeeshu nam aek yahoodee ttonha aur jootta bhvishyadvkta mila.
vah siraagiyus paulus soobe ke sath tha, jo buddhmaian puroosh tha: us ne baranabas aur shaaul ko apane pas bulakar parameshvar ka vachan sunana chaha.
parantu ileemas ttonhe ne, kyonki yahee usake nam ka arth haai un ka samhana karake, soobe ko vishvas karane se rokata chaha.
tab shaaul ne jis ka nam paulus bhee haai, pavitra atma se paaripoorn ho us kee or ttkattkee lagakar kaha.
he sare kapatt aur sab chaturai se bhre huae shautan kee santan, sakal dharma ke baairee, kya too prabhu ke seedho magorn ko tteddha karana n chhodega?
ab dek, prabhu ka hath tujh par laga haai aur too kuchh samay tak andha rahega aur soorya ko n dekhega: tab turant dhaundhalai aur andhora us par chha gaya, aur vah idhar udhar ttttolane laga, taki koi usaka hath pakadke le chale.
tab soobe ne jo kuchh hua tha, dekhkar aur prabhu ke upadesh se chakit hokar vishvas kiya..
paulus aur usake sathee pafaus se jahaj kholakar panfooliya ke piraga men aae: aur yoohanna unhen chhodkar yarooshalem ko lautt gaya.
aur piraga se age baddhkar ke pisidiya ke antaakiya men pahunche aur sabt ke din aradhanalay men jakar baaitt gaae.
tab paulus ne khde hokar aur hath se saain karake kaha he israaeliyo, aur parameshvar se dranevalo, suno.
in israaelee logon ke parameshvar ne hamare bapadadon ko chun liya, aur jab ye misar desh men paradeshaee hokar rahate the, to un kee unnati kee aur balavant bhuja se nikal laya.
aur vah koi chalees varsha tak jangal men un kee sahata raha.
aur kanan desh men sat jaatiyon ka nash karake un ka desh koi saddhe char sau varsha men in kee meeras men kar diya.
is ke bad us ne samuel bhvishyadvkta tak un men nyayee ttharaae.
usake bad unhon ne ek raja manga: tab parameshvar ne chalees vashau ke liye binyameen ke gotra men se ek manushy arthata keesh ke putra shaaul ko un par raja ttharaya.
fir use alag karake daud ko un ka raja banaya jis ke vishay men us ne gavahee dee, ki mujhe aek manushy yishau ka putra daud, mere man ke anusar mil gaya haai. vahee mere saree ichchha pooree karega.
isee ke vansh men se parameshvar ne apanee pratigyaa ke anusar israael ke pas aek uddharakarta, arthata yeeshu ko bheja.
jis ke ane se paahile yoohanna ne sab israaeliyon ko man firav ke bapatisma ka prachar kiya.
aur jab yoohanna apana daur poora karane par tha, to us ne kaha, tum mujhe kya samajhte ho? maain vah naheen! baran dekho, mere bad aek anevala haai, jis ke panvon kee jootee maain kholane ke yogy naheen.
he bhaiyo, tum jo ibraaheem kee santan ho aur tum jo parameshvar se drate ho, tumhare pas is uddhar ka vachan bheja gaya haai.
kyonaki yarooshalem ke rahanevalon aur unake saradaron ne, n use pahachana, aur n bhvishyadvktaon kee baten samajhee jo har sabt ke din paddhee jatee haai, isaaliye use doshaee ttharakar un ko poora kiya.
unhon ne mar dalane ke yogy koi dosh us men ne paya, taubhee peelatus se binatee kee, ki vah mar dala jae.
aur jab unhon ne usake vishay men likhee hui sab baten pooree kee, to use kroos par se utar kar kabra men rakha.
aur vah unhen jo usake sath galeel se yarooshalem aae the, bahut dinon tak dikhai deta raha logon ke samhane ab ve bhee usake gavah haain.
aur ham tumhen us praatigyaa ke vishay me, jo bapadadon se kee gai thee, yah susamachar sunate haain.
ki parameshvar ne yeeshu ko jilakar, vahee pratigyaa hamaree santan ke liye pooree kee, jaaisa doosare bhjan men bhee likha haai, ki too mera putra haai aj maain hee ne tujhe janmaya haai.
aur usake is reeati se mare huon men se jilane ke vishay men bhee, ki vah kabhee n sade, us ne yon kaha haai ki maain daud par kee pavitra aur achal krapa tum par karoonga.
isaliye us ne aek aur bhjan men bhee kaha haai ki too apane pavitra jan ko sadne n dega.
kyonaki daud to parameshvar kee ichchha ke anusar apane samay men seva karake so gaya aur apane bapadadon men ja mila aur sad bhee gaya.
parantu jis ko parameshvar ne jilaya, vah sadne naheen paya.
isaliye, he bhaiyo tum jan lo ki isee ke dara papon kee kshama ka samachar tumhen diya jata haai.
aur jin baton se tum moosa kee vyavastha ke dara nirdosh naheen tthar sakate the, unheen sab se har aek vishvas karanevala usake dara nirdosh ttharata haai.
isaliye chaukas raho, aeesa n ho, ki jo bhvishyadvktaon kee pustak men aya haai,
tum pr bhee a pade ki he ninda karanevalo, dekho, aur chaakit ho, aur mitt jao kyonaki maain tumhare dinon men aek kam karata hoon aeesa kam, ki yadi koi tum se usakee charcha kare, to tum kabhee prateeati n karoge..
un ke bahar nikalate samay log un se binatee karane lage, ki agale sabt ke din hamen ye baten fir sunai jaen.
aur jab sabha utt gai to yahoodiyon aur yahoodee mat men aae huae bhkton men se bahutere paulus aur baranabas ke peechhe ho liae aur unhon ne un se baten karake samajhaya, ki parameshvar ke anugrah men bane raho..
agale sabt ke din nagar ke praaya: sab log parameshvar ka vachan sunane ko ikatthe ho gaae.
tab polus aur baranabas ne nidr hokar kaha, avashy tha, ki parameshvar ka vachan paahile tumhen sunaya jata: parantu jab ki tum use door karate ho, aur apane ko anant jeevan ke yogy naheen ttharate, to dekho, ham anyajatiyon kee or firate haain.
