parantu n mananevale yahoodiyon ne anyajatiyon ke man bhaiyon ke virodha men usakaa, aur bigad kar diae.
aur ve bahut din tak vahan rahe, aur prabhu ke bhrose par hiyav se baten karate the: aur vah un ke hathon se chinh aur adabhut kam karavakar apane anugrah ke vachan par gavahee deta tha.
parantu nagar ke logon men foott pad gai thee is se kitane to yahoodiyon kee or, aur kitane praeariton kee or ho gaae.
