adhaee rat ke lagabhg paulus aur seelas praarthna karate huae parameshvar ke bhjan ga rahe the, aur bandhauae un kee sun rahe the.
ki itane men aekaaek bada bhuidol hua, yahan tak ki bandeegrah kee nev hil gai, aur turant sab dar khul gaae aur sab ke bandhan khul pade.
aur daroga jag utta, aur bandeegrah ke dar khule dekhkar samajha ki bandhauae bhag gaa, so us ne talavar kheenchakar apane ap ko mar dalana chaha.
parantu paulus ne unche shabd se pukarakar kaha apane ap ko kuchh hani n pahuncha, kyonki ham sab yahan haain.
tab vah deeya mangavakar bheetar lapak gaya, aur kanpata hua paulus aur seelas ke age gira.
aur unhen bahar lakar kaha, he sahibo, uddhar pane ke liye maain kya karoon?
unhon ne kaha, prabhu yeeshu maseeh par vishvas kar, to too aur tera gharana uddhar paega.
aur unhon ne us ko, aur usake sare ghar ke logon ko prabhu ka vachan sunaya.
aur us ne unhen apane ghar men le jakar, un ke age bhojan rakha aur sare gharane samet parameshvar par vishvas karake anand kiya..
jab din hua tak haakimon ne pyadon ke hath kahala bheja ki un manushyon ko chhod do.
daroga ne ye baten paulus se kah sunai, ki hakimon ne tumhare chhod dene kee agyaa bhej dee haai, so ab nikalakar kushal se chale jao.
parantu paulus ne us se kaha, unhon ne hamen jo romee manushy haai, doshaee ttharaae bina, logon ke samhane mara, aur bandeegrah men dala, aur ab kya chupake se nikal dete haain? aeesa nahee, parantu ve ap akar hamen bahar le jaaen.
pyadon ne ye baten hakimon se kah dee, aur ve yah sunakar ki romee haai, dr gaae.
aur akar unhen manaya, aur bahar le jakar binatee kee ki nagar se chale jaaen.
ve bandeegrah se nikal kar luadiya ke yahan gaa, aur bhaiyon se bhentt karake unhen shaaantai dee, aur chale gaae..
fir ve amfaipualis aur apulloniya hokar thaissaluneeke men aa, jahan yahoodiyon ka aek aradhanalay tha.
aur paulus apanee reeti ke anusar un ke pas gaya, aur teen sabt ke din pavitra shaasren se un ke sath vivad kiya.
aur un ka arth khol kholakar samajhata tha, ki maseeh ka dukh uttana, aur mare huon men se jee uttna, avashy tha aur yahee yeeshu jis kee maain tumhen katha sunata hoo, maseeh haai.
parantu yahoodiyon ne dah se bhrakar bajaroo logon men se kai dushtt manushyon ko apane sath men liya, aur bheed lagakar nagar men hullad machane lage, aur yason ke ghar par chaddhai karake unhen logon ke samhane lana chaha.
aur unhen n pakar, ve yah chillate huae yason aur kitane aur bhaiyon ko nagar ke haakimon ke samhane kheench laa, ki ye log jinhon ne jagal ko ulatta pulatta kar diya haai, yahan bhee aae haain.
aur yamon ne unhen apane yahan utara haai, aur ye sab ke sab yah kahate haain ki yeeshu raja haai, aur kaaisar kee agyaaon ka virodha karate haain.
unhon ne logon ko aur nagar ke haakimon ko yah sunakar ghabara diya.
aur unhon ne yason aur bakee logon se muchalaka lekar unhen chhod diya..
bhaiyon ne turant rat hee rat paulus aur seelas ko bireeya men bhej diya: aur ve vahan pahunchakar yahoodiyon ke aradhanalay men gaae.
ye log to thaissaluneeke ke yahoodiyon se bhle the aur unhon ne badee lalasa se vachan grahan kiya, aur praati din pavitra shaasren men ddoonddhte rahe ki ye baten yoheen haai, ki naheen.
so un men se bahuton ne, aur yoonanee kuleen striayon men se, aur purooshaen men se bahuteron ne vishvas kiya.
kintu jab thaissaluneeke ke yahoodee jan gaa, ki paulus bireeya men bhee parameshvar ka vachan sunata haai, to vahan bhee akar logon ko usakane aur halachal machane lage.
tab bhaiyon ne turant paulus ko vida kiya, ki samudra ke kinare chala jaae parantu seelas aur teemuthaiyus vaheen rah gaae.
paulus ke pahunchanevale use athene tak le gaa, aur seelas aur teemuthaiyus ke liye yah agyaa lekar vida hua, ki mere pas bahut shaeegha ao..
jab paulus athene men un kee batt joh raha tha, to nagar ko mooraton se bhra hua dekhkar usaka jee jal gaya.
so vah aradhanalay men yahoodiyon aur bhkton se aur chauk men jo log milate the, un se har din vada-vivad kiya karata tha.
tab iapikooree aur stoikee panditon men se kitane us se tarka karane lage, aur kitanon ne kaha, yah bakavadee kya kahana chahata haai? parantu auron ne kaha vah any devataon ka pracharak maloom padta haai, kyonki vah yeeshu ka, aur punarootthan ka susamachar sunata tha.
tab ve use apane sath ariyupagus par le gaae aur poochha, kya ham jan sakate haai, ki yah naya mat jo too sunata haai, kya haai?
kyonaki too anokhee baten hamen sunata haai, isaliye ham janana chahate haain ki in ka arth kya haai?
isaliye ki sab athenavee aur paradeshaee jo vahan rahate the nai nai baten kahane aur sunane ke sivay aur kisee kam men samay naheen bitate the.
tab paulus ne ariyupagus ke beech men khda hokar kaha he athene ke logon maain dekhta hoo, ki tum har bat men devataon ke bade mananevale ho.
kyonaki maain firate huae tumharee poojane kee vastuon ko dekh raha tha, to aek aeesee vedee bhee pai, jis par likha tha, ki anajane ishvar ke liye. so jise tum bina jane poojate ho, maain tumhen usaka samachar sunata hoon.
n kisee vastu ka prayojan rakhkar manushyon ke hathon kee seva leta haai, kyonki vah to ap hee sab ko jeevan aur svas aur sab kuchh deta haai.
us ne ek hee mool se manushyon kee sab jaatiyan saree prathvee par rahane ke liye banai haain aur un ke ttharaae huae samay, aur nivas ke sivanon ko isaaliye bandha haai.
ki ve parameshvar ko ddoonddhe, kadaachit use ttttolakar pa jaaen taubhee vah ham men se kisee se door naheen!
kyonaki ham usee men jeeavit rahate, aur chalate-afirate, aur sthiar rahate haain jaaise tumhare kitane kaviyon ne bhee kaha haai, ki ham to usee ke vansh bhee haain.
so parameshvar ka vansh hokar hamen yah samajhta uchit nahee, ki ishvaratv, sone ya roope ya patthr ke saman haai, jo manushy kee kareegaree aur kalpata se gaddhe gaae hon.
isaliye parameshvar agyaanata ke samayon men anakanee karake, ab har jagah sab manushyon ko man firane kee agyaa deta haai.
kyonaki us ne aek din ttharaya haai, jis men vah us manushy ke dara dharma se jagat ka nyay karega, jise us ne ttharaya haai aur use mare huon men se jilakar, yah bat sab par praamaanait kar dee haai..
mare huon ke punarootthan kee bat sunakar kitane to ttttha karane lage, aur kitanon ne kaha, yah bat ham tujh se fir kabhee sunenge.
is par paulus un ke beech men se nikal gaya.
is ke bad paulus athene ko chhodkar kuarinthus men aya.
aur vahan akvaila nam aek yahoodee mila, jis ka janm puntus ka tha aur apanee patnee pirsakilla samet italiya se naya aya tha, kyonaki klauadiyus ne sab yahoodiyon ko rom se nikal jane kee agyaa dee thee, so vah un ke yahan gaya.
aur usaka aur un ka aek hee udhym tha isaaliye vah un ke sath raha, aur ve kam karane lage, aur un ka udhym tamboo banane ka tha.
aur vah har aek sabt ke din aradhanalay men vada-vivad karake yahoodiyon aur yoonaaniyon ko bhee samajhata tha..
jab seelas aur teemuathaiyus maakiduaniya se aa, to paulus vachan sunane kee dhaun men lagakar yahoodiyon ko gavahee deta tha ki yeeshu hee maseeh haai.
parantu jab ve virodha aur ninda karane lage, to us ne apane kapade jhadkar un se kaha tumhara lohoo tumharee gardan par rahe: maain nidaush hoon: ab aee maain anyajatiyon ke pas jaunga.
aur vahan se chalakar vah titus yustus nam parameshvar ke aek bhkt ke ghar men aya, jis ka ghar aradhanalay se laga hua tha.
tab aradhanalay ke saradar krispus ne apane sare gharane samet prabhu par vishvas kiya aur bahut se kurinthee sunakar vishvas laae aur bapatisma liya.
aur prabhu ne rat ko darshan ke dara paulus se kaha, mat dr, baran kahe ja, aur chup mat raha.
kyonaki maain tere sath hoon: aur koi tujh par chaddhai karake teree haati n karega kyonaki is nagar men mere bahut se log haain.
so vah un men parameshvar ka vachan sikhate huae deddh varsha tak raha..
jab gaallaiyo akhaya desh ka hakim tha to yahoodee log aeka karake paulus par chaddh aa, aur use nyay asan ke samhane lakar, kahane lage.
ki yah logon ko samajhata haai, ki parameshvar kee upasana aeesee reeti se kare, jo vyavastha ke vipareet haai.
jab paulus bolane par tha, to gallaiyo ne yahoodiyon se kaha he yahoodiyo, yaadi yah kuchh anyay ya dushttta kee bat hotee to uchit tha ki maain tumharee sunata.
parantu yadi yah vada-vivad shabdo, aur namo, aur tumhare yahan kee vyavastha ke vishay men haai, to tum hee jano kyonaki maain in baton ka nyayee banana naheen chahata.
aur us ne unhen nyay asan ke samhane se nikalava diya.
tab sab loagen ne aradhanalay ke saradar sosthianes ko pakad ke nyay asan ke samhane mara: parantu gaallaiyo ne in baton kee kuchh bhee chinta n kee..
so paulus bahut din tak vahan raha, fir bhaiyon se vida hokar kinakhaiya men isaliye sir mundaya kyonaki us ne mannat manee thee aur jahaj par sooriya ko chal diya aur usake sath pirsakilla aur akvaila the.
aur us ne iafisus men pahunchakar un ko vahan chhoda, aur ap hee aradhanalay men jakar yahoodiyon se vivad karane laga.
jab unhon ne us se binatee kee, ki hamare sath aur kuchh din rah, to us ne sveekar n kiya.
tab iafisus se jahaj kholakar chal diya, aur kaaisaariya men utar kar yarooshalem ko gaya aur kaleesiya ko namaskar karake antakiya men aya.
fir kuchh din rahakar vahan se chala gaya, aur aek or se galatiya aur oogiya men sab chelon ko sthiar karata fira..
apullos nam aek yahoodee jis ka janm sikandaariya men hua tha, jo vidan puroosh tha aur paavitra shaasr ko achchhee tarah se janata tha ifisus men aya.
us ne prabhu ke marga kee shaiksha pai thee, aur man lagakar yeeshu ke vishay men tteek tteek sunata, aur sikhata tha, parantu vah keval yoohanna ke bapaatisma kee bat janata tha.
vah aradhanalay men nidr hokar bolane laga, par piraskailla aur akvaila us kee baten sunakar, use apane yahan le gaae aur parameshvar ka marga us ko aur bhee tteek tteek bataya.
aur jab us ne nishchay kiya ki par utarakar akhaya ko jaae to bhaiyon ne use ddhaddhs dekar chelon ko likha ki ve us se achchhee tarah mile, aur us ne pahunchakar vahan un logon kee badee sahayata kee jinhon ne anugrah ke karan vishvas kiya tha.
kyonaki vah pavitra shaasr se praman de dekar, ki yeeshu hee maseeh haai badee prabalata se yahoodiyon ko sab ke samhane niroottr karata raha..
aur jab apullos kurinthus men tha, to paulus upar se sare desh se hokar iafisus men aya, aur kai chelon ko dekhkara.
us ne un se kaha to fir tum ne kis ka bapaatisma liya? unhon ne kaha yoohanna ka bapaatisma.
paulus ne kaha yoohanna ne yah kahakar man firav ka bapatisma diya, ki jo mere bad anevala haai, us par arthata yeeshu par vishvas karana.
yah sunakar unhon ne prabhu yeeshu ke nam ka bapatisma liya.
aur jab paulus ne un par hath rakhe, to un par paavitra atma utara, aur ve bhainn bhasha bolane aur bhvishyadvvanee karane lage.
ye sab lagabhg barah puroosh the..
aur vah aradhanalay men jakar teen maheene tak nidr hokar bolata raha, aur parameshvar ke rajy ke vishay men vivad karata aur samajhata raha.
parantu jab kitanon ne kattor hokar us kee naheen manee baran logon ke samhane is marga ko bura kahane lage, to us ne un ko chhodkar chelon ko alag kar liya, aur praati din turannus kee pattshaala men vivad kiya karata tha.
do varsha tak yahee hota raha, yahan tak ki asiya ke rahanevale kya yahoodee, kya yoonanee sab ne prabhu ka vachan sun liya.
aur parameshvar paulus ke hathon se samarth ke anokhe kam dikhata tha.
yahan tak ki roomal aur angochhe us kee deh se chhulavakar beemaron par dalate the, aur un kee beemariyan jatee rahatee thee aur dushttatmaaen un men se nikal jaya karatee theen.
parantu kitane yahoodee jo jhada foonkee karate firate the, yah karane lage, ki jin men dushttatma hon un par prabhu yeeshu ka nam yah kahakar foonke ki jis yeeshu ka prachar paulus karata haai, maain tumhen usee kee shapath deta hoon.
aur skikava nam ke aek yahoodee mahayajak ke sat putra the, jo aeesa hee karate the.
par dushttatma ne uttr diya, ki yeeshu ko maain janatee hoo, aur paulus ko bhee pahachanatee hoon parantu tum kaun ho?
aur us manushy ne jis men dushtt atma thee un par lapakakar, aur unhen vash men lakar, un par aeesa upadrav kiya, ki ve nange aur ghaayal hokar us ghar se nikal bhage.
aur yah bat iafisus ke rahanevale yahoodee aur yoonanee bhee sab jan gaa, aur un sab par bhy chha gaya aur prabhu yeeshu ke nam kee badai hui.
aur jinhon ne vishvas kiya tha, un men se bahuteron ne akar apane apane kamon ko man liya aur pragatt kiya.
aur jadoo karanevalon men se bahuton ne apanee apanee pothaiyan ikatthee karake sab ke samhane jala deen aur jab un ka dam joda gaya, jo pachas hajar roopaye kee nikaleen.
yon prabhu ka vachan bal poorvak faailata gaya aur prabal hota gaya..
jab ye baten ho chukee, to paulus ne atma men ttana ki makiduaniya aur akhaya se hokar yarooshalem ko jau, aur kaha, ki vahan jane ke bad mujhe roma ko bhee dekhna avashy haai.
so apanee seva karanevalon men se teemuathaiyus aur irastus ko makiduaniya men bhejakar ap kuchh din asiya men rah gaya.
us samay men panth ke vishay men bada hullad hua.
us ne un ko, aur, aur aeesee vastuon ke kareegaron ko ikatthe karake kaha he manushyo, tum janate ho, ki is kam men hamen kitana dhan milata haai.
aur tum dekhte aur sunate ho, ki keval iafisus hee men nahee, baran praaya: sare asiya men yah kah kahakar is paulus ne bahut logon ko samajhaya aur bhramaya bhee haai, ki jo hath kee kareegaree haai, ve ishvar naheen.
aur ab keval isee aek bat ka hee dr nahee, ki hamare is dhandho kee pratishtta jatee rahegee baran yah ki mahan devee araatimis ka mandair tuchchh samajha jaaega aur jis sara aasiya aur jagat poojata haai usaka mahatv bhee jata rahega.
ve yah sunakar krodha se bhr gaa, aur chilla chillakar kahane lage, iafisiyon kee aratimis mahan haai!
aur sare nagar men bada kolahal mach gaya aur logon ne gayus aur aristarakhus makiduaniyon ko jo paulus ke sangee yatraee the, pakad liya, aur aekachitt hokar rangashaala men daud gaae.
jab paulus ne logon ke pas bheetar jana chaha to chelon ne use jane n diya.
aasiya ke haakimon men se bhee usake kai mitraen ne usake pas kahala bheja, aur binatee kee, ki rangashaala men jakar jokhaim n uttana.
tab unhon ne sikandar ko, jis yahoodiyon ne khda kiya tha, bheed men se age baddhaya, aur sikandar hath se saain karake logon ke samhane uttr diya chahata tha.
parantu jab unhon ne jan liya ki vah yahoodee haai, to sab ke sab aek shabd se koi do ghantte tak chillate rahe, ki ifaasiyon kee aratimis mahan haai.
tab nagar ke mantraee ne logon ko shaant karake kaha he ifisiyo, kaun naheen janata, ki ifisiyon ka nagar badee devee aratimis ke mandair, aur jyoos kee or se giree hui moorat ka tthalua haai.
so jab ki in baton ka khndn hee naheen ho sakata, to uchitt haai, ki tum chupake raho aur bina soche vichare kuchh n karo.
kyonaki tum in manushyon ko laae ho, jo n maandair ke loottnevale haai, aur n hamaree devee ke nindak haain.
yaadi demeatraiyus aur usake sathee kareegaron ko kisee se vivad ho to kachaharee khulee haai, aur hakim bhee haain ve aek doosare par naalish karen.
parantu yadi tum kisee aur bat ke vishay men kuchh poochhna chahate ho, to niyat sabha men faaisala kiya jaaega.
kyonaki aj ke balave ke karan ham par dosh lagaae jane ka dr haai, isaaliye ki is ka koi karan nahee, so ham is bheed ke ikattha hone ka koi uttr n de sakenge.
aur yah kah ke us ne sabha ko vida kiya..
he thaiyuafilus, maain ne paahilee puastaika un sab baton ke vishay men likhee, jo yeeshu ne arambh men kiya aur karata aur sikhata raha.
us din tak jab vah un prariton ko jinhen us ne chuna tha, paavitra atma ke dara agyaa dekar upar uttaya n gaya.
aur us ne du:kh uttane ke bad bahut se pakke pramanon se apane ap ko unhen jeeavit dikhaya, aur chalees din tak vah unhen dikhai deta raha: aur parameshvar ke rajy kee baten karata raha.
or un se milakar unhen agyaa dee, ki yarooshalem ko n chhodo, parantu pita kee us praatigyaa ke poore hone kee batt jahate raho, jis kee charcha tum mujh se sun chuke ho.
kyonaki yoohanna ne to panee men bapatisma diya haai parantu thode dinon ke bad tum paavitraatma se bapaatisma paoge.
so unheen ne ikatthe hokar us se poochha, ki he prabhu, kya too isee samay israael ko rajy faer dega?
us ne un se kaha un samayon ya kalon ko janana, jin ko pita ne apane hee aadhaikar men rakha haai, tumhara kam naheen.
parantu jab pavitra atma tum par aaega tab tum samarth paoge aur yarooshalem aur sare yahoodiya aur samariya me, aur prathvee kee chhor tak mere gavah hoge.
yah kahakar vah un ke dekhte dekhte upar utta liya gaya aur badal ne use un kee ankhon se chhpai liya.
aur usake jate samay jab ve akash kee or tak rahe the, to dekho, do puroosh shvet vasr paahine huae un ke pas a khde hue.
aur kahane lage he galeelee purooshae, tum kyon khde svarga kee or dekh rahe ho? yahee yeeshu, jo tumhare pas se svarga par utta liya gaya haai, jis reeti se tum ne use svarga ko jate dekha haai usee reeti se vah fir aaega..
tab ve jaaitoon nam ke pahad se jo yarooshalem ke nikatt aek sabt ke din kee dooree par haai, yarooshalem ko lautte.
aur jab vahan pahunche to ve us attaree par gaa, jahan pataras aur yoohanna aur yakoob aur aandairyas aur filippus aur thoma aur baratulamai aur mattee aur halafai ka putra yakoob aur shamaun jelotes aur yakoob ka putra yahooda rahate the.
aur unheen dinon men pataras bhaiyon ke beech men jo aek sau bees vyaktai ke lagabhg ikatthe the, khda hokar kahane laga.
he bhaiyo, avashy tha ki pavitra shaasr ka vah lekh poora ho, jo paavitra atma ne daud ke mukh se yahooda ke vishay men jo yeeshu ke pakadnevalon ka aguva tha, paahile se kahee thee.
kyonaki vah to ham men gina gaya, aur is sevakai men sahabhagee hua.
us ne adharma kee kamai se ek khet mol liya aur sir ke bal gira, aur usaka pett fatt gaya, aur us kee sab antadiyan nikal padee.
aur is bat ko yarooshalem ke sab rahanevale jan gaa, yahan tak ki us khet ka nam un kee bhasha men hakaladama arthata lohoo ka khet pad gaya.
kyonaki bhjan saahinta men likha haai, ki usaka ghar ujad jaa, aur us men koi n base aur usaka pad koi doosara le le.
uchit haai ki un men se ek vyaaktai hamare sath usake jee uttne ka gavah ho jae.
tak unhon ne do ko khda kiya, aek yusufa ko, jo bara-saba kahalata haai, jis ka upanam yoosatus haai, doosara maatiayyah ko.
aur yah kahakar praarthna kee ki he prabhu, too jo sab ke man janata haai, yah pragatt kar ki in danon men se too ne kis ko chuna haai.
ki vah is sevakai aur praaritai ka pad le jise yahooda chhod kar apane sthan ko gaya.
tab unhon ne un ke bare men chitthiyan dalee, aur chitthee maatiayyah ke nam par nikalee, so vah un gyarah praeariton ke sath gina gaya..
jab hullad thm gaya, to paulus ne chelon ko bulavakar samajhaya, aur un se vida hokar makiduaniya kee aur chal diya.
aur us sare desh men se hokar aur unhen bahut samajhakar, vah yoonan men aya.
jab teen maheene rahakar jahaj par sooriya kee or jane par tha, to yahoodee us kee ghaat men lage, isaliye us ne yah salah kee ki makiduaniya hokar lott aae.
bireeya ke purroos ka putra sopatraus aur thaissalooneeakiyon men se aaristarkhus aur sikundus aur aasiya ka tuakhaikus aur traufimus aasiya tak usake sath ho liae.
ve age jakar traeas men hamaree batt johate rahe.
aur ham akhmeeree rottee ke dinon ke ba filippee se jahaj par chaddhkar panch din men traeas men un ke pas pahunche, aur sat din tak vaheen rahe..
saptah ke paahile din jab ham rottee todne ke liye ikatthe hua, to paulus ne jo doosare din chale jane par tha, un se baten kee, aur adhaee rat tak baten karata raha.
jis attaree par ham ikatthe the, us men bahut deeye jal rahe the.
aur yootukhus nam ka aek javan khaidkee par baaitta hua gaharee neend se jhuk raha tha, aur jab paulus der tak baten karata raha to vah neend ke jhoke men teesaree attaree par se gir pada, aur mara hua uttaya gaya.
parantu paulus utarakar us se lipatt gaya, aur gale lagakar kaha ghabarao naheen kyonaki usaka praan usee men haai.
aur upar jakar rottee todee aur khakar itanee der tak un se baten karata raha, ki pau fatt gai fir vah chala gaya.
aur ve us ladke ko jeeavit le aa, aur bahut shaantai pai..
ham paahile se jahaj par chaddhkar assus ko is vichar se age gaa, ki vahan se ham paulus ko chaddha len kyonki us ne yah isaaliye ttharaya tha, ki ap hee paaidal janevala tha.
jab vah assus men hamen mila to ham use chaddhakar mitulene men aae.
aur vahan se jahaj kholakar ham doosare din khaiyus ke samhane pahunche, aur agale din samus men lagan kiya, fir doosare din meeletus men aae.
kyonaki paulus ne iafisus ke pas se hokar jane kee ttanee thee, ki kaheen aeesa n ho, ki use aasiya men der lage kyonki vah jaldee karata tha, ki yadi ho sake, to use pintekus ka din yarooshalem men katte..
aur us ne meeletus se iafisus men kahala bheja, aur kaleeasiya ke praacheenon ko bulavaya.
jab ve us ke pas aa, to un se kaha, tum janate ho, ki pahile hee din se jab maain aasiya men pahuncha, maain har samay tumhare sath kis prakar raha.
