parantu jo apane padosee par anyay kar raha tha, us ne use yah kahakar hatta diya, ki tujhe kis ne ham par hakim aur nyayee ttharaya haai?
kya jis reeti se too ne kal misaree ko mar dala mujhe bhee mar dalana chahata haai?
yah bat sunakar, moosa bhaga aur midhan desh men paradeshaee hokar rahane laga: aur vahan usake do putra utpann hue.
jab poore chalees varsha beet gaa, to aek svarga doot ne seenaai pahad ke jangal men use jalatee hui jhadee kee jvala men darshan diya.
moosa ne us darshan ko dekhkar achambha kiya, aur jab dekhne ke liye pas gaya, to prabhu ka yah shabd hua.
ki maain tere bapadado, ibraaheem, isahak aur yakoob ka parameshvar hoon: tab to moosa kanp utta, yahan tak ki use dekhne ka hiyav n raha.
tab prabhu ne us se kaha apane pavon se jootee utar le, kyonaki jis jagah too khda haai, vah pavitra boomi haai.
jis moosa ko unhon ne yah kahakar nakara tha ki tujhe kis ne ham par hakim aur nyayee ttharaya haai usee ko parameshvar ne haakim aur chhudanevala ttharakar, us svarga doot ke dara jis ne use jhadee men darshan diya tha, bheja.
yahee vyaaktai misar aur lal samudra aur jangal men chalees varsha tak adabhut kam aur chinh dikha dikhakar unhen nikal laya.
yah vahee moosa haai, jis ne israaeliyon se kaha ki parameshvar tumhare bhaiyon men se tumhare liye mujh sa aek bhavishyadvkta uttaaega.
yah vahee haai, jis ne jangal men kaleeasiya ke beech us svargadoot ke sath seenaai pahad par us se baten kee, aur hamare bapadadon ke sath tha: usee ko jeeavit vachan mile, ki ham tak pahunchaae.
parantu hamare bapadadon ne us kee manana n chaha baran use hattakar apane man misar kee or faere.
aur haroon se kaha hamare liye aeesa devata bana, jo hamare age age chalen kyonaki yah moosa ja hamen misar desh se nikal laya, ham naheen janate use kya hua?
un dinon men unhon ne ek bachhda banakar, us kee moorat ke age bali chaddhaya aur apane hathon ke kamon men magan hone lage.
so parameshvar ne munh modkar unhen chhod diya, ki akashagan poojen jaaisa bhvishyadvktaon kee pustak men likha haai ki he israael ke gharane, kya tum jangal men chalees varsha tak pashuubaali aur annabaali mujh hee ko chaddhate rahe?
aur tum molek ke tamboo aur rifaan devata ke tare ko liae firate the arthata un akaron ko jinhen tum ne dandvat karane ke liye banaya tha: so maain tumhen babur ke pare le jakar basaunga.
sakshaee ka tamboo jangal men hamare bapadadon ke beech men tha jaaisa us ne ttharaya, jis ne moosa se kaha ki jo akar too ne dekha haai, usake anusar ise bana.
us par parameshvar ne anugrah kiya, so us ne binatee kee, ki maain yakoob ke parameshvar ke liye nivas stha ttharaun.
parantu sulaaiman ne usake liye ghar banaya.
parantu param pradhaan hath ke banaae gharon men naheen rahata, jaaisa ki bhvishyadvkta ne kaha.
ki prabhu kahata haai, svarga mera sihansan aur prathvee mere panvon tale kee peeddhee haai, mere liye tum kis prakar ka ghar banaoge? aur mere vishraam ka kaun sa sthan hoga?
kya ye sab vastuen mere hath kee banai naheen? he hatteele, aur man aur kan ke khtanaraahit logo, tum sada pavitra atma ka samhana karate ho.
jaaisa tumhare bapadade karate the, vaaise hee tum bhee karate ho.
bhavishyadvktaon men se kis ko tumhare bapadadon ne naheen sataya, aur unhon ne us dharmee ke agaman ka poorvakal se sandesh denevalon ko mar dala, aur ab tum bhee usake pakadvanevale aur mar dalanevale hue.
tum ne svargadooton ke dara ttharai hui vyavastha to pai, parantu usaka palan naheen kiya..
ye baten sunakar ve jal gaae aur us par dant peesane lage.
parantu us ne pavitra atma se paaripoorn hokar svarga kee or dekha aur parameshvar kee maahima ko aur yeeshu ko parameshvar kee dahinee or khda dekhkara.
kaha dekho, maain svarga ko khula hua, aur manushy ke putra ko parameshvar ke dahinee or khda hua dekhta hoon.
tab unhon ne bade shabd se chillakar kan band kar lia, aur aek chitt hokar us par jhpatte.
aur use nagar ke bahar nikalakar patthravah karane lage, aur gavahon ne apane kapade utar rakhe.
aur ve staiufanus ko patthravah karate rahe, aur vah yah kahakar praarthna karata raha ki he prabhu yeeshu, meree atma ko grahan kara.
fir ghauttne ttekakar unche shabd se pukara, he prabhu, yah pap un par mat laga, aur yah kahakar so gaya: aur shaaul usake badha meen sahamat tha..
usee din yarooshalem kee kaleesiya par bada upadrav hone laga aur praeriton ko chhod sab ke sab yahoodiya aur samariya deshaen men tittr bittr ho gae.
aur bhkton ne staifanus ko kabra men rakha aur usake liye bada vilap kiya.
shaaul kaleesiya ko ujad raha tha aur ghar ghar ghausakar purooshaen aur striayon ko ghaseett ghaseettkar bandeegrah men dalata tha..
aur filippus samaariya nagar men jakar logon men maseeh ka prachar karane laga.
aur jo baten filippus ne kaheen unhen logon ne sunakar aur jo chinh vah dikhata tha unhen dekh dekhkar, aek chitt hokar man lagaya.
kyonaki bahuton men se ashuuddh atmaaen bade shabd se chillatee hui nikal gai, aur bahut se jhole ke mare huae aur langade bhee achchhe kiae gaae.
aur us nagar men bada anand hua..
is se paahile us nagar men shamaun nam aek manushy tha, jo ttona karake samaariya ke logon ko chakit karata aur apane ap ko koi bada puroosh banata than
aur sab chhotte se bade tak use man kar kahate the, ki yah manushy paramashevar kee vah shaktai haai, jo mahan kahalatee haai.
us ne bahut dinon se unhen apane ttone ke kamon se chaakit kar rakha tha, isee liye ve us ko bahut manate the.
parantu jab unhon ne filippus kee prateeati kee jo parameshvar ke rajy aur yeeshu ke nam ka susamachar sunata tha to log, kya puroosha, kya sree bapaatisma lene lage.
tab shamaun ne ap bhee prateeati kee aur bapaatisma lekar filippus ke sath rahane laga aur chinh aur bade bade samarth ke kam hote dekhkar chakit hota tha.
jab praariton ne jo yarooshalem men the suna ki samaariyon ne parameshvar ka vachan man liya haai to pataras aur yoohanna ko un ke pas bheja.
aur unhon ne jakar un ke liye praarthna kee ki pavitra atma paaen.
tab unhon ne un par hath rakhe aur unhon ne pavitra atma paya.
jab shamaun ne dekha ki prariton ke hath rakhne se paavitra atma diya jata haai, to un ke pas roopaye lakar kaha.
ki yah adhaikar mujhe bhee do, ki jis kisee par hath rakoo, vah pavitra atma paae.
pataras ne us se kaha tere roopaye tere sath nash ho, kyonki too ne parameshvar ka dan roopayon se mol lene ka vichar kiya.
is bat men n tera hissa haai, n bantta kyonki tera man parameshvar ke age seedha naheen.
isaliye apanee is burai se man firakar prabhu se praarthna kar, sambhv haai tere man ka vichar kshama kiya jaae.
kyonaki maain dekhta hoo, ki too pitt kee see kadvahatt aur adharma ke bandhan men pada haai.
shamaun ne uttr diya, ki tum mere liye prabhu se praarthna karo ki jo baten tum ne kahee, un men se koi mujh par n a pade..
so ve gavahee dekar aur prabhu ka vachan sunakar, yarooshalem ko lautt gaa, aur samariyon ke bahut gavon men susamachar sunate gaae..
fir prabhu ke aek svargadoot ne filippus se kaha uttkar daakkhian kee or us marga par ja, jo yarooshalem se ajjah ko jata haai, aur jangal men haai.
vah uttkar chal diya, aur dekho, koosh desh ka aek manushy a raha tha jo khoja aur kooshaiyon kee ranee kandake ka mantraee aur khjanchee tha, aur bhjan karane ko yarooshalem aya tha.
aur vah apane rath par baaitta hua tha, aur yashaayah bhavishyadvkta kee pustak paddhta hua lautta ja raha tha.
tab atma ne filippus se kaha, nikatt jakar is rath ke sath ho le.
filippus ne us or daudkar use yashaayah bhavishyadvkta kee pustak paddhte huae suna, aur poochha, ki too jo paddh raha haai kya use samajhta bhee haai?
us ne kaha, jab tak koi mujhe n samajhaae to maain kyanekar samajoon? aur us ne filippus se binatee kee, ki chaddhkar mere pas baaitt.
paavitra shaasr ka jo adhyay vah paddh raha tha, vah yah tha ki vah bhed kee nain vadha hone ko pahunchaya gaya, aur jaaisa memna apane un kataranevalon ke samhane chupachap rahata haai, vaaise hee us ne bhee apana munh n khola.
us kee deenata men usaka nyay hone naheen paya, aur usake samay ke logon ka varnn kaun karega, kyonki prathvee se usaka praan uttaya jata haai.
tab filippus ne apana munh khola, aur isee shaasr se arambh karake use yeeshu ka susamachar sunaya.
marga men chalate chalate ve kisee jal kee jagah pahunche, tab khoje ne kaha, dekh yahan jal haai, ab mujhe bapaatisma lene men kya rok haai.
filippus ne kaha, yaadi too sare man se vishvas karata haai to ho sakata haai: us ne uttr diya maain vishvas karata hoon ki yeeshu maseeh parameshvar ka putra haai.
tab us ne rath khda karane kee agyaa dee, aur filippus aur khoja donon jal men utar pade, aur us ne use bapaatisma diya.
jab ve jal men se nikalakar upar aa, to prabhu ka atma filippus ko utta le gaya, so khoje ne use fir n dekha, aur vah anand karata hua apane marga chala gaya.
aur filippus ashadod men a nikala, aur jab tak kaaisariya men n pahuncha, tab tak nagar nagar susamachar sunata gaya..
aur shaaul jo ab tak prabhu ke chelon ko dhamakane aur ghaat karane kee dhaun men tha, mahayajak ke pas gaya.
aur us se daamishk kee aradhanalayon ke nam par is abhaipraay kee chitthiyan mangee, ki kya puroosha, kya sre, jinhen vah is panth par paae unhen bandhakar yarooshalem men le aae.
parantu chalate chalate jab vah damishk ke nikatt pahuncha, to aekaaek akash se usake charon or jyoti chamakee.
aur vah boomi par gir pada, aur yah shabd suna, ki he shaaul, he shaaul, too mujhe kyon satata haai?
us ne poochha he prabhu, too kaun haai? us ne kaha maain yeeshu hoon jise too satata haai.
parantu ab uttkar nagar men ja, aur jo kuchh karana haai, vah tujh se kaha jaaega.
tab shaaul boomi par se utta, parantu jab ankhe kholeen to use kuchh dikhai n diya aur ve usaka hath pakadke daamishk men le gaae.
aur vah teen din tak n dekh saka, aur n khaya aur n peeya.
daamishk men hananyah nam aek chela tha, us se prabhu ne darshan men kaha, he hananyaha! us ne kaha han prabhu.
tab prabhu ne us se kaha, uttkar us galee men ja jo seedhaee kahalatee haai, aur yahooda ke ghar men shaaul nam aek tarasee ko poochh le kyonaki dek, vah praarthna kar raha haai.
aur us ne hananyah nam aek puroosh ko bheetar ate, aur apane upar ate dekha haai taki fir se drashtti paae.
hananyah ne uttr diya, ki he prabhu, maain ne is manushy ke vishay men bahuton se suna haai, ki is ne yarooshalem men tere pavitra logon ke sath badee badee buraiyan kee haain.
aur yahan bhee is ko mahayajakon kee or se adhaikar mila haai, ki jo log tera nam lete haai, un sab ko bandha le.
parantu prabhu ne us se kaha, ki too chala ja kyonaki yah, to anyajatiyon aur rajao, aur israaeliyon ke samhane mera nam pragatt karane ke liye mera chuna hua patra haai.
aur maain use bataunga, ki mere nam ke liye use kaaisa kaaisa dukh uttana padega.
tab hananyah uttkar us ghar men gaya, aur us par apana hath rakhkar kaha, he bhai shaaul, prabhu, arthata yeeshu, jo us raste me, jis se too aya tujhe dikhai diya tha, usee ne mujhe bheja haai, ki too fir drashtti paae aur paavitra atma se paaripoorn ho jaae.
aur turant us kee ankhon se chhlaike se gire, aur vah dekhne laga aur uttkar bapaatisma liya fir bhojan karake bal paya..
aur vah kai din un chelon ke sath raha jo damishk men the.
aur vah turant aradhanalayon men yeeshu ka prachar karane laga, ki vah parameshvar ka putra haai.
aur sab sunanevale chaakit hokar kahane lage kya yah vahee vyaaktai naheen haai jo yarooshalem men unhen jo is nam ko lete the nash karata tha, aur yahan bhee isee liye aya tha, ki unhon bandhakar mahayajakon ke pas le aae?
parantu shaaul aur bhee samarthee hota gaya, aur is bat ka praman de dekar ki maseeh yahee haai, daamishk ke rahanevale yahoodiyon ka munh band karata raha..
jab bahut din beet gaa, to yahoodiyon ne milakar usake mar dalane kee yuktai nikalee.
parantu rat ko usake chelon ne use lekar ttokare men baaittaya, aur shaharapanah par aee lattkakar utar diya..
yarooshalem men pahunchakar us ne chelon ke sath mil jane ka upay kiya: parantu sab us se drate the, kyonki un ko prateeati n hota tha, ki vah bhee chela haai.
parantu baranaba use apane sath praeariton ke pas le jakar un se kaha, ki is ne kis reeti se marga men prabhu ko dekha, aur is ne is se baten keen fir damishk men is ne kaaise hiyav se yeeshu ke nam ka prachar kiya.
vah un ke sath yarooshalem men ata jata raha.
aur nidhadk hokar prabhu ke nam se prachar karata tha: aur yoonanee bhasha bolanevale yahoodiyon ke sath batacheet aur vada-avivad karata tha parant uve usake mar dalane ka yatn karane lage.
yah janakar bhai use kaaisaariya men le aa, aur tarasus ko bhej diya..
so sare yahoodiya, aur galeel, aur samariya men kaleesiya ko chaain mila, aur usakee unnaati hotee gai aur vah prabhu ke bhy aur paavitra atma kee shaantai men chalatee aur baddhtee jatee thee..
aur aeesa hua ki pataras har jagah firata hua, un paavitra logon ke pas bhee pahuncha, jo lua men rahate the.
vahan use aeeaniyas nam jhole ka mara hua aek manushy mila, jo att varsha se khatt par pada tha.
pataras ne us se kaha he aeeniyasa! yeeshu maseeh tujhe changa karata haai ut, apana bichhauna bichha tab vah turant utt khd hua.
aur lua aur shaaron ke sab rahanevale use dekhkar prabhu kee or fire..
yafaa men tabeeta arthata dorakas nam aek vishvasinee rahatee thee, vah bahutere bhle bhle kam aur dan kiya karatee thee.
unheen dinon men vah beemar hokar mar gai aur unhon ne use nahalakar attaree par rakh diya.
tab pataras uttkar un ke sath ho liya, aur jab pahunch gaya, to ve use us attaree par le gaae aur sab vidhavaaen rotee hui usake pas a khdee hui: aur jo kurate aur kapade dorakas ne un ke sath rahate huae banaae the, dikhane lageen.
tab pataras ne sab ko bahar kar diya, aur ghauttne ttekakar praarthna kee aur loth kee or dekhkar kaha he tabeeta utt: tab us ne apanee ankhe khol dee aur pataras ko dekhkar utt baaittee.
us ne hath dekar use uttaya aur paavitra logon aur vidhavaon ko bulakar use jeevit aur jagrat dikha diya.
yah bat sare yafaa me faail gai: aur bahuteron ne prabhu par vishvas kiya.
aur pataras yafaa men shamaun nam kisee chamade ke dhandha karanevale ke yahan bahut din tak raha..
he bhaiyo, mere man kee abhailasha aur un ke liye parameshvar se meree praarthna haai, ki ve uddhar paaen.
kyonaki maain un kee gavahee deta hoo, ki un ko parameshvar ke liye dhaun rahatee haai, parantu buddhmaianee ke sath naheen.
kyonkai ve parameshvar kee dhaaarmikata se anajan hokar, aur apanee dhaaarmikata sthapan karane ka yatn karake, parameshvar kee dhaarmikata ke adhaeen n huae.
kyonaki har aek vishvas karanevale ke liye dhaarmikata ke nimitt maseeh vyavastha ka ant haai.
kyonaki moosa ne yah likha haai, ki jo manushy us dhaaarmikata par jo vyavastha se haai, chalata haai, vah isee karan jeevit rahega.
parantu jo dhaaarmikata vishvas se haai, vah yon kahatee haai, ki too apane man men yah n kahana ki svarga par kaun chaddhega? arthata maseeh ko utar lane ke liye!
ya gaahirav men kaun utarega? arthata maseeh ko mare huon men se jilakar upar lane ke liye!
parantu kya kahatee haai? yah, ki vachan tere nikatt haai, tere munh men aur tere man men haai yah vahee vishvas ka vachan haai, jo ham prachar karate haain.
ki yadi too apane munh se yeeshu ko prabhu janakar angeekar kare aur apane man se vishvas kare, ki parameshvar ne use mare huon men se jilaya, to too nishchay uddhar paaega.
kyonaki dhaaarmikata ke liye man se vishvas kiya jata haai, aur uddhar ke liye munh se angeekar kiya jata haai.
yahoodiyon aur yoonaaniyon men kuchh bhed nahee, isaaliye ki vah sab ka prabhu haai aur apane sab nam lenevalon ke liye udar haai.
kyonaki jo koi prabhu ka nam lega, vah uddhar paaega.
fir jis par unhon ne vishvas naheen kiya, ve usaka nam kyonkar len? aur jis kee naheen sunee us par kyonkar vishvas karen?
aur pracharak bina kyonkar sunen? aur yadi bheje n jaae, to kyonkar prachar karen? jaaisa likha haai, ki un ke panv kya hee sohavane haai, jo achchhee baton ka susamachar sunate haain.
parantu sab ne us susamachar par kan n lagaya: yashaayah kahata haai, ki he prabhu, kis ne hamare samachar kee prateeati kee haai?
so vishvas sunane se, aur sunana maseeh ke vachan se hota haai.
parantu maain kahata hoo, kya unhon ne naheen suna? suna to sahee kyonaki likha haai ki un ke svar saree prathvee par, aur un ke vachan jagat kee chhor tak pahunch gaae haain.
fir maain kahata hoon. kya israaelee naheen janate the? paahile to moosa kahata haai, ki maain un ke dara jo jati nahee, tumhare man men jalan upajaunga, maain aek mooddh jati ke dara tumhen ris dilaunga.
fir yashaayah bade hiyav ke sath kahata haai, ki jo mujhe naheen ddoonddhte the, unhon ne mujhe pa liya: aur jo mujhe poochhte bhee n the, un par maain pragatt ho gaya.
parantu israael ke vishay men vah yah kahata haai ki maain sare din apane hath aek agyaa n mananevalee aur vivad karanevalee praja kee or pasare raha..
isaliye maain kahata hoo, kya parameshvar ne apanee praja ko tyag diya? kadapi naheen maain bhee to israaelee hoon: ibraaheem ke vansh aur binyameen ke gotra men se hoon.
parameshvar ne apanee us praja ko naheen tyaga, jise us ne paahile hee se jana: kya tum naheen janate, ki pavitra shaasr aeliyah kee katha men kya kahata haai ki vah israael ke virodha men parameshvar se binatee karata haai.
ki he prabhu, unhon ne tere bhvishyadvktaon ko ghaat kiya, aur teree vediyon ko ddha diya haai aur maain hee akela bach raha hoo, aur ve mere praan ke bhee khojee haain.
parantu parameshvar se use kya uttr mila ki maain ne apane liye sat hajar purooshaen ko rakh chhoda haai jinhon ne baal ke ag ghauttne naheen tteke haain.
yaadi yah anugrah se hua haai, to fir karmon se nahee, naheen to anugrah fir anugrah naheen raha.
so paarinam kya hua? yah ki israaelee jis kee khoj men haai, vah un ko naheen mila parantu chune huon ko mila aur shosh log kattor kiae gaae haain.
jaaisa likha haai, ki parameshvar ne unhen aj ke din tak bharee neend men dal rakha haai aur aeesee ankhen dee jo n dekhen aur aeese kan jo n sunen.
aur daud kahata haai un ka bhojan un ke liye jal, aur fanda, aur ttokar, aur dand ka karan ho jaae.
un kee ankhon par andhora chha jaae taaki n dekhe, aur too sada un kee peett ko jhukaae rakh.
so maain kahata hoon kya unhon ne isaaliye ttokar khai, ki gir paden? kadapi naheen: parantu un ke girane ke karan anyajaniyon ko uddhar mila, ki unhen jalan ho.
so yaadi un ka girana jagat ke liye dhan aur un kee ghattee anyajaatiyon ke liye sampaati ka karan hua, to un kee bhrapooree se kitana n hoga..
maain tum anyajaatiyon se yah baten kahata hoon: jab ki maain anyajatiyon ke liye praerit hoo, to maain apanee seva kee badai karata hoon.
taaki kisee reeati se maain apane kuttumbaiyon se jalan karavakar un men se kai aek ka uddhar karaun.
kyonaki jab ki un ka tyag diya jana jagat ke milap ka karan hua, to kya un ka grahan kiya jana mare huon men se jee uttne ke barabar n hoga?
jab bhentt ka pahila peda paavitra tthara, to poora gundha hua atta bhee paavitra haai: aur jab jad paavitra ttharee, to daaliyan bhee aeesee hee haain.
aur yaadi kai aek dalee tod dee gai, aur too jangalee jalapai hokar un men satta gaya, aur jalapai kee jad kee chikanai ka bhagee hua haai.
to daaliyon par ghamand n karana: aur yadi too ghamand kare, to jan rak, ki too jad ko nahee, parantu jad tujhe sambhalatee haai.
fir too kahega daliyan isaliye todee gai, ki maain satta jaun.
kyonaki jab parameshvar ne svabhavik daliyan n chhodee, to tujhe bhee n chhodega.
isaliye parameshvar kee krapa aur kadai ko dekh! jo gir gaa, un par kadai, parantu tujh par krapa, yadi too us men bana rahe, naheen to, too bhee katt dala jaaega.
aur ve bhee yaadi avishvas men n rahe, to satte jaaenge kyonaki paramashevar unhen fir satt sakata haai.
kyonaki yadi too us jalapai se, jo svabhav se jangalee haai katta gaya aur svabhav ke virooddh achchhee jalapai men satta gaya to ye jo svabhavik daliyan haai, apane hee jalapai men satte kyon n jaaenge.
he bhaiyo, kaheen aeesa n ho, ki tum apane ap ko buddhmaian samajh lo isaaliye maain naheen chahata ki tum is bhed se anajan raho, ki jab tak anyajaatiyan pooree reeati se pravesh n kar le, tab tak israael ka aek bhag aeesa hee kattor rahega.
aur is reeati se sara israael uddhar paaega jaaisa likha haai, ki chhudanevala siyyon se aaega, aur abhktai ko yakoob se door karega.
aur un ke sath meree yahee vacha hogee, jab ki maain un ke papon ko door kar doonga.
ve susamachar ke bhav se to tumhare baairee haai, parantu chun liye jane ke bhav se bapadadon ke pyare haain.
kyonaki parameshvar apane baradanon se, aur bulahatt se kabhee peechhe naheen hattta.
