aur ham jatane haai, ki aeese aeese kam karanevalon par parameshvar kee or se tteek tteek dand kee agyaa hotee haai.
aur he manushy, too jo aeese aeese kam karanevalon par dosh lagata haai, aur ap ve hee kam karata haai kya yah samajhta haai, ki too parameshvar kee dand kee agyaa se bach jaaega?
kya too us kee krapa, aur sahanashaeelata, aur dhaeerajaroopee dhan ko tuchchh janata haai? aur kaya yah naheen samajhta, ki parameshvar kee krapa tujhe man firav ko sikhatee haai?
par apanee kattorata aur hatteele man ke anusar usake krodha ke din ke liye, jis men parameshvar ka sachcha nyay pragatt hoga, apane nimitt krodha kama raha haai.
jo sukarma men sthiar rahakar maahima, aur adar, aur amarata kee khoj men haai, unhen anant jeevan dega.
par jo vivadee haai, aur saty ko naheen manate, baran adharma ko manate haai, un par krodha aur kop padega.
aur klesh aur sankatt har aek manushy ke praan par jo bura karata haai, pahile yahoodee par fir yoonanee para.
par maahima aur adar or kalyan har aek ko milega, jo bhla karata haai, pahile yahoodee ko fir yoonanee ko.
kyonaki parameshvar kisee ka paksha naheen karata.
isaliye ki jinhon ne bina vyavastha paae pap kiya, ve bina vyavastha ke nash bhee honge, aur jinhon ne vyavastha pakar pap kiya, un ka dand vyavastha ke anusar hoga.
kyonaki parameshvar ke yahan vyavastha ke sunanevale dharmee nahee, par vyavastha par chalanevale dharmee ttharaae jaaenge.
fir jab anyajaati log jin ke pas vyavastha nahee, svabhav hee se vyavastha kee baton par chalate haai, to vyavastha un ke pas n hone par bhee ve apane liye ap hee vyavastha haain.
jis din parameshvar mere susamachar ke anusar yeeshu maseeh ke dara manushyon kee gupt baton ka nyay karega..
yaadi too yahoodee kahalata haai, aur vyavastha par bhrosa rakhta haai, aur parameshvar ke vishay men ghamand karata haai.
aur us kee ichchha janata aur vyavastha kee shaiksha pakar uttm uttm baton ko piry janata haai.
aur apane par bhrosa rakhta haai, ki maain andhaen ka aguva, aur andhakar men pade huon kee jyoti.
aur buaddhhaieenon ka sikhanevala, aur balakon ka upadeshak hoo, aur gyaan, aur saty ka namoona, jo vyavastha men haai, mujhe mila haai.
so kya too jo auron ko sikhata haai, apane ap ko naheen sikhata? kya too choree n karane ka upadesh deta haai, ap hee choree karata haai?
too jo kahata haai, vyaabhaichar n karana, kya ap hee vyabhaichar karata haai? too jo mooraton se gharana karata haai, kya ap hee maandairon ko loottta haai.
too jo vyavastha ke vishay men ghamand karata haai, kya vyavastha n manakar, parameshvar ka anadar karata haai?
kyonaki tumhare karan anyajaatiyon men parameshvar ke nam kee ninda kee jatee haai jaaisa likha bhee haai.
yaadi too vyavastha par chale, to khtane se laabh to haai, parantu yadi too vyavastha ko n mane, to tera khtana bin khtana kee dasha tthara.
so yaadi khtanaraahit manushy vyavastha kee vidhaiyon ko mana kare, to kya us kee bin khtana kee dasha khtane ke barabar n ginee jaaegee?
aur jo manushy jaati ke karan bin khtana raha yaadi vah vyavastha ko poora kare, to kya tujhe jo lekh pane aur khtana kiae jane par bhee vyavastha ko mana naheen karata haai, doshaee n ttharaaega?
kyonaki vah yahoodee nahee, par pragatt men haai, aur deh men haai.
par yahoodee vahee haai, jo man men haai aur khtana vahee haai, jo day ka aur atma men haai n ki lekh ka: aeese kee prashansa manushyon kee or se nahee, parantu parameshvar kee or se hotee haai..
so yahoodee kee kya badai, ya khtane ka kya labh?
har prakar se bahut kuchh. pahile to yah ki paramashevar ke vachan un ko saunpe gaae.
yaadi kitane vishvasaghaatee nikale bhee to kya hua. kya unake vishvasaghaatee hone se parameshvar kee sachchai vyarth ttharegee?
kadapi nahee, baran parameshvar sachcha aur har aek manushy jootta tthare, jaaisa likha haai, ki jis se too apanee baton men dharmee tthare aur nyay karate samay too jay paae.
so yaadi hamara adharma parameshvar kee dhaaarmikata tthara deta haai, to ham kya kahen? kya yah ki parameshvar jo krodha karata haai anyayee haai? yah to maain manushy kee reeti par kahata hoon.
kadapi nahee, naheen to parameshvar kyonkar jagat ka nyay karega?
yaadi mere joott ke karan parameshvar kee sachchai us ko mahima ke liye aadhaik karake pragatt hui, to fir kyon papee kee nai maain dand ke yogy ttharaya jata hoon?
to fir kya hua? kya ham un se achchhe haain? kabhee nahanee kyonki ham yahoodiyon aur yoonaaniyon donon par yah dosh laga chuke haain ki ve sab ke sab pap ke vash men haain.
jaaisa likha haai, ki koi dharmee nahee, aek bhee naheen.
koi samajhdar nahee, koi parameshvar ka khojanevala naheen.
sab bhttk gaae haai, sab ke sab nikamme ban gaa, koi bhlai karanevala nahee, aek bhee naheen.
un ka gala khulee hui kabra haai: unheen ne apanee jeebhon se chhl kiya haai: un ke hotton men sapon ka vish haai.
aur un ka munh shraap aur kadvahatt se bhra haai.
un ke panv lohoo bahane ko faurteele haain.
unhon ne kushal ka marga naheen jana.
un kee ankhon ke samhane parameshvar ka bhy naheen.
ham janate haai, ki vyavastha jo kuchh kahatee haai unheen se kahatee haai, jo vyavastha ke adhaeen haain: isaliye ki har aek munh band kiya jaa, aur sara sansar parameshvar ke dand ke yogy tthare.
kyeanki vyavastha ke kamon se koi praanee usake samhane dharmee naheen ttharega, isaaliye ki vyavastha ke dara pap kee paahichan hotee haai.
par ab bina vyavastha parameshvar kee dhaarmikata pragatt hui haai, jis kee gavahee vyavastha aur bhvishyadvkta dete haain.
arthata parameshvar kee vah dhaarmikata, jo yeeshu maseeh par vishvas karane se sab vishvas karanevalon ke liye haai kyonki kuchh bhed naheen.
isaliye ki sab ne pap kiya haai aur parameshvar kee maahima se raahit haai.
parantu usake anugrah se us chhuttkare ke dara jo maseeh yeeshu men haai, sent ment dharmee ttharaae jate haain.
use parameshvar ne usake lohoo ke karan ek aeesa praayaashchaitt ttharaya, jo vishvas karane se karyakaree hota haai, ki jo pap pahile kiae gaa, aur jin kee parameshvar ne apanee sahanashaeelata se anakanee kee un ke vishay men vah apanee dhaarmikata pragatt kare.
baran isee samay us kee dhaaarmikata pragatt ho ki jis se vah ap hee dharmee tthare, aur jo yeeshu par vishvas kare, usaka bhee dharmee ttharanevala ho.
to ghamand karana kahan raha? us kee to jagah hee naheen: kaun see vyavastha ke karan se? kya karmon kee vyavastha se? nahee, baran vishvas kee vyavastha ke karan.
isaliye ham is paarinam par pahunchate haai, ki manushy vyavastha ke kamon ke bina vishvas ke dara dharmee ttharata haai.
kya parameshvar keval yahoodiyon heen ka haai? kya anyajatiyon ka naheen? ha, anyajaatiyon ka bhee haai.
kyonaki aek hee parameshvar haai, jo khtanavalon ko vishvas se aur khtanaraahiton ko bhee vishvas ke dara dharmee ttharaaega.
te kya ham vyavastha ko vishvas ke dara vyarth ttharate haain? kadaapi naheen baran vyavastha ko sthiar karate haain..
so ham kya kahe, ki hamare shaareerik pita ibraaheem ko kya praapt hua?
kyonaki yadi ibraaheem kamon se dharmee ttharaya jata, to use ghamand karane kee jagah hotee, parantu parameshvar ke nikatt naheen.
paavitra shaasr kya kahata haai? yah ki ibraaheem ne parameshvar par vishvas kiya, aur yah usake liye dhaarmikata gina gaya.
kam karanevale kee majadooree dena dan nahee, parantu hakk samajha jata haai.
parantu jo kam naheen karata baran bhktaiheen ke dharmee ttharanevale par vishvas karata haai, usaka vishvas usake liye dhaarmikata gina jata haai.
jise parameshvar bina kamon ke dharmee ttharata haai, use daud bhee dhany kahata haai.
ki dhany ve haai, jin ke adharma kshama hua, aur jin ke pap ddhape gaae.
te yah dhany kahana, kya khtanavalon hee ke liye haai, ya khtanaraahiton ke liye bhee? ham yah kahate haai, ki ibraaheem ke liye usaka vishvas dhaaarmikata gina gaya.
to vah kyonkar gina gaya? khtane kee dasha men ya bina khtane kee dasha men? khtane kee dasha men naheen parantu bina khtane kee dasha men.
aur us ne khtane ka chinh paya, ki us vishvas kee dhaaarmikata par chhap ho jaa, jo us ne bina khtane kee dasha men rakha tha: jis se vah un sab ka pita tthare, jo bina khtane kee dasha men vishvas karate haai, aur ki ve bhee dharmee ttharen.
aur un khtana kiae huon ka pita ho, jo n keval khtana kiae huae haai, parantu hamare pita ibraaheem ke us vishvas kee leek par bhee chalate haai, jo us ne bin khtane kee dasha men kiya tha.
kyonaki yah pratigyaa ki vah jagat ka vaaris hoga, n ibraaheem ko, n usake vansh ko vyavastha ke dara dee gai thee, parantu vishvas kee dhaaarmikata ke dara milee.
kyonaki yadi vyavasthavale varis haai, to vishvas vyarth aur pratigyaa nishfal ttharee.
isee karan vah vishvas ke dara milatee haai, ki anugrah kee reeti par ho, ki pratigyaa sab vansh ke liye draddh ho, n ki keval usak liye jo vyavasthavala haai, baran un ke liye bhee jo ibraaheem ke saman vishvasavale haain: vahee to ham sab ka pita haai.
jaaisa likha haai, ki maain ne tujhe bahut see jaatiyon ka pita ttharaya haai us paramashevar ke samhane jis par us ne vishvas kiya aur jo mare huon ko jilata haai, aur jo baten haain hee nahee, un ka nam aeesa leta haai, ki mano ve haain.
us ne nirasha men bhee asha rakhkar vishvas kiya, isaliye ki us vachan ke anusar ki tera vansh aeesa hoga vah bahut see jatiyon ka pita ho.
aur vah jo aek sau varsha ka tha, apane mare huae se shareer aur sara ke garbh kee maree hui kee see dasha janakar bhee vishvas men nirbal n hua.
aur n avishvasee hokar parameshvar kee pratigyaa par sandeh kiya, par vishvas men draddh hokar parameshvar kee mahima kee.
aur nishchay jana, ki jis bat kee us ne pratigyaa kee haai, vah use pooree karane ko bhee samarthee haai.
is kara, yah usake liye dhaarmikata gina gaya.
aur yah vachan, ki vishvas usake liye dhaarmikata giya gaya, n keval usee ke liye likha gaya.
baran hamare liye bhee jin ke liye vishvas dhaaarmikata gina jaaega, arthata hamare liye jo us par vishvas karate haai, jis ne hamare prabhu yeeshu ko mare huon men se jilaya.
vah hamare aparadhaen ke liye pakadvaya gaya, aur hamare dharmee ttharane ke liye jilaya bhee gaya..
se jab ham vishvas se dharmee tthare, to apane prabhu yeeshu maseeh ke dara parameshvar ke sath mel rakhen.
jis ke dara vishvas ke karan us anugrah tak, jis men ham bane haai, hamaree pahunch bhee hui, aur parameshvar kee maahima kee asha par ghamand karen.
keval yahee nahee, baran ham kleshaen men bhee ghamand kare, yahee janakar ki klesh se dhaeeraja.
or dhaeeraj se khra nikalana, aur khre nikalane se asha utpann hotee haai.
aur asha se lajja naheen hotee, kyonki pavitra atma jo hamen diya gaya haai usake dara parameshvar ka praem hamare man men dala gaya haai.
kyonaki jab ham nirbal hee the, to maseeh tteek samay par bhaktaiheenon ke liye mara.
kisee dharmee jan ke liye koi mare, yah to durlabh haai, parantu kya jane kisee bhle manushy ke liye koi marane ka bhee hiyav kare.
parantu parameshvar ham par apane praem kee bhlai is reeati se pragatt karata haai, ki jab ham papee hee the tabhee maseeh hamare liye mara.
so jab ki ham, ab usake lohoon ke karan dharmee tthare, to usake dara krodha se kyon n bachenge?
kyonaki baairee hone kee dasha men to usake putra kee mratyu ke dara hamara mel parameshvar ke sath hua fir mel ho jane par usake jeevan ke karan ham uddhar kyon n paaenge?
aur keval yahee nahee, parantu ham apane prabhu yeeshu maseeh ke dara jis ke dara hamara mel hua haai, parameshvar ke vishay men ghamand bhee karate haain..
isaliye jaaisa aek manushy ke dara pap jagat men aya, aur pap ke dara mratyu ai, aur is reeti se mratyu sab manushyon men faail gai, isaliye ki sab ne pap kiya.
kyonaki vyavastha ke diae jane tak pap jagat men to tha, parantu jahan vyavastha nahee, vahan pap gina naheen jata.
par jaaisa aparadha kee dasha haai, vaaisee anugrah ke baradan kee nahee, kyonki jab aek manushy ke aparadha se bahut log mare, to parameshvar ka anugrah aur usaka jo dan aek manushy ke, arthata yeeshu maseeh ke anugrah se hua bahutere lagon par avashy hee adhaikai se hua.
aur jaaisa aek manushy ke pap karane ka fal hua, vaaisa hee dan kee dasha nahee, kyonki aek hee ke karan dand kee agyaa ka faaisala hu, parantu bahutere aparadhaen se aeesa baradan utpann hua, ki log dharmee tthare.
kyonaki jab aek manushy ke aparadha ke karan mratyu ne us aek hee ke dara rajy kiya, to jo log anugrah aur dharmaroomee baradan bahutayat se pate haain ve aek manushy ke, arthata yeeshu maseeh ke dara avashy hee anant jeevan men rajy karenge.
isaliye jaaisa aek aparadha sab manushyon ke liye dand kee agyaa ka karan hua, vesa hee aek dharma ka kam bhee sab manushyon ke liye jeevan ke nimitt dharmee ttharaae jane ka karan hua.
kyonaki jaaisa aek manushy ke agyaa n manane se bahut log papee tthare, vaaise hee aek manushy ke agyaa manane se bahut log dharmee ttharenge.
ki jaaisa pap ne mratyu faailate huae rajy kiya, vaaisa hee hamare prabhu yeeshu maseeh ke dara anugrah bhee anant jeevan ke liye dharmee ttharate huae rajy kare..
so ham kya kahen? kya ham pap karate rahe, ki anugrah bahut ho?
kadapi nahee, ham jab pap ke liye mar gaae to fir age ko us men kyonkar jeevan binaaen?
kya tum naheen janate, ki ham jitanon ne maseeh yeeshu ka bapaatisma liya to us kee mratyu ka bapatisma liya?
so us mratyu ka bapatisma pane se ham usake sath gade gaa, taki jaaise maseeh pita kee maahima ke dara mare huon men se jilaya gaya, vaaise hee ham bhee naae jeevan kee see chal chalen.
kyonaki yadi ham us kee mratyu kee samanata men usake sath jutt gaae haai, to nishchay usake jee uttne kee samanata men bhee jutt jaaenge.
kyonaki ham janate haain ki hamara purana manushyatv usake sath kroos par chaddhaya gaya, taaki pap ka shareer vyarth ho jaa, taaki ham age ko pap ke dasatv men n rahen.
kyonaki jo mar gaya, vah pap se choottkar dharmee tthara.
so yaadi ham maseeh ke sath mar gaa, to hamara vishvas yah haai, ki usake sath jeeaenge bhee.
kyonaki yah janate haai, ki maseeh mare huon men se jee uttkar fir marane ka nahee, us par fir mratyu kee prabhuta naheen hone kee.
kyonaki vah jo mar gaya to pap ke liye aek hee bar mar gaya parantu jo jeeavit haai, to parameshvar ke liye jeeavit haai.
aeese hee tum bhee apane ap ko pap ke liye to mara, parantu parameshvar ke liye maseeh yeeshu men jeeavit samajho.
isaliye pap tumhare maranahar shareer men rajy n kare, ki tum us kee lalasaon ke adhaeen raho.
aur n apane ango ko adharma ke hathaiyar hone ke liye pap ko saunpo, par apane ap ko mare huon men se jee utta hua janakar paramashevar ko saunpo, aur apane ango ko dharma ke hathaiyar hone ke liye parameshvar ko saunpo.
aur tum par pap kee prabhuta n hogee, kyonaki tum vyavastha ke adhaeen naheen baran anugrah ke adhaeen ho..
to kya hua? kya ham isaaliye pap kare, ki ham vyavastha ke adhaeen naheen baran anugrah ke adhaeen haain? kadaapi naheen.
kya tum naheen janate, ki jis kee agyaa manane ke liye tum apane ap ko dason kee nain saunp dete ho, usee ke das ho: aur jis kee manate ho, chahe pap ke, jis ka ant mratyu haai, chahe agyaa manane ke, jis ka ant dhaarmikata haai?
parantu paramashevar ka dhanyavad ho, ki tum jo pap ke das the taubhee man se us upadesh ke mananevale ho gaa, jis ke sanche men ddhale gaae the.
aur pap se chhudaae jakar dharma ke das ho gaae.
maain tumharee shaareearik durbalata ke karan manushyon kee reeati par kahata hoo, jaaise tum ne apane ango ko kukarma ke liye ashuuddhta aur kukarma ke das karake saunpa tha, vaaise hee ab apane angon ko paavitrata ke liye dharma ke das karake saunp do.
jab tum pap ke das the, to dharma kee or se svatantra the.
so jin baton se ab tum laajjait hote ho, un se us samay tum kya fal pate the?
kyonaki un ka ant to mratyu haai parantu ab pap se svatantra hokar aur parameshvar ke das banakar tum ko fal mila jis se pavitrata praapt hotee haai, aur usaka ant anant jeevan haai.
kyonaki pap kee majadooree to mratyu haai, parantu parameshvar ka baradan hamare prabhu yeeshu maseeh men anant jeevan haai..
kyonaki vivaahita sree vyavastha ke anusar apane paati ke jeete jee us se bandhaee haai, parantu yaadi pati mar jaa, to vah pati kee vyavastha se choott gai.
so yaadi pati ke jeete jee vah kisee doosare puroosh kee ho jaa, to vyaabhaichaarinee kahalaaegee, parantu yaadi pati mar jaa, to vah us vyavastha se choott gai, yahan tak ki yadi kisee doosare puroosh kee ho jaa, taubhee vyabhaichaarinee n ttharegee.
so he mere bhaiyo, tum bhee maseeh kee deh ke dara vyavastha ke liye mare huae ban gaa, ki us doosare ke ho jao, jo mare huon men se jee utta: taaki ham parameshvar ke liye fal laaen.
kyonaki jab ham shaareerik the, to papon kee aabhailashaayen jo vyavastha ke dara thee, mratyu ka fal utpann karane ke liye hamare angon men kam karatee theen.
to ham kya kahen? kya vyavastha pap haai? kadaapi naheen! baran bina vyavastha ke maain pap ko naheen paahichanata: vyavastha yaadi n kahatee, ki lalach mat kar to maain lalach ko n janata.
parantu pap ne avasar pakar agyaa ke dara mujh men sab prakar ka lalach utpann kiya, kyonaki bina vyavastha ke pap murda haai.
maain to vyavastha bina paahile jeeavit tha, parantu jab agyaa ai, to pap jee gaya, aur maain mar gaya.
aur vahee agyaa jo jeevan ke liye thee mere liye mratyu ka karan ttharee.
kyonaki pap ne avasar pakar agyaa ke dara mujhai bahakaya, aur usee ke dara mujhe mar bhee dala.
isaliye vyavastha paavitra haai, aur agyaa bhee tteek aur achchhee haai.
to kya vah jo achchhee thee, mere liye mratyu ttharee? kadapi naheen! parantu pap us achchhee vastu ke dara mere liye mratyu ka utpann karanevala hua ki usaka pap hona pragatt ho, aur agyaa ke dara pap bahut hee papamay tthare.
kyonaki ham janate haain ki vyavastha to atmaik haai, parantu maain shareerik aur pap ke hath bika hua hoon.
aur jo maain karata hoo, us ko naheen janata, kyonaki jo maain chahata hoo, vah naheen kiya karata, parantu jis se mujhe gharana atee haai, vahee karata hoon.
aur yaadi, jo maain naheen chahata vahee karata hoo, to maain man leta hoo, ki vyavastha bhlee haai.
to aeesee dasha men usaka karanevala maain nahee, baran pap haai, jo mujh men basa hua haai.
kyonaki maain janata hoo, ki mujh men arthata mere shareer men koi achchhee vastu vas naheen karatee, ichchha to mujh men haai, parantu bhle kam mujh se ban naheen padte.
kyonaki jis achchhe kam kee maain ichchha karata hoo, vah to naheen karata, parantu jis burai kee ichchha naheen karata vahee kiya karata hoon.
parantu yadi maain vahee karata hoo, jis kee ichchha naheen karata, to usaka karanevala maain n raha, parantu pap jo mujh men basa hua haai.
so maain yah vyavastha pata hoo, ki jab bhlai karane kee ichchha karata hoo, to burai mere pas atee haai.
kyonaki maain bheetaree manushyatv se to parameshvar kee vyavastha se bahut prasann rahata hoon.
parantu mujhe apane ango men doosare prakar kee vyavastha dikhai padtee haai, jo meree buaddh ikee vyavastha se ladtee haai, aur mujhe pap kee vyavastha ke bandhan men dalatee haai jo mere angon men haai.
maain kaaisa abhaga manushy hoon! mujhe is mratyu kee deh se kaun chhudaaega?
maain apane prabhu yeeshu maseeh ke dara parameshvar ka dhanyavad karata hoon: nidan maain ap buddh ise to parameshvar kee vyavastha ka, parantu shareer se pap kee vyavastha ka sevan karata hoon..
so ab jo maseeh yeeshu men haai, un par dand kee agyaa naheen: kyonki ve shareer ke anusar naheen baran atma ke anusar chalate haain.
kyonaki jeevan kee atma kee vyavastha ne maseeh yeeshu men mujhe pap kee, aur mratyu kee vyavastha se svatantra kar diya.
kyonaki jo kam vyavastha shareer ke karan durbal hokar n kar sakee, us ko parameshvar ne kiya, arthata apane hee putra ko papamay shareer kee samanata me, aur pap ke balidan hone ke liye bhejakar, shareer men pap par dand kee agyaa dee.
isaliye ki vyavastha kee vidhai ham men jo shareer ke anusar naheen baran atma ke anusar chalate haai, pooree kee jaae.
kyonaki shareearik vyaaktai shareer kee baton par man lagate haain parantu adhyaatmaik atma kee baton par man lagate haain.
shareer par man lagana to mratyu haai, parantu atma par man lagana jeevan aur shaantai haai.
aur jo shaareearik dasha men haai, ve parameshvar ko prasann naheen kar sakate.
parantu jab ki parameshvar ka atma tum men basata haai, to tum shaareearik dasha men nahee, parantu aatmaik dasha men ho. yaadi kisee men maseeh ka atma naheen to vah usaka jan naheen.
aur yaadi maseeh tum men haai, to deh pap ke karan maree hui haai parantu atma dharma ke karan jeeavit haai.
so he bhaiyo, ham shareer ke karjadan nahee, taki shareer ke anusar din katten.
