kyonaki likha haai, ki he banj, too jo naheen janatee anand kar, tu jis ko peedaaen naheen uttteen gala kholakar jay jayakar kar, kyonki tyagee hui kee santan suhagin kee santan se bhee adhaik haai.
he bhaiyo, ham isahak kee nain pratigyaa kee santan haain.
aur jaaisa us samay shareer ke anusar janma hua atma ke anusar janme huae ko satata tha, vaaisa hee ab bhee hota haai.
parantu pavitra shaasr kya kahata haai? dasee aur usake putra ko nikal de, kyonaki dasee ka putra svatantra sree ke putra ke sath uttraadhaikaree naheen hoga.
isaliye he bhaiyo, ham dasee ke naheen parantu svatantra sree ke santan haain.
maseeh ne svatantrata ke liye hamen svatantra kiya haai so isee men sthiar raho, aur dasatv ke jooae men fir se n juto..
dekho, maain paulus tum se kahata hoo, ki yadi khtana karaoge, to maseeh se tumhen kuchh labh n hoga.
fir bhee maain har aek khtana karanevale ko jataae deta hoo, ki use saree vyavastha mananee padegee.
tum jo vyavastha ke dara dharmee ttharana chahate ho, maseeh se alag aur anugrah se gir gaae ho.
kyonaki atma ke kara, ham vishvas se, asha kee hui dhaaarmikata kee batt johate haain.
aur maseeh yeeshu men n khtana, n khtanarahit kuchh kam ka haai, parantu keval vishvas ka jo praem ke dara prabhav karata haai.
tum to bhlee bhanati daud rahe the, ab kis ne tumhen rok diya, ki saty ko n mano.
aeesee seekh tumhare bulanevale kee or se naheen.
thoda sa khmeer sare goondho huae atte ko khmeer kar dalata haai.
maain prabhu par tumhare vishay men bhrosa rakhtah hoo, ki tumhara koi doosara vichar n hoga parantu jo tumhen ghabara deta haai, vah koi kyon n ho dand paaega.
parantu he bhaiyo, yadi maain ab tak khtana ka prachar karata hoo, to kyon ab tak sataya jata hoon fir to kroos kee ttokar jatee rahee.
bhla hota, ki jo tumhen danvadol karate haai, ve katt dale jate!
he bhaiyo, tum svatantra hone ke liye bulaae gaae ho parantu aeesa n ho, ki yah svatantrata shaareearik kamon ke liye avasar bane, baran praem se aek doosare ke das bano.
par yaadi tum aek doosare ko dant se kattte aur faad khate ho, to chaukas raho, ki aek doosare ka satyanash n kar do..
par maain kahata hoo, atma ke anusar chalo, to tum shareer kee lalasa kisee reeati se pooree n karoge.
aur yaadi tum atma ke chalaae chalate ho to vyavastha ke adhaeen n rahe.
shareer ke kam to pragatt haai, arthata vyaabhaichar, gande kam, luchapana.
mooti pooja, ttona, baair, jhgada, ishrya, krodha, virodha, foot, vidharma.
dah, malavalapan, leelakreeda, aur in ke aeese aur aur kam haai, in ke vishay men maain tum ko pahile se kah deta hoon jaaisa paahile kah bhee chuka hoo, ki aeese aeese kam karanevale parameshvar ke rajy ke vaaris n honge.
par atma ka fal praem, anand, mel, dhaeeraj,
aur krapa, bhalai, vishvas, namrata, aur sanyam haain aeese aeese kamon ke virodha men koi vyavastha naheen.
aur jo maseeh yeeshu ke haai, unhon ne shareer ko us kee lalasaon aur abhailashaen samet kroos par chaddha diya haai..
yaadi ham atma ke dara jeeavit haai, to atma ke anusar chalen bhee.
ham ghamandee hokar n aek doosare ko chhede, aur n aee doosare se dah karen.
he bhaiyo, yadi koi manushy kisee aparadha men pakada jaa, to tum jo aatmaik jo, namrata ke sath aeese ko sanbhalo, aur apanee bhee chaukasee rakho, ki tum bhee pareeksha men n pado.
tum aek doosare ke bhar uttao, aur is prakar maseeh kee vyavastha ko pooree karo.
kyonaki yadi koi kuchh n hone par bhee apane ap ko kuchh samajhta haai, to apane ap ko dhaekha deta haai.
par har aek apane hee kam ko janch le, aur tak doosare ke vishay men naheen parantu apane hee vishay men usako ghamand karane ka avasar hoga.
kyonaki har aek vyaaktai apana hee bojh uttaaega..
jo vachan kee shaiksha pata haai, vah sab achchhee vastuon men sikhanevale ko bhagee kare.
dhaekha n khao, parameshvar tttthon men naheen udaya jata, kyonaki manushy jo kuchh bota haai, vahee kattega.
kyonaki jo apane shareer ke liye bota haai, vah shareer ke dara vinash kee kattnee kattega aur jo atma ke liye bota haai, vah atma ke dara anant jeevan kee kattnee kattega.
ham bhle kam karane men hiyav n chhode, kyonki yadi ham ddheele n hane, to tteek samay par kattnee kattenge.
isaliye jahan tak avasar mile ham sab ke sath bhlai karen vishosh karake vishvasee bhaiyon ke sath..
dekho, maain ne kaaise bade bade aksharon men tum ko apane hath se likha haai.
jitane log shareearik dikhv chahate haain ve tumhare khtana karavane ke liye dabav dete haai, keval isaliye ki ve maseeh ke kroos ke karan sataae n jaaen.
kyonaki khtana karanevale ap to, vyavastha par naheen chalate, par tumhara khtana karana isaaliye chahate haai, ki tumharee shaareearik dasha par ghamand karen.
par aeesa n ho, ki maain aur kisee bat ka ghamand karoo, keval hamare prabhu yeeshu maseeh ke kroos ka jis ke dara sansar meree drashtti men aur maain sansar kee draashtti men kroos par chaddhaya gaya hoon.
kyonaki n khtana, aur n khtanaraahit kuchh haai, parantu nai sraashtti.
aur jitane is niyam par chalenge un par, aur parameshvar ke israael par, shaantai aur daya hotee rahe..
age ko koi mujhe dukh n de, kyonaki maain yeeshu ke dagon ko apanee deh men liye firata hoon..
paulus kee or se jo parameshvar kee ichchha se yeeshu maseeh ka praearit haai, un paavitra aur maseeh yeeshu men vishvasee logon ke nam jo ifisus men haain..
hamare pita parameshvar aur prabhu yeeshu maseeh kee or se tumhen anugrah aur shaaantai milatee rahe..
hamare prabhu yeeshu maseeh ke parameshvar aur pita ka dhanyavad ho, ki us ne hamen maseeh men svargeey sthanon men sab prakar kee ashaeesh dee haai.
aur apanee ichchha kee sumati ke anusar hamen apane liye paahile se ttharaya, ki yeeshu maseeh ke dara ham usake lepalak putra ho,
ki usake us anugrah kee mahima kee stuti ho, jise us ne hamen us pyare men sent ment diya.
ham ko us men usake lohoo ke dara chhuttkara, arthata aparadhaen kee kshama, usake us anugrah ke dhan ke anusar mila haai.
jise us ne sare gyaan aur samajh saahit ham par bahutayat se kiya.
ki us ne apanee ichchha ka bhed us sumaati ke anusar hamen bataya jise us ne apane ap men ttan liya tha.
ki samayon ke poore hone ka aeesa prabandha ho ki jo kuchh svarga men haai, aur jo kuchh prathvee par haai, sab kuchh vah maseeh men aekatra kare.
usee men jis men ham bhee usee kee manasa se jo apanee ichchha ke mat ke anusar sab kuchh karata haai, pahile se ttharaae jakar meeras bane.
ki ham jinhon ne pahile se maseeh par asha rakhee thee, us kee mahima kee stuti ke karan hon.
aur usee men tum par bhee jab tum ne saty ka vachan suna, jo tumhare uddhar ka susamachar haai, aur jis par tum ne vishvas kiya, praatigyaa kiae huae paavitra atma kee chhap lagee.
vah usake mol liae huon ke chhuttkare ke liye hamaree meeras ka bayana haai, ki us kee mahima kee stuti ho..
is kara, maain bhee us vishvas ka samachar sunakar jo tum logon men prabhu yeeshu par haai aur sab paavitra logon par pragatt haai.
tumhare liye dhanyavad karana naheen chhodta, aur apanee praarthnaon men tumhen smaran kiya karata hoon.
ki hamare prabhu yeeshu maseeh ka parameshvar jo maahima ka pita haai, tumhen apanee pahachan me, gyaan aur prakash ka atma de.
aur tumhare man kee ankhen jyotirmay hon ki tum jan lo ki usake bulane se kaaisee asha hotee haai, aur paavitra logon men us kee meeras kee maahima ka dhan kaaisa haai.
aur us kee samarth hamaree or jo vishvas karate haai, kitanee mahan haai, s kee shaaktai ke prabhav ke us kayrya ke anusara.
jo us ne maseeh ke vishay men kiya, ki us ko mare huon men se jilakar svargeey sthanon men apanee dahinee ora.
sab prakar kee pradhaanata, aur adhaikar, aur samarth, aur prabhuta ke, aur har aek nam ke upar, jo n keval is lok me, par anevale lok men bhee liya jaaega, baaittaya.
aur sab kuchh usake panvon tale kar diya: aur use sab vastuon par shairomanai ttharakar kaleesiya ko de diya.
yah usakee deh haai, aur usee kee paaripoornta haai, jo sab men sab kuchh poorn karata haai..
aur us ne tumhen bhee jilaya, jo apane aparadhaen aur papon ke karan mare huae the.
jin men tum pahile is sansar kee reeati par, aur akash ke aadhaikar ke haakim arthata us atma ke anusar chalate the, jo ab bhee agyaa n mananevalon men kayrya karata haai.
in men ham bhee sab ke sab paahile apane shareer kee lalasaon men din bitate the, aur shareer, aur man kee manasaaen pooree karate the, aur aur logon ke saman svabhav hee se krodha kee santan the.
parantu parameshvar ne jo daya ka dhanee haai apane us bade praem ke kara, jis se us ne ham se praem kiya.
jab ham aparadhaen ke karan mare huae the, to hamen maseeh ke sath jilaya anugrah hee se tumhara uddhar hua haai.
aur maseeh yeeshu men usake sath uttaya, aur svargeey sthanon men usake sath baaittaya.
kyonaki vishvas ke dara anugrah hee se tumhara uddhar hua haai, aur yah tumharee or se nahee, baran parameshvar ka dan haai.
aur n karmon ke kara, aeesa n ho ki koi ghamand kare.
kyonaki ham usake banaae huae haain aur maseeh yeeshu men un bhle kamon ke liye sraje gaae jinhen parameshvar ne pahile se hamare karane ke liye taaiyar kiya..
is karan smaran karo, ki tum jo shaareerik reeti se anyajaati ho, aur jo log shareer men hath ke kiae huae khtane se khtanavale kahalate haai, ve tum ko khtanaraahit kahate haain.
par ab to maseeh yeeshu men tum jo paahile door the, maseeh ke lohoo ke dara nikatt ho gaae ho.
kyonaki vahee hamara mel haai, jis ne donon ko aek kar liya: aur alag karaneval deevar ko jo beech men thee, ddha diya.
aur apane shareer men baair arthata vah vyavastha jis kee agyaaaen vidhaiyon kee reeati par thee, mitta diya, ki donon se apane men aek naya manushy utpann karake mel kara de.
aur kroos par baair ko nash karake is ke dara danon ko aek deh banakar parameshvar se milaae.
aur us ne akar tumhen jo door the, aur unhen jo nikatt the, danon ko mela-milap ka susamachar sunaya.
kyonaki us hee ke dara ham danon kee aek atma men pita ke pas panhuch hotee haai.
isaliye tum ab videshaee aur musaafir naheen rahe, parantu paavitra logon ke sangee svadeshaee aur parameshvar ke gharane ke ho gaae.
aur praeriton aur bhavishyadvktaon kee nev par jis ke kone ka patthr maseeh yeeshu ap hee haai, banaae gaae ho.
jis men saree rachana aek sath milakar prabhu men aek paavitra maandair banatee jatee haai.
jis men tum bhee atma ke dara parameshvar ka nivasasthan hone ke liye aek sath banaae jate ho..
isee karan maain paulus jo tum anyajatiyon ke liye maseeh yeeshu ka bandhaua hoon
yaadi tum ne parameshvar ke us anugrah ke prabandha ka samachar suna ho, jo tumhare liye mujhe diya gaya.
arthata yah, ki vah bhed mujh par prakash ke dara pragatt hua, jaaisa maain pahile sankshop men likh chuka hoon.
jis se tum paddhkar jan sakate ho, ki maain maseeh ka vah bhed kahan tak samajhta hoon.
jo aur aur samayon men manushyon kee santanon ko aeesa naheen bataya gaya tha, jaaisa ki atma ke dara ab usake paavitra praariton aur bhavishyadvktaon par pragatt kiya gaya haain.
arthata yah, ki maseeh yeeshu men susamachar ke dara anyajateey lag meeras men sajhee, aur aek hee deh ke aur pratigyaa ke bhagee haain.
aur maain parameshvar ke anugrah ke us dan ke anusar, jo samarth ke prabhav ke anusar mujhe diya gaya, us susamachar ka sevak bana.
mujh par jo sab paavitra logon men se chhotte se bhee chhotta hoo, yah anugrah hua, ki maain anyajatiyon ko maseeh ke agamy dhan ka susamachar sunaun.
aur sab par yah bat prakashait karoo, ki us bhed ka prabandha kya haai, jo sab ke srajanahar parameshvar men adi se gupt tha.
taaki ab kaleeasiya ke dara, parameshvar ka nana prakar ka gyaan, un pradhaanon aur adhaikaariyon par, jo svargeey sthanon men haain pragatt kiya jaae.
us sanatan manasa ke anusar, jo us ne hamare prabhu maseeh yeeshu men kee theen.
jis men ham ko us par vishvas rakhne se hiyav aur bhrose se nikatt ane ka adhaikar haai.
isaliye maain binatee karata hoon ki jo klesh tumhare liye mujhe ho rahe haai, unake karan hiyav n chhodo, kyonki un men tumharee maahima haai..
maain isee karan us pita ke samhane ghauttne ttekata hoo,
ki vah apanee mahima ke dhan ke anusar tumhen yah dan de, ki tum usake atma se apane bheetaree manushyatv men samarth pakar balavant hote jao.
aur vishvas ke dara maseeh tumhare day men base ki tum praem men jad pakadkar aur nev dal kara.
sab paavitra lagon ke sath bhlee bhanti samajhne kee shaaktai pao ki usakee chaudai, aur lambai, aur unchai, aur gaharai kitanee haai.
aur maseeh ke us praem ko jan sako jo gyaan se pare haai, ki tum parameshvar kee saree bhrapooree tak paaripoorn ho jao..
ab jo aeesa samarthee haai, ki hamaree binatee aur samajh se kaheen adhaik kam kar sakata haai, us samarth ke anusar jo ham men kayrya karata haai,
so maain jo prabhu men bandhaua hoon tum se binatee karata hoo, ki jis bulahatt se tum bulaae gaae the, usake yogy chal chalo.
arthata saree deenata aur namrata sahit, aur dhaeeraj dharakar praem se aek doosare ko sah lo.
aur mel ke bandha men atma kee aekata rakhne ka yatn karo.
aek hee deh haai, aur aek hee atma jaaise tumhen jo bulaae gaae the apane bulaae jane se aek hee asha haai.
aek hee prabhu haai, aek hee vishvas, aek hee bapatisma.
aur sab ka aek hee parameshvar aur pita haai, jo sab ke upar aur sab ke madhy me, aur sab men haai.
par ham men se har aek ko maseeh ke dan ke pariman se anugrah mila haai.
isaliye vah kahata haai, ki vah unche par chaddha, aur bandhauvai ko bandha le gaya, aur manushyon ko dan diae.
usake chaddhne se, aur kya paya jata haai keval yah, ki vah prathvee kee nichalee jagahon men utara bhee tha.
aur jo utar gaya yah vahee haai jo sare akash ke upar chaddh bhee gaya, ki sab kuchh paripoorn kare.
aur us ne kitanon ko bhvishyadvkata niyukt karake, aur kitanon ko susamachar sunanevale niyukt karake, aur kitanon ko rakhvale aur upadeshak niyukt karake de diya.
jis se pavitra log siddh jo jaae, aur seva ka kam kiya jaa, aur maseeh kee deh unnati paae.
jab tak ki ham sab ke sab vishvas, aur parameshvar ke putra kee pahichan men aek n ho jaae, aur aek siddh manushy n ban jaaen aur maseeh ke poore deel daul tak n baddh jaaen.
taaki ham age ko balak n rahe, jo manushyon kee ttga-avidha aur chaturai se un ke bhram kee yuktaiyon kee, aur upadesh kee, har aek bayar se uchhale, aur idhara-udhar ghaumaae jate hon.
baran praem men sachchai se chalate hua, sab baton men us men ja sir haai, arthata maseeh men baddhte jaaen.
jis se saree deh har aek jod kee sahayata se aek sath milakar, aur aek sath gattkar us prabhav ke anusar jo har aek bhag ke pariman se us men hata haai, apane ap ko baddhatee haai, ki vah praem men unnaati karatee jaae..
isaliye maain yah kahata hoo, aur prabhu men jataae deta hoon ki jaaise anyajateey log apane man kee anarth kee reeti par chalate haai, tum ab se fir aeese n chalo.
kyonaki unakee buddh iandhoree ho gai haai aur us agyaanata ke karan jo un men haai aur unake man kee kattorata ke karan ve parameshvar ke jeevan se alag kiae huae haain.
aur ve sunn hokar, luchapan men lag gaae haai, ki sab prakar ke gande kam lalasa se kiya karen.
par tum ne maseeh kee aeesee shaiksha naheen pai.
baran tum ne sachamuch usee kee sunee, aur jaaisa yeeshu me saty haai, usee men sikhaae bhee gaae.
ki tum agale chalachalan ke purane manushyatv ko jo bhramanevalee abhailashaaon ke anusar bhrashtt hota jata haai, utar dalo.
aur apane man ke aatmaik svabhav men naye banate jao.
is karan joott bolana chhodkar har aek apane padosee se sach bole, kyonaki ham apas men aek doosare ke ang haain.
krodha to karo, par pap mat karo: soorya ast hone tak tumhara krodha n rahe.
aur n shautan ko avasar do.
choree karanevala fir choree n kare baran bhle kam karane men apane hathon se parishram kare isaaliye ki jise prayojan ho, use dene ko usake pas kuchh ho.
