yah bhed to bada haai par maain maseeh aur kaleeasiya ke vishay men kahata hoon.
par tum men se har aek apanee patnee se apane saman praem rakhe, aur patnee bhee apane pati ka bhy mane..
he balako, prabhu men apane mata pita ke agyaakaree bano, kyonaki yah uchit haai.
apanee mata aur pita ka adar kar yah paahilee agyaa haai, jis ke sath pratigyaa bhee haai.
ki tera bhla ho, aur too dharatee par bahut din jeevit rahe.
aur he bachchevalon apane bachchon ko ris n dilao parantu prabhu kee shaiksha, aur chitavanee dete hua, un ka palana-poshan karo..
he daso, jo log shareer ke anusar tumhare svamee haai, apane man kee seedhaai se drate, aur kanpate hua, jaaise maseeh kee, vaaise hee un kee bhee agyaa mano.
aur manushyon ko prasann karanevalon kee nai dikhane ke liye seva n karo, par maseeh ke dason kee nai man se parameshvar kee ichchha par chalo.
aur us seva ko manushyon kee nahee, parantu prabhu kee janakar suichchha se karo.
