aur tum usee men bhrapoor ho gaae ho jo saree pradhaanata aur adhaikar ka shairomanai haai.
usee men tumhara aeesa khtana hua haai, jo hath se naheen hota, arthata maseeh ka khtana, jis se shaareerik deh utar dee jatee haai.
aur us ne tumhen bhee, jo apane aparadhae, aur apane shareer kee khtanarahit dasha men murda the, use sath jilaya, aur hamare sab aparadhaen ko kshama kiya.
aur vidhaiyon ka vah lekh jo hamare nam par aur hamare virodha men tha mitta dala aur us ko kroos par keelon se jadkar samhane se hatta diya haai.
aur us ne pradhaanataon aur adhaikaron ko apane upar se utar kar un ka khullamakhulla tamasha banaya aur kroos ke karan un par jaya-jaya-kar kee ghvaani sunai ..
isaliye khane peene ya pabrba ya naae chand, ya sabton ke vishay men tumhara koi faaisala n kare.
kyonaki ye sab anevalee baton kee chhaya haai, par mool vastuaen maseeh kee haain.
koi manushy deenata aur svargadooton kee pooja karake tumhen dod ke pratifal se vanchit n kare. aeesa manushy dekhee hui baton men laga rahata haai aur apanee shaareearik samajh par vyarth foolata haai.
aur us shairomanai ko pakade naheen rahata jis se saree deh jodon aur patthon ke dara palana-poshan pakar aur aek sath gattkar, parameshvar kee or se baddhtee jatee haai..
jab ki tum maseeh ke sath sansar kee aadi shaiksha kee or se mar gaae ho, to fir un ke saman jo sansar men jeevan bitate haain manushyon kee agyaaon aur shaikshaanusar
aur aeesee vidhaiyon ke vash men kyon rahate ho? ki yah n choona, use n chakhna, aur use hath n lagana.
kyonaki ye sab vastu kam men late late nash ho jaaengee.
in vidhaiyon men apanee ichchha ke anusar gaddhee hui bhktai kee reeti, aur deenata, aur shaareerik yogabhyas ke bhav se gyaan ka nam to haai, parantu shaareearik lalasaon ko rokane men in ke kuchh bhee labh naheen hota..
so jab tum maseeh ke sath jilaae gaa, to svargeey vastuon kee khoj men raho, jahan maseeh vartaman haai aur parameshvar ke daahinee or baaitta haai.
prathvee par kee naheen parantu svargeey vastuon par dhyan lagao.
jab maseeh jo hamara jeevan haai, pragatt hoga, tab tum bhee usake sath mahima saahit pragatt kiae jaoge.
isaliye apane un ango ko mar dalo, jo prathvee par haai, arthata vyaabhaichar, ashuuddhta, dushkamana, buree lalasa aur lobh ko jo moorti pooja ke barabar haai.
in hee ke karan parameshvar ka prakop agyaa n mananevalon par padta haai.
aur tum bhee, jab in buraiyon men jeevan bitate the, to inheen ke anusar chalate the.
par ab tum bhee in sab ko arthata krodha, rosha, baairabhav, ninda, aur munh se gaaliyan bakana ye sab baten chhod do.
aek doosare se joott mat bolo kyonki tum ne purane manushyatv ko usake kamon samet utar dala haai.
aur naae manushyatv ko paahin liya haai jo apane srajanahar ke svaroop ke anusar gyaan praapt karane ke liye naya banata jata haai.
us men n to yoonanee raha, n yahoodee, n khtana, n khtanaraahit, n jangalee, n skootee, n das aur n svatantra: keval maseeh sab kuchh aur sab men haai..
isaliye parameshvar ke chune huon kee nain jo pavitra aur piry haai, badee karoona, aur bhlai, aur deenata, aur namrata, aur sahanashaeelata dhaaran karo.
aur yaadi kisee ko kisee par dosh dene ko koi karan ho, to aek doosare kee sah lo, aur aek doosare ke aparadha kshama karo: jaaise prabhu ne tumhare aparadha kshama kia, vaaise hee tum bhee karo.
aur in sab ke upar praem ko jo siddhta ka kattbaindha haai bandha lo.
aur maseeh kee shaaantai jis ke liye tum aek deh hokar bulaae bhee gaae ho, tumhare day men rajy kare, aur tum dhanyavadee bane raho.
maseeh ke vachan ko apane day men aadhaikai se basane do aur siddh gyaan sahit aek doosare ko sikhao, aur chitao, aur apane apane man men anugrah ke sath parameshvar ke liye bhjan aur stuatigan aur aatmaik geet gao.
aur vachan se ya kam se jo kuchh bhee karo sab prabhu yeeshu ke nam se karo, aur usake dara parameshvar pita ka dhanyavad karo..
he paatnaiyo, jesa prabhu men uchit haai, vaaisa hee apane apane paati ke adhaeen raho.
he balako, sab baton men apane apane mata-pita kee agyaa ka palan karo, kyonki prabhu is se prasann hota haai.
he bachchevalo, apane balakon ko tang n karo, n ho ki un ka sahas toott jaae.
he sevako, jo shareer ke anusar tumhare svamee haai, sab baton men un kee agyaa ka palan karo, manushyon ko prasann karanevalon kee nain dikhane ke liye nahee, parantu man kee seedhaai aur parameshvar ke bhy se.
aur jo kuchh tum karate ho, tan man se karo, yah samajhkar ki manushyon ke liye naheen parantu prabhu ke liye karate ho.
kyonaki tum janate ho ki tumhen is ke badale prabhu se meeras milegee: tum prabhu maseeh kee seva karate ho.
kyonaki jo bura karata haai, vah apanee burai ka fal paaega vahan kisee ka pakshapat naheen.
he svamiyo, apane apane dason ke sath nyay aur tteek tteek vyavahar karo, yah samajhkar ki svarga men tumhara bhee aek svamee haai..
praarthna men lage raho, aur dhanyavad ke sath us men jagrat raho.
aur is ke sath hee sath hamare liye bhee praarthna karate raho, ki parameshvar hamare liye vachan sunane ka aeesa dar khol de, ki ham maseeh ke us bhed ka varnn kar saken jis ke karan maain kaaid men hoon.
aur use aeesa pragatt karoo, jaaisa mujhe karana uchit haai.
avasar ko bahumooly samajhkar baharavalon ke sath buddhmaianee se bartav karo.
tumhara vachan sada anugrah sahit aur salona ho, ki tumhen har manushy ko uchit reeti se uttr dena a jaae.
piry bhai aur vishvasayogy sevak, tuakhaikus jo prabhu men mera sahakarmee haai, meree sab baten tumhen bata dega.
use maain ne isaliye tumhare pas bheja haai, ki tumhen hamaree dasha maloom ho jaae aur vah tumhare dayon ko shaaantai de.
aaristarkhus jo mere sath kaaidee haai, aur marakus jo baranaba ka bhai lagata haai. jis ke vishay men tum ne agyaa pai thee ki yadi vah tumhare pas aa, to us se achchhee tarah vyavahar karana.
aur yeeshu jo yoostus kahalata haai, tumhen namaskar kahate haain. khtana kiae huae logon men se keval ye hee parameshvar ke rajy ke liye mere sahakarmee aur meree shaaantai ka karan rahe haain.
ipaas jo tum men se haai, aur maseeh yeeshu ka das haai, tum se namaskar kahata haai aur sada tumhare liye praarthnaon men prayatn karata haai, taki tum siddh hokar poorn vishvas ke sath parameshvar kee ichchha par sthiar raho.
maain usaka gavah hoo, ki vah tumhare liye aur laudeekiya aur hiyarapualisavalon ke liye bada yatn karata rahata haai.
piry vaaidh looka aur demas ka tumhen namaskara.
laudeekiya ke bhaiyon ko aur tumafaas aur un ke ghar kee kaleesiya ko namaskar kahana.
aur jab yah patra tumhare yahan paddh liya jaa, to aeesa karana ki laudeeakiya kee kaleesiya men bhee paddha jaa, aur vah patra jo laudeeakiya se aae use tum bhee paddhna.
fir akhairppus se kahana ki jo seva prabhu men tujhe saunpee gai haai, use savadhaanee ke sath pooree karana..
mujh paulus ka apane hath se likha hua namaskara. meree janjeeron ko smaran rakhna tum par anugrah hota rahe. ameena..
paulus kee or se jo parameshvar ka das aur yeeshu maseeh ka praearit haai, parameshvar ke chune huae logon ke vishvas, aur bhaktai ke anusar haai.
us anant jeevan kee asha par, jis kee pratigyaa parameshvar ne jo joott bol naheen sakata sanatan se kee haai.
par tteek samay par apane vachan ko us prachar ke dara pragatt kiya, jo hamare uddharakarta parameshvar kee agyaa ke anusar mujhe saunpa gaya.
teetus ke nam jo vishvas kee sahabhagita ke vichar se mera sachcha putra haai: parameshvar pita aur hamare uddharakarta maseeh yeeshu se anugrah aur shaantai hotee rahe..
maain isaaliye tujhe krete men chhod aya tha, ki too shosh rahee hui baton ko sudhaare, aur meree agyaa ke anusar nagar nagar praacheenon ko niyukt kare.
kyonaki adhyaksha ko parameshvar ka bhndaree hone ke karan nirdosh hona chahiae n hattee, n krodhae, n piyakkad, n marapeett karanevala, aur n neech kamai ka lobhee.
par pahunai karanevala, bhlai ka chahanevala, sanyamee, nyayee, paavitra aur jiteandairy ho.
aur vishvasayogy vachan par jo dharmopadesh ke anusar haai, sthiar rahe ki khree shaiksha se upadesh de sake aur vivaadiyon ka munh bhee band kar sake..
kyonaki bahut se log nirankush bakavadee aur dhaekha denevale haain vishosh karake khtanavalon men se.
in ka munh band karana chaahiae: ye log neech kamai ke liye anuchit baten sikhakar ghar ke ghar bigad dete haain.
unheen men se ek jan ne jo unheen bhavishyadakta haai, kaha haai, ki kretee log sada jootte, dushtt pashu aur alasee petoo hote haain.
yah gavahee sach haai, isaaliye unahen kadai se chitaunee diya kar, ki ve vishvas men pakke ho jaaen.
aur ve yahoodiyon kee katha kahaaniyon aur un manushyon kee agyaaon par man n lagaae, jo saty se bhttk jate haain.
shuuddh logon ke liye sab vastu shuuddh haai, par ashuuddh aur avishvasiyon ke liye kuchh bhee shuuddh naheen: baran un kee buaddh iddh aur vivek donon ashuuddh haain.
ve kahate haai, ki ham parameshvar ko janate haain: par apane kamon se usaka inkar karate haai, kyonki ve gharaanait aur agyaa n mananevale haain: aur kisee achchhe kam ke yogy naheen..
par too aeesee baten kaha kar, jo khre upadesh ke yogy haain.
arthata booddhe puroosha, sachet aur gambheer aur sanyamee ho, aur un ka vishvas aur praem aur dhaeeraj pakka ho.
isee prakar booddhee striayon ka chal chalan paavitra logon sa ho, dosh laganevalee aur piyakkad naheen par achchhee baten sikhanevalee hon.
taaki ve javan striayon ko chitaunee detee rahe, ki apane patiyon aur bachchon se praeeti rakhen.
aur sanyamee, pativrata, ghar ka karabar karanevalee, bhlee aur apane apane paati ke adhaeen rahanevalee ho, taki parameshvar ke vachan kee ninda n hone paae.
sab baton men apane am ko bhle kamon ka namoona bana: tere upadesh men safaai, gambheerata.
aur aeesee khrai pai jaa, ki koi use bura n kah sake jis se virodhaee ham par koi dosh lagane kee gaun n pakar lajjait hon.
dason ko samajha, ki apane apane svamee ke adhaeen rahe, aur sab baton men unhen prasann rakhe, aur ulattkar javab n den.
choree chalakee n karen par sab prakar se poore vishvasee nikale, ki ve sab baton men hamare uddharakarta parameshvar ke upadesh kee shaebha den.
kyonaki parameshvar ka anugrah pragatt haai, jo sab manushyon ke uddhar ka karan haai.
aur hamen chitata haai, ki ham abhaktai aur sansarik abhailashaaon se man faerakar is yug men sanyam aur dharma aur bhaktai se jeevan bitaaen.
aur us dhany asha kee arthata apane mahan parameshvar aur uddharakarta yeeshu maseeh kee mahima ke pragatt hone kee batt johate rahen.
jis ne apane ap ko hamare liye de diya, ki hamen har prakar ke adharma se chhuda le, aur shuuddh karake apane liye aek aeesee jati bana le jo bhle bhle kamon men saragarma ho..
poore aadhaikar ke sath ye baten kah aur samajha aur sikhata raha: koi tujhe tuchd n janane paae..
logon ko sudhai dila, ki hakimon aur aadhaikaariyon ke adhaeen rahe, aur un kee agyaa mane, aur har aek achchhe kam ke liye taaiyar raha.
kisee ko badanam n karen jhgadaloo n hon: par komal svabhav ke ho, aur sab manushyon ke sath badee namrata ke sath rahen.
kyonaki ham bhee pahile, nirbuaddh,i aur agyaa n mananevale, aur bhram men pade hua, aur rang rang ke abhailashaaon aur sukhavilas ke dasatv men the, aur baairabhav, aur dah karane men jeevan nirvah karate the, aur gharanait the, aur aek doosare se baair rakhte the.
par jab hamare uddharakarta parameshvar kee krapa, aur manushyon par usakee praeeti pragatt hui.
jise us ne hamare uddharakarta yeeshu maseeh ke dara ham par adhaikai se undela.
jis se ham usake anugrah se dharmee ttharakar, anant jeevan kee asha ke anusar vaaris banen.
yah bat sach haai, aur maain chahata hoo, ki too in baton ke vishay men draddhta se bole isaaliye ki jinhon ne parameshvar kee prateeati kee haai, ve bhle-bhle kamon me lage rahate ka dhyan rakhen: ye baten bhlee, aur manushyon ke labh kee haain.
par moorkhta ke vivado, aur vanshaavaliyo, aur baair virodha, aur un jhgadon se, jo vyavastha ke vishay men hon bacha raha kyonaki ve nishfal aur vyarth haain.
kisee pakhndee ko aek do bar samajha bujhakar us se alag raha.
yah janakar ki aeesa manushy bhttk gaya haai, aur apane ap ko doshaee ttharakar pap karata rahata haai..
jab maain tere pas aratimas ya tuakhaikus ko bhejoo, to mere pas neekupualis ane ka yatn karana: kyonki maain ne vaheen jada kattne kee ttanee haai.
jenas vyavasthapak aur apullos ko yatn karake age pahuncha de, aur dek, ki unhen kisee vastu kee ghattee n hone paae.
aur hamare log bhee avashyakataon ko poora karane ke liye achchhe kamon men lage rahana seekhen taki nishfal n rahen..
mere sab sathaiyon ka tujhe namaskar aur jo vishvas ke karan ham se praeeti rakhte haai, un ko namaskara.. tum sab par anugrah hota rahe..
paulus kee or se jo maseeh yeeshu ka kaaidee haai, aur bhai timuathaiyus kee or se hamare piry sahakarmee filemona.
aur baahin afaafiya, aur hamare sathee yoddha arakhaippus aur filemon ke ghar kee kaleeasiya ke nama..
hamare pita parameshvar aur prabhu yeeshu maseeh kee or se anugrah aur shaaantai tumhen milatee rahe..
maain tere us praem aur vishvas kee charcha sunakar, jo sab pavitra logon ke sath aur prabhu yeeshu par haai.
sada parameshvar ka dhanyavad karata hoon aur apanee praarthnaon men bhee tujhe smaran karata hoon.
ki tera vishvas men sahabhagee hona tumharee saree bhlai kee pahichan men maseeh ke liye prabhavashaalee ho.
isaliye yadhypi mujhe maseeh men bada hiyav to haai, ki jo bat tteek haai, us kee agyaa tujhe doon.
taubhee mujh booddhe paulus ko jo ab maseeh yeeshu ke liye kaaidee hoo, yah aur bhee bhla jan pada ki praem se binatee karoon.
maain apane bachche uneasimus ke liye jo mujh se meree kaaid men janma haai tujh se binatee karata hoon.
vah to paahile tere kuchh kam ka n tha, par ab tere aur mere donon ke bade kam ka haai.
usee ko arthata jo mere day ka ttukada haai, maain ne use tere pas lautta diya haai.
use maain apane hee pas rakhna chahata tha ki teree or se is kaaid men jo susamachar ke karan haai, meree seva kare.
par maain ne teree ichchha bina kuchh bhee karana n chaha ki teree yah krapa dabav se naheen par anand se ho.
kyonaki kya jane vah tujh se kuchh din tak ke liye isee karan alag hua ki sadaaiv tere nikatt rahe.
parantu ab se das kee nai nahee, baran das se bhee uttm, arthata bhai ke saman hare jo shareer men bhee aur vishosh kar prabhu men bhee mera piry ho.
so yaadi too mujhe sahabhagee samajhta haai, to use is prakar grahan kar jaaise mujhe.
aur yaadi us ne teree kuchh haani kee haai, ya us par tera kuchh ata haai, to mere nam par likh le.
maain paulus apane hath se likhta hoo, ki maain ap bhr doonga aur ham ke kahane kee kuchh avashyakata nahee, ki mera karja jo tujh par haai vah too hee haai.
maain tere agyaakaree hone ka bhrosa rakhkar, tujhe likhta hoon aur yah janata hoo, ki jo kuchh maain kahata hoo, too us se kaheen baddhkar karega.
aur yah bhee, ki mere liye utarane kee jagah taaiyar rakh mujhe asha haai, ki tumharee praarthnaon ke dara maain tumhen de diya jaunga..
ipaas jo maseeh yeeshu men mere sath kaaidee haai.
aur marakus aur aaristarkhus aur demas aur looka jo mere sahakarmee haai in ka tujhe namaskara..
hamare prabhu yeeshu maseeh ka anugrah tumharee atma par hota rahe. ameena..
kyonaki vyavastha jis men anevalee achchhee vastuon ka pratibimb haai, par un ka asalee svaroop nahee, isaaliye un aek hee prakar ke balidanon ke dara, jo praati varsha achook chaddhaae jate haai, pas anevalon ko kadapi siddh naheen kar sakateen.
naheen to un ka chaddhana band kyon n ho jata? isaliye ki jab seva karanevale aek hee bar shuuddh ho jate, to fir un ka vivek unhen papee n ttharata.
parantu un ke dara praati varsha papon ka smaran hua karata haai.
kyonaki anahona haai, ki baailon aur bakaron ka lohoo papon ko door kare.
isee karan vah jagat men ane samay kahata haai, ki balidan aur bhentt too ne n chahee, par mere liye aek deh taaiyar kiya.
homa-baliyon aur papa-baliyon se too prasann naheen hua.
tab maain ne kaha, dek, maain a gaya hoo, paavitra shasr men mere vishay men likha hua haai taaki he parameshvar teree ichchha pooree karoon.
upar to vah kahata haai, ki n too ne baalidan aur bhentt aur homa-baaliyon aur papa-baliyon ko chaha, aur n un se prasann hua yadhyapi ye balidan to vyavastha ke anusar chaddhaae jate haain.
fir yah bhee kahata haai, ki dek, maain a gaya hoo, taki teree ichchha pooree karoon nidan vah paahile ko utta deta haai, taki doosare ko niyukt kare.
usee ichchha se ham yeeshu maseeh kee deh ke ek hee bar balidan chaddhaae jane ke dara paavitra kiae gaae haain.
aur har aek yajak to khde hokar praati din seva karata haai, aur aek hee prakar ke baalidan ko jo papon ko kabhee bhee door naheen kar sakate bar bar chaddhata haai.
par yah vyaktai to papon ke badale aek hee baalidan sarvada ke liye chaddhakar parameshvar ke dahine ja baaitta.
kyonaki us ne aek hee chaddhave ke dara unhen jo pavitra kiae jate haai, sarvada ke liye siddh kar diya haai.
aur paavitra atma bhee hamen yahee gavahee deta haai kyonaki us ne pahile kaha tha
ki prabhu kahata haai ki jo vacha maain un dinon ke bad un se bandhoonga vah yah haai ki maain apanee vyavasthaon ko unake day par likoonga aur maain un ke vivek men daloonga.
fir vah yah kahata haai, ki maain un ke papon ko, aur un ke adharma ke kamon ko fir kabhee smaran n karoonga.
aur jab in kee kshama ho gai haai, to fir pap ka balidan naheen raha..
so he bhaiyo, jab ki hamen yeeshu ke lohoo ke dara us naae aur jeevate marga se paavitra sthan men pravesh karane ka hiyav ho gaya haai.
jo us ne parade arthata apane shareer men se hokar, hamare liye aabhaishok kiya haai,
aur isaliye ki hamara aeesa mahan yajak haai, jo parameshvar ke ghar ka adhaikaree haai.
to ao ham sachche man, aur poore vishvas ke sat, aur vivek ko dosh door karane ke liye day par chhdikav lekar, aur deh ko shuuddh jal se dhaulavakar parameshvar ke sameep jaaen.
aur apanee asha ke angeekar ko draddhta se thamen rahen kyonki jis ne pratigyaa kiya haai, vah sachcha haai.
aur praem, aur bhle kamon men uskane ke liye aek doosare kee chinta kiya karen.
kyonaki sachchai kee paahichan praapt karane ke bad yaadi ham jan boojhkar pap karate rahe, to papon ke liye fir koi baalidan bakee naheen.
ha, dand ka aek bhyanak batt johana aur ag ka jvalan bakee haai jo virodhaiyon ko bhsm kar dega.
jab ki moosa kee vyavastha ka n mananevala do ya teen janon kee gavahee par, bina daya ke mar dala jata haai.
to soch lo ki vah kitane aur bhee bharee dand ke yogy ttharega, jis ne parameshvar ke putra ko panvon se raunda, aur vacha ke lohoo ko jis ke dara vah paavitra ttharaya gaya tha, apavitra jana haai, aur anugrah kee atma ka apaman kiya.
kyonaki ham use janate haai, jis ne kaha, ki palatta lena mera kam haai, maain hee badala doonga: aur fir yah, ki prabhu apane logon ka nyay karega.
jeevate parameshvar ke hathon men padna bhyanak bat haai..
parantu un pahile dinon ko smaran karo, jin men tum jyoti pakar dukhon ke bade jhmele men sthiar rahe.
kuchh to yo, ki tum ninda, aur klesh sahate huae tamasha bane, aur kuchh yo, ki tum un ke sajhee huae jin kee durdasha kee jatee theen.
kyonaki tum kaaiadiyon ke dukh men bhee dukhee hua, aur apanee sanpati bhee anand se luttne dee yah janakar, ki tumhare pas aek aur bhee uttm aur sarvada ttharanevalee sanpaati haai.
so apana hiyav n chhodo kyonki usaka pratifal bada haai.
kyonaki tumhen dhaeeraj dharana avashy haai, taaki parameshvar kee ichchha ko pooree karake tum pratigyaa ka fal pao.
kyonaki ab bahut hee thoda samay rah gaya haai jab ki anevala aaega, aur der n karega.
aur mera dharmee jan vishvas se jeevit rahega, aur yadi vah peechhe hatt jaae to mera man us se prasann n hoga.
par ham hattnevale nahee, ki nash ho jaaen par vishvas karanevale haai, ki praanon ko bachaaen..
ab vishvas asha kee hui vastuon ka nishchay, aur man dekhee vastuon ka praman haai.
kyonaki isee ke vishay men praacheenon kee achchhee gavahee dee gain.
vishvas hee se ham jan jate haai, ki saree sraashtti kee rachana parameshvar ke vachan ke dara hui haai. yah nahee, ki jo kuchh dekhne men ata haai, vah dekhee hui vastuon se bana ho.
vishvas kee se habil ne kaain se uttm balidan parameshvar ke liye chaddhaya aur usee ke dara usake dharmee hone kee gavahee bhee dee gai: kyonaki parameshvar ne us kee bhentton ke vishay men gavahee dee aur usee ke dara vah marane par bhee ab tak baten karata haai.
aur vishvas bina use prasann karana anahona haai, kyonki parameshvar ke pas anevale ko vishvas karana chahia, ki vah haai aur apane khojanevalon ko praatifal deta haai.
vishvas hee se nooh ne un baton ke vishay men jo us samay dikhai n padtee thee, chitaunee pakar bhaktai ke sath apane gharane ke bachav ke liye jahaj banaya, aur usake dara us ne sansar ko doshaee ttharaya aur us dharma ka varis hua, jo vishvas se hota haai.
vishvas hee se ibraaheem jab bulaya gaya to agyaa manakar aeesee jagah nikal gaya jise meeras men lenevala tha, aur yah n janata tha, ki maain kidhar jata hoon taubhee nikal gaya.
vishvas hee se us ne pratigyaa kiae huae desh men jaaise paraae desh men paradeshaee rahakar isahak aur yakoob samet jo usake sath usee pratigyaa ke vaaris the, tambooon men vas kiya.
kyonaki vah us sthiar nevavale nagar kee batt johata tha, jis ka rachanevala aur bananevala parameshvar haai.
vishvas se sara ne ap booddhee hone par bhee garbh dhaaran karane kee samarth pai kyonaki us ne pratigyaa karanevale ko sachcha jana tha.
is karan aek hee jan se jo mara hua sa tha, akash ke taron aur samudra ke teer ke baloo kee nai, anaaginit vansh utpann hua..
ye sab vishvas hee kee dasha men mare aur unhon ne pratigyaa kee hui vastuen naheen pai par unhen door se dekhkar anandait huae aur man liya, ki ham prathvee par paradeshaee aur baharee haain.
jo aeesee aeesee baten kahate haai, ve pragatt karate haai, ki svadesh kee khoj men haain.
aur jis desh se ve nikal aae the, yaadi us kee sudhai karate to unhen lautt jane ka avasar tha.
vishvas hee se ibraaheem ne, parakhe jane ke samay me, isahak ko balidan chaddhaya, aur jis ne pratigyaaon ko sach mana tha.
aur jis se yah kaha gaya tha, ki isahak se tera vansh kahalaaega vah apane aekalaute ko chaddhane laga.
kyonaki us ne vichar kiya, ki parameshvar samarthee haai, ki mare huon men se jilaa, so unheen men se drashttant kee reeti par vah use fir mila.
vishvas hee se isahak ne yakoob aur aesav ko anevalee baton ke vishay me ashaeesh dee.
vishvas hee se yakoob ne marate samay yoosufa ke donon putraen men se aek aek ko ashaeesh dee, aur apanee lattee ke sire par sahara lekar dandvat kiya.
vishvas hee se yoosufa ne, jab vah marane par tha, to israael kee santan ke nikal jane kee charcha kee, aur apanee haaddiyon ke vishay men agyaa dee.
vishvas hee se moosa ke mata pita ne us ko, utpann hone ke bad teen maheene tak chhpai rakha kyonaki unhon ne dekha, ki balak sundar haai, aur ve raja kee agyaa se n dre.
vishvas hee se moosa ne sayana hokar firaun kee bettee ka putra kahalane se inkar kiya.
isaliye ki use pap men thode din ke sukh bhogane se parameshvar ke logon ke sath dukh bhogana aur uttm laga.
aur maseeh ke karan nindait hone ko misar ke bhndar se bada dhan samajha: kyonaki us kee ankhe fal pane kee or lagee theen.
vishvas hee se raja ke krodha se n drakar us ne misar ko chhod diya, kyonaki vah anadekhe ko manon dekhta hua draddh raha.
vishvas hee se us ne fasah aur lohoo chhdikane kee vidhai manee, ki pahilautton ka nash karanevala israaeliyon par hath n dale.
vishvas hee se ve lal samudra ke par aeese utar gaa, jaaise sookhee boomi par se aur jab misriyon ne vaaisa hee karana chaha, to sab oob mare.
vishvas hee se yareeho kee shaharapanah, jab sat din tak usaka chakkar laga chuke to vah gir padee.
vishvas hee se rahab veshya agyaa ne mananevalon ke sath nash naheen hui isaliye ki us ne bhediyon ko kushal se rakha tha.
ab aur kya kahoo? kyonki samay naheen raha, ki gidon ka, aur barak aur samasoon ka, aur yifatah ka, aur daud ka aur shaamuael ka, aur bhavishyadvktaon ka varnn karoon.
inhon ne vishvas hee ke dara rajy jeete dharma ke kam kiae praatigyaa kee hui vastuen praapt kee, sinhon ke munh band kiae.
ag hee jvala ko ttnda kiya talavar kee dhaar se bach nikale, nirbalata men balavant hue ladai men veer nikale videashaiyon kee faojon ko mar bhgaya.
striayon ne apane mare huon ko fir jeevate paya kitane to mar khate khate mar gaae aur chhuttkara n chaha isaaliye ki uttm punarootthan ke bhagee hon.
patthravah kiae gaae are se cheere gaae un kee pareeksha kee gai talavar se mare gaae ve kangalee men aur klesh men aur dukh bhogate huae bhedon aur bakariyon kee khalen oddhe hua, idhar udhar mare mare fire.
aur jangalo, aur pahado, aur gufaaon me, aur prathvee kee dararon men bhttkate fire.
sansar un ke yogay n tha: aur vishvas hee ke dara in sab ke vishay men achchhee gavahee dee gai, tobhee unhen praatigyaa kee hui vastu n milee.
kyonaki parameshvar ne hamare liye paahile se aek uttm bat ttharai, ki ve hamare bina siddhta ko n pahunche..
is karan jab ki gavahon ka aeesa bada badal ham ko ghore huae haai, to ao, har aek rokanevalee vastu, aur ulajhanevale pap ko door karake, vah daud jis meen hamen daudna haai, dhaeeraj se dauden.
aur vishvas ke karta aur siddh karanevale yeeshu kee or se takate rahen jis ne us anand ke liye jo usake age dhara tha, lajja kee kuchh chinta n karake, kroos ka dukh saha aur sinhasan par parameshvar ke daahine ja baaitta.
isaliye us par dhyan karo, jis ne apane virodha men papiyon ka itana vada-avivad sah liya ki tum nirash hokar hiyav n chhod do.
tum ne pap se ladte huae us se aeesee muttbhed naheen kee, ki tumhara lohoo baha ho.
aur tum us upadesh ko jo tum ko putraen kee nai diya jata haai, bool gaae ho, ki he mere putra, prabhu kee tadna ko halakee bat n jan, aur jab vah tujhe ghaudke to hiyav n chhod.
tum dukh ko tadna samajhkar sah lo: parameshvar tumhen putra janakar tumhare sath bartav karata haai, vah kaun sa putra haai, jis kee tadna pita naheen karata?
yaadi vah tadna jis ke bhagee sab hote haai, tumharee naheen hui, to tum putra nahee, par vyaabhaichar kee santan tthare!
fir jab ki hamare shaareerik pita bhee hamaree tadna kiya karate the, to kya atmaon ke pita ke aur bhee adhaeen n rahen jis se jeevit rahen.
ve to apanee apanee samajh ke anusar thode dinon ke liye tadna karate the, par yah to hamare labh ke liye karata haai, ki ham bhee us kee pavitrata ke bhagee ho jaaen.
aur vartaman men har prakar kee tadna anand kee nahee, par shaek hee kee bat dikhai padtee haai, taubhee jo us ko sahate sahate pakke ho gaae haai, peechhe unhen chaain ke sath dharma ka praatifal milata haai.
isaliye ddheele hathon aur nirbal ghauttnon ko seedho karo.
aur apane panvon ke liye seedho marga banao, ki langada bhttk n jaa, par bhla changa ho jaae..
sab se mel milap rakhne, aur us paavitrata ke khojee ho jis ke bina koi prabhu ko kadapi n dekhega.
aur dhyan se dekhte raho, aeesa n ho, ki koi parameshvar ke anugrah se vanchit rah jaa, ya koi kadvee jad foottkar kashtt de, aur usake dara bahut se log ashuuddh ho jaaen.
aeesa n ho, ki koi jan vyabhaicharee, ya aesav kee nai adharmee ho, jis n aek bar ke bhojan ke badale apane pahilautte hone ka pad bech dala.
tum janate to ho, ki bad ko jab us ne ashaeesh panee chahee, to ayogy gina gaya, aur ansoo baha bahakar khojane par bhee man firav ka avasar use n mila..
tum to us pahad ke pas jo chooa ja sakata tha aur ag se prajvaalit tha, aur kalee ghatta, aur andhora, aur andhaee ke pasa.
aur turahee kee dhvani, aur bolanevale ke aeese shabd ke pas naheen aa, jis ke sunanevalon ne binatee hee, ki ab ham se aur baten n kee jaaen.
kyonaki ve us agyaa ko n sah sake, ki yadi koi pashu bhee pahad ko chooa, to patthravah kiya jaae.
aur vah darshan aeesa dravana tha, ki moosa ne kaha maain bahut drata aur kanpata hoon.
par tum siyyon ke pahad ke pas, aur jeevate parameshvar ke nagar svargeey yarooshalem ke pasa.
aur lakhon svargadooton aur un paahilautton kee sadhaaran sabha aur kaleeasiya jin ke nam svarga men likhe huae haain: aur sab ke nyayee parameshvar ke pas, aur siddh kiae huae dhaarmiyon kee atmaon.
aur nai vacha ke madhyasth yeeshu, aur chhdikav ke us lohoo ke pas aae ho, jo haabil ke lohoo se uttm baten kahata haai.
savadhaan raho, aur us kahanevale se munh n faero, kyonki ve log jab prathvee par ke chitavanee denevale se munh modkar n bach sake, to ham svarga par se chitavanee karanevale se munh modkar kyonkar bach sakenge?
us samay to usake shabd ne prathvee ko hila diya par ab us ne yah praatigyaa kee haai, ki ek bar fir maain keval prathvee ko nahee, baran akash ko bhee hila doonga.
is karan ham is rajy ko pakar jo hilane ka nahee, us anugrah ko hath se n jane de, jis ke dara ham bhaktai, aur bhy sahit, parameshvar kee aeesee aradhana kar sakate haain jis se vah prasann hota haai.
kyonaki hamara parameshvar bhsm karanevalee ag haai..
bhaichare kee praeeati banee rahe.
pahunai karana n boolana, kyonki is ke dara kitanon ne anajane svargadooton kee pahunai kee haai.
kaaidiyon kee aeesee sudhai lo, ki mano un ke sath tum bhee kaaid ho aur jin ke sath bura bartav kiya jata haai, un kee bhee yah samajhkar sudhai liya karo, ki hamaree bhee deh haai.
vivah sab men adar kee bat samajhee jaa, aur bichhauna nishkalank rahe kyonaki parameshvar vyaabhaichaariyo, aur parasreegamiyon ka nyay karega.
tumhara svabhav lobhrahit ho, aur jo tumhare pas haai, usee par santosh kiya karo kyonki us ne ap hee kaha haai, ki maain tujhe kabhee n chhooonga, aur n kabhee tujhe tyagoonga.
isaliye ham bedhadk hokar kahate haai, ki prabhu, mera sahayak haai maain n droonga manushy mera kya kar sakata haai..
yeeshu maseeh kal aur aj aur yuganuyug aekasa haai.
nana prakar ke aur uparee upadeshaen se n bhramaae jao, kyonki man ka anugrah se draddh rahana bhla haai, n ki un khane kee vastuon se jin se kam rakhnevalon ko kuchh labh n hua.
hamaree aek aeesee vedee haai, jis par se khane ka aadhaikar un logon ko nahee, jo tamboo kee seva karate haain.
kyonaki jin pashuuon ka lohoo mahayajak papa-bali ke liye paavitra sthan men le jata haai, un kee deh chhavanee ke bahar jalai jatee haai.
isee kara, yeeshu ne bhee logon ko apane hee lohoo ke dara pavitra karane ke liye faattk ke bahar dukh uttaya.
so ao us kee ninda apane upar liae huae chhavanee ke bahar usake pas nikal chalen.
kyonaki yahan hamara koi sthiar rahanevala nagar nahee, baran ham aek anevale nagar kee khoj men haain.
isaliye ham usake dara stuatiroopee balidan, arthata un hotton ka fal jo usake nam ka angeekar karate haai, parameshvar ke liye sarvada chaddhaya karen.
par bhlai karana, aur udarata n boolo kyonaki parameshvar aeese baalidanon se prasann hota haai.
apane aguvon kee mano aur unake adhaeen raho, kyonaki ve un kee nai tumhare praanon ke liye jagate rahate, jinhen lekha dena padega, ki ve yah kam anand se kare, n ki ttndee sans le lekar, kyonaki is dasha men tumhen kuchh labh naheen.
hamare liye praarthna karate raho, kyonaki hamen bhrosa haai, ki hamara vivek shuuddh haai aur ham sab baton men achchhee chal chalana chahate haain.
aur is ke karane ke liye maain tumhen aur bhee samajhata hoo, ki maain shaeegha tumhare pas fir a sakoon..
ab shaantaidata parameshvar jo hamare prabhu yeeshu ko jo bhedon ka mahan rakhvala haai sanatan vacha ke lohoo ke gun se mare huon men se jilakar le aya.
tumhen har aek bhlee bat men siddh kare, jis se tum us kee ichchha pooree karo, aur jo kuchh us ko bhata haai, use yeeshu maseeh ke dara ham men utpann kare, jis kee badai yuganuyug hotee rahe. ameena..
he bhaiyon maain tum se binatee karata hoo, ki in upadesh kee baton ko sah leo kyonaki maain ne tumhen bahut sankshop men likha haai.
tum yah jan lo ki teemuathaiyus hamara bhai choott gaya haai aur yadi vah shaeegha a gaya, to maain usake sath tum se bhentt karoonga.
apane sab aguvon aur sab paavitra logon ko namaskar kaho. itaaliyavale tumhen namaskar kahate haain..
tum sab par anugrah hota rahe. ameena..
poorva yug men parameshvar ne bapadadon se thoda thoda karake aur bhanati bhanati se bhvishyadvktaon ke dara baten karake.
in dinon ke ant men ham se putra ke dara baten kee, jise us ne saree vastuon ka vaaris ttharaya aur usee ke dara us ne saree srashtti rachee haai.
vah us kee maahima ka prakasha, aur usake tatv kee chhap haai, aur sab vastuon ko apanee samarth ke vachan se sanbhalata haai: vah papon ko dhaekar unche sthanon par mahamaahiman ke daahine ja baaitta.
kyonaki svargadooton men se us ne kab kisee se kaha, ki too mera putra haai, aj too mujh se utpann hua? aur fir yah, ki maain usaka pita hoonga, aur vah mera putra hoga?
aur jab paahilautte ko jagat men fir lata haai, to kahata haai, ki parameshvar ke sab svargadoot use dandvat karen.
aur svargadooton ke vishay men yah kahata haai, ki vah apane dooton ko pavan, aur apane sevakon ko dhadhakatee ag banata haai.
parantu putra se kahata haai, ki he parameshvar tera sinhasan yuganuyug rahega: tere rajy ka rajadand nyay ka rajadand haai.
too ne dharma se praem aur adharma se baair rakha is karan parameshvar tere parameshvar ne tere sathaiyon se baddhkar harsharoopee tel se tujhe aabhaishok kiya.
aur yah ki, he prabhu, aadi men too ne prathvee kee nev dalee, aur svarga tere hathon kee kareegaree haai.
ve to nash ho jaaenge parantu too bana rahega: aur ve sab vasr kee nai purane ho jaaenge.
aur svargadooton men se un ne kis se kab kaha, ki too mere daahine baait, jab ki maain tere baaiariyon ko tere panvon ke neeche kee peeddhee n kar doon?
kya ve sab seva tthal karanevalee atmaaen naheen jo uddhar panevalon ke liye seva karane ko bhejee jatee haain?
is karan chahia, ki ham un baton par jo ham ne sunee haain aur bhee man lagaae, aeesa n ho ki bahakar un se door chale jaaen.
kyonaki jo vachan svargadooton ke dara kaha gaya tha jab vah sthiar raha or har aek aparadha aur agyaa n manane ka tteek tteek badala mila.
to ham log aeese bade uddhar se nishchaint rahakar kyonkar bach sakate haain? jis kee charcha paahile paahil prabhu ke dara hui, aur sunanevalon ke dara hamen nishchay hua.
aur sath hee parameshvar bhee apanee ichchha ke anusar chinho, aur adabhut kamo, aur nana prakar ke samarth ke kamo, aur pavitra atma ke varadanon ke banttne ke dara is kee gavahee deta raha..
us ne us anevale jagat ko jis kee charcha ham kar rahe haai, svargadooton ke adhaeen n kiya.
baran kisee ne kahee, yah gavahee dee haai, ki manushy kya haai, ki too us kee sudhai leta haai? ya manushy ka putra kya haai, ki too us par drashtti karata haai?
too ne use svargadooton se kuchh hee kam kiya too ne us par maahima aur adar ka mukutt rakha aur use apane hathon ke kamon par aadhaikar diya.
too ne sab kuchh usake panvon ke neeche kar diya: isaliye jab ki us ne sab kuchh usake adhaeen kar diya, to us ne kuchh bhee rakh n chhoda, jo usake adhaeen n ho : par ham ab tak sab kuchh usake adhaeen naheen dekhte.
par ham ko yeeshu jo svargadooton se kuchh hee kam kiya gaya tha, mratyu ka dukh uttane ke karan maahima aur adar ka mukutt paahine huae dekhte haain taki parameshvar ke anugrah se har aek manushy ke liye mratyu ka svad chakhe.
kyonaki jis ke liye sab kuchh haai, aur jis ke dara sab kuchh haai, use yahee achchha laga ki jab vah bahut se putraen ko maahima men pahunchaa, to un ke uddhar ke karta ko dukh uttane ke dara siddh kare.
kyonaki pavitra karanevala aur jo paavitra kiae jate haai, sab aek hee mool se haain: isee karan vah unhen bhai kahane se naheen lajata.
par kahata haai, ki maain tera nam apane bhaiyon ko sunaunga, sabha ke beech men maain tera bhjan gaunga.
aur fir yah, ki maain us par bhrosa rakoonga aur fir yah ki dek, maain un ladkon saahit jise parameshvar ne mujhe diae.
isaliye jab ki ladke mans aur lohoo ke bhagee haai, to vah ap bhee un ke saman un ka sahabhagee ho gaya taaki mratyu ke dara use jise mratyu par shaaktai milee thee, arthata shautan ko nikamma kar de.
aur jitane mratyu ke bhy ke mare jeevan bhr dasatv men fanse the, unhen chhuda le.
kyonaki vah to svargadooton ko naheen baran ibraaheem ke vansh ko sanbhalata haai.
is karan usako chahiae tha, ki sab baton men apane bhaiyon ke saman bane jis se vah un baton men jo parameshvar se sambandha rakhtee haai, aek dayalu aur vishvasayogy mahayajak bane taaki logon ke papon ke liye praayaashchaitt kare.
kyonaki jab us ne pareeksha kee dasha men dukh uttaya, to vah un kee bhee sahayata kar sakata haai, jin kee pareeksha hotee haai..
so he paavitra bhaiyon tum jo svargeey bulahatt men bhagee ho, us praearit aur mahayajak yeeshu par jise ham angeekar karate haain dhyan karo.
jo apane niyukt karanevale ke liye vishvasayogy tha, jaaisa moosa bhee usake sare ghar men tha.
kyonaki har aek ghar ka koi n koi bananevala hota haai, par jis ne sab kuchh banaya vah parameshvar haai.
moosa to usake sare ghar men sevak kee nai vishvasayogy raha, ki jin baton ka varnn honevala tha, un kee gavahee de.
par maseeh putra kee nai usake ghar ka adhaikaree haai, aur usaka ghar ham haai, yadi ham sahas par, aur apanee asha ke ghamand par ant tak draddhta se sthiar rahen.
so jaaisa paavitra atma kahata haai, ki yadi aj tum usaka shabd suno.
to apane man ko kattor n karo, jaaisa ki krodha dilane ke samay aur pareeksha ke din jangal men kiya tha.
jahan tumhare bapadadon ne mujhe janchakar parakha aur chalees varsha tak mere kam dekhe.
tab maain ne krodha men akar shapath khai, ki ve mere vishraam men pravesh karane n paaenge.
he bhaiyo, chaukas raho, ki tum men aeesa bura aur avishvasee n man ho, jo jeevate parameshvar se door hatt jaae.
baran jis din tak aj ka din kaha jata haai, har din aek doosare ko samajhate raho, aeesa n ho, ki tum men se koi jan pap ke chhl men akar kattor ho jaae.
kyonaki ham maseeh ke bhagee huae haai, yadi ham apane prathm bhrose par ant tak draddhta se sthiar rahen.
jaaisa kaha jata haai, ki yadi aj tum usaka shabd suno, to apane manon ko kattor n karo, jaaisa ki krodha dilane ke samay kiya tha.
bhla kin logon ne sunakar krodha dilaya? kya un sab ne naheen jo moosa ke dara misar se nikale the?
aur vah chalees varsha tak kin logon se rootta raha? kya unheen se nahee, jinhon ne pap kiya, aur un kee lothen jangal men padee raheen?
aur us ne kin se shapath khai, ki tum mere vishraam men pravesh karane n paoge: keval un se jinhon ne agyaa n manee?
so ham dekhte haai, ki ve avishvas ke karan pravesh n kar sake..
isaliye jab ki usake vishraam men pravesh karane kee praatigyaa ab tak haai, to hamen drana chaahiae aeesa ne ho, ki tum men se koi jang us se rahit jan pade.
kyonaki hamen unheen kee nai susamachar sunaya gaya haai, par sune huae vachan se unhen kuchh loth n hua kyonki sunanevalon ke man men vishvas ke sath naheen baaitta.
aur ham jinhon ne vishvas kiya haai, us vishraam men pravesh karate haain jaaisa us ne kaha, ki maain ne apane krodha men shapath khai, ki ve mere vishraam men pravesh karane n paaenge, yadhyapi jagat kee utpaati ke samay se use kam ho chuke the.
kyonaki sataven din ke vishay men us ne kaheen yon kaha haai, ki parameshvar ne sataven din apane sab kamon ko nipatta karake vishraam kiya.
aur is jagah fir yah kahata haai, ki ve mere vishraam men pravesh n karane paaenge.
to jab yah bat bakee haai ki kitane aur haain jo us vishraam men pravesh kare, aur jinhen usaka susamachar paahile sunaya gaya, unhon ne agyaa n manane ke karan us men pravesh n kiya.
to fir vah kisee vishosh din kee ttharakar itane din ke bad daud kee pustak men use aj ka din kahata haai, jaaise paahile kaha gaya, ki yadi aj tum usaka shabd suno, to apane manon ko kattor n karo.
aur yaadi yahoshoo unhen vishraam men pravesh kar leta, to usake bad doosare din kee charcha n hotee.
so jan lo ki parameshvar ke logon ke liye sabt ka vishraam bakee haai.
kyonaki jis ne usake vishraam men pravesh kiya haai, us ne bhee parameshvar kee nai apane kamon ko poora karake vishraam kiya haai.
so ham us vishraam men pravesh karane ka prayatn kare, aeesa n ho, ki koi jan un kee nai agyaa n manakar gir pade.
kyonaki parameshvar ka vachan jeeavit, aur prabal, aur har aek dodhaaree talavar se bhee bahut chokha haai, aur jeev, aur atma ko, aur gantt gant, aur goode goode ko alag karake, var par chhedata haai aur man kee bhavanaon aur vicharon ko janchata haai.
aur sraashtti kee koi vastu us se chhpaiee naheen haai baran jis se hamen kam haai, us kee ankhon ke samhane sab vastuaen khulee aur beparad haain..
so jab hamara aeesa bada mahayajak haai, jo svagorn se hokar gaya haai, arthata parameshvar ka putra yeeshuu to ao, ham apane angeekar ko draddhta se thamen rahe.
isaliye ao, ham anugrah ke sinhasan ke nikatt hiyav bandhakar chale, ki ham par daya ho, aur vah anugrah paae, jo avashyakata ke samay hamaree sahayata kare..
kyonaki har aek mahayajak manushyon men se liya jata haai, aur manushyon hee ke liye un baton ke vishay men jo parameshvar se sambandha rakhtee haai, ttharaya jata haai: ki bhentt aur pap baali chaddhaya kare.
aur vah agyaano, aur boole bhttkon ke sath narmee se vyavahar kar sakata haai isaaliye ki vah ap bhee nirbalata se ghaira haai.
aur isee liye use chahia, ki jaaise logon ke liye, vaaise hee apane liye bhee papa-bali chaddhaya kare.
aur yah adar ka pad koi apane ap se naheen leta, jab tak ki haroon kee nai parameshvar kee or se ttharaya n jaae.
vah doosaree jagah men bhee kahata haai, too malikisidak kee reeati par sada ke liye yajak haai.
us ne apanee deh men rahane ke dinon men unche shabd se pukar pukarakar, aur ansoo baha bahakar us se jo us ko mratyu se bacha sakata tha, praarthnaen aur binatee kee aur bhktai ke karan us kee sunee gai.
aur putra hone par bhee, us ne dukh utta uttakar agyaa mananee seekhee.
aur siddh banakar, apane sab agyaa mananevalon ke liye sada kal ke uddhar ka karan ho gaya.
aur use parameshvar kee or se malikisidak kee reeati par mahayajak ka pad mila..
is ke vishay men hamen bahut see baten kahanee haai, jin ka samajhna bhee kaattnai haai isaliye ki tum uncha sunane lage ho.
samay ke vichar se to tumhen guroo ho jana chahiae tha, taubhee kya yah avashyak haai, ki koi tumhen parameshvar ke vachanon kee aadi shaiksha fir se sikhaae? or aeese ho gaae ho, ki tumhen ann ke badale ab tak doodha hee chaahiae.
kyonaki doodha peenevale bachche ko to dharma ke vachan kee paahichan naheen hotee, kyonaki vah balak haai.
par ann sayanon ke liye haai, jin ke gyaaneandairy abhyas karate karate, bhle bure men bhed karane ke liye pakke ho gaae haain..
isaliye ao maseeh kee shaiksha kee arambh kee baton ko chhodkar, ham siddhta kee or baddhte jaae, aur mare huae kamon se man firane, aur parameshvar par vishvas karane.
aur bapatismon aur hath rakhne, aur mare huon ke jee uttne, aur antaim nyay kee shaikshaaroopee nev, fir se n dalen.
aur yaadi parameshvar chahe, to ham yaheen karenge.
kyonaki jinhon ne aek bar jyoti pai haai, jo svargeey varadan ka svad chakh chuke haain aur paavitra atma ke bhagee ho gaae haain.
aur parameshvar ke uttm vachan ka aur anevale yug kee samathorn ka svad chakh chuke haain.
yaadi ve bhttk jaaen to unhen man firav ke liye fir naya banana anhona haai kyonaki ve parameshvar ke putra ko apane liye fir kroos par chaddhate haain aur pragatt men. us par kalank lagate haain.
kyonaki jo boomi vashara ke panee ko jo us par bar bar padta haai, pee peekar jin logon ke liye vah jotee-boi jatee haai, un ke kam ka saga-pat upajatee haai, vah parameshvar se ashaeesh patee haai.
par yaadi vah jhadee aur unttkattare ugatee haai, to nikammee aur sraapit hone par haai, aur usaka ant jalaya jana haai..
par he piryo yadhyapi ham ye baten kahate haain taubhee tumhare vishay men ham is se achchha aur uddharavalee baton ka bhrosa karate haain.
kyonaki parameshvar anyayee nahee, ki tumhare kam, aur us praem ko bool jaa, jo tum ne unake nam ke liye is reeati se dikhaya, ki pavitra logon kee seva kee, aur kar rahe ho.
par ham bahut chahate haai, ki tum men se har aek jan ant tak pooree asha ke liye aeesa hee prayatn karata rahe.
taaki tum alasee n ho jao baran un ka anukaran karo, jo vishvas aur dhaeeraj ke dara praatigyaaon ke varis hote haain.
aur parameshvar ne ibraaheem ko pratigyaa dete samay jab ki shapath khane ke liye kisee ko apane se bada n paya, to apanee hee shapath khakar kaha.
ki maain sachamuch tujhe bahut ashaeesh doonga, aur teree santan ko baddhata jaunga.
aur is reeati se us ne dhaeeraj dharakar pratigyaa kee hui bat praapt kee.
isaliye jab parameshvar ne praatigyaa ke vaarison par aur bhee safa reeati se pragatt karana chaha, ki usakee manasa badal naheen sakatee to shapath ko beech men laya.
taaki do be-badal baton ke dara jin ke vishay men parameshvar ka jootta ttharana anhona haai, hamara draddhta se ddhaddhs bandha jaa, jo sharan lene ko isaaliye daude haai, ki us asha ko jo samhane rakhee hui haai praapt karen.
vah asha hamare praan ke liye aeesa langar haai jo sthiar aur draddh haai, aur parade ke bheetar tak pahunchata haai.
jahan yeeshu maalikisidak kee reeati par sada kal ka mahayajak banakar, hamare liye agua kee reeati par pravesh hua haai..
isee ko ibraaheem ne sab vastuon ka dasavan ansh bhee diya: yah paahile apane nam ke arth ke anusar, dharma ka raja haai.
jis ka n pita, n mata, n vanshaavalee haai, jis ke n dinon ka aadi haai aur n jeevan ka anat haai parantu parameshvar ke putra ke svaroop tthara..
ab is par dhyan karo ki yah kaaisa mahan tha jis ko kulapati ibraaheem ne achchhe se achchhe mal kee loott ka dasavan ansh diya.
levee kee santan men se jo yajak ka pad pate haai, unhen agyaa milee haai, ki logo, arthata apane bhaiyon se chahe, ve ibraaheem hee kee deh se kyon n janmen ha, vyavastha ke anusar dasavan ansh len.
par is ne, jo un kee vanshaavalee men ka bhee n tha ibraaheem se dasavan ansh liya aur jise praatigyaaaen milee thee use ashaeesh dee.
aur us men sandeh nahee, ki chhotta bade se ashaeesh pata haai.
aur yahan to maranahar manushy dasavan ansh lete haain par vahan vahee leta haai, jis kee gavahee dee jatee haai, ki vah jeevit haai.
to ham yah bhee kah sakate haai, ki levee ne bhee, jo dasavan ansh leta haai, ibraaheem ke dara dasavan ansh diya.
kyonaki jis samay maalikisidak ne usake pita se bhentt kee, us samay yah apane pita kee deh men tha..
tak yaadi leveey yajak pad ke dara siddh iho sakatee haai jis ke sahare se logon ko vyavastha milee thee to fir kya avashyakata thee, ki doosara yajak malikisidak kee reeati par khda ho, aur haroon kee reeati ka n kahalaae?
kyonaki jab yajak ka pad badala jata haai? to vyavastha ka bhee badalana avashy haai.
kyonaki jis ke vishay men ye baten kahee jatee haain ki vah doosare gotra ka haai, jis men se kisee ne vedee kee seva naheen kee.
to pragatt haai, ki hamara prabhu yahooda ke gotra men se uday hua haai aur is gotra ke vishay men moosa ne yajak pad kee kuchh charcha naheen kee.
or jab maalikisidak ke saman aek aur aeesa yajak utpann honevala tha.
jo shaareearik agyaa kee vyavastha ke anusar nahee, par avinashaee jeevan kee samarth ke anusar niyukt ho to hamara dava aur bhee spashttta se pragatt ho gaya.
kyonaki usake vishay men yah gavahee dee gai haai, ki too malikisidak kee reeati par yuganuyug yajak haai.
nidan, pahilee agyaa nirbala aur nishfal hone ke karan lop ho gai.
isaliye ki vyavastha ne kisee bat kee siddh inaheen ki aur usake sthan par aek aeesee uttm asha rakhee gai haai jis ke dara ham parameshvar ke sameep ja sakate haain.
aur isaliye ki maseeh kee niyuaktai bina shapath naheen hui.
kyonaki ve to bina shapath yajak ttharaae gaae par yah shapath ke sath us kee or se niyukt kiya gaya jis ne usake vishay men kaha, ki prabhu ne shapath khai, aur vah us se fir ne pachhtaaega, ki too yuganuyug yajak haai.
so yeeshu aek uttm vacha ka jamin tthara.
ve to bahut se yajak banate aa, is ka karan yah tha ki mratyu unhen rahane naheen detee thee.
par yah yuganuyug rahata haai is karan usaka yajak pad attl haai.
isee liye jo usake dara parameshvar ke pas ate haai, vah un ka poora poora uddhar kar sakata haai, kyonki vah un ke liye binatee karane ko sarvada jeevit haai..
so aeesa hee mahayajak hamare yogy tha, jo pavitra, aur nishkapatt aur nirmal, aur papiyon se alag, aur svarga se bhee uncha kiya hua ho.
kyonaki vyavastha to nirbal manushyon ko mahayajak niyukt karatee haai parantu us shapath ka vachan jo vyavastha ke bad khai gai, us putra ko niyukt karata haai jo yuganuyug ke liye siddh kiya gaya haai..
ab to baten ham kah rahe haai, un men se sab se badee bat yah haai, ki hamara aeesa mahayajak haai, jo svarga par mahamaahiman ke sinhasan ke daahine ja baaitta.
aur paavitra sthan aur us sachche tamboo ka sevak hua, jise kisee manushy ne nahee, baran prabhu ne khda kiya tha.
aur yaadi prathvee par hota to kabhee yajak n hota, isaliye ki vyavastha ke anusar bhentt chaddhanevale to haain.
jo svarga men kee vastuon ke pratiroop aur praatibimb kee seva karate haai, jaaise jab moosa tamboo banane par tha, to use yah chitavanee milee, ki dekh jo namoona tujhe pahad par dikhaya gaya tha, usake anusar sab kuchh banana.
par us ko un kee sevakai se baddhkar milee, kyonaki vah aur bhee uttm vacha ka madhyasth tthara, jo aur uttm pratigyaaon ke sahare bandhaee gai haai.
kyonaki yadi vah pahilee vacha nirdosh hotee, to doosaree ke liye avasar n ddoonddha jata.
par vah un par dosh lagakar kahata haai, ki prabhu kahata haai, dekho ve din ate haai, ki maain israael ke gharane ke sat, aur yahooda ke gharane ke sat, nai vacha bandhoonga.
yah us vacha ke saman n hogee, jo maain ne un ke bapadadon ke sath us samay bandhaee thee, jab maain un ka hath pakadkar unhen misar desh se nikal laya, kyonki ve meree vacha par sthiar n rahe, aur maain ne un kee sudhai n lee prabhu yahee kahata haai.
fir prabhu kahata haai, ki jo vacha maain un dinon ke bad israael ke gharane ke sath bandhoonga, vah yah haai, ki maain apanee vyavastha ko un ke manon men daloonga, aur use un ke day par likoonga, aur maain un ka parameshvar ttharoonga, aur ve mere log ttharenge.
aur har aek apane deshavale ko aur apane bhai ko yah shaiksha n dega, ki too prabhu ko paahichan kayonaki chhotte se bade tak sab mujhe jan lenge.
kyonaki maain un ke adharma ke vishay me dayavant hoonga, aur un ke papon ko fir smaran n karoonga.
nai vacha ke sthapan se us ne prathm vacha ko puranee ttharai, aur jo vastu puranee aur jeern jo jatee haai usaka mitt jana aanivarya haai..
nidan, us pahilee vacha men bhee seva ke niyam the aur aeesa pavitrasthan jo is jagat ka tha.
arthata aek tamboo banaya gaya, pahile tamboo men deevat, aur mej, aur bhentt kee rottyaian thee aur vah paavitrasthan kahalata haai.
aur doosare parade ke peechhe vah tamboo tha, jo param pavitrasthan kahalata haai.
us men sone kee dhoopadanee, aur charon or sone se maddha hua vacha ka sandook aur is men manna se bhra hua sone ka martaban aur haroon kee chhdee jis men fool fal a gaae the aur vacha kee pattyaian theen.
aur usake upar donon tejomay karoob the, jo praayashchaitt ke ddhkane par chhaya kiae huae the: inheen ka aek aek karake bakhan karane ka abhee avasar naheen haai.
jab ye vastuaen is reeati se taaiyar ho chukee, tak paahile tamboo men to yajak har samay pravesh karake seva ke kam nibahate haain
par doosare men keval mahayajak varsha bhr men aek hee bar jata haai aur bina lohoo liye naheen jata jise vah apane liye aur logon kee bool chook ke liye chaddhava chaddhata haai.
is se paavitra atma yahee dikhata haai, ki jab tak pahila tamboo khda haai, tab tak pavitrasthan ka marga pragatt naheen hua.
aur yah tamboo to vartaman samay ke liye aek drashttant haai jis men aeesee bhentt aur balidan chaddhaae jate haai, jin se aradhana karanevalon ke vivek siddh naheen ho sakate.
isaliye ki ve keval khane peene kee vastuo, aur bhanati bhanati ke snan vidhai ke adhaar par shaareerik niyam haai, jo sudhaar ke samay tak ke liye niyukt kiae gaae haain..
parantu jab maseeh anevalee achchhee achchhee vastuon ka mahayajak hokar aya, to us ne aur bhee bade aur siddh tamboo se hokar jo hath ka banaya hua nahee, arthata srashtti ka naheen.
aur bakaron aur bachhdon ke lohoo ke dara nahee, par apane hee lohoo ke dara aek hee bar pavitra sthan men pravesh kiya, aur anant chhuttkara praapt kiya.
kyonaki jab bakaron aur baailon ka lohoo aur kalor kee rakh apaavitra logon par chhdike jane se shareer kee shuuddhta ke liye paavitra karatee haai.
to maseeh ka lohoo jis ne apane ap ko sanatan atma ke dara parameshvar ke samhane nirdosh chaddhaya, tumhare vivek ko mare huae kamon se kyon n shuuddh karega, taaki tum jeevate parameshvar kee seva karo.
aur isee karan vah nai vacha ka madhyasth haai, taaki us mratyu ke dara jo paahilee vacha ke samay ke aparadhaen se chhuttkara pane ke liye hui haai, bulaae huae log pratigyaa ke anusar anant meeras ko praapt karen.
kyonaki jahan vacha bandhaee gai haai vahan vacha bandhanevale kee mratyu ka samajh lena bhee avashy haai.
isee liye paahilee vacha bhee bina lohoo ke naheen bandhaee gai.
kyonaki jab moosa sab logon ko vyavastha kee har aek agyaa suna chuka, to us ne bachhdon aur bakaron ka lohoo lekar, panee aur lal un, aur joofaa ke sat, us pustak par aur sab logon par chhdik diya.
aur isee reeti se us ne tamboo aur seva ke sare saman par lohoo chhdika.
aur vyavastha ke anusar praaya: sab vastuaen lohoo ke dara shuuddh kee jatee haain aur bina lohoo bahaae kshama naheen hotee..
isaliye avashy haai, ki svarga men kee vastuon ke praatiroop in ke dara shuuddh kiae jaaen par svarga men kee vastuaen ap in se uttm balidanon ke dara.
kyonaki maseeh ne us hath ke banaae huae pavitra sthan men jo sachche pavitra sthan ka namoona haai, pravesh naheen kiya, par svarga hee men pravesh kiya, taaki hamare liye ab parameshvar ke samhane dikhai de.
yah naheen ki vah apane ap ko bar bar chaddhaa, jaaisa ki mahayajak praati varsha doosare ka lohoo liye paavitrasthan men pravesh kiya karata haai.
naheen to jagat kee utpaati se lekar us ko bar bar dukh uttana padta par ab yug ke ant men vah aek bar pragatt hua haai, taaki apane hee balidan ke dara pap ko door kar de.
aur jaaise manushyon ke liye aek bar marana aur usake bad nyay ka hona niyukt haai.
vaaise hee maseeh bhee bahuton ke papon ko utta lene ke liye aek bar baalidan hua aur jo log us kee batt johate haai, un ke uddhar ke liye doosaree bar bina pap ke dikhai dega..
parameshvar ke aur prabhu yeeshu maseeh ke das yakoob kee or se un barahon gotraen ko jo tittr bittr hokar rahate haain namaskar pahunche..
he mere bhaiyo, jab tum nana prakar kee pareekshaaon men pado
to ise poore anand kee bat samajho, yah janakar, ki tumhare vishvas ke parakhe jane se dhaeeraj utpann hota haai.
par dhaeeraj ko apana poora kam karane do, ki tum poore aur siddh ho jao aur tum men kisee bat kee ghattee n rahe..
par yaadi tum men se kisee ko buaddh ikee ghattee ho, to parameshvar se mange, jo bina ulahana diae sab ko udarata se deta haai aur us ko dee jaaegee.
par vishvas se mange, aur kuchh sandeh n kare kyonki sandeh karanevala samudra kee lahar ke saman haai jo hava se bahatee aur uchhlatee haai.
aeesa manushy yah n samajhe, ki mujhe prabhu se kuchh milega.
vah vyaktai duchitta haai, aur apanee saree baton men chanchal haai..
deen bhai apane unche pad par ghamand kare.
aur dhanavan apanee neech dasha para: kyonaki vah ghaas ke fool kee nai jata rahega.
kyonaki soorya uday hote hee kadee dhoop padtee haai aur ghaas ko sukha detee haai, aur usaka fool jhd jata haai, aur us kee shaebha jatee rahatee haai usee prakar dhanavan bhee apane marga par chalate chalate dhool men mil jaaega.
dhany haai vah manushy, jo pareeksha men sthiar rahata haai kyonki vah khra nikalakar jeevan ka vah mukutt paaega, jis kee pratigyaa prabhu ne apane praem karanevalon ko dee haai.
jab kisee hee pareeksha ho, to vah yah n kahe, ki meree pareeksha parameshvar kee or se hotee haai kyonaki n to buree baton se parameshvar kee pareeksha ho sakatee haai, aur n vahee kisee kee pareeksha ap karata haai.
parantu pratyek vyaaktai apanee hee abhailasha men khainchakar, aur fansakar pareeksha men padta haai.
fir abhailasha garbhvatee hokar pap ko janata haai aur pap baddh jata haai to mratyu ko utpann karata haai.
he mere piry bhaiyo, dhaekha n khao.
kyonaki har aek achchha varadan aur har aek uttm dan upar hee se haai, aur jyotiyon ke pita kee or se milata haai, jis men n to koi parivartan ho sakata haai, or n adal badal ke karan us par chhaya padtee haai.
us ne apanee hee ichchha se hamen saty ke vachan ke dara utpann kiya, taaki ham us kee srashtti kee hui vastuon men se ek prakar ke prathm fal hon..
he mere piry bhaiyo, yah bat tum janate ho: isaliye har aek manushy sunane ke liye tatpar aur bolane men dhaeera aur krodha men dhaeema ho.
isaliye saree malinata aur baair bhav kee baddhtee ko door karake, us vachan ko namrata se grahan kar lo, jo day men boya gaya aur jo tumhare praanon ka uddhar kar sakata haai.
kyonaki jo koi vachan ka sunanevala ho, aur us par chalanevala n ho, to vah us manushy ke saman haai jo apana svabhavik munh darpan men dekhta haai.
isaliye ki vah apane ap ko dekhkar chala jata, aur turant bool jata haai ki maain kaaisa tha.
par jo vyaktai svatantrata kee siddh vyavastha par dhyan karata rahata haai, vah apane kam men isaaliye ashaeesh paaega ki sunakar nahee, par vaaisa hee kam karata haai.
yaadi koi apane ap ko bhkt samajhe, aur apanee jeebh par lagam n de, par apane day ko dhaekha de, to us kee bhaktai vyarth haai.
hamare parameshvar aur pita ke nikatt shuuddh aur nirmal bhaktai yah haai, ki anathon or vidhavaon ke klesh men un kee suadhai le, aur apane ap ko sansar se nishkalank rakhen..
he mere bhaiyo, hamare mahimayukt prabhu yeeshu maseeh ka vishvas tum men pakshapat ke sath n ho.
kyonaki yadi aek puroosh sone ke chhlle aur sundar vasr pahine huae tumharee sabha men aae aur aek kangal bhee maaile kuchaaile kapade paahine huae aae.
aur tum us sundar vasrvale ka munh dekhkar kaho ki too vahan achchhee jagah baaitt aur us kangal se kaho, ki too yahan khda rah, ya mere panv kee peeddhee ke pas baaitt.
to kya tum ne apas men bhed bhav n kiya aur kuavichar se nyay karanevale n tthare?
he mere piry bhaiyon suno kya parameshvar ne is jagat ke kangalon ko naheen chuna ki vishvas men dharmee, aur us rajy ke adhaikaree ho, jis kee pratigyaa us ne un se kee haai jo us se praem rakhte haain?
par tum ne us kangal ka apaman kiya: kya dhanee log tum par atyachar naheen karate aur kya ve hee tumhen kachahariyon men ghaseett ghaseett kar naheen le jate?
kya ve us uttm nam kee ninda naheen karate jis ke tum kahalaae jate ho?
taubhee yadi tum pavitra shaasr ke is vachan ke anusar, ki too apane padosee se apane saman praem rak, sachamuch us rajy vyavastha ko pooree karate ho, to achchha karate ho.
par yaadi tum pakshapat karate ho, to pap karate ho aur vyavastha tumhen aparadhaee ttharatee haai.
kyonaki jo koi saree vyavastha ka palan karata haai parantu aek hee bat men chook jaae to vah sab baton me doshaee tthara.
isaliye ki jis ne yah kaha, ki too vyaabhaichar n karana usee ne yah bhee kaha, ki too hatya n karana isaliye yaadi too ne vyaabhaichar to naheen kiya, par hatya kee taubhee too vyavastha ka ulanghan karane vala tthara.
tum un logon kee nai vachan bolo, aur kam bhee karo, jin ka nyay svatantrata kee vyavastha ke anusar hoga.
kyonaki jis ne daya naheen kee, usaka nyay bina daya ke hoga: daya nyay par jayavant hotee haai..
he mere bhaiyo, yadi koi kahe ki mujhe vishvas haai par vah karma n karata ho, to us se kya labh? kya aeesa vishvas kabhee usaka uddhar kar sakata haai?
yaadi koi bhai ya bahin nagen ughaade ho, aur unhen prati din bhojan kee ghattee ho.
aur tum men se koi un se kahe, kushal se jao, tum garam raho aur trapt raho par jo vastuaen deh ke liye avashyak haain vah unhen n de, to kya labh?
vaaise hee vishvas bhee, yadi karma saahit n ho to apane svabhav men mara hua haai.
baran koi kah sakata haai ki tujhe vishvas haai, aur maain karma karata hoon: too apana vishvas mujhe karma bina to dikha aur maain apana vishvas apane karmon ke dara tujhe dikhaunga.
tujhe vishvas haai ki aek hee parameshvar haai: too achchha karata haai: dushttatma bhee vishvas rakhte, aur thrathrate haain.
par he nikamme manushy kya too yah bhee naheen janata, ki karma bina vishvas vyarth haai?
jab hamare pita ibraaheem ne apane putra isahak ko vedee par chaddhaya, to kya vah karmo se dhaaarmik n tthara tha.
so too ne dekh liya ki vishvas ne us ke kamon ke sath milakar prabhav dala haai aur karmo se vishvas siddh hua.
aur paavitra shaasr ka yah vachan poora hua, ki ibraaheem ne parameshvar kee prateeti kee, aur yah usake liye dharma gina gaya, aur vah parameshvar ka mitra kahalaya.
nidan, jaaise deh atma bina maree hui haai vaaisa hee vishvas bhee karma bina mara hua haai..
he mere bhaiyo, tum men se bahut upadeshak n bane, kyonki janate ho, ki ham upadeshak aur bhee doshaee ttharenge.
isaliye ki ham sab bahut bar chook jate haain: jo koi vachan men naheen chookata, vahee to siddh manushy haai aur saree deh par bhee lagam laga sakata haai.
jab ham apane vash men karane ke liye ghaedon ke munh men lagam lagate haai, to ham un kee saree deh ko bhee faer sakate haain.
dekho, jahaj bhee, yadhypi aeese bade hote haai, aur prachand vayu se chalaae jate haai, taubhee aek chhottee see patavar ke dara manjhee kee ichchha ke anusar ghaumaae jate haain.
vaaise hee jeebh bhee aek chhotta sa ang haai aur badee badee deenge maratee haai: dekho, thodee see ag se kitane bade ban men ag lag jatee haai.
jeebh bhee aek ag haai: bhee hamare angon men adharma ka aek lok haai aur saree deh par kalank lagatee haai, aur bhvachakr men ag laga detee haai aur narak kund kee ag se jalatee rahatee haai.
kyonaki har prakar ke bana-pashu, pakshae, aur renganevale jantu aur jalachar to manushy jaati ke vash men ho sakate haain aur ho bhee gaae haain.
par jeebh ko manushyon men se koi vash men naheen kar sakata vah aek aeesee bala haai jo kabhee rookatee hee naheen vah praan nashak vish se bhree hui haai.
isee se ham prabhu aur pita kee stuti karate haain aur isee se manushyon ko jo parameshvar ke svaroop men utpann huae haain srap dete haain.
aek hee munh se dhanyavad aur srap donon nikalate haain.
he mere bhaiyo, aeesa nahee hona chaahiae.
kya sote ke aek hee munh se meetta aur khara jal donon nikalata haai? he mere bhaiyo, kya anjeer ke ped men jaaitoon, ya dakh kee lata men anjeer lag sakate haain? vaaise hee khare sote se meetta panee naheen nikal sakata..
tum men gyaanavan aur samajhdar kaun haai? jo aeesa ho vah apane kamon ko achchhe chalachalan se us namrata sahit pragatt kare jo gyaan se utpann hotee haai.
par yaadi tum apane apane man men kadvee dah aur virodha rakhte ho, to saty ke virodha men ghamand n karana, aur n to joott bolana.
yah gyaan vah nahee, jo upar se utarata haai baran sansaarik, aur shaareearik, aur shautanee haai.
isaliye ki jahan dah aur virodha hota haai, vahan bakheda aur har prakar ka dushkarma bhee hota haai.
par jo gyaan upar se ata haai vah paahile to paavitra hota haai fir milanasar, komal aur mradubhav aur daya, aur achchhe falon se lada hua aur pakshapat aur kapatt rahit hota haai.
aur milap karanevalon ke liye dhaarmikata ka fal mela-milap ke sath boya jata haai..
tum men ladaiyan aur jhgade kahan se a gaae? kya un sukh-avilason se naheen jo tumhare angon men ladte-bhaidte haain?
tum lalasa rakhte ho, aur tumhen milata naheen tum hatya aur dah karate ho, or kuchh praapt naheen kar sakate tum jhgadte aur ladte ho tumhen isaliye naheen milata, ki mangate naheen.
tum mangate ho aur pate nahee, isaaliye ki buree ichchha se mangate ho, taki apane bhog vilas men uda do.
he vyabhaichaarinaiyo, kya tum naheen janatee, ki sansar se mitrata karanee parameshvar se baair karana haai? so jo koi sansar ka mitra hona chahata haai, vah apane ap ko parameshvar ka baairee banata haai.
kya tum yah samajhte ho, ki pavitra shaasr vyarth kahata haai? jis atma ko us ne hamare bheetar basaya haai, kya vah aeesee lalasa karata haai, jis ka pratifal dah ho?
vah to aur bhee anugrah deta haai is karan yah likha haai, ki parameshvar abhaimaaniyon se virodha karata haai, par deenon par anugrah karata haai.
isaliye parameshvar ke adhaeen ho jao aur shautan ka samhana karo, to vah tumhare pas se bhag nikalega.
parameshvar ke nikatt ao, to vah bhee tumhare nikatt aaega: he paapiyo, apane hath shuuddh karo aur he duchitte logon apane day ko paavitra karo.
dukhee hoo, aur shaek kara, aur roo: tumharee hansee shaek se aur tumhara anand udasee se badal jaae.
prabhu ke samhane deen bano, to vah tumhen shairomanai banaaega.
tum jo yah kahate ho, ki aj ya kal ham kisee aur nagar men jakar vahan aek varsha bitaaenge, aur vyapar karake labh uttaaenge.
aur yah naheen janate ki kal kya hoga: sun to lo, tumhara jeevan haai hee kya? tum to mano bhap saman ho, jo thodee der dikhai detee haai, fir lop ho jatee haai.
is ke vipareet tumhen yah kahana chahia, ki yadi prabhu chahe to ham jeevit rahenge, aur yah ya vah kam bhee karenge.
par ab tum apanee deeng par ghamand karate ho aeesa sab ghamand bura hota haai.
isaliye jo koi bhlai karana janata haai aur naheen karata, usake liye yah pap haai..
he dhanavanon sun to lo tum apane anevale kleshaen par chillakar roo.
tumhara dhan bigad gaya aur tumhare vasren ko keede kha gaae.
tumhare sone-chandee men kai lag gai haai aur vah kai tum par gavahee degee, aur ag kee nai tumhara mans kha jaaegee: tum ne antaim yug men dhan battora haai.
dekho, jin majadooron ne tumhare khet katte, un kee vah majadooree jo tum ne dhaekha dekar rakh lee haai chilla rahee haai, aur lavanevalon kee dohai, senaon ke prabhu ke kanon tak pahunch gai haai.
tum prathvee par bhoga-avilas men lage rahe aur bada hee sukh bhoga tum ne is vadha ke din ke liye apane day ka palana-poshan karake motta taja kiya.
tum ne dharmee ko doshaee ttharakar mar dala vah tumhara samhana naheen karata..
so he bhaiyo, prabhu ke agaman tak dhaeeraj dharo, dekho, grahastha prathvee ke bahumooly fal kee asha rakhta hua prathm aur aantaim vashara hone tak dhaeeraj dharata haai.
tum bhee dhaeeraj dharo, aur apane day ko draddh karo, kyonaki prabhu ka shuubhagaman nikatt haai.
he bhaiyo, aek doosare par dosh n lagao taaki tum doshaee n ttharo, dekho, haakim dar par khda haai.
he bhaiyo, jin bhvishyadvktaon ne prabhu ke nam se baten kee, unhen dukh uttane aur dhaeeraj dharane ka aek adarsha samajho.
dekho, ham dhaeeraj dharanevalon ko dhany kahate haain: tum ne aeeyoob ke dhaeeraj ke vishay men to suna hee haai, aur prabhu kee or se jo usaka pratifal hua use bhee jan liya haai, jis se prabhu kee atyant karoona aur daya pragatt hotee haai.
par he mere bhaiyo, sab se shraeshtt bat yah haai, ki shapath n khana n svarga kee n prathvee kee, n kisee aur vastu kee, par tumharee batacheet han kee ha, aur naheen kee naheen ho, ki tum dand ke yogy n ttharo..
yaadi tum men koi dukhee ho to vah praarthna kare: yadi anaandait ho, to vah stuati ke bhjan gaae.
yaadi tum men koi rogee ho, to kaleeasiya ke praacheenon ko bulaa, aur ve prabhu ke nam se us par tel mal kar usake liye praarthna karen.
aur vishvas kee praarthna ke dara rogee bach jaaega aur prabhu us ko uttakar khda karega aur yaadi us ne pap bhee kiae ho, to un kee bhee kshama ho jaaegee.
isaliye tum apas men aek doosare ke samhane apane apane papon ko man lo aur aek doosare ke liye praarthna karo, jis ke change ho jao dharmee jan kee praarthna ke prabhav se bahut kuchh ho sakata haai.
aeliyyah bhee to hamare saman dukh-sukh bhogee manushy tha aur us ne gidgida kar praarthna kee ki menh n barase aur saddhe teen varsha tak boomi par menh naheen barasa.
fir us ne praarthna kee, to akash se vashara hui, aur boomi falavant hui..
he mere bhaiyo, yadi tum men koi saty ke marga se bhttk jaa, aur koi us ko faer laae.
to vah yah jan le, ki jo koi kisee bhttke huae papee ko faer laaega, vah aek praan ko mratyu se bachaaega, aur anek papon par parada dalega..
yahooda kee or se jo yeeshu maseeh ka das aur yakoob ka bhai haai, un bulaae huon ke nam jo parameshvar pita men piry aur yeeshu maseeh ke liye surakshiat haain..
daya aur shaaantai aur praem tumhen bahutayat se praapt hota rahe..
he piryo, jab maain tumhen us uddhar ke vishay men likhne men atyant paarishram se prayatn kar raha tha, jis men ham sab sahabhagee haain to maain ne tumhen yah samajhana avashyak jana ki us vishvas ke liye poora yatn karo jo paavitra logon ko aek hee bar saunpa gaya tha.
par yadhypi tum sab bat aek bar jan chuke ho, taubhee maain tumhen is bat kee suadhai dilana chahata hoo, ki prabhu ne aek kul ko misr desh se chhudane ke bad vishvas n lanevalon ko nash kar diya.
jis reeti se sadom aur amora aur un ke as pas ke nagar, jo in kee nai vyaabhaicharee ho gaae the aur paraye shareer ke peechhe lag gaae the ag ke anant dand men padkar drashttant tthare haain.
usee reeti se ye svapnadasharee bhee apane apane shareer ko ashuuddh karate, aur prabhuta ko tuchchh janate haain aur unche padavalon ko bura bhla kahate haain.
parantu pradhaan svargadoot meekail ne, jab shautan se moosa kee loth ke vishay men vada-avivad karata tha, to us ko bura bhla kahake dosh lagane ka sahas n kiya par yah kaha, ki prabhu tujhe dantte.
par ye log jin baton ko naheen janate, un ko bura bhla kahate haain par jin baton ko achetan pashuuon kee nai svabhav hee se janate haai, un men apane ap ko nash karate haain.
un par haya! ki ve kaain kee see chal chale, aur majadooree ke liye bilam kee nai bhrashtt ho gaae haain: aur korah kee nai virodha karake nash huae haain.
yah tumharee praem sabhaon men tumhare sath khate-peete, samudra men chhpaiee hui chattan sareekhe haai, aur bedhadk apana hee pett bhranevale rakhvale haain ve nirjal badal haain jinhen hava uda le jatee haai patajhd ke nishfal ped haai, jo do bar mar chuke haain aur jad se ukhd gaae haain.
ye samudra ke prachand hilakore haai, jo apanee lajja ka faen uchhalate haain: ye danvadol tare haai, jin ke liye sada kal tak ghaer andhakar rakha gaya haai.
aur hanok ne bhee jo adam se sataveen peeddhee men tha, in ke vishay men yah bhavishyadvvanee kee, ki dekho, prabhu apane lakhon paavitraen ke sath aya.
ki sab ka nyay kare, aur sab bhktaiheenon ko un ke abhaktai ke sab kamon ke vishay me, jo bhktaiheen paapiyon ne usake virodha men kahee haai, doshaee ttharaae.
ye to asantusht, kudkudanevale, aur apane abhailashaaon ke anusar chalanevale haain aur apane munh se ghamand kee baten bolate haain aur ve labh ke liye munh dekhee badai kiya karate haain..
par he piryo, tum un baton ko smaran rakho jo hamare prabhu yeeshu maseeh ke praerit pahile kah chuke haain.
ve tum se kaha karate the, ki pichhle dinon men aeese ttttha karanevale honge, jo apanee abhktai ke abhailashaaon ke anusar chalenge.
ye to ve haai, jo foott dalate haain ye shaareearik log haai, jin men atma naheen.
par he piryon tum apane ati pavitra vishvas men apanee unnati karate huae aur paavitra atma men praarthna karate hue.
apane ap ko parameshvar ke praem men banaae rakho aur anant jeevan ke liye hamare prabhu yeeshu maseeh kee daya kee asha dekhte raho.
aur un par jo shanka men haain daya karo.
aur bahuton ko ag men se jhpattkar nikalo, aur bahuton par bhy ke sath daya karo baran us vasr se bhee gharana karo jo shareer ke dara kalanakit ho gaya haai..
ab jo tumhen ttokar khane se bacha sakata haai, aur apanee maahima kee bhrapooree ke samhane magan aur nirdosh karake khda kar sakata haai.
us advait parameshvar hamare uddharakarta kee maahima, aur gaurav, aur parakram, aur adhaikar, hamare prabhu yeeshu maseeh ke dara jaaisa sanatan kal se haai, ab bhee ho aur yuganuyug rahe. ameena..
fir maain ne aek aur balee svargadoot ko badal oddhe huae svarga se utarate dekha, usake sir par meghadhanush tha: aur usaka munh soorya ka sa aur usake panv ag ke khnbhe ke se the.
aur usake hath men aek chhottee see khulee hui pustak thee us ne apana dahina panv samudra par, aur bayan prathvee par rakha.
aur aeese bade shabd se chillaya, jaaisa sinh garajata haai aur jab vah chillaya to garjan ke sat shabd sunai diae.
aur jab saton garjan ke shabd sunai de chuke, to maain likhne par tha, aur maain ne svarga se yah shabd suna, ki jo baten garjan ke un sat shabdon se sunee haai, unhen gupt rak, aur mat likh.
aur jis svargadoot ko maain ne samudra aur prathvee par khde dekh tha us ne apana daahina hath svarga kee or uttaya.
aur jo yuganuyug jeevata rahega, aur jis ne savarga ko aur jo kuchh us men haai, aur prathvee ko aur jo kuchh us par haai, aur samudra ko aur jo kuchh us men haai sraja usee kee shapath khakar kaha, ab to aur der n hogee.
baran sataven svargadoot ke shabd dene ke dinon men jab vah turahee foonkane par hoga, to parameshvar ka gupt manorath us susamachar ke anusar jo us ne apane das bhvishyadvktaon ko diya poora hoga.
aur jis shabd karanevale ko maain ne svarga se bolate suna tha, vah fir mere sath baten karane laga ki ja, jo svargadoot samudra aur prathvee par khda haai, usake hath men kee khulee huin pustak le le.
so maain vah chhottee pustak us svargadoot ke hath se lekar kha gaya, vah mere munh men madha see meettee to lagee, par jab maain use kha gaya, to mera pett kadva ho gaya.
tab mujh se yah kaha gaya, ki tujhe bahut se logo, aur jatiyo, aur bhashaao, aur rajaon par, fir bhvishyadvvanee karanee hogee..
aur maandair ke barah ka angan chhod de us mat nap, kyonaki vah anyajaatiyon ko diya gaya haai, aur ve paavitra nagar ko bayalees maheene tak raundengee.
aur maain apane do gavahon ko yah adhaikar doonga, ki ttatt oddhe huae aek hajar do sau satt din tak bhvishyadvvanee karen.
ye ve hee jaaitoon ke do ped aur do deevatt haain jo prathvee ke prabhu ke samhane khde rahate haain.
aur yaadi koi un ko haani pahunchana chahata haai, to un ke munh se ag nikalakar un ke baairiyon ko bhsm karatee haai, aur yaadi koi un ko haani pahunchana chahega, to avashy isee reeati se mar dala jaaega.
inhen aadhaikar haai, ki akash ko band kare, ki un kee bhvishyadvvanee ke dinon men menh n barase, aur unhen sab panee par adhaikar haai, ki use lohoo banaae, aur jab jab chahen tab tab prathvee par har prakar kee apaati laaen.
aur jab ve apanee gavahee de chukenge, to vah pashu jo athah kund men se nikalega, un se ladkar unhen jeetega aur unhen mar dalega.
aur un kee lothen us bade nagar ke chauk men padee rahengee, jo atmaik reeti se sadom aur misar kahalata haai, jahan un ka prabhu bhee kroos par chaddhaya gaya tha.
aur sab logo, aur kulo, aur bhashaao, aur jatiyon men se log un kee lothen saddhe teen din tak dekhte rahenge, aur un kee lothen kabra men rakhne ne denge.
aur prathvee ke rahanevale, un ke marane se anandait aur magan honge, aur aek doosare ke pas bhentt bhejenge, kyonki in donon bhavishyadvktaon ne prathvee ke rahanevalon ko sataya tha
aur saddhe teen din ke bad parameshvar kee or se jeevan kee atma un men paaitt gai aur ve apane panvon ke bal khde ho gaa, aur unake dekhnevalon par bada bhy chha gaya.
aur unhen svarga se aek bada shabd sunai diya, ki yahan upar ao yah sun ve badal par savar hokar apane baaiariyon ke dekhte dekhte svarga par chaddh gaae.
fir usee ghadee aek bada bhuindol hua, aur nagar ka dasavan ansh gir pada aur us bhuindol se sat hajar manushy mar gaae aur shosh dr gaa, aur svarga ke parameshvar kee mahima kee..
doosaree vipaati beet chukee, dekho, teesaree vipaati shaeegha anevalee haai..
aur jab sataven doot ne turahee foonkee, to svarga men is vishay ke bade bade shabd hone lage ki jagat ka rajy hamare prabhu ka, aur usake maseeh ka ho gaya.
aur vah yuganuyug rajy karega, aur chaubeeson praacheen jo parameshvar ke samhane apane apane sinhasan par baaitte the, munh ke bal girakar parameshvar ko dandvat karake.
yah kahane lage, ki he sarvashaktaiman prabhu parameshvar, jo haai, aur jo tha, ham tera dhanyavad karate haai, ki too ne apanee badee samrth kam men lakar rajy kiya haai.
aur anyajatiyon ne krodha kiya, aur tera prakop a pada aur vah samay a pahuncha haai, ki mare huon ka nyay kiya jaa, aur tere das bhvishyadvktaon aur pavitra logon ko aur un chhotte badon ko jo tere nam se drate haai, badala diya jaa, aur prathvee ke bigadnevale nash kiae jaaen..
aur parameshvar ka jo maandair svarga men haai, vah khola gaya, aur usake maandair men us kee vacha ka sandook dikhai diya, aur bijaaliyan aur shabd aur garjan aur bhuindol hua, aur bade bade ole pade..
fir svarga par aek bada chinh dikhai diya, arthata aek sree jo sooyrya oddhe huae thee, aur chand usake panvon tale tha, aur usake sir par barah taron ka mukutt tha.
aur vah garbhvatee hui, aur chillatee thee kayonaki prasav kee peeda use lagee thee aur vah bachcha janane kee peeda men thee.
aur aek aur chinh svarga par dikhai diya, aur dekho aek bada lal ajagar tha jis ke sat sir aur das seeng the, aur usake siron par sat rajamukutt the.
aur us kee poonchh ne akash ke taron kee aek tihai ko kheenchakar prathvee par dal diya, aur vah ajagar us sree se samhane jo jachcha thee, khda hua, ki jab vah bachcha jane to usake bachche ko nigal jaae.
aur vah betta janee jo lohe ka dand liae hua, sab jatiyon par rajy karane par tha, aur usaka bachcha aekaaek parameshvar ke pas, aur usake sinhasan ke pas uttakar pahuncha diya gaya.
aur vah sree us jangal ko bhag gai, jahan parameshvar kee or se usake liye aek jagah taaiyar kee gai thee, ki vahan vah aek hajar do sau satt din tak palee jaae..
fir svarga par ladai hui, meekail aur usake svargadoot ajagar se ladne ko nikale, aur ajagar or unake doot us se lade.
parantu prabal n hua, aur svarga men un ke liye fir jagah n rahee.
fir maain ne svarga par se yah bada shabd ate huae suna, ki ab hamare parameshvar ka uddhar, aur samarth, aur rajy, aur usake maseeh ka aadhaikar pragatt hua haai kyonki hamare bhaiyon par dosh laganevala, jo rat din hamare parameshvar ke samhane un par dosh lagaya karata tha, gira diya gaya.
aur ve memne ke lohoo ke kara, aur apanee gavahee ke vachan ke kara, us par jayavant hua, aur unhon ne apane praanon ko piry n jana, yahan tak ki mratyu bhee sah lee.
is kara, he svagor, aur un men ke rahanevalon magan ho he prathvee, aur samudra, tum par haya! kyonki shautan bade krodha ke sath tumhare pas utar aya haai kyonki janata haai, ki usaka thoda hee samay aur bakee haai..
aur us sree ko bade ukab ke do pankh diae gaa, ki sanp ke samhane se udkar jangal men us jagah pahunch jaa, jahan vah aek samay, aur samayo, aur adho samay tak palee jaae.
aur sanp ne us sree ke peechhe apane munh se nadee kee nai panee bahaya, ki use is nadee se baha de.
parantu prathvee ne us sree kee sahayata kee, aur apana munh kholakar us nadee ko jo ajagar ne apane munh se bahai thee, pee liya.
aur ajagar sree par krodhait hua, aur usakee shosh santan se jo parameshvar kee agyaaon ko manate, aur yeeshu kee gavahee dene par sthiar haai, ladne ko gaya. aur vah samudra ke baloo par ja khda hua..
aur maain ne aek pashu ko samudra men se nikalate huae dekha, jis ke das seeng aur sat sir the aur usake siron par ninda ke nam likhe huae the.
aur jo pashu maain ne dekha, vah cheete kee nai tha aur usake panv bhaloo ke se, aur munh sinh ka sa tha aur us ajagar ne apanee samarth, aur apana sinhasan, aur bada adhaikar, use de diya.
aur maain ne usake siron men se aek par aeesa bharee ghaav laga dekha, mano vah mane par haai fir usaka praanghaatak ghaav achchha ho gaya, aur saree prathvee ke log us pashu ke peechhe peechhe achanbha karate huae chale.
aur unhon ne ajagar kee pooja kee, kyonaki us ne pashu ko apana aadhaikar de diya tha aur yah kahakar pashu kee pooja kee, ki is pashu ke saman kaun haai?
kaun us se lad sakata haai? aur bade bol bolane aur ninda karane ke liye use aek munh diya gaya, aur use bayalees maheene tak kam karane ka aadhaikar diya gaya.
aur us ne parameshvar kee ninda karane ke liye munh khola, ki usake nam aur usake tamboo arthata svarga ke rahanevalon kee ninda kare.
aur use yah adhaikar diya gaya, ki pavitra logon se lade, aur un par jay paa, aur use har aek kul, aur log, aur bhasha, aur jati par adhaikar diya gaya.
aur prathvee ke ve sab rahanevale jin ke nam us memne kee jeevan kee pustak men likhe naheen gaa, jo jangal kee utpaati ke samay se ghaat hua haai, us pashu kee pooja karenge.
jis ke kan hon vah sune.
jis ko kaaid men padna haai, vah kaaid men padega, jo talavar se marega, avashy haai ki vah talavar se mara jaaega, pavitra logon ka dhaeeraj aur vishvas isee men haai..
fir maain ne aek aur pashu ko prathvee men se nikalate huae dekha, usake memne ke se do seeng the aur vah ajagar kee nain bolata tha.
aur yah us paahile pashu ka sara aadhaikar usake samhane kam men lata tha, aur prathvee aur usake rahanevalon se us paahile pashu kee jis ka praanghaatak ghaav achchha ho gaya tha, pooja karata tha.
aur vah bade bade chinh dikhata tha, yahan tak ki manushyon ke samhane svarga se prathvee par ag barasa deta tha.
aur un chinhon ke karan jinhen us pashu ke samhane dikhane ka adhaikar use diya gaya tha vah prathvee ke rahanevalon ko is prakar bhramata tha, ki prathvee ke rahanevalon se kahata tha, ki jis pashu ke talavar lagee thee, vah jee gaya haai, us kee moorat banao.
